480221,110,680,56,96,1,267,29,"Evaṃ catasso disā, catasso anudisā, heṭṭhā, uparīti dasa disā anuviloketvā attanā sadisaṃ kañci adisvā‘‘ ayaṃ uttarādisā’’ ti sattapadavītihārena agamāsi, mahābrahmunā setacchattaṃ dhāriyamāno, suyāmena vāḷabījaniṃ, aññāhi ca devatāhi sesarājakakudhabhaṇḍahatthāhi anugammamāno. "
