480325,110,693,61,84,1,135,17,"Deva, mama sippaṃ sikkhanakiccaṃ natthi, nagare mama sippadassanatthaṃ bheriṃ carāpetha‘‘ ito sattame divase ñātakānaṃ sippaṃ dassessāmī’’ ti. "
480326,110,693,85,88,1,16,3,Rājā tathā akāsi. 
