480351,110,696,37,79,1,286,31,"So‘‘ ko nu kho maṃ imamhā ṭhānā cāvetukāmo’’ ti upadhārento bodhisattassa alaṅkāretukāmataṃ ñatvā vissakammaṃ āmantesi‘‘ samma vissakamma, siddhatthakumāro ajja aḍḍharattasamaye mahābhinikkhamanaṃ nikkhamissati, ayamassa pacchimo alaṅkāro, uyyānaṃ gantvā mahāpurisaṃ dibbālaṅkārehi alaṅkarohī’’ ti. "
