480367,110,701,2,28,1,150,19,"Bodhisatto taṃ sutvā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ evamāha‘ evarūpaṃ attabhāvaṃ passantiyā mātu hadayaṃ nibbāyati, pitu hadayaṃ nibbāyati, pajāpatiyā hadayaṃ nibbāyatī’ ti! "
480368,110,701,29,40,1,51,9,Kismiṃ nu kho nibbute hadayaṃ nibbutaṃ nāma hotī’’ ti? 
