480371,110,701,73,107,1,243,28,"Ayaṃ me sussavanaṃ sāvesi, ahañhi nibbānaṃ gavesanto carāmi, ajjeva mayā gharāvāsaṃ chaḍḍetvā nikkhamma pabbajitvā nibbānaṃ gavesituṃ vaṭṭati, ayaṃ imissā ācariyabhāgo hotū’’ ti kaṇṭhato omuñcitvā kisāgotamiyā satasahassagghanakaṃ muttāhāraṃ pesesi. "
