480380,110,702,124,143,1,90,13,"‘‘ upaddutaṃ vata bho, upassaṭṭhaṃ vata bho’’ ti udānaṃ pavattesi, ativiya pabbajjāya cittaṃ nami. "
480381,110,703,2,26,1,107,15,So ‘‘ ajjeva mayā mahābhinikkhamanaṃ nikkhamituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti sayanā uṭṭhāya dvārasamīpaṃ gantvā‘‘ ko etthā’’ ti āha. 
480382,110,703,27,42,1,62,10,Ummāre sīsaṃ katvā nipanno channo‘‘ ahaṃ ayyaputta channo’’ ti āha.
480383,110,703,43,58,1,72,10,"‘‘ Ahaṃ ajja mahābhinikkhamanaṃ nikkhamitukāmo, ekaṃ me assaṃ kappehī’’ ti āha. "
480384,110,703,59,93,1,221,26,So‘‘ sādhu devā’’ ti assabhaṇḍikaṃ gahetvā assasālaṃ gantvā gandhatelapadīpesu jalantesu sumanapaṭṭavitānassa heṭṭhā ramaṇīye bhūmibhāge ṭhitaṃ kaṇḍakaṃ assarājānaṃ disvā‘‘ ajja mayā imameva kappetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti kaṇḍakaṃ kappesi. 
480385,110,703,94,121,1,171,20,"So kappiyamānova aññāsi‘‘ ayaṃ kappanā atigāḷhā , aññesu divasesu uyyānakīḷādigamane kappanā viya na hoti, mayhaṃ ayyaputto ajja mahābhinikkhamanaṃ nikkhamitukāmo bhavissatī’’ ti. "
480386,110,703,122,126,1,34,4,Tato tuṭṭhamānaso mahāhasitaṃ hasi. 
480387,110,703,127,142,1,103,14,"So saddo sakalanagaraṃ pattharitvā gaccheyya, devatā pana taṃ saddaṃ nirumbhitvā na kassaci sotuṃ adaṃsu. "
480388,110,704,2,22,1,149,16,Bodhisattopi kho channaṃ pesetvāva‘‘ puttaṃ tāva passissāmī’’ ti cintetvā nisinnapallaṅkato uṭṭhāya rāhulamātāya vasanaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā gabbhadvāraṃ vivari. 
480389,110,704,23,39,1,166,15,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe antogabbhe gandhatelapadīpo jhāyati, rāhulamātā sumanamallikādīnaṃ pupphānaṃ ambaṇamattena abhippakiṇṇasayane puttassa matthake hatthaṃ ṭhapetvā niddāyati. "
480390,110,704,40,74,1,221,27,"Bodhisatto ummāre pādaṃ ṭhapetvā ṭhitakova oloketvā‘‘ sacāhaṃ deviyā hatthaṃ apanetvā mama puttaṃ gaṇhissāmi, devī pabujjhissati, evaṃ me gamanantarāyo bhavissati, buddho hutvāva āgantvā puttaṃ passissāmī’’ ti pāsādatalato otari. "
480391,110,704,75,96,1,124,15,"Yaṃ pana jātakaṭṭhakathāyaṃ‘‘ tadā sattāhajāto rāhulakumāro hotī’’ ti vuttaṃ, taṃ sesaṭṭhakathāsu natthi, tasmā idameva gahetabbaṃ. "
