480400,110,705,118,130,1,118,8,"Bodhisatto thāmabalasampanno, hatthigaṇanāya koṭisahassahatthīnaṃ balaṃ dhāreti, purisagaṇanāya dasakoṭisahassapurisānaṃ . "
480401,110,705,131,159,1,199,23,"So cintesi‘‘ sace dvāraṃ na vivarīyati, ajja kaṇḍakassa piṭṭhe nisinnova vāladhiṃ gahetvā ṭhitena channena saddhiṃyeva kaṇḍakaṃ ūrūhi nippīḷetvā aṭṭhārasahatthubbedhaṃ pākāraṃ uppatitvā atikkamissāmī’’ ti. "
480402,110,705,160,186,1,187,21,"Channopi cintesi‘‘ sace dvāraṃ na vivarīyati, ahaṃ ayyaputtaṃ khandhe nisīdāpetvā kaṇḍakaṃ dakkhiṇena hatthena kucchiyaṃ parikkhipanto upakacchantare katvā pākāraṃ uppatitvā atikkamissāmī’’ ti. "
