480407,110,706,17,42,1,157,17,"‘‘ mārisa, mā nikkhama, ito te sattame divase cakkaratanaṃ pātubhavissati, dvisahassaparittadīpaparivārānaṃ catunnaṃ mahādīpānaṃ rajjaṃ kāressasi, nivatta mārisā’’ ti."
480408,110,706,43,50,1,12,3,‘‘ Kosi tvan’’ ti?
480409,110,706,51,58,1,17,3,‘‘ Ahaṃ vasavattī’’ ti.
