480510,110,726,79,111,1,184,24,"Taṃ pana pāyāsaṃ paribhuñjitvā suvaṇṇapātiṃ gahetvā‘‘ sacāhaṃ, ajja buddho bhavituṃ sakkhissāmi, ayaṃ pāti paṭisotaṃ gacchatu, no ce sakkhissāmi, anusotaṃ gacchatū’’ ti vatvā nadīsote pakkhipi. "
480511,110,726,112,146,1,288,30,Sā sotaṃ chindamānā nadīmajjhaṃ gantvā majjhamajjhaṭṭhāneneva javasampanno asso viya asītihatthamattaṭṭhānaṃ paṭisotaṃ gantvā ekasmiṃ āvaṭṭe nimujjitvā kāḷanāgarājabhavanaṃ gantvā tiṇṇaṃ buddhānaṃ paribhogapātiyo‘‘ kili kilī’’ ti ravaṃ kārayamānā paharitvāva tāsaṃ sabbaheṭṭhimā hutvā aṭṭhāsi. 
