480603,110,752,2,8,1,42,5,"Gahakāraṃ gavesanto, dukkhā jāti punappunaṃ."
480604,110,753,2,11,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Gahakāraka diṭṭhosi, puna gehaṃ na kāhasi; "
