480607,110,756,2,16,1,111,12,"Iti tusitapurato paṭṭhāya yāva ayaṃ bodhimaṇḍe sabbaññutappatti, ettakaṃ ṭhānaṃ avidūrenidānaṃ nāmāti veditabbaṃ. "
480608,110,757,2,4,1,27,2,Avidūrenidānakathā niṭṭhitā.
480609,110,758,2,4,1,18,2,3 . Santikenidānakathā
480610,110,759,2,14,1,80,9,‘ ‘ Santikenidānaṃ pana‘ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
480611,110,759,15,34,1,121,16,Vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyan’ ti evaṃ tesu tesu ṭhānesu viharato tasmiṃ tasmiṃ ṭhāneyeva labbhatī’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
480612,110,759,35,100,1,508,57,"Kiñcāpi evaṃ vuttaṃ, atha kho pana tampi ādito paṭṭhāya evaṃ veditabbaṃ– udānaṃ udānetvā jayapallaṅke nisinnassa hi bhagavato etadahosi‘‘ ahaṃ kappasatasahassādhikāni cattāri asaṅkhyeyyāni imassa pallaṅkassa kāraṇā sandhāviṃ, ettakaṃ me kālaṃ imasseva pallaṅkassa kāraṇā alaṅkatasīsaṃ gīvāya chinditvā dinnaṃ, suañjitāni akkhīni hadayamaṃsañca ubbaṭṭetvā dinnaṃ, jālīkumārasadisā puttā kaṇhājinakumārisadisā dhītaro maddīdevisadisā bhariyāyo ca paresaṃ dāsatthāya dinnā, ayaṃ me pallaṅko jayapallaṅko varapallaṅko ca. "
480613,110,759,101,120,1,137,16,"Ettha me nisinnassa saṅkappā paripuṇṇā, na tāva ito uṭṭhahissāmī’’ ti anekakoṭisatasahassā samāpattiyo samāpajjanto sattāhaṃ tattheva nisīdi. "
480614,110,759,121,145,1,93,11,Yaṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ‘‘ atha kho bhagavā sattāhaṃ ekapallaṅkena nisīdi vimuttisukhapaṭisaṃvedī’’ ti( udā.1; mahāva.1). 
480615,110,760,2,22,1,128,15,"Atha ekaccānaṃ devatānaṃ‘‘ ajjāpi nūna siddhatthassa kattabbakiccaṃ atthi, pallaṅkasmiñhi ālayaṃ na vijahatī’’ ti parivitakko udapādi. "
480616,110,760,23,34,1,111,10,Satthā devatānaṃ parivitakkaṃ ñatvā tāsaṃ vitakkavūpasamanatthaṃ vehāsaṃ abbhuggantvā yamakapāṭihāriyaṃ dassesi. 
480617,110,760,35,48,1,164,10,"Mahābodhimaṇḍasmiñhi katapāṭihāriyañca, ñātisamāgame katapāṭihāriyañca, pāthikaputtasamāgame katapāṭihāriyañca, sabbaṃ kaṇḍambarukkhamūle yamakapāṭihāriyasadisaṃ ahosi. "
480618,110,761,2,44,1,367,37,"Evaṃ satthā iminā pāṭihāriyena devatānaṃ vitakkaṃ vūpasametvā pallaṅkato īsakaṃ pācīnanissite uttaradisābhāge ṭhatvā‘‘ imasmiṃ vata me pallaṅke sabbaññutaññāṇaṃ paṭividdhan’’ ti cattāri asaṅkhyeyyāni kappasatasahassañca pūritānaṃ pāramīnaṃ phalādhigamaṭṭhānaṃ pallaṅkaṃ bodhirukkhañca animisehi akkhīhi olokayamāno sattāhaṃ vītināmesi, taṃ ṭhānaṃ animisacetiyaṃ nāma jātaṃ. "
480619,110,761,45,66,1,176,19,"Atha pallaṅkassa ca ṭhitaṭṭhānassa ca antarā caṅkamaṃ māpetvā puratthimapacchimato āyate ratanacaṅkame caṅkamanto sattāhaṃ vītināmesi, taṃ ṭhānaṃ ratanacaṅkamacetiyaṃ nāma jātaṃ. "
480620,110,762,2,23,1,203,19,"Catutthe pana sattāhe bodhito pacchimuttaradisābhāge devatā ratanagharaṃ māpayiṃsu, tattha pallaṅkena nisīditvā abhidhammapiṭakaṃ visesato cettha anantanayaṃ samantapaṭṭhānaṃ vicinanto sattāhaṃ vītināmesi. "
480621,110,762,24,46,1,134,15,"Ābhidhammikā panāhu‘‘ ratanagharaṃ nāma na sattaratanamayaṃ gehaṃ, sattannaṃ pana pakaraṇānaṃ sammasitaṭṭhānaṃ‘ ratanagharan’ ti vuccatī’’ ti. "
480622,110,762,47,56,1,74,8,"Yasmā panettha ubhopete pariyāyā yujjanti, tasmā ubhayampetaṃ gahetabbameva. "
480623,110,762,57,65,1,59,8,Tato paṭṭhāya pana taṃ ṭhānaṃ ratanagharacetiyaṃ nāma jātaṃ. 
480624,110,762,66,84,1,183,17,"Evaṃ bodhisamīpeyeva cattāri sattāhāni vītināmetvā pañcame sattāhe bodhirukkhamūlā yena ajapālanigrodho tenupasaṅkami, tatrāpi dhammaṃ vicinantoyeva vimuttisukhaṃ paṭisaṃvedento nisīdi. "
480625,110,763,2,35,1,224,28,"Tasmiṃ samaye māro devaputto‘‘ ettakaṃ kālaṃ anubandhanto otārāpekkhopi imassa na kiñci khalitaṃ addasaṃ, atikkantodāni esa mama vasan’’ ti domanassappatto mahāmagge nisīditvā soḷasa kāraṇāni cintento bhūmiyaṃ soḷasa lekhā kaḍḍhi–"
480626,110,763,36,56,1,87,15,"‘‘ ahaṃ eso viya dānapāramiṃ na pūresiṃ, tenamhi iminā sadiso na jāto’’ ti ekaṃ lekhaṃ kaḍḍhi. "
480627,110,763,57,95,1,213,24,"Tathā‘‘ ahaṃ eso viya sīlapāramiṃ, nekkhammapāramiṃ, paññāpāramiṃ, vīriyapāramiṃ, khantipāramiṃ, saccapāramiṃ, adhiṭṭhānapāramiṃ, mettāpāramiṃ, upekkhāpāramiṃ na pūresiṃ , tenamhi iminā sadiso na jāto’’ ti dasamaṃ lekhaṃ kaḍḍhi. "
480628,110,763,96,122,1,171,21,"Tathā‘‘ ahaṃ eso viya asādhāraṇassa indriyaparopariyattañāṇassa paṭivedhāya upanissayabhūtā dasa pāramiyo na pūresiṃ, tenamhi iminā sadiso na jāto’’ ti ekādasamaṃ lekhaṃ kaḍḍhi. "
480629,110,763,123,157,1,246,25,"Tathā‘‘ ahaṃ eso viya asādhāraṇassa āsayānusayañāṇassa, mahākaruṇāsamāpattiñāṇassa, yamakapāṭihīrañāṇassa, anāvaraṇañāṇassa, sabbaññutaññāṇassa paṭivedhāya upanissayabhūtā dasa pāramiyo na pūresiṃ, tenamhi iminā sadiso na jāto’’ ti soḷasamaṃ lekhaṃ kaḍḍhi. "
480630,110,763,158,166,1,60,8,Evaṃ imehi kāraṇehi mahāmagge soḷasa lekhā kaḍḍhamāno nisīdi. 
480631,110,764,2,47,1,223,32,"Tasmiṃ samaye taṇhā, arati, ragāti tisso māradhītaro‘‘ pitā no na paññāyati, kahaṃ nu kho etarahī’’ ti olokayamānā taṃ domanassappattaṃ bhūmiṃ vilekhamānaṃ nisinnaṃ disvā pitu santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ kasmā, tāta, dukkhī dummano’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
480632,110,764,48,66,1,120,15,"Ammā, ayaṃ mahāsamaṇo mayhaṃ vasaṃ atikkanto, ettakaṃ kālaṃ olokento otāramassa daṭṭhuṃ nāsakkhiṃ, tenāhaṃ dukkhī dummanoti. "
480633,110,764,67,79,1,71,10,"Yadi evaṃ mā cintayittha, mayametaṃ attano vase katvā ādāya āgamissāmāti. "
480634,110,764,80,95,1,76,12,"Na sakkā, ammā, eso kenaci vase kātuṃ, acalāya saddhāya patiṭṭhito eso purisoti."
480635,110,764,96,126,1,153,21,"‘‘ Tāta mayaṃ itthiyo nāma idāneva naṃ rāgapāsādīhi bandhitvā ānessāma, tumhe mā cintayitthā’’ ti bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ pāde te samaṇa paricāremā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
480636,110,764,127,146,1,140,16,"Bhagavā va tāsaṃ vacanaṃ manasi akāsi, na akkhīni ummīletvā olokesi, anuttare upadhisaṅkhaye vimuttamānaso vivekasukhaññeva anubhavanto nisīdi. "
480637,110,765,2,64,1,399,45,"Puna māradhītaro‘‘ uccāvacā kho purisānaṃ adhippāyā, kesañci kumārikāsu pemaṃ hoti, kesañci paṭhamavaye ṭhitāsu, kesañci majjhimavaye ṭhitāsu, yaṃnūna mayaṃ nānappakārehi rūpehi palobheyyāmā’’ ti ekamekā kumārivaṇṇādivasena sataṃ sataṃ attabhāve abhinimminitvā kumāriyo, avijātā, sakiṃvijātā, duvijātā, majjhimitthiyo, mahitthiyo ca hutvā chakkhattuṃ bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ pāde te samaṇa paricāremā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
480638,110,765,65,75,1,71,9,"Tampi bhagavā na manasākāsi, yathā taṃ anuttare upadhisaṅkhayeva vimutto. "
480639,110,765,76,103,1,141,19,"Keci panācariyā vadanti‘‘ tā mahitthibhāvena upagatā disvā bhagavā‘ evamevaṃ etā khaṇḍadantā palitakesā hontū’ ti adhiṭṭhāsī’’ ti, taṃ na gahetabbaṃ. "
480640,110,765,104,110,1,40,6,Na hi satthā evarūpaṃ adhiṭṭhānaṃ karoti. 
480641,110,765,111,146,1,186,26,"Bhagavā pana‘‘ apetha tumhe, kiṃ disvā evaṃ vāyamatha, evarūpaṃ nāma avītarāgādīnaṃ purato kātuṃ yuttaṃ, tathāgatassa pana rāgo pahīno, doso pahīno, moho pahīno’’ ti attano kilesappahānaṃ ārabbha–"
480642,110,766,2,12,1,49,8,"‘ ‘ Yassa jitaṃ nāvajīyati, jitamassa noyāti koci loke; "
