480648,110,771,2,8,1,60,6,Bhagavāpi tattha sattāhaṃ vītināmetvā mucalindamūlaṃ agamāsi. 
480649,110,771,9,33,1,283,23,"Tattha sattāhavaddalikāya uppannāya sītādipaṭibāhanatthaṃ mucalindena nāgarājena sattakkhattuṃ bhogehi parikkhitto asambādhāya gandhakuṭiyaṃ viharanto viya vimuttisukhaṃ paṭisaṃvediyamāno sattāhaṃ vītināmetvā rājāyatanaṃ upasaṅkami, tatthāpi vimuttisukhaṃ paṭisaṃvediyamānoyeva nisīdi. "
