480652,110,772,2,18,1,113,12,Athassa tasmiṃ sattasattāhamatthake ekūnapaññāsatime divase tattha nisinnassa‘‘ mukhaṃ dhovissāmī’’ ti cittaṃ udapādi. 
480653,110,772,19,32,1,98,11,"Sakko devānamindo agadaharīṭakaṃ āharitvā adāsi, satthā taṃ paribhuñji, tenassa sarīravaḷañjaṃ ahosi. "
480654,110,772,33,39,1,69,5,Athassa sakkoyeva nāgalatādantakaṭṭhañceva mukhadhovanaudakañca adāsi. 
480655,110,772,40,50,1,98,10,Satthā taṃ dantakaṭṭhaṃ khāditvā anotattadahodakena mukhaṃ dhovitvā tattheva rājāyatanamūle nisīdi. 
480656,110,773,2,42,1,320,34,"Tasmiṃ samaye tapussabhallikā nāma dve vāṇijā pañcahi sakaṭasatehi ukkalājanapadā majjhimadesaṃ gacchantā attano ñātisālohitāya devatāya sakaṭāni sannirumbhitvā satthu āhārasampādane ussāhitā manthañca madhupiṇḍikañca ādāya‘‘ paṭiggaṇhātu no, bhante, bhagavā imaṃ āhāraṃ anukampaṃ upādāyā’’ ti satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā aṭṭhaṃsu. "
480657,110,773,43,64,1,142,16,"Bhagavā pāyāsapaṭiggahaṇadivaseyeva pattassa antarahitattā‘‘ na kho tathāgatā hatthesu paṭiggaṇhanti, kimhi nu kho ahaṃ paṭiggaṇheyyan’’ ti cintesi. "
480658,110,773,65,79,1,109,13,"Athassa cittaṃ ñatvā catūhi disāhi cattāro mahārājāno indanīlamaṇimaye patte upanāmesuṃ, bhagavā te paṭikkhipi. "
