480672,110,776,62,73,1,118,10,Atha ne sabbadevamanussesu anodissakavasena pharaṇasamatthaṃ mettacittaṃ saṅkhipitvā odissakavasena mettacittena phari. 
480673,110,776,74,97,1,225,22,"Te bhagavatā mettacittena phuṭṭhā tathāgate upasaṅkamante sakāya katikāya saṇṭhātuṃ asakkontā abhivādanapaccuṭṭhānādīni sabbakiccāni akaṃsu, sammāsambuddhabhāvaṃ panassa ajānamānā kevalaṃ nāmena ca āvusovādena ca samudācaranti. "
480674,110,777,2,45,1,325,33,"Atha ne bhagavā‘‘ mā vo, bhikkhave, tathāgataṃ nāmena ca āvusovādena ca samudācaratha, arahaṃ, bhikkhave, tathāgato sammāsambuddho’’ ti attano buddhabhāvaṃ saññāpetvā paññatte varabuddhāsane nisinno uttarāsāḷhanakkhattayoge vattamāne aṭṭhārasahi brahmakoṭīhi parivuto pañcavaggiye there āmantetvā dhammacakkappavattanasuttantaṃ desesi. "
