480737,110,800,139,168,1,110,18,"Rājā‘‘ neva gato āgacchati, na sāsanaṃ suyyatī’’ ti‘‘ ehi, bhaṇe, tvaṃ gacchāhī’’ ti teneva niyāmena aññaṃ amaccaṃ pesesi. "
