480740,110,801,2,33,1,199,25,"Rājā sāsanamattampi āharitvā ācikkhantaṃ alabhitvā cintesi‘‘ ettakā janā mayi sinehābhāvena sāsanamattampi na paccāhariṃsu, ko nu kho mama vacanaṃ karissatī’’ ti sabbaṃ rājabalaṃ olokento kāḷudāyiṃ addasa. "
480741,110,801,34,47,1,122,13,So kira rañño sabbatthasādhako amacco abbhantariko ativissāsiko bodhisattena saddhiṃ ekadivase jāto sahapaṃsukīḷako sahāyo. 
