481128,110,929,2,5,1,25,3,Evan ti opammapaṭipādanaṃ. 
481129,110,929,6,26,1,99,13,"{Munī}ti monaṃ vuccati ñāṇaṃ, kāyamoneyyādīsu vā aññataraṃ, tena samannāgatattā puggalo‘‘ munī’’ ti vuccati. "
481130,110,929,27,42,1,98,9,"So panesa agāriyamuni, anagāriyamuni , sekkhamuni, asekkhamuni, paccekabuddhamuni, munimunīti anekavidho. "
481131,110,929,43,49,1,50,5,Tattha {agāriyamunī}ti gihī āgataphalo viññātasāsano. 
