481222,110,956,112,135,1,113,14,Tassāpi dārakassa panthe jātattā paṭhamajātassa‘‘ mahāpanthako’’ ti nāmaṃ katvā itarassa‘‘ cūḷapanthako’’ ti nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
481223,110,956,136,143,1,53,7,Te dvepi dārake gahetvā attano vasanaṭṭhānameva āgatā. 
481224,110,957,2,56,1,229,33,"Tesaṃ tattha vasantānaṃ ayaṃ mahāpanthakadārako aññe dārake‘‘ cūḷapitā mahāpitā’’ ti,‘‘ ayyako ayyikā’’ ti ca vadante sutvā mātaraṃ pucchi‘‘ amma, aññe dārakā‘ cūḷapitā mahāpitā’ tipi vadanti,‘ ayyako ayyikā’ tipi vadanti, amhākaṃ ñātakā natthī’’ ti."
481225,110,957,57,82,1,115,17,"‘‘ Āma, tāta, tumhākaṃ ettha ñātakā natthi, rājagahanagare pana vo dhanaseṭṭhi nāma ayyako, tattha tumhākaṃ bahū ñātakā’’ ti."
481226,110,957,83,94,1,33,6,"‘‘ Kasmā tattha na gacchatha, ammā’’ ti? "
481227,110,957,95,105,1,85,10,Sā attano agamanakāraṇaṃ puttassa akathetvā puttesu punappunaṃ kathentesu sāmikaṃ āha–
481228,110,957,106,128,1,115,16,"‘‘ ime dārakā maṃ ativiya kilamenti, kiṃ no mātāpitaro disvā maṃsaṃ khādissanti, ehi dārakānaṃ ayyakakulaṃ dassessāmā’’ ti."
481229,110,957,129,144,1,66,10,"‘‘ Ahaṃ sammukhā bhavituṃ na sakkhissāmi, taṃ pana tattha nayissāmī’’ ti."
481230,110,957,145,180,1,229,29,"‘‘ Sādhu, ayya, yena kenaci upāyena dārakānaṃ ayyakakulameva daṭṭhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti dvepi janā dārake ādāya anupubbena rājagahaṃ patvā nagaradvāre ekissā sālāya nivāsaṃ katvā dārakamātā dve dārake gahetvā āgatabhāvaṃ mātāpitūnaṃ ārocāpesi. "
481231,110,958,2,45,1,234,35,"Te taṃ sāsanaṃ sutvā‘‘ saṃsāre vicarantānaṃ na putto na dhītā nāma natthi, te amhākaṃ mahāparādhikā, na sakkā tehi amhākaṃ cakkhupathe ṭhātuṃ, ettakaṃ pana dhanaṃ gahetvā dvepi janā phāsukaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā jīvantu, dārake pana idha pesentū’’ ti. "
481232,110,958,46,60,1,117,13,"Seṭṭhidhītā mātāpitūhi pesitaṃ dhanaṃ gahetvā dārake āgatadūtānaṃyeva hatthe datvā pesesi, dārakā ayyakakule vaḍḍhanti. "
481233,110,958,61,73,1,102,11,"Tesu cūḷapanthako atidaharo, mahāpanthako pana ayyakena saddhiṃ dasabalassa dhammakathaṃ sotuṃ gacchati. "
481234,110,958,74,83,1,70,9,Tassa niccaṃ satthu sammukhā dhammaṃ suṇantassa pabbajjāya cittaṃ nami. 
481235,110,958,84,98,1,60,9,"So ayyakaṃ āha‘‘ sace tumhe sampaṭicchatha, ahaṃ pabbajeyyan’’ ti."
481236,110,958,99,125,1,139,18,"‘‘ Kiṃ vadesi, tāta, mayhaṃ sakalalokassapi pabbajjāto taveva pabbajjā bhaddikā, sace sakkosi, pabbaja tātā’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā satthu santikaṃ gato. "
481237,110,958,126,137,1,41,7,Satthā‘‘ kiṃ mahāseṭṭhi dārako te laddho’’ ti.
481238,110,958,138,157,1,78,12,"‘‘ Āma, bhante ayaṃ dārako mayhaṃ nattā, tumhākaṃ santike pabbajāmīti vadatī’’ ti āha. "
481239,110,958,158,172,1,72,9,Satthā aññataraṃ piṇḍacārikaṃ bhikkhuṃ‘‘ imaṃ dārakaṃ pabbājehī’’ ti āṇāpesi. 
481240,110,958,173,178,1,56,5,Thero tassa tacapañcakakammaṭṭhānaṃ ācikkhitvā pabbājesi. 
481241,110,958,179,186,1,66,7,So bahuṃ buddhavacanaṃ uggaṇhitvā paripuṇṇavasso upasampadaṃ labhi. 
481242,110,958,187,195,1,67,8,Upasampanno hutvā yoniso manasikāre kammaṃ karonto arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
481243,110,959,2,22,1,111,14,"So jhānasukhena, maggasukhena, phalasukhena vītināmento cintesi‘‘ sakkā nu kho imaṃ sukhaṃ cūḷapanthakassa dātun’’ ti. "
481244,110,959,23,41,1,111,13,"Tato ayyakaseṭṭhissa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ mahāseṭṭhi sace tumhe sampaṭicchatha, ahaṃ cūḷapanthakaṃ pabbājeyyan’’ ti āha."
481245,110,959,42,50,1,20,3,"‘‘ Pabbājetha, bhante’’ ti. "
