481248,110,960,2,12,1,63,8,"‘ ‘ Padumaṃ yathā kokanadaṃ sugandhaṃ, pāto siyā phullamavītagandhaṃ; "
481249,110,961,2,28,1,58,5,"Aṅgīrasaṃ passa virocamānaṃ, tapantamādiccamivantalikkhe’’ ti.( saṃ. ni.1.123; a. ni.5.195)– "
481250,110,962,2,8,1,46,6,Imaṃ ekagāthaṃ catūhi māsehi gaṇhituṃ nāsakkhi. 
481251,110,962,9,20,1,124,11,So kira kassapasammāsambuddhakāle pabbajitvā paññavā hutvā aññatarassa dandhabhikkhuno uddesaggahaṇakāle parihāsakeḷiṃ akāsi. 
481252,110,962,21,32,1,71,10,"So bhikkhu tena parihāsena lajjito neva uddesaṃ gaṇhi, na sajjhāyamakāsi. "
481253,110,962,33,46,1,98,12,"Tena kammena ayaṃ pabbajitvāva dandho jāto, gahitagahitaṃ padaṃ uparūpari padaṃ gaṇhantassa nassati. "
481254,110,962,47,55,1,64,8,Tassa imameva gāthaṃ gahetuṃ vāyamantassa cattāro māsā atikkantā. 
481255,110,963,2,37,1,199,27,"Atha naṃ mahāpanthako āha‘‘ cūḷapanthaka, tvaṃ imasmiṃ sāsane abhabbo, catūhi māsehi ekampi gāthaṃ gahetuṃ na sakkosi, pabbajitakiccaṃ pana tvaṃ kathaṃ matthakaṃ pāpessasi, nikkhama ito’’ ti vihārā nikkaḍḍhi. "
481256,110,963,38,44,1,57,6,Cūḷapanthako buddhasāsane sinehena gihibhāvaṃ na pattheti. 
