481278,110,971,2,25,1,70,9,"Etaṃ rajaṃ vippajahitva bhikkhavo, viharanti te vigatarajassa sāsane’’ ti.( mahāni.209; cūḷani. udayamāṇavapucchāniddesa74); "
481279,110,972,2,13,1,110,10,"Gāthāpariyosāne cūḷapanthako saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ pāpuṇi, paṭisambhidāhiyevassa tīṇi piṭakāni āgamaṃsu. "
481280,110,972,14,33,1,137,18,"So kira pubbe rājā hutvā nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karonto nalāṭato sede muccante parisuddhena sāṭakena nalāṭantaṃ puñchi, sāṭako kiliṭṭho ahosi. "
481281,110,972,34,57,1,126,17,"So‘‘ imaṃ sarīraṃ nissāya evarūpo parisuddho sāṭako pakatiṃ jahitvā kiliṭṭho jāto, aniccā vata saṅkhārā’’ ti aniccasaññaṃ paṭilabhi. "
481282,110,972,58,63,1,44,5,Tena kāraṇenassa rajoharaṇameva paccayo jāto. 
481283,110,973,2,8,1,61,6,Jīvakopi kho komārabhacco dasabalassa dakkhiṇodakaṃ upanāmesi. 
481284,110,973,9,25,1,65,10,"Satthā‘‘ nanu, jīvaka, vihāre bhikkhū atthī’’ ti hatthena pattaṃ pidahi. "
481285,110,973,26,38,1,48,7,"Mahāpanthako‘‘ bhante, vihāre natthi bhikkhū’’ ti āha. "
