481302,110,976,115,118,1,18,3,Jīvako tathā akāsi. 
481303,110,976,119,129,1,83,10,Thero sīhanādaṃ nadanto taruṇasīho viya tīṇi piṭakāni saṃkhobhetvā anumodanaṃ akāsi. 
481304,110,977,2,27,1,280,25,Satthā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhikkhusaṅghaparivāro vihāraṃ gantvā bhikkhūhi vatte dassite uṭṭhāyāsanā gandhakuṭippamukhe ṭhatvā bhikkhusaṅghassa sugatovādaṃ datvā kammaṭṭhānaṃ kathetvā bhikkhusaṅghaṃ uyyojetvā surabhigandhavāsitaṃ gandhakuṭiṃ pavisitvā dakkhiṇena passena sīhaseyyaṃ upagato. 
481305,110,977,28,91,1,463,51,"Atha sāyanhasamaye dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū ito cito ca samosaritvā rattakambalasāṇiṃ parikkhipantā viya nisīditvā satthu guṇakathaṃ ārabhiṃsu‘‘ āvuso, mahāpanthako cūḷapanthakassa ajjhāsayaṃ ajānanto‘ catūhi māsehi ekagāthaṃ gaṇhituṃ na sakkoti, dandho ayan’ ti vihārā nikkaḍḍhi, sammāsambuddho pana attano anuttaradhammarājatāya ekasmiṃyevassa antarabhatte saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ adāsi, tīṇi piṭakāni paṭisambhidāhiyeva āgatāni, aho buddhānaṃ balaṃ nāma mahantan’’ ti. "
481306,110,978,2,53,1,523,46,Atha bhagavā dhammasabhāyaṃ imaṃ kathāpavattiṃ ñatvā‘‘ ajja mayā gantuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti buddhaseyyāya uṭṭhāya surattadupaṭṭaṃ nivāsetvā vijjulataṃ viya kāyabandhanaṃ bandhitvā rattakambalasadisaṃ sugatamahācīvaraṃ pārupitvā surabhigandhakuṭito nikkhamma mattavāraṇo viya sīhavikkantavilāsena vijambhamāno sīho viya anantāya buddhalīlāya dhammasabhaṃ gantvā alaṅkatamaṇḍapamajjhe supaññattavarabuddhāsanaṃ abhiruyha chabbaṇṇabuddharasmiyo vissajjento aṇṇavakucchiṃ obhāsayamāno yugandharamatthake bālasūriyo viya āsanamajjhe nisīdi. 
481307,110,978,54,62,1,76,8,Sammāsambuddhe pana āgatamatte bhikkhusaṅgho kathaṃ pacchinditvā tuṇhī ahosi. 
481308,110,979,2,77,1,505,59,"Satthā mudukena mettacittena parisaṃ oloketvā‘‘ ayaṃ parisā ativiya sobhati, ekassapi hatthakukkuccaṃ vā pādakukkuccaṃ vā ukkāsitasaddo vā khipitasaddo vā natthi, sabbepime buddhagāravena sagāravā buddhatejena tajjitā mayi āyukappampi akathetvā nisinne paṭhamaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpetvā na kathessanti, kathāsamuṭṭhāpanavattaṃ nāma mayāva jānitabbaṃ, ahameva paṭhamaṃ kathessāmī’’ ti madhurena brahmassarena bhikkhū āmantetvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave , etarahi kathāya sannisinnā, kā ca pana vo antarākathā vippakatā’’ ti āha. "
481309,110,979,78,135,1,391,46,"Bhante, na mayaṃ imasmiṃ ṭhāne nisinnā aññaṃ tiracchānakathaṃ kathema, tumhākaṃyeva pana guṇe vaṇṇayamānā nisinnāmha‘‘ āvuso mahāpanthako cūḷapanthakassa ajjhāsayaṃ ajānanto‘ catūhi māsehi ekaṃ gāthaṃ gaṇhituṃ na sakkoti, dandho ayan’ ti vihārā nikkaḍḍhi, sammāsambuddho pana anuttaradhammarājatāya ekasmiṃyevassa antarabhatte saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ adāsi, aho buddhānaṃ balaṃ nāma mahantan’’ ti. "
481310,110,979,136,164,1,171,22,"Satthā bhikkhūnaṃ kathaṃ sutvā‘‘ bhikkhave, cūḷapanthako maṃ nissāya idāni tāva dhammesu dhammamahantataṃ patto, pubbe pana maṃ nissāya bhogesupi bhogamahantataṃ pāpuṇī’’ ti āha. "
481311,110,979,165,170,1,54,5,Bhikkhū tassatthassa āvibhāvatthaṃ bhagavantaṃ yāciṃsu. 
481312,110,979,171,177,1,55,6,Bhagavā bhavantarena paṭicchannaṃ kāraṇaṃ pākaṭaṃ akāsi. 
481313,110,980,2,24,1,185,20,"Atīte kāsiraṭṭhe bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto seṭṭhikule nibbattitvā vayappatto seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ labhitvā cūḷaseṭṭhi nāma ahosi, so paṇḍito byatto sabbanimittāni jānāti. "
481314,110,980,25,53,1,214,23,So ekadivasaṃ rājupaṭṭhānaṃ gacchanto antaravīthiyaṃ matamūsikaṃ disvā taṅkhaṇaññeva nakkhattaṃ samānetvā idamāha‘‘ sakkā cakkhumatā kulaputtena imaṃ undūraṃ gahetvā puttadārabharaṇañca kātuṃ kammante ca payojetun’’ ti? 
481315,110,980,54,85,1,223,27,Aññataro duggatakulaputto taṃ seṭṭhissa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ nāyaṃ ajānitvā kathessatī’’ ti taṃ mūsikaṃ gahetvā ekasmiṃ āpaṇe biḷālassatthāya vikkiṇitvā kākaṇikaṃ labhitvā tāya kākaṇikāya phāṇitaṃ gahetvā ekena ghaṭena pānīyaṃ gaṇhi. 
481316,110,980,86,104,1,132,17,"So araññato āgacchante mālākāre disvā thokaṃ thokaṃ phāṇitakhaṇḍaṃ datvā uḷuṅkena pānīyaṃ adāsi, te cassa ekekaṃ pupphamuṭṭhiṃ adaṃsu. "
481317,110,980,105,114,1,87,9,So tena pupphamūlena punadivasepi phāṇitañca pānīyaghaṭañca gahetvā pupphārāmameva gato. 
481318,110,980,115,123,1,66,8,Tassa taṃ divasaṃ mālākārā aḍḍhocitake pupphagacche datvā agamaṃsu. 
481319,110,980,124,132,1,50,8,So na cirasseva iminā upāyena aṭṭha kahāpaṇe labhi. 
481320,110,981,2,22,1,139,18,"Puna ekasmiṃ vātavuṭṭhidivase rājuyyāne bahū sukkhadaṇḍakā ca sākhā ca palāsañca vātena pātitaṃ hoti, uyyānapālo chaḍḍetuṃ upāyaṃ na passati . "
481321,110,981,23,54,1,136,21,"So tattha gantvā‘‘ sace imāni dārupaṇṇāni mayhaṃ dassasi, ahaṃ te imāni sabbāni nīharissāmī’’ ti uyyānapālaṃ āha, so‘‘ gaṇha ayyā’’ ti sampaṭicchi. "
481322,110,981,55,68,1,127,13,Cūḷantevāsiko dārakānaṃ kīḷanamaṇḍalaṃ gantvā phāṇitaṃ datvā muhuttena sabbāni dārupaṇṇāni nīharāpetvā uyyānadvāre rāsiṃ kāresi. 
481323,110,981,69,83,1,124,14,Tadā rājakumbhakāro rājakule bhājanānaṃ pacanatthāya dārūni pariyesamāno uyyānadvāre tāni disvā tassa hatthato kiṇitvā gaṇhi. 
481324,110,981,84,95,1,90,11,Taṃ divasaṃ cūḷantevāsiko dāruvikkayena soḷasa kahāpaṇe cāṭiādīni ca pañca bhājanāni labhi. 
481325,110,982,2,25,1,154,19,So catuvīsatiyā kahāpaṇesu jātesu‘‘ atthi ayaṃ upāyo mayhan’’ ti nagaradvārato avidūre ṭhāne ekaṃ pānīyacāṭiṃ ṭhapetvā pañcasate tiṇahārake pānīyena upaṭṭhahi. 
481326,110,982,26,42,1,56,10,"Te āhaṃsu‘‘ samma, tvaṃ amhākaṃ bahūpakāro, kiṃ te karomā’’ ti? "
481327,110,982,43,65,1,139,18,So‘‘ mayhaṃ kicce uppanne karissathā’’ ti vatvā ito cito ca vicaranto thalapathakammikena ca jalapathakammikena ca saddhiṃ mittasanthavaṃ akāsi. 
481328,110,982,66,82,1,100,12,Tassa thalapathakammiko‘‘ sve imaṃ nagaraṃ assavāṇijako pañca assasatāni gahetvā āgamissatī’’ ti ācikkhi. 
481329,110,982,83,108,1,128,20,"So tassa vacanaṃ sutvā tiṇahārake āha‘‘ ajja mayhaṃ ekekaṃ tiṇakalāpaṃ detha, mayā ca tiṇe avikkiṇite attano tiṇaṃ mā vikkiṇathā’’ ti. "
481330,110,982,109,125,1,80,10,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā pañca tiṇakalāpasatāni āharitvā tassa ghare pāpayiṃsu. 
481331,110,982,126,137,1,86,11,Assavāṇijo sakalanagare assānaṃ gocaraṃ alabhitvā tassa sahassaṃ datvā taṃ tiṇaṃ gaṇhi. 
481332,110,983,2,15,1,86,9,Tato katipāhaccayenassa jalapathakammiko sahāyako ārocesi‘‘ paṭṭanamhi mahānāvā āgatā’’ ti. 
481333,110,983,16,60,1,297,35,So‘‘ atthi ayaṃ upāyo’’ ti aṭṭhahi kahāpaṇehi sabbaparivārasampannaṃ tāvakālikaṃ rathaṃ gahetvā mahantena yasena nāvāpaṭṭanaṃ gantvā ekaṃ aṅgulimuddikaṃ nāvikassa saccakāraṃ datvā avidūre ṭhāne sāṇiyā parikkhipāpetvā nisinno purise āṇāpesi‘‘ bāhirato vāṇijesu āgatesu tatiyena paṭihārena maṃ ārocethā’’ ti .
481334,110,983,61,80,1,75,11,‘‘ Nāvā āgatā’’ ti sutvā bārāṇasito satamattā vāṇijā‘‘ bhaṇḍaṃ gaṇhāmā’’ ti āgamiṃsu. 
481335,110,983,81,91,1,76,9,"Bhaṇḍaṃ tumhe na labhissatha, asukaṭṭhāne nāma mahāvāṇijena saccakāro dinnoti. "
481336,110,983,92,98,1,33,6,Te taṃ sutvā tassa santikaṃ āgatā. 
481337,110,983,99,106,1,81,7,Pādamūlikapurisā purimasaññāvasena tatiyena paṭihārena tesaṃ āgatabhāvaṃ ārocesuṃ. 
481338,110,983,107,127,1,153,20,Te satamattā vāṇijā ekekaṃ sahassaṃ datvā tena saddhiṃ nāvāya pattikā hutvā puna ekekaṃ sahassaṃ datvā pattiṃ vissajjāpetvā bhaṇḍaṃ attano santakamakaṃsu. 
481339,110,984,2,23,1,146,17,Cūḷantevāsiko dve satasahassāni gaṇhitvā bārāṇasiṃ āgantvā‘‘ kataññunā me bhavituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti ekaṃ satasahassaṃ gāhāpetvā cūḷaseṭṭhissa samīpaṃ gato. 
481340,110,984,24,42,1,63,12,"Atha naṃ seṭṭhi‘‘ kiṃ te, tāta, katvā idaṃ dhanaṃ laddhan’’ ti pucchi. "
481341,110,984,43,60,1,109,13,So‘‘ tumhehi kathitaupāye ṭhatvā catumāsambhantareyeva laddhan’’ ti matamūsikaṃ ādiṃ katvā sabbaṃ vatthuṃ kathesi. 
481342,110,984,61,84,1,149,19,Cūḷaseṭṭhi tassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ idāni evarūpaṃ dārakaṃ mama santakaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti vayappattaṃ attano dhītaraṃ datvā sakalakuṭumbassa sāmikaṃ akāsi. 
481343,110,984,85,92,1,54,7,So seṭṭhino accayena tasmiṃ nagare seṭṭhiṭṭhānaṃ labhi. 
481344,110,984,93,96,1,32,3,Bodhisattopi yathākammaṃ agamāsi. 
481345,110,985,2,10,1,80,8,Sammāsambuddhopi imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ kathetvā abhisambuddhova imaṃ gāthaṃ kathesi– 
481346,110,986,2,4,1,0,0,4.
481347,110,987,2,9,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Appakenapi medhāvī, pābhatena vicakkhaṇo; "
481348,110,988,2,11,1,46,6,"Samuṭṭhāpeti attānaṃ, aṇuṃ aggiṃva sandhaman’’ ti. "
481349,110,989,2,8,1,43,4,Tattha {appakenapī}ti thokenapi parittakenapi. 
481350,110,989,9,12,1,17,2,{Medhāvī}ti paññavā. 
481351,110,989,13,16,1,24,2,{Pābhatenā}ti bhaṇḍamūlena. 
481352,110,989,17,20,1,25,2,{Vicakkhaṇo}ti vohārakusalo. 
481353,110,989,21,32,1,98,11,Samuṭṭhāpeti attānan ti mahantaṃ dhanañca yasañca uppādetvā tattha attānaṃ saṇṭhāpeti patiṭṭhāpeti. 
481354,110,989,33,35,1,9,2,Yathā kiṃ? 
481355,110,989,36,87,1,399,44,"Aṇuṃ aggiṃva sandhamaṃ, yathā paṇḍitapuriso parittaṃ aggiṃ anukkamena gomayacuṇṇādīni pakkhipitvā mukhavātena dhamanto samuṭṭhāpeti vaḍḍheti mahantaṃ aggikkhandhaṃ karoti, evameva paṇḍito thokampi pābhataṃ labhitvā nānāupāyehi payojetvā dhanañca yasañca vaḍḍheti , vaḍḍhetvā ca pana tattha attānaṃ patiṭṭhāpeti, tāya eva vā pana dhanayasamahantatāya attānaṃ samuṭṭhāpeti, abhiññātaṃ pākaṭaṃ karotīti attho. "
481356,110,990,2,51,1,319,38,"Iti bhagavā‘‘ bhikkhave, cūḷapanthako maṃ nissāya idāni dhammesu dhammamahantataṃ patto, pubbe pana bhogesupi bhogamahantataṃ pāpuṇī’’ ti evaṃ imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ dassetvā dve vatthūni kathetvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ tadā cūḷantevāsiko cūḷapanthako ahosi, cūḷakaseṭṭhi pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti desanaṃ niṭṭhāpesi. "
481357,110,991,2,4,1,32,2,Cūḷaseṭṭhijātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
481358,110,993,2,4,1,24,2,5 . Taṇḍulanāḷijātakavaṇṇanā 
481359,110,994,2,12,1,89,9,Kimagghati {taṇḍulanāḷikā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto lāludāyittheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
481360,110,994,13,21,1,66,8,Tasmiṃ samaye āyasmā dabbo mallaputto saṅghassa bhattuddesako hoti. 
481361,110,994,22,33,1,106,10,"Tasmiṃ pātova salākabhattāni uddisamāne lāludāyittherassa kadāci varabhattaṃ pāpuṇāti, kadāci lāmakabhattaṃ. "
481362,110,994,34,56,1,113,16,"So lāmakabhattassa pattadivase salākaggaṃ ākulaṃ karoti,‘‘ kiṃ dabbova salākaṃ dātuṃ jānāti, amhe na jānāmā’’ ti vadati. "
481363,110,994,57,73,1,88,12,Tasmiṃ salākaggaṃ ākulaṃ karonte‘‘ handa dāni tvameva salākaṃ dehī’’ ti salākapacchiṃ adaṃsu. 
481364,110,994,74,80,1,40,6,Tato paṭṭhāya so saṅghassa salākaṃ adāsi. 
481365,110,994,81,130,1,191,27,"Dento ca pana‘‘ idaṃ varabhattan’’ ti vā‘‘ lāmakabhattan’’ ti vā‘‘ asukavassagge varabhattan’’ ti vā‘‘ asukavassagge lāmakabhattan’’ ti vā na jānāti, ṭhitikaṃ karontopi‘‘ asukavassagge ṭhitikā’’ ti na sallakkheti. "
481366,110,994,131,153,1,118,17,"Bhikkhūnaṃ ṭhitavelāya‘‘ imasmiṃ ṭhāne ayaṃ ṭhitikā ṭhitā, imasmiṃ ṭhāne ayan’’ ti bhūmiyaṃ vā bhittiyaṃ vā lekhaṃ kaḍḍhati. "
481367,110,994,154,171,1,111,15,"Punadivase salākagge bhikkhū mandatarā vā honti bahutarā vā, tesu mandataresu lekhā heṭṭhā hoti, bahutaresu upari. "
481368,110,994,172,178,1,46,6,So ṭhitikaṃ ajānanto lekhāsaññāya salākaṃ deti. 
481369,110,995,2,30,1,139,20,"Atha naṃ bhikkhū‘‘ āvuso, udāyi, lekhā nāma heṭṭhā vā hoti upari vā, varabhattaṃ pana asukavassagge ṭhitaṃ, lāmakabhattaṃ asukavassagge’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
481370,110,995,31,57,1,125,19,"So bhikkhū paṭippharanto‘‘ yadi evaṃ ayaṃ lekhā kasmā evaṃ ṭhitā, kiṃ ahaṃ tumhākaṃ saddahāmi, imissā lekhāya saddahāmī’’ ti vadati. "
481371,110,995,58,88,1,157,23,"Atha naṃ daharā ca sāmaṇerā ca‘‘ āvuso lāludāyi tayi salākaṃ dente bhikkhū lābhena parihāyanti, na tvaṃ dātuṃ anucchaviko, gaccha ito’’ ti salākaggato nikkaḍḍhiṃsu. "
481372,110,995,89,95,1,47,6,Tasmiṃ khaṇe salākagge mahantaṃ kolāhalaṃ ahosi. 
481373,110,995,96,115,1,93,13,"Taṃ sutvā satthā ānandattheraṃ pucchi‘‘ ānanda, salākagge mahantaṃ kolāhalaṃ, kiṃ saddo nāmeso’’ ti. "
481374,110,995,116,120,1,36,4,Thero tathāgatassa tamatthaṃ ārocesi.
481375,110,995,121,140,1,93,13,"‘‘ Ānanda, na idāneva lāludāyi attano bālatāya paresaṃ lābhahāniṃ karoti, pubbepi akāsiyevā’’ ti āha. "
481376,110,995,141,146,1,49,5,Thero tassatthassa āvibhāvatthaṃ bhagavantaṃ yāci. 
481377,110,995,147,153,1,55,6,Bhagavā bhavantarena paṭicchannaṃ kāraṇaṃ pākaṭaṃ akāsi. 
481378,110,996,2,8,1,51,6,Atīte kāsiraṭṭhe bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatto rājā ahosi. 
481379,110,996,9,15,1,47,6,Tadā amhākaṃ bodhisatto tassa agghāpaniko ahosi. 
481380,110,996,16,27,1,105,10,"Hatthiassādīni ceva maṇisuvaṇṇādīni ca agghāpesi, agghāpetvā bhaṇḍasāmikānaṃ bhaṇḍānurūpameva mūlaṃ dāpesi. "
481381,110,996,28,57,1,170,23,"Rājā pana luddho hoti, so lobhapakatitāya evaṃ cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ agghāpaniko evaṃ agghāpento na cirasseva mama gehe dhanaṃ parikkhayaṃ gamessati, aññaṃ agghāpanikaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
481382,110,996,58,94,1,229,26,"So sīhapañjaraṃ ugghāṭetvā rājaṅgaṇaṃ olokento ekaṃ gāmikamanussaṃ lolabālaṃ rājaṅgaṇena gacchantaṃ disvā‘‘ esa mayhaṃ agghāpanikakammaṃ kātuṃ sakkhissatī’’ ti taṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ sakkhissasi, bhaṇe, amhākaṃ agghāpanikakammaṃ kātun’’ ti āha. "
481383,110,996,95,98,1,18,2,"Sakkhissāmi, devāti. "
481384,110,996,99,106,1,66,7,Rājā attano dhanarakkhaṇatthāya taṃ bālaṃ agghāpanikakamme ṭhapesi. 
481385,110,996,107,118,1,82,10,Tato paṭṭhāya so bālo hatthiassādīni agghāpento agghaṃ hāpetvā yathāruciyā katheti. 
481386,110,996,119,129,1,58,9,"Tassa ṭhānantare ṭhitattā yaṃ so katheti, tameva mūlaṃ hoti. "
481387,110,997,2,10,1,63,8,Tasmiṃ kāle uttarāpathato eko assavāṇijo pañca assasatāni ānesi. 
481388,110,997,11,17,1,44,6,Rājā taṃ purisaṃ pakkosāpetvā asse agghāpesi. 
481389,110,997,18,24,1,56,6,So pañcannaṃ assasatānaṃ ekaṃ taṇḍulanāḷikaṃ agghamakāsi. 
481390,110,997,25,42,1,90,12,Katvā ca pana‘‘ assavāṇijassa ekaṃ taṇḍulanāḷikaṃ dethā’’ ti vatvā asse assasālāyaṃ saṇṭhāpesi. 
481391,110,997,43,59,1,99,12,Assavāṇijo porāṇaagghāpanikassa santikaṃ gantvā taṃ pavattiṃ ārocetvā‘‘ idāni kiṃ kattabban’’ ti pucchi. 
481392,110,997,60,116,1,334,45,"So āha‘‘ tassa purisassa lañjaṃ datvā evaṃ pucchatha‘ amhākaṃ tāva assā ekaṃ taṇḍulanāḷikaṃ agghantīti ñātametaṃ, tumhe pana nissāya taṇḍulanāḷiyā agghaṃ jānitukāmamhā, sakkhissatha no rañño santike ṭhatvā sā taṇḍulanāḷikā idaṃ nāma agghatīti vattun’ ti, sace sakkomīti vadati, taṃ gahetvā rañño santikaṃ gacchatha, ahampi tattha āgamissāmī’’ ti. "
481393,110,998,2,18,1,102,11,Assavāṇijo ‘‘ sādhū’’ ti bodhisattassa vacanaṃ sampaṭicchitvā agghāpanikassa lañjaṃ datvā tamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
481394,110,998,19,30,1,59,7,So lañjaṃ labhitvāva‘‘ sakkhissāmi taṇḍulanāḷiṃ agghāpetun’’ ti.
481395,110,998,31,45,1,62,10,‘‘ Tena hi gacchāma rājakulan’’ ti taṃ ādāya rañño santikaṃ agamāsi. 
481396,110,998,46,51,1,40,5,Bodhisattopi aññepi bahū amaccā agamiṃsu. 
481397,110,998,52,56,1,31,4,Assavāṇijo rājānaṃ vanditvā āha–
481398,110,998,57,79,1,132,16,"‘‘ deva, pañcannaṃ assasatānaṃ ekaṃ taṇḍulanāḷiṃ agghanakabhāvaṃ jānāma, sā pana taṇḍulanāḷi kiṃ agghatīti agghāpanikaṃ pucchatha devā’’ ti. "
481399,110,998,80,97,1,84,12,"Rājā taṃ pavattiṃ ajānanto‘‘ ambho agghāpanika, pañca assasatāni kiṃ agghantī’’ ti pucchi. "
481400,110,998,98,101,1,19,2,"Taṇḍulanāḷiṃ, devāti."
481401,110,998,102,112,1,42,6,"‘‘ Hotu, bhaṇe, assā tāva taṇḍulanāḷiṃ agghantu. "
481402,110,998,113,122,1,43,7,Sā pana kiṃ agghati taṇḍulanāḷikā’’ ti pucchi. 
481403,110,998,123,135,1,67,8,So bālapuriso‘‘ bārāṇasiṃ santarabāhiraṃ agghati taṇḍulanāḷikā’’ ti āha. 
481404,110,998,136,145,1,71,9,So kira pubbe rājānaṃ anuvattanto ekaṃ taṇḍulanāḷiṃ assānaṃ agghamakāsi. 
481405,110,998,146,156,1,98,10,Puna vāṇijassa hatthato lañjaṃ labhitvā tassā taṇḍulanāḷikāya bārāṇasiṃ santarabāhiraṃ agghamakāsi. 
