481704,110,1082,2,18,1,131,14,Yañca aññe na {rakkhantī}ti idaṃ satthā anupiyanagaraṃ nissāya anupiyaambavane viharanto sukhavihāriṃ bhaddiyattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
481705,110,1082,19,24,1,69,5,Sukhavihārī bhaddiyatthero chakhattiyasamāgame upālisattamo pabbajito. 
481706,110,1082,25,50,1,168,19,"Tesu bhaddiyatthero ca, kimilatthero ca, bhagutthero ca, upālitthero ca arahattaṃ pattā, ānandatthero sotāpanno jāto, anuruddhatthero dibbacakkhuko, devadatto jhānalābhī jāto. "
481707,110,1082,51,59,1,81,8,Channaṃ pana khattiyānaṃ vatthu yāva anupiyanagarā khaṇḍahālajātake āvibhavissati. 
481708,110,1082,60,98,1,310,32,"Āyasmā pana bhaddiyo rājakāle attano rakkhasaṃvidhānañceva tāva bahūhi rakkhāhi rakkhiyamānassa uparipāsādavaratale mahāsayane samparivattamānassāpi attano bhayuppattiñca idāni arahattaṃ patvā araññādīsu yattha katthaci viharantopi attano vigatabhayatañca samanussaranto‘‘ aho sukhaṃ, aho sukhan’’ ti udānaṃ udānesi. "
481709,110,1082,99,113,1,71,10,Taṃ sutvā bhikkhū‘‘ āyasmā bhaddiyo aññaṃ byākarotī’’ ti bhagavato ārocesuṃ. 
