481783,110,1108,2,11,1,44,6,"Atha passasimaṃ kāḷaṃ, suvihīnaṃva ñātibhī’’ ti. "
481784,110,1109,2,9,1,63,6,Tattha sīlavatan ti sukhasīlatāya sīlavantānaṃ ācārasampannānaṃ. 
481785,110,1109,10,13,1,14,2,{Attho}ti vuḍḍhi. 
481786,110,1109,14,26,1,128,11,"Paṭisanthāravuttinan ti dhammapaṭisanthāro ca āmisapaṭisanthāro ca etesaṃ vuttīti paṭisanthāravuttino, tesaṃ paṭisanthāravuttinaṃ. "
