481789,110,1109,52,66,1,80,10,Idāni taṃ vuḍḍhiṃ dassetuṃ puttamātaraṃ ālapanto viya‘‘ lakkhaṇaṃ passā’’ tiādimāha. 
481790,110,1109,67,81,1,139,12,Tatrāyaṃ saṅkhepattho– ācārapaṭisanthārasampannaṃ attano puttaṃ ekamigampi avināsetvā ñātisaṅghena purakkhataṃ parivāritaṃ āgacchantaṃ passa. 
481791,110,1109,82,97,1,146,15,Tāya pana ācārapaṭisanthārasampadāya vihīnaṃ dandhapaññaṃ atha passasimaṃ kāḷaṃ ekampi ñātiṃ anavasesetvā suvihīnameva ñātīhi ekakaṃ āgacchantanti. 
