481798,110,1114,2,13,1,100,10,Nigrodhameva {seveyyā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kumārakassapattherassa mātaraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
481799,110,1114,14,32,1,172,17,"Sā kira rājagahanagare mahāvibhavassa seṭṭhino dhītā ahosi ussannakusalamūlā parimadditasaṅkhārā pacchimabhavikā, antoghaṭe padīpo viya tassā hadaye arahattūpanissayo jalati. "
481800,110,1114,33,43,1,83,10,Sā attānaṃ jānanakālato paṭṭhāya gehe anabhiratā pabbajitukāmā hutvā mātāpitaro āha–
481801,110,1114,44,63,1,104,12,"‘‘ ammatātā, mayhaṃ gharāvāse cittaṃ nābhiramati, ahaṃ niyyānike buddhasāsane pabbajitukāmā, pabbājetha man’’ ti. "
481802,110,1114,64,81,1,91,13,"Amma, kiṃ vadesi, idaṃ kulaṃ bahuvibhavaṃ, tvañca amhākaṃ ekadhītā, na labbhā tayā pabbajitunti. "
481803,110,1114,82,103,1,126,15,"Sā punappunaṃ yācitvāpi mātāpitūnaṃ santikā pabbajjaṃ alabhamānā cintesi‘‘ hotu, patikulaṃ gatā sāmikaṃ ārādhetvā pabbajissāmī’’ ti. "
481804,110,1114,104,114,1,87,10,Sā vayappattā patikulaṃ gantvā patidevatā hutvā sīlavatī kalyāṇadhammā agāraṃ ajjhāvasi. 
481805,110,1115,2,7,1,50,5,Athassā saṃvāsamanvāya kucchiyaṃ gabbho patiṭṭhahi. 
481806,110,1115,8,13,1,39,5,Sā gabbhassa patiṭṭhitabhāvaṃ na aññāsi. 
481807,110,1115,14,30,1,128,13,"Atha tasmiṃ nagare nakkhattaṃ ghosayiṃsu, sakalanagaravāsino nakkhattaṃ kīḷiṃsu, nagaraṃ devanagaraṃ viya alaṅkatapaṭiyattaṃ ahosi. "
481808,110,1115,31,45,1,114,13,"Sā pana tāva uḷārāyapi nakkhattakīḷāya vattamānāya attano sarīraṃ na vilimpati nālaṅkaroti, pakativeseneva vicarati. "
