481850,110,1139,111,142,1,278,26,"Punadivase rājānaṃ pasenadikosalaṃ mahāanāthapiṇḍikaṃ cūḷaanāthapiṇḍikaṃ visākhaṃ mahāupāsikaṃ aññāni ca abhiññātāni mahākulāni pakkosāpetvā sāyanhasamaye catūsu parisāsu sannipatitāsu upālittheraṃ āmantesi‘‘ gaccha, tvaṃ catuparisamajjhe imissā daharabhikkhuniyā kammaṃ sodhehī’’ ti."
481851,110,1139,143,191,1,280,36,"‘‘ Sādhu, bhante’’ ti thero parisamajjhaṃ gantvā attano paññattāsane nisīditvā rañño purato visākhaṃ upāsikaṃ pakkosāpetvā imaṃ adhikaraṇaṃ paṭicchāpesi‘‘ gaccha visākhe,‘ ayaṃ daharā asukamāse asukadivase pabbajitā’ ti tathato ñatvā imassa gabbhassa pure vā pacchā vā laddhabhāvaṃ jānāhī’’ ti. "
481852,110,1139,192,218,1,238,22,Upāsikā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā sāṇiṃ parikkhipāpetvā antosāṇiyaṃ daharabhikkhuniyā hatthapādanābhiudarapariyosānādīni oloketvā māsadivase samānetvā gihibhāve gabbhassa laddhabhāvaṃ tathato ñatvā therassa santikaṃ gantvā tamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
481853,110,1139,219,225,1,51,6,Thero catuparisamajjhe taṃ bhikkhuniṃ suddhaṃ akāsi. 
481854,110,1139,226,236,1,91,10,Sā suddhā hutvā bhikkhusaṅghañca satthārañca vanditvā bhikkhunīhi saddhiṃ upassayameva gatā. 
481855,110,1139,237,244,1,89,7,Sā gabbhaparipākamanvāya padumuttarapādamūle patthitapatthanaṃ mahānubhāvaṃ puttaṃ vijāyi. 
481856,110,1140,2,11,1,86,8,Athekadivasaṃ rājā bhikkhunupassayasamīpena gacchanto dārakasaddaṃ sutvā amacce pucchi. 
481857,110,1140,12,30,1,83,12,"Amaccā taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā‘‘ deva, daharabhikkhunī puttaṃ vijātā, tasseso saddo’’ ti āhaṃsu."
481858,110,1140,31,54,1,147,16,"‘‘ Bhikkhunīnaṃ, bhaṇe, dārakapaṭijagganaṃ nāma palibodho, mayaṃ naṃ paṭijaggissāmā’’ ti rājā taṃ dārakaṃ nāṭakitthīnaṃ dāpetvā kumāraparihārena vaḍḍhāpesi. "
481859,110,1140,55,65,1,47,6,Nāmaggahaṇadivase cassa‘‘ kassapo’’ ti nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
481860,110,1140,66,77,1,65,7,Atha naṃ kumāraparihārena vaḍḍhitattā‘‘ kumārakassapo’’ ti sañjāniṃsu. 
481861,110,1140,78,92,1,139,14,So sattavassikakāle satthu santike pabbajitvā paripuṇṇavasso upasampadaṃ labhitvā gacchante gacchante kāle dhammakathikesu citrakathī ahosi. 
481862,110,1140,93,124,1,119,14,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ cittakathikānaṃ yadidaṃ kumārakassapo’’ ti( a. ni.1.209,217) etadagge ṭhapesi. "
481863,110,1140,125,140,1,39,5,So pacchā vammikasutte( ma. ni.1.249 ādayo) arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
481864,110,1140,141,147,1,57,6,Mātāpissa bhikkhunī vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā aggaphalaṃ pattā. 
481865,110,1140,148,156,1,73,7,Kumārakassapatthero buddhasāsane gaganamajjhe puṇṇacando viya pākaṭo jāto. 
481866,110,1141,2,12,1,100,9,Athekadivasaṃ tathāgato pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto bhikkhūnaṃ ovādaṃ datvā gandhakuṭiṃ pāvisi. 
481867,110,1141,13,58,1,386,39,"Bhikkhū ovādaṃ gahetvā attano attano rattiṭṭhānadivāṭṭhānesu divasabhāgaṃ khepetvā sāyanhasamaye dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitvā‘‘ āvuso, devadattena attano abuddhabhāvena ceva khantimettādīnañca abhāvena kumārakassapatthero ca therī ca ubho nāsitā, sammāsambuddho pana attano dhammarājatāya ceva khantimettānuddayasampattiyā ca ubhinnampi tesaṃ paccayo jāto’’ ti buddhaguṇe vaṇṇayamānā nisīdiṃsu. "
481868,110,1141,59,79,1,122,14,"Satthā buddhalīlāya dhammasabhaṃ āgantvā paññattāsane nisīditvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchi."
481869,110,1141,80,91,1,51,6,"‘‘ Bhante, tumhākameva guṇakathāyā’’ ti sabbaṃ ārocayiṃsu. "
481870,110,1141,92,108,1,94,13,"Na, bhikkhave, tathāgato idāneva imesaṃ ubhinnaṃ paccayo ca patiṭṭhā ca jāto, pubbepi ahosiyevāti. "
481871,110,1141,109,113,1,53,4,Bhikkhū tassatthassāvibhāvatthāya bhagavantaṃ yāciṃsu. 
481872,110,1141,114,120,1,55,6,Bhagavā bhavantarena paṭicchannaṃ kāraṇaṃ pākaṭaṃ akāsi. 
481873,110,1142,2,11,1,88,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārayamāne bodhisatto migayoniyaṃ paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
481874,110,1142,12,43,1,264,25,"So mātukucchito nikkhanto suvaṇṇavaṇṇo ahosi, akkhīni panassa maṇiguḷasadisāni ahesuṃ, siṅgāni rajatavaṇṇāni, mukhaṃ rattakambalapuñjavaṇṇaṃ, hatthapādapariyantā lākhārasaparikammakatā viya, vāladhi camarassa viya ahosi, sarīraṃ panassa mahantaṃ assapotakappamāṇaṃ ahosi. "
481875,110,1142,44,53,1,74,8,So pañcasatamigaparivāro araññe vāsaṃ kappesi nāmena nigrodhamigarājā nāma. 
481876,110,1142,54,65,1,92,10,"Avidūre panassa aññopi pañcasatamigaparivāro sākhamigo nāma vasati, sopi suvaṇṇavaṇṇova ahosi. "
481877,110,1143,2,22,1,164,18,"Tena samayena bārāṇasirājā migavadhappasuto hoti, vinā maṃsena na bhuñjati, manussānaṃ kammacchedaṃ katvā sabbe negamajānapade sannipātetvā devasikaṃ migavaṃ gacchati. "
481878,110,1143,23,25,1,16,2,Manussā cintesuṃ–
481879,110,1143,26,54,1,168,22,"‘‘ ayaṃ rājā amhākaṃ kammacchedaṃ karoti, yaṃnūna mayaṃ uyyāne migānaṃ nivāpaṃ vapitvā pānīyaṃ sampādetvā bahū mige uyyānaṃ pavesetvā dvāraṃ bandhitvā rañño niyyādeyyāmā’’ ti. "
481880,110,1143,55,91,1,298,31,Te sabbe uyyāne migānaṃ nivāpatiṇāni ropetvā udakaṃ sampādetvā dvāraṃ yojetvā vāgurāni ādāya muggarādinānāvudhahatthā araññaṃ pavisitvā mige pariyesamānā‘‘ majjhe ṭhite mige gaṇhissāmā’’ ti yojanamattaṃ ṭhānaṃ parikkhipitvā saṅkhipamānā nigrodhamigasākhamigānaṃ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ majjhe katvā parikkhipiṃsu. 
481881,110,1143,92,147,1,410,48,"Atha naṃ migagaṇaṃ disvā rukkhagumbādayo ca bhūmiñca muggarehi paharantā migagaṇaṃ gahanaṭṭhānato nīharitvā asisattidhanuādīni āvudhāni uggiritvā mahānādaṃ nadantā taṃ migagaṇaṃ uyyānaṃ pavesetvā dvāraṃ pidhāya rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ deva, nibaddhaṃ migavaṃ gacchantā amhākaṃ kammaṃ nāsetha, amhehi araññato mige ānetvā tumhākaṃ uyyānaṃ pūritaṃ, ito paṭṭhāya tesaṃ maṃsāni khādathā’’ ti rājānaṃ āpucchitvā pakkamiṃsu. "
481882,110,1144,2,16,1,95,14,Rājā tesaṃ vacanaṃ sutvā uyyānaṃ gantvā mige olokento dve suvaṇṇamige disvā tesaṃ abhayaṃ adāsi. 
481883,110,1144,17,33,1,113,15,"Tato paṭṭhāya pana kadāci sayaṃ gantvā ekaṃ migaṃ vijjhitvā āneti, kadācissa bhattakārako gantvā vijjhitvā āharati. "
481884,110,1144,34,52,1,123,15,"Migā dhanuṃ disvāva maraṇabhayena tajjitā palāyanti, dve tayo pahāre labhitvā kilamantipi, gilānāpi honti, maraṇampi pāpuṇanti. "
481885,110,1144,53,58,1,43,5,Migagaṇo taṃ pavattiṃ bodhisattassa ārocesi. 
481886,110,1144,59,63,1,26,4,So sākhaṃ pakkosāpetvā āha–
481887,110,1144,64,86,1,125,17,"‘‘ samma, bahū migā nassanti, ekaṃsena maritabbe sati ito paṭṭhāya mā kaṇḍena mige vijjhantu, dhammagaṇḍikaṭṭhāne migānaṃ vāro hotu. "
481888,110,1144,87,114,1,169,22,"Ekadivasaṃ mama parisāya vāro pāpuṇātu, ekadivasaṃ tava parisāya, vārappatto migo gantvā dhammagaṇḍikāya gīvaṃ ṭhapetvā nipajjatu, evaṃ sante migā kilantā na bhavissantī’’ ti. "
481889,110,1144,115,123,1,23,4,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
481890,110,1144,124,141,1,138,15,"Tato paṭṭhāya vārappattova migo gantvā dhammagaṇḍikāya gīvaṃ ṭhapetvā nipajjati, bhattakārako āgantvā tattha nipannakameva gahetvā gacchati. "
481891,110,1145,2,10,1,69,7,Athekadivasaṃ sākhamigassa parisāya ekissā gabbhinimigiyā vāro pāpuṇi. 
481892,110,1145,11,35,1,115,17,"Sā sākhaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ sāmi, ahaṃ gabbhinī, puttaṃ vijāyitvā dve janā vāraṃ gamissāma, mayhaṃ vāraṃ atikkāmehī’’ ti āha. "
481893,110,1145,36,56,1,85,14,"So‘‘ na sakkā tava vāraṃ aññesaṃ pāpetuṃ, tvameva tuyhaṃ vāraṃ jānissasi, gacchāhī’’ ti āha. "
481894,110,1145,57,66,1,81,9,Sā tassa santikā anuggahaṃ alabhamānā bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā tamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
481895,110,1145,67,91,1,119,18,"So tassā vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ hotu gaccha tvaṃ, ahaṃ te vāraṃ atikkāmessāmī’’ ti sayaṃ gantvā dhammagaṇḍikāya sīsaṃ katvā nipajji. "
481896,110,1145,92,113,1,117,16,"Bhattakārako taṃ disvā‘‘ laddhābhayo migarājā dhammagaṇḍikāya nipanno, kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti vegena gantvā rañño ārocesi. "
481897,110,1146,2,30,1,152,22,"Rājā tāvadeva rathaṃ āruyha mahantena parivārena āgantvā bodhisattaṃ disvā āha‘‘ samma migarāja, nanu mayā tuyhaṃ abhayaṃ dinnaṃ, kasmā tvaṃ idha nipanno’’ ti. "
481898,110,1146,31,76,1,248,36,"Mahārāja, gabbhinī migī āgantvā‘‘ mama vāraṃ aññassa pāpehī’’ ti āha, na sakkā kho pana mayā ekassa maraṇadukkhaṃ aññassa upari nikkhipituṃ, svāhaṃ attano jīvitaṃ tassā datvā tassā santakaṃ maraṇaṃ gahetvā idha nipanno, mā aññaṃ kiñci āsaṅkittha, mahārājāti. "
481899,110,1146,77,79,1,8,2,Rājā āha–
481900,110,1146,80,107,1,153,18,"‘‘ sāmi, suvaṇṇavaṇṇamigarāja, mayā na tādiso khantimettānuddayasampanno manussesupi diṭṭhapubbo, tena te pasannosmi, uṭṭhehi, tuyhañca tassā ca abhayaṃ dammī’’ ti."
481901,110,1146,108,121,1,53,8,"‘‘ Dvīhi abhaye laddhe avasesā kiṃ karissanti, narindā’’ ti?"
481902,110,1146,122,132,1,34,5,"‘‘ Avasesānampi abhayaṃ dammi, sāmī’’ ti."
481903,110,1146,133,149,1,74,10,"‘‘ Mahārāja, evampi uyyāneyeva migā abhayaṃ labhissanti, sesā kiṃ karissantī’’ ti?"
481904,110,1146,150,160,1,30,5,"‘‘ Etesampi abhayaṃ dammi, sāmī’’ ti."
481905,110,1146,161,178,1,68,10,"‘‘ Mahārāja, migā tāva abhayaṃ labhantu, sesā catuppadā kiṃ karissantī’’ ti ?"
481906,110,1146,179,189,1,30,5,"‘‘ Etesampi abhayaṃ dammi, sāmī’’ ti."
481907,110,1146,190,205,1,67,9,"‘‘ Mahārāja, catuppadā tāva abhayaṃ labhantu, dijagaṇā kiṃ karissantī’’ ti?"
481908,110,1146,206,216,1,30,5,"‘‘ Etesampi abhayaṃ dammi, sāmī’’ ti."
481909,110,1146,217,234,1,78,11,"‘‘ Mahārāja, dijagaṇā tāva abhayaṃ labhantu, udake vasantā macchā kiṃ karissantī’’ ti?"
481910,110,1146,235,245,1,30,5,"‘‘ Etesampi abhayaṃ dammi, sāmī’’ ti. "
481911,110,1146,246,296,1,383,44,"Evaṃ mahāsatto rājānaṃ sabbasattānaṃ abhayaṃ yācitvā uṭṭhāya rājānaṃ pañcasu sīlesu patiṭṭhāpetvā‘‘ dhammaṃ cara, mahārāja, mātāpitūsu puttadhītāsu brāhmaṇagahapatikesu negamajānapadesu dhammaṃ caranto samaṃ caranto kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ gamissasī’’ ti rañño buddhalīlāya dhammaṃ desetvā katipāhaṃ uyyāne vasitvā rañño ovādaṃ datvā migagaṇaparivuto araññaṃ pāvisi. "
481912,110,1146,297,303,1,53,6,Sāpi kho migadhenu pupphakaṇṇikasadisaṃ puttaṃ vijāyi. 
481913,110,1146,304,309,1,42,5,So kīḷamāno sākhamigassa santikaṃ gacchati. 
481914,110,1146,310,337,1,152,21,"Atha naṃ mātā tassa santikaṃ gacchantaṃ disvā‘‘ putta, ito paṭṭhāya mā etassa santikaṃ gaccha, nigrodhasseva santikaṃ gaccheyyāsī’’ ti ovadantī imaṃ gāthamāha– "
481915,110,1147,2,4,1,0,0,12.
481916,110,1148,2,11,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Nigrodhameva seveyya, na sākhamupasaṃvase; "
481917,110,1149,2,12,1,50,7,"Nigrodhasmiṃ mataṃ seyyo, yañce sākhasmi jīvitan’’ ti. "
481918,110,1150,2,34,1,218,28,"Tattha nigrodhameva {seveyyā}ti tāta tvaṃ vā añño vā attano hitakāmo nigrodhameva seveyya bhajeyya upasaṅkameyya, na {sākhamupasaṃvase}ti sākhamigaṃ pana na upasaṃvase upagamma na saṃvaseyya, etaṃ nissāya jīvikaṃ na kappeyya. "
481919,110,1150,35,45,1,79,9,Nigrodhasmiṃ mataṃ {seyyo}ti nigrodharañño pādamūle maraṇampi seyyo varaṃ uttamaṃ. 
481920,110,1150,46,64,1,102,17,"Yañce sākhasmi jīvitan ti yaṃ pana sākhassa santike jīvitaṃ, taṃ neva seyyo na varaṃ na uttamanti attho. "
481921,110,1151,2,35,1,196,27,"Tato paṭṭhāya ca pana abhayaladdhakā migā manussānaṃ sassāni khādanti, manussā‘‘ laddhābhayā ime migā’’ ti mige paharituṃ vā palāpetuṃ vā na visahanti, te rājaṅgaṇe sannipatitvā rañño tamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. "
481922,110,1151,36,68,1,159,24,"Rājā‘‘ mayā pasannena nigrodhamigarājassa varo dinno, ahaṃ rajjaṃ jaheyyaṃ, na ca taṃ paṭiññaṃ bhindāmi, gacchatha na koci mama vijite mige paharituṃ labhatī’’ ti āha. "
481923,110,1151,69,110,1,264,32,"Nigrodhamigo taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā migagaṇaṃ sannipātāpetvā‘‘ ito paṭṭhāya paresaṃ sassaṃ khādituṃ na labhissathā’’ ti mige ovaditvā manussānaṃ ārocāpesi‘‘ ito paṭṭhāya sassakārakā manussā sassarakkhaṇatthaṃ vatiṃ mā karontu, khettaṃ pana āvijjhitvā paṇṇasaññaṃ bandhantū’’ ti. "
481924,110,1151,111,117,1,54,6,Tato paṭṭhāya kira khettesu paṇṇabandhanasaññā udapādi. 
481925,110,1151,118,124,1,52,6,Tato paṭṭhāya paṇṇasaññaṃ atikkamanamigo nāma natthi. 
481926,110,1151,125,130,1,40,5,Ayaṃ kira nesaṃ bodhisattato laddhaovādo. 
481927,110,1151,131,150,1,150,18,"Evaṃ migagaṇaṃ ovaditvā bodhisatto yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā saddhiṃ migehi yathākammaṃ gato, rājāpi bodhisattassa ovāde ṭhatvā puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. "
481928,110,1152,2,61,1,375,43,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevāhaṃ theriyā ca kumārakassapassa ca avassayo, pubbepi avassayo evā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā catusaccadhammadesanaṃ vinivaṭṭetvā dve vatthūni kathetvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ tadā sākhamigo devadatto ahosi, parisāpissa devadattaparisāva, migadhenu therī ahosi, putto kumārakassapo, rājā ānando, nigrodhamigarājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
481929,110,1153,2,4,1,32,2,Nigrodhamigajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
481930,110,1155,2,7,1,18,2,[ 13]3. Kaṇḍijātakavaṇṇanā 
481931,110,1156,2,15,1,100,11,Dhiratthu kaṇḍinaṃ sallan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto purāṇadutiyikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
481932,110,1156,16,20,1,45,4,Taṃ aṭṭhakanipāte indriyajātake āvibhavissati. 
481933,110,1156,21,43,1,129,17,"Bhagavā pana taṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavoca‘‘ bhikkhu, pubbepi tvaṃ etaṃ mātugāmaṃ nissāya jīvitakkhayaṃ patvā vītaccitesu aṅgāresu pakko’’ ti. "
481934,110,1156,44,54,1,107,9,"Bhikkhū tassatthassāvibhāvatthāya bhagavantaṃ yāciṃsu, bhagavā bhavantarena paṭicchannakāraṇaṃ pākaṭaṃ akāsi. "
481935,110,1156,55,85,1,254,24,"Ito paraṃ pana bhikkhūnaṃ yācanaṃ bhavantarapaṭicchannatañca avatvā‘‘ atītaṃ āharī’’ ti ettakameva vakkhāma, ettake vuttepi yācanañca valāhakagabbhato candanīharaṇūpamāya bhavantarapaṭicchannakāraṇabhāvo cāti sabbametaṃ heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva yojetvā veditabbaṃ. "
481936,110,1157,2,8,1,54,6,Atīte magadharaṭṭhe rājagahe magadharājā rajjaṃ kāresi. 
481937,110,1157,9,14,1,56,5,Magadhavāsikānaṃ sassasamaye migānaṃ mahāparipantho hoti. 
481938,110,1157,15,19,1,32,4,Te araññe pabbatapādaṃ pavisanti. 
481939,110,1157,20,42,1,211,22,Tattha eko araññavāsī pabbateyyamigo ekāya gāmantavāsiniyā migapotikāya saddhiṃ santhavaṃ katvā tesaṃ migānaṃ pabbatapādato oruyha puna gāmantaṃ otaraṇakāle migapotikāya paṭibaddhacittattā tehi saddhiṃyeva otari. 
481940,110,1157,43,47,1,15,4,Atha naṃ sā āha–
481941,110,1157,48,71,1,99,15,"‘‘ tvaṃ khosi, ayya, pabbateyyo bālamigo, gāmanto ca nāma sāsaṅko sappaṭibhayo, mā amhehi saddhiṃ otarī’’ ti. "
481942,110,1157,72,78,1,59,6,So tassā paṭibaddhacittattā anivattitvā saddhiṃyeva agamāsi. 
481943,110,1157,79,93,1,98,10,Magadhavāsino‘‘ idāni migānaṃ pabbatapādā otaraṇakālo’’ ti ñatvā magge paṭicchannakoṭṭhakesu tiṭṭhanti. 
481944,110,1157,94,102,1,71,8,Tesampi dvinnaṃ āgamanamagge eko luddako paṭicchannakoṭṭhake ṭhito hoti. 
481945,110,1157,103,122,1,114,15,Migapotikā manussagandhaṃ ghāyitvā‘‘ eko luddako ṭhito bhavissatī’’ ti taṃ bālamigaṃ purato katvā sayaṃ pacchato ahosi. 
481946,110,1157,123,129,1,51,6,Luddako ekeneva sarappahārena migaṃ tattheva pāteti. 
481947,110,1157,130,137,1,65,7,Migapotikā tassa viddhabhāvaṃ ñatvā uppatitvā vātagatiyāva palāyi. 
481948,110,1157,138,160,1,205,22,Luddako koṭṭhakato nikkhamitvā migaṃ okkantitvā aggiṃ katvā vītaccitesu aṅgāresu madhuramaṃsaṃ pacitvā khāditvā pānīyaṃ pivitvā avasesaṃ lohitabindūhi paggharantehi kājenādāya dārake tosento gharaṃ agamāsi. 
481949,110,1158,2,11,1,65,8,Tadā bodhisatto tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe rukkhadevatā hutvā nibbatto hoti. 
481950,110,1158,12,33,1,110,17,"So taṃ kāraṇaṃ disvā‘‘ imassa bālamigassa maraṇaṃ neva mātaraṃ nissāya, na pitaraṃ nissāya, atha kho kāmaṃ nissāya. "
481951,110,1158,34,52,1,176,14,"Kāmanimittañhi sattā sugatiyaṃ hatthacchedādikaṃ, duggatiyañca pañcavidhabandhanādinānappakārakaṃ dukkhaṃ pāpuṇanti, paresaṃ maraṇadukkhuppādanampi nāma imasmiṃ loke garahitameva. "
481952,110,1158,53,63,1,84,9,"Yaṃ janapadaṃ mātugāmo vicāreti anusāsati, so itthipariṇāyako janapadopi garahitoyeva. "
481953,110,1158,64,94,1,231,27,"Ye sattā mātugāmassa vasaṃ gacchanti, tepi garahitāyevā’’ ti ekāya gāthāya tīṇi garahavatthūni dassetvā vanadevatāsu sādhukāraṃ datvā gandhapupphādīhi pūjayamānāsu madhurena sarena taṃ vanasaṇḍaṃ unnādento imāya gāthāya dhammaṃ desesi– "
481954,110,1159,2,4,1,0,0,13.
481955,110,1160,2,10,1,47,6,"‘ ‘ Dhiratthu kaṇḍinaṃ sallaṃ, purisaṃ gāḷhavedhinaṃ; "
481956,110,1161,2,8,1,45,5,"Dhiratthu taṃ janapadaṃ, yatthitthī pariṇāyikā; "
481957,110,1162,2,14,1,48,9,"Te cāpi dhikkitā sattā, ye itthīnaṃ vasaṃ gatā’’ ti. "
481958,110,1163,2,12,1,86,8,"Tattha {dhiratthū}ti garahaṇatthe nipāto, svāyamidha uttāsubbegavasena garahaṇe daṭṭhabbo. "
481959,110,1163,13,18,1,42,5,Uttasitubbiggo hi honto bodhisatto evamāha. 
481960,110,1163,19,25,1,37,5,"Kaṇḍamassa atthīti kaṇḍī, taṃ kaṇḍinaṃ. "
481961,110,1163,26,45,1,104,14,"Taṃ pana kaṇḍaṃ anupavisanaṭṭhena‘‘ sallan’’ ti vuccati, tasmā kaṇḍinaṃ sallan ti ettha sallakaṇḍinanti attho. "
481962,110,1163,46,53,1,39,6,"Sallaṃ vā assatthītipi sallo, taṃ sallaṃ. "
481963,110,1163,54,65,1,93,10,"Mahantaṃ vaṇamukhaṃ katvā balavappahāraṃ dento gāḷhaṃ vijjhatīti gāḷhavedhī, taṃ gāḷhavedhinaṃ. "
481964,110,1163,66,79,1,138,12,"Nānappakārena kaṇḍena, kumudapattasaṇṭhānathalena ujukagamaneneva sallena ca samannāgataṃ gāḷhavedhinaṃ purisaṃ dhiratthūti ayamettha attho. "
481965,110,1163,80,84,1,32,3,{Pariṇāyikā}ti issarā saṃvidhāyikā. 
481966,110,1163,85,88,1,19,2,{Dhikkitā}ti garahitā. 
481967,110,1163,89,91,1,25,2,Sesamettha uttānatthameva. 
481968,110,1163,92,104,1,73,11,"Ito paraṃ pana ettakampi avatvā yaṃ yaṃ anuttānaṃ, taṃ tadeva vaṇṇayissāma. "
481969,110,1163,105,117,1,102,12,Evaṃ ekāya gāthāya tīṇi garahavatthūni dassetvā bodhisatto vanaṃ unnādetvā buddhalīlāya dhammaṃ desesi. 
481970,110,1164,2,13,1,111,10,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. "
481971,110,1164,14,23,1,68,8,Satthā dve vatthūni kathetvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi. 
481972,110,1164,24,54,1,149,20,"Ito paraṃ pana‘‘ dve vatthūni kathetvā’’ ti idaṃ avatvā‘‘ anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā’’ ti ettakameva vakkhāma, avuttampi pana heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva yojetvā gahetabbaṃ. "
481973,110,1165,2,17,1,132,13,"Tadā pabbateyyamigo ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu ahosi, migapotikā purāṇadutiyikā, kāmesu dosaṃ dassetvā dhammadesakadevatā pana ahameva ahosinti. "
481974,110,1166,2,4,1,25,2,Kaṇḍijātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
481975,110,1168,2,7,1,21,2,[ 14]4. Vātamigajātakavaṇṇanā 
481976,110,1169,2,15,1,102,11,Na kiratthi rasehi {pāpiyo}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto cūḷapiṇḍapātikatissattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
481977,110,1169,16,49,1,327,33,Satthari kira rājagahaṃ upanissāya veḷuvane viharante tissakumāro nāma mahāvibhavassa seṭṭhikulassa putto ekadivasaṃ veḷuvanaṃ gantvā satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā pabbajitukāmo pabbajjaṃ yācitvā mātāpitūhi ananuññātattā paṭikkhitto sattāhaṃ bhattacchedaṃ katvā raṭṭhapālatthero viya mātāpitaro anujānāpetvā satthu santike pabbaji. 
481978,110,1169,50,58,1,74,8,Satthā taṃ pabbājetvā aḍḍhamāsamattaṃ veḷuvane viharitvā jetavanaṃ agamāsi. 
481979,110,1169,59,86,1,203,22,"Tatrāyaṃ kulaputto terasa dhutaṅgāni samādāya sāvatthiyaṃ sapadānaṃ piṇḍāya caramāno kālaṃ vītināmeti,‘‘ cūḷapiṇḍapātikatissatthero nāmā’’ ti vutte gaganatale puṇṇacando viya buddhasāsane pākaṭo paññāto ahosi. "
481980,110,1170,2,55,1,358,45,"Tasmiṃ kāle rājagahe nakkhattakīḷāya vattamānāya therassa mātāpitaro yaṃ tassa gihikāle ahosi ābharaṇabhaṇḍakaṃ, taṃ ratanacaṅkoṭake nikkhipitvā ure ṭhapetvā‘‘ aññāsu nakkhattakīḷāsu amhākaṃ putto iminā alaṅkārena alaṅkato nakkhattaṃ kīḷati, taṃ no ekaputtaṃ gahetvā samaṇo gotamo sāvatthinagaraṃ gato, kahaṃ nu kho so etarahi nisinno, kahaṃ ṭhito’’ ti vatvā rodanti. "
481981,110,1171,2,22,1,94,14,"Athekā vaṇṇadāsī taṃ kulaṃ gantvā seṭṭhibhariyaṃ rodantiṃ disvā pucchi‘‘ kiṃ pana, ayye, rodasī’’ ti?"
481982,110,1171,23,30,1,20,3,‘‘ Sā tamatthaṃ ārocesi’’.
481983,110,1171,31,43,1,35,6,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana, ayye, ayyaputto piyāyatī’’ ti?"
481984,110,1171,44,51,1,20,3,‘‘ Asukañca asukañcā’’ ti.
481985,110,1171,52,71,1,80,13,"‘‘ Sace tumhe imasmiṃ gehe sabbaṃ issariyaṃ mayhaṃ detha, ahaṃ vo puttaṃ ānessāmī’’ ti. "
481986,110,1171,72,98,1,130,17,"Seṭṭhibhariyā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā paribbayaṃ datvā mahantena parivārena taṃ uyyojesi‘‘ gaccha, attano balena mama puttaṃ ānehī’’ ti. "
481987,110,1171,99,140,1,379,40,Sā paṭicchannayāne nisinnā sāvatthiṃ gantvā therassa bhikkhācāravīthiyaṃ nivāsaṃ gahetvā seṭṭhikulā āgate manusse therassa adassetvā attano parivāreneva parivutā therassa piṇḍāya paviṭṭhassa āditova uḷuṅkayāguñca rasakabhikkhañca datvā rasataṇhāya bandhitvā anukkamena gehe nisīdāpetvā bhikkhaṃ dadamānā ca attano vasaṃ upagatabhāvaṃ ñatvā gilānālayaṃ dassetvā antogabbhe nipajji. 
481988,110,1171,141,147,1,62,6,Theropi bhikkhācāravelāya sapadānaṃ caranto gehadvāraṃ agamāsi. 
481989,110,1171,148,155,1,56,7,Parijano therassa pattaṃ gahetvā theraṃ ghare nisīdāpesi. 
481990,110,1171,156,166,1,41,6,Thero nisīditvāva‘‘ kahaṃ upāsikā’’ ti pucchi.
481991,110,1171,167,179,1,42,6,"‘‘ Gilānā, bhante, tumhākaṃ dassanaṃ icchatī’’ ti. "
481992,110,1171,180,190,1,80,9,So rasataṇhāya baddho attano vatasamādānaṃ bhinditvā tassā nipannaṭṭhānaṃ pāvisi. 
481993,110,1171,191,209,1,161,18,Sā attano āgatakāraṇaṃ kathetvā taṃ palobhetvā rasataṇhāya bandhitvā uppabbājetvā attano vase ṭhapetvā yāne nisīdāpetvā mahantena parivārena rājagahameva agamāsi. 
481994,110,1171,210,214,1,22,4,Sā pavatti pākaṭā jātā. 
481995,110,1172,2,20,1,137,14,Bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ sannisinnā‘‘ cūḷapiṇḍapātikatissattheraṃ kira ekā vaṇṇadāsī rasataṇhāya bandhitvā ādāya gatā’’ ti kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ. 
481996,110,1172,21,40,1,114,13,"Satthā dhammasabhaṃ upagantvā alaṅkatadhammāsane nisīditvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti āha. "
481997,110,1172,41,45,1,26,4,Te taṃ pavattiṃ kathayiṃsu.
481998,110,1172,46,71,1,122,18,"‘‘ Na, bhikkhave, idāneva eso bhikkhu rasataṇhāya bajjhitvā tassā vasaṃ gato, pubbepi tassā vasaṃ gatoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
481999,110,1173,2,10,1,68,8,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ rañño brahmadattassa sañjayo nāma uyyānapālo ahosi. 
482000,110,1173,11,25,1,94,13,"Atheko vātamigo taṃ uyyānaṃ āgantvā sañjayaṃ disvā palāyati, sañjayopi na taṃ tajjetvā nīharati. "
482001,110,1173,26,31,1,39,5,So punappunaṃ āgantvā uyyāneyeva carati. 
482002,110,1173,32,41,1,84,9,Uyyānapālo uyyāne nānappakārāni pupphaphalāni gahetvā divase divase rañño abhiharati. 
482003,110,1173,42,60,1,83,12,"Atha naṃ ekadivasaṃ rājā pucchi‘‘ samma uyyānapāla, uyyāne kiñci acchariyaṃ passasī’’ ti?"
482004,110,1173,61,81,1,77,13,"‘‘ Deva, aññaṃ na passāmi, eko pana vātamigo āgantvā uyyāne carati, etaṃ passāmī’’ ti."
482005,110,1173,82,91,1,31,5,‘‘ Sakkhissati pana taṃ gahetun’’ ti.
482006,110,1173,92,107,1,74,10,"‘‘ Thokaṃ madhuṃ labhanto anto rājanivesanampi naṃ ānetuṃ sakkhissāmi, devā’’ ti. "
482007,110,1173,108,112,1,24,4,Rājā tassa madhuṃ dāpesi. 
482008,110,1173,113,125,1,86,11,So taṃ gahetvā uyyānaṃ gantvā vātamigassa caraṇaṭṭhāne tiṇāni madhunā makkhetvā nilīyi. 
482009,110,1173,126,137,1,100,11,Migo āgantvā madhumakkhitāni tiṇāni khāditvā rasataṇhāya baddho aññatra agantvā uyyānameva āgacchati. 
482010,110,1173,138,146,1,84,8,Uyyānapālo tassa madhumakkhitatiṇesu paluddhabhāvaṃ ñatvā anukkamena attānaṃ dassesi. 
482011,110,1173,147,162,1,131,15,So taṃ disvā katipāhaṃ palāyitvā punappunaṃ passanto vissāsaṃ āpajjitvā anukkamena uyyānapālassa hatthe ṭhitatiṇāni khādituṃ ārabhi. 
482012,110,1174,2,30,1,263,28,So tassa vissāsaṃ āpannabhāvaṃ ñatvā yāva rājanivesanā vīthiṃ kilañjehi parikkhipitvā tahiṃ tahiṃ sākhābhaṅgaṃ pātetvā madhulābukaṃ aṃse laggetvā tiṇakalāpaṃ upakacchake ṭhapetvā madhumakkhitāni tiṇāni migassa purato purato vikiranto antorājanivesanaṃyeva agamāsi. 
482013,110,1174,31,36,1,35,5,Mige anto paviṭṭhe dvāraṃ pidahiṃsu. 
482014,110,1174,37,45,1,86,8,Migo manusse disvā kampamāno maraṇabhayatajjito antonivesanaṅgaṇe ādhāvati paridhāvati. 
482015,110,1174,46,93,1,307,39,"Rājā pāsādā oruyha taṃ kampamānaṃ disvā‘‘ vātamigo nāma manussānaṃ diṭṭhaṭṭhānaṃ sattāhaṃ na gacchati, tajjitaṭṭhānaṃ yāvajīvaṃ na gacchati, so evarūpo gahananissito vātamigo rasataṇhāya baddho idāni evarūpaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgato, natthi vata bho loke rasataṇhāya pāpataraṃ nāmā’’ ti imāya gāthāya dhammadesanaṃ paṭṭhapesi– "
482016,110,1175,2,4,1,0,0,14.
482017,110,1176,2,12,1,49,8,"‘ ‘ Na kiratthi rasehi pāpiyo, āvāsehiva santhavehi vā; "
482018,110,1177,2,11,1,53,6,"Vātamigaṃ gahananissitaṃ, vasamānesi rasehi sañjayo’’ ti. "
482019,110,1178,2,7,1,35,4,Tattha {kirā}ti anussavanatthe nipāto. 
482020,110,1178,8,12,1,41,3,{Rasehī}ti jivhāviññeyyehi madhurambilādīhi. 
482021,110,1178,13,16,1,17,2,{Pāpiyo}ti pāpataro. 
482022,110,1178,17,50,1,331,30,"Āvāsehiva santhavehi {vā}ti nibaddhavasanaṭṭhānasaṅkhātesu hi āvāsesupi mittasanthavesupi chandarāgo pāpakova, tehi pana sacchandarāgaparibhogehi āvāsehi vā mittasanthavehi vā sataguṇena ca sahassaguṇena ca satasahassaguṇena ca dhuvapaṭisevanaṭṭhena āhāraṃ vinā jīvitindriyapālanāya abhāvena ca sacchandarāgaparibhogarasāva pāpatarāti. "
482023,110,1178,51,72,1,108,15,"Bodhisatto pana anussavāgataṃ viya imamatthaṃ katvā‘‘ na kiratthi rasehi pāpiyo, āvāsehiva santhavehi vā’’ ti āha. "
482024,110,1178,73,83,1,54,6,Idāni tesaṃ pāpiyabhāvaṃ dassento‘‘ vātamigan’’ tiādimāha. 
482025,110,1178,84,88,1,45,4,Tattha gahananissitan ti gahanaṭṭhānanissitaṃ. 
482026,110,1178,89,120,1,258,28,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– passatha rasānaṃ pāpiyabhāvaṃ, idaṃ nāma araññāyatane gahananissitaṃ vātamigaṃ sañjayo uyyānapālo madhurasehi attano vasaṃ ānesi, sabbathāpi sacchandarāgaparibhogehi rasehi nāma aññaṃ pāpataraṃ lāmakataraṃ natthīti rasataṇhāya ādīnavaṃ kathesi. "
482027,110,1178,121,128,1,44,7,Kathetvā ca pana taṃ migaṃ araññameva pesesi. 
482028,110,1179,2,31,1,177,22,"Satthāpi ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, sā vaṇṇadāsī idāneva etaṃ rasataṇhāya bandhitvā attano vase karoti, pubbepi akāsiyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi."
482029,110,1179,32,50,1,94,12,"‘‘ Tadā sañjayo ayaṃ vaṇṇadāsī ahosi, vātamigo cūḷapiṇḍapātiko, bārāṇasirājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482030,110,1180,2,4,1,30,2,Vātamigajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
482031,110,1182,2,7,1,22,2,[ 15]5. Kharādiyajātakavaṇṇanā 
482032,110,1183,2,14,1,97,10,Aṭṭhakkhuraṃ {kharādiye}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ dubbacabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482033,110,1183,15,22,1,41,7,So kira bhikkhu dubbaco ovādaṃ na gaṇhāti. 
482034,110,1183,23,40,1,76,13,Atha naṃ satthā pucchi‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu dubbaco ovādaṃ na gaṇhāsī’’ ti?
482035,110,1183,41,48,1,17,3,‘‘ Saccaṃ bhagavā’’ ti. 
482036,110,1183,49,68,1,115,15,Satthā‘‘ pubbepi tvaṃ dubbacatāya paṇḍitānaṃ ovādaṃ aggahetvā pāsena baddho jīvitakkhayaṃ patto’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. 
482037,110,1184,2,13,1,97,11,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto migo hutvā migagaṇaparivuto araññe vasati. 
482038,110,1184,14,33,1,107,13,"Athassa bhaginimigī puttakaṃ dassetvā‘‘ bhātika, ayaṃ te bhāgineyyo, etaṃ migamāyaṃ uggaṇhāpehī’’ ti paṭicchāpesi. "
482039,110,1184,34,47,1,60,9,So taṃ bhāgineyyaṃ‘‘ asukavelāya nāma āgantvā uggaṇhāhī’’ ti āha. 
482040,110,1184,48,51,1,25,3,So vuttavelāya nāgacchati. 
482041,110,1184,52,68,1,107,14,"Yathā ca ekadivasaṃ, evaṃ satta divase sattovāde atikkanto so migamāyaṃ anuggaṇhitvāva vicaranto pāse bajjhi. "
482042,110,1184,69,86,1,90,11,"Mātāpissa bhātaraṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ kiṃ te, bhātika, bhāgineyyo migamāyaṃ uggaṇhāpito’’ ti pucchi. "
482043,110,1184,87,112,1,133,19,"Bodhisatto ca‘‘ tassa anovādakassa mā cintayi, na te puttena migamāyā uggahitā’’ ti vatvā idānipi taṃ anovaditukāmova hutvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
482044,110,1185,2,4,1,0,0,15.
482045,110,1186,2,9,1,44,5,"‘ ‘ Aṭṭhakkhuraṃ kharādiye, migaṃ vaṅkātivaṅkinaṃ; "
482046,110,1187,2,11,1,44,6,"Sattahi kālātikkantaṃ, na naṃ ovaditussahe’’ ti. "
482047,110,1188,2,11,1,73,9,Tattha aṭṭhakkhuran ti ekekasmiṃ pāde dvinnaṃ dvinnaṃ vasena aṭṭhakkhuraṃ. 
482048,110,1188,12,17,1,30,4,{Kharādiye}ti taṃ nāmena ālapati. 
482049,110,1188,18,21,1,30,3,Migan ti sabbasaṅgāhikavacanaṃ. 
482050,110,1188,22,39,1,127,14,"Vaṅkātivaṅkinan ti mūle vaṅkāni, agge ativaṅkānīti vaṅkātivaṅkāni, tādisāni siṅgāni assa atthīti vaṅkātivaṅkī, taṃ vaṅkātivaṅkinaṃ. "
482051,110,1188,40,47,1,62,7,Sattahi kālātikkantan ti sattahi ovādakālehi ovādaṃ atikkantaṃ. 
482052,110,1188,48,66,1,119,16,"Na naṃ {ovaditussahe}ti etaṃ dubbacamigaṃ ahaṃ ovadituṃ na ussahāmi, etassa me ovādatthāya cittampi na uppajjatīti dasseti. "
482053,110,1188,67,77,1,69,10,Atha naṃ dubbacamigaṃ pāse baddhaṃ luddo māretvā maṃsaṃ ādāya pakkāmi. 
482054,110,1189,2,24,1,131,16,"Satthāpi ‘‘ na tvaṃ bhikkhu idāneva dubbaco, pubbepi dubbacoyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi."
482055,110,1189,25,43,1,94,12,"‘‘ Tadā bhāgineyyo migo dubbacabhikkhu ahosi, bhaginī uppalavaṇṇā, ovādamigo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482056,110,1190,2,4,1,30,2,Kharādiyajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
482057,110,1192,2,7,1,28,2,[ 16]6. Tipallatthamigajātakavaṇṇanā 
482058,110,1193,2,15,1,109,12,Migaṃ tipallatthan ti idaṃ satthā kosambiyaṃ badarikārāme viharanto sikkhākāmaṃ rāhulattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482059,110,1193,16,37,1,180,20,"Ekasmiñhi kāle satthari āḷavinagaraṃ upanissāya aggāḷave cetiye viharante bahū upāsakā upāsikā bhikkhū bhikkhuniyo ca vihāraṃ dhammassavanatthāya gacchanti, divā dhammassavanaṃ hoti. "
482060,110,1193,38,52,1,88,13,"Gacchante pana kāle upāsikāyo bhikkhuniyo ca na gacchiṃsu, bhikkhū ceva upāsakā ca ahesuṃ. "
482061,110,1193,53,58,1,41,5,Tato paṭṭhāya rattiṃ dhammassavanaṃ jātaṃ. 
482062,110,1193,59,66,1,76,7,Dhammassavanapariyosāne therā bhikkhū attano attano vasanaṭṭhānāni gacchanti. 
482063,110,1193,67,74,1,61,7,Daharā sāmaṇerā ca upāsakehi saddhiṃ upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ sayanti. 
482064,110,1193,75,90,1,123,13,"Tesu niddaṃ upagatesu ekacce ghurughurupassāsā kākacchamānā dante khādantā nipajjiṃsu, ekacce muhuttaṃ niddāyitvā uṭṭhahiṃsu. "
482065,110,1193,91,97,1,42,6,Te taṃ vippakāraṃ disvā bhagavato ārocesuṃ. 
482066,110,1193,98,120,1,113,13,Bhagavā‘‘ yo pana bhikkhu anupasampannena sahaseyyaṃ kappeyya pācittiyan’’ ti( pāci.49) sikkhāpadaṃ paññapetvā kosambiṃ agamāsi. 
482067,110,1194,2,7,1,40,5,Tattha bhikkhū āyasmantaṃ rāhulaṃ āhaṃsu–
482068,110,1194,8,25,1,86,11,"‘‘ āvuso rāhula, bhagavatā sikkhāpadaṃ paññattaṃ, idāni tvaṃ attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃ jānāhī’’ ti. "
482069,110,1194,26,49,1,195,22,"Pubbe pana te bhikkhū bhagavati ca gāravaṃ tassa cāyasmato sikkhākāmataṃ paṭicca taṃ attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃ āgataṃ ativiya saṅgaṇhanti, khuddakamañcakaṃ paññapetvā ussīsakakaraṇatthāya cīvaraṃ denti. "
482070,110,1194,50,57,1,60,7,Taṃ divasaṃ pana sikkhāpadabhayena vasanaṭṭhānampi na adaṃsu. 
482071,110,1194,58,108,1,247,31,"Rāhulabhaddopi‘‘ pitā me’’ ti dasabalassa vā,‘‘ upajjhāyo me’’ ti dhammasenāpatino vā,‘‘ ācariyo me’’ ti mahāmoggallānassa vā,‘‘ cūḷapitā me’’ ti ānandattherassa vā santikaṃ agantvā dasabalassa vaḷañjanavaccakuṭiṃ brahmavimānaṃ pavisanto viya pavisitvā vāsaṃ kappesi. "
482072,110,1194,109,125,1,141,13,"Buddhānañhi vaḷañjanakuṭiyaṃ dvāraṃ supihitaṃ hoti, gandhaparibhaṇḍakatā bhūmi, gandhadāmamālādāmāni osāritāneva honti, sabbarattiṃ dīpo jhāyati. "
482073,110,1194,126,154,1,175,22,"Rāhulabhaddo pana na tassā kuṭiyā imaṃ sampattiṃ paṭicca tattha vāsaṃ upagato, bhikkhūhi pana‘‘ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ jānāhī’’ ti vuttattā ovādagāravena sikkhākāmatāya tattha vāsaṃ upagato. "
482074,110,1194,155,185,1,194,24,"Antarantarā hi bhikkhū taṃ āyasmantaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ disvā tassa vīmaṃsanatthāya muṭṭhisammajjaniṃ vā kacavarachaḍḍanakaṃ vā bahi khipitvā tasmiṃ āgate ‘‘ āvuso, imaṃ kena chaḍḍitan’’ ti vadanti. "
482075,110,1194,186,225,1,153,24,"Tattha kehici‘‘ rāhulo iminā maggena gato’’ ti vutte so āyasmā‘‘ nāhaṃ, bhante, etaṃ jānāmī’’ ti avatvāva taṃ paṭisāmetvā‘‘ khamatha me, bhante’’ ti khamāpetvā gacchati. "
482076,110,1194,226,228,1,18,2,Evamesa sikkhākāmo. 
482077,110,1195,2,9,1,53,7,So taṃ sikkhākāmataṃyeva paṭicca tattha vāsaṃ upagato. 
482078,110,1195,10,19,1,72,8,"Atha satthā purearuṇaṃyeva vaccakuṭidvāre ṭhatvā ukkāsi, sopāyasmā ukkāsi."
482079,110,1195,20,27,1,9,3,‘‘ Ko eso’’ ti?
482080,110,1195,28,37,1,32,5,‘‘ Ahaṃ rāhulo’’ ti nikkhamitvā vandi.
482081,110,1195,38,48,1,35,6,‘‘ Kasmā tvaṃ rāhula idha nipannosī’’ ti?
482082,110,1195,49,55,1,24,2,‘‘ Vasanaṭṭhānassa abhāvato’’.
482083,110,1195,56,87,1,171,22,"‘‘ Pubbe hi, bhante, bhikkhū mama saṅgahaṃ karonti, idāni attano āpattibhayena vasanaṭṭhānaṃ na denti, svāhaṃ‘ idaṃ aññesaṃ asaṅghaṭṭanaṭṭhānan’ ti iminā kāraṇena idha nipannosmīti. "
482084,110,1195,88,108,1,120,15,"Atha bhagavato‘‘ rāhulaṃ tāva bhikkhū evaṃ pariccajanti, aññe kuladārake pabbājetvā kiṃ karissantī’’ ti dhammasaṃvego udapādi. "
482085,110,1196,2,24,1,132,16,"Atha bhagavā pātova bhikkhū sannipātāpetvā dhammasenāpatiṃ pucchi‘‘ jānāsi pana tvaṃ, sāriputta, ajja katthaci rāhulassa vutthabhāvan’’ ti?"
482086,110,1196,25,34,1,19,4,"‘‘ Na jānāmi, bhante’’ ti."
482087,110,1196,35,55,1,123,15,"‘‘ Sāriputta, ajja rāhulo vaccakuṭiyaṃ vasi, sāriputta, tumhe rāhulaṃ evaṃ pariccajantā aññe kuladārake pabbājetvā kiṃ karissatha? "
482088,110,1196,56,90,1,242,31,"Evañhi sante imasmiṃ sāsane pabbajitā na patiṭṭhā bhavissanti, ito dāni paṭṭhāya anupasampannena ekaṃ dve divase attano santike vasāpetvā tatiyadivase tesaṃ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ ñatvā bahi vāsethā’’ ti imaṃ anupaññattiṃ katvā puna sikkhāpadaṃ paññapesi. "
482089,110,1197,2,47,1,292,34,"Tasmiṃ samaye dhammasabhāyaṃ sannisinnā bhikkhū rāhulassa guṇakathaṃ kathenti‘‘ passathāvuso, yāva sikkhākāmo vatāyaṃ rāhulo,‘ tava vasanaṭṭhānaṃ jānāhī’ ti vutto nāma‘ ahaṃ dasabalassa putto, tumhākaṃ senāsanasmā tumheyeva nikkhamathā’ ti ekaṃ bhikkhumpi appaṭippharitvā vaccakuṭiyaṃ vāsaṃ kappesī’’ ti. "
482090,110,1197,48,70,1,129,16,"Evaṃ tesu kathayamānesu satthā dhammasabhaṃ gantvā alaṅkatāsane nisīditvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti āha."
482091,110,1197,71,84,1,55,7,"‘‘ Bhante, rāhulassa sikkhākāmakathāya, na aññāya kathāyā’’ ti. "
482092,110,1197,85,106,1,117,14,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, rāhulo idāneva sikkhākāmo, pubbe tiracchānayoniyaṃ nibbattopi sikkhākāmoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
482093,110,1198,2,10,1,44,6,Atīte rājagahe eko magadharājā rajjaṃ kāresi. 
482094,110,1198,11,18,1,70,7,Tadā bodhisatto migayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā migagaṇaparivuto araññe vasati. 
482095,110,1198,19,37,1,96,13,"Athassa bhaginī attano puttakaṃ upanetvā‘‘ bhātika, imaṃ te bhāgineyyaṃ migamāyaṃ sikkhāpehī’’ ti āha. "
482096,110,1198,38,60,1,88,12,"Bodhisatto‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā‘‘ gaccha, tāta, asukavelāya nāma āgantvā sikkheyyāsī’’ ti āha. "
482097,110,1198,61,69,1,71,8,So mātulena vuttavelaṃ anatikkamitvā taṃ upasaṅkamitvā migamāyaṃ sikkhi. 
482098,110,1198,70,93,1,125,18,"So ekadivasaṃ vane vicaranto pāsena baddho baddharavaṃ ravi, migagaṇo palāyitvā‘‘ putto te pāsena baddho’’ ti tassa mātuyā ārocesi. "
482099,110,1198,94,110,1,77,11,"Sā bhātu santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ bhātika, bhāgineyyo te migamāyaṃ sikkhāpito’’ ti pucchi. "
482100,110,1198,111,136,1,130,18,"Bodhisatto‘‘ mā tvaṃ puttassa kiñci pāpakaṃ āsaṅki, suggahitā tena migamāyā, idāni taṃ hāsayamāno āgacchissatī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
482101,110,1199,2,4,1,0,0,16.
482102,110,1200,2,9,1,59,5,"‘ ‘ Migaṃ tipallatthamanekamāyaṃ, aṭṭhakkhuraṃ aḍḍharattāpapāyiṃ; "
482103,110,1201,2,12,1,60,7,"Ekena sotena chamāssasanto, chahi kalāhitibhoti bhāgineyyo’’ ti. "
482104,110,1202,2,6,1,31,4,Tattha migan ti bhāgineyyamigaṃ. 
482105,110,1202,7,30,1,171,20,"Tipallatthan ti pallatthaṃ vuccati sayanaṃ, ubhohi passehi ujukameva ca nipannakavasenāti tīhākārehi pallatthaṃ assa, tīṇi vā pallatthāni assāti tipallattho, taṃ tipallatthaṃ. "
482106,110,1202,31,35,1,36,4,Anekamāyan ti bahumāyaṃ bahuvañcanaṃ. 
482107,110,1202,36,46,1,82,10,Aṭṭhakkhuran ti ekekasmiṃ pāde dvinnaṃ dvinnaṃ vasena aṭṭhahi khurehi samannāgataṃ. 
482108,110,1202,47,60,1,134,13,Aḍḍharattāpapāyin ti purimayāmaṃ atikkamitvā majjhimayāme araññato āgamma pānīyassa pivanato aḍḍharatte āpaṃ pivatīti aḍḍharattāpapāyī. 
482109,110,1202,61,65,1,29,4,Taṃ aḍḍharatte apāyinti attho. 
482110,110,1202,66,73,1,59,7,Mama bhāgineyyaṃ migaṃ ahaṃ sādhukaṃ migamāyaṃ uggaṇhāpesiṃ. 
482111,110,1202,74,75,1,6,1,Kathaṃ? 
482112,110,1202,76,85,1,65,7,"Yathā ekena sotena chamāssasanto, chahi kalāhitibhoti {bhāgineyyo}ti. "
482113,110,1202,86,119,1,253,29,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– ahañhi tava puttaṃ tathā uggaṇhāpesiṃ, yathā ekasmiṃ uparimanāsikāsote vātaṃ sannirumbhitvā pathaviyā allīnena ekena heṭṭhimasotena tattheva chamāyaṃ assasanto chahi kalāhi luddakaṃ atibhoti, chahi koṭṭhāsehi ajjhottharati vañcetīti attho. "
482114,110,1202,120,122,1,14,2,Katamāhi chahi? 
482115,110,1202,123,140,1,168,13,"Cattāro pāde pasāretvā ekena passena seyyāya, khurehi tiṇapaṃsukhaṇanena, jivhāninnāmanena udarassa uddhumātabhāvakaraṇena, uccārapassāvavissajjanena, vātasannirumbhanenāti. "
482116,110,1203,2,45,1,255,31,"Aparo nayo– pādena paṃsuṃ gahetvā abhimukhākaḍḍhanena, paṭipaṇāmanena, ubhosu passesu sañcaraṇena, udaraṃ uddhaṃ pakkhipanena, adho avakkhipanenāti imāhi chahi kalāhi yathā atibhoti,‘‘ mato ayan’’ ti saññaṃ uppādetvā vañceti, evaṃ taṃ migamāyaṃ uggaṇhāpesinti dīpeti. "
482117,110,1204,2,27,1,168,21,"Aparo nayo– tathā naṃ uggaṇhāpesiṃ, yathā ekena sotena chamāssasanto chahi kalāhiti dvīsupi nayesu dassitehi chahi kāraṇehi kalāhiti kalāyissati, luddaṃ vañcessatīti attho. "
482118,110,1204,28,32,1,24,3,{Bhotī}ti bhaginiṃ ālapati. 
482119,110,1204,33,41,1,65,7,{Bhāgineyyo}ti evaṃ chahi kāraṇehi vañcanakaṃ bhāgineyyaṃ niddisati. 
482120,110,1204,42,51,1,94,9,Evaṃ bodhisatto bhāgineyyassa migamāyāya sādhukaṃ uggahitabhāvaṃ dassento bhaginiṃ samassāseti. 
482121,110,1205,2,47,1,450,45,Sopi migapotako pāse baddho avipphanditvāyeva bhūmiyaṃ mahāphāsukapassena pāde pasāretvā nipanno pādānaṃ āsannaṭṭhāne khureheva paharitvā paṃsuñca tiṇāni ca uppāṭetvā uccārapassāvaṃ vissajjetvā sīsaṃ pātetvā jivhaṃ ninnāmetvā sarīraṃ kheḷakilinnaṃ katvā vātaggahaṇena udaraṃ uddhumātakaṃ katvā akkhīni parivattetvā heṭṭhā nāsikāsotena vātaṃ sañcarāpento uparimanāsikāsotena vātaṃ sannirumbhitvā sakalasarīraṃ thaddhabhāvaṃ gāhāpetvā matākāraṃ dassesi. 
482122,110,1205,48,57,1,68,8,"Nīlamakkhikāpi naṃ samparivāresuṃ, tasmiṃ tasmiṃ ṭhāne kākā nilīyiṃsu. "
482123,110,1205,58,93,1,211,26,"Luddo āgantvā udaraṃ hatthena paharitvā‘‘ atipātova baddho bhavissati, pūtiko jāto’’ ti tassa bandhanarajjukaṃ mocetvā‘‘ etthevadāni naṃ ukkantitvā maṃsaṃ ādāya gamissāmī’’ ti nirāsaṅko hutvā sākhāpalāsaṃ gahetuṃ āraddho. "
482124,110,1205,94,110,1,134,16,Migapotakopi uṭṭhāya catūhi pādehi ṭhatvā kāyaṃ vidhunitvā gīvaṃ pasāretvā mahāvātena chinnavalāhako viya vegena mātu santikaṃ agamāsi. 
482125,110,1206,2,26,1,141,16,"Satthāpi ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, rāhulo idāneva sikkhākāmo, pubbepi sikkhākāmoyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
482126,110,1206,27,44,1,89,11,"‘‘ tadā bhāgineyyamigapotako rāhulo ahosi, mātā uppalavaṇṇā, mātulamigo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482127,110,1207,2,4,1,36,2,Tipallatthamigajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
482128,110,1209,2,7,1,19,2,[ 17]7. Mālutajātakavaṇṇanā 
482129,110,1210,2,17,1,90,13,Kāḷe vā yadi vā {juṇhe}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto dve vuḍḍhapabbajite ārabbha kathesi. 
482130,110,1210,18,25,1,49,6,Te kira kosalajanapade ekasmiṃ araññāvāse vasanti. 
482131,110,1210,26,33,1,40,6,"Eko kāḷatthero nāma, eko juṇhatthero nāma. "
482132,110,1210,34,51,1,75,12,"Athekadivasaṃ juṇho kāḷaṃ pucchi‘‘ bhante kāḷa, sītaṃ nāma kasmiṃ kāle hotī’’ ti. "
482133,110,1210,52,61,1,19,5,So‘‘ kāḷe hotī’’ ti āha. 
482134,110,1210,62,66,1,32,4,Athekadivasaṃ kāḷo juṇhaṃ pucchi–
482135,110,1210,67,80,1,43,8,"‘‘ bhante juṇha, sītaṃ nāma kasmiṃ kāle hotī’’ ti. "
482136,110,1210,81,90,1,20,5,So‘‘ juṇhe hotī’’ ti āha. 
482137,110,1210,91,115,1,134,19,"Te ubhopi attano kaṅkhaṃ chindituṃ asakkontā satthu santikaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā‘‘ bhante, sītaṃ nāma kasmiṃ kāle hotī’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
482138,110,1210,116,142,1,145,19,"Satthā tesaṃ kathaṃ sutvā‘‘ pubbepi ahaṃ, bhikkhave, tumhākaṃ imaṃ pañhaṃ kathesiṃ, bhavasaṅkhepagatattā pana na sallakkhayitthā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
482139,110,1211,2,14,1,81,12,Atīte ekasmiṃ pabbatapāde sīho ca byaggho ca dve sahāyā ekissāyeva guhāya vasanti. 
482140,110,1211,15,22,1,71,7,Tadā bodhisattopi isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā tasmiṃyeva pabbatapāde vasati. 
482141,110,1211,23,30,1,60,7,Athekadivasaṃ tesaṃ sahāyakānaṃ sītaṃ nissāya vivādo udapādi. 
482142,110,1211,31,41,1,34,6,Byaggho‘‘ kāḷeyeva sītaṃ hotī’’ ti āha. 
482143,110,1211,42,52,1,32,6,Sīho‘‘ juṇheyeva sītaṃ hotī’’ ti āha. 
482144,110,1211,53,61,1,66,8,Te ubhopi attano kaṅkhaṃ chindituṃ asakkontā bodhisattaṃ pucchiṃsu. 
482145,110,1211,62,65,1,25,3,Bodhisatto imaṃ gāthamāha– 
482146,110,1212,2,4,1,0,0,17.
482147,110,1213,2,13,1,40,9,"‘ ‘ Kāḷe vā yadi vā juṇhe, yadā vāyati māluto; "
482148,110,1214,2,10,1,40,5,"Vātajāni hi sītāni, ubhotthamaparājitā’’ ti. "
482149,110,1215,2,14,1,59,10,Tattha kāḷe vā yadi vā {juṇhe}ti kāḷapakkhe vā juṇhapakkhe vā. 
482150,110,1215,15,29,1,89,12,"Yadā vāyati {māluto}ti yasmiṃ samaye puratthimādibhedo vāto vāyati, tasmiṃ samaye sītaṃ hoti. "
482151,110,1215,30,31,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
482152,110,1215,32,50,1,113,16,"Vātajāni hi sītāni, yasmā vāte vijjanteyeva sītāni honti, kāḷapakkho vā juṇhapakkho vā ettha apamāṇanti vuttaṃ hoti. "
482153,110,1215,51,58,1,59,6,{Ubhotthamaparājitā}ti ubhopi tumhe imasmiṃ pañhe aparājitāti. 
482154,110,1215,59,64,1,37,5,Evaṃ bodhisatto te sahāyake saññāpesi. 
482155,110,1216,2,28,1,164,19,"Satthāpi ‘‘ bhikkhave, pubbepi mayā tumhākaṃ ayaṃ pañho kathito’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne dvepi therā sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahiṃsu. "
482156,110,1216,29,52,1,128,16,"Satthā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ tadā byaggho kāḷo ahosi, sīho juṇho, pañhavissajjanakatāpaso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482157,110,1217,2,4,1,27,2,Mālutajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
482158,110,1219,2,7,1,25,2,[ 18]8. Matakabhattajātakavaṇṇanā 
482159,110,1220,2,14,1,86,12,Evaṃ ce sattā jāneyyun ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto matakabhattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482160,110,1220,15,27,1,95,12,Tasmiñhi kāle manussā bahū ajeḷakādayo māretvā kālakate ñātake uddissa matakabhattaṃ nāma denti. 
482161,110,1220,28,50,1,138,18,"Bhikkhū te manusse tathā karonte disvā satthāraṃ pucchiṃsu‘‘ etarahi, bhante, manussā bahū pāṇe jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā matakabhattaṃ nāma denti. "
482162,110,1220,51,62,1,35,7,"Atthi nu kho, bhante, ettha vuḍḍhī’’ ti? "
482163,110,1220,63,95,1,197,25,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave,‘ matakabhattaṃ dassāmā’ ti katepi pāṇātipāte kāci vuḍḍhi nāma atthi, pubbe paṇḍitā ākāse nisajja dhammaṃ desetvā ettha ādīnavaṃ kathetvā sakalajambudīpavāsike etaṃ kammaṃ jahāpesuṃ. "
482164,110,1220,96,107,1,69,9,Idāni pana bhavasaṅkhepagatattā puna pātubhūtan’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. 
482165,110,1221,2,25,1,161,19,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente eko tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū disāpāmokkho ācariyabrāhmaṇo‘‘ matakabhattaṃ dassāmī’’ ti ekaṃ eḷakaṃ gāhāpetvā antevāsike āha–
482166,110,1221,26,46,1,103,14,"‘‘ tātā, imaṃ eḷakaṃ nadiṃ netvā nhāpetvā kaṇṭhe mālaṃ parikkhipitvā pañcaṅgulikaṃ datvā maṇḍetvā ānethā’’ ti. "
482167,110,1221,47,63,1,83,12,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā taṃ ādāya nadiṃ gantvā nhāpetvā maṇḍetvā nadītīre ṭhapesuṃ. 
482168,110,1221,64,104,1,253,32,So eḷako attano pubbakammaṃ disvā‘‘ evarūpā nāma dukkhā ajja muccissāmī’’ ti somanassajāto mattikāghaṭaṃ bhindanto viya mahāhasitaṃ hasitvā puna‘‘ ayaṃ brāhmaṇo maṃ ghātetvā mayā laddhadukkhaṃ labhissatī’’ ti brāhmaṇe kāruññaṃ uppādetvā mahantena saddena parodi. 
482169,110,1222,2,32,1,125,22,"Atha naṃ te māṇavā pucchiṃsu‘‘ samma eḷaka , tvaṃ mahāsaddena hasi ceva rodi ca, kena nu kho kāraṇena hasi, kena kāraṇena parodī’’ ti?"
482170,110,1222,33,46,1,64,9,‘‘ Tumhe maṃ imaṃ kāraṇaṃ attano ācariyassa santike puccheyyāthā’’ ti. 
482171,110,1222,47,55,1,52,8,Te taṃ ādāya gantvā idaṃ kāraṇaṃ ācariyassa ārocesuṃ. 
482172,110,1222,56,75,1,77,13,"Ācariyo tesaṃ vacanaṃ sutvā eḷakaṃ pucchi‘‘ kasmā tvaṃ eḷaka, hasi, kasmā rodī’’ ti? "
482173,110,1222,76,134,1,402,46,"Eḷako attanā katakammaṃ jātissarañāṇena anussaritvā brāhmaṇassa kathesi‘‘ ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, pubbe tādisova mantajjhāyakabrāhmaṇo hutvā‘ matakabhattaṃ dassāmī’ ti ekaṃ eḷakaṃ māretvā matakabhattaṃ adāsiṃ, svāhaṃ ekassa eḷakassa ghātitattā ekenūnesu pañcasu attabhāvasatesu sīsacchedaṃ pāpuṇiṃ, ayaṃ me koṭiyaṃ ṭhito pañcasatimo attabhāvo, svāhaṃ‘ ajja evarūpā dukkhā muccissāmī’ ti somanassajāto iminā kāraṇena hasiṃ. "
482174,110,1222,135,171,1,226,31,"Rodanto pana‘ ahaṃ tāva ekaṃ eḷakaṃ māretvā pañca jātisatāni sīsacchedadukkhaṃ patvā ajja tamhā dukkhā muccissāmi, ayaṃ pana brāhmaṇo maṃ māretvā ahaṃ viya pañca jātisatāni sīsacchedadukkhaṃ labhissatī’ ti tayi kāruññena rodin’’ ti."
482175,110,1222,172,185,1,37,7,"‘‘ Eḷaka, mā bhāyi, nāhaṃ taṃ māressāmī’’ ti."
482176,110,1222,186,205,1,83,13,"‘‘ Brāhmaṇa, kiṃ vadesi, tayi mārentepi amārentepi na sakkā ajja mayā maraṇā muccitun’’ ti."
482177,110,1222,206,223,1,71,11,"‘‘ Eḷaka, mā bhāyi, ahaṃ te ārakkhaṃ gahetvā tayā saddhiṃyeva vicarissāmī’’ ti."
482178,110,1222,224,240,1,73,10,"‘‘ Brāhmaṇa, appamattako tava ārakkho, mayā katapāpaṃ pana mahantaṃ balavan’’ ti. "
482179,110,1223,2,21,1,110,15,Brāhmaṇo eḷakaṃ muñcitvā‘‘ imaṃ eḷakaṃ kassacipi māretuṃ na dassāmī’’ ti antevāsike ādāya eḷakeneva saddhiṃ vicari. 
482180,110,1223,22,33,1,101,11,Eḷako vissaṭṭhamattova ekaṃ pāsāṇapiṭṭhiṃ nissāya jātagumbe gīvaṃ ukkhipitvā paṇṇāni khādituṃ āraddho. 
482181,110,1223,34,53,1,142,16,"Taṅkhaṇaññeva tasmiṃ pāsāṇapiṭṭhe asani pati, tato ekā pāsāṇasakalikā chijjitvā eḷakassa pasāritagīvāya patitvā sīsaṃ chindi, mahājano sannipati. "
482182,110,1223,54,62,1,56,7,Tadā bodhisatto tasmiṃ ṭhāne rukkhadevatā hutvā nibbatto. 
482183,110,1223,63,91,1,200,24,So passantasseva tassa mahājanassa devatānubhāvena ākāse pallaṅkena nisīditvā‘‘ ime sattā evaṃ pāpassa phalaṃ jānamānā appevanāma pāṇātipātaṃ na kareyyun’’ ti madhurassarena dhammaṃ desento imaṃ gāthamāha– 
482184,110,1224,2,4,1,0,0,18.
482185,110,1225,2,11,1,45,7,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ ce sattā jāneyyuṃ, dukkhāyaṃ jātisambhavo; "
482186,110,1226,2,13,1,44,8,"Na pāṇo pāṇinaṃ haññe, pāṇaghātī hi socatī’’ ti. "
482187,110,1227,2,13,1,59,11,Tattha evaṃ ce sattā jāneyyun ti ime sattā evaṃ ce jāneyyuṃ. 
482188,110,1227,14,15,1,6,1,Kathaṃ? 
482189,110,1227,16,40,1,212,19,Dukkhāyaṃ {jātisambhavo}ti ayaṃ tattha tattha jāti ca jātassa anukkamena vaḍḍhisaṅkhāto sambhavo ca jarābyādhimaraṇaappiyasampayogapiyavippayogahatthapādacchedādīnaṃ dukkhānaṃ vatthubhūtattā‘‘ dukkho’’ ti yadi jāneyyuṃ. 
482190,110,1227,41,76,1,210,28,"Na pāṇo pāṇinaṃ {haññe}ti‘‘ paraṃ vadhanto jātisambhave vadhaṃ labhati, pīḷento pīḷaṃ labhatī’’ ti jātisambhavassa dukkhavatthutāya dukkhabhāvaṃ jānanto koci pāṇo aññaṃ pāṇinaṃ na haññe, satto sattaṃ na haneyyāti attho. "
482191,110,1227,77,78,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
482192,110,1227,79,113,1,326,31,"Pāṇaghātī hi {socatī}ti, yasmā sāhatthikādīsu chasu payogesu yena kenaci payogena parassa jīvitindriyupacchedanena pāṇaghātī puggalo aṭṭhasu mahānirayesu soḷasasu ussadanirayesu nānappakārāya tiracchānayoniyā pettivisaye asurakāyeti imesu catūsu apāyesu mahādukkhaṃ anubhavamāno dīgharattaṃ antonijjhāyanalakkhaṇena sokena socati. "
482193,110,1227,114,134,1,132,18,"Yathā vāyaṃ eḷako maraṇabhayena socati, evaṃ dīgharattaṃ socatītipi ñatvā na pāṇo pāṇinaṃ haññe, koci pāṇātipātakammaṃ nāma na kareyya. "
482194,110,1227,135,145,1,82,10,Mohena pana mūḷhā avijjāya andhīkatā imaṃ ādīnavaṃ apassantā pāṇātipātaṃ karontīti. 
482195,110,1228,2,8,1,52,6,Evaṃ mahāsatto nirayabhayena tajjetvā dhammaṃ desesi. 
482196,110,1228,9,16,1,69,7,Manussā taṃ dhammadesanaṃ sutvā nirayabhayabhītā pāṇātipātā viramiṃsu. 
482197,110,1228,17,36,1,154,17,"Bodhisattopi dhammaṃ desetvā mahājanaṃ sīle patiṭṭhāpetvā yathākammaṃ gato, mahājanopi bodhisattassa ovāde ṭhatvā dānādīni puññāni katvā devanagaraṃ pūresi. "
482198,110,1228,37,55,1,116,14,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ ahaṃ tena samayena rukkhadevatā ahosin’’ ti. 
482199,110,1229,2,4,1,33,2,Matakabhattajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
482200,110,1231,2,7,1,26,2,[ 19]9. Āyācitabhattajātakavaṇṇanā 
482201,110,1232,2,16,1,99,12,Sace mucce pecca {mucce}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto devatānaṃ āyācanabalikammaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482202,110,1232,17,43,1,181,22,Tadā kira manussā vaṇijjāya gacchantā pāṇe vadhitvā devatānaṃ balikammaṃ katvā‘‘ mayaṃ anantarāyena atthasiddhiṃ patvā āgantvā puna tumhākaṃ balikammaṃ karissāmā’’ ti āyācitvā gacchanti. 
482203,110,1232,44,83,1,214,28,"Tatthānantarāyena atthasiddhiṃ patvā āgatā‘‘ devatānubhāvena idaṃ jātan’’ ti maññamānā bahū pāṇe vadhitvā āyācanato muccituṃ balikammaṃ karonti, taṃ disvā bhikkhū‘‘ atthi nu kho, bhante, ettha attho’’ ti bhagavantaṃ pucchiṃsu. "
482204,110,1232,84,87,1,20,3,Bhagavā atītaṃ āhari. 
482205,110,1233,2,26,1,184,20,Atīte kāsiraṭṭhe ekasmiṃ gāmake kuṭumbiko gāmadvāre ṭhitanigrodharukkhe devatāya balikammaṃ paṭijānitvā anantarāyena āgantvā bahū pāṇe vadhitvā‘‘ āyācanato muccissāmī’’ ti rukkhamūlaṃ gato. 
482206,110,1233,27,32,1,48,5,Rukkhadevatā khandhaviṭape ṭhatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
482207,110,1234,2,4,1,0,0,19.
482208,110,1235,2,12,1,44,8,"‘ ‘ Sace mucce pecca mucce, muccamāno hi bajjhati; "
482209,110,1236,2,13,1,50,8,"Na hevaṃ dhīrā muccanti, mutti bālassa bandhanan’’ ti. "
482210,110,1237,2,16,1,77,12,"Tattha sace mucce pecca {mucce}ti bho purisa, tvaṃ sace mucce yadi muccitukāmosi. "
482211,110,1237,17,27,1,53,8,"Pecca {mucce}ti yathā paraloke na bajjhasi, evaṃ muccāhi. "
482212,110,1237,28,46,1,110,15,"Muccamāno hi {bajjhatī}ti yathā pana tvaṃ pāṇaṃ vadhitvā muccituṃ icchasi, evaṃ muccamāno hi pāpakammena bajjhati. "
482213,110,1237,47,61,1,80,12,"Tasmā na hevaṃ dhīrā {muccantī}ti ye paṇḍitapurisā, te evaṃ paṭissavato na muccanti. "
482214,110,1237,62,63,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
482215,110,1237,64,80,1,110,15,"Evarūpā hi mutti bālassa bandhanaṃ, esā pāṇātipātaṃ katvā mutti nāma bālassa bandhanameva hotīti dhammaṃ desesi. "
482216,110,1237,81,92,1,90,10,Tato paṭṭhāya manussā evarūpā pāṇātipātakammā viratā dhammaṃ caritvā devanagaraṃ pūrayiṃsu. 
