482218,110,1239,2,4,1,33,2,Āyācitabhattajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
482219,110,1241,2,7,1,21,2,[ 20]10. Naḷapānajātakavaṇṇanā 
482220,110,1242,2,19,1,157,16,Disvā padamanuttiṇṇan ti idaṃ satthā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno naḷakapānagāmaṃ patvā naḷakapānapokkharaṇiyaṃ ketakavane viharanto naḷadaṇḍake ārabbha kathesi. 
482221,110,1242,20,59,1,276,32,"Tadā kira bhikkhū naḷakapānapokkharaṇiyaṃ nhatvā sūcigharatthāya sāmaṇerehi naḷadaṇḍake gāhāpetvā te sabbatthakameva chidde disvā satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ bhante, mayaṃ sūcigharatthāya naḷadaṇḍake gaṇhāpema, te mūlato yāva aggā sabbatthakameva chiddā, kiṃ nu kho etan’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
482222,110,1242,60,75,1,70,9,"Satthā‘‘ idaṃ, bhikkhave, mayhaṃ porāṇakaadhiṭṭhānan’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
482223,110,1243,2,8,1,36,6,Pubbe kira so vanasaṇḍo arañño ahosi. 
482224,110,1243,9,15,1,57,6,Tassāpi pokkharaṇiyā eko dakarakkhaso otiṇṇotiṇṇe khādati. 
482225,110,1243,16,27,1,126,11,Tadā bodhisatto rohitamigapotakappamāṇo kapirājā hutvā asītisahassamattavānaraparivuto yūthaṃ pariharanto tasmiṃ araññe vasati. 
482226,110,1243,28,56,1,202,22,"So vānaragaṇassa ovādaṃ adāsi‘‘ tātā, imasmiṃ araññe visarukkhāpi amanussapariggahitapokkharaṇiyopi honti, tumhe akhāditapubbaṃ phalāphalaṃ khādantā vā apītapubbaṃ pānīyaṃ pivantā vā maṃ paṭipuccheyyāthā’’ ti. "
482227,110,1243,57,82,1,194,21,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā ekadivasaṃ agatapubbaṭṭhānaṃ gatā tattha bahudeva divasaṃ caritvā pānīyaṃ gavesamānā ekaṃ pokkharaṇiṃ disvā pānīyaṃ apivitvāva bodhisattassāgamanaṃ olokayamānā nisīdiṃsu. 
482228,110,1243,83,97,1,53,9,"Bodhisatto āgantvā‘‘ kiṃ tātā, pānīyaṃ na pivathā’’ ti āha."
482229,110,1243,98,106,1,28,4,‘‘ Tumhākaṃ āgamanaṃ olokemā’’ ti.
482230,110,1243,107,126,1,98,12,"‘‘ Suṭṭhu, tātā’’ ti bodhisatto pokkharaṇiṃ āvijjhitvā padaṃ paricchindanto otiṇṇameva passi, na uttiṇṇaṃ. "
482231,110,1243,127,154,1,119,16,"So‘‘ nissaṃsayaṃ esā amanussapariggahitā’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ suṭṭhu vo kataṃ, tātā, pānīyaṃ apivantehi, amanussapariggahitā ayan’’ ti āha. "
482232,110,1244,2,29,1,187,20,"Dakarakkhasopi tesaṃ anotaraṇabhāvaṃ ñatvā nīlodaro paṇḍaramukho surattahatthapādo bībhacchadassano hutvā udakaṃ dvidhā katvā nikkhamitvā‘‘ kasmā nisinnāttha, otaritvā pānīyaṃ pivathā’’ ti āha. "
482233,110,1244,30,42,1,62,8,Atha naṃ bodhisatto pucchi‘‘ tvaṃ idha nibbattadakarakkhasosī’’ ti?
482234,110,1244,43,51,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, ahan’’ ti."
482235,110,1244,52,61,1,36,5,‘‘ Tvaṃ pokkharaṇiṃ otiṇṇake labhasī’’ ti?
482236,110,1244,62,83,1,99,14,"‘‘ Āma, labhāmi, ahaṃ idhotiṇṇaṃ antamaso sakuṇikaṃ upādāya na kiñci muñcāmi, tumhepi sabbe khādissāmī’’ ti."
482237,110,1244,84,95,1,43,7,‘‘ Na mayaṃ attānaṃ tuyhaṃ khādituṃ dassāmā’’ ti.
482238,110,1244,96,104,1,26,4,‘‘ Pānīyaṃ pana pivissathā’’ ti.
482239,110,1244,105,120,1,49,9,"‘‘ Āma, pānīyaṃ pivissāma, na ca te vasaṃ gamissāmā’’ ti."
482240,110,1244,121,130,1,33,5,‘‘ Atha kathaṃ pānīyaṃ pivissathā’’ ti? 
482241,110,1244,131,142,1,44,7,Kiṃ pana tvaṃ maññasi‘‘ otaritvā pivissantī’’ ti.
482242,110,1244,143,169,1,174,21,"‘‘ Mayañhi anotaritvā asītisahassānipi ekamekaṃ naḷadaṇḍakaṃ gahetvā uppalanāḷena udakaṃ pivantā viya tava pokkharaṇiyā pānīyaṃ pivissāma, evaṃ no tvaṃ khādituṃ na sakkhissasī’’ ti. "
482243,110,1244,170,179,1,84,9,Etamatthaṃ viditvā satthā abhisambuddho hutvā imissā gāthāya purimapadadvayaṃ abhāsi– 
482244,110,1245,2,4,1,0,0,20.
