482246,110,1247,2,18,1,114,13,"Tassattho – bhikkhave, so kapirājā tassā pokkharaṇiyā ekampi uttiṇṇapadaṃ nāddasa, otaritaṃ pana otiṇṇapadameva addasa. "
482247,110,1247,19,40,1,136,17,Evaṃ disvā padaṃ anuttiṇṇaṃ disvāna otaritaṃ padaṃ‘‘ addhāyaṃ pokkharaṇī amanussapariggahitā’’ ti ñatvā tena saddhiṃ sallapanto sapariso āha–
