482252,110,1251,2,12,1,73,10,Evaṃ naḷena pānīyaṃ pivantaṃ saparisampi maṃ tvaṃ neva vadhissasīti attho. 
482253,110,1252,2,26,1,171,21,"Evañca pana vatvā bodhisatto ekaṃ naḷadaṇḍakaṃ āharāpetvā pāramiyo āvajjetvā saccakiriyaṃ katvā mukhena dhami, naḷo anto kiñci gaṇṭhiṃ asesetvā sabbatthakameva susiro ahosi . "
