482257,110,1252,65,70,1,64,5,Bodhisattānañhi hitūpacārassa mahantatāya adhiṭṭhānaṃ samijjhati. 
482258,110,1252,71,80,1,77,9,Tato paṭṭhāya sabbepi taṃ pokkharaṇiṃ parivāretvā uṭṭhitanaḷā ekacchiddā jātā. 
482259,110,1252,81,86,1,52,5,Imasmiñhi kappe cattāri kappaṭṭhiyapāṭihāriyāni nāma. 
482260,110,1252,87,89,1,16,2,Katamāni cattāri? 
482261,110,1252,90,127,1,326,34,"Cande sasalakkhaṇaṃ sakalampi imaṃ kappaṃ ṭhassati, vaṭṭakajātake aggino nibbutaṭṭhānaṃ sakalampi imaṃ kappaṃ aggi na jhāyissati, ghaṭīkāranivesanaṭṭhānaṃ sakalampi imaṃ kappaṃ anovassakaṃ ṭhassati, imaṃ pokkharaṇiṃ parivāretvā uṭṭhitanaḷā sakalampi imaṃ kappaṃ ekacchiddā bhavissantīti imāni cattāri kappaṭṭhiyapāṭihāriyāni nāma. "
482262,110,1253,2,9,1,53,7,Bodhisatto evaṃ adhiṭṭhahitvā ekaṃ naḷaṃ ādāya nisīdi. 
482263,110,1253,10,17,1,70,7,Tepi asītisahassavānarā ekekaṃ ādāya pokkharaṇiṃ parivāretvā nisīdiṃsu. 
482264,110,1253,18,28,1,84,10,Tepi bodhisattassa naḷena ākaḍḍhitvā pānīyaṃ pivanakāle sabbe tīre nisinnāva piviṃsu. 
482265,110,1253,29,39,1,85,10,Evaṃ tehi pānīye pivite dakarakkhaso kiñci alabhitvā anattamano sakanivesanameva gato. 
482266,110,1253,40,44,1,41,4,Bodhisattopi saparivāro araññameva pāvisi. 
482267,110,1254,2,25,1,161,17,"Satthā pana‘‘ imesaṃ, bhikkhave, naḷānaṃ ekacchiddabhāvo nāma mayhamevetaṃ porāṇakaadhiṭṭhānan’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
482268,110,1254,26,44,1,109,12,"‘‘ tadā dakarakkhaso devadatto ahosi, asītisahassavānarā buddhaparisā, upāyakusalo pana kapirājā ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482269,110,1255,2,4,1,28,2,Naḷapānajātakavaṇṇanā dasamā. 
482270,110,1256,2,4,1,16,2,Sīlavaggo dutiyo. 
482271,110,1257,2,3,1,11,1,Tassuddānaṃ – 
482272,110,1258,2,8,1,46,5,"Nigrodhaṃ lakkhaṇaṃ kaṇḍi, vātamigaṃ kharādiyaṃ; "
482273,110,1259,2,7,1,42,4,"Tipallatthaṃ mālutañca, matabhatta ayācitaṃ; "
482274,110,1260,2,5,1,21,3,Naḷapānanti te dasāti.
482275,110,1261,2,4,1,12,2,3 . Kuruṅgavaggo
482276,110,1263,2,7,1,24,2,[ 21]1. Kuruṅgamigajātakavaṇṇanā 
482277,110,1264,2,15,1,80,9,Ñātametaṃ {kuruṅgassā}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482278,110,1264,16,47,1,237,24,"Ekasmiñhi samaye dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitā bhikkhū‘‘ āvuso devadatto tathāgatassa ghātanatthāya dhanuggahe payojesi, silaṃ pavijjhi, dhanapālaṃ vissajjesi, sabbathāpi dasabalassa vadhāya parisakkatī’’ ti devadattassa avaṇṇaṃ kathentā nisīdiṃsu. "
482279,110,1264,48,66,1,94,12,"Satthā āgantvā paññattāsane nisinno‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchi. "
482280,110,1264,67,76,1,82,8,"Bhante, devadatto tumhākaṃ vadhāya parisakkatīti tassa aguṇakathāya sannisinnāmhāti. "
482281,110,1264,77,107,1,151,22,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, devadatto idāneva mama vadhāya parisakkati, pubbepi mama vadhāya parisakkiyeva, na ca pana maṃ vadhituṃ asakkhī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
482282,110,1265,2,15,1,118,13,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kuruṅgamigo hutvā ekasmiṃ araññāyatane phalāni khādanto vasati. 
482283,110,1265,16,23,1,66,7,So ekasmiṃ kāle phalasampanne sepaṇṇirukkhe sepaṇṇiphalāni khādati. 
482284,110,1265,24,47,1,211,23,Atheko gāmavāsī aṭṭakaluddako phalarukkhamūlesu migānaṃ padāni upadhāretvā uparirukkhe aṭṭakaṃ bandhitvā tattha nisīditvā phalāni khādituṃ āgatāgate mige sattiyā vijjhitvā tesaṃ maṃsaṃ vikkiṇanto jīvikaṃ kappeti. 
482285,110,1265,48,70,1,184,22,So ekadivasaṃ tasmiṃ rukkhamūle bodhisattassa padavaḷañjaṃ disvā tasmiṃ sepaṇṇirukkhe aṭṭakaṃ bandhitvā pātova bhuñjitvā sattiṃ ādāya vanaṃ pavisitvā taṃ rukkhaṃ āruhitvā aṭṭake nisīdi. 
482286,110,1265,71,106,1,230,26,"Bodhisattopi pātova vasanaṭṭhānā nikkhamitvā‘‘ sepaṇṇiphalāni khādissāmī’’ ti āgamma taṃ rukkhamūlaṃ sahasāva apavisitvā‘‘ kadāci aṭṭakaluddakā rukkhesu aṭṭakaṃ bandhanti, atthi nu kho evarūpo upaddavo’’ ti pariggaṇhanto bāhiratova aṭṭhāsi. "
482287,110,1266,2,15,1,115,12,Luddakopi bodhisattassa anāgamanabhāvaṃ ñatvā aṭṭake nisinnova sepaṇṇiphalāni khipitvā khipitvā tassa purato pātesi. 
482288,110,1266,16,79,1,374,49,"Bodhisatto‘‘ imāni phalāni āgantvā mayhaṃ purato patanti, atthi nu kho upari luddako’’ ti punappunaṃ ullokento luddakaṃ disvā apassanto viya hutvā‘‘ ambho, rukkha-pubbe tvaṃ olambakaṃ cārento viya ujukameva phalāni pātesi, ajja pana te rukkhadhammo pariccatto, evaṃ tayā rukkhadhamme pariccatte ahampi aññaṃ rukkhamūlaṃ upasaṅkamitvā mayhaṃ āhāraṃ pariyesissāmī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
482289,110,1267,2,4,1,0,0,21.
482290,110,1268,2,11,1,45,7,"‘ ‘ Ñātametaṃ kuruṅgassa, yaṃ tvaṃ sepaṇṇi seyyasi; "
482291,110,1269,2,14,1,49,9,"Aññaṃ sepaṇṇi gacchāmi, na me te ruccate phalan’’ ti. "
482292,110,1270,2,7,1,29,5,Tattha ñātan ti pākaṭaṃ jātaṃ. 
482293,110,1270,8,11,1,12,3,Etan ti idaṃ. 
482294,110,1270,12,15,1,27,2,{Kuruṅgassā}ti kuruṅgamigassa. 
482295,110,1270,16,38,1,157,20,"Yaṃ tvaṃ sepaṇṇi {seyyasī}ti yaṃ tvaṃ ambho sepaṇṇirukkha purato phalāni pātayamāno seyyasi viseyyasi visiṇṇaphalo hosi, taṃ sabbaṃ kuruṅgamigassa pākaṭaṃ jātaṃ. "
482296,110,1270,39,61,1,123,20,"Na me te ruccate phalan ti evaṃ phalaṃ dadamānāya na me tava phalaṃ ruccati, tiṭṭha tvaṃ, ahaṃ aññattha gacchissāmīti agamāsi. "
482297,110,1271,2,19,1,83,12,"Athassa luddako aṭṭake nisinnova sattiṃ khipitvā‘‘ gaccha, viraddho dānimhi tan’’ ti āha. "
482298,110,1271,20,45,1,173,19,"Bodhisatto nivattitvā ṭhito āha‘‘ ambho purisa, idānīsi kiñcāpi maṃ viraddho, aṭṭha pana mahāniraye soḷasaussadaniraye pañcavidhabandhanādīni ca kammakāraṇāni aviraddhoyevāsī’’ ti. "
482299,110,1271,46,57,1,76,10,"Evañca pana vatvā palāyitvā yathāruciṃ gato, luddopi otaritvā yathāruciṃ gato. "
482300,110,1272,2,34,1,189,24,"Satthāpi ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, devadatto idāneva mama vadhāya parisakkati, pubbepi parisakkiyeva, na ca pana maṃ vadhituṃ asakkhī’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
482301,110,1272,35,49,1,69,9,"‘‘ tadā aṭṭakaluddako devadatto ahosi, kuruṅgamigo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482302,110,1273,2,4,1,32,2,Kuruṅgamigajātakavaṇṇanā paṭhamā.
482303,110,1275,2,7,1,20,2,[ 22]2. Kukkurajātakavaṇṇanā 
482304,110,1276,2,14,1,75,9,Ye {kukkurā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ñātatthacariyaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482305,110,1276,15,19,1,49,4,Sā dvādasakanipāte bhaddasālajātake āvibhavissati. 
482306,110,1276,20,26,1,44,6,Idaṃ pana vatthuṃ patiṭṭhapetvā atītaṃ āhari. 
482307,110,1277,2,17,1,151,14,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tathārūpaṃ kammaṃ paṭicca kukkurayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā anekasatakukkuraparivuto mahāsusāne vasati. 
482308,110,1277,18,33,1,152,15,Athekadivasaṃ rājā setasindhavayuttaṃ sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍitaṃ rathaṃ āruyha uyyānaṃ gantvā tattha divasabhāgaṃ kīḷitvā atthaṅgate sūriye nagaraṃ pāvisi. 
482309,110,1277,34,46,1,94,11,"Tassa taṃ rathavarattaṃ yathānaddhameva rājaṅgaṇe ṭhapayiṃsu, so rattibhāge deve vassante tinto. "
482310,110,1277,47,54,1,73,7,Uparipāsādato koleyyakasunakhā otaritvā tassa cammañca naddhiñca khādiṃsu. 
482311,110,1277,55,72,1,106,12,"Punadivase rañño ārocesuṃ‘‘ deva, niddhamanamukhena sunakhā pavisitvā rathassa cammañca naddhiñca khādiṃsū’’ ti. "
482312,110,1277,73,85,1,68,8,Rājā sunakhānaṃ kujjhitvā‘‘ diṭṭhadiṭṭhaṭṭhāne sunakhe ghātethā’’ ti āha. 
482313,110,1277,86,91,1,45,5,Tato paṭṭhāya sunakhānaṃ mahābyasanaṃ udapādi. 
482314,110,1277,92,101,1,90,9,Te diṭṭhidiṭṭhaṭṭhāne ghātiyamānā palāyitvā susānaṃ gantvā bodhisattassa santikaṃ agamaṃsu. 
482315,110,1278,2,16,1,62,10,"Bodhisatto ‘ tumhe bahū sannipatitā, kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti pucchi. "
482316,110,1278,17,45,1,153,21,"Te‘‘ antepure kira rathassa cammañca naddhi ca sunakhehi khāditā’ ti kuddho rājā sunakhavadhaṃ āṇāpesi, bahū sunakhā vinassanti, mahābhayaṃ uppannan’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
482317,110,1278,46,61,1,123,12,"Bodhisatto cintesi‘‘ ārakkhaṭṭhāne bahi sunakhānaṃ okāso natthi, antorājanivesane koleyyakasunakhānameva taṃ kammaṃ bhavissati. "
482318,110,1278,62,83,1,130,17,"Idāni pana corānaṃ kiñci bhayaṃ natthi, acorā maraṇaṃ labhanti, yaṃnūnāhaṃ core rañño dassetvā ñātisaṅghassa jīvitadānaṃ dadeyyan’’ ti. "
482319,110,1278,84,133,1,261,37,"So ñātake samassāsetvā‘‘ tumhe mā bhāyittha, ahaṃ vo abhayaṃ āharissāmi, yāva rājānaṃ passāmi, tāva idheva hothā’’ ti pāramiyo āvajjetvā mettābhāvanaṃ purecārikaṃ katvā‘‘ mayhaṃ upari leḍḍuṃ vā muggaraṃ vā mā koci khipituṃ ussahī’’ ti adhiṭṭhāya ekakova antonagaraṃ pāvisi. "
482320,110,1278,134,142,1,56,8,Atha naṃ disvā ekasattopi kujjhitvā olokento nāma nāhosi. 
482321,110,1278,143,150,1,59,7,Rājāpi sunakhavadhaṃ āṇāpetvā sayaṃ vinicchaye nisinno hoti. 
482322,110,1278,151,159,1,68,8,Bodhisatto tattheva gantvā pakkhanditvā rañño āsanassa heṭṭhā pāvisi. 
482323,110,1278,160,169,1,54,8,"Atha naṃ rājapurisā nīharituṃ āraddhā, rājā pana vāresi. "
482324,110,1279,2,20,1,99,13,"So thokaṃ vissamitvā heṭṭhāsanā nikkhamitvā rājānaṃ vanditvā‘‘ deva, tumhe kukkure mārāpethā’’ ti pucchi."
482325,110,1279,21,30,1,18,3,"‘‘ Āma, mārāpemahan’’ ti ."
482326,110,1279,31,40,1,28,5,‘‘ Ko nesaṃ aparādho narindā’’ ti?
482327,110,1279,41,52,1,50,6,‘‘ Rathassa me parivāracammañca naddhiñca khādiṃsū’’ ti.
482328,110,1279,53,63,1,25,5,"‘‘ Ye khādiṃsu, te jānāthā’’ ti?"
482329,110,1279,64,71,1,12,3,‘‘ Na jānāmā’’ ti.
482330,110,1279,72,91,1,96,12,"‘‘‘ Ime nāma cammakhādakacorā’ ti tathato ajānitvā diṭṭhadiṭṭhaṭṭhāneyeva mārāpanaṃ na yuttaṃ, devā’’ ti."
482331,110,1279,92,108,1,92,10,‘‘ Rathacammassa kukkurehi khāditattā‘ diṭṭhadiṭṭhe sabbeva mārethā’ ti sunakhavadhaṃ āṇāpesin’’ ti.
482332,110,1279,109,126,1,78,12,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana vo manussā sabbeva kukkure mārenti, udāhu maraṇaṃ alabhantāpi atthī’’ ti?"
482333,110,1279,127,140,1,52,8,"‘‘ Atthi, amhākaṃ ghare koleyyakā maraṇaṃ na labhantī’’ ti. "
482334,110,1279,141,176,1,191,24,"Mahārāja idāneva tumhe‘‘ rathacammassa kukkurehi khāditattā‘ diṭṭhadiṭṭhe sabbeva mārethā’ ti sunakhavadhaṃ āṇāpesin’’ ti avocuttha, idāni pana‘‘ amhākaṃ ghare koleyyakā maraṇaṃ na labhantī’’ ti vadetha."
482335,110,1279,177,223,1,290,35,"‘‘ Nanu evaṃ sante tumhe chandādivasena agatigamanaṃ gacchatha, agatigamanañca nāma na yuttaṃ, na ca rājadhammo, raññā nāma kāraṇagavesakena tulāsadisena bhavituṃ vaṭṭati, idāni ca koleyyakā maraṇaṃ na labhanti, dubbalasunakhāva labhanti, evaṃ sante nāyaṃ sabbasunakhaghaccā, dubbalaghātikā nāmesā’’ ti. "
482336,110,1279,224,248,1,133,18,"Evañca pana vatvā mahāsatto madhurassaraṃ nicchāretvā‘‘ mahārāja, yaṃ tumhe karotha, nāyaṃ dhammo’’ ti rañño dhammaṃ desento imaṃ gāthamāha– "
482337,110,1280,2,4,1,0,0,22.
482338,110,1281,2,12,1,56,7,"‘ ‘ Ye kukkurā rājakulamhi vaddhā, koleyyakā vaṇṇabalūpapannā; "
482339,110,1282,2,14,1,67,9,"Teme na vajjhā mayamasma vajjhā, nāyaṃ saghaccā dubbalaghātikāyan’’ ti. "
482340,110,1283,2,8,1,30,5,Tattha ye {kukkurā}ti ye sunakhā. 
482341,110,1283,9,58,1,199,25,"Yathā hi dhāruṇhopi passāvo‘‘ pūtimuttan’’ ti, tadahujātopi siṅgālo‘‘ jarasiṅgālo’’ ti, komalāpi galocilatā‘‘ pūtilatā’’ ti, suvaṇṇavaṇṇopi kāyo‘‘ pūtikāyo’’ ti vuccati, evamevaṃ vassasatikopi sunakho‘‘ kukkuro’’ ti vuccati. "
482342,110,1283,59,70,1,56,7,Tasmā mahallakā kāyabalūpapannāpi te‘‘ kukkurā’’ tveva vuttā. 
482343,110,1283,71,74,1,17,2,{Vaddhā}ti vaḍḍhitā. 
482344,110,1283,75,81,1,44,5,{Koleyyakā}ti rājakule jātā sambhūtā saṃvaḍḍhā. 
482345,110,1283,82,89,1,60,6,{Vaṇṇabalūpapannā}ti sarīravaṇṇena ceva kāyabalena ca sampannā. 
482346,110,1283,90,100,1,52,9,Teme na {vajjhā}ti te ime sassāmikā sārakkhā na vajjhā. 
482347,110,1283,101,110,1,60,8,Mayamasma {vajjhā}ti assāmikā anārakkhā mayaṃ vajjhā nāma jātā. 
482348,110,1283,111,122,1,64,10,Nāyaṃ {saghaccā}ti evaṃ sante ayaṃ avisesena saghaccā nāma na hoti. 
482349,110,1283,123,133,1,80,9,Dubbalaghātikāyan ti ayaṃ pana dubbalānaṃyeva ghātanato dubbalaghātikā nāma hoti. 
482350,110,1283,134,141,1,39,6,"Rājūhi nāma corā niggaṇhitabbā, no acorā. "
482351,110,1283,142,152,1,60,9,"Idha pana corānaṃ kiñci bhayaṃ natthi, acorā maraṇaṃ labhanti. "
482352,110,1283,153,162,1,54,8,"Aho imasmiṃ loke ayuttaṃ vattati, aho adhammo vattatīti. "
482353,110,1284,2,8,1,36,5,Rājā bodhisattassa vacaraṃ sutvā āha–
482354,110,1284,9,23,1,56,8,"‘‘ jānāsi tvaṃ, paṇḍita, asukehi nāma rathacammaṃ khāditan’’ ti?"
482355,110,1284,24,32,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, jānāmī’’ ti."
482356,110,1284,33,40,1,16,3,‘‘ Kehi khāditan’’ ti?
482357,110,1284,41,50,1,46,5,‘‘ Tumhākaṃ gehe vasanakehi koleyyakasunakhehī’’ ti.
482358,110,1284,51,60,1,37,5,‘‘ Kathaṃ tehi khāditabhāvo jānitabbo’’ ti?
482359,110,1284,61,70,1,36,5,‘‘ Ahaṃ tehi khāditabhāvaṃ dassesāmī’’ ti.
482360,110,1284,71,78,1,18,3,‘‘ Dassehi paṇḍitā’’ ti.
482361,110,1284,79,93,1,87,10,‘‘ Tumhākaṃ ghare koleyyakasunakhe āharāpetvā thokaṃ takkañca dabbatiṇāni ca āharāpethā’’ ti. 
482362,110,1284,94,97,1,16,3,Rājā tathā akāsi. 
482363,110,1284,98,114,1,77,12,Atha naṃ mahāsatto‘‘ imāni tiṇāni takkena maddāpetvā ete sunakhe pāyethā’’ ti āha. 
482364,110,1284,115,126,1,67,10,"Rājā tathā katvā pāyāpesi, pītā pītā sunakhā saddhiṃ cammehi vamiṃsu. "
482365,110,1284,127,141,1,88,10,Rājā‘‘ sabbaññubuddhassa byākaraṇaṃ viyā’’ ti tuṭṭho bodhisattassa setacchattena pūjaṃ akāsi. 
482366,110,1284,142,189,1,241,27,"Bodhisatto‘‘ dhammaṃ cara, mahārāja, mātāpitūsu khattiyā’’ tiādīhi( jā.2.17.39) tesakuṇajātake āgatāhi dasahi dhammacariyagāthāhi rañño dhammaṃ desetvā‘‘ mahārāja, ito paṭṭhāya appamatto hohī’’ ti rājānaṃ pañcasu sīlesu patiṭṭhāpetvā setacchattaṃ raññova paṭiadāsi. "
482367,110,1285,2,29,1,243,26,Rājā mahāsattassa dhammakathaṃ sutvā sabbasattānaṃ abhayaṃ datvā bodhisattaṃ ādiṃ katvā sabbasunakhānaṃ attano bhojanasadisameva niccabhattaṃ paṭṭhapetvā bodhisattassa ovāde ṭhito yāvatāyukaṃ dānādīni puññāni katvā kālaṃ katvā devaloke uppajji. 
482368,110,1285,30,34,1,39,4,Kukkurovādo dasa vassasahassāni pavatti. 
482369,110,1285,35,40,1,48,5,Bodhisattopi yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
482370,110,1286,2,27,1,149,18,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, tathāgato idāneva ñātakānaṃ atthaṃ carati, pubbepi cariyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
482371,110,1286,28,46,1,88,12,"‘‘ tadā rājā ānando ahosi, avasesā parisā buddhaparisā, kukkurapaṇḍito pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482372,110,1287,2,4,1,27,2,Kukkurajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
482373,110,1289,2,7,1,24,2,[ 23]3. Bhojājānīyajātakavaṇṇanā 
482374,110,1290,2,16,1,97,12,Api passena {semāno}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ossaṭṭhavīriyaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482375,110,1290,17,43,1,148,20,"Tasmiñhi samaye satthā taṃ bhikkhuṃ āmantetvā‘‘ bhikkhu, pubbe paṇḍitā anāyatanepi vīriyaṃ akaṃsu, pahāraṃ laddhāpi neva ossajiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
482376,110,1291,2,15,1,140,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto bhojājānīyasindhavakule nibbatto sabbālaṅkārasampanno bārāṇasirañño maṅgalasso ahosi. 
482377,110,1291,16,35,1,290,17,"So satasahassagghanikāya suvaṇṇapātiyaṃyeva nānaggarasasampannaṃ tivassikagandhasālibhojanaṃ bhuñjati, cātujjātikagandhūpalittāyameva bhūmiyaṃ tiṭṭhati, taṃ ṭhānaṃ rattakambalasāṇiparikkhittaṃ upari suvaṇṇatārakakhacitacelavitānaṃ samosaritagandhadāmamālādāmaṃ avijahitagandhatelapadīpaṃ hoti. "
482378,110,1291,36,42,1,49,6,Bārāṇasirajjaṃ pana apatthentā rājāno nāma natthi. 
482379,110,1291,43,64,1,115,16,"Ekaṃ samayaṃ satta rājāno bārāṇasiṃ parikkhipitvā‘‘ amhākaṃ rajjaṃ vā detu, yuddhaṃ vā’’ ti bārāṇasirañño paṇṇaṃ pesesuṃ. "
482380,110,1291,65,82,1,80,12,"Rājā amacce sannipātetvā taṃ pavattiṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ idāni kiṃ karoma, tātā’’ ti pucchi."
482381,110,1291,83,109,1,130,18,"‘‘ Deva, tumhehi tāva āditova yuddhāya na gantabbaṃ, asukaṃ nāma assārohaṃ pesetvā yuddhaṃ kāretha, tasmiṃ asakkonte pacchā jānissāmā’’ ti. "
482382,110,1291,110,128,1,82,12,"Rājā taṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ sakkhissasi, tāta, sattahi rājūhi saddhiṃ yuddhaṃ kātun’’ ti āha."
482383,110,1291,129,149,1,119,13,"‘‘ Deva, sace bhojājānīyasindhavaṃ labhāmi, tiṭṭhantu satta rājāno, sakalajambudīpe rājūhipi saddhiṃ yujjhituṃ sakkhissāmī’’ ti."
482384,110,1291,150,170,1,82,13,"‘‘ Tāta, bhojājānīyasindhavo vā hotu añño vā, yaṃ icchasi, taṃ gahetvā yuddhaṃ karohī’’ ti. "
482385,110,1292,2,69,1,543,59,"So ‘‘ sādhu, devā’’ ti rājānaṃ vanditvā pāsādā oruyha bhojājānīyasindhavaṃ āharāpetvā suvammitaṃ katvā attanāpi sabbasannāhasannaddho khaggaṃ bandhitvā sindhavapiṭṭhivaragato nagarā nikkhamma vijjulatā viya caramāno paṭhamaṃ balakoṭṭhakaṃ bhinditvā ekaṃ rājānaṃ jīvaggāhameva gahetvā āgantvā nagare balassa niyyādetvā puna gantvā dutiyaṃ balakoṭṭhakaṃ bhinditvā tathā tatiyanti evaṃ pañca rājāno jīvaggāhaṃ gahetvā chaṭṭhaṃ balakoṭṭhakaṃ bhinditvā chaṭṭhassa rañño gahitakāle bhojājānīyo pahāraṃ labhati, lohitaṃ paggharati, vedanā balavatiyo vattanti. "
482386,110,1292,70,84,1,133,14,Assāroho tassa pahaṭabhāvaṃ ñatvā bhojājānīyasindhavaṃ rājadvāre nipajjāpetvā sannāhaṃ sithilaṃ katvā aññaṃ assaṃ sannayhituṃ āraddho. 
482387,110,1292,85,174,1,623,73,"Bodhisatto mahāphāsukapassena nipannova akkhīni ummiletvā assārohaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ aññaṃ assaṃ sannayhati, ayañca asso sattamaṃ balakoṭṭhakaṃ bhinditvā sattamaṃ rājānaṃ gaṇhituṃ na sakkhissati, mayā katakammañca nassissati, appaṭisamo assārohopi nassissati, rājāpi parahatthaṃ gamissati, ṭhapetvā maṃ añño asso sattamaṃ balakoṭṭhakaṃ bhinditvā sattamaṃ rājānaṃ gahetuṃ samattho nāma natthī’’ ti nipannakova assārohaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ samma assāroha, sattamaṃ balakoṭṭhakaṃ bhinditvā sattamaṃ rājānaṃ gahetuṃ samattho ṭhapetvā maṃ añño asso nāma natthi, nāhaṃ mayā katakammaṃ nāsessāmi, mamaññeva uṭṭhāpetvā sannayhāhī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
