482478,110,1327,2,35,1,222,25,"Bodhisatto ‘‘ esa attano sindhavatāya jigucchanto ettha nhāyituṃ na icchati, imaṃ aññatitthe nhāpetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti tassa āsayaṃ ñatvā‘‘ bho assagopaka, sappimadhuphāṇitādibhisaṅkhatapāyāsampi tāva punappunaṃ bhuñjantassa titti hoti. "
482479,110,1327,36,60,1,118,20,"Ayaṃ asso bahū vāre idha titthe nhāto, aññampi tāva naṃ titthaṃ otāretvā nhāpetha ca pāyetha cā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
