482498,110,1334,2,4,1,27,2,Titthajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
482499,110,1336,2,7,1,24,2,[ 26]6. Mahiḷāmukhajātakavaṇṇanā 
482500,110,1337,2,13,1,85,10,Purāṇacorāna vaco {nisammā}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482501,110,1337,14,19,1,62,5,Devadatto ajātasattukumāraṃ pasādetvā lābhasakkāraṃ nipphādesi. 
482502,110,1337,20,33,1,143,12,Ajātasattukumāro devadattassa gayāsīse vihāraṃ kāretvā nānaggarasehi tivassikagandhasālibhojanassa divase divase pañca thālipākasatāni abhihari. 
482503,110,1337,34,46,1,101,11,"Lābhasakkāraṃ nissāya devadattassa parivāro mahanto jāto, devadatto parivārena saddhiṃ vihāreyeva hoti. "
482504,110,1337,47,52,1,39,5,Tena samayena rājagahavāsikā dve sahāyā. 
482505,110,1337,53,61,1,50,7,"Tesu eko satthu santike pabbajito, eko devadattassa. "
482506,110,1337,62,72,1,74,9,"Te aññamaññaṃ tasmiṃ tasmiṃ ṭhānepi passanti, vihāraṃ gantvāpi passantiyeva. "
482507,110,1338,2,8,1,47,5,Athekadivasaṃ devadattassa nissitako itaraṃ āha–
482508,110,1338,9,56,1,322,38,"‘‘ āvuso, kiṃ tvaṃ devasikaṃ sedehi muccamānehi piṇḍāya carasi, devadatto gayāsīsavihāre nisīditvāva nānaggarasehi subhojanaṃ bhuñjati, evarūpo upāyo natthi, kiṃ tvaṃ dukkhaṃ anubhosi, kiṃ te pātova gayāsīsaṃ āgantvā sauttaribhaṅgaṃ yāguṃ pivitvā aṭṭhārasavidhaṃ khajjakaṃ khāditvā nānaggarasehi subhojanaṃ bhuñjituṃ na vaṭṭatī’’ ti? "
482509,110,1338,57,70,1,110,13,So punappunaṃ vuccamāno gantukāmo hutvā tato paṭṭhāya gayāsīsaṃ gantvā bhuñjitvā kālasseva veḷuvanaṃ āgacchati. 
482510,110,1338,71,92,1,123,15,"So sabbakālaṃ paṭicchādetuṃ nāsakkhi,‘‘ gayāsīsaṃ gantvā devadattassa paṭṭhapitaṃ bhattaṃ bhuñjatī’’ ti na cirasseva pākaṭo jāto . "
482511,110,1338,93,112,1,93,13,"Atha naṃ sahāyā pucchiṃsu‘‘ saccaṃ kira, tvaṃ āvuso, devadattassa paṭṭhapitaṃ bhattaṃ bhuñjasī’’ ti."
482512,110,1338,113,120,1,13,3,‘‘ Ko evamāhā’’ ti?
482513,110,1338,121,130,1,20,5,‘‘ Asuko ca asuko cā’’ ti.
482514,110,1338,131,153,1,99,16,"‘‘ Saccaṃ ahaṃ āvuso gayāsīsaṃ gantvā bhuñjāmi, na pana me devadatto bhattaṃ deti, aññe manussā dentī’’ ti."
482515,110,1338,154,193,1,280,32,"‘‘ Āvuso, devadatto buddhānaṃ paṭikaṇṭako dussīlo ajātasattuṃ pasādetvā adhammena attano lābhasakkāraṃ uppādesi, tvaṃ evarūpe niyyānike buddhasāsane pabbajitvā devadattassa adhammena uppannaṃ bhojanaṃ bhuñjasi, ehi taṃ satthu santikaṃ nessāmā’’ ti taṃ bhikkhuṃ ādāya dhammasabhaṃ āgamiṃsu. "
482516,110,1339,2,18,1,77,10,"Satthā disvāva‘‘ kiṃ, bhikkhave, etaṃ bhikkhuṃ anicchantaññeva ādāya āgatatthā’’ ti?"
482517,110,1339,19,37,1,104,13,"‘‘ Āma bhante, ayaṃ bhikkhu tumhākaṃ santike pabbajitvā devadattassa adhammena uppannaṃ bhojanaṃ bhuñjatī’’ ti."
482518,110,1339,38,52,1,77,10,‘‘ Saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu devadattassa adhammena uppannaṃ bhojanaṃ bhuñjasī’’ ti?
482519,110,1339,53,71,1,70,11,"‘‘ Na bhante, devadatto mayhaṃ deti, aññe manussā denti, tamahaṃ bhuñjāmī’’ ti. "
482520,110,1339,72,108,1,236,29,"Satthā‘‘ mā bhikkhu ettha parihāraṃ kari, devadatto anācāro dussīlo, kathañhi nāma tvaṃ idha pabbajitvā mama sāsanaṃ bhajantoyeva devadattassa bhattaṃ bhuñjasi, niccakālampi bhajanasīlakova tvaṃ diṭṭhadiṭṭheyeva bhajasī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
482521,110,1340,2,11,1,74,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa amacco ahosi. 
482522,110,1340,12,25,1,87,11,"Tadā rañño mahiḷāmukho nāma maṅgalahatthī ahosi sīlavā ācārasampanno, na kañci viheṭheti. "
482523,110,1340,26,85,1,440,48,"Athekadivasaṃ tassa sālāya samīpe rattibhāgasamanantare corā āgantvā tassa avidūre nisinnā coramantaṃ mantayiṃsu‘‘ evaṃ ummaṅgo bhinditabbo, evaṃ sandhicchedakammaṃ kattabbaṃ, ummaṅgañca sandhicchedañca maggasadisaṃ titthasadisaṃ nijjaṭaṃ niggumbaṃ katvā bhaṇḍaṃ harituṃ vaṭṭati, harantena māretvāva haritabbaṃ, evaṃ uṭṭhātuṃ samattho nāma na bhavissati, corena ca nāma sīlācārayuttena na bhavitabbaṃ, kakkhaḷena pharusena sāhasikena bhavitabban’’ ti. "
482524,110,1340,86,91,1,46,5,Evaṃ mantetvā aññamaññaṃ uggaṇhāpetvā agamaṃsu. 
482525,110,1340,92,101,1,81,9,Eteneva upāyena punadivasepi punadivasepīti bahū divase tattha āgantvā mantayiṃsu. 
482526,110,1340,102,128,1,128,18,So tesaṃ vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ te maṃ sikkhāpentī’’ ti saññāya‘‘ idāni mayā kakkhaḷena pharusena sāhasikena bhavitabban’’ ti tathārūpova ahosi. 
482527,110,1340,129,137,1,68,8,Pātova āgataṃ hatthigopakaṃ soṇḍāya gahetvā bhūmiyaṃ pothetvā māresi. 
482528,110,1340,138,144,1,53,6,Aparampi tathā aparampi tathāti āgatāgataṃ māretiyeva.
