482564,110,1351,23,30,1,54,7,Tesu eko pabbajitvā devasikaṃ itarassa gharaṃ gacchati. 
482565,110,1351,31,54,1,185,22,"So tassa bhikkhaṃ datvā sayampi bhuñjitvā teneva saddhiṃ vihāraṃ gantvā yāva sūriyatthaṅgamanā ālāpasallāpena nisīditvā nagaraṃ pavisati, itaropi naṃ yāva nagaradvārā anugantvā nivattati. "
482566,110,1351,55,62,1,46,7,So tesaṃ vissāso bhikkhūnaṃ antare pākaṭo jāto. 
482567,110,1351,63,70,1,75,7,Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū tesaṃ vissāsakathaṃ kathentā dhammasabhāyaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
482568,110,1351,71,99,1,108,16,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchi, te‘‘ imāya nāma, bhante’’ ti kathayiṃsu. "
482569,110,1351,100,120,1,92,13,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva ime vissāsikā, pubbepi vissāsikāyeva ahesun’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
