482571,110,1352,12,22,1,106,10,Tadā eko kukkuro maṅgalahatthisālaṃ gantvā maṅgalahatthissa bhuñjanaṭṭhāne patitāni bhattasitthāni khādati. 
482572,110,1352,23,39,1,127,15,"So teneva bhojanena saṃvaddhamāno maṅgalahatthissa vissāsiko jāto hatthisseva santike bhuñjati, ubhopi vinā vattituṃ na sakkonti. "
482573,110,1352,40,52,1,86,11,"So hatthī naṃ soṇḍāya gahetvā aparāparaṃ karonto kīḷati, ukkhipitvā kumbhe patiṭṭhāpeti. "
482574,110,1352,53,65,1,99,12,Athekadivasaṃ eko gāmikamanusso hatthigopakassa mūlaṃ datvā taṃ kukkuraṃ ādāya attano gāmaṃ agamāsi. 
482575,110,1352,66,78,1,76,12,Tato paṭṭhāya so hatthī kukkuraṃ apassanto neva khādati na pivati na nhāyati. 
482576,110,1352,79,82,1,24,3,Tamatthaṃ rañño ārocesuṃ. 
