482592,110,1357,36,44,1,54,7,Na {kuse}ti khādanatthāya dinnāni tiṇānipi nālaṃ gahetuṃ. 
482593,110,1357,45,52,1,53,7,Na ghaṃsitun ti nhāpiyamāno sarīrampi ghaṃsituṃ nālaṃ. 
482594,110,1357,53,78,1,145,20,"Evaṃ yaṃ yaṃ so hatthī kātuṃ na samattho, taṃ taṃ sabbaṃ rañño ārocetvā tassa asamatthabhāve attanā sallakkhitakāraṇaṃ ārocento‘‘ maññāmī’’ tiādimāha. "
482595,110,1358,2,16,1,61,10,Rājā tassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ idāni kiṃ kātabbaṃ paṇḍitā’’ ti pucchi.
482596,110,1358,17,48,1,155,23,"‘‘‘ Amhākaṃ kira maṅgalahatthissa sahāyaṃ sunakhaṃ eko manusso gahetvā gato, yassa ghare taṃ sunakhaṃ passanti, tassa ayaṃ nāma daṇḍo’ ti bheriṃ carāpetha devā’’ ti. "
482597,110,1358,49,52,1,17,3,Rājā tathā kāresi. 
482598,110,1358,53,66,1,99,12,"Taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā so puriso sunakhaṃ vissajjesi, sunakho vegenāgantvā hatthissa santikameva agamāsi. "
482599,110,1358,67,82,1,113,15,Hatthī taṃ soṇḍāya gahetvā kumbhe ṭhapetvā roditvā paridevitvā kumbhā otāretvā tena bhutte pacchā attanāpi bhuñji.
482600,110,1358,83,96,1,74,9,‘‘ Tiracchānagatassa āsayaṃ jānātī’’ ti rājā bodhisattassa mahantaṃ yasaṃ adāsi. 
482601,110,1359,2,28,1,164,18,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, ime idāneva vissāsikā, pubbepi vissāsikāyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā catusaccakathāya vinivaṭṭetvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi. "
482602,110,1359,29,35,1,65,6,Idaṃ catusaccakathāya vinivaṭṭanaṃ nāma sabbajātakesupi atthiyeva. 
