482649,110,1377,2,7,1,18,2,[ 29]9. Kaṇhajātakavaṇṇanā 
482650,110,1378,2,14,1,89,12,Yato yato garu dhuran ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto yamakapāṭihāriyaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482651,110,1378,15,32,1,72,7,Taṃ saddhiṃ devorohaṇena terasakanipāte sarabhamigajātake( jā.1.13.134 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
482652,110,1378,33,95,1,451,50,"Sammāsambuddhe pana yamakapāṭihāriyaṃ katvā devaloke temāsaṃ vasitvā mahāpavāraṇāya saṅkassanagaradvāre oruyha mahantena parivārena jetavanaṃ paviṭṭhe bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitvā‘‘ āvuso, tathāgato nāma asamadhuro, tathāgatena vuḷhadhuraṃ añño vahituṃ samattho nāma natthi, cha satthāro‘ mayameva pāṭihāriyaṃ karissāma, mayameva pāṭihāriyaṃ karissāmā’ ti vatvā ekampi pāṭihāriyaṃ na akaṃsu, aho satthā asamadhuro’’ ti satthu guṇakathaṃ kathentā nisīdiṃsu. "
482653,110,1378,96,113,1,73,10,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchi."
482654,110,1378,114,131,1,72,10,"‘‘ Mayaṃ, bhante, na aññāya kathāya, evarūpāya nāma tumhākameva guṇakathāyā’’ ti. "
482655,110,1378,132,157,1,148,19,"Satthā‘‘ bhikkhave, idāni mayā vuḷhadhuraṃ ko vahissati, pubbe tiracchānayoniyaṃ nibbattopi ahaṃ attanā samadhuraṃ kañci nālatthan’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
482656,110,1379,2,12,1,83,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto goyoniyaṃ paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
482657,110,1379,13,25,1,114,12,Atha naṃ sāmikā taruṇavacchakakāleyeva ekissā mahallikāya ghare vasitvā tassā nivāsavetanato paricchinditvā adaṃsu. 
482658,110,1379,26,33,1,65,7,Sā taṃ yāgubhattādīhi paṭijaggamānā puttaṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā vaḍḍhesi. 
482659,110,1379,34,43,1,39,5,So‘‘ ayyikākāḷako’’ tveva nāmaṃ paññāyittha. 
482660,110,1379,44,54,1,80,9,"Vayappatto ca añjanavaṇṇo hutvā gāmagoṇehi saddhiṃ carati, sīlācārasampanno ahosi. "
482661,110,1379,55,68,1,105,11,"Gāmadārakā siṅgesupi kaṇṇesupi galepi gahetvā olambanti, naṅguṭṭhepi gahetvā kīḷanti, piṭṭhiyampi nisīdanti. "
482662,110,1379,69,93,1,138,18,"So ekadivasaṃ cintesi‘‘ mayhaṃ mātā duggatā, maṃ puttaṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā dukkhena posesi, yaṃnūnāhaṃ bhatiṃ katvā imaṃ duggatabhāvato moceyyan’’ ti. "
482663,110,1379,94,100,1,42,6,So tato paṭṭhāya bhatiṃ upadhārento carati. 
482664,110,1380,2,26,1,205,22,"Athekadivasaṃ eko satthavāhaputto pañcahi sakaṭasatehi visamatitthaṃ sampatto, tassa goṇā sakaṭāni uttāretuṃ na sakkonti, pañcasu sakaṭasatesu goṇā yugaparamparāya yojitā ekampi sakaṭaṃ uttāretuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu. "
482665,110,1380,27,33,1,52,6,Bodhisattopi gāmagoṇehi saddhiṃ tattha samīpe carati. 
482666,110,1380,34,96,1,336,47,"Satthavāhaputtopi gosuttavittako, so‘‘ atthi nu kho etesaṃ gunnaṃ antare imāni sakaṭāni uttāretuṃ samattho usabhājānīyo’’ ti upadhārayamāno bodhisattaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ ājānīyo sakkhissati mayhaṃ sakaṭāni uttāretuṃ, ko nu kho assa sāmiko’’ ti gopālake pucchi‘‘ ko nu kho bho imassa sāmiko, ahaṃ imaṃ sakaṭe yojetvā sakaṭesu uttāritesu vetanaṃ dassāmī’’ ti. "
482667,110,1380,97,113,1,67,11,"Te āhaṃsu‘‘ gahetvā naṃ yojetha, natthi imassa imasmiṃ ṭhāne sāmiko’’ ti. "
482668,110,1380,114,123,1,63,8,So naṃ nāsāya rajjukena bandhitvā ākaḍḍhento cāletumpi nāsakkhi. 
482669,110,1380,124,137,1,57,8,Bodhisatto kira‘‘ bhatiyā kathitāya gamissāmī’’ ti na agamāsi. 
482670,110,1380,138,162,1,151,19,"Satthavāhaputto tassādhippāyaṃ ñatvā‘‘ sāmi, tayā pañcasu sakaṭasatesu uttāritesu ekekassa sakaṭassa dve dve kahāpaṇe bhatiṃ katvā sahassaṃ dassāmī’’ ti āha. "
482671,110,1380,163,167,1,32,4,Tadā bodhisatto sayameva agamāsi. 
482672,110,1380,168,173,1,38,5,Atha naṃ purisā purimasakaṭesu yojesuṃ. 
482673,110,1380,174,180,1,50,6,Atha naṃ ekavegeneva ukkhipitvā thale patiṭṭhāpesi. 
482674,110,1380,181,184,1,34,3,Etenupāyena sabbasakaṭāni uttāresi. 
482675,110,1381,2,13,1,93,11,Satthavāhaputto ekekassa sakaṭassa ekekaṃ katvā pañcasatāni bhaṇḍikaṃ katvā tassa gale bandhi. 
482676,110,1381,14,37,1,136,18,"So‘‘ ayaṃ mayhaṃ yathāparicchinnaṃ bhatiṃ na deti, na dānissa gantuṃ dassāmī’’ ti gantvā sabbapurimasakaṭassa purato maggaṃ nivāretvā aṭṭhāsi. "
482677,110,1381,38,43,1,45,5,Apanetuṃ vāyamantāpi naṃ apanetuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu. 
482678,110,1381,44,73,1,164,21,Satthavāhaputto‘‘ jānāti maññe esa attano bhatiyā ūnabhāvan’’ ti ekekasmiṃ sakaṭe dve dve katvā sahassabhaṇḍikaṃ bandhitvā‘‘ ayaṃ te sakaṭuttaraṇabhatī’’ ti gīvāyaṃ laggesi. 
482679,110,1381,74,80,1,47,6,So sahassabhaṇḍikaṃ ādāya mātu santikaṃ agamāsi. 
482680,110,1381,81,95,1,80,9,Gāmadārakā‘‘ kiṃ nāmetaṃ ayyikākāḷakassa gale’’ ti bodhisattassa santikaṃ āgacchanti. 
482681,110,1381,96,104,1,56,8,So te anubandhitvā dūratova palāpento mātu santikaṃ gato. 
482682,110,1381,105,113,1,80,8,Pañcannaṃ pana sakaṭasatānaṃ uttāritattā rattehi akkhīhi kilantarūpo paññāyittha. 
482683,110,1381,114,168,1,362,43,"Ayyikā tassa gīvāya sahassatthavikaṃ disvā‘‘ tāta, ayaṃ te kahaṃ laddhā’’ ti gopālakadārake pucchitvā tamatthaṃ sutvā‘‘ tāta, kiṃ ahaṃ tayā laddhabhatiyā jīvitukāmā, kiṃkāraṇā evarūpaṃ dukkhaṃ anubhosī’’ ti vatvā bodhisattaṃ uṇhodakena nhāpetvā sakalasarīraṃ telena makkhetvā pānīyaṃ pāyetvā sappāyaṃ bhojanaṃ bhojetvā jīvitapariyosāne saddhiṃ bodhisattena yathākammaṃ gatā. "
482684,110,1382,2,28,1,163,19,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, tathāgato idāneva asamadhuro, pubbepi asamadhuroyevā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā abhisambuddho hutvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
482685,110,1383,2,4,1,0,0,29.
482686,110,1384,2,12,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Yato yato garu dhuraṃ, yato gambhīravattanī; "
482687,110,1385,2,13,1,51,8,"Tadāssu kaṇhaṃ yuñjanti, svāssu taṃ vahate dhuran’’ ti. "
482688,110,1386,2,21,1,115,18,"Tattha yato yato garu dhuran ti yasmiṃ yasmiṃ ṭhāne dhuraṃ garu bhāriyaṃ hoti, aññe balibaddā ukkhipituṃ na sakkonti. "
482689,110,1386,22,43,1,163,17,"Yato {gambhīravattanī}ti vattanti etthāti vattanī, maggassetaṃ nāmaṃ, yasmiṃ ṭhāne udakacikkhallamahantatāya vā visamacchinnataṭabhāvena vā maggo gambhīro hotīti attho. "
482690,110,1386,44,57,1,80,10,"Tadāssu kaṇhaṃ {yuñjantī}ti ettha {assū}ti nipātamattaṃ, tadā kaṇhaṃ yuñjantīti attho. "
482691,110,1386,58,74,1,102,15,"Yadā dhurañca garu hoti maggo ca gambhīro, tadā aññe balibadde apanetvā kaṇhameva yojentīti vuttaṃ hoti. "
482692,110,1386,75,90,1,87,13,"Svāssu taṃ vahate dhuran ti etthāpi {assū}ti nipātamattameva, so taṃ dhuraṃ vahatīti attho. "
482693,110,1387,2,22,1,105,14,"Evaṃ bhagavā‘‘ tadā, bhikkhave, kaṇhova taṃ dhuraṃ vahatī’’ ti dassetvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
482694,110,1387,23,37,1,68,9,"‘‘ tadā mahallikā uppalavaṇṇā ahosi, ayyikākāḷako pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482695,110,1388,2,4,1,25,2,Kaṇhajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
482696,110,1390,2,7,1,19,2,[ 30]10. Munikajātakavaṇṇanā 
482697,110,1391,2,14,1,93,10,Mā munikassa {pihayī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto thullakumārikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482698,110,1391,15,30,1,57,5,Taṃ terasakanipāte cūḷanāradakassapajātake( jā.1.13.40 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
482699,110,1391,31,46,1,72,11,Satthā pana taṃ bhikkhuṃ‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchi.
482700,110,1391,47,55,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, bhante’’ ti."
482701,110,1391,56,63,1,14,3,‘‘ Kiṃ nissāyā’’ ti?
482702,110,1391,64,71,1,34,3,‘‘ Thullakumārikāpalobhanaṃ bhante’’ ti. 
482703,110,1391,72,95,1,149,18,"Satthā‘‘ bhikkhu esā tava anatthakārikā, pubbepi tvaṃ imissā vivāhadivase jīvitakkhayaṃ patvā mahājanassa uttaribhaṅgabhāvaṃ patto’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
482704,110,1392,2,27,1,176,20,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto ekasmiṃ gāmake ekassa kuṭumbikassa gehe goyoniyaṃ nibbatti‘‘ mahālohito’’ ti nāmena, kaniṭṭhabhātāpissa cūḷalohito nāma ahosi. "
482705,110,1392,28,36,1,58,8,Teyeva dve bhātike nissāya tasmiṃ kule kammadhuraṃ vattati. 
482706,110,1392,37,51,1,87,13,"Tasmiṃ pana kule ekā kumārikā atthi, taṃ eko nagaravāsī kulaputto attano puttassa vāresi. "
482707,110,1392,52,72,1,133,15,Tassā mātāpitaro‘‘ kumārikāya vivāhakāle āgatānaṃ pāhunakānaṃ uttaribhaṅgo bhavissatī’’ ti yāgubhattaṃ datvā munikaṃ nāma sūkaraṃ posesuṃ. 
482708,110,1392,73,111,1,215,30,"Taṃ disvā cūḷalohito bhātaraṃ pucchi‘‘ imasmiṃ kule kammadhuraṃ vattamānaṃ amhe dve bhātike nissāya vattati, ime pana amhākaṃ tiṇapalālādīneva denti, sūkaraṃ yāgubhattena posenti, kena nu kho kāraṇena esa etaṃ labhatī’’ ti. "
482709,110,1392,112,129,1,95,13,"Athassa bhātā‘‘ tāta cūḷalohita, mā tvaṃ etassa bhojanaṃ pihayi, ayaṃ sūkaro maraṇabhattaṃ bhuñjati. "
482710,110,1392,130,169,1,307,35,"Etissā hi kumārikāya vivāhakāle āgatānaṃ pāhunakānaṃ uttaribhaṅgo bhavissatīti ime etaṃ sūkaraṃ posenti, ito katipāhaccayena te manussā āgamissanti, atha naṃ sūkaraṃ pādesu gahetvā kaḍḍhentā heṭṭhāmañcato nīharitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā pāhunakānaṃ sūpabyañjanaṃ kariyamānaṃ passissasī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
482711,110,1393,2,4,1,0,0,30.
482712,110,1394,2,10,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Mā munikassa pihayi, āturannāni bhuñjati; "
482713,110,1395,2,11,1,48,6,"Appossukko bhusaṃ khāda, etaṃ dīghāyulakkhaṇan’’ ti. "
482714,110,1396,2,41,1,188,28,"Tattha mā munikassa {pihayī}ti munikassa bhojane pihaṃ mā uppādayi,‘‘ esa muniko subhojanaṃ bhuñjatī’’ ti mā munikassa pihayi,‘‘ kadā nu kho ahampi evaṃ sukhito bhaveyyan’’ ti mā munikabhāvaṃ patthayi. "
482715,110,1396,42,45,1,26,3,Ayañhi āturannāni bhuñjati. 
482716,110,1396,46,49,1,28,2,{Āturannānī}ti maraṇabhojanāni. 
482717,110,1396,50,63,1,84,11,Appossukko bhusaṃ {khādā}ti tassa bhojane nirussukko hutvā attanā laddhaṃ bhusaṃ khāda. 
482718,110,1396,64,70,1,53,6,Etaṃ dīghāyulakkhaṇan ti etaṃ dīghāyubhāvassa kāraṇaṃ. 
482719,110,1396,71,82,1,76,10,"Tato na cirasseva te manussā āgamiṃsu, munikaṃ ghātetvā nānappakārehi paciṃsu. "
482720,110,1396,83,97,1,51,8,"Bodhisatto cūḷalohitaṃ āha‘‘ diṭṭho te, tāta, muniko’’ ti. "
482721,110,1396,98,115,1,160,14,"Diṭṭhaṃ me, bhātika, munikassa bhojanaphalaṃ, etassa bhojanato sataguṇena sahassaguṇena amhākaṃ tiṇapalālabhusamattameva uttamañca anavajjañca dīghāyulakkhaṇañcāti. "
482722,110,1397,2,33,1,224,25,"Satthā ‘‘ evaṃ kho tvaṃ bhikkhu pubbepi imaṃ kumārikaṃ nissāya jīvitakkhayaṃ patvā mahājanassa uttaribhaṅgabhāvaṃ gato’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhito bhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhāsi. "
482723,110,1397,34,40,1,46,5,Satthā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi –
482724,110,1397,41,62,1,116,14,"‘‘ tadā munikasūkaro ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu ahosi, thullakumārikā esā eva, cūḷalohito ānando, mahālohito pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482725,110,1398,2,4,1,26,2,Munikajātakavaṇṇanā dasamā. 
482726,110,1399,2,4,1,19,2,Kuruṅgavaggo tatiyo. 
482727,110,1400,2,3,1,11,1,Tassuddānaṃ – 
482728,110,1401,2,7,1,44,4,"Kuruṅgaṃ kukkurañceva, bhojājānīyañca ājaññaṃ; "
482729,110,1402,2,7,1,50,4,"Titthaṃ mahiḷāmukhābhiṇhaṃ, nandikaṇhañca munikanti."
482730,110,1403,2,4,1,13,2,4 . Kulāvakavaggo
482731,110,1405,2,7,1,21,2,[ 31]1. Kulāvakajātakavaṇṇanā 
482732,110,1406,2,15,1,94,11,{Kulāvakā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aparissāvetvā pānīyaṃ pītaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482733,110,1406,16,39,1,181,19,Sāvatthito kira dve sahāyakā daharabhikkhū janapadaṃ gantvā ekasmiṃ phāsukaṭṭhāne yathājjhāsayaṃ vasitvā‘‘ sammāsambuddhaṃ passissāmā’’ ti puna tato nikkhamitvā jetavanābhimukhā pāyiṃsu. 
482734,110,1406,40,47,1,46,6,"Ekassa hatthe parissāvanaṃ atthi, ekassa natthi. "
482735,110,1406,48,53,1,40,5,Dvepi ekato pānīyaṃ parissāvetvā pivanti. 
482736,110,1406,54,58,1,28,4,Te ekadivasaṃ vivādaṃ akaṃsu. 
482737,110,1406,59,78,1,172,18,"Parissāvanasāmiko itarassa parissāvanaṃ adatvā sayameva pānīyaṃ parissāvetvā pivi, itaro pana parissāvanaṃ alabhitvā pipāsaṃ sandhāretuṃ asakkonto aparissāvetvā pānīyaṃ pivi. "
482738,110,1406,79,87,1,65,8,Te ubhopi anupubbena jetavanaṃ patvā satthāraṃ vanditvā nisīdiṃsu. 
482739,110,1406,88,100,1,60,8,Satthā sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ kathetvā‘‘ kuto āgatatthā’’ ti pucchi.
482740,110,1406,101,118,1,99,12,"‘‘ Bhante, mayaṃ kosalajanapade ekasmiṃ gāmake vasitvā tato nikkhamitvā tumhākaṃ dassanatthāya āgatā’’ ti."
482741,110,1406,119,129,1,34,6,‘‘ Kacci pana vo samaggā āgatatthā’’ ti? 
482742,110,1406,130,148,1,92,12,"Aparissāvanako āha‘‘ ayaṃ, bhante, antarāmagge mayā saddhiṃ vivādaṃ katvā parissāvanaṃ nādāsī’’ ti. "
482743,110,1406,149,165,1,70,10,"Itaropi āha‘‘ ayaṃ, bhante, aparissāvetvāva jānaṃ sapāṇakaṃ udakaṃ pivī’’ ti."
482744,110,1406,166,179,1,55,9,‘‘ Saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu jānaṃ sapāṇakaṃ udakaṃ pivī’’ ti?
482745,110,1406,180,190,1,39,5,"‘‘ Āma, bhante, aparissāvitaṃ udakaṃ pivinti . "
482746,110,1406,191,226,1,246,29,Satthā‘‘ bhikkhu pubbe paṇḍitā devanagare rajjaṃ kārentā yuddhaparājitā samuddapiṭṭhena palāyantā‘ issariyaṃ nissāya pāṇavadhaṃ na karissāmā’ ti tāva mahantaṃ yasaṃ pariccajitvā supaṇṇapotakānaṃ jīvitaṃ datvā rathaṃ nivattayiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. 
482747,110,1407,2,10,1,58,7,Atīte magadharaṭṭhe rājagahe eko māgadharājā rajjaṃ kāresi. 
482748,110,1407,11,28,1,148,16,"Tadā bodhisatto yathā etarahi sakko purimattabhāve magadharaṭṭhe macalagāmake nibbatti, evaṃ tasmiṃyeva macalagāmake mahākulassa putto hutvā nibbatti. "
482749,110,1407,29,39,1,54,6,Nāmaggahaṇadivase cassa‘‘ maghakumāro’’ tveva nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
482750,110,1407,40,49,1,40,5,So vayappatto‘‘ maghamāṇavo’’ ti paññāyittha. 
482751,110,1407,50,55,1,54,5,Athassa mātāpitaro samānajātikakulato dārikaṃ ānayiṃsu. 
482752,110,1407,56,65,1,63,8,"So puttadhītāhi vaḍḍhamāno dānapati ahosi, pañca sīlāni rakkhati. "
482753,110,1407,66,82,1,112,14,"Tasmiñca gāme tettiṃseva kulāni honti, tepi tettiṃsa kulā manussā ekadivasaṃ gāmamajjhe ṭhatvā gāmakammaṃ karonti. "
482754,110,1407,83,100,1,121,16,"Bodhisatto ṭhitaṭṭhāne pādehi paṃsuṃ viyūhitvā taṃ padesaṃ ramaṇīyaṃ katvā aṭṭhāsi, athañño eko āgantvā tasmiṃ ṭhāne ṭhito. "
482755,110,1407,101,111,1,67,9,"Bodhisatto aparaṃ ṭhānaṃ ramaṇīyaṃ katvā aṭṭhāsi, tatrāpi añño ṭhito. "
482756,110,1407,112,136,1,202,22,"Bodhisatto aparampi aparampīti sabbesampi ṭhitaṭṭhānaṃ ramaṇīyaṃ katvā aparena samayena tasmiṃ ṭhāne maṇḍapaṃ kāresi, maṇḍapampi apanetvā sālaṃ kāresi, tattha phalakāsanāni santharitvā pānīyacāṭiṃ ṭhapesi. "
482757,110,1408,2,9,1,68,7,Aparena samayena tepi tettiṃsajanā bodhisattena samānacchandā ahesuṃ. 
482758,110,1408,10,22,1,94,12,Te bodhisatto pañcasu sīlesu patiṭṭhāpetvā tato paṭṭhāya tehi saddhiṃ puññāni karonto vicarati. 
482759,110,1408,23,59,1,276,29,"Tepi teneva saddhiṃ puññāni karontā kālasseva vuṭṭhāya vāsipharasumusalahatthā catumahāpathādīsu musalena pāsāṇe ubbattetvā pavaṭṭenti, yānānaṃ akkhapaṭighātarukkhe haranti, visamaṃ samaṃ karonti, setuṃ attharanti, pokkharaṇiyo khaṇanti, sālaṃ karonti, dānāni denti, sīlāni rakkhanti. "
482760,110,1408,60,68,1,76,8,Evaṃ yebhuyyena sakalagāmavāsino bodhisattassa ovāde ṭhatvā sīlāni rakkhiṃsu. 
482761,110,1409,2,63,1,354,47,"Atha nesaṃ gāmabhojako cintesi‘‘ ahaṃ pubbe etesu suraṃ pivantesu pāṇātipātādīni karontesu cāṭikahāpaṇādivasena ceva daṇḍabalivasena ca dhanaṃ labhāmi, idāni pana magho māṇavo sīlaṃ rakkhāpeti, tesaṃ pāṇātipātādīni kātuṃ na deti, idāni pana te pañca sīlāni na rakkhāpessāmī’’ ti kuddho rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ deva, bahū corā gāmaghātādīni karontā vicarantī’’ ti āha. "
482762,110,1409,64,78,1,47,9,"Rājā tassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ gaccha, te ānehī’’ ti āha. "
482763,110,1409,79,97,1,70,12,"So gantvā sabbepi te bandhitvā ānetvā‘‘ ānītā, deva, corā’’ ti rañño ārocesi. "
482764,110,1409,98,111,1,59,9,Rājā tesaṃ kammaṃ asodhetvāva‘‘ hatthinā ne maddāpethā’’ ti āha. 
482765,110,1409,112,119,1,55,7,Tato sabbepi te rājaṅgaṇe nipajjāpetvā hatthiṃ ānayiṃsu. 
482766,110,1409,120,145,1,141,20,"Bodhisatto tesaṃ ovādaṃ adāsi‘‘ tumhe sīlāni āvajjetha, pesuññakārake ca raññe ca hatthimhi ca attano sarīre ca ekasadisameva mettaṃ bhāvethā’’ ti. "
482767,110,1409,146,149,1,15,3,Te tathā akaṃsu. 
482768,110,1409,150,155,1,41,5,Atha nesaṃ maddanatthāya hatthiṃ upanesuṃ. 
482769,110,1409,156,164,1,62,7,"So upanīyamānopi na upagacchati, mahāviravaṃ viravitvā palāyati. "
482770,110,1409,165,173,1,51,7,"Aññaṃ aññaṃ hatthiṃ ānayiṃsu, tepi tatheva palāyiṃsu. "
482771,110,1410,2,21,1,72,11,Rājā ‘‘ etesaṃ hatthe kiñci osadhaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ vicinathā’’ ti āha. 
482772,110,1410,22,33,1,38,6,"Vicinantā adisvā‘‘ natthi, devā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
482773,110,1410,34,50,1,78,11,"Tena hi kiñci mantaṃ parivattessanti, pucchatha ne‘‘ atthi vo parivattanamanto’’ ti? "
482774,110,1410,51,62,1,44,6,"Rājapurisā pucchiṃsu, bodhisatto‘‘ atthī’’ ti āha. "
482775,110,1410,63,89,1,107,15,"Rājapurisā‘‘ atthi kira, devā’’ ti ārocayiṃsu, rājā sabbepi te pakkosāpetvā‘‘ tumhākaṃ jānanamantaṃ kathethā’’ ti āha. "
482776,110,1410,90,151,1,300,45,"Bodhisatto avoca‘‘ deva, añño amhākaṃ manto nāma natthi, amhe pana tettiṃsamattā janā pāṇaṃ na hanāma, adinnaṃ nādiyāma, micchācāraṃ na carāma, musāvādaṃ na bhaṇāma, majjaṃ na pivāma, mettaṃ bhāvema, dānaṃ dema, maggaṃ samaṃ karoma, pokkharaṇiyo khaṇāma, sālaṃ karoma, ayaṃ amhākaṃ manto ca parittañca vuḍḍhi cā’’ ti. "
482777,110,1410,152,169,1,127,16,"Rājā tesaṃ pasanno pesuññakārakassa sabbaṃ gehavibhavaṃ tañca tesaṃyeva dāsaṃ katvā adāsi, taṃ hatthiñca gāmañca tesaṃyeva adāsi. "
482778,110,1411,2,22,1,127,15,Te tato paṭṭhāya yathāruciyā puññāni karontā‘‘ catumahāpathe mahantaṃ sālaṃ kāressāmā’’ ti vaḍḍhakiṃ pakkosāpetvā sālaṃ paṭṭhapesuṃ. 
482779,110,1411,23,32,1,73,8,Mātugāmesu pana vigatacchandatāya tassā sālāya mātugāmānaṃ pattiṃ nādaṃsu. 
482780,110,1411,33,48,1,85,12,"Tena ca samayena bodhisattassa gehe sudhammā, cittā, nandā, sujāti catasso itthiyo honti. "
482781,110,1411,49,70,1,109,16,"Tāsu sudhammā vaḍḍhakinā saddhiṃ ekato hutvā‘‘ bhātika, imissā sālāya maṃ jeṭṭhikaṃ karohī’’ ti vatvā lañjaṃ adāsi. "
482782,110,1411,71,89,1,136,14,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā paṭhamameva kaṇṇikārukkhaṃ sukkhāpetvā tacchetvā vijjhitvā kaṇṇikaṃ niṭṭhāpetvā vatthena paliveṭhetvā ṭhapesi. 
482783,110,1411,90,107,1,72,11,"Atha sālaṃ niṭṭhāpetvā kaṇṇikāropanakāle‘‘ aho, ayyā, ekaṃ na sarimhā’’ ti āha."
482784,110,1411,108,117,1,15,4,"‘‘ Kiṃ nāma, bho’’ ti."
482785,110,1411,118,126,1,26,4,‘‘ Kaṇṇikā laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti.
482786,110,1411,127,134,1,18,3,‘‘ Hotu āharissāmā’’ ti?
482787,110,1411,135,153,1,109,13,"‘‘ Idāni chinnarukkhena kātuṃ na sakkā, pubbeyeva chinditvā tacchetvā vijjhitvā ṭhapitakaṇṇikā laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti."
482788,110,1411,154,162,1,21,4,‘‘ Idāni kiṃ kātabban’’ ti?
482789,110,1411,163,178,1,80,10,"‘‘ Sace kassaci gehe niṭṭhāpetvā ṭhapitā vikkāyikakaṇṇikā atthi, sā pariyesitabbā’’ ti. "
482790,110,1411,179,187,1,55,8,Te pariyesantā sudhammāya gehe disvā mūlena na labhiṃsu.
482791,110,1411,188,212,1,93,15,"‘‘ Sace maṃ sālāya pattikaṃ karotha, dassāmī’’ ti vutte‘‘ na mayaṃ mātugāmānaṃ pattiṃ damhā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
482792,110,1412,2,33,1,170,23,"Atha ne vaḍḍhakī āha‘‘ ayyā, tumhe kiṃ kathetha, ṭhapetvā brahmalokaṃ aññaṃ mātugāmarahitaṭṭhānaṃ nāma natthi, gaṇhatha kaṇṇikaṃ, evaṃ sante amhākaṃ kammaṃ niṭṭhaṃ gamissatī’’ ti. "
482793,110,1412,34,51,1,119,13,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti kaṇṇikaṃ gahetvā sālaṃ niṭṭhāpetvā āsanaphalakāni santharitvā pānīyacāṭiyo ṭhapetvā yāgubhattaṃ nibandhiṃsu. 
482794,110,1412,52,63,1,102,11,Sālaṃ pākārena parikkhipitvā dvāraṃ yojetvā antopākāre vālukaṃ ākiritvā bahipākāre tālapantiyo ropesuṃ. 
482795,110,1412,64,81,1,96,12,"Cittāpi tasmiṃ ṭhāne uyyānaṃ kāresi,‘‘ pupphūpagaphalūpagarukkho asuko nāma tasmiṃ natthī’’ ti nāhosi. "
482796,110,1412,82,91,1,86,9,Nandāpi tasmiṃyeva ṭhāne pokkharaṇiṃ kāresi pañcavaṇṇehi padumehi sañchannaṃ ramaṇīyaṃ. 
482797,110,1412,92,96,1,19,4,Sujā na kiñci akāsi. 
482798,110,1413,2,19,1,155,15,Bodhisatto mātu upaṭṭhānaṃ pitu upaṭṭhānaṃ kule jeṭṭhāpacāyikakammaṃ saccavācaṃ apharusavācaṃ apisuṇavācaṃ maccheravinayanti imāni satta vatapadāni pūretvā–
482799,110,1414,2,9,1,43,5,"‘ ‘ Mātāpettibharaṃ jantuṃ, kule jeṭṭhāpacāyinaṃ; "
482800,110,1415,2,6,1,43,3,"Saṇhaṃ sakhilasambhāsaṃ, pesuṇeyyappahāyinaṃ."
