482809,110,1419,34,65,1,214,26,"Atha te‘‘ jarasakko amhe matte katvā mahāsamuddapiṭṭhe khipitvā amhākaṃ devanagaraṃ gaṇhi, te mayaṃ tena saddhiṃ yujjhitvā amhākaṃ devanagarameva gaṇhissāmā’’ ti kipillikā viya thambhaṃ sineruṃ anusañcaramānā uṭṭhahiṃsu. "
