482849,110,1428,165,168,1,16,3,Evaṃ sesesu sesā. 
482850,110,1429,2,39,1,355,35,"Imesu pana pañcasu ṭhānesu ārakkhaṃ ṭhapetvā sakke devānaminde dibbasampattiṃ anubhavamāne sudhammā cavitvā tasseva pādaparicārikā hutvā nibbatti, kaṇṇikāya dinnanissandena cassā pañcayojanasatikā sudhammā nāma devasabhā udapādi, yattha dibbasetacchattassa heṭṭhā yojanappamāṇe kañcanapallaṅke nisinno sakko devānamindo devamanussānaṃ kattabbakiccāni karoti. "
