482854,110,1430,14,78,1,409,52,"Sakko‘‘ sujā na paññāyati, kattha nu kho nibbattā’’ ti āvajjento taṃ disvā tattha gantvā taṃ ādāya devalokaṃ āgantvā tassā ramaṇīyaṃ devanagaraṃ sudhammaṃ devasabhaṃ cittalatāvanaṃ nandāpokkharaṇiñca dassetvā‘‘ etā kusalaṃ katvā mayhaṃ pādaparicārikā hutvā nibbattā, tvaṃ pana kusalaṃ akatvā tiracchānayoniyaṃ nibbattā , ito paṭṭhāya sīlaṃ rakkhāhī’’ ti taṃ ovaditvā pañcasu sīlesu patiṭṭhāpetvā tattheva netvā vissajjesi. "
482855,110,1430,79,85,1,33,5,Sāpi tato paṭṭhāya sīlaṃ rakkhati. 
