482876,110,1433,2,43,1,296,35,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ evaṃ bhikkhu pubbe paṇḍitā devanagare rajjaṃ kārayamānā attano jīvitaṃ pariccajantāpi pāṇātipātaṃ na kariṃsu, tvaṃ nāma evarūpe niyyānike sāsane pabbajitvā aparissāvitaṃ sapāṇakaṃ udakaṃ pivissasī’’ ti taṃ bhikkhuṃ garahitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
