482879,110,1436,2,7,1,18,2,[ 32]2. Naccajātakavaṇṇanā 
482880,110,1437,2,14,1,92,12,Rudaṃ manuññan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ bahubhaṇḍikaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482881,110,1437,15,28,1,46,4,Vatthu heṭṭhā devadhammajātake( jā.1.1.6) vuttasadisameva. 
482882,110,1437,29,43,1,65,10,Satthā taṃ bhikkhuṃ‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu bahubhaṇḍo’’ ti pucchi.
482883,110,1437,44,52,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, bhante’’ ti."
482884,110,1437,53,63,1,43,6,‘‘ Kiṃkāraṇā tvaṃ bhikkhu bahubhaṇḍo jātosī’’ ti? 
482885,110,1437,64,83,1,113,15,So ettakaṃ sutvāva kuddho nivāsanapārupanaṃ chaḍḍetvā‘‘ iminā dāni nīhārena vicarāmī’’ ti satthu purato naggo aṭṭhāsi. 
482886,110,1437,84,93,1,25,5,Manussā‘‘ dhī dhī’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
482887,110,1437,94,98,1,29,4,So tato palāyitvā hīnāyāvatto. 
482888,110,1437,99,115,1,101,12,Bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ sannisinnā‘‘ satthu nāma purato evarūpaṃ karissatī’’ ti tassa aguṇakathaṃ kathesuṃ. 
482889,110,1437,116,133,1,81,11,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti bhikkhū pucchi. "
482890,110,1437,134,162,1,197,23,"Bhante,‘‘ so hi nāma bhikkhu tumhākaṃ purato catuparisamajjhe hirottappaṃ pahāya gāmadārako viya naggo ṭhatvā manussehi jigucchiyamāno hīnāyāvattitvā sāsanā parihīno’’ ti tassa aguṇakathāya nisinnāmhāti. "
482891,110,1437,163,186,1,144,16,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva so bhikkhu hirottappābhāvena ratanasāsanā parihīno, pubbe itthiratanapaṭilābhatopi parihīnoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
482892,110,1438,2,16,1,91,10,"Atīte paṭhamakappe catuppadā sīhaṃ rājānaṃ akaṃsu, macchā ānandamacchaṃ, sakuṇā suvaṇṇahaṃsaṃ. "
482893,110,1438,17,24,1,63,7,Tassa pana suvaṇṇahaṃsarājassa dhītā haṃsapotikā abhirūpā ahosi. 
482894,110,1438,25,35,1,58,9,"So tassā varaṃ adāsi, sā attano cittarucitaṃ sāmikaṃ vāresi. "
482895,110,1438,36,53,1,152,16,"Haṃsarājā tassā varaṃ datvā himavante sabbe sakuṇe sannipātāpesi, nānappakārā haṃsamorādayo sakuṇagaṇā samāgantvā ekasmiṃ mahante pāsāṇatale sannipatiṃsu. "
482896,110,1438,54,67,1,77,9,Haṃsarājā‘‘ attano cittarucitaṃ sāmikaṃ āgantvā gaṇhātū’’ ti dhītaraṃ pakkosāpesi. 
482897,110,1438,68,85,1,97,13,Sā sakuṇasaṅghaṃ olokentī maṇivaṇṇagīvaṃ citrapekhuṇaṃ moraṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ me sāmiko hotū’’ ti ārocesi. 
482898,110,1438,86,108,1,131,17,"Sakuṇasaṅghā moraṃ upasaṅkamitvā āhaṃsu‘‘ samma mora, ayaṃ rājadhītā ettakānaṃ sakuṇānaṃ majjhe sāmikaṃ rocentī tayi ruciṃ uppādesī’’ ti. "
482899,110,1438,109,137,1,170,22,"Moro‘‘ ajjāpi tāva me balaṃ na passatī’’ ti atituṭṭhiyā hirottappaṃ bhinditvā tāva mahato sakuṇasaṅghassa majjhe pakkhe pasāretvā naccituṃ ārabhi, naccanto appaṭicchanno ahosi. "
482900,110,1439,2,27,1,183,19,"Suvaṇṇahaṃsarājā lajjito‘‘ imassa neva ajjhattasamuṭṭhānā hirī atthi, na bahiddhāsamuṭṭhānaṃ ottappaṃ, nāssa bhinnahirottappassa mama dhītaraṃ dassāmī’’ ti sakuṇasaṅghamajjhe imaṃ gāthamāha– "
