482906,110,1443,28,31,1,46,2,{Veḷuriyavaṇṇūpanibhā}ti veḷuriyamaṇivaṇṇasadisā. 
482907,110,1443,32,35,1,32,2,{Byāmamattānī}ti ekabyāmappamāṇāni. 
482908,110,1443,36,39,1,20,2,{Pekhuṇānī}ti piñchāni. 
482909,110,1443,40,64,1,208,23,Naccena te dhītaraṃ no {dadāmī}ti hirottappaṃ bhinditvā naccitabhāveneva te evarūpassa nillajjassa dhītaraṃ no dadāmīti vatvā haṃsarājā tasmiṃyeva parisamajjhe attano bhāgineyyassa haṃsapotakassa dhītaraṃ adāsi. 
482910,110,1443,65,73,1,60,7,Moro haṃsapotikaṃ alabhitvā lajjitvā tatova uppatitvā palāyi. 
482911,110,1443,74,78,1,40,4,Haṃsarājāpi attano vasanaṭṭhānameva gato. 
482912,110,1444,2,30,1,190,20,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva esa hirottappaṃ bhinditvā ratanasāsanā parihīno, pubbepi itthiratanapaṭilābhato parihīnoyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
482913,110,1444,31,45,1,61,9,"‘‘ tadā moro bahubhaṇḍiko ahosi, haṃsarājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482914,110,1445,2,4,1,25,2,Naccajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
482915,110,1447,2,7,1,24,2,[ 33]3. Sammodamānajātakavaṇṇanā 
482916,110,1448,2,13,1,106,10,{Sammodamānā}ti idaṃ satthā kapilavatthuṃ upanissāya nigrodhārāme viharanto cumbaṭakakalahaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482917,110,1448,14,27,1,30,4,So kuṇālajātake( jā.2.21. kuṇālajātaka) āvi bhavissati. 
482918,110,1448,28,66,1,248,31,"Tadā pana satthā ñātake āmantetvā‘‘ mahārājā ñātakānaṃ aññamaññaṃ viggaho nāma na yutto, tiracchānagatāpi hi pubbe samaggakāle paccāmitte abhibhavitvā sotthiṃ pattā yadā vivādamāpannā, tadā mahāvināsaṃ pattā’’ ti vatvā ñātirājakulehi āyācito atītaṃ āhari. "
482919,110,1449,2,13,1,128,11,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto vaṭṭakayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā anekavaṭṭakasahassaparivāro araññe paṭivasati. 
482920,110,1449,14,44,1,240,30,Tadā eko vaṭṭakaluddako tesaṃ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā vaṭṭakavassitaṃ katvā tesaṃ sannipatitabhāvaṃ ñatvā tesaṃ upari jālaṃ khipitvā pariyantesu maddanto sabbe ekato katvā pacchiṃ pūretvā gharaṃ gantvā te vikkiṇitvā tena mūlena jīvikaṃ kappeti. 
482921,110,1449,45,50,1,39,5,Athekadivasaṃ bodhisatto te vaṭṭake āha–
482922,110,1449,51,102,1,324,43,"‘‘ ayaṃ sākuṇiko amhākaṃ ñātake vināsaṃ pāpeti, ahaṃ ekaṃ upāyaṃ jānāmi, enesa amhe gaṇhituṃ na sakkhissati, ito dāni paṭṭhāya etena tumhākaṃ upari jāle khittamatte ekeko ekekasmiṃ jālakkhike sīsaṃ ṭhapetvā jālaṃ ukkhipitvā icchitaṭṭhānaṃ haritvā ekasmiṃ kaṇṭakagumbe pakkhipatha, evaṃ sante heṭṭhā tena tena ṭhānena palāyissāmā’’ ti. "
482923,110,1449,103,112,1,30,5,Te sabbe‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇiṃsu. 
482924,110,1449,113,132,1,147,17,Dutiyadivase upari jāle khitte te bodhisattena vuttanayeneva jālaṃ ukkhipitvā ekasmiṃ kaṇṭakagumbe khipitvā sayaṃ heṭṭhābhāgena tato tato palāyiṃsu. 
482925,110,1449,133,143,1,76,9,"Sākuṇikassa gumbato jālaṃ mocentasseva vikālo jāto, so tucchahatthova agamāsi. "
482926,110,1450,2,7,1,47,5,Punadivasato paṭṭhāyapi vaṭṭakā tatheva karonti. 
482927,110,1450,8,18,1,90,10,Sopi yāva sūriyatthaṅgamanā jālameva mocento kiñci alabhitvā tucchahatthova gehaṃ gacchati. 
482928,110,1450,19,40,1,119,16,"Athassa bhariyā kujjhitvā‘‘ tvaṃ divase divase tucchahattho āgacchasi, aññampi te bahi positabbaṭṭhānaṃ atthi maññe’’ ti āha. "
482929,110,1450,41,98,1,348,46,"Sākuṇiko‘‘ bhadde, mama aññaṃ positabbaṭṭhānaṃ natthi, apica kho pana te vaṭṭakā samaggā hutvā caranti, mayā khittamatte jālaṃ ādāya kaṇṭakagumbe khipitvā gacchanti, na kho panete sabbakālameva sammodamānā viharissanti, tvaṃ mā cintayi, yadā te vivādamāpajjissanti, tadā te sabbeva ādāya tava mukhaṃ hāsayamāno āgacchissāmī’’ ti vatvā bhariyāya imaṃ gāthamāha– "
482930,110,1451,2,4,1,0,0,33.
482931,110,1452,2,9,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Sammodamānā gacchanti, jālamādāya pakkhino; "
482932,110,1453,2,13,1,44,8,"Yadā te vivadissanti, tadā ehinti me vasan’’ ti. "
482933,110,1454,2,20,1,120,15,"Tattha yadā te {vivadissantī}ti yasmiṃ kāle te vaṭṭakā nānāladdhikā nānāgāhā hutvā vivadissanti, kalahaṃ karissantīti attho. "
482934,110,1454,21,33,1,71,12,Tadā ehinti me vasan ti tasmiṃ kāle sabbepi te mama vasaṃ āgacchissanti. 
482935,110,1454,34,43,1,74,9,Athāhaṃ te gahetvā tava mukhaṃ hāsento āgacchissāmīti bhariyaṃ samassāsesi. 
482936,110,1455,2,25,1,132,18,"Katipāhasseva pana accayena eko vaṭṭako gocarabhūmiṃ otaranto asallakkhetvā aññassa sīsaṃ akkami, itaro‘‘ ko maṃ sīse akkamī’’ ti kujjhiṃ."
482937,110,1455,26,39,1,58,8,"‘‘ Ahaṃ asallakkhetvā akkamiṃ, mā kujjhī’’ ti vuttepi kujjhiyeva. "
482938,110,1455,40,55,1,82,11,Te punappunaṃ kathentā‘‘ tvameva maññe jālaṃ ukkhipasī’’ ti aññamaññaṃ vivādaṃ kariṃsu. 
482939,110,1455,56,91,1,203,27,"Tesu vivadantesu bodhisatto cintesi‘‘ vivādake sotthibhāvo nāma natthi, idāneva te jālaṃ na ukkhipissanti, tato mahantaṃ vināsaṃ pāpuṇissanti, sākuṇiko okāsaṃ labhissati, mayā imasmiṃ ṭhāne na sakkā vasitun’’ ti. "
482940,110,1455,92,98,1,37,6,So attano parisaṃ ādāya aññattha gato. 
482941,110,1455,99,112,1,102,11,Sākuṇikopi kho katipāhaccayena āgantvā vaṭṭakavassitaṃ vassitvā tesaṃ sannipatitānaṃ upari jālaṃ khipi. 
482942,110,1455,113,131,1,94,13,"Atheko vaṭṭako‘‘ tuyhaṃ kira jālaṃ ukkhipantasseva matthake lomāni patitāni, idāni ukkhipā’’ ti āha. "
482943,110,1455,132,150,1,92,13,"Aparo‘‘ tuyhaṃ kira jālaṃ ukkhipantasseva dvīsu pakkhesu pattāni patitāni, idāni ukkhipā’’ ti āha. "
482944,110,1455,151,177,1,152,21,"Iti tesaṃ‘‘ tvaṃ ukkhipa, tvaṃ ukkhipā’’ ti vadantānaññeva sākuṇiko jālaṃ ukkhipitvā sabbeva te ekato katvā pacchiṃ pūretvā bhariyaṃ hāsayamāno gehaṃ agamāsi. "
482945,110,1456,2,26,1,149,19,"Satthā ‘‘ evaṃ mahārājā ñātakānaṃ kalaho nāma na yutto, kalaho vināsamūlameva hotī’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
482946,110,1456,27,41,1,74,9,"‘‘ tadā apaṇḍitavaṭṭako devadatto ahosi, paṇḍitavaṭṭako pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482947,110,1457,2,4,1,31,2,Sammodamānajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
482948,110,1459,2,7,1,19,2,[ 34]4. Macchajātakavaṇṇanā 
482949,110,1460,2,16,1,100,14,Na maṃ sītaṃ na maṃ uṇhan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto purāṇadutiyikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482950,110,1460,17,33,1,75,12,Tadā hi satthā taṃ bhikkhuṃ‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchi.
482951,110,1460,34,42,1,17,3,"‘‘ Saccaṃ, bhagavā’’ ti."
482952,110,1460,43,50,1,22,3,‘‘ Kenāsi ukkaṇṭhāpito’’ ti?
482953,110,1460,51,66,1,68,9,"‘‘ Purāṇadutiyikā me, bhante madhurahattharasā, taṃ jahituṃ na sakkomī’’ ti. "
482954,110,1460,67,95,1,142,22,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ bhikkhu esā itthī tava anatthakārikā , pubbepi tvaṃ etaṃ nissāya maraṇaṃ pāpuṇanto maṃ āgamma maraṇā mutto’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
482955,110,1461,2,11,1,76,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa purohito ahosi. 
482956,110,1461,12,17,1,35,5,Tadā kevaṭṭā nadiyaṃ jālaṃ khipiṃsu. 
482957,110,1461,18,26,1,71,8,Atheko mahāmaccho rativasena attano macchiyā saddhiṃ kīḷamāno āgacchati. 
482958,110,1461,27,37,1,78,10,Tassa sā macchī purato gacchamānā jālagandhaṃ ghāyitvā jālaṃ pariharamānā gatā. 
482959,110,1461,38,44,1,53,6,So pana kāmagiddho lolamaccho jālakucchimeva paviṭṭho. 
482960,110,1461,45,72,1,173,21,"Kevaṭṭā tassa jālaṃ paviṭṭhabhāvaṃ ñatvā jālaṃ ukkhipitvā macchaṃ gahetvā amāretvāva vālikāpiṭṭhe khipitvā ‘‘ imaṃ aṅgāresu pacitvā khādissāmā’’ ti aṅgāre karonti, sūlaṃ tacchenti. "
482961,110,1461,73,114,1,205,32,"Maccho‘‘ etaṃ aṅgāratāpanaṃ vā sūlavijjhanaṃ vā aññaṃ vā pana dukkhaṃ na maṃ kilameti, yaṃ panesā macchī‘ aññaṃ so nūna ratiyā gato’ ti mayi domanassaṃ āpajjati, tameva maṃ bādhatī’’ ti paridevamāno imaṃ gāthamāha– "
482962,110,1462,2,4,1,0,0,34.
482963,110,1463,2,15,1,49,11,"‘ ‘ Na maṃ sītaṃ na maṃ uṇhaṃ, na maṃ jālasmi bādhanaṃ; "
482964,110,1464,2,14,1,48,9,"Yañca maṃ maññate macchī, aññaṃ so ratiyā gato’’ ti. "
482965,110,1465,2,36,1,168,28,"Tattha na maṃ sītaṃ na maṃ uṇhan ti macchānaṃ udakā nīhaṭakāle sītaṃ hoti, tasmiṃ vigate uṇhaṃ hoti, tadubhayampi sandhāya‘‘ na maṃ sītaṃ na maṃ uṇhaṃ bādhatī’’ ti paridevati. "
482966,110,1465,37,54,1,92,12,"Yampi aṅgāresu paccanamūlakaṃ dukkhaṃ bhavissati, tampi sandhāya‘‘ na maṃ uṇhan’’ ti paridevateva. "
482967,110,1465,55,71,1,93,15,"Na maṃ jālasmi bādhanan ti yampi me jālasmiṃ bādhanaṃ ahosi, tampi maṃ na bādhetīti paridevati."
482968,110,1465,72,117,1,267,35,"‘‘ Yañca man’’ tiādīsu ayaṃ piṇḍattho– sā macchī mama jāle patitassa imehi kevaṭṭehi gahitabhāvaṃ ajānantī maṃ apassamānā‘‘ so maccho idāni aññaṃ macchiṃ kāmaratiyā gato bhavissatī’’ ti cinteti, taṃ tassā domanassappattāya cintanaṃ maṃ bādhatīti vālikāpiṭṭhe nipanno paridevati. "
482969,110,1466,2,9,1,63,7,Tasmiṃ samaye purohito dāsaparivuto nhānatthāya nadītīraṃ āgato. 
482970,110,1466,10,14,1,25,4,So pana sabbarutaññū hoti. 
482971,110,1466,15,57,1,269,32,"Tenassa macchaparidevanaṃ sutvā etadahosi‘‘ ayaṃ maccho kilesavasena paridevati, evaṃ āturacitto kho panesa mīyamāno nirayeyeva nibbattissati, ahamassa avassayo bhavissāmī’’ ti kevaṭṭānaṃ santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ ambho tumhe amhākaṃ ekadivasampi byañjanatthāya macchaṃ na dethā’’ ti āha. "
482972,110,1466,58,75,1,79,10,"Kevaṭṭā‘‘ kiṃ vadetha, sāmi, tumhākaṃ ruccanakamacchaṃ gaṇhitvā gacchathā’’ ti āhaṃsu."
482973,110,1466,76,88,1,46,7,"‘‘ Amhākaṃ aññena kammaṃ natthi, imaññeva dethā’’ ti."
482974,110,1466,89,96,1,16,3,‘‘ Gaṇhatha sāmī’’ ti. 
482975,110,1466,97,133,1,218,29,"Bodhisatto taṃ ubhohi hatthehi gahetvā nadītīre nisīditvā‘‘ ambho maccha, sace tāhaṃ ajja na passeyyaṃ, jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇeyyāsi, idāni ito paṭṭhāya mā kilesavasiko ahosī’’ ti ovaditvā udake vissajjetvā nhatvā nagaraṃ pāvisi. "
482976,110,1467,2,14,1,111,10,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhāsi. "
482977,110,1467,15,21,1,48,5,Satthāpi anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
482978,110,1467,22,38,1,89,11,"‘‘ tadā macchī purāṇadutiyikā ahosi, maccho ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu purohito pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
482979,110,1468,2,4,1,28,2,Macchajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
482980,110,1470,2,7,1,20,2,[ 35]5. Vaṭṭakajātakavaṇṇanā 
482981,110,1471,2,14,1,93,11,Santi pakkhā {apatanā}ti idaṃ satthā magadhesu cārikaṃ caramāno dāvagginibbānaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
482982,110,1471,15,30,1,164,15,Ekasmiñhi samaye satthā magadhesu cārikaṃ caramāno aññatarasmiṃ magadhagāmake piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto bhikkhugaṇaparivuto maggaṃ paṭipajji. 
482983,110,1471,31,52,1,137,19,"Tasmiṃ samaye mahāḍāho uṭṭhahi, purato ca pacchato ca bahū bhikkhū dissanti, sopi kho aggi ekadhūmo ekajālo hutvā avattharamāno āgacchateva. "
482984,110,1471,53,74,1,146,16,"Tattheke puthujjanabhikkhū maraṇabhayabhītā‘‘ paṭaggiṃ dassāma, tena daḍḍhaṭṭhānaṃ itaro aggi na ottharissatī’’ ti araṇisahitaṃ nīharitvā aggiṃ karonti. "
482985,110,1471,75,133,1,388,45,"Apare āhaṃsu‘‘ āvuso, tumhe kiṃ nāma karotha, gaganamajjhe ṭhitaṃ candamaṇḍalaṃ, pācīnalokadhātuto uggacchantaṃ sahassaraṃsipaṭimaṇḍitaṃ sūriyamaṇḍalaṃ, velāya tīre ṭhitā samuddaṃ, sineruṃ nissāya ṭhitā sineruṃ apassantā viya sadevake loke aggapuggalaṃ attanā saddhiṃ gacchantameva sammāsambuddhaṃ anoloketvā‘ paṭaggiṃ demā’ ti vadatha, buddhabalaṃ nāma na jānātha, etha satthu santikaṃ gamissāmā’’ ti. "
482986,110,1471,134,146,1,84,12,Te purato ca pacchato ca gacchantā sabbepi ekato hutvā dasabalassa santikaṃ agamaṃsu. 
482987,110,1471,147,152,1,60,5,Satthā mahābhikkhusaṅghaparivāro aññatarasmiṃ padese aṭṭhāsi. 
482988,110,1471,153,158,1,45,5,Dāvaggi abhibhavanto viya viravanto āgacchati. 
482989,110,1471,159,177,1,193,17,"Āgantvā tathāgatassa ṭhitaṭṭhānaṃ patvā tassa padesassa samantā soḷasakarīsamattaṭṭhānaṃ patto udake opilāpitatiṇukkā viya nibbāyi, vinibbedhato dvattiṃsakarīsamattaṭṭhānaṃ avattharituṃ nāsakkhi. "
482990,110,1472,2,7,1,35,4,Bhikkhū satthu guṇakathaṃ ārabhiṃsu–
482991,110,1472,8,39,1,155,22,"‘‘ aho buddhānaṃ guṇā nāma, ayañhi nāma acetano aggi buddhānaṃ ṭhitaṭṭhānaṃ avattharituṃ na sakkoti, udake tiṇukkā viya nibbāyati, aho buddhānaṃ ānubhāvo nāmā’’ ti. "
482992,110,1472,40,62,1,112,17,"Satthā tesaṃ kathaṃ sutvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, etaṃ etarahi mayhaṃ balaṃ, yaṃ imaṃ bhūmippadesaṃ patvā esa aggi nibbāyati. "
482993,110,1472,63,67,1,35,4,Idaṃ pana mayhaṃ porāṇakasaccabalaṃ. 
482994,110,1472,68,83,1,94,12,"Imasmiñhi padese sakalampi imaṃ kappaṃ aggi na jalissati, kappaṭṭhiyapāṭihāriyaṃ nāmetan’’ ti āha. "
482995,110,1472,84,96,1,103,11,"Athāyasmā ānando satthu nisīdanatthāya catugguṇaṃ saṅghāṭiṃ paññapesi, nisīdi satthā pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā. "
482996,110,1472,97,102,1,54,5,Bhikkhusaṅghopi tathāgataṃ vanditvā parivāretvā nisīdi. 
482997,110,1472,103,129,1,121,18,"Atha satthā‘‘ idaṃ tāva, bhante, amhākaṃ pākaṭaṃ, atītaṃ paṭicchannaṃ, taṃ no pākaṭaṃ karothā’’ ti bhikkhūhi āyācito atītaṃ āhari. "
482998,110,1473,2,18,1,174,16,Atīte magadharaṭṭhe tasmiṃyeva padese bodhisatto vaṭṭakayoniyaṃ paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā mātukucchito jāto aṇḍakosaṃ padāletvā nikkhantakāle mahāgeṇḍukappamāṇo vaṭṭakapotako ahosi. 
482999,110,1473,19,28,1,81,9,Atha naṃ mātāpitaro kulāvake nipajjāpetvā mukhatuṇḍakena gocaraṃ āharitvā posenti. 
483000,110,1473,29,41,1,87,12,Tassa pakkhe pasāretvā ākāse gamanabalaṃ vā pāde ukkhipitvā thale gamanabalaṃ vā natthi. 
483001,110,1473,42,73,1,271,28,"Tañca padesaṃ saṃvacchare saṃvacchare dāvaggi gaṇhāti, so tasmimpi samaye mahāravaṃ ravanto taṃ padesaṃ gaṇhi, sakuṇasaṅghā attano attano kulāvakehi nikkhamitvā maraṇabhayabhītā viravantā palāyanti, bodhisattassapi mātāpitaro maraṇabhayabhītā bodhisattaṃ chaḍḍetvā palāyiṃsu. "
483002,110,1473,74,97,1,181,20,"Bodhisatto kulāvake nipannakova gīvaṃ ukkhipitvā avattharitvā āgacchantaṃ aggiṃ disvā cintesi‘‘ sace mayhaṃ pakkhe pasāretvā ākāsena gamanabalaṃ bhaveyya, uppatitvā aññattha gaccheyyaṃ. "
483003,110,1473,98,107,1,72,8,"Sace pāde ukkhipitvā gamanabalaṃ bhaveyya, padavārena aññattha gaccheyyaṃ. "
483004,110,1473,108,118,1,82,10,Mātāpitaropi kho me maraṇabhayabhītā maṃ ekakaṃ pahāya attānaṃ parittāyantā palātā. 
483005,110,1473,119,138,1,88,15,"Idāni me aññaṃ paṭisaraṇaṃ natthi, atāṇomhi asaraṇo, kiṃ nu kho ajja mayā kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
483006,110,1474,2,78,1,598,63,"Athassa etadahosi‘‘ imasmiṃ loke sīlaguṇo nāma atthi, saccaguṇo nāma atthi, atīte pāramiyo pūretvā bodhimūle nisīditvā abhisambuddhā sīlasamādhipaññāvimuttivimuttiñāṇadassanasampannā saccānuddayakāruññakhantisamannāgatā sabbasattesu samappavattamettābhāvanā sabbaññubuddhā nāma atthi, tehi ca paṭividdhā dhammaguṇā nāma atthi, mayi cāpi ekaṃ saccaṃ atthi, saṃvijjamāno eko sabhāvadhammo paññāyati, tasmā atīte buddhe ceva tehi paṭividdhaguṇe ca āvajjetvā mayi vijjamānaṃ saccasabhāvadhammaṃ gahetvā saccakiriyaṃ katvā aggiṃ paṭikkamāpetvā ajja mayā attano ceva sesasakuṇānañca sotthibhāvaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
483007,110,1474,79,81,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
483008,110,1475,2,10,1,41,6,"‘ ‘ Atthi loke sīlaguṇo, saccaṃ soceyyanuddayā; "
483009,110,1476,2,7,1,41,4,"Tena saccena kāhāmi, saccakiriyamanuttaraṃ."
483010,110,1477,2,10,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Āvajjetvā dhammabalaṃ, saritvā pubbake jine; "
483011,110,1478,2,16,1,42,3,"Saccabalamavassāya , saccakiriyamakāsahan’’ ti.( cariyā.3.79-80); "
483012,110,1479,2,17,1,137,15,Atha bodhisatto atīte parinibbutānaṃ buddhānaṃ guṇe āvajjetvā attani vijjamānaṃ saccasabhāvaṃ ārabbha saccakiriyaṃ karonto imaṃ gāthamāha– 
483013,110,1480,2,4,1,0,0,35.
483014,110,1481,2,11,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Santi pakkhā apatanā, santi pādā avañcanā; "
483015,110,1482,2,11,1,43,6,"Mātāpitā ca nikkhantā, jātaveda paṭikkamā’’ ti. "
483016,110,1483,2,22,1,124,18,"Tattha santi pakkhā {apatanā}ti mayhaṃ pakkhā nāma atthi upalabbhanti, no ca kho sakkā etehi uppatituṃ ākāsena gantunti apatanā. "
483017,110,1483,23,39,1,100,14,"Santi pādā {avañcanā}ti pādāpi me atthi, tehi pana vañcituṃ padavāragamanena gantuṃ na sakkāti avañcanā. "
483018,110,1483,40,54,1,89,12,"Mātāpitā ca {nikkhantā}ti ye ca maṃ aññattha neyyuṃ, tepi maraṇabhayena mātāpitaro nikkhantā. "
483019,110,1483,55,59,1,24,3,{Jātavedā}ti aggiṃ ālapati. 
483020,110,1483,60,74,1,57,9,"So hi jātova vedayati paññāyati, tasmā‘‘ jātavedo’’ ti vuccati. "
483021,110,1483,75,81,1,50,5,{Paṭikkamā}ti paṭigaccha nivattāti jātavedaṃ āṇāpeti. 
483022,110,1484,2,49,1,293,36,"Iti mahāsatto‘‘ sace mayhaṃ pakkhānaṃ atthibhāvo, te ca pasāretvā ākāse apatanabhāvo, pādānaṃ atthibhāvo, te ca ukkhipitvā avañcanabhāvo, mātāpitūnaṃ maṃ kulāvakeyeva chaḍḍetvā palātabhāvo ca sacco sabhāvabhūtoyeva, jātaveda, etena saccena tvaṃ ito paṭikkamā’’ ti kulāvake nipannakova saccakiriyaṃ akāsi. "
483023,110,1484,50,57,1,67,7,Tassa saha saccakiriyāya soḷasakarīsamatte ṭhāne jātavedo paṭikkami. 
483024,110,1484,58,72,1,89,13,"Paṭikkamanto ca na jhāyamānova aññaṃ gato, udake pana opilāpitā ukkā viya tattheva nibbāyi. "
483025,110,1484,73,75,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
483026,110,1485,2,13,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Saha sacce kate mayhaṃ, mahāpajjalito sikhī; "
483027,110,1486,2,21,1,51,8,"Vajjesi soḷasa karīsāni, udakaṃ patvā yathā sikhī’’ ti.( cariyā.3.82); "
483028,110,1487,2,13,1,98,11,Taṃ pana ṭhānaṃ sakalepi imasmiṃ kappe agginā anabhibhavanīyattā kappaṭṭhiyapāṭihāriyaṃ nāma jātaṃ. 
483029,110,1487,14,21,1,68,7,Evaṃ bodhisatto saccakiriyaṃ katvā jīvitapariyosāne yathākammaṃ gato. 
483030,110,1488,2,30,1,180,21,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, imassa vanassa agginā anajjhottharaṇaṃ etarahi mayhaṃ balaṃ, porāṇaṃ panetaṃ vaṭṭapotakakāle mayhameva saccabalan’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi. "
483031,110,1488,31,45,1,93,11,"Saccapariyosāne keci sotāpannā ahesuṃ, keci sakadāgāmino, keci anāgāmino, keci arahattaṃ pattāti. "
483032,110,1488,46,51,1,48,5,Satthāpi anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
483033,110,1488,52,67,1,78,10,"‘‘ tadā mātāpitaro etarahi mātāpitarova ahesuṃ, vaṭṭakarājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483034,110,1489,2,4,1,28,2,Vaṭṭakajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
483035,110,1491,2,7,1,19,2,[ 36]6. Sakuṇajātakavaṇṇanā 
483036,110,1492,2,13,1,86,10,Yaṃ {nissitā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto daḍḍhapaṇṇasālaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483037,110,1492,14,30,1,139,16,Eko kira bhikkhu satthu santike kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā jetavanato nikkhamma kosalesu ekaṃ paccantagāmaṃ nissāya ekasmiṃ araññasenāsane vasati. 
483038,110,1492,31,35,1,43,4,Athassa paṭhamamāseyeva paṇṇasālā ḍayhittha. 
483039,110,1492,36,50,1,59,9,"So‘‘ paṇṇasālā me daḍḍhā, dukkhaṃ vasāmī’’ ti manussānaṃ ācikkhi. "
483040,110,1492,51,102,1,212,29,"Manussā‘‘ idāni no khettaṃ parisukkhaṃ, kedāre pāyetvā karissāma’’, tasmiṃ pāyite‘‘ bījaṃ vapitvā’’, bīje vutte‘‘ vatiṃ katvā’’, vatiyā katāya‘‘ niddāyitvā, lāyitvā, madditvā’’ ti evaṃ taṃ taṃ kammaṃ apadisantāyeva temāsaṃ vītināmesuṃ. "
483041,110,1492,103,115,1,96,11,So bhikkhu temāsaṃ ajjhokāse dukkhaṃ vasanto kammaṭṭhānaṃ vaḍḍhetvā visesaṃ nibbattetuṃ nāsakkhi. 
483042,110,1492,116,124,1,63,8,Pavāretvā pana satthu santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
483043,110,1492,125,145,1,117,15,"Satthā tena saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ kiṃ bhikkhu sukhena vassaṃvutthosi, kammaṭṭhānaṃ te matthakaṃ pattan’’ ti pucchi. "
483044,110,1492,146,163,1,97,13,So taṃ pavattiṃ ācikkhitvā‘‘ senāsanasappāyassa me abhāvena kammaṭṭhānaṃ matthakaṃ na pattan’’ ti āha. 
483045,110,1492,164,184,1,111,15,"Satthā‘‘ pubbe bhikkhu tiracchānagatāpi attano sappāyāsappāyaṃ jāniṃsu, tvaṃ kasmā na aññāsī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483046,110,1493,2,18,1,163,14,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sakuṇayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā sakuṇasaṅghaparivuto araññāyatane sākhāviṭapasampannaṃ mahārukkhaṃ nissāya vasati. 
483047,110,1493,19,30,1,88,10,"Athekadivasaṃ tassa rukkhassa sākhāsu aññamaññaṃ ghaṃsantīsu cuṇṇaṃ patati, dhūmo uṭṭhāti. "
483048,110,1493,31,70,1,225,31,"Taṃ disvā bodhisatto cintesi‘‘ imā dve sākhā evaṃ ghaṃsamānā aggiṃ vissajjessanti, so patitvā purāṇapaṇṇāni gaṇhissati, tato paṭṭhāya imampi rukkhaṃ jhāpessati, na sakkā idha amhehi vasituṃ, ito palāyitvā aññattha gantuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
483049,110,1493,71,75,1,33,4,So sakuṇasaṅghassa imaṃ gāthamāha– 
483050,110,1494,2,4,1,0,0,36.
483051,110,1495,2,12,1,56,8,"‘ ‘ Yaṃ nissitā jagatiruhaṃ vihaṅgamā, svāyaṃ aggiṃ pamuñcati; "
483052,110,1496,2,12,1,47,7,"Disā bhajatha vakkaṅgā, jātaṃ saraṇato bhayan’’ ti. "
483053,110,1497,2,19,1,88,12,"Tattha jagatiruhan ti jagati vuccati pathavī, tattha jātattā rukkho‘‘ jagatiruho’’ ti vuccati. "
483054,110,1497,20,36,1,77,10,"{Vihaṅgamā}ti vihaṃ vuccati ākāsaṃ, tattha gamanato pakkhī‘‘ vihaṅgamā’’ ti vuccanti. "
483055,110,1497,37,48,1,73,10,Disā {bhajathā}ti imaṃ rukkhaṃ muñcitvā ito palāyantā catasso disā bhajatha. 
483056,110,1497,49,53,1,25,3,{Vakkaṅgā}ti sakuṇe ālapati. 
483057,110,1497,54,71,1,78,12,"Te hi uttamaṅgaṃ galaṃ kadāci kadāci vaṅkaṃ karonti, tasmā‘‘ vakkaṅgā’’ ti vuccanti. "
483058,110,1497,72,80,1,52,8,Vaṅkā vā tesaṃ ubhosu passesu pakkhā jātāti vakkaṅgā. 
483059,110,1497,81,93,1,95,11,"Jātaṃ saraṇato bhayan ti amhākaṃ avassayarukkhatoyeva bhayaṃ nibbattaṃ, etha aññattha gacchāmāti. "
483060,110,1498,2,11,1,90,9,Bodhisattassa vacanakarā paṇḍitasakuṇā tena saddhiṃ ekappahāreneva uppatitvā aññattha gatā. 
483061,110,1498,12,33,1,109,16,"Ye pana apaṇḍitā, te‘‘ evameva esa bindumatte udake kumbhīle passatī’’ ti tassa vacanaṃ aggahetvā tattheva vasiṃsu. "
483062,110,1498,34,44,1,84,10,Tato na cirasseva bodhisattena cintitākāreneva aggi nibbattitvā taṃ rukkhaṃ aggahesi. 
483063,110,1498,45,62,1,117,15,"Dhūmesu ca jālāsu ca uṭṭhitāsu dhūmandhā sakuṇā aññattha gantuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu, aggimhi patitvā patitvā vināsaṃ pāpuṇiṃsu. "
483064,110,1499,2,28,1,160,20,"Satthā ‘‘ evaṃ bhikkhu pubbe tiracchānagatāpi rukkhagge vasantā attano sappāyāsappāyaṃ jānanti, tvaṃ kasmā na aññāsī’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi. "
483065,110,1499,29,34,1,52,5,Saccapariyosāne so bhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhito. 
483066,110,1499,35,40,1,48,5,Satthāpi anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
483067,110,1499,41,57,1,93,11,"‘‘ tadā bodhisattassa vacanakarā sakuṇā buddhaparisā ahesuṃ, paṇḍitasakuṇo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483068,110,1500,2,4,1,27,2,Sakuṇajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
483069,110,1502,2,7,1,20,2,[ 37]7. Tittirajātakavaṇṇanā 
483070,110,1503,2,14,1,109,10,Ye {vuḍḍhamapacāyantī}ti idaṃ satthā sāvatthiṃ gacchanto sāriputtattherassa senāsanapaṭibāhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483071,110,1503,15,38,1,158,19,Anāthapiṇḍikena hi vihāraṃ kāretvā dūte pesite satthā rājagahā nikkhamma vesāliṃ patvā tattha yathābhirantaṃ viharitvā‘‘ sāvatthiṃ gamissāmī’’ ti maggaṃ paṭipajji. 
483072,110,1503,39,68,1,204,23,"Tena ca samayena chabbaggiyānaṃ antevāsikā purato purato gantvā therānaṃ senāsanesu aggahitesveva‘‘ idaṃ senāsanaṃ amhākaṃ upajjhāyassa, idaṃ ācariyassa, idaṃ amhākameva bhavissatī’’ ti senāsanāni palibundhenti. "
483073,110,1503,69,75,1,41,6,Pacchā āgatā therā senāsanāni na labhanti. 
483074,110,1503,76,83,1,74,7,Sāriputtattherassāpi antevāsikā therassa senāsanaṃ pariyesantā na labhiṃsu. 
483075,110,1503,84,98,1,115,14,Thero senāsanaṃ alabhanto satthu senāsanassa avidūre ekasmiṃ rukkhamūle nisajjāya ca caṅkamena ca rattiṃ vītināmesi. 
483076,110,1503,99,106,1,54,6,"Satthā paccūsasamaye nikkhamitvā ukkāsi, theropi ukkāsi."
483077,110,1503,107,114,1,9,3,‘‘ Ko eso’’ ti?
483078,110,1503,115,125,1,24,4,"‘‘ Ahaṃ, bhante, sāriputto’’ ti."
483079,110,1503,126,138,1,41,7,"‘‘ Sāriputta, imāya velāya idha kiṃ karosī’’ ti?"
483080,110,1503,139,147,1,23,4,‘‘ So taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesi’’. 
483081,110,1503,148,175,1,175,22,"Satthā therassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ idāni tāva mayi jīvanteyeva bhikkhū aññamaññaṃ agāravā apatissā viharanti, parinibbute kiṃ nu kho karissantī’’ ti āvajjentassa dhammasaṃvego udapādi. "
483082,110,1504,2,29,1,173,20,"So pabhātāya rattiyā bhikkhusaṅghaṃ sannipātāpetvā bhikkhū pucchi‘‘ saccaṃ kira, bhikkhave, chabbaggiyā bhikkhū purato purato gantvā therānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ senāsanaṃ paṭibāhantī’’ ti."
483083,110,1504,30,38,1,17,3,"‘‘ Saccaṃ, bhagavā’’ ti? "
483084,110,1504,39,62,1,126,17,"Tato chabbaggiye garahitvā dhammiṃ kathaṃ katvā bhikkhū āmantesi‘‘ ko nu kho, bhikkhave, aggāsanaṃ aggodakaṃ aggapiṇḍaṃ arahatī’’ ti? "
483085,110,1504,63,105,1,193,22,"Ekacce‘‘ khattiyakulā pabbajito’’ ti āhaṃsu, ekacce‘‘ brāhmaṇakulā, gahapatikulā pabbajito’’ ti, apare‘‘ vinayadharo, dhammakathiko, paṭhamassa jhānassa lābhī, dutiyassa, tatiyassa, catutthassa jhānassa lābhī’’ ti. "
483086,110,1504,106,124,1,70,9,"Apare‘‘ sotāpanno, sakadāgāmī, anāgāmī, arahā, tevijjo, chaḷabhiñño’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
483087,110,1504,125,135,1,85,10,Evaṃ tehi bhikkhūhi attano attano rucivasena aggāsanādirahānaṃ kathitakāle satthā āha–
483088,110,1504,136,193,1,371,41,"‘‘ na, bhikkhave, mayhaṃ sāsane aggāsanādīni patvā khattiyakulā pabbajito pamāṇaṃ, na brāhmaṇakulā pabbajito, na gahapatikulā pabbajito, na vinayadharo, na suttantiko, na ābhidhammiko, na paṭhamajjhānādilābhino, na sotāpannādayo pamāṇaṃ, atha kho, bhikkhave, imasmiṃ sāsane yathāvuḍḍhaṃ abhivādanaṃ paccuṭṭhānaṃ añjalikammaṃ sāmīcikammaṃ kātabbaṃ, aggāsanaṃ aggodakaṃ aggapiṇḍo laddhabbo. "
483089,110,1504,194,196,1,17,2,Idamettha pamāṇaṃ. 
483090,110,1504,197,202,1,43,5,Tasmā vuḍḍhataro bhikkhu etesaṃ anucchaviko. 
483091,110,1504,203,242,1,262,31,"Idāni kho pana, bhikkhave, sāriputto mayhaṃ aggasāvako anudhammacakkappavattako mamānantaraṃ senāsanaṃ laddhuṃ arahati, so imaṃ rattiṃ senāsanaṃ alabhanto rukkhamūle vītināmesi, tumhe idāneva evaṃ agāravā apatissā, gacchante gacchante kāle kinti katvā viharissathā’’ ti. "
483092,110,1504,243,297,1,345,42,"Atha nesaṃ ovādadānatthāya‘‘ pubbe, bhikkhave, tiracchānagatāpi‘ na kho panetaṃ amhākaṃ patirūpaṃ, yaṃ mayaṃ aññamaññaṃ agāravā apatissā asabhāgavuttino vihareyyāma, amhesu mahallakataraṃ jānitvā tassa abhivādanādīni karissāmā’ ti sādhukaṃ vīmaṃsitvā‘ ayaṃ no mahallako’ ti ñatvā tassa abhivādanādīni katvā devapathaṃ pūrayamānā gatā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483093,110,1505,2,16,1,99,11,"Atīte himavantappadese ekaṃ mahānigrodhaṃ upanissāya tayo sahāyā vihariṃsu– tittiro, makkaṭo, hatthīti. "
483094,110,1505,17,23,1,53,6,Te aññamaññaṃ agāravā apatissā asabhāgavuttino ahesuṃ. 
483095,110,1505,24,49,1,131,18,"Atha nesaṃ etadahosi‘‘ na yuttaṃ amhākaṃ evaṃ viharituṃ, yaṃnūna mayaṃ yo no mahallakataro, tassa abhivādanādīni karontā vihareyyāmā’’ ti."
483096,110,1505,50,92,1,215,29,"‘‘ Ko pana no mahallakataro’’ ti cintentā ekadivasaṃ‘‘ attheso upāyo’’ ti tayopi janā nigrodhamūle nisīditvā tittiro ca makkaṭo ca hatthiṃ pucchiṃsu‘‘ samma hatthi, tvaṃ imaṃ nigrodharukkhaṃ kīvappamāṇakālato paṭṭhāya jānāsī’’ ti? "
483097,110,1505,93,131,1,247,31,"So āha‘‘ sammā, ahaṃ taruṇapotakakāle imaṃ nigrodhagacchaṃ antarasatthīsu katvā gacchāmi, avattharitvā ṭhitakāle ca pana me etassa aggasākhā nābhiṃ ghaṭṭeti, evāhaṃ imaṃ gacchakālato paṭṭhāya jānāmī’’ ti puna ubhopi janā purimanayeneva makkaṭaṃ pucchiṃsu. "
483098,110,1505,132,158,1,169,20,"So āha‘‘ ahaṃ sammā makkaṭacchāpako samāno bhūmiyaṃ nisīditvā gīvaṃ anukkhipitvāva imassa nigrodhapotakassa aggaṅkure khādāmi, evāhaṃ imaṃ khuddakakālato paṭṭhāya jānāmī’’ ti. "
483099,110,1505,159,165,1,51,6,Atha itare ubhopi purimanayeneva tittiraṃ pucchiṃsu. 
483100,110,1505,166,207,1,225,32,"So āha‘‘ sammā, pubbe asukasmiṃ nāma ṭhāne mahānigrodharukkho ahosi, ahaṃ tassa phalāni khāditvā imasmiṃ ṭhāne vaccaṃ pātesiṃ, tato esa rukkho jāto, evāhaṃ imaṃ ajātakālato paṭṭhāya jānāmi, tasmā ahaṃ tumhehi jātiyā mahallakataro’’ ti. "
483101,110,1506,2,43,1,291,33,"Evaṃ vutte makkaṭo ca hatthī ca tittirapaṇḍitaṃ āhaṃsu‘‘ samma, tvaṃ amhehi mahallakataro, ito paṭṭhāya mayaṃ tava sakkāragarukāramānanavandanapūjanāni ceva abhivādanapaccuṭṭhānaañjalikammasāmīcikammāni ca karissāma, ovāde ca te ṭhassāma, tvaṃ pana ito paṭṭhāya amhākaṃ ovādānusāsaniṃ dadeyyāsī’’ ti. "
483102,110,1506,44,57,1,84,11,"Tato paṭṭhāya tittiro tesaṃ ovādaṃ adāsi, sīlesu patiṭṭhāpesi, sayampi sīlāni samādiyi. "
483103,110,1506,58,73,1,133,14,Te tayopi janā pañcasu sīlesu patiṭṭhāya aññamaññaṃ sagāravā sappatissā sabhāgavuttino hutvā jīvitapariyosāne devalokaparāyaṇā ahesuṃ. 
483104,110,1506,74,81,1,58,7,Tesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ samādānaṃ tittiriyaṃ brahmacariyaṃ nāma ahosi. 
483105,110,1507,2,24,1,164,19,"Te hi nāma, bhikkhave, tiracchānagatā aññamaññaṃ sagāravā sappatissā vihariṃsu, tumhe evaṃ svākhāte dhammavinaye pabbajitvā kasmā aññamaññaṃ agāravā apatissā viharatha. "
483106,110,1507,25,66,1,326,34,"Anujānāmi, bhikkhave, ito paṭṭhāya tumhākaṃ yathāvuḍḍhaṃ abhivādanaṃ paccuṭṭhānaṃ añjalikammaṃ sāmīcikammaṃ, yathāvuḍḍhaṃ aggāsanaṃ aggodakaṃ aggapiṇḍaṃ, na ito paṭṭhāya ca navakatarena vuḍḍhataro senāsanena paṭibāhitabbo, yo paṭibāheyya, āpattidukkaṭassāti evaṃ satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā abhisambuddho hutvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
483107,110,1508,2,4,1,0,0,37.
483108,110,1509,2,10,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Ye vuḍḍhamapacāyanti, narā dhammassa kovidā; "
483109,110,1510,2,12,1,47,7,"Diṭṭheva dhamme pāsaṃsā, samparāye ca suggatī’’ ti. "
483110,110,1511,2,13,1,76,8,"Tattha ye {vuḍḍhamapacāyantī}ti jātivuḍḍho, vayovuḍḍho, guṇavuḍḍhoti tayo vuḍḍhā. "
483111,110,1511,14,28,1,89,11,"Tesu jātisampanno jātivuḍḍho nāma, vaye ṭhito vayovuḍḍho nāma , guṇasampanno guṇavuḍḍho nāma. "
483112,110,1511,29,41,1,62,8,Tesu guṇasampanno vayovuḍḍho imasmiṃ ṭhāne‘‘ vuḍḍho’’ ti adhippeto. 
483113,110,1511,42,46,1,42,3,{Apacāyantī}ti jeṭṭhāpacāyikakammena pūjenti. 
483114,110,1511,47,53,1,56,5,Dhammassa {kovidā}ti jeṭṭhāpacāyanadhammassa kovidā kusalā. 
483115,110,1511,54,59,1,39,4,Diṭṭheva {dhamme}ti imasmiṃyeva attabhāve. 
483116,110,1511,60,63,1,21,2,{Pāsaṃsā}ti pasaṃsārahā. 
483117,110,1511,64,77,1,96,12,Samparāye ca {suggatī}ti samparetabbe imaṃ lokaṃ hitvā gantabbe paralokepi tesaṃ sugatiyeva hotīti. 
483118,110,1511,78,125,1,333,42,"Ayaṃ panettha piṇḍattho– bhikkhave, khattiyā vā hontu brāhmaṇā vā vessā vā suddā vā gahaṭṭhā vā pabbajitā vā tiracchānagatā vā, ye keci sattā jeṭṭhāpacitikamme chekā kusalā guṇasampannānaṃ vayovuḍḍhānaṃ apacitiṃ karonti, te imasmiñca attabhāve jeṭṭhāpacitikārakāti pasaṃsaṃ vaṇṇanaṃ thomanaṃ labhanti, kāyassa ca bhedā sagge nibbattantīti. "
483119,110,1512,2,11,1,87,9,Evaṃ satthā jeṭṭhāpacitikammassa guṇaṃ kathetvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
483120,110,1512,12,29,1,88,11,"‘‘ tadā hatthināgo moggallāno ahosi, makkaṭo sāriputto, tittirapaṇḍito pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483121,110,1513,2,4,1,28,2,Tittirajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
483122,110,1515,2,7,1,17,2,[ 38]8. Bakajātakavaṇṇanā 
483123,110,1516,2,15,1,95,10,Nāccantaṃ {nikatippañño}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto cīvaravaḍḍhakaṃ bhikkhu ārabbha kathesi. 
483124,110,1516,16,28,1,116,11,"Eko kira jetavanavāsiko bhikkhu yaṃkiñci cīvare kattabbaṃ chedanaghaṭṭanavicāraṇasibbanādikaṃ kammaṃ, tattha sukusalo. "
483125,110,1516,29,43,1,74,9,"So tāya kusalatāya cīvaraṃ vaḍḍheti, tasmā‘‘ cīvaravaḍḍhako’’ tveva paññāyittha. "
483126,110,1516,44,47,1,19,3,Kiṃ panesa karotīti? 
483127,110,1516,48,64,1,162,16,Jiṇṇapilotikāsu hatthakammaṃ dassetvā suphassikaṃ manāpaṃ cīvaraṃ katvā rajanapariyosāne piṭṭhodakena rajitvā saṅkhena ghaṃsitvā ujjalaṃ manuññaṃ katvā nikkhipati. 
483128,110,1516,65,91,1,143,21,"Cīvarakammaṃ kātuṃ ajānantā bhikkhū ahate sāṭake gahetvā tassa santikaṃ āgantvā‘‘ mayaṃ cīvaraṃ kātuṃ na jānāma, cīvaraṃ no katvā dethā’’ ti vadanti. "
483129,110,1516,92,116,1,134,18,"So‘‘ cīvaraṃ āvuso kariyamānaṃ cirena niṭṭhāti, mayā katacīvarameva atthi, ime sāṭake ṭhapetvā taṃ gaṇhitvā gacchathā’’ ti nīharitvā dasseti. "
483130,110,1516,117,136,1,126,15,Te tassa vaṇṇasampattimeva disvā antaraṃ ajānantā‘‘ thiran’’ ti saññāya ahatasāṭake cīvaravaḍḍhakassa datvā taṃ gaṇhitvā gacchanti. 
483131,110,1516,137,155,1,135,16,"Taṃ tehi thokaṃ kiliṭṭhakāle uṇhodakena dhoviyamānaṃ attano pakatiṃ dasseti, tattha tattha jiṇṇaṭṭhānaṃ paññāyati, te vippaṭisārino honti. "
483132,110,1516,156,165,1,67,9,Evaṃ āgatāgate pilotikāhi vañcento so bhikkhu sabbattha pākaṭo jāto. 
483133,110,1517,2,13,1,80,10,"Yathā cesa jetavane, tathā aññatarasmiṃ gāmakepi eko cīvaravaḍḍhako lokaṃ vañceti. "
483134,110,1517,14,33,1,94,13,"Tassa sambhattā bhikkhū‘‘ bhante, jetavane kira eko cīvaravaḍḍhako evaṃ lokaṃ vañcetī’’ ti ārocesuṃ. "
483135,110,1517,34,55,1,137,16,"Athassa etadahosi‘‘ handāhaṃ, taṃ nagaravāsikaṃ vañcemī’’ ti pilotikacīvaraṃ atimanāpaṃ katvā surattaṃ rajitvā taṃ pārupitvā jetavanaṃ agamāsi. "
483136,110,1517,56,73,1,78,12,"Itaro taṃ disvāva lobhaṃ uppādetvā‘‘ bhante, imaṃ cīvaraṃ tumhehi katan’’ ti pucchi."
483137,110,1517,74,80,1,10,2,‘‘ Āmāvuso’’ ti.
483138,110,1517,81,96,1,59,9,"‘‘ Bhante, imaṃ cīvaraṃ mayhaṃ detha, tumhe aññaṃ labhissathā’’ ti?"
483139,110,1517,97,114,1,84,11,"‘‘ Āvuso, mayaṃ gāmavāsikā dullabhapaccayā, imāhaṃ tuyhaṃ datvā attanā kiṃ pārupissāmī’’ ti?"
483140,110,1517,115,132,1,76,11,"‘‘ Bhante, mama santike ahatasāṭakā atthi, te gahetvā tumhākaṃ cīvaraṃ karothā’’ ti."
483141,110,1517,133,163,1,159,23,"‘‘ Āvuso, mayā ettha hatthakammaṃ dassitaṃ, tayi pana evaṃ vadante kiṃ sakkā kātuṃ, gaṇhāhi nan’’ ti tassa pilotikacīvaraṃ datvā ahatasāṭake ādāya taṃ vañcetvā pakkāmi. "
483142,110,1517,164,189,1,208,20,Jetavanavāsikopi taṃ cīvaraṃ pārupitvā katipāhaccayena uṇhodakena dhovanto jiṇṇapilotikabhāvaṃ disvā lajjito‘‘ gāmavāsicīvaravaḍḍhakena kira jetavanavāsiko vañcito’’ ti tassa vañcitabhāvo saṅghamajjhe pākaṭo jāto. 
483143,110,1518,2,10,1,66,7,Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ taṃ kathaṃ kathentā nisīdiṃsu. 
483144,110,1518,11,27,1,73,10,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchi. "
483145,110,1518,28,31,1,21,3,Te tamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. 
483146,110,1518,32,47,1,88,10,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, jetavanavāsī cīvaravaḍḍhako idāneva aññe vañceti, pubbepi vañcesiyeva. "
483147,110,1518,48,64,1,107,13,"Na gāmavāsikenāpi idāneva esa jetavanavāsī cīvaravaḍḍhako vañcito, pubbepi vañcitoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483148,110,1519,2,14,1,114,12,Atīte ekasmiṃ araññāyatane bodhisatto aññataraṃ padumasaraṃ nissāya ṭhite varaṇarukkhe rukkhadevatā hutvā nibbatti. 
483149,110,1519,15,28,1,93,12,"Tadā aññatarasmiṃ nātimahante sare nidāghasamaye udakaṃ mandaṃ ahosi, bahū cettha macchā honti. "
483150,110,1519,29,49,1,113,16,Atheko bako te macche disvā‘‘ ekena upāyena ime macche vañcetvā khādissāmī’’ ti gantvā udakapariyante cintento nisīdi. 
483151,110,1519,50,66,1,62,10,"Atha naṃ macchā disvā‘‘ kiṃ, ayya, cintento nisinnosī’’ ti pucchiṃsu."
483152,110,1519,67,75,1,31,4,‘‘ Tumhākaṃ cintento nisinnomhī’’ ti.
483153,110,1519,76,86,1,27,5,"‘‘ Kiṃ amhākaṃ cintesi, ayyā’’ ti?"
483154,110,1519,87,115,1,130,19,"‘‘‘ Imasmiṃ sare udakaṃ parittaṃ, gocaro mando, nidāgho ca mahanto, idānime macchā kiṃ nāma karissantī’ ti tumhākaṃ cintento nisinnomhī’’ ti."
483155,110,1519,116,126,1,23,5,"‘‘ Atha kiṃ karoma, ayyā’’ ti?"
483156,110,1519,127,149,1,138,16,"‘‘ Tumhe sace mayhaṃ vacanaṃ kareyyātha , ahaṃ vo ekekaṃ mukhatuṇḍakena gahetvā ekaṃ pañcavaṇṇapadumasañchannaṃ mahāsaraṃ netvā vissajjeyyan’’ ti."
483157,110,1519,150,168,1,102,12,"‘‘ Ayya, paṭhamakappikato paṭṭhāya macchānaṃ cintanakabako nāma natthi, tvaṃ amhesu ekekaṃ khāditukāmosī’’ ti."
483158,110,1519,169,178,1,40,5,‘‘ Nāhaṃ tumhe mayhaṃ saddahante khādissāmi’’.
483159,110,1519,179,199,1,102,15,"‘‘ Sace pana sarassa atthibhāvaṃ mayhaṃ na saddahatha, ekaṃ macchaṃ mayā saddhiṃ saraṃ passituṃ pesethā’’ ti. "
483160,110,1519,200,223,1,109,15,Macchā tassa saddahitvā‘‘ ayaṃ jalepi thalepi samattho’’ ti ekaṃ kāḷamahāmacchaṃ adaṃsu‘‘ imaṃ gahetvā gacchathā’’ ti. 
483161,110,1519,224,239,1,106,15,So taṃ gahetvā netvā sare vissajjetvā sabbaṃ saraṃ dassetvā puna ānetvā tesaṃ macchānaṃ santike vissajjesi. 
483162,110,1519,240,246,1,44,6,So tesaṃ macchānaṃ sarassa sampattiṃ vaṇṇesi. 
483163,110,1519,247,267,1,81,13,"Te tassa kathaṃ sutvā gantukāmā hutvā‘‘ sādhu, ayya, amhe gaṇhitvā gacchāhī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
483164,110,1520,2,53,1,359,45,"Bako paṭhamaṃ taṃ kāḷamahāmacchameva gahetvā saratīraṃ netvā saraṃ dassetvā saratīre jāte varaṇarukkhe nilīyitvā taṃ viṭapantare pakkhipitvā tuṇḍena vijjhanto jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā maṃsaṃ khāditvā kaṇṭake rukkhamūle pātetvā puna gantvā‘‘ vissaṭṭho, me so maccho, añño āgacchatū’’ ti etenupāyena ekekaṃ gahetvā sabbe macche khāditvā puna āgato ekaṃ macchampi nāddasa. "
483165,110,1520,54,58,1,32,4,Eko panettha kakkaṭako avasiṭṭho. 
483166,110,1520,59,83,1,125,17,"Bako tampi khāditukāmo hutvā‘‘ bho, kakkaṭaka, mayā sabbete macchā netvā padumasañchanne mahāsare vissajjitā, ehi tampi nessāmī’’ ti."
483167,110,1520,84,94,1,42,6,‘‘ Maṃ gahetvā gacchanto kathaṃ gaṇhissasī’’ ti?
483168,110,1520,95,102,1,22,3,‘‘ Ḍaṃsitvā gaṇhissāmī’’ ti.
483169,110,1520,103,120,1,73,11,"‘‘ Tvaṃ evaṃ gahetvā gacchanto maṃ pātessasi, nāhaṃ tayā saddhiṃ gamissāmī’’ ti."
483170,110,1520,121,134,1,49,8,"‘‘ Mā bhāyi, ahaṃ taṃ suggahitaṃ gahetvā gamissāmī’’ ti. "
483171,110,1520,135,146,1,66,9,Kakkaṭako cintesi‘‘ imassa macche netvā sare vissajjanaṃ nāma natthi. 
483172,110,1520,147,155,1,48,7,"Sace pana maṃ sare vissajjessati, iccetaṃ kusalaṃ. "
483173,110,1520,156,167,1,60,8,"No ce vissajjessati, gīvamassa chinditvā jīvitaṃ harissāmī’’ ti. "
483174,110,1521,2,40,1,200,29,"Atha naṃ evamāha‘‘ samma baka, na kho tvaṃ suggahitaṃ gahetuṃ sakkhissasi, amhākaṃ pana gahaṇaṃ suggahaṇaṃ , sacāhaṃ aḷehi tava gīvaṃ gahetuṃ labhissāmi, tava gīvaṃ suggahitaṃ katvā tayā saddhiṃ gamissāmī’’ ti. "
483175,110,1521,41,59,1,59,10,So taṃ‘‘ vañcetukāmo esa man’’ ti ajānanto‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
483176,110,1521,60,77,1,93,13,Kakkaṭako attano aḷehi kammārasaṇḍāsena viya tassa gīvaṃ suggahitaṃ katvā‘‘ idāni gacchā’’ ti āha. 
483177,110,1521,78,85,1,55,7,So taṃ netvā saraṃ dassetvā varaṇarukkhābhimukho pāyāsi. 
483178,110,1521,86,104,1,61,12,"Kakkaṭako āha‘‘ mātula, ayaṃ saro etto, tvaṃ pana ito kiṃ nesī’’ ti? "
483179,110,1521,105,157,1,239,38,"Bako‘‘ na te mātulo ahaṃ, na bhaginiputtosi vata me tvan’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tvaṃ‘ esa maṃ ukkhipitvā vicaranto mayhaṃ dāso’ ti saññaṃ karosi maññe, passetaṃ varaṇarukkhassa mūle kaṇṭakarāsiṃ, yathā me te sabbe macchā khāditā, tampi tatheva khādissāmī’’ ti āha. "
483180,110,1521,158,180,1,117,18,"Kakkaṭako‘‘ ete macchā attano bālatāya tayā khāditā, ahaṃ pana te maṃ khādituṃ na dassāmi, taññeva pana vināsaṃ pāpessāmi. "
483181,110,1521,181,209,1,172,23,"Tvañhi bālatāya mayā vañcitabhāvaṃ na jānāsi, marantā ubhopi marissāma, ahaṃ te sīsaṃ chinditvā bhūmiyaṃ khipissāmī’’ ti vatvā kammārasaṇḍāsena viya aḷehi tassa gīvaṃ nippīḷesi. "
483182,110,1521,210,233,1,118,17,"So vivaṭena mukhena akkhīhi assunā paggharantena maraṇabhayatajjito‘‘ sāmi, ahaṃ taṃ na khādissāmi, jīvitaṃ me dehī’’ ti āha."
483183,110,1521,234,245,1,45,7,‘‘ Yadi evaṃ otaritvā maṃ sarasmiṃ vissajjehī’’ ti. 
483184,110,1521,246,265,1,159,18,"So nivattitvā sarameva otaritvā kakkaṭakaṃ sarapariyante paṅkapiṭṭhe ṭhapesi, kakkaṭako kattarikāya kumudanāḷaṃ kappento viya tassa gīvaṃ kappetvā udakaṃ pāvisi. "
483185,110,1522,2,15,1,120,13,Taṃ acchariyaṃ disvā varaṇarukkhe adhivatthā devatā sādhukāraṃ dadamānā vanaṃ unnādayamānā madhurassarena imaṃ gāthamāha– 
483186,110,1523,2,4,1,0,0,38.
483187,110,1524,2,9,1,43,5,"‘ ‘ Nāccantaṃ nikatippañño, nikatyā sukhamedhati; "
483188,110,1525,2,10,1,43,5,"Ārādheti nikatippañño, bako kakkaṭakāmivā’’ ti. "
483189,110,1526,2,37,1,256,28,"Tattha nāccantaṃ nikatippañño, nikatyā {sukhamedhatī}ti nikati vuccati vañcanā, nikatippañño vañcanapañño puggalo tāya nikatyā nikatiyā vañcanāya na accantaṃ sukhamedhati, niccakāle sukhasmiṃyeva patiṭṭhātuṃ na sakkoti, ekaṃsena pana vināsaṃ pāpuṇātiyevāti attho. "
483190,110,1526,38,41,1,22,2,{Ārādhetī}ti paṭilabhati. 
483191,110,1526,42,55,1,122,12,{Nikatippañño}ti kerāṭikabhāvaṃ sikkhitapañño pāpapuggalo attanā katassa pāpassa phalaṃ ārādheti paṭilabhati vindatīti attho. 
483192,110,1526,56,57,1,6,1,Kathaṃ? 
483193,110,1526,58,85,1,216,25,"Bako kakkaṭakāmiva, yathā bako kakkaṭakā gīvacchedaṃ pāpuṇāti, evaṃ pāpapuggalo attanā katapāpato diṭṭhadhamme vā samparāye vā bhayaṃ ārādheti paṭilabhatīti imamatthaṃ pakāsento mahāsatto vanaṃ unnādento dhammaṃ desesi. "
483194,110,1527,2,25,1,153,16,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva gāmavāsicīvaravaḍḍhakenesa vañcito, atītepi vañcitoyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
483195,110,1527,26,46,1,116,14,"‘‘ tadā so bako jetavanavāsī cīvaravaḍḍhako ahosi, kakkaṭako gāmavāsī cīvaravaḍḍhako, rukkhadevatā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483196,110,1528,2,4,1,25,2,Bakajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
483197,110,1530,2,7,1,18,2,[ 39]9. Nandajātakavaṇṇanā 
483198,110,1531,2,15,1,104,11,Maññe sovaṇṇayo {rāsī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto sāriputtattherassa saddhivihārikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483199,110,1531,16,27,1,84,10,"So kira bhikkhu subbaco ahosi vacanakkhamo, therassa mahantenussāhena upakāraṃ karoti. "
483200,110,1531,28,37,1,88,9,Athekaṃ samayaṃ thero satthāraṃ āpucchitvā cārikaṃ caranto dakkhiṇāgirijanapadaṃ agamāsi. 
483201,110,1531,38,63,1,134,20,"So bhikkhu tattha gatakāle mānatthaddho hutvā therassa vacanaṃ na karoti‘‘ āvuso, idaṃ nāma karohī’’ ti vutte pana therassa paṭipakkho hoti. "
483202,110,1531,64,69,1,28,5,Thero tassa āsayaṃ na jānāti. 
483203,110,1531,70,77,1,46,7,So tattha cārikaṃ caritvā puna jetavanaṃ āgato. 
483204,110,1531,78,87,1,75,9,So bhikkhu therassa jetavanavihāraṃ āgatakālato paṭṭhāya puna tādisova jāto. 
483205,110,1531,88,121,1,177,25,"Thero tathāgatassa ārocesi‘‘ bhante, mayhaṃ eko saddhivihāriko ekasmiṃ ṭhāne satena kītadāso viya hoti, ekasmiṃ ṭhāne mānatthaddho hutvā‘ idaṃ nāma karohī’ ti vutte paṭipakkho hotī’’ ti. "
483206,110,1531,122,141,1,100,14,"Satthā‘‘ nāyaṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhu idāneva evaṃsīlo, pubbepesa ekaṃ ṭhānaṃ gato satena kītadāso viya hoti. "
483207,110,1531,142,156,1,79,12,Ekaṃ ṭhānaṃ gato paṭipakkho paṭisattu hotī’’ ti vatvā therena yācito atītaṃ āhari. 
483208,110,1532,2,13,1,95,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto ekasmiṃ kuṭumbiyakule paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
483209,110,1532,14,24,1,65,8,"Tasseko sahāyako kuṭumbiko sayaṃ mahallako, bhariyā panassa taruṇī. "
483210,110,1532,25,30,1,31,5,Sā taṃ nissāya puttaṃ paṭilabhi. 
