483392,110,1582,187,196,1,76,9,Tassa patte yāguṃ dānakāle manussānaṃ bhājane yāgu antaradhāyatītipi vadanti. 
483393,110,1582,197,200,1,25,3,Khajjakādīsupi eseva nayo. 
483394,110,1583,2,12,1,90,10,So aparena samayena vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā aggaphale arahatte patiṭṭhitopi appalābhova ahosi. 
483395,110,1583,13,19,1,71,6,Athassa anupubbena āyusaṅkhāresu parihīnesu parinibbānadivaso sampāpuṇi. 
483396,110,1583,20,47,1,187,22,"Dhammasenāpati āvajjento tassa parinibbānabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ ayaṃ losakatissatthero ajja parinibbāyissati, ajja mayā etassa yāvadatthaṃ āhāraṃ dātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti taṃ ādāya sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. "
483397,110,1583,48,58,1,90,10,Thero taṃ nissāya tāva bahumanussāya sāvatthiyā hatthaṃ pasāretvā vandanamattampi nālattha. 
483398,110,1583,59,73,1,62,9,"Atha naṃ thero‘‘ gacchāvuso, āsanasālāya nisīdā’’ ti uyyojetvā gato. "
483399,110,1583,74,88,1,61,9,"Taṃ āgatameva manussā‘‘ ayyo, āgato’’ ti āsane nisīdāpetvā bhojesi. "
483400,110,1583,89,101,1,50,7,Theropi‘‘ imaṃ losakassa dethā’’ ti laddhāhāraṃ pesesi. 
483401,110,1583,102,109,1,63,7,Taṃ gahetvā gatā losakatissattheraṃ asaritvā sayameva bhuñjiṃsu. 
483402,110,1583,110,135,1,141,18,"Atha therassa uṭṭhāya vihāraṃ gamanakāle losakatissatthero āgantvā theraṃ vandi, thero nivattitvā ṭhitakova‘‘ laddhaṃ te, āvuso, bhattan’’ ti pucchi. "
483403,110,1583,136,140,1,22,3,"Labhissāma no, bhanteti. "
483404,110,1583,141,148,1,47,6,"Thero saṃvegapatto kālaṃ olokesi, kālo atikkanto. "
483405,110,1583,149,165,1,100,11,"Thero‘‘ hotāvuso, idheva nisīdā’’ ti losakattheraṃ āsanasālāyaṃ nisīdāpetvā kosalarañño nivesanaṃ agamāsi. "
483406,110,1583,166,180,1,80,10,Rājā therassa pattaṃ gāhāpetvā‘‘ bhattassa akālo’’ ti pattapūraṃ catumadhuraṃ dāpesi. 
483407,110,1583,181,200,1,93,14,"Thero taṃ ādāya gantvā‘‘ ehāvuso, tissa imaṃ catumadhuraṃ bhuñjā’’ ti vatvā pattaṃ gahetvā aṭṭhāsi. "
483408,110,1583,201,207,1,42,6,So there gāravena lajjanto na paribhuñjati. 
483409,110,1583,208,225,1,90,13,"Atha naṃ thero‘‘ ehāvuso tissa, ahaṃ imaṃ pattaṃ gahetvāva ṭhassāmi, tvaṃ nisīditvā paribhuñja. "
483410,110,1583,226,240,1,60,10,"Sace ahaṃ pattaṃ hatthato muñceyyaṃ, kiñci na bhaveyyā’’ ti āha. "
483411,110,1583,241,251,1,101,9,Athāyasmā losakatissatthero aggasāvake dhammasenāpatimhi pattaṃ gahetvā ṭhite catumadhuraṃ paribhuñji. 
483412,110,1583,252,258,1,51,6,Taṃ therassa ariyiddhibalena parikkhayaṃ na agamāsi. 
483413,110,1583,259,272,1,122,12,"Tadā losakatissatthero yāvadatthaṃ udarapūraṃ katvā paribhuñji, taṃ divasaṃyeva ca anupādisesāya nibbānadhātuyā parinibbāyi. "
483414,110,1583,273,283,1,84,9,"Sammāsambuddho santike ṭhatvā sarīranikkhepaṃ kāresi, dhātuyo gahetvā cetiyaṃ kariṃsu. "
483415,110,1584,2,27,1,175,19,"Tadā bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitvā‘‘ āvuso, aho losakatissatthero appapuñño appalābhī, evarūpena nāma appapuññena appalābhinā kathaṃ ariyadhammo laddho’’ ti kathentā nisīdiṃsu. "
483416,110,1584,28,45,1,85,11,"Satthā dhammasabhaṃ gantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchi. "
483417,110,1584,46,57,1,34,6,"Te‘‘ imāya nāma, bhante’’ ti ārocayiṃsu. "
483418,110,1584,58,70,1,90,9,"Satthā‘‘ bhikkhave, eso bhikkhu attano alābhibhāvañca ariyadhammalābhibhāvañca attanāva akāsi. "
483419,110,1584,71,100,1,158,20,"Ayañhi pubbe paresaṃ lābhantarāyaṃ katvā appalābhī jāto,‘‘ aniccaṃ, dukkhaṃ, anattā’’ ti vipassanāya yuttabhāvassa balena ariyadhammalābhī jāto’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483420,110,1585,2,16,1,138,14,Atīte kira kassapasammāsambuddhakāle aññataro bhikkhu ekaṃ kuṭumbikaṃ nissāya gāmakāvāse vasati pakatatto sīlavā vipassanāya yuttappayutto. 
483421,110,1585,17,27,1,116,10,Atheko khīṇāsavatthero samavattavāsaṃ vasamāno anupubbena tassa bhikkhuno upaṭṭhākakuṭumbikassa vasanagāmaṃ sampatto. 
483422,110,1585,28,60,1,221,25,"Kuṭumbiko therassa iriyāpatheyeva pasīditvā pattaṃ ādāya gharaṃ pavesetvā sakkaccaṃ bhojetvā thokaṃ dhammakathaṃ sutvā theraṃ vanditvā‘‘ bhante, amhākaṃ dhuravihārameva gacchatha, mayaṃ sāyanhasamaye āgantvā passissāmā’’ ti āha. "
483423,110,1585,61,69,1,73,8,Thero vihāraṃ gantvā nevāsikattheraṃ vanditvā āpucchitvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
483424,110,1585,70,87,1,75,11,"Sopi tena saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ laddho te, āvuso, bhikkhāhāro’’ ti pucchi."
483425,110,1585,88,96,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, laddho’’ ti."
483426,110,1585,97,104,1,15,3,‘‘ Kahaṃ laddho’’ ti?
483427,110,1585,105,113,1,36,4,‘‘ Tumhākaṃ dhuragāme kuṭumbikaghare’’ ti. 
483428,110,1585,114,128,1,130,14,Evañca pana vatvā attano senāsanaṃ pucchitvā paṭijaggitvā pattacīvaraṃ paṭisāmetvā jhānasukhena phalasukhena ca vītināmento nisīdi. 
483429,110,1586,2,28,1,156,19,"Sopi kuṭumbiko sāyanhe gandhamālañceva padīpeyyañca gāhāpetvā vihāraṃ gantvā nevāsikattheraṃ vanditvā‘‘ bhante, eko āgantukatthero atthi, āgato nu kho’’ ti pucchi."
483430,110,1586,29,37,1,12,3,"‘‘ Āma, āgato’’ ti."
483431,110,1586,38,45,1,14,3,‘‘ Idāni kahan’’ ti.
483432,110,1586,46,53,1,21,3,‘‘ Asukasenāsane nāmā’’ ti. 
483433,110,1586,54,73,1,151,19,So tassa santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno dhammakathaṃ sutvā sītalavelāya cetiyañca bodhiñca pūjetvā dīpe jāletvā ubhopi jane nimantetvā gato. 
483434,110,1586,74,119,1,262,34,"Nevāsikattheropi kho‘‘ ayaṃ kuṭumbiko paribhinno, sacāyaṃ bhikkhu imasmiṃ vihāre vasissati, na maṃ esa kismiñci gaṇayissatī’’ ti there anattamanataṃ āpajjitvā‘‘ imasmiṃ vihāre etassa avasanākāro mayā kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti tena upaṭṭhānavelāya āgatena saddhiṃ kiñci na kathesi. "
483435,110,1586,120,145,1,168,21,Khīṇāsavatthero tassa ajjhāsayaṃ jānitvā‘‘ ayaṃ thero mama kule vā gaṇe vā apalibuddhabhāvaṃ na jānātī’’ ti attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā jhānasukhena phalasukhena vītināmesi. 
483436,110,1587,2,13,1,103,11,Nevāsikopi punadivase nakhapiṭṭhena gaṇḍiṃ paharitvā nakhena dvāraṃ ākoṭetvā kuṭumbikassa gehaṃ agamāsi. 
483437,110,1587,14,30,1,86,11,"So tassa pattaṃ gahetvā paññattāsane nisīdāpetvā‘‘ āgantukatthero kahaṃ, bhante’’ ti pucchi."
483438,110,1587,31,68,1,247,29,"‘‘ Nāhaṃ tava kulūpakassa pavattiṃ jānāmi, gaṇḍiṃ paharantopi dvāraṃ ākoṭentopi pabodhetuṃ nāsakkhiṃ, hiyyo tava gehe paṇītabhojanaṃ bhuñjitvā jīrāpetuṃ asakkonto idāni niddaṃ okkantoyeva bhavissati, tvaṃ pasīdamāno evarūpesuyeva ṭhānesu pasīdasī’’ ti āha–"
483439,110,1587,69,82,1,126,11,‘‘ khīṇāsavattheropi attano bhikkhācāravelaṃ sallakkhetvā sarīraṃ paṭijaggitvā pattacīvaramādāya ākāse uppatitvā aññattha agamāsi. 
483440,110,1587,83,109,1,186,20,"So kuṭumbiko nevāsikattheraṃ sappimadhusakkharābhisaṅkhataṃ pāyāsaṃ pāyetvā pattaṃ gandhacuṇṇehi ubbaṭṭetvā puna pūretvā‘‘ bhante, so thero maggakilanto bhavissati, idamassa harathā’’ ti adāsi. "
483441,110,1587,110,128,1,126,15,"Itaro apaṭikkhipitvāva gahetvā gacchanto‘‘ sace so bhikkhu imaṃ pāyāsaṃ pivissati, gīvāyaṃ gahetvā nikkaḍḍhiyamānopi na gamissati. "
483442,110,1587,129,140,1,73,10,"Sace panāhaṃ imaṃ pāyāsaṃ manussānaṃ dassāmi, pākaṭaṃ me kammaṃ bhavissati. "
483443,110,1587,141,149,1,54,6,"Sace udake opilāpessāmi, udakapiṭṭhe sappi paññāyissati . "
483444,110,1587,150,156,1,54,5,"Sace bhūmiyaṃ chaḍḍessāmi, kākasannipātena paññāyissati. "
483445,110,1587,157,207,1,327,43,"Kattha nu kho imaṃ chaḍḍeyyan’’ ti upadhārento ekaṃ jhāmakkhettaṃ disvā aṅgāre viyūhitvā tattha pakkhipitvā upari aṅgārehi paṭicchādetvā vihāraṃ gato taṃ bhikkhuṃ adisvā cintesi‘‘ addhā so bhikkhu khīṇāsavo mama ajjhāsayaṃ viditvā aññattha gato bhavissati, aho mayā udarahetu ayuttaṃ katan’’ ti tāvadevassa mahantaṃ domanassaṃ udapādi. "
483446,110,1587,208,219,1,77,11,Tato paṭṭhāyeva ca manussapeto hutvā na cirasseva kālaṃ katvā niraye nibbatti. 
483447,110,1588,2,17,1,138,15,So bahūni vassasatasahassāni niraye paccitvā pakkāvasesena paṭipāṭiyā pañcajātisatesu yakkho hutvā ekadivasampi udarapūraṃ āhāraṃ na labhi. 
483448,110,1588,18,23,1,44,5,Ekadivasaṃ pana gabbhamalaṃ udarapūraṃ labhi. 
483449,110,1588,24,28,1,34,4,Puna pañcajātisatesu sunakho ahosi. 
483450,110,1588,29,43,1,103,13,"Tadāpi ekadivasaṃ bhattavamanaṃ udarapūraṃ labhi, sesakāle pana tena udarapūro āhāro nāma na laddhapubbo. "
483451,110,1588,44,52,1,71,8,Sunakhayonito pana cavitvā kāsiraṭṭhe ekasmiṃ gāme duggatakule nibbatti. 
