483453,110,1588,67,78,1,38,6,Tassa pana ‘‘ mittavindako’’ ti nāmaṃ ahosi. 
483454,110,1588,79,94,1,90,10,Mātāpitaro chātakadukkhaṃ adhivāsetuṃ asakkontā‘‘ gaccha kāḷakaṇṇī’’ ti taṃ pothetvā nīhariṃsu. 
483455,110,1588,95,100,1,42,5,So apaṭisaraṇo vicaranto bārāṇasiṃ agamāsi. 
483456,110,1588,101,111,1,89,10,Tadā bodhisatto bārāṇasiyaṃ disāpāmokkho ācariyo hutvā pañca māṇavakasatāni sippaṃ vāceti. 
483457,110,1588,112,119,1,66,7,Tadā bārāṇasivāsino duggatānaṃ paribbayaṃ datvā sippaṃ sikkhāpenti. 
483458,110,1588,120,126,1,57,6,Ayampi mittavindako bodhisattassa santike sippaṃ sikkhati. 
483459,110,1588,127,140,1,96,12,"So pharuso anovādakkhamo taṃ taṃ paharanto vicarati, bodhisattena ovadiyamānopi ovādaṃ na gaṇhāti. "
483460,110,1588,141,146,1,31,5,Taṃ nissāya āyopissa mando jāto. 
483461,110,1589,2,18,1,124,16,Atha so māṇavakehi saddhiṃ bhaṇḍitvā ovādaṃ aggaṇhanto tato palāyitvā āhiṇḍanto ekaṃ paccantagāmaṃ patvā bhatiṃ katvā jīvati. 
483462,110,1589,19,26,1,54,7,So tattha ekāya duggatitthiyā saddhiṃ saṃvāsaṃ kappesi. 
483463,110,1589,27,33,1,32,6,Sā taṃ nissāya dve dārake vijāyi. 
483464,110,1589,34,52,1,115,13,Gāmavāsino‘‘ amhākaṃ susāsanaṃ dussāsanaṃ āroceyyāsī’’ ti mittavindakassa bhatiṃ datvā taṃ gāmadvāre kuṭikāya vasāpesuṃ. 
483465,110,1589,53,71,1,151,16,"Taṃ pana mittavindakaṃ nissāya te paccantagāmavāsino sattakkhattuṃ rājadaṇḍaṃ agamaṃsu, sattakkhattuṃ nesaṃ gehāni jhāyiṃsu, sattakkhattuṃ taḷākaṃ bhijji. "
483466,110,1589,72,95,1,152,18,"Te cintayiṃsu‘‘ amhākaṃ pubbe imassa mittavindakassa anāgamanakāle evarūpaṃ natthi, idāni panassa āgatakālato paṭṭhāya parihāyāmā’’ ti taṃ pothetvā nīhariṃsu. "
483467,110,1590,2,12,1,81,10,So attano dārake gahetvā aññattha gacchanto ekaṃ amanussapariggahaṃ aṭaviṃ pāvisi. 
483468,110,1590,13,21,1,63,8,Tatthassa amanussā dārake ca bhariyañca māretvā maṃsaṃ khādiṃsu. 
483469,110,1590,22,38,1,134,16,So tato palāyitvā tato tato āhiṇḍanto ekaṃ gambhīraṃ nāma paṭṭanagāmaṃ nāvāvissajjanadivaseyeva patvā kammakārako hutvā nāvaṃ abhiruhi. 
483470,110,1590,39,50,1,93,11,Nāvā samuddapiṭṭhe sattāhaṃ gantvā sattame divase samuddamajjhe ākoṭetvā ṭhapitā viya aṭṭhāsi. 
483471,110,1590,51,58,1,66,6,"Te kāḷakaṇṇisalākaṃ cāresuṃ, sattakkhattuṃ mittavindakasseva pāpuṇi. "
