483473,110,1590,73,94,1,225,20,Mittavindako veḷukalāpe nipajjitvā samuddapiṭṭhe gacchanto kassapasammāsambuddhakāle rakkhitasīlassa phalena samuddapiṭṭhe ekasmiṃ phalikavimāne catasso devadhītaro paṭilabhitvā tāsaṃ santike sukhaṃ anubhavamāno sattāhaṃ vasi. 
483474,110,1590,95,104,1,65,8,"Tā pana vimānapetiyo sattāhaṃ sukhaṃ anubhavanti, sattāhaṃ dukkhaṃ. "
483475,110,1590,105,123,1,95,13,"Sattāhaṃ dukkhaṃ anubhavituṃ gacchamānā‘‘ yāva mayaṃ āgacchāma, tāva idheva hohī’’ ti vatvā agamaṃsu. "
483476,110,1591,2,14,1,103,11,Mittavindako tāsaṃ gatakāle veḷukalāpe nipajjitvā purato gacchanto rajatavimāne aṭṭha devadhītaro labhi. 
483477,110,1591,15,25,1,81,9,"Tatopi paraṃ gacchanto maṇivimāne soḷasa, kanakavimāne dvattiṃsa devadhītaro labhi. "
483478,110,1591,26,35,1,78,9,Tāsampi vacanaṃ akatvā parato gacchanto antaradīpake ekaṃ yakkhanagaraṃ addasa. 
483479,110,1591,36,40,1,36,4,Tatthekā yakkhinī ajarūpena vicarati. 
