483481,110,1591,62,75,1,134,13,So tāya khitto samuddamatthakena gantvā bārāṇasiyaṃ parikhāpiṭṭhe ekasmiṃ kaṇṭakagumbamatthake patitvā pavaṭṭamāno bhūmiyaṃ patiṭṭhāsi. 
483482,110,1591,76,85,1,70,9,Tasmiñca samaye tasmiṃ parikhāpiṭṭhe rañño ajikā caramānā corā haranti. 
483483,110,1591,86,98,1,56,7,Ajikagopakā‘‘ core gaṇhissāmā’’ ti ekamantaṃ nilīnā aṭṭhaṃsu. 
483484,110,1591,99,120,1,133,19,Mittavindako pavaṭṭitvā bhūmiyaṃ ṭhito tā ajikā disvā cintesi‘‘ ahaṃ samudde ekasmiṃ dīpake ajikaṃ pāde gahetvā tāya khitto idha patito. 
483485,110,1591,121,138,1,103,14,"Sace idāni ekaṃ ajikaṃ pāde gahessāmi, sā maṃ parato samuddapiṭṭhe vimānadevatānaṃ santike khipissatī’’ ti. "
483486,110,1591,139,150,1,69,10,"So evaṃ ayoniso manasikaritvā ajikaṃ pāde gaṇhi, sā gahitamattā viravi. "
483487,110,1591,151,175,1,135,20,Ajikagopakā ito cito ca āgantvā taṃ gahetvā‘‘ ettakaṃ kālaṃ rājakule ajikakhādako esa coro’’ ti taṃ koṭṭetvā bandhitvā rañño santikaṃ nenti. 
483488,110,1592,2,16,1,131,14,Tasmiṃ khaṇe bodhisatto pañcasatamāṇavakaparivuto nagarā nikkhamma nhāyituṃ gacchanto mittavindakaṃ disvā sañjānitvā te manusse āha–
