483500,110,1596,8,12,1,38,3,{Hitānukampino}ti hitena anukampamānassa. 
483501,110,1596,13,18,1,45,4,{Ovajjamāno}ti mudukena hitacittena ovadiyamāno. 
483502,110,1596,19,30,1,64,10,"Na karoti sāsanan ti anusiṭṭhaṃ na karoti, dubbaco anovādako hoti. "
483503,110,1596,31,52,1,146,18,"Mittako viya {socatī}ti yathāyaṃ mittavindako ajikāya pādaṃ gahetvā socati kilamati, evaṃ niccakālaṃ socatīti imāya gāthāya bodhisatto dhammaṃ desesi. "
483504,110,1597,2,11,1,76,9,Evaṃ tena therena ettake addhāne tīsuyeva attabhāvesu kucchipūro laddhapubbo. 
483505,110,1597,12,28,1,152,13,"Yakkhena hutvā ekadivasaṃ gabbhamalaṃ laddhaṃ, sunakhena hutvā ekadivasaṃ bhattavamanaṃ, parinibbānadivase dhammasenāpatissānubhāvena catumadhuraṃ laddhaṃ. "
483506,110,1597,29,35,1,60,6,Evaṃ parassa lābhantarāyakaraṇaṃ nāma mahādosanti veditabbaṃ. 
483507,110,1597,36,44,1,61,8,Tasmiṃ pana kāle sopi ācariyo mittavindakopi yathākammaṃ gato. 
483508,110,1598,2,25,1,161,17,"Satthā ‘‘ evaṃ, bhikkhave, attano appalābhibhāvañca ariyadhammalābhibhāvañca sayameva esa akāsī’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
483509,110,1598,26,40,1,83,9,"‘‘ tadā mittavindako losakatissatthero ahosi, disāpāmokkhācariyo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483510,110,1599,2,4,1,27,2,Losakajātakavaṇṇanā paṭhamā.
483511,110,1601,2,7,1,19,2,[ 42]2. Kapotajātakavaṇṇanā 
483512,110,1602,2,13,1,87,10,Yo {atthakāmassā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ lolabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483513,110,1602,14,20,1,54,6,Tassa lolabhāvo navakanipāte kākajātake āvi bhavissati. 
483514,110,1602,21,38,1,65,11,"Tadā pana taṃ bhikkhū‘‘ ayaṃ, bhante, bhikkhu lolo’’ ti satthu ārocesuṃ. "
483515,110,1602,39,54,1,57,10,Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu lolosī’’ ti pucchi.
483516,110,1602,55,63,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, bhante’’ ti. "
483517,110,1602,64,87,1,136,18,"Satthā‘‘ pubbepi tvaṃ bhikkhu lolo lolakāraṇā jīvitakkhayaṃ patto, paṇḍitāpi taṃ nissāya attano vasanaṭṭhānā parihīnā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483518,110,1603,2,10,1,80,8,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto pārāvatayoniyaṃ nibbatti. 
483519,110,1603,11,21,1,105,10,Tadā bārāṇasivāsino puññakāmatāya tasmiṃ tasmiṃ ṭhāne sakuṇānaṃ sukhavasanatthāya thusapacchiyo olambenti. 
483520,110,1603,22,35,1,115,12,"Bārāṇasiseṭṭhinopi bhattakārako attano mahānase ekaṃ thusapacchiṃ olambetvā ṭhapesi, bodhisatto tattha vāsaṃ kappesi. "
483521,110,1603,36,47,1,79,11,So pātova nikkhamitvā gocare caritvā sāyaṃ āgantvā tattha vasanto kālaṃ khepesi. 
483522,110,1603,48,101,1,406,43,Athekadivasaṃ eko kāko mahānasamatthakena gacchanto ambilānambilamacchamaṃsānaṃ dhūpanavāsaṃ ghāyitvā lobhaṃ uppādetvā‘‘ kaṃ nu kho nissāya imaṃ macchamaṃsaṃ labhissāmī’’ ti avidūre nisīditvā pariggaṇhanto sāyaṃ bodhisattaṃ āgantvā mahānasaṃ pavisantaṃ disvā‘‘ imaṃ pārāvataṃ nissāya macchamaṃsaṃ labhissāmī’’ ti punadivase pātova āgantvā bodhisattassa nikkhamitvā gocaratthāya gamanakāle piṭṭhito piṭṭhito agamāsi. 
483523,110,1603,102,119,1,65,11,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto‘‘ kasmā tvaṃ, samma, amhehi saddhiṃ carasī’’ ti āha."
483524,110,1603,120,136,1,72,10,"‘‘ Sāmi, tumhāhaṃ kiriyā mayhaṃ ruccati, ito paṭṭhāya tumhe upaṭṭhahissāmī’’ ti."
483525,110,1603,137,154,1,78,10,"‘‘ Samma, tumhe aññagocarā, mayaṃ aññagocarā, tumhehi amhākaṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ dukkaran’’ ti."
483526,110,1603,155,170,1,87,10,"‘‘ Sāmi, tumhākaṃ gocaraggahaṇakāle ahampi gocaraṃ gahetvā tumhehi saddhiṃyeva gamissāmī’’ ti."
483527,110,1603,171,190,1,111,14,"‘‘ Sādhu, kevalaṃ te appamattena bhavitabban’’ ti evaṃ bodhisatto kākaṃ ovaditvā gocaraṃ caranto tiṇabījādīni khādati. "
483528,110,1603,191,230,1,288,33,"Bodhisattassa pana gocaraggahaṇakāle kāko gantvā gomayapiṇḍaṃ apanetvā pāṇake khāditvā udaraṃ pūretvā bodhisattassa santikaṃ āgantvā‘‘ sāmi, tumhe ativelaṃ caratha, atibahubhakkhena nāma bhavituṃ na vaṭṭatī’’ ti vatvā bodhisattena gocaraṃ gahetvā sāyaṃ āgacchantena saddhiṃyeva mahānasaṃ pāvisi. "
483529,110,1603,231,246,1,78,10,Bhattakārako ‘‘ amhākaṃ kapoto aññampi gahetvā āgato’’ ti kākassapi pacchiṃ ṭhapesi. 
483530,110,1603,247,252,1,30,5,Tato paṭṭhāya dve janā vasanti. 
483531,110,1604,2,7,1,51,5,Athekadivasaṃ seṭṭhissa bahuṃ macchamaṃsaṃ āhariṃsu. 
483532,110,1604,8,15,1,54,7,Taṃ ādāya bhattakārako mahānase tattha tattha olambesi. 
483533,110,1604,16,35,1,111,15,Kāko taṃ disvā lobhaṃ uppādetvā‘‘ sve gocarabhūmiṃ agantvā mayā idameva khāditabban’’ ti rattiṃ nitthunanto nipajji. 
483534,110,1604,36,51,1,62,9,"Punadivase bodhisatto gocarāya gacchanto‘‘ ehi, samma, kākā’’ ti āha."
483535,110,1604,52,65,1,47,7,"‘‘ Sāmi, tumhe gacchatha, mayhaṃ kucchirogo atthī’’ ti."
483536,110,1604,66,116,1,305,39,"‘‘ Samma, kākānaṃ kucchirogo nāma na kadāci bhūtapubbo, rattiṃ tīsu yāmesu ekekasmiṃ yāme mucchitā honti, dīpavaṭṭiṃ gilitakāle pana nesaṃ muhuttaṃ titti hoti, tvaṃ imaṃ macchamaṃsaṃ khāditukāmo bhavissasi, ehi manussaparibhogo nāma tumhākaṃ dupparibhuñjiyo, mā evarūpaṃ akāsi, mayā saddhiṃyeva gocarāya gacchāhī’’ ti."
483537,110,1604,117,126,1,18,4,"‘‘ Na sakkomi, sāmī’’ ti."
483538,110,1604,127,147,1,110,15,"‘‘ Tena hi paññāyissasi sakena kammena, lobhavasaṃ agantvā appamatto hohī’’ ti taṃ ovaditvā bodhisatto gocarāya gato. "
483539,110,1605,2,19,1,193,16,Bhattakārako nānappakāraṃ macchamaṃsavikatiṃ sampādetvā usumanikkhamanatthaṃ bhājanāni thokaṃ vivaritvā rasaparissāvanakaroṭiṃ bhājanamatthake ṭhapetvā bahi nikkhamitvā sedaṃ puñchamāno aṭṭhāsi. 
483540,110,1605,20,78,1,382,46,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe kāko pacchito sīsaṃ ukkhipitvā bhattagehaṃ olokento tassa nikkhantabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ ayaṃdāni mayhaṃ manorathaṃ pūretvā maṃsaṃ khādituṃ kālo, kiṃ nu kho mahāmaṃsaṃ khādāmi, udāhu cuṇṇikamaṃsan’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ cuṇṇikamaṃsena nāma khippaṃ kucchiṃ pūretuṃ na sakkā, mahantaṃ maṃsakhaṇḍaṃ āharitvā pacchiyaṃ nikkhipitvā khādamāno nipajjissāmī’’ ti pacchito uppatitvā rasakaroṭiyaṃ nilīyi. "
483541,110,1605,79,87,1,22,4,Sā‘‘ kirī’’ ti saddamakāsi. 
483542,110,1605,88,148,1,366,48,"Bhattakārako taṃ saddaṃ sutvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho etan’’ ti paviṭṭho kākaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ duṭṭhakāko mahāseṭṭhino pakkamaṃsaṃ khāditukāmo, ahaṃ kho pana seṭṭhiṃ nissāya jīvāmi, na imaṃ bālaṃ, kiṃ me iminā’’ ti dvāraṃ pidhāya kākaṃ gahetvā sakalasarīre pattāni luñcitvā allasiṅgīveraloṇajīrakādayo koṭṭetvā ambilatakkena āloḷetvā tenassa sakalasarīraṃ makkhetvā taṃ kākaṃ pacchiyaṃ khipi. "
483543,110,1605,149,153,1,46,4,So adhimattavedanābhibhūto nitthunanto nipajji. 
483544,110,1606,2,26,1,142,19,"Bodhisatto sāyaṃ āgantvā taṃ byasanappattaṃ disvā‘‘ lolakāka, mama vacanaṃ akatvā tava lobhaṃ nissāya mahādukkhaṃ pattosī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
483545,110,1607,2,4,1,0,0,42.
483546,110,1608,2,12,1,58,8,"‘ ‘ Yo atthakāmassa hitānukampino, ovajjamāno na karoti sāsanaṃ; "
483547,110,1609,2,11,1,57,6,"Kapotakassa vacanaṃ akatvā, amittahatthatthagatova setī’’ ti. "
483548,110,1610,2,10,1,74,7,Tattha kapotakassa vacanaṃ {akatvā}ti pārāvatassa hitānusāsanavacanaṃ akatvā. 
483549,110,1610,11,30,1,179,18,Amittahatthatthagatova {setī}ti amittānaṃ anatthakārakānaṃ dukkhuppādakapuggalānaṃ hatthatthaṃ hatthapathaṃ gato ayaṃ kāko viya so puggalo mahantaṃ byasanaṃ patvā anusocamāno setīti. 
483550,110,1611,2,22,1,90,15,Bodhisatto imaṃ gāthaṃ vatvā‘‘ idāni mayā ca imasmiṃ ṭhāne na sakkā vasitun’’ ti aññattha gato. 
483551,110,1611,23,27,1,35,4,Kākopi tattheva jīvitakkhayaṃ patto. 
483552,110,1611,28,36,1,69,8,Atha naṃ bhattakārako saddhiṃ pacchiyā gahetvā saṅkāraṭṭhāne chaḍḍesi. 
483553,110,1612,2,36,1,206,27,"Satthāpi ‘‘ na tvaṃ bhikkhu idāneva lolo, pubbepi loloyeva, tañca pana te lolyaṃ nissāya paṇḍitāpi sakāvāsā parihīnā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne so bhikkhu anāgāmiphalaṃ patto. "
483554,110,1612,37,42,1,46,5,Satthā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
483555,110,1612,43,57,1,59,9,"‘‘ tadā kāko lolabhikkhu ahosi, pārāvato pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483556,110,1613,2,4,1,26,2,Kapotajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
483557,110,1615,2,7,1,19,2,[ 43]3. Veḷukajātakavaṇṇanā 
483558,110,1616,2,14,1,90,10,Yo {atthakāmassā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ dubbacabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483559,110,1616,15,63,1,233,32,"Tañhi bhagavā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu dubbacosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ na tvaṃ bhikkhu idāneva dubbaco, pubbepi dubbacoyeva, dubbacattāyeva ca paṇḍitānaṃ vacanaṃ akatvā sappamukhe jīvitakkhayaṃ patto’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483560,110,1617,2,42,1,377,40,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe mahābhogakule nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā kāmesu ādīnavaṃ nekkhamme cānisaṃsaṃ disvā kāme pahāya himavantaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā kasiṇaparikammaṃ katvā pañcābhiññā aṭṭha samāpattiyo ca uppādetvā jhānasukhena vītināmento aparabhāge mahāparivāro pañcahi tāpasasatehi parivuto gaṇassa satthā hutvā vihāsi. 
483561,110,1617,43,52,1,86,9,Atheko āsivisapotako attano dhammatāya caranto aññatarassa tāpasassa assamapadaṃ patto. 
483562,110,1617,53,62,1,80,9,Tāpaso tasmiṃ puttasinehaṃ uppādetvā taṃ ekasmiṃ veḷupabbe sayāpetvā paṭijaggati. 
483563,110,1617,63,74,1,50,7,Tassa veḷupabbe sayanato‘‘ veḷuko’’ tveva nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
483564,110,1617,75,87,1,71,8,Taṃ puttasinehena paṭijagganato tāpasassa‘‘ veḷukapitā’’ tveva nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
483565,110,1618,2,51,1,206,31,"Tadā bodhisatto‘‘ eko kira tāpaso āsivisaṃ paṭijaggatī’’ ti sutvā taṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ āsivisaṃ paṭijaggasī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccan’’ ti vutte‘‘ āsivisena saddhiṃ vissāso nāma natthi, mā evaṃ jaggāhī’’ ti āha."
483566,110,1618,52,67,1,59,10,"‘‘ So me ācariya putto, nāhaṃ tena vinā vattituṃ sakkhissāmī’’ ti."
483567,110,1618,68,79,1,53,7,‘‘ Tena hi etasseva santikā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇissasī’’ ti. 
483568,110,1618,80,89,1,65,8,"Tāpaso bodhisattassa vacanaṃ na gaṇhi, āsivisampi jahituṃ nāsakkhi. "
483569,110,1618,90,115,1,221,24,"Tato katipāhaccayeneva sabbe tāpasā phalāphalatthāya gantvā gataṭṭhāne phalāphalassa sulabhabhāvaṃ disvā dve tayo divase tattheva vasiṃsu, veḷukapitāpi tehi saddhiṃ gacchanto āsivisaṃ veḷupabbeyeva sayāpetvā pidahitvā gato. "
483570,110,1618,116,144,1,142,18,"So puna tāpasehi saddhiṃ dvīhatīhaccayena āgantvā‘‘ veḷukassa gocaraṃ dassāmī’’ ti veḷupabbaṃ ugghāṭetvā‘‘ ehi, puttaka, chātakosī’’ ti hatthaṃ pasāresi. "
483571,110,1618,145,157,1,120,12,Āsiviso dvīhatīhaṃ nirāhāratāya kujjhitvā pasāritahatthaṃ ḍaṃsitvā tāpasaṃ tattheva jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā araññaṃ pāvisi. 
483572,110,1618,158,163,1,39,5,Tāpasā taṃ disvā bodhisattassa ārocesuṃ. 
483573,110,1618,164,176,1,99,11,Bodhisatto tassa sarīrakiccaṃ kāretvā isigaṇassa majjhe nisīditvā isīnaṃ ovādavasena imaṃ gāthamāha– 
483574,110,1619,2,4,1,0,0,43.
483575,110,1620,2,13,1,58,8,"‘ ‘ Yo atthakāmassa hitānukampino, ovajjamāno na karoti sāsanaṃ; "
483576,110,1621,2,13,1,43,8,"Evaṃ so nihato seti, veḷukassa yathā pitā’’ ti. "
483577,110,1622,2,31,1,164,26,"Tattha evaṃ so nihato {setī}ti yo hi isīnaṃ ovādaṃ na gaṇhāti, so yathā esa tāpaso āsivisamukhe pūtibhāvaṃ patvā nihato seti, evaṃ mahāvināsaṃ patvā nihato setīti attho. "
483578,110,1622,32,42,1,96,10,Evaṃ bodhisatto isigaṇaṃ ovaditvā cattāro brahmavihāre bhāvetvā āyupariyosāne brahmaloke uppajji. 
483579,110,1623,2,30,1,179,21,"Satthā ‘‘ na tvaṃ bhikkhu idāneva dubbaco, pubbepi dubbacoyeva, dubbacabhāveneva ca āsivisamukhe pūtibhāvaṃ patto’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
483580,110,1623,31,48,1,94,11,"‘‘ tadā veḷukapitā dubbacabhikkhu ahosi, sesaparisā buddhaparisā, gaṇasatthā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483581,110,1624,2,4,1,26,2,Veḷukajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
483582,110,1626,2,7,1,19,2,[ 44]4. Makasajātakavaṇṇanā 
483583,110,1627,2,15,1,107,12,Seyyo {amitto}ti idaṃ satthā magadhesu cārikaṃ caramāno aññatarasmiṃ gāmake bālagāmikamanusse ārabbha kathesi. 
483584,110,1627,16,29,1,114,13,Tathāgato kira ekasmiṃ samaye sāvatthito magadharaṭṭhaṃ gantvā tattha cārikaṃ caramāno aññataraṃ gāmakaṃ sampāpuṇi. 
483585,110,1627,30,36,1,54,6,So ca gāmako yebhuyyena andhabālamanussehiyeva ussanno. 
483586,110,1627,37,100,1,419,52,"Tatthekadivasaṃ te andhabālamanussā sannipatitvā‘‘ bho, amhe araññaṃ pavisitvā kammaṃ karonte makasā khādanti, tappaccayā amhākaṃ kammacchedo hoti, sabbeva dhanūni ceva āvudhāni ca ādāya gantvā makasehi saddhiṃ yujjhitvā sabbamakase vijjhitvā chinditvā ca māressāmā’’ ti mantayitvā araññaṃ gantvā‘‘ makase vijjhissāmā’’ ti aññamaññaṃ vijjhitvā ca paharitvā ca dukkhappattā āgantvā antogāme ca gāmamajjhe ca gāmadvāre ca nipajjiṃsu. "
483587,110,1628,2,8,1,53,6,Satthā bhikkhusaṅghaparivuto taṃ gāmaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
483588,110,1628,9,24,1,147,14,Avasesā paṇḍitamanussā bhagavantaṃ disvā gāmadvāre maṇḍapaṃ kāretvā buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa mahādānaṃ datvā satthāraṃ vanditvā nisīdiṃsu. 
483589,110,1628,25,48,1,107,17,"Satthā tasmiṃ tasmiṃ ṭhāne patitamanusse disvā te upāsake pucchi ‘‘ bahū ime gilānā manussā, kiṃ etehi katan’’ ti?"
483590,110,1628,49,69,1,94,13,"‘‘ Bhante, ete manussā‘ makasayuddhaṃ karissāmā’ ti gantvā aññamaññaṃ vijjhitvā sayaṃ gilānā jātā’’ ti. "
483591,110,1628,70,102,1,184,23,"Satthā‘‘ na idāneva andhabālamanussā‘ makase paharissāmā’ ti attānaṃ paharanti, pubbepi‘ makasaṃ paharissāmā’ ti paraṃ paharaṇakamanussā ahesuṃyevā’’ ti vatvā tehi manussehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
483592,110,1629,2,11,1,81,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto vaṇijjāya jīvikaṃ kappeti. 
483593,110,1629,12,20,1,58,7,Tadā kāsiraṭṭhe ekasmiṃ paccantagāme bahū vaḍḍhakī vasanti. 
483594,110,1629,21,38,1,155,16,"Tattheko khalitavaḍḍhakī rukkhaṃ tacchati, athassa eko makaso tambalohathālakapiṭṭhisadise sīse nisīditvā sattiyā paharanto viya sīsaṃ mukhatuṇḍakena vijjhi. "
483595,110,1629,39,45,1,37,6,So attano santike nisinnaṃ puttaṃ āha–
483596,110,1629,46,63,1,70,11,"‘‘ tāta, mayhaṃ sīsaṃ makaso sattiyā paharanto viya vijjhati, vārehi nan’’ ti."
483597,110,1629,64,76,1,47,6,"‘‘ Tāta, adhivāsehi, ekappahāreneva taṃ māressāmī’’ ti. "
483598,110,1629,77,90,1,104,13,Tasmiṃ samaye bodhisattopi attano bhaṇḍaṃ pariyesamāno taṃ gāmaṃ patvā tassā vaḍḍhakisālāya nisinno hoti. 
483599,110,1629,91,96,1,27,5,Atha so vaḍḍhakī puttaṃ āha–
483600,110,1629,97,107,1,27,5,"‘‘ tāta, imaṃ makasaṃ vārehī’’ ti. "
483601,110,1629,108,139,1,167,21,"So‘‘ vāressāmi, tātā’’ ti tikhiṇaṃ mahāpharasuṃ ukkhipitvā pitu piṭṭhipasse ṭhatvā‘‘ makasaṃ paharissāmī’’ ti pitu matthakaṃ dvidhā bhindi, vaḍḍhakī tattheva jīvitakkhayaṃ patto. "
483602,110,1630,2,12,1,62,8,Bodhisatto tassa taṃ kammaṃ disvā‘‘ paccāmittopi paṇḍitova seyyo. 
