483634,110,1644,9,22,1,75,10,"Yañce {bālānukampako}ti ettha yan ti liṅgavipallāso kato, {ce}ti nāmatthe nipāto. "
483635,110,1644,23,37,1,94,12,"Yo nāma bālo anukampako, tato sataguṇena sahassaguṇena paṇḍito amitto hontopi seyyoyevāti attho. "
483636,110,1644,38,49,1,65,10,"Atha vā yan ti paṭisedhanatthe nipāto, no ce bālānukampakoti attho. "
483637,110,1644,50,54,1,25,4,Jammin ti lāmikaṃ dandhaṃ. 
