483643,110,1648,2,7,1,24,2,[ 46]6. Ārāmadūsakajātakavaṇṇanā 
483644,110,1649,2,14,1,101,11,Na ve {anatthakusalenā}ti idaṃ satthā aññatarasmiṃ kosalagāmake viharanto uyyānadūsakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483645,110,1649,15,23,1,65,8,Satthā kira kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno aññataraṃ gāmakaṃ sampāpuṇi. 
483646,110,1649,24,47,1,161,18,"Tattheko kuṭumbiko tathāgataṃ nimantetvā attano uyyāne nisīdāpetvā buddhappamukhassa saṅghassa mahādānaṃ datvā‘‘ bhante, yathāruciyā imasmiṃ uyyāne vicarathā’’ ti āha. "
483647,110,1649,48,86,1,217,31,"Bhikkhū uṭṭhāya uyyānapālaṃ gahetvā uyyāne vicarantā ekaṃ aṅgaṇaṭṭhānaṃ disvā uyyānapālaṃ pucchiṃsu‘‘ upāsaka, imaṃ uyyānaṃ aññattha sandacchāyaṃ, imasmiṃ pana ṭhāne na koci rukkho vā gaccho vā atthi, kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti?"
483648,110,1649,87,107,1,133,16,"‘‘ Bhante, imassa uyyānassa ropanakāle eko gāmadārako udakaṃ siñcanto imasmiṃ ṭhāne rukkhapotake ummūlaṃ katvā mūlappamāṇena udakaṃ siñci . "
483649,110,1649,108,112,1,30,4,Te rukkhapotakā milāyitvā matā. 
483650,110,1649,113,122,1,43,7,Iminā kāraṇena idaṃ ṭhānaṃ aṅgaṇaṃ jātan’’ ti. 
483651,110,1649,123,128,1,51,5,Bhikkhū satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. 
483652,110,1649,129,149,1,99,13,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, so gāmadārako idāneva ārāmadūsako, pubbepi ārāmadūsakoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483653,110,1650,2,10,1,78,8,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bārāṇasiyaṃ nakkhattaṃ ghosayiṃsu. 
483654,110,1650,11,17,1,94,6,Nakkhattabherisaddasavanakālato paṭṭhāya sakalanagaravāsino nakkhattanissitakā hutvā vicaranti. 
483655,110,1650,18,24,1,38,6,Tadā rañño uyyāne bahū makkaṭā vasanti. 
483656,110,1650,25,73,1,292,33,"Uyyānapālo cintesi‘‘ nagare nakkhattaṃ ghuṭṭhaṃ, ime vānare‘ udakaṃ siñcathā’ ti vatvā ahaṃ nakkhattaṃ kīḷissāmī’’ ti jeṭṭhakavānaraṃ upasaṅkamitvā ‘‘ samma vānarajeṭṭhaka, imaṃ uyyānaṃ tumhākampi bahūpakāraṃ, tumhe ettha pupphaphalapallavāni khādatha, nagare nakkhattaṃ ghuṭṭhaṃ, ahaṃ nakkhattaṃ kīḷissāmi. "
483657,110,1650,74,88,1,91,11,"Yāvāhaṃ āgacchāmi, tāva imasmiṃ uyyāne rukkhapotakesu udakaṃ siñcituṃ sakkhissathā’’ ti pucchi."
483658,110,1650,89,97,1,19,3,"‘‘ Sādhu, siñcissāmī’’ ti."
483659,110,1650,98,115,1,87,13,‘‘ Tena hi appamattā hothā’’ ti udakasiñcanatthāya tesaṃ cammakuṭe ca dārukuṭe ca datvā gato. 
483660,110,1650,116,125,1,72,9,Vānarā cammakuṭe ceva dārukuṭe ca gahetvā rukkhapotakesu udakaṃ siñcanti. 
483661,110,1650,126,164,1,253,30,"Atha ne vānarajeṭṭhako evamāha‘‘ bhonto vānarā, udakaṃ nāma rakkhitabbaṃ, tumhe rukkhapotakesu udakaṃ siñcantā uppāṭetvā uppāṭetvā mūlaṃ oloketvā gambhīragatesu mūlesu bahuṃ udakaṃ siñcatha, agambhīragatesu appaṃ, pacchā amhākaṃ udakaṃ dullabhaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti. "
483662,110,1650,165,175,1,39,6,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā tathā akaṃsu. 
483663,110,1651,2,29,1,171,22,"Tasmiṃ samaye eko paṇḍitapuriso rājuyyāne te vānare tathā karonte disvā evamāha‘‘ bhonto vānarā, kasmā tumhe rukkhapotake uppāṭetvā uppāṭetvā mūlappamāṇena udakaṃ siñcathā’’ ti? "
483664,110,1651,30,41,1,43,7,Te‘‘ evaṃ no vānarajeṭṭhako ovadatī’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
483665,110,1651,42,67,1,114,18,"So taṃ vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ aho vata bho bālā apaṇḍitā,‘ atthaṃ karissāmā’ ti anatthameva karontī’’ ti cintetvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
483666,110,1652,2,4,1,0,0,46.
483667,110,1653,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Na ve anatthakusalena, atthacariyā sukhāvahā; "
483668,110,1654,2,12,1,44,7,"Hāpeti atthaṃ dummedho, kapi ārāmiko yathā’’ ti. "
483669,110,1655,2,6,1,24,3,Tattha {ve}ti nipātamattaṃ. 
483670,110,1655,7,19,1,86,10,"{Anatthakusalenā}ti anatthe anāyatane kusalena, atthe āyatane kāraṇe akusalena vāti attho. "
483671,110,1655,20,23,1,26,2,{Atthacariyā}ti vuḍḍhikiriyā. 
483672,110,1655,24,38,1,123,12,"{Sukhāvahā}ti evarūpena anatthakusalena kāyikacetasikasukhasaṅkhātassa atthassa cariyā na sukhāvahā, na sakkā āvahitunti attho. "
483673,110,1655,39,40,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
483674,110,1655,41,60,1,104,13,"Ekanteneva hi hāpeti atthaṃ {dummedho}ti, bālapuggalo‘‘ atthaṃ karissāmī’’ ti atthaṃ hāpetvā anatthameva karoti. "
483675,110,1655,61,95,1,198,26,"Kapi ārāmiko {yathā}ti yathā ārāme niyutto ārāmarakkhanako makkaṭo‘‘ atthaṃ karissāmī’’ ti anatthameva karoti, evaṃ yo koci anatthakusalo, tena na sakkā atthacariyaṃ āvahituṃ, so ekaṃsena atthaṃ hāpetiyevāti. "
483676,110,1655,96,110,1,99,13,Evaṃ so paṇḍito puriso imāya gāthāya vānarajeṭṭhakaṃ garahitvā attano parisaṃ ādāya uyyānā nikkhami. 
483677,110,1656,2,27,1,151,17,"Satthāpi ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, esa gāmadārako idāneva ārāmadūsako, pubbepi ārāmadūsakoyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
483678,110,1656,28,42,1,84,9,"‘‘ tadā vānarajeṭṭhako ārāmadūsakagāmadārako ahosi, paṇḍitapuriso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483679,110,1657,2,4,1,32,2,Ārāmadūsakajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
483680,110,1659,2,7,1,25,2,[ 47]7. Vāruṇidūsakajātakavaṇṇanā 
483681,110,1660,2,13,1,84,10,Na ve {anatthakusalenā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto vāruṇidūsakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483682,110,1660,14,44,1,213,25,"Anāthapiṇḍikassa kira sahāyo eko vāruṇivāṇijo tikhiṇaṃ vāruṇiṃ yojetvā hiraññasuvaṇṇādīni gahetvā vikkiṇanto mahājane sannipatite‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ mūlaṃ gahetvā vāruṇiṃ dehī’’ ti antevāsikaṃ āṇāpetvā sayaṃ nhāyituṃ agamāsi. "
483683,110,1660,45,74,1,211,24,"Antevāsiko mahājanassa vāruṇiṃ dento manusse antarantarā loṇasakkharā āharāpetvā khādante disvā‘‘ ayaṃ surā aloṇikā bhavissati, loṇamettha pakkhipissāmī’’ ti surācāṭiyaṃ nāḷimattaṃ loṇaṃ pakkhipitvā tesaṃ suraṃ adāsi. "
483684,110,1660,75,89,1,61,10,Te mukhaṃ pūretvā pūretvā chaḍḍetvā‘‘ kiṃ te katan’’ ti pucchiṃsu.
483685,110,1660,90,103,1,60,9,‘‘ Tumhe suraṃ pivitvā loṇaṃ āharāpente disvā loṇena yojesin’’ ti.
483686,110,1660,104,119,1,81,11,‘‘ Evarūpaṃ nāma manāpaṃ vāruṇiṃ nāsesi bālā’’ ti taṃ garahitvā uṭṭhāyuṭṭhāya pakkantā. 
483687,110,1660,120,138,1,89,12,"Vāruṇivāṇijo āgantvā ekampi adisvā ‘‘ vāruṇipāyakā kahaṃ gatā’’ ti pucchi, so tamatthaṃ ārocesi. "
483688,110,1660,139,159,1,100,15,"Atha naṃ ācariyo‘‘ bāla, evarūpā nāma te surā nāsitā’’ ti garahitvā imaṃ kāraṇaṃ anāthapiṇḍikassa ārocesi. "
483689,110,1660,160,176,1,103,12,Anāthapiṇḍiko‘‘ atthidāni me idaṃ kathāpābhatan’’ ti jetavanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā etamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
483690,110,1660,177,198,1,102,14,"Satthā‘‘ na esa, gahapati, idāneva vāruṇidūsako, pubbepi vāruṇidūsakoyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
483691,110,1661,2,12,1,80,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto bārāṇasiyaṃ seṭṭhi ahosi. 
483692,110,1661,13,18,1,38,5,Taṃ upanissāya eko vāruṇivāṇijo jīvati. 
483693,110,1661,19,34,1,75,11,So tikhiṇaṃ suraṃ yojetvā‘‘ imaṃ vikkiṇāhī’’ ti antevāsikaṃ vatvā nhāyituṃ gato. 
483694,110,1661,35,45,1,86,10,Antevāsiko tasmiṃ gatamatteyeva surāya loṇaṃ pakkhipitvā imināva nayena suraṃ vināsesi. 
483695,110,1661,46,54,1,59,8,Athassa ācariyo āgantvā taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā seṭṭhissa ārocesi. 
483696,110,1661,55,74,1,94,13,Seṭṭhi‘‘ anatthakusalā nāma bālā‘ atthaṃ karissāmā’ ti anatthameva karontī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
483697,110,1662,2,4,1,0,0,47.
483698,110,1663,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Na ve anatthakusalena, atthacariyā sukhāvahā; "
483699,110,1664,2,12,1,48,7,"Hāpeti atthaṃ dummedho, koṇḍañño vāruṇiṃ yathā’’ ti. "
483700,110,1665,2,35,1,224,27,"Tattha koṇḍañño vāruṇiṃ {yathā}ti yathā ayaṃ koṇḍaññanāmako antevāsiko‘‘ atthaṃ karissāmī’’ ti loṇaṃ pakkhipitvā vāruṇiṃ hāpesi parihāpesi vināsesi, evaṃ sabbopi anatthakusalo atthaṃ hāpetīti bodhisatto imāya gāthāya dhammaṃ desesi. "
483701,110,1666,2,21,1,119,14,"Satthāpi ‘‘ na esa gahapati idāneva vāruṇidūsako, pubbepi vāruṇidūsakoyevā’’ ti vatvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
483702,110,1666,22,37,1,84,10,"‘‘ tadā vāruṇidūsako idānipi vāruṇidūsakova ahosi, bārāṇasiseṭṭhi pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483703,110,1667,2,4,1,33,2,Vāruṇidūsakajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
483704,110,1669,2,7,1,20,2,[ 48]8. Vedabbajātakavaṇṇanā 
483705,110,1670,2,13,1,85,11,Anupāyena yo atthan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto dubbacabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483706,110,1670,14,56,1,254,34,"Tañhi bhikkhuṃ satthā‘‘ na tvaṃ bhikkhu idāneva dubbaco, pubbepi dubbacoyeva, teneva ca kāraṇena paṇḍitānaṃ vacanaṃ akatvā tiṇhena asinā dvidhā katvā chinno hutvā magge nipatittha, tañca ekakaṃ nissāya purisasahassaṃ jīvitakkhayaṃ pattan’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483707,110,1671,2,15,1,105,13,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente ekasmiṃ gāmake aññataro brāhmaṇo vedabbaṃ nāma mantaṃ jānāti. 
483708,110,1671,16,33,1,124,15,"So kira manto anaggho mahāraho, nakkhattayoge laddhe taṃ mantaṃ parivattetvā ākāse ullokite ākāsato sattaratanavassaṃ vassati. "
483709,110,1671,34,41,1,58,7,Tadā bodhisatto tassa brāhmaṇassa santike sippaṃ uggaṇhāti. 
483710,110,1671,42,63,1,191,20,"Athekadivasaṃ brāhmaṇo bodhisattaṃ ādāya kenacideva karaṇīyena attano gāmā nikkhamitvā cetaraṭṭhaṃ agamāsi, antarāmagge ca ekasmiṃ araññaṭṭhāne pañcasatā pesanakacorā nāma panthaghātaṃ karonti. "
483711,110,1671,64,68,1,44,4,Te bodhisattañca vedabbabrāhmaṇañca gaṇhiṃsu. 
483712,110,1671,69,78,1,37,5,Kasmā panete‘‘ pesanakacorā’’ ti vuccanti? 
483713,110,1671,79,96,1,89,12,"Te kira dve jane gahetvā ekaṃ dhanāharaṇatthāya pesenti, tasmā‘‘ pesanakacorā’’ tveva vuccanti. "
483714,110,1671,97,115,1,93,14,Tepi ca pitāputte gahetvā pitaraṃ‘‘ tvaṃ amhākaṃ dhanaṃ āharitvā puttaṃ gahetvā yāhī’’ ti vadanti. 
483715,110,1671,116,132,1,150,13,"Etenupāyena mātudhītaro gahetvā mātaraṃ vissajjenti, jeṭṭhakaniṭṭhe gahetvā jeṭṭhabhātikaṃ vissajjenti, ācariyantevāsike gahetvā antevāsikaṃ vissajjenti. "
483716,110,1671,133,140,1,63,7,Te tasmiṃ kāle vedabbabrāhmaṇaṃ gahetvā bodhisattaṃ vissajjesuṃ. 
483717,110,1672,2,35,1,234,27,"Bodhisatto ācariyaṃ vanditvā‘‘ ahaṃ ekāhadvīhaccayena āgamissāmi, tumhe mā bhāyittha, apica kho pana mama vacanaṃ karotha, ajja dhanavassāpanakanakkhattayogo bhavissati, mā kho tumhe dukkhaṃ asahantā mantaṃ parivattetvā dhanaṃ vassāpayittha. "
483718,110,1672,36,56,1,116,16,"Sace vassāpessatha, tumhe ca vināsaṃ pāpuṇissatha, ime ca pañcasatā corā’’ ti evaṃ ācariyaṃ ovaditvā dhanatthāya agamāsi. "
483719,110,1672,57,63,1,57,6,Corāpi sūriye atthaṅgate brāhmaṇaṃ bandhitvā nipajjāpesuṃ. 
483720,110,1672,64,68,1,62,4,Taṅkhaṇaññeva pācīnalokadhātuto paripuṇṇacandamaṇḍalaṃ uṭṭhahi. 
483721,110,1672,69,110,1,250,29,"Brāhmaṇo nakkhattaṃ olokento‘‘ dhanavassāpanakanakkhattayogo laddho, kiṃ me dukkhena anubhūtena, mantaṃ parivattetvā ratanavassaṃ vassāpetvā corānaṃ dhanaṃ datvā yathāsukhaṃ gamissāmī’’ ti cintetvā core āmantesi‘‘ bhonto corā, tumhe maṃ kimatthāya gaṇhathā’’ ti?"
483722,110,1672,111,119,1,19,3,"‘‘ Dhanatthāya, ayyā’’ ti."
483723,110,1672,120,144,1,147,18,"‘‘ Sace vo, dhanena attho, khippaṃ maṃ bandhanā mocetvā sīsaṃ nhāpetvā ahatavatthāni acchādetvā gandhehi vilimpāpetvā pupphāni pilandhāpetvā ṭhapethā’’ ti."
483724,110,1672,145,155,1,36,6,‘‘ Corā tassa kathaṃ sutvā tathā akaṃsu’’. 
483725,110,1673,2,15,1,99,11,"Brāhmaṇo nakkhattayogaṃ ñatvā mantaṃ parivattetvā ākāsaṃ ullokesi, tāvadeva ākāsato ratanāni patiṃsu. "
483726,110,1673,16,24,1,66,8,Corā taṃ dhanaṃ saṅkaḍḍhitvā uttarāsaṅgesu bhaṇḍikaṃ katvā pāyiṃsu. 
483727,110,1673,25,29,1,35,4,Brāhmaṇopi tesaṃ pacchatova agamāsi. 
483728,110,1673,30,37,1,41,7,Atha te core aññe pañcasatā corā gaṇhiṃsu.
483729,110,1673,38,55,1,57,9,‘‘ Kimatthaṃ amhe gaṇhathā’’ ti ca vuttā‘‘ dhanatthāyā’’ ti āhaṃsu.
483730,110,1673,56,79,1,114,16,"‘‘ Yadi vo dhanena attho, etaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ gaṇhatha, eso ākāsaṃ ulloketvā dhanaṃ vassāpesi, amhākampetaṃ eteneva dinnan’’ ti. "
483731,110,1673,80,93,1,65,9,Corā core vissajjetvā‘‘ amhākampi dhanaṃ dehī’’ ti brāhmaṇaṃ gaṇhiṃsu. 
483732,110,1673,94,107,1,108,10,"Brāhmaṇo‘‘ ahaṃ tumhākaṃ dhanaṃ dadeyyaṃ, dhanavassāpanakanakkhattayogo pana ito saṃvaccharamatthake bhavissati. "
483733,110,1673,108,121,1,68,9,"Yadi vo dhanenattho, adhivāsetha, tadā dhanavassaṃ vassāpessāmī’’ ti āha. "
483734,110,1673,122,179,1,400,50,"Corā kujjhitvā‘‘ ambho, duṭṭhabrāhmaṇa, aññesaṃ idāneva dhanaṃ vassāpetvā amhe aññaṃ saṃvaccharaṃ adhivāsāpesī’’ ti tiṇhena asinā brāhmaṇaṃ dvidhā chinditvā magge chaḍḍetvā vegena anubandhitvā tehi corehi saddhiṃ yujjhitvā te sabbepi māretvā dhanaṃ ādāya puna dve koṭṭhāsā hutvā aññamaññaṃ yujjhitvā aḍḍhateyyāni purisasatāni ghātetvā etena upāyena yāva dve janā avasiṭṭhā ahesuṃ, tāva aññamaññaṃ ghātayiṃsu. "
483735,110,1673,180,185,1,38,5,Evaṃ taṃ purisasahassaṃ vināsaṃ pattaṃ. 
483736,110,1674,2,30,1,185,25,"Te pana dve janā upāyena taṃ dhanaṃ āharitvā ekasmiṃ gāmasamīpe gahanaṭṭhāne dhanaṃ paṭicchādetvā eko khaggaṃ gahetvā rakkhanto nisīdi, eko taṇḍule gahetvā bhattaṃ pacāpetuṃ gāmaṃ pāvisi. "
483737,110,1674,31,57,1,173,21,"Lobho ca nāmesa vināsamūlamevāti dhanasantike nisinno cintesi‘‘ tasmiṃ āgate idaṃ dhanaṃ dve koṭṭhāsā bhavissanti, yaṃnūnāhaṃ taṃ āgatamattameva khaggena paharitvā ghāteyyan’’ ti. "
483738,110,1674,58,65,1,53,7,So khaggaṃ sannayhitvā tassa āgamanaṃ olokento nisīdi. 
483739,110,1674,66,91,1,158,20,"Itaropi cintesi‘‘ taṃ dhanaṃ dve koṭṭhāsā bhavissanti, yaṃnūnāhaṃ bhatte visaṃ pakkhipitvā taṃ purisaṃ bhojetvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā ekakova dhanaṃ gaṇheyyan’’ ti. "
483740,110,1674,92,104,1,84,12,So niṭṭhite bhatte sayaṃ bhuñjitvā sesake visaṃ pakkhipitvā taṃ ādāya tattha agamāsi. 
483741,110,1674,105,123,1,161,18,Taṃ bhattaṃ otāretvā ṭhitamattameva itaro khaggena dvidhā chinditvā taṃ paṭicchannaṭṭhāne chaḍḍetvā tañca bhattaṃ bhuñjitvā sayampi tattheva jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇi. 
483742,110,1674,124,131,1,51,7,Evañca taṃ dhanaṃ nissāya sabbeva vināsaṃ pāpuṇiṃsu. 
483743,110,1675,2,36,1,229,28,"Bodhisattopi kho ekāhadvīhaccayena dhanaṃ ādāya āgato tasmiṃ ṭhāne ācariyaṃ adisvā vippakiṇṇaṃ pana dhanaṃ disvā‘‘ ācariyena mama vacanaṃ akatvā dhanaṃ vassāpitaṃ bhavissati, sabbehi vināsaṃ pattehi bhavitabban’’ ti mahāmaggena pāyāsi. "
483744,110,1675,37,120,1,574,71,"Gacchanto ācariyaṃ mahāmagge dvidhā chinnaṃ disvā‘‘ mama vacanaṃ akatvā mato’’ ti dārūni uddharitvā citakaṃ katvā ācariyaṃ jhāpetvā vanapupphehi pūjetvā purato gacchanto jīvitakkhayaṃ patte pañcasate, purato aḍḍhateyyasateti anukkamena avasāne dve jane jīvitakkhayaṃ patte disvā cintesi‘‘ imaṃ dvīhi ūnaṃ purisasahassaṃ vināsaṃ pattaṃ, aññehi dvīhi corehi bhavitabbaṃ, tepi santhambhituṃ na sakkhissanti, kahaṃ nu kho te gatā’’ ti gacchanto tesaṃ dhanaṃ ādāya gahanaṭṭhānaṃ paviṭṭhamaggaṃ disvā gacchanto bhaṇḍikabaddhassa dhanassa rāsiṃ disvā ekaṃ bhattapātiṃ avattharitvā mataṃ addasa. "
483745,110,1675,121,185,1,378,49,"Tato‘‘ idaṃ nāma tehi kataṃ bhavissatī’’ ti sabbaṃ ñatvā‘‘ kahaṃ nu kho so puriso’’ ti vicinanto tampi paṭicchannaṭṭhāne apaviddhaṃ disvā‘‘ amhākaṃ ācariyo mama vacanaṃ akatvā attano dubbacabhāvena attanāpi vināsaṃ patto, aparampi tena purisasahassaṃ vināsitaṃ, anupāyena vata akāraṇena attano vuḍḍhiṃ patthayamānā amhākaṃ ācariyo viya mahāvināsameva pāpuṇissantī’’ ti cintetvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
483746,110,1676,2,4,1,0,0,48.
483747,110,1677,2,11,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Anupāyena yo atthaṃ, icchati so vihaññati; "
483748,110,1678,2,12,1,49,7,"Cetā haniṃsu vedabbaṃ, sabbe te byasanamajjhagū’’ ti. "
483749,110,1679,2,27,1,144,19,Tattha so {vihaññatī}ti so anupāyena‘‘ attano atthaṃ vuḍḍhiṃ sukhaṃ icchāmī’’ ti akāle vāyāmaṃ karonto puggalo vihaññati kilamati mahāvināsaṃ pāpuṇāti. 
483750,110,1679,28,32,1,28,3,{Cetā}ti cetaraṭṭhavāsino corā. 
483751,110,1679,33,46,1,79,9,Haniṃsu vedabban ti vedabbamantavasena‘‘ vedabbo’’ ti laddhanāmaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ haniṃsu. 
483752,110,1679,47,59,1,105,11,Sabbe te {byasanamajjhagū}ti tepi ca anavasesā aññamaññaṃ ghātayamānā byasanaṃ adhigacchiṃsu paṭilabhiṃsūti. 
483753,110,1680,2,70,1,499,59,"Evaṃ bodhisatto‘‘ yathā amhākaṃ ācariyo anupāyena aṭṭhāne parakkamaṃ karonto dhanaṃ vassāpetvā attanāpi jīvitakkhayaṃ patto, aññesañca vināsapaccayo jāto, evameva yo aññopi anupāyena attano atthaṃ icchanto vāyāmaṃ karissati, sabbo so attanā ca vinassissati, paresañca vināsapaccayo bhavissatī’’ ti vanaṃ unnādento devatāsu sādhukāraṃ dadamānāsu imāya gāthāya dhammaṃ desetvā taṃ dhanaṃ upāyena attano gehaṃ āharitvā dānādīni puññāni karonto yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā jīvitapariyosāne saggapathaṃ pūrayamāno agamāsi. "
483754,110,1681,2,28,1,163,20,"Satthāpi ‘‘ na tvaṃ bhikkhu idāneva dubbaco, pubbepi dubbacova, dubbacattā pana mahāvināsaṃ patto’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
483755,110,1681,29,43,1,75,9,"‘‘ tadā vedabbabrāhmaṇo dubbacabhikkhu ahosi, antevāsiko pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483756,110,1682,2,4,1,28,2,Vedabbajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
483757,110,1684,2,7,1,22,2,[ 49]9. Nakkhattajātakavaṇṇanā 
483758,110,1685,2,14,1,92,11,Nakkhattaṃ patimānentan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ ājīvakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483759,110,1685,15,58,1,255,33,"Sāvatthiyaṃ kirekaṃ kuladhītaraṃ janapade eko kulaputto attano puttassa vāretvā‘‘ asukadivase nāma gaṇhissāmī’’ ti divasaṃ ṭhapetvā tasmiṃ divase sampatte attano kulūpakaṃ ājīvakaṃ pucchi‘‘ bhante, ajja mayaṃ ekaṃ maṅgalaṃ karissāma, sobhanaṃ nu kho nakkhattan’’ ti. "
483760,110,1685,59,99,1,202,27,"So‘‘ ayaṃ maṃ paṭhamaṃ apucchitvāva divasaṃ ṭhapetvā idāni paṭipucchati, hotu, sikkhāpessāmi nan’’ ti kujjhitvā‘‘ ajja asobhanaṃ nakkhattaṃ, mā ajja maṅgalaṃ karittha, sace karissatha, mahāvināso bhavissatī’’ ti āha. "
483761,110,1685,100,109,1,61,9,Tasmiṃ kule manussā tassa saddahitvā taṃ divasaṃ na gacchiṃsu. 
483762,110,1685,110,152,1,240,33,"Nagaravāsino sabbaṃ maṅgalakiriyaṃ katvā tesaṃ anāgamanaṃ disvā‘‘ tehi ajja divaso ṭhapito, no ca kho āgatā, amhākampi bahu vayakammaṃ kataṃ, kiṃ no tehi, amhākaṃ dhītaraṃ aññassa dassāmā’’ ti yathākateneva maṅgalena dhītaraṃ aññassa kulassa adaṃsu. "
483763,110,1686,2,14,1,51,8,Itare punadivase āgantvā‘‘ detha no dārikan’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
483764,110,1686,15,43,1,179,21,"Atha ne sāvatthivāsino‘‘ janapadavāsino nāma tumhe gahapatikā pāpamanussā divasaṃ ṭhapetvā avaññāya na āgatā, āgatamaggeneva paṭigacchatha , amhehi aññesaṃ dārikā dinnā’’ ti paribhāsiṃsu. "
483765,110,1686,44,53,1,71,9,Te tehi saddhiṃ kalahaṃ katvā dārikaṃ alabhitvā yathāgatamaggeneva gatā. 
483766,110,1686,54,64,1,91,10,Tenapi ājīvakena tesaṃ manussānaṃ maṅgalantarāyassa katabhāvo bhikkhūnaṃ antare pākaṭo jāto. 
483767,110,1686,65,82,1,106,12,"Te bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitā‘‘ āvuso, ājīvakena kulassa maṅgalantarāyo kato’’ ti kathayamānā nisīdiṃsu. "
483768,110,1686,83,99,1,73,10,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchi. "
483769,110,1686,100,109,1,27,5,Te‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti kathayiṃsu.
483770,110,1686,110,135,1,141,18,"‘‘ Na, bhikkhave, idāneva ājīvako tassa kulassa maṅgalantarāyaṃ karoti, pubbepi esa tesaṃ kujjhitvā maṅgalantarāyaṃ akāsiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483771,110,1687,2,33,1,211,25,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente nagaravāsino janapadavāsīnaṃ dhītaraṃ vāretvā divasaṃ ṭhapetvā attano kulūpakaṃ ājīvakaṃ pucchiṃsu‘‘ bhante, ajja amhākaṃ ekā maṅgalakiriyā, sobhanaṃ nu kho nakkhattan’’ ti. "
483772,110,1687,34,75,1,190,26,"So‘‘ ime attano ruciyā divasaṃ ṭhapetvā idāni maṃ pucchantī’’ ti kujjhitvā‘‘ ajja nesaṃ maṅgalantarāyaṃ karissāmī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ ajja asobhanaṃ nakkhattaṃ, sace karotha, mahāvināsaṃ pāpuṇissathā’’ ti āha. "
483773,110,1687,76,81,1,30,5,Te tassa saddahitvā na gamiṃsu. 
483774,110,1687,82,108,1,137,20,"Janapadavāsino tesaṃ anāgamanaṃ ñatvā‘‘ te ajja divasaṃ ṭhapetvāpi na āgatā, kiṃ no tehi, aññesaṃ dhītaraṃ dassāmā’’ ti aññesaṃ dhītaraṃ adaṃsu. "
483775,110,1687,109,114,1,47,5,Nagaravāsino punadivase āgantvā dārikaṃ yāciṃsu. 
483776,110,1687,115,138,1,150,17,"Janapadavāsino‘‘ tumhe nagaravāsino nāma chinnahirikā gahapatikā, divasaṃ ṭhapetvā dārikaṃ na gaṇhittha, mayaṃ tumhākaṃ anāgamanabhāvena aññesaṃ adamhā’’ ti. "
483777,110,1687,139,158,1,81,12,"Mayaṃ ājīvakaṃ paṭipucchitvā‘‘‘ nakkhattaṃ na sobhanan’ ti nāgatā, detha no dārikan’’ ti."
483778,110,1687,159,175,1,89,11,"‘‘ Amhehi tumhākaṃ anāgamanabhāvena aññesaṃ dinnā, idāni dinnadārikaṃ kathaṃ puna ānessāmā’’ ti. "
483779,110,1688,2,45,1,282,34,"Evaṃ tesu aññamaññaṃ kalahaṃ karontesu eko nagaravāsī paṇḍitapuriso ekena kammena janapadaṃ gato tesaṃ nagaravāsīnaṃ‘‘ mayaṃ ājīvakaṃ pucchitvā nakkhattassa asobhanabhāvena nāgatā’’ ti kathentānaṃ sutvā‘‘ nakkhattena ko attho, nanu dārikāya laddhabhāvova nakkhattan’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
483780,110,1689,2,4,1,0,0,49.
483781,110,1690,2,12,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Nakkhattaṃ patimānentaṃ, attho bālaṃ upaccagā; "
483782,110,1691,2,12,1,50,7,"Attho atthassa nakkhattaṃ, kiṃ karissanti tārakā’’ ti. "
483783,110,1692,2,20,1,104,12,"Tattha patimānentan ti olokentaṃ,‘‘ idāni nakkhattaṃ bhavissati, idāni nakkhattaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti āgamayamānaṃ. "
483784,110,1692,21,31,1,87,9,Attho bālaṃ {upaccagā}ti etaṃ nagaravāsikaṃ bālaṃ dārikāpaṭilābhasaṅkhāto attho atikkanto. 
483785,110,1692,32,47,1,105,14,"Attho atthassa nakkhattan ti yaṃ atthaṃ pariyesanto carati, so paṭiladdho atthova atthassa nakkhattaṃ nāma. "
483786,110,1692,48,63,1,97,13,"Kiṃ karissanti {tārakā}ti itare pana ākāse tārakā kiṃ karissanti, kataraṃ atthaṃ sādhessantīti attho. "
483787,110,1692,64,70,1,55,6,Nagaravāsino kalahaṃ katvā dārikaṃ alabhitvāva agamaṃsu. 
483788,110,1693,2,28,1,159,19,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, esa ājīvako idāneva kulassa maṅgalantarāyaṃ karoti, pubbepi akāsiyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
483789,110,1693,29,53,1,125,17,"‘‘ tadā ājīvako etarahi ājīvakova ahosi, tānipi kulāni etarahi kulāniyeva, gāthaṃ vatvā ṭhito paṇḍitapuriso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483790,110,1694,2,4,1,29,2,Nakkhattajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
483791,110,1696,2,7,1,21,2,[ 50]10. Dummedhajātakavaṇṇanā 
483792,110,1697,2,11,1,77,9,Dummedhānan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto lokatthacariyaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483793,110,1697,12,27,1,49,5,Sā dvādasakanipāte mahākaṇhajātake( jā.1.12.61 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
483794,110,1698,2,14,1,108,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa rañño aggamahesiyā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
483795,110,1698,15,27,1,83,8,Tassa mātukucchito nikkhantassa nāmaggahaṇadivase‘‘ brahmadattakumāro’’ ti nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
483796,110,1698,28,48,1,162,18,"So soḷasavassuddesiko hutvā takkasilāyaṃ sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāraṃ gantvā aṭṭhārasannaṃ vijjaṭṭhānānaṃ nipphattiṃ pāpuṇi, athassa pitā oparajjaṃ adāsi. "
483797,110,1698,49,68,1,178,17,"Tasmiṃ samaye bārāṇasivāsino devatāmaṅgalikā honti, devatā namassanti, bahū ajeḷakakukkuṭabhūkarādayo vadhitvā nānappakārehi pupphagandhehi ceva maṃsalohitehi ca balikammaṃ karonti. "
483798,110,1698,69,102,1,210,25,"Bodhisatto cintesi‘‘ idāni sattā devatāmaṅgalikā, bahuṃ pāṇavadhaṃ karonti, mahājano yebhuyyena adhammasmiṃyeva niviṭṭho, ahaṃ pitu accayena rajjaṃ labhitvā ekampi akilametvā upāyeneva pāṇavadhaṃ kātuṃ na dassāmī’’ ti. "
483799,110,1698,103,128,1,202,23,"So ekadivasaṃ rathaṃ abhiruyha nagarā nikkhanto addasa ekasmiṃ mahante vaṭarukkhe mahājanaṃ sannipatitaṃ, tasmiṃ rukkhe nibbattadevatāya santike puttadhītuyasadhanādīsu yaṃ yaṃ icchati, taṃ taṃ patthentaṃ. "
483800,110,1698,129,154,1,202,25,So taṃ disvā rathā oruyha taṃ rukkhaṃ upasaṅkamitvā gandhapupphehi pūjetvā udakena abhisekaṃ katvā rukkhaṃ padakkhiṇaṃ katvā devatāmaṅgaliko viya hutvā devataṃ namassitvā rathaṃ abhiruyha nagaraṃ pāvisi. 
483801,110,1698,155,167,1,90,11,Tato paṭṭhāya imināva niyāmena antarantare tattha gantvā devatāmaṅgaliko viya pūjaṃ karoti. 
483802,110,1699,2,28,1,185,23,"So aparena samayena pitu accayena rajje patiṭṭhāya catasso agatiyo vajjetvā dasa rājadhamme akopento dhammena rajjaṃ kārento cintesi‘‘ mayhaṃ manoratho matthakaṃ patto, rajje patiṭṭhitomhi. "
483803,110,1699,29,61,1,179,25,"Yaṃ panāhaṃ pubbe ekaṃ atthaṃ cintayiṃ, idāni taṃ matthakaṃ pāpessāmī’’ ti amacce ca brāhmaṇagahapatikādayo ca sannipātāpetvā āmantesi‘‘ jānātha bho mayā kena kāraṇena rajjaṃ pattan’’ ti?"
483804,110,1699,62,71,1,17,4,"‘‘ Na jānāma, devā’’ ti."
