483814,110,1701,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Dummedhānaṃ sahassena, yañño me upayācito; "
483815,110,1702,2,12,1,45,7,"Idāni khohaṃ yajissāmi, bahu adhammiko jano’’ ti. "
483816,110,1703,2,41,1,252,29,"Tattha dummedhānaṃ {sahassenā}ti‘‘ idaṃ kammaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭati, idaṃ na vaṭṭatī’’ ti ajānanabhāvena, dasasu vā pana akusalakammapathesu samādāya vattanabhāvena duṭṭhā medhā etesanti dummedhā, tesaṃ dummedhānaṃ nippaññānaṃ bālapuggalānaṃ gaṇitvā gahitena sahassena. "
483817,110,1703,42,58,1,78,11,Yañño me {upayācito}ti mayā devataṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ evaṃ yajissāmī’’ ti yañño yācito. 
483818,110,1703,59,71,1,87,11,Idāni khohaṃ {yajissāmī}ti so ahaṃ iminā āyācanena rajjassa paṭiladdhattā idāni yajissāmi. 
483819,110,1703,72,73,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
