483835,110,1715,2,7,1,23,2,[ 51]1. Mahāsīlavajātakavaṇṇanā 
483836,110,1716,2,14,1,91,10,Āsīsetheva {puriso}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ossaṭṭhavīriyaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483837,110,1716,15,28,1,64,9,Tañhi satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ossaṭṭhavīriyosī’’ ti pucchi.
483838,110,1716,29,68,1,203,28,"‘‘ Āma, bhante’’ ti ca vutte‘‘ kasmā tvaṃ bhikkhu evarūpe niyyānikasāsane pabbajitvā vīriyaṃ ossaji, pubbe paṇḍitā rajjā parihāyitvāpi attano vīriye ṭhatvāva naṭṭhampi yasaṃ puna uppādayiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483839,110,1717,2,12,1,93,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto rañño aggamahesiyā kucchimhi nibbatto. 
483840,110,1717,13,23,1,52,6,Tassa nāmaggahaṇadivase‘‘ sīlavakumāro’’ ti nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
483841,110,1717,24,39,1,141,15,So soḷasavassuddesikova sabbasippesu nipphattiṃ patvā aparabhāge pitu accayena rajje patiṭṭhito mahāsīlavarājā nāma ahosi dhammiko dhammarājā. 
483842,110,1717,40,77,1,281,31,"So nagarassa catūsu dvāresu catasso, majjhe ekaṃ, nivesanadvāre ekanti niccaṃ cha dānasālāyo kārāpetvā kapaṇaddhikānaṃ dānaṃ deti, sīlaṃ rakkhati, uposathakammaṃ karoti, khantimettānuddayasampanno aṅke nisinnaṃ puttaṃ paritosayamāno viya sabbasatte paritosayamāno dhammena rajjaṃ kāreti. "
483843,110,1717,78,85,1,58,7,Tasseko amacco antepure padubbhitvā aparabhāge pākaṭo jāto. 
483844,110,1717,86,89,1,21,3,Amaccā rañño ārocesuṃ. 
483845,110,1717,90,124,1,202,28,"Rājā pariggaṇhanto attanā paccakkhato ñatvā taṃ amaccaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ andhabāla ayuttaṃ te kataṃ, na tvaṃ mama vijite vasituṃ arahasi, attano dhanañca puttadāre ca gahetvā aññattha yāhī’’ ti raṭṭhā pabbājesi. "
483846,110,1717,125,138,1,131,13,So nikkhamitvā kāsiraṭṭhaṃ atikkamma kosalajanapadaṃ gantvā kosalarājānaṃ upaṭṭhahanto anukkamena rañño abbhantariko vissāsiko jāto. 
483847,110,1718,2,6,1,31,4,So ekadivasaṃ kosalarājānaṃ āha–
483848,110,1718,7,25,1,124,12,"‘‘ deva bārāṇasirajjaṃ nāma nimmakkhikamadhupaṭalasadisaṃ, rājā atimuduko, appeneva balavāhanena sakkā bārāṇasirajjaṃ gaṇhitun’’ ti. "
483849,110,1718,26,66,1,187,27,"Rājā tassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ bārāṇasirajjaṃ nāma mahā, ayañca‘ appeneva balavāhanena sakkā bārāṇasirajjaṃ gaṇhitun’ ti āha, kiṃ nu kho pana payuttakacoro siyā’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ payuttakosi maññe’’ ti āha."
483850,110,1718,67,77,1,37,5,"‘‘ Nāhaṃ, deva, payuttako, saccameva vadāmi. "
483851,110,1718,78,100,1,131,18,"Sace me na saddahatha, manusse pesetvā paccantagāmaṃ hanāpetha, te manusse gahetvā attano santikaṃ nīte dhanaṃ datvā vissajjessatī’’ ti. "
483852,110,1718,101,121,1,101,14,"Rājā‘‘ ayaṃ ativiya sūro hutvā vadati, vīmaṃsissāmi tāvā’’ ti attano purise pesetvā paccantagāmaṃ hanāpesi. "
483853,110,1718,122,128,1,46,6,Manussā te core gahetvā bārāṇasirañño dassesuṃ. 
483854,110,1718,129,143,1,48,9,"Rājā te disvā‘‘ tātā, kasmā gāmaṃ hanathā’’ ti pucchi."
483855,110,1718,144,176,1,150,22,"‘‘ Jīvituṃ asakkontā, devā’’ ti vutte rājā‘‘ atha kasmā mama santikaṃ nāgamittha, itodāni paṭṭhāya evarūpaṃ kammaṃ mā karitthā’’ ti tesaṃ dhanaṃ datvā vissajjesi. "
483856,110,1718,177,183,1,43,6,Te gantvā kosalarañño taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesuṃ. 
483857,110,1718,184,191,1,61,7,So ettakenāpi gantuṃ avisahanto puna majjhejanapadaṃ hanāpesi. 
483858,110,1718,192,199,1,46,7,Tepi core rājā tatheva dhanaṃ datvā vissajjesi. 
483859,110,1718,200,214,1,110,13,"So ettakenāpi agantvā puna pesetvā antaravīthiyaṃ vilumpāpesi, rājā tesampi corānaṃ dhanaṃ datvā vissajjesiyeva. "
483860,110,1718,215,236,1,100,13,Tadā kosalarājā‘‘ ativiya dhammiko rājā’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ bārāṇasirajjaṃ gahessāmī’’ ti balavāhanaṃ ādāya niyyāsi. 
483861,110,1719,2,25,1,234,22,Tadā pana bārāṇasirañño mattavāraṇepi abhimukhaṃ āgacchante anivattanadhammā asaniyāpi sīse patantiyā asantasanasabhāvā sīlavamahārājassa ruciyā sati sakalajambudīpe rajjaṃ gahetuṃ samatthā sahassamattā abhejjavarasūrā mahāyodhā honti. 
483862,110,1719,26,62,1,188,23,"Te‘‘ kosalarājā āgacchatī’’ ti sutvā rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ deva, kosalarājā kira‘ bārāṇasirajjaṃ gaṇhissāmī’ ti āgacchati, gacchāma, naṃ amhākaṃ rajjasīmaṃ anokkantameva pothetvā gaṇhāmā’’ ti vadiṃsu. "
483863,110,1719,63,83,1,101,13,"Rājā‘‘ tātā, maṃ nissāya aññesaṃ kilamanakiccaṃ natthi, rajjatthiko rajjaṃ gaṇhātu, māgamitthā’’ ti nivāresi. "
483864,110,1719,84,89,1,56,5,Kosalarājā rajjasīmaṃ atikkamitvā janapadamajjhaṃ pāvisi. 
483865,110,1719,90,100,1,80,9,"Amaccā punapi rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā tatheva vadiṃsu, rājā purimanayeneva nivāresi. "
483866,110,1719,101,117,1,90,12,Kosalarājā bahinagare ṭhatvā‘‘ rajjaṃ vā detu yuddhaṃ vā’’ ti sīlavamahārājassa sāsanaṃ pesesi. 
483867,110,1719,118,135,1,79,12,"Rājā taṃ sutvā‘‘ natthi mayā saddhiṃ yuddhaṃ, rajjaṃ gaṇhātū’’ ti paṭisāsanaṃ pesesi. "
483868,110,1719,136,171,1,241,27,"Punapi amaccā rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ deva, na mayaṃ kosalarañño nagaraṃ pavisituṃ dema, bahinagareyeva naṃ pothetvā gaṇhāmā’’ ti āhaṃsu, rājā purimanayeneva nivāretvā nagaradvārāni vivarāpetvā saddhiṃ amaccasahassena mahātale pallaṅkamajjhe nisīdi. "
483869,110,1720,2,7,1,50,5,Kosalarājā mahantena balavāhanena bārāṇasiṃ pāvisi. 
483870,110,1720,8,66,1,474,50,"So ekampi paṭisattuṃ apassanto rañño nivesanadvāraṃ gantvā amaccagaṇaparivuto apārutadvāre nivesane alaṅkatapaṭiyattaṃ mahātalaṃ āruyha nisinnaṃ nirāparādhaṃ sīlavamahārājānaṃ saddhiṃ amaccasahassena gaṇhāpetvā‘‘ gacchatha, imaṃ rājānaṃ saddhiṃ amaccehi pacchābāhaṃ gāḷhabandhanaṃ bandhitvā āmakasusānaṃ netvā galappamāṇe āvāṭe khanitvā yathā ekopi hatthaṃ ukkhipituṃ na sakkoti, evaṃ paṃsuṃ pakkhipitvā nikhanatha, rattiṃ siṅgālā āgantvā etesaṃ kātabbayuttakaṃ karissantī’’ ti āha. "
483871,110,1720,67,78,1,102,11,Manussā corarañño āṇaṃ sutvā rājānaṃ saddhiṃ amaccehi pacchābāhaṃ gāḷhabandhanaṃ bandhitvā nikkhamiṃsu. 
483872,110,1720,79,85,1,60,6,Tasmimpi kāle sīlavamahārājā corarañño āghātamattampi nākāsi. 
483873,110,1720,86,98,1,92,12,Tesupi amaccesu evaṃ bandhitvā nīyamānesu ekopi rañño vacanaṃ bhindituṃ samattho nāma nāhosi. 
483874,110,1720,99,103,1,28,4,Evaṃ suvinītā kirassa parisā. 
483875,110,1720,104,130,1,215,24,"Atha te rājapurisā sāmaccaṃ sīlavamahārājānaṃ āmakasusānaṃ netvā galappamāṇe āvāṭe khanitvā sīlavamahārājānaṃ majjhe , ubhosu passesu sesaamacceti evaṃ sabbepi āvāṭesu otāretvā paṃsuṃ ākiritvā ghanaṃ ākoṭetvā agamaṃsu. "
483876,110,1720,131,150,1,99,14,"Tadā sīlavamahārājā amacce āmantetvā‘‘ corarañño upari kopaṃ akatvā mettaṃ eva bhāvetha, tātā’’ ti ovadi. "
483877,110,1721,2,13,1,66,7,Atha aḍḍharattasamaye‘‘ manussamaṃsaṃ khādissāmā’’ ti siṅgālā āgamiṃsu. 
483878,110,1721,14,26,1,78,11,"Te disvā rājā ca amaccā ca ekappahāreneva saddamakaṃsu, siṅgālā bhītā palāyiṃsu. "
483879,110,1721,27,36,1,79,9,Te nivattitvā olokentā pacchato kassaci anāgamanabhāvaṃ ñatvā puna paccāgamiṃsu. 
483880,110,1721,37,40,1,28,3,Itarepi tatheva saddamakaṃsu. 
483881,110,1721,41,67,1,172,22,Evaṃ yāvatatiyaṃ palāyitvā puna olokentā tesu ekassapi anāgamanabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ vajjhappattā ete bhavissantī’’ ti sūrā hutvā nivattitvā puna tesu saddaṃ karontesupi na palāyiṃsu. 
483882,110,1721,68,78,1,82,9,"Jeṭṭhakasiṅgālo rājānaṃ upagañchi, sesā siṅgālā sesānaṃ amaccānaṃ santikaṃ agamaṃsu. "
483883,110,1721,79,117,1,319,36,"Upāyakusalo rājā tassa attano santikaṃ āgatabhāvaṃ ñatvā ḍaṃsituṃ okāsaṃ dento viya gīvaṃ ukkhipitvā taṃ gīvāya ḍaṃsamānaṃ hanukaṭṭhikena ākaḍḍhitvā yante pakkhipitvā viya gāḷhaṃ gaṇhi, nāgabalena raññā hanukaṭṭhikena ākaḍḍhitvā gīvāya gāḷhaṃ gahitasiṅgālo attānaṃ mocetuṃ asakkonto maraṇabhayatajjito mahāviravaṃ viravi. "
483884,110,1721,118,139,1,147,17,Avasesā siṅgālā tassa taṃ aṭṭassaraṃ sutvā‘‘ ekena purisena suggahito bhavissatī’’ ti amacce upasaṅkamituṃ asakkontā maraṇabhayatajjitā sabbe palāyiṃsu. 
483885,110,1721,140,150,1,89,10,Rañño hanukaṭṭhikena daḷhaṃ katvā gahitasiṅgāle aparāparaṃ sañcarante paṃsu sithilā ahosi. 
483886,110,1721,151,189,1,354,37,"Sopi siṅgālo maraṇabhayabhīto catūhi pādehi rañño uparibhāge paṃsuṃ apabyūhi, rājā paṃsuno sithilabhāvaṃ ñatvā siṅgālaṃ vissajjetvā nāgabalo thāmasampanno aparāparaṃ sañcaranto ubho hatthe ukkhipitvā āvāṭamukhavaṭṭiyaṃ olubbha vātacchinnavalāhako viya nikkhamitvā ṭhito amacce assāsetvā paṃsuṃ viyūhitvā sabbe uddharitvā amaccaparivuto āmakasusāne aṭṭhāsi. "
483887,110,1722,2,14,1,103,11,Tasmiṃ samaye manussā ekaṃ matamanussaṃ āmakasusāne chaḍḍentā dvinnaṃ yakkhānaṃ sīmantarikāya chaḍḍesuṃ. 
483888,110,1722,15,66,1,266,38,"Te yakkhā taṃ matamanussaṃ bhājetuṃ asakkontā‘‘ na mayaṃ imaṃ bhājetuṃ sakkoma, ayaṃ sīlavarājā dhammiko, esa no bhājetvā dassati, etassa santikaṃ gacchāmā’’ ti taṃ matamanussaṃ pāde gahetvā ākaḍḍhantā rañño santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ deva, amhākaṃ imaṃ matakaṃ bhājetvā dehī’’ ti āhaṃsu."
483889,110,1722,67,86,1,86,12,"‘‘ Bho yakkhā, ahaṃ imaṃ tumhākaṃ bhājetvā dadeyyaṃ, aparisuddho panamhi, nhāyissāmi tāvā’’ ti. "
483890,110,1722,87,97,1,90,10,Yakkhā corarañño ṭhapitaṃ vāsitaudakaṃ attano ānubhāvena āharitvā rañño nhānatthāya adaṃsu. 
483891,110,1722,98,123,1,228,23,"Nhatvā ṭhitassa saṃharitvā ṭhapite corarañño sāṭake āharitvā adaṃsu, te nivāsetvā ṭhitassa catujjātiyagandhasamuggaṃ āharitvā adaṃsu, gandhe vilimpitvā ṭhitassa suvaṇṇasamugge maṇitālavaṇṭesu ṭhapitāni nānāpupphāni āharitvā adaṃsu. "
483892,110,1722,124,136,1,60,8,Pupphāni piḷandhitvā ṭhitakāle‘‘ aññaṃ kiṃ karomā’’ ti pucchiṃsu. 
483893,110,1722,137,156,1,164,16,"Rājā attano chātakākāraṃ dassesi, te gantvā corarañño sampāditaṃ nānaggarasabhojanaṃ āharitvā adaṃsu, rājā nhātānulitto sumaṇḍitappasādhito nānaggarasabhojanaṃ bhuñji. "
483894,110,1722,157,165,1,94,8,Yakkhā corarañño ṭhapitaṃ vāsitapānīyaṃ suvaṇṇabhiṅkāreneva suvaṇṇasarakenapi saddhiṃ āhariṃsu. 
483895,110,1722,166,180,1,144,14,Athassa pānīyaṃ pivitvā mukhaṃ vikkhāletvā hatthe dhovitvā ṭhitakāle corarañño sampāditaṃ pañcasugandhikasuparibhāvitaṃ tambūlaṃ āharitvā adaṃsu. 
483896,110,1722,181,193,1,52,8,Taṃ khāditvā ṭhitakāle‘‘ aññaṃ kiṃ karomā’’ ti pucchiṃsu. 
483897,110,1722,194,200,1,62,6,Gantvā corarañño ussīsake nikkhittaṃ maṅgalakhaggaṃ āharathāti. 
483898,110,1722,201,204,1,21,3,Tampi gantvā āhariṃsu. 
483899,110,1722,205,232,1,212,26,"Rājā taṃ khaggaṃ gahetvā taṃ matamanussaṃ ujukaṃ ṭhapāpetvā matthakamajjhe asinā paharitvā dve koṭṭhāse katvā dvinnaṃ yakkhānaṃ samavibhattameva vibhajitvā adāsi, datvā ca pana khaggaṃ dhovitvā sannayhitvā aṭṭhāsi. "
483900,110,1722,233,254,1,104,15,"Atha te yakkhā manussamaṃsaṃ khāditvā suhitā hutvā tuṭṭhacittā‘‘ aññaṃ te, mahārāja, kiṃ karomā’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
483901,110,1722,255,272,1,116,16,"Tena hi tumhe attano ānubhāvena maṃ corarañño sirigabbhe otāretha, ime ca amacce attano attano gehesu patiṭṭhāpethāti. "
483902,110,1722,273,284,1,44,7,Te‘‘ sādhu devā’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā tathā akaṃsu. 
483903,110,1723,2,9,1,76,7,Tasmiṃ samaye corarājā alaṅkatasirigabbhe sirisayanapiṭṭhe nipanno niddāyati. 
483904,110,1723,10,17,1,62,7,Rājā tassa pamattassa niddāyantassa khaggatalena udaraṃ pahari. 
483905,110,1723,18,56,1,289,32,"So bhīto pabujjhitvā dīpālokena sīlavamahārājānaṃ sañjānitvā sayanā uṭṭhāya satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā ṭhito rājānaṃ āha‘‘ mahārāja, evarūpāya rattiyā gahitārakkhe pihitadvāre bhavane ārakkhamanussehi nirokāse ṭhāne khaggaṃ sannayhitvā alaṅkatapaṭiyatto kathaṃ nāma tvaṃ imaṃ sayanapiṭṭhaṃ āgatosī’’ ti. "
483906,110,1723,57,63,1,50,6,Rājā attano āgamanākāraṃ sabbaṃ vitthārato kathesi. 
483907,110,1723,64,170,1,768,89,"Taṃ sutvā corarājā saṃviggamānaso‘‘ mahārāja, ahaṃ manussabhūtopi samāno tumhākaṃ guṇe na jānāmi, paresaṃ lohitamaṃsakhādakehi pana kakkhaḷehi pharusehi yakkhehi tava guṇā ñātā, na dānāhaṃ, narinda , evarūpe sīlasampanne tayi dubbhissāmī’’ ti khaggaṃ ādāya sapathaṃ katvā rājānaṃ khamāpetvā mahāsayane nipajjāpetvā attanā khuddakamañcake nipajjitvā pabhātāya rattiyā uṭṭhite sūriye bheriṃ carāpetvā sabbaseniyo ca amaccabrāhmaṇagahapatike ca sannipātāpetvā tesaṃ purato ākāse puṇṇacandaṃ ukkhipanto viya sīlavarañño guṇe kathetvā parisamajjheyeva puna rājānaṃ khamāpetvā rajjaṃ paṭicchāpetvā‘‘ mahārāja, ito paṭṭhāya tumhākaṃ uppanno corūpaddavo mayhaṃ bhāro, mayā gahitārakkhā tumhe rajjaṃ karothā’’ ti vatvā pesuññakārakassa āṇaṃ kāretvā attano balavāhanaṃ ādāya sakaraṭṭhameva gato. "
483908,110,1724,2,45,1,357,38,"Sīlavarājāpi kho alaṅkatapaṭiyatto setacchattassa heṭṭhā sarabhapādake kañcanapallaṅke nisinno attano sampattiṃ oloketvā‘‘ ayañca evarūpā sampatti amaccasahassassa ca jīvitapaṭilābho mayi vīriyaṃ akaronte na kiñci abhavissa, vīriyabalena panāhaṃ naṭṭhañca imaṃ yasaṃ paṭilabhiṃ, amaccasahassassa ca jīvitadānaṃ adāsiṃ, āsacchedaṃ vata akatvā vīriyameva kattabbaṃ. "
483909,110,1724,46,59,1,83,11,Katavīriyassa hi phalaṃ nāma evaṃ samijjhatī’’ ti cintetvā udānavasena imaṃ gāthamāha– 
483910,110,1725,2,4,1,0,0,51.
483911,110,1726,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Āsīsetheva puriso, na nibbindeyya paṇḍito; "
483912,110,1727,2,13,1,47,8,"Passāmi vohaṃ attānaṃ, yathā icchiṃ tathā ahū’’ ti. "
483913,110,1728,2,20,1,107,13,Tattha {āsīsethevā}ti‘‘ evāhaṃ vīriyaṃ ārabhanto imamhā dukkhā muccissāmī’’ ti attano vīriyabalena āsaṃ karotheva. 
483914,110,1728,21,47,1,160,20,"Na nibbindeyya {paṇḍito}ti paṇḍito upāyakusalo yuttaṭṭhāne vīriyaṃ karonto‘‘ ahaṃ imassa vīriyassa phalaṃ na labhissāmī’’ ti na ukkaṇṭheyya, āsacchedaṃ kareyyāti attho. "
483915,110,1728,48,62,1,74,11,"Passāmi vohaṃ attānan ti ettha {vo}ti nipātamattaṃ , ahaṃ ajja attānaṃ passāmi. "
483916,110,1728,63,86,1,147,21,"Yathā icchiṃ tathā {ahū}ti ahañhi āvāṭe nikhāto tamhā dukkhā muccitvā puna attano rajjasampattiṃ icchiṃ, so ahaṃ imaṃ sampattiṃ pattaṃ attānaṃ passāmi. "
483917,110,1728,87,95,1,46,7,"Yathevāhaṃ pubbe icchiṃ, tatheva me attā jātoti. "
483918,110,1728,96,119,1,147,19,Evaṃ bodhisatto‘‘ aho vata bho sīlasampannānaṃ vīriyaphalaṃ nāma samijjhatī’’ ti imāya gāthāya udānaṃ udānetvā yāvajīvaṃ puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
