483965,110,1750,2,7,1,21,2,[ 54]4. Kiṃphalajātakavaṇṇanā 
483966,110,1751,2,16,1,97,12,Nāyaṃ rukkho {durāruhā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ phalakusalaṃ upāsakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
483967,110,1751,17,44,1,210,23,Eko kira sāvatthivāsī kuṭumbiko buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ nimantetvā attano ārāme nisīdāpetvā yāgukhajjakaṃ datvā uyyānapālaṃ āṇāpesi‘‘ bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ uyyāne vicaritvā ayyānaṃ ambādīni nānāphalāni dehī’’ ti. 
483968,110,1751,45,74,1,139,19,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā bhikkhūsaṅghamādāya uyyāne vicaranto rukkhaṃ ulloketvāva‘‘ etaṃ phalaṃ āmaṃ, etaṃ na supakkaṃ, etaṃ supakkan’’ ti jānāti. "
483969,110,1751,75,82,1,30,6,"Yaṃ so vadati, taṃ tatheva hoti. "
483970,110,1751,83,112,1,164,22,"Bhikkhū gantvā tathāgatassa ārocesuṃ‘‘ bhante, ayaṃ uyyānapālo phalakusalo bhūmiyaṃ ṭhitova rukkhaṃ ulloketvā‘ etaṃ phalaṃ āmaṃ, etaṃ na supakkaṃ, etaṃ supakkan’ ti jānāti. "
483971,110,1751,113,123,1,33,7,"Yaṃ so vadati, taṃ tatheva hotī’’ ti. "
483972,110,1751,124,145,1,111,14,"Satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, ayameva uyyānapālo phalakusalo, pubbe paṇḍitāpi phalakusalāyeva ahesun’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
483973,110,1752,2,64,1,429,51,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto satthavāhakule nibbattitvā vayappatto pañcahi sakaṭasatehi vaṇijjaṃ karonto ekasmiṃ kāle mahāvattaniaṭaviṃ patvā aṭavimukhe ṭhatvā sabbe manusse sannipātāpetvā‘‘ imissā aṭaviyā visarukkhā nāma honti, visapattāni, visapupphāni, visaphalāni, visamadhūni hontiyeva, pubbe tumhehi aparibhuttaṃ, yaṃ kiñci pattaṃ vā pupphaṃ vā phalaṃ vā pallavaṃ vā maṃ aparipucchitvā mā khādathā’’ ti āha. "
483974,110,1752,65,75,1,42,6,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā aṭaviṃ otariṃsu. 
483975,110,1752,76,90,1,124,12,"Aṭavimukhe ca ekasmiṃ gāmadvāre kiṃphalarukkho nāma atthi, tassa khandhasākhāpalāsapupphaphalāni sabbāni ambasadisāneva honti. "
483976,110,1752,91,107,1,155,14,"Na kevalaṃ vaṇṇasaṇṭhānatova, gandharasehipissa āmapakkāni phalāni ambaphalasadisāneva, khāditāni pana halāhalavisaṃ viya taṅkhaṇaññeva jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpenti. "
483977,110,1752,108,135,1,149,18,"Purato gacchantā ekacce lolapurisā‘‘ amburukkho ayan’’ ti saññāya phalāni khādiṃsu, ekacce‘‘ satthavāhaṃ pucchitvāva khādissāmā’’ ti hatthena gahetvā aṭṭhaṃsu. "
483978,110,1752,136,150,1,63,9,"Te satthavāhe āgate‘‘ ayya, imāni ambaphalāni khādāmā’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
483979,110,1752,151,178,1,112,16,"Bodhisatto‘‘ nāyaṃ ambarukkho’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ kiṃ phalarukkho nāmesa, nāyaṃ ambarukkho, mā khāditthā’’ ti vāretvā ye khādiṃsu. "
483980,110,1752,179,185,1,48,6,Tepi vamāpetvā catumadhuraṃ pāyetvā niroge akāsi. 
483981,110,1753,2,21,1,128,15,Pubbe pana imasmiṃ rukkhamūle manussā nivāsaṃ kappetvā‘‘ ambaphalānī’’ ti saññāya imāni visaphalāni khāditvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇanti. 
483982,110,1753,22,38,1,154,16,Punadivase gāmavāsino nikkhamitvā matamanusse disvā pāde gaṇhitvā paṭicchannaṭṭhāne chaḍḍetvā sakaṭehi saddhiṃyeva sabbaṃ tesaṃ santakaṃ gahetvā gacchanti. 
483983,110,1753,39,80,1,217,29,"Te taṃ divasampi aruṇuggamanakāleyeva‘‘ mayhaṃ balibaddo bhavissati, mayhaṃ sakaṭaṃ, mayhaṃ bhaṇḍan’’ ti vegena taṃ rukkhamūlaṃ gantvā manusse niroge disvā‘‘ kathaṃ tumhe imaṃ rukkhaṃ‘ nāyaṃ ambarukkho’ ti jānitthā’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
483984,110,1753,81,95,1,57,9,"Te‘‘ mayaṃ na jānāma, satthavāhajeṭṭhako no jānātī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
483985,110,1753,96,113,1,100,12,"Manussā bodhisattaṃ pucchiṃsu‘‘ paṇḍita, kinti katvā tvaṃ imassa rukkhassa anambarukkhabhāvaṃ aññāsī’’ ti? "
483986,110,1753,114,126,1,49,8,So‘‘ dvīhi kāraṇehi aññāsin’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
483987,110,1754,2,4,1,0,0,54.
483988,110,1755,2,12,1,39,7,"‘ ‘ Nāyaṃ rukkho durāruho, napi gāmato ārakā; "
483989,110,1756,2,11,1,40,6,"Ākāraṇena jānāmi, nāyaṃ sāduphalo dumo’’ ti. "
483990,110,1757,2,18,1,121,14,"Tattha nāyaṃ rukkho {durāruho}ti ayaṃ visarukkho na dukkhāruho, ukkhipitvā ṭhapitanisseṇī viya sukhenārohituṃ sakkāti vadati. "
483991,110,1757,19,32,1,76,11,"Napi gāmato {ārakā}ti gāmato dūre ṭhitopi na hoti, gāmadvāre ṭhitoyevāti dīpeti. "
483992,110,1757,33,42,1,66,8,Ākāraṇena {jānāmī}ti iminā duvidhena kāraṇenāhaṃ imaṃ rukkhaṃ jānāmi. 
483993,110,1757,43,44,1,5,1,Kinti? 
483994,110,1757,45,49,1,22,3,Nāyaṃ sāduphalo {dumo}ti. 
483995,110,1757,50,71,1,156,19,"Sace hi ayaṃ madhuraphalo ambarukkho abhavissa, evaṃ sukhāruḷhe avidūre ṭhite etasmiṃ ekampi phalaṃ na tiṭṭheyya, phalakhādakamanussehi niccaṃ parivutova assa. "
483996,110,1757,72,85,1,119,13,Evaṃ ahaṃ attano ñāṇena paricchinditvā imassa visarukkhabhāvaṃ aññāsinti mahājanassa dhammaṃ desetvā sotthigamanaṃ gato. 
483997,110,1758,2,24,1,129,15,"Satthāpi ‘‘ evaṃ, bhikkhave, pubbe paṇḍitāpi phalakusalā ahesun’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
483998,110,1758,25,39,1,65,9,"‘‘ tadā parisā buddhaparisā ahesuṃ, satthavāho pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
483999,110,1759,2,4,1,30,2,Kiṃphalajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
484000,110,1761,2,7,1,23,2,[ 55]5. Pañcāvudhajātakavaṇṇanā 
484001,110,1762,2,16,1,97,12,Yo alīnena {cittenā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ossaṭṭhavīriyaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484002,110,1762,17,59,1,219,29,"Tañhi bhikkhuṃ satthā āmantetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ossaṭṭhavīriyosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhagavā’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhu pubbe paṇḍitā vīriyaṃ kātuṃ yuttaṭṭhāne vīriyaṃ katvā rajjasampattiṃ pāpuṇiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
484003,110,1763,2,13,1,100,11,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa rañño aggamahesiyā kucchismiṃ nibbatti. 
484004,110,1763,14,22,1,87,8,Tassa nāmaggahaṇadivase aṭṭhasate brāhmaṇe sabbakāmehi santappetvā lakkhaṇāni pucchiṃsu. 
484005,110,1763,23,49,1,191,19,"Lakkhaṇakusalā brāhmaṇā lakkhaṇasampattiṃ disvā‘‘ puññasampanno, mahārāja, kumāro tumhākaṃ accayena rajjaṃ pāpuṇissati, pañcāvudhakamme paññāto pākaṭo jambudīpe aggapuriso bhavissatī’’ ti byākariṃsu. "
484006,110,1763,50,66,1,87,11,Rājā brāhmaṇānaṃ vacanaṃ sutvā kumārassa nāmaṃ gaṇhanto‘‘ pañcāvudhakumāro’’ ti nāmaṃ akāsi. 
484007,110,1763,67,85,1,91,13,"Atha naṃ viññutaṃ patvā soḷasavassuddese ṭhitaṃ rājā āmantetvā‘‘ tāta, sippaṃ uggaṇhāhī’’ ti āha."
484008,110,1763,86,96,1,31,5,"‘‘ Kassa santike uggaṇhāmi, devā’’ ti?"
484009,110,1763,97,119,1,147,15,"‘‘ Gaccha, tāta, gandhāraraṭṭhe takkasilanagare disāpāmokkhassa ācariyassa santike uggaṇha, idañcassa ācariyabhāgaṃ dajjeyyāsī’’ ti sahassaṃ datvā uyyojesi. "
484010,110,1763,120,136,1,163,16,So tattha gantvā sippaṃ sikkhitvā ācariyena dinnaṃ pañcāvudhaṃ gahetvā ācariyaṃ vanditvā takkasilanagarato nikkhamitvā sannaddhapañcāvudho bārāṇasimaggaṃ paṭipajji. 
484011,110,1764,2,10,1,69,8,So antarāmagge silesalomayakkhena nāma adhiṭṭhitaṃ ekaṃ aṭaviṃ pāpuṇi. 
484012,110,1764,11,39,1,156,21,"Atha naṃ aṭavimukhe manussā disvā‘‘ bho māṇava, mā imaṃ aṭaviṃ pavisa, silesalomayakkho nāmettha atthi, so diṭṭhadiṭṭhe manusse jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetī’’ ti vārayiṃsu. "
484013,110,1764,40,47,1,70,7,Bodhisatto attānaṃ takkento asambhītakesarasīho viya aṭaviṃ pāvisiyeva. 
484014,110,1764,48,85,1,250,30,"Tasmiṃ aṭavimajjhaṃ sampatte so yakkho tālamatto hutvā kūṭāgāramattaṃ sīsaṃ pattappamāṇāni akkhīni, dakalimakuḷamattā dve dāṭhā ca māpetvā setamukho kabarakucchi nīlahatthapādo hutvā bodhisattassa attānaṃ dassetvā‘‘ kahaṃ yāsi, tiṭṭha bhakkhosi me’’ ti āha. "
484015,110,1764,86,105,1,102,14,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto ‘‘ yakkha, ahaṃ attānaṃ takketvā idha paviṭṭho, tvaṃ appamatto hutvā maṃ upagaccheyyāsi. "
484016,110,1764,106,126,1,140,17,"Visapītena hi sarena taṃ vijjhitvā ettheva pātessāmī’’ ti santajjetvā halāhalavisapītaṃ saraṃ sannayhitvā muñci, so yakkhassa lomesuyeva allīyi. "
484017,110,1764,127,141,1,80,12,"Tato aññaṃ, tato aññanti evaṃ paññāsa sare muñci, sabbe tassa lomesuyeva allīyiṃsu. "
484018,110,1764,142,152,1,82,10,Yakkho sabbepi te sare phoṭetvā attano pādamūleyeva pātetvā bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkami. 
484019,110,1765,2,14,1,98,11,"Bodhisatto punapi taṃ tajjetvā khaggaṃ kaḍḍhitvā pahari, tettiṃsaṅgulāyato khaggo lomesuyeva allīyi. "
484020,110,1765,15,23,1,47,7,"Atha naṃ kaṇayena pahari, sopi lomesuyeva allīyi. "
484021,110,1765,24,33,1,64,8,"Tassa allīnabhāvaṃ ñatvā muggarena pahari, sopi lomesuyeva allīyi. "
484022,110,1765,34,43,1,62,8,"Tassa allīnabhāvaṃ ñatvā kuntena pahari, sopi lomesuyeva allīyi. "
484023,110,1765,44,95,1,315,39,"Tassa allīnabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ bho yakkhana, te ahaṃ‘ pañcāvudhakumāro nāmā’ ti sutapubbo, ahaṃ tayā adhiṭṭhitaṃ aṭaviṃ pavisanto na dhanuādīni takketvā paviṭṭho, attānaṃyeva pana takketvā paviṭṭho, ajja taṃ pothetvā cuṇṇavicuṇṇaṃ karissāmī’’ ti unnādento attānaṃ takketvā dakkhiṇahatthena yakkhaṃ pahari, hattho lomesuyeva allīyi. "
484024,110,1765,96,101,1,31,4,"Vāmahatthena pahari, sopi allīyi. "
484025,110,1765,102,107,1,33,4,"Dakkhiṇapādena pahari, sopi allīyi. "
484026,110,1765,108,113,1,29,4,"Vāmapādena pahari, sopi allīyi."
484027,110,1765,114,130,1,84,11,"‘‘ Sīsena taṃ pothetvā cuṇṇavicuṇṇaṃ karissāmī’’ ti sīsena pahari, tampi lomesuyeva allīyi. "
484028,110,1765,131,140,1,76,9,So pañcoḍḍito pañcasu ṭhānesu baddho olambantopi nibbhayo nissārajjova ahosi. 
484029,110,1766,2,41,1,224,31,"Yakkho cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ eko purisasīho purisājānīyo, na purisamattova, mādisena nāmassa yakkhena gahitassa santāsamattampi na bhavissati, mayā imaṃ maggaṃ hanantena ekopi evarūpo puriso na diṭṭhapubbo, kasmā nu kho esa na bhāyatī’’ ti. "
484030,110,1766,42,62,1,85,14,"So taṃ khādituṃ avisahanto‘‘ kasmā nu kho, tvaṃ māṇava, maraṇabhayaṃ na bhāyasī’’ ti pucchi."
484031,110,1766,63,70,1,27,3,"‘‘ Kiṃkāraṇā, yakkha, bhāyissāmi. "
484032,110,1766,71,82,1,85,10,"Ekasmiñhi attabhāve ekaṃ maraṇaṃ niyatameva, apica mayhaṃ kucchimhi vajirāvudhaṃ atthi. "
484033,110,1766,83,101,1,120,15,"Sace maṃ khādissasi, taṃ āvudhaṃ jīrāpetuṃ na sakkhissasi, taṃ te antāni khaṇḍākhaṇḍikaṃ chinditvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpessati. "
484034,110,1766,102,113,1,53,8,"Iti ubhopi nassissāma, iminā kāraṇenāhaṃ na bhāyāmī’’ ti. "
484035,110,1766,114,122,1,66,8,Idaṃ kira bodhisatto attano abbhantare ñāṇāvudhaṃ sandhāya kathesi. 
484036,110,1766,123,182,1,367,45,"Taṃ sutvā yakkho cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ māṇavo saccameva bhaṇati, imassa purisasīhassa sarīrato muggabījamattampi maṃsakhaṇḍaṃ mayhaṃ kucchi jīretuṃ na sakkhissati, vissajjessāmi nan’’ ti maraṇabhayatajjito bodhisattaṃ vissajjetvā‘‘ māṇava, purisasīho tvaṃ, na te ahaṃ maṃsaṃ khādissāmi, tvaṃ ajja rāhumukhā muttacando viya mama hatthato muccitvā ñātisuhajjamaṇḍalaṃ tosento yāhī’’ ti āha. "
484037,110,1767,2,6,1,23,4,Atha naṃ bodhisatto āha–
484038,110,1767,7,26,1,123,15,"‘‘ yakkha, ahaṃ tāva gacchissāmi, tvaṃ pana pubbepi akusalaṃ katvā luddo lohitapāṇi pararuhiramaṃsabhakkho yakkho hutvā nibbatto. "
484039,110,1767,27,114,1,746,79,"Sace idhāpi ṭhatvā akusalameva karissasi, andhakārā andhakārameva gamissasi, maṃ diṭṭhakālato paṭṭhāya pana na sakkā tayā akusalaṃ kātuṃ, pāṇātipātakammaṃ nāma niraye tiracchānayoniyaṃ pettivisaye asurakāye ca nibbatteti, manussesu nibbattanibbattaṭṭhāne appāyukasaṃvattanikaṃ hotī’’ ti evamādinā nayena pañcannaṃ dussīlyakammānaṃ ādīnavaṃ, pañcannaṃ sīlānaṃ ānisaṃsañca kathetvā nānākāraṇehi yakkhaṃ tajjetvā dhammaṃ desetvā dametvā nibbisevanaṃ katvā pañcasu sīlesu patiṭṭhāpetvā tassāyeva naṃ aṭaviyā balipaṭiggāhakaṃ devataṃ katvā appamādena ovaditvā aṭavito nikkhamitvā aṭavimukhe manussānaṃ ācikkhitvā sannaddhapañcāvudho bārāṇasiṃ gantvā mātāpitaro disvā aparabhāge rajje patiṭṭhāya dhammena rajjaṃ kārento dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. "
484040,110,1768,2,10,1,71,8,Satthāpi imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā abhisambuddho hutvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
484041,110,1769,2,4,1,0,0,55.
484042,110,1770,2,10,1,35,6,"‘ ‘ Yo alīnena cittena, alīnamanaso naro; "
484043,110,1771,2,8,1,45,5,"Bhāveti kusalaṃ dhammaṃ, yogakkhemassa pattiyā; "
484044,110,1772,2,9,1,42,4,"Pāpuṇe anupubbena, sabbasaṃyojanakkhayan’’ ti. "
484045,110,1773,2,68,1,563,54,"Tatrāyaṃ piṇḍattho– yo puriso alīnena asaṃkuṭitena cittena pakatiyāpi alīnamano alīnajjhāsayova hutvā anavajjaṭṭhena kusalaṃ sattatiṃ sabodhipakkhiyabhedaṃ dhammaṃ bhāveti vaḍḍheti, visālena cittena vipassanaṃ anuyuñjati catūhi yogehi khemassa nibbānassa pattiyā, so evaṃ sabbasaṅkhāresu‘‘ aniccaṃ dukkhaṃ anattā’’ ti tilakkhaṇaṃ āropetvā taruṇavipassanato paṭṭhāya uppanne bodhipakkhiyadhamme bhāvento anupubbena ekasaṃyojanampi anavasesetvā sabbasaṃyojanakkhayakarassa catutthamaggassa pariyosāne uppannattā‘‘ sabbasaṃyojanakkhayo’’ ti saṅkhyaṃ gataṃ arahattaṃ pāpuṇeyyāti. "
484046,110,1774,2,19,1,129,15,"Evaṃ satthā arahattena dhammadesanāya kūṭaṃ gahetvā matthake cattāri saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne so bhikkhu arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
484047,110,1774,20,25,1,46,5,Satthā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
484048,110,1774,26,40,1,68,9,"‘‘ tadā yakkho aṅgulimālo ahosi, pañcāvudhakumāro pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
484049,110,1775,2,4,1,31,2,Pañcāvudhajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
484050,110,1777,2,7,1,28,2,[ 56]6. Kañcanakkhandhajātakavaṇṇanā 
484051,110,1778,2,15,1,89,11,Yo pahaṭṭhena {cittenā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484052,110,1778,16,27,1,90,11,Eko kira sāvatthivāsī kulaputto satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā ratanasāsane uraṃ datvā pabbaji. 
484053,110,1778,28,59,1,182,18,"Athassa ācariyupajjhāyā‘‘ āvuso, ekavidhena sīlaṃ nāma, duvidhena, tividhena, catubbidhena, pañcavidhena, chabbidhena, sattavidhena, aṭṭhavidhena, navavidhena, dasavidhena, bahuvidhena sīlaṃ nāma. "
484054,110,1778,60,71,1,63,9,"Idaṃ cūḷasīlaṃ nāma, idaṃ majjhimasīlaṃ nāma, idaṃ mahāsīlaṃ nāma. "
484055,110,1778,72,92,1,146,15,"Idaṃ pātimokkhasaṃvarasīlaṃ nāma, idaṃ indriyasaṃvarasīlaṃ nāma, idaṃ ājīvapārisuddhisīlaṃ nāma, idaṃ paccayapaṭisevanasīlaṃ nāmā’’ ti sīlaṃ ācikkhanti. "
484056,110,1778,93,131,1,207,30,"So cintesi‘‘ idaṃ sīlaṃ nāma atibahu, ahaṃ ettakaṃ samādāya vattituṃ na sakkhissāmi, sīlaṃ pūretuṃ asakkontassa ca nāma pabbajjāya ko attho, ahaṃ gihī hutvā dānādīni puññāni ca karissāmi, puttadārañca posessāmī’’ ti. "
484057,110,1778,132,162,1,164,22,"Evañca pana cintetvā‘‘ bhante, ahaṃ sīlaṃ rakkhituṃ na sakkhissāmi, asakkontassa ca nāma pabbajjāya ko attho, ahaṃ hīnāyāvattissāmi, tumhākaṃ pattacīvaraṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti āha. "
484058,110,1779,2,24,1,112,17,Atha naṃ āhaṃsu‘‘ āvuso evaṃ sante dasabalaṃ vanditvāva yāhī’’ ti te taṃ ādāya satthu santikaṃ dhammasabhaṃ agamaṃsu. 
484059,110,1779,25,41,1,71,10,"Satthā disvāva‘‘ kiṃ, bhikkhave, anatthikaṃ bhikkhuṃ ādāya āgatatthā’’ ti āha. "
484060,110,1779,42,64,1,115,16,"Bhante, ayaṃ bhikkhu‘‘ ahaṃ sīlaṃ rakkhituṃ na sakkhissāmī’’ ti pattacīvaraṃ niyyādeti, atha naṃ mayaṃ gahetvā āgatamhāti."
484061,110,1779,65,78,1,66,9,"‘‘ Kasmā pana tumhe, bhikkhave, imassa bhikkhuno bahuṃ sīlaṃ ācikkhatha. "
484062,110,1779,79,86,1,54,6,"Yattakaṃ esa rakkhituṃ sakkoti, tattakameva rakkhissati. "
484063,110,1779,87,115,1,151,22,"Ito paṭṭhāya tumhe etaṃ mā kiñci avacuttha, ahamettha kattabbaṃ jānissāmi, ehi tvaṃ bhikkhu, kiṃ te bahunā sīlena, tīṇiyeva sīlāni rakkhituṃ sakkhissasī’’ ti?"
484064,110,1779,116,124,1,21,3,"‘‘ Rakkhissāmi, bhante’’ ti. "
484065,110,1779,125,148,1,126,19,"Tena hi tvaṃ ito paṭṭhāya kāyadvāraṃ vacīdvāraṃ manodvāranti tīṇi dvārāni rakkha, mā kāyena pāpakammaṃ kari, mā vācāya, mā manasā."
484066,110,1779,149,162,1,53,8,"‘‘ Gaccha mā hīnāyāvatti, imāni tīṇiyeva sīlāni rakkhā’’ ti. "
484067,110,1779,163,185,1,135,16,"Ettāvatā so bhikkhu tuṭṭhamānaso‘‘ sādhu, bhante, rakkhissāmi imāni tīṇi sīlānī’’ ti satthāraṃ vanditvā ācariyupajjhāyehi saddhiṃyeva agamāsi. "
484068,110,1779,186,234,1,356,40,"So tāni tīṇi sīlāni pūrentova aññāsi‘‘ ācariyupajjhāyehi mayhaṃ ācikkhitaṃ sīlampi ettakameva, te pana attano abuddhabhāvena maṃ bujjhāpetuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu, sammāsambuddho attano buddhasubuddhatāya anuttaradhammarājatāya ettakaṃ sīlaṃ tīsuyeva dvāresu pakkhipitvā maṃ gaṇhāpesi, avassayo vata me satthā jāto’’ ti vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā katipāheneva arahatte patiṭṭhāsi. "
484069,110,1780,2,44,1,274,34,"Taṃ pavattiṃ ñatvā dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitā bhikkhū‘‘ āvuso, taṃ kira bhikkhuṃ‘ bahusīlāni rakkhituṃ na sakkomī’ ti hīnāyāvattantaṃ sabbāni sīlāni tīhi koṭṭhāsehi saṅkhipitvā gāhāpetvā satthā arahattaṃ pāpesi, aho buddhānaṃ balaṃ nāma acchariyan’’ ti buddhaguṇe kathentā nisīdiṃsu. "
484070,110,1780,45,100,1,305,39,"Atha satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhave, atigarukopi bhāro koṭṭhāsavasena bhājetvā dinno lahuko viya hoti, pubbepi paṇḍitā mahantaṃ kañcanakkhandhaṃ labhitvā ukkhipituṃ asakkontā vibhāgaṃ katvā ukkhipitvā agamaṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
484071,110,1781,2,13,1,84,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto ekasmiṃ gāmake kassako ahosi. 
484072,110,1781,14,21,1,61,7,So ekadivasaṃ aññatarasmiṃ chaḍḍitagāmake khette kasiṃ kasati. 
484073,110,1781,22,34,1,119,12,Pubbe ca tasmiṃ gāme eko vibhavasampanno seṭṭhi ūrumattapariṇāhaṃ catuhatthāyāmaṃ kañcanakkhandhaṃ nidahitvā kālamakāsi. 
484074,110,1781,35,40,1,45,5,Tasmiṃ bodhisattassa naṅgalaṃ lagitvā aṭṭhāsi. 
484075,110,1781,41,73,1,216,24,So‘‘ mūlasantānakaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti paṃsuṃ viyūhanto taṃ disvā paṃsunā paṭicchādetvā divasaṃ kasitvā atthaṅgate sūriye yuganaṅgalādīni ekamante nikkhipitvā‘‘ kañcanakkhandhaṃ gaṇhitvā gacchissāmī’’ ti taṃ ukkhipituṃ nāsakkhi. 
484076,110,1781,74,99,1,178,18,"Asakkonto nisīditvā‘‘ ettakaṃ kucchibharaṇāya bhavissati, ettakaṃ nidahitvā ṭhapessāmi, ettakena kammante payojessāmi, ettakaṃ dānādipuññakiriyāya bhavissatī’’ ti cattāro koṭṭhāse akāsi. "
484077,110,1781,100,107,1,61,7,Tassevaṃ vibhattakāle so kañcanakkhandho sallahuko viya ahosi. 
484078,110,1781,108,120,1,89,12,So taṃ ukkhipitvā gharaṃ netvā catudhā vibhajitvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
484079,110,1782,2,12,1,74,9,Iti bhagavā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā abhisambuddho hutvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
