484085,110,1787,7,20,1,121,11,"{Pahaṭṭhamanaso}ti tāya eva vinīvaraṇatāya pahaṭṭhamānaso, suvaṇṇaṃ viya pahaṃsitvā samujjotitasappabhāsacitto hutvāti attho. "
484086,110,1788,2,11,1,86,9,Evaṃ satthā arahattakūṭena desanaṃ niṭṭhāpetvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
