484089,110,1791,2,7,1,22,2,[ 57]7. Vānarindajātakavaṇṇanā 
484090,110,1792,2,16,1,104,12,Yassete caturo {dhammā}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattassa vadhāya parisakkanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484091,110,1792,17,54,1,196,25,"Tasmiñhi samaye satthā‘‘ devadatto vadhāya parisakkatī’’ ti sutvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva devadatto mayhaṃ vadhāya parisakkati, pubbepi parisakkiyeva, tāsamattampi pana kātuṃ nāsakkhī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
484092,110,1793,2,17,1,157,15,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kapiyoniyaṃ nibbattitvā vuḍḍhimanvāya assapotakappamāṇo thāmasampanno ekacaro hutvā nadītīre viharati. 
484093,110,1793,18,28,1,89,10,Tassā pana nadiyā vemajjhe eko dīpako nānappakārehi ambapanasādīhi phalarukkhehi sampanno. 
484094,110,1793,29,50,1,164,19,"Bodhisatto nāgabalo thāmasampanno nadiyā orimatīrato uppatitvā dīpakassa orato nadīmajjhe eko piṭṭhipāsāṇo atthi, tasmiṃ nipatati, tato uppatitvā tasmiṃ dīpake patati. "
484095,110,1793,51,65,1,126,14,Tattha nānappakārāni phalāni khāditvā sāyaṃ teneva upāyena paccāgantvā attano vasanaṭṭhāne vasitvā punadivasepi tatheva karoti. 
484096,110,1793,66,71,1,35,5,Iminā niyāmena tattha vāsaṃ kappeti. 
484097,110,1794,2,11,1,62,9,Tasmiṃ pana kāle eko kumbhīlo sapajāpatiko tassā nadiyā vasati. 
484098,110,1794,12,26,1,111,12,Tassa bhariyā bodhisattaṃ aparāparaṃ gacchantaṃ disvā bodhisattassa hadayamaṃse dohaḷaṃ uppādetvā kumbhīlaṃ āha –
484099,110,1794,27,42,1,65,9,"‘‘ mayhaṃ kho, ayya, imassa vānarindassa hadayamaṃse dohaḷo uppanno’’ ti. "
484100,110,1794,43,69,1,120,16,"Kumbhīlo‘‘ sādhu, bhadde, lacchasī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ ajja taṃ sāyaṃ dīpakato āgacchantameva gaṇhissāmī’’ ti gantvā piṭṭhipāsāṇe nipajji. "
484101,110,1795,2,10,1,72,8,Bodhisatto divasaṃ caritvā sāyanhasamaye dīpake ṭhitova pāsāṇaṃ oloketvā–
484102,110,1795,11,27,1,64,11,"‘‘ ayaṃ pāsāṇo idāni uccataro khāyati, kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti cintesi. "
484103,110,1795,28,34,1,67,6,Tassa kira udakappamāṇañca pāsāṇappamāṇañca suvavatthāpitameva hoti. 
484104,110,1795,35,69,1,173,27,"Tenassa etadahosi‘‘ ajja imissā nadiyā udakaṃ neva hāyati, na ca vaḍḍhati, atha ca panāyaṃ pāsāṇo mahā hutvā paññāyati, kacci nu kho ettha mayhaṃ gahaṇatthāya kumbhīlo nipanno’’ ti. "
484105,110,1795,70,105,1,143,22,So‘‘ vīmaṃsāmi tāva nan’’ ti tattheva ṭhatvā pāsāṇena saddhiṃ kathento viya‘‘ bho pāsāṇā’’ ti vatvā paṭivacanaṃ alabhanto yāvatatiyaṃ‘‘ bho pāsāṇā’’ ti āha. 
484106,110,1795,106,110,1,30,4,Pāsāṇo kiṃ paṭivacanaṃ dassati. 
484107,110,1795,111,128,1,67,12,"Punapi vānaro‘‘ kiṃ bho pāsāṇa, ajja mayhaṃ paṭivacanaṃ na desī’’ ti āha. "
484108,110,1795,129,158,1,138,19,"Kumbhīlo‘‘ addhā aññesu divasesu ayaṃ pāsāṇo vānarindassa paṭivacanaṃ adāsi, dassāmi dānissa paṭivacanan’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ kiṃ, bho vānarindā’’ ti āha."
484109,110,1795,159,166,1,12,3,‘‘ Kosi tvan’’ ti?
484110,110,1795,167,174,1,16,3,‘‘ Ahaṃ kumbhīlo’’ ti.
484111,110,1795,175,183,1,28,4,‘‘ Kimatthaṃ ettha nipannosī’’ ti?
484112,110,1795,184,192,1,33,4,‘‘ Tava hadayamaṃsaṃ patthayamāno’’ ti. 
484113,110,1795,193,210,1,82,12,"Bodhisatto cintesi‘‘ añño me gamanamaggo natthi, ajja mayā esa kumbhīlo vañcetabbo’’ ti. "
484114,110,1795,211,235,1,127,18,"Atha naṃ evamāha‘‘ samma kumbhīla, ahaṃ attānaṃ tuyhaṃ pariccajissāmi, tvaṃ mukhaṃ vivaritvā maṃ tava santikaṃ āgatakāle gaṇhāhī’’ ti. "
484115,110,1795,236,241,1,45,5,Kumbhīlānañhi mukhe vivaṭe akkhīni nimmīlanti. 
484116,110,1795,242,252,1,69,9,"So taṃ kāraṇaṃ asallakkhetvā mukhaṃ vivari, athassa akkhīni pithīyiṃsu. "
484117,110,1795,253,259,1,46,6,So mukhaṃ vivaritvā akkhīni nimmīletvā nipajji. 
484118,110,1795,260,276,1,140,16,Bodhisatto tathābhāvaṃ ñatvā dīpakā uppatito gantvā kumbhīlassa matthake akkamitvā tato uppatito vijjulatā viya vijjotamāno paratīre aṭṭhāsi. 
484119,110,1796,2,30,1,165,20,"Kumbhīlo taṃ acchariyaṃ disvā‘‘ iminā vānarindena atiaccherakaṃ katan’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ bho vānarinda, imasmiṃ loke catūhi dhammehi samannāgato puggalo paccāmitte adhibhavati. "
484120,110,1796,31,43,1,64,10,Te sabbepi tuyhaṃ abbhantare atthi maññe’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
