484122,110,1798,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Yassete caturo dhammā, vānarinda yathā tava; "
484123,110,1799,2,13,1,49,8,"Saccaṃ dhammo dhiti cāgo, diṭṭhaṃ so ativattatī’’ ti. "
484124,110,1800,2,9,1,39,5,Tattha {yassā}ti yassa kassaci puggalassa. 
484125,110,1800,10,16,1,42,5,{Ete}ti idāni vattabbe paccakkhato niddisati. 
484126,110,1800,17,22,1,28,4,Caturo {dhammā}ti cattāro guṇā. 
484127,110,1800,23,42,1,102,14,"Saccan ti vacīsaccaṃ,‘‘ mama santikaṃ āgamissāmī’’ ti vatvā musāvādaṃ akatvā āgatoyevāti etaṃ te vacīsaccaṃ. "
484128,110,1800,43,61,1,83,12,"{Dhammo}ti vicāraṇapaññā,‘‘ evaṃ kate idaṃ nāma bhavissatī’’ ti esā te vicāraṇapaññā atthi. "
484129,110,1800,62,71,1,52,7,"{Dhitī}ti abbocchinnaṃ vīriyaṃ vuccati, etampi te atthi. "
484130,110,1800,72,83,1,66,8,"{Cāgo}ti attapariccāgo, tvaṃ attānaṃ pariccajitvā mama santikaṃ āgato. "
484131,110,1800,84,91,1,47,6,"Yaṃ panāhaṃ gaṇhituṃ nāsakkhiṃ, mayhamevesa doso. "
484132,110,1800,92,95,1,22,3,Diṭṭhan ti paccāmittaṃ. 
484133,110,1800,96,122,1,158,22,"So {ativattatī}ti yassa puggalassa yathā tava, evaṃ ete cattāro dhammā atthi, so yathā maṃ ajja tvaṃ atikkanto, tatheva attano paccāmittaṃ atikkamati abhibhavatīti. "
484134,110,1800,123,130,1,60,7,Evaṃ kumbhīlo bodhisattaṃ pasaṃsitvā attano vasaṭṭhānaṃ gato. 
484135,110,1801,2,27,1,159,18,"Satthāpi ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, devadatto idāneva mayhaṃ vadhāya parisakkati, pubbepi parisakkiyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
