484167,110,1812,20,25,1,47,4,{Paññā}ti paññāpadaṭṭhānāya upāyapaññāyetaṃ nāmaṃ. 
484168,110,1813,2,20,1,103,14,Evaṃ so dakarakkhaso imāya gāthāya bodhisattassa thutiṃ katvā‘‘ imāni pupphāni kimatthaṃ harasī’’ ti pucchi.
484169,110,1813,21,34,1,49,8,"‘‘ Pitā maṃ rājānaṃ kātukāmo, tena kāraṇena harāmī’’ ti."
484170,110,1813,35,53,1,110,14,‘‘ Na sakkā tādisena uttamapurisena pupphāni vahituṃ ahaṃ vahissāmī’’ ti ukkhipitvā tassa pacchato pacchato agamāsi. 
484171,110,1813,54,90,1,215,27,"Athassa pitā dūratova taṃ disvā‘‘ ahaṃ imaṃ‘ rakkhasabhattaṃ bhavissatī’ ti pahiṇiṃ, so dānesa rakkhasaṃ pupphāni gāhāpento āgacchati, idānimhi naṭṭho’’ ti cintento sattadhā hadayaphālanaṃ patvā tattheva jīvitakkhayaṃ patto. "
