484176,110,1817,2,7,1,24,2,[ 59]9. Bherivādakajātakavaṇṇanā 
484177,110,1818,2,13,1,86,10,Dhame {dhame}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ dubbacabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484178,110,1818,14,53,1,167,25,"Tañhi bhikkhuṃ satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu dubbacosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhagavā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na tvaṃ bhikkhu idāneva dubbaco, pubbepi dubbacoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
484179,110,1819,2,12,1,97,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto bherivādakakule nibbattitvā gāmake vasati. 
484180,110,1819,13,42,1,153,20,So‘‘ bārāṇasiyaṃ nakkhattaṃ ghuṭṭhan’’ ti sutvā‘‘ samajjamaṇḍale bheriṃ vādetvā dhanaṃ āharissāmī’’ ti puttaṃ ādāya tattha gantvā bheriṃ vādetvā bahudhanaṃ labhi. 
484181,110,1819,43,86,1,264,33,"So taṃ ādāya attano gāmaṃ gacchanto corāṭaviṃ patvā puttaṃ nirantaraṃ bheriṃ vādentaṃ vāresi‘‘ tāta, nirantaraṃ avādetvā maggapaṭipannassa issarassa bheriṃ viya antarantarā vādehī’’ ti so pitarā vāriyamānopi‘‘ bherisaddeneva core palāpessāmī’’ ti vatvā nirantarameva vādesi. "
484182,110,1819,87,119,1,195,24,Corā paṭhamaññeva bherisaddaṃ sutvā‘‘ issarabherī bhavissatī’’ ti palāyitvā ati viya ekābaddhaṃ saddaṃ sutvā‘‘ nāyaṃ issarabherī bhavissatī’’ ti āgantvā upadhārentā dveyeva jane disvā pothetvā vilumpiṃsu. 
484183,110,1819,120,138,1,98,14,Bodhisatto‘‘ kicchena vata no laddhaṃ dhanaṃ ekābaddhaṃ katvā vādento nāsesī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
