484214,110,1843,2,7,1,23,2,[ 61]1. Asātamantajātakavaṇṇanā 
484215,110,1844,2,17,1,89,11,Asā lokitthiyo {nāmā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ukkaṇṭhitaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484216,110,1844,18,23,1,43,5,Tassa vatthu ummādantijātake āvi bhavissati. 
484217,110,1844,24,51,1,155,22,"Taṃ pana bhikkhuṃ satthā‘‘ bhikkhu itthiyo nāma asātā asatiyo lāmikā pacchimikā, tvaṃ evarūpaṃ lāmikaṃ itthiṃ nissāya kasmā ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
484218,110,1845,2,23,1,195,21,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto gandhāraraṭṭhe takkasilāyaṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto tīsu vedesu sabbasippesu ca nipphattiṃ patto disāpāmokkho ācariyo ahosi. 
484219,110,1845,24,34,1,95,10,Tadā bārāṇasiyaṃ ekasmiṃ brāhmaṇakule puttassa jātadivase aggiṃ gahetvā anibbāyantaṃ ṭhapayiṃsu. 
484220,110,1845,35,51,1,111,13,"Atha naṃ brāhmaṇakumāraṃ soḷasavassakāle mātāpitaro āhaṃsu‘‘ putta, mayaṃ tava jātadivase aggiṃ gahetvā ṭhapayimha. "
484221,110,1845,52,66,1,124,13,"Sace brahmalokaparāyaṇo bhavitukāmo, tvaṃ aggiṃ ādāya araññaṃ pavisitvā aggiṃ bhagavantaṃ namassamāno brahmalokaparāyaṇo hohi. "
484222,110,1845,67,83,1,121,13,"Sace agāraṃ ajjhāvasitukāmo, takkasilaṃ gantvā disāpāmokkhassa ācariyassa santike sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā kuṭumbaṃ saṇṭhapehī’’ ti. "
484223,110,1845,84,108,1,177,19,"Māṇavo‘‘ nāhaṃ sakkhissāmi araññe aggiṃ paricarituṃ, kuṭumbameva saṇṭhapessāmī’’ ti mātāpitaro vanditvā ācariyabhāgaṃ sahassaṃ gahetvā takkasilaṃ gantvā sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā paccāgamāsi. "
484224,110,1846,2,11,1,76,8,"Mātāpitaro panassa anatthikā gharāvāsena, araññe aggiṃ paricarāpetukāmā honti. "
484225,110,1846,12,37,1,146,21,Atha naṃ mātā itthīnaṃ dosaṃ dassetvā araññaṃ pesetukāmā‘‘ so ācariyo paṇḍito byatto sakkhissati me puttassa itthīnaṃ dosaṃ kathetun’’ ti cintetvā āha–
484226,110,1846,38,49,1,27,5,"‘‘ uggahitaṃ te, tāta, sippan’’ ti."
484227,110,1846,50,58,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, ammā’’ ti."
484228,110,1846,59,68,1,27,4,‘‘ Asātamantopi te uggahito’’ ti.
484229,110,1846,69,78,1,19,4,"‘‘ Na uggahito, ammā’’ ti."
484230,110,1846,79,102,1,89,15,"‘‘ Tāta, yadi te asātamanto na uggahito, kiṃ nāma te sippaṃ uggahitaṃ, gaccha, uggaṇhitvā ehī’’ ti. "
484231,110,1846,103,113,1,41,6,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti puna takkasilābhimukho pāyāsi. 
484232,110,1846,114,120,1,51,5,Tassapi ācariyassa mātā mahallikā vīsativassasatikā . 
484233,110,1846,121,129,1,53,7,So taṃ sahatthā nhāpento bhojento pāyento paṭijaggati. 
484234,110,1846,130,136,1,43,6,Aññe manussā naṃ tathā karontaṃ jigucchanti. 
484235,110,1846,137,151,1,81,10,So cintesi‘‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ araññaṃ pavisitvā tattha mātaraṃ paṭijagganto vihareyyan’’ ti. 
484236,110,1846,152,168,1,159,16,Athekasmiṃ vivitte araññe udakaphāsukaṭṭhāne paṇṇasālaṃ kāretvā sappitaṇḍulādīni āharāpetvā mātaraṃ ukkhipitvā tattha gantvā mātaraṃ paṭijagganto vāsaṃ kappesi. 
484237,110,1847,2,24,1,129,18,Sopi kho māṇavo takkasilaṃ gantvā ācariyaṃ apassanto‘‘ kahaṃ ācariyo’’ ti pucchitvā taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā tattha gantvā vanditvā aṭṭhāsi. 
484238,110,1847,25,41,1,53,10,"Atha naṃ ācariyo‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, tāta, atisīghaṃ āgatosī’’ ti?"
484239,110,1847,42,54,1,51,8,‘‘ Nanu ahaṃ tumhehi asātamanto nāma na uggaṇhāpito’’ ti?
484240,110,1847,55,67,1,51,8,‘‘ Ko pana te asātamante uggaṇhitabbe katvā kathesī’’ ti?
484241,110,1847,68,76,1,22,4,‘‘ Mayhaṃ mātā ācariyā’’ ti. 
484242,110,1847,77,96,1,105,14,"Bodhisatto cintesi‘‘ asātamanto nāma koci natthi, imassa pana mātā imaṃ itthidose jānāpetukāmā bhavissatī’’ ti. "
484243,110,1847,97,145,1,330,39,"Atha naṃ‘‘ sādhu, tāta, dassāmi te asātamante, tvaṃ ajja ādiṃ katvā mama ṭhāne ṭhatvā mama mātaraṃ sahatthā nhāpento bhojento pāyento paṭijaggāhi, hatthapādasīsapiṭṭhisambāhanādīni cassā karonto‘ ayye jaraṃ pattakālepi tāva te evarūpaṃ sarīraṃ, daharakāle kīdisaṃ ahosī’ ti hatthapādaparikammādikaraṇakāle hatthapādādīnaṃ vaṇṇaṃ katheyyāsi. "
484244,110,1847,146,170,1,130,19,"Yañca te mama mātā katheti, taṃ alajjanto aniguhanto mayhaṃ āroceyyāsi, evaṃ karonto asātamante lacchasi, akaronto na lacchasī’’ ti āha. "
484245,110,1847,171,187,1,94,12,So‘‘ sādhu ācariyā’’ ti tassa vacanaṃ sampaṭicchitvā tato paṭṭhāya sabbaṃ yathāvuttavidhānaṃ akāsi. 
484246,110,1848,2,23,1,137,16,Athassā tasmiṃ māṇave punappunaṃ vaṇṇayamāne‘‘ ayaṃ mayā saddhiṃ abhiramitukāmo bhavissatī’’ ti andhāya jarājiṇṇāya abbhantare kileso uppajji . 
484247,110,1848,24,40,1,94,12,Sā ekadivasaṃ attano sarīravaṇṇaṃ kathayamānaṃ māṇavaṃ āha‘‘ mayā saddhiṃ abhiramituṃ icchasī’’ ti?
