484249,110,1848,56,68,1,36,7,"‘‘ Sace maṃ icchasi, puttaṃ me mārehī’’ ti."
484250,110,1848,69,86,1,104,13,‘‘ Ahaṃ ācariyassa santike ettakaṃ sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā kilesamattaṃ nissāya kinti katvā ācariyaṃ māressāmī’’ ti.
484251,110,1848,87,103,1,61,11,"‘‘ Tena hi sace tvaṃ maṃ na pariccajasi, ahameva naṃ māressāmī’’ ti. "
484252,110,1848,104,125,1,148,19,"Evaṃ itthiyo nāma asātā lāmikā pacchimikā, tathārūpe nāma vaye ṭhitā rāgacittaṃ uppādetvā kilesaṃ anuvattamānā evaṃ upakārakaṃ puttaṃ māretukāmā jātā. "
484253,110,1848,126,132,1,46,6,Māṇavo sabbaṃ taṃ kathaṃ bodhisattassa ārocesi. 
484254,110,1849,2,57,1,305,38,"Bodhisatto ‘‘ suṭṭhu te, māṇava, kataṃ mayhaṃ ārocentenā’’ ti vatvā mātu āyusaṅkhāraṃ olokento‘‘ ajjeva marissatī’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ ehi, māṇava, vīmaṃsissāma nan’’ ti ekaṃ udumbararukkhaṃ chinditvā attano pamāṇena kaṭṭharūpakaṃ katvā sasīsaṃ pārupitvā attano sayanaṭṭhāne uttānaṃ nipajjāpetvā rajjukaṃ bandhitvā antevāsikaṃ āha–"
484255,110,1849,58,72,1,51,9,"‘‘ tāta, pharasuṃ ādāya gantvā mama mātu saññaṃ dehī’’ ti. "
