484281,110,1859,7,24,1,105,15,"Velā tāsaṃ na {vijjatī}ti amma, tāsaṃ itthīnaṃ kilesuppattiṃ patvā velā saṃvaro mariyādā pamāṇaṃ nāma natthi. "
484282,110,1859,25,51,1,191,21,"Sārattā ca pagabbhā {cā}ti velā ca etāsaṃ natthi, pañcasu kāmaguṇesu sārattā allīnā, tathā kāyapāgabbhiyena, vācāpāgabbhiyena, manopāgabbhiyenāti tividhena pāgabbhiyena samannāgatattā pagabbhā cetā. "
484283,110,1859,52,63,1,88,10,"Etāsañhi abbhantare kāyadvārādīni patvā saṃvaro nāma natthi, lolā kākapaṭibhāgāti dasseti. "
484284,110,1859,64,106,1,230,28,"Sikhī sabbaghaso {yathā}ti amma, yathā jālasikhāya‘‘ sikhī’’ ti saṅkhaṃ gato aggi nāma gūthagatādibhedaṃ asucimpi, sappimadhuphāṇitādibhedaṃ sucimpi, iṭṭhampi aniṭṭhampi yaṃ yadeva labhati, sabbaṃ ghasati khādati, tasmā‘‘ sabbaghaso’’ ti vuccati. "
484285,110,1859,107,135,1,244,24,"Tatheva tā itthiyopi hatthimeṇḍagomeṇḍādayo vā hontu hīnajaccā hīnakammantā, khattiyādayo vā hontu uttamakammantā, hīnukkaṭṭhabhāvaṃ acintetvā lokassādavasena kilesasanthave uppanne yaṃ yaṃ labhanti, sabbameva sevantīti sabbaghasasikhisadisā honti. "
484286,110,1859,136,143,1,50,6,"Tasmā sikhī sabbaghaso yathā, tathevetāti veditabbā. "
484287,110,1860,2,17,1,114,13,Tā hitvā {pabbajissāmī}ti ahaṃ tā lāmikā dukkhavatthubhūtā itthiyo hitvā araññaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajissāmi. 
484288,110,1860,18,30,1,115,11,"Vivekamanubrūhayanti kāyaviveko cittaviveko upadhivivekoti tayo vivekā, tesu idha kāyavivekopi vaṭṭati cittavivekopi. "
484289,110,1860,31,65,1,228,29,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– ahaṃ, amma, pabbajitvā kasiṇaparikammaṃ katvā aṭṭha samāpattiyo ca pañcābhiññā ca uppādetvā gaṇato kāyaṃ, kilesehi ca cittaṃ vivecetvā imaṃ vivekaṃ brūhento vaḍḍhento brahmalokaparāyaṇo bhavissāmi, alaṃ me agārenāti. "
484290,110,1860,66,79,1,130,13,Evaṃ itthiyo garahitvā mātāpitaro vanditvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā pabbajitvā vuttappakāraṃ vivekaṃ brūhento brahmalokaparāyaṇo ahosi. 
484291,110,1861,2,28,1,169,20,"Satthāpi ‘‘ evaṃ bhikkhu itthiyo nāma asātā lāmikā pacchimikā dukkhadāyikā’’ ti itthīnaṃ aguṇaṃ kathetvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne so bhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhāsi. "
