484295,110,1864,2,7,1,22,2,[ 62]2. Aṇḍabhūtajātakavaṇṇanā 
484296,110,1865,2,12,1,82,9,Yaṃ brāhmaṇo {avādesī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ukkaṇṭhitamevārabbha kathesi. 
484297,110,1865,13,54,1,205,28,"Tañhi satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccan’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhu itthiyo nāma arakkhiyā, pubbe paṇḍitā itthiṃ gabbhato paṭṭhāya rakkhantāpi rakkhituṃ nāsakkhiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
484298,110,1866,2,23,1,192,21,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa aggamahesiyā kucchismiṃ nibbattitvā vayappatto sabbasippesu nipphattiṃ patvā pitu accayena rajje patiṭṭhāya dhammena rajjaṃ kāresi. 
