484477,110,1904,2,4,1,32,2,Takkapaṇḍitajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
484478,110,1906,2,7,1,21,2,[ 64]4. Durājānajātakavaṇṇanā 
484479,110,1907,2,15,1,86,13,Māsu nandi icchati man ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ upāsakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484480,110,1907,16,36,1,146,17,"Eko kira sāvatthivāsī upāsako tīsu saraṇesu pañcasu ca sīlesu patiṭṭhito buddhamāmako, dhammamāmako, saṅghamāmako, bhariyā panassa dussīlā pāpadhammā. "
484481,110,1907,37,56,1,127,17,"Yaṃ divasaṃ micchācāraṃ carati, taṃ divasaṃ satakītadāsī viya hoti, micchācārassa pana akatadivase sāminī viya hoti caṇḍā pharusā. "
484482,110,1907,57,70,1,80,12,"So tassā bhāvaṃ jānituṃ na sakkoti, atha tāya ubbāḷho buddhūpaṭṭhānaṃ na gacchati. "
484483,110,1907,71,81,1,79,10,Atha naṃ ekadivasaṃ gandhapupphādīni ādāya āgantvā vanditvā nisinnaṃ satthā āha–
484484,110,1907,82,98,1,70,10,"‘‘ kiṃ nu kho tvaṃ, upāsaka, sattaṭṭha divase buddhūpaṭṭhānaṃ nāgacchasī’’ ti. "
484485,110,1907,99,116,1,96,14,"Gharaṇī me, bhante, ekasmiṃ divase satakītadāsī viya hoti, ekasmiṃ divase sāminī viya caṇḍā pharusā. "
484486,110,1907,117,129,1,85,11,"Ahaṃ tassā bhāvaṃ jānituṃ na sakkomi, svāhaṃ tāya ubbāḷho buddhūpaṭṭhānaṃ nāgacchāmīti. "
484487,110,1907,130,165,1,193,27,"Athassa vacanaṃ sutvā satthā‘‘ upāsaka,‘ mātugāmassa bhāvo nāma dujjāno’ ti pubbepi te paṇḍitā kathayiṃsu, tvaṃ pana taṃ bhavasaṅkhepagatattā sallakkhetuṃ na sakkosī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
484488,110,1908,2,16,1,121,13,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto disāpāmokkho ācariyo hutvā pañca māṇavakasatāni sippaṃ sikkhāpeti. 
484489,110,1908,17,43,1,220,25,Atheko tiroraṭṭhavāsiko brāhmaṇamāṇavako āgantvā tassa santike sippaṃ uggaṇhanto ekāya itthiyā paṭibaddhacitto hutvā taṃ bhariyaṃ katvā tasmiṃyeva bārāṇasinagare vasanto dve tisso velāyo ācariyassa upaṭṭhānaṃ na gacchati. 
484490,110,1908,44,49,1,37,5,Sā panassa bhariyā dussīlā pāpadhammā. 
484491,110,1908,50,62,1,82,11,"Micchācāraṃ ciṇṇadivase dāsī viya hoti, aciṇṇadivase sāminī viya hoti caṇḍā pharusā. "
484492,110,1908,63,75,1,91,12,So tassā bhāvaṃ jānituṃ asakkonto tāya ubbāḷho ākulacitto ācariyassa upaṭṭhānaṃ na gacchati. 
484493,110,1908,76,96,1,86,13,"Atha naṃ sattaṭṭha divase atikkamitvā āgataṃ‘‘ kiṃ, māṇava , na paññāyasī’’ ti ācariyo pucchi. "
484494,110,1908,97,113,1,76,11,"So‘‘ bhariyā maṃ, ācariya, ekadivasaṃ icchati pattheti, dāsī viya nihatamānā hoti. "
484495,110,1908,114,137,1,138,19,"Ekadivasaṃ sāminī viya thaddhā caṇḍā pharusā, ahaṃ tassā bhāvaṃ jānituṃ na sakkomi, tāya ubbāḷho ākulacitto tumhākaṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ nāgatomhī’’ ti. "
484496,110,1908,138,156,1,104,13,"Ācariyo‘‘ evametaṃ, māṇava, itthiyo nāma anācāraṃ ciṇṇadivase sāmikaṃ anuvattanti, dāsī viya nihatamānā honti. "
484497,110,1908,157,164,1,57,7,Anāciṇṇadivase pana mānatthaddhā hutvā sāmikaṃ na gaṇenti. 
484498,110,1908,165,188,1,159,19,"Evaṃ itthiyo nāmetā anācārā dussīlā, tāsaṃ bhāvo nāma dujjāno, tāsu icchantīsupi anicchantīsupi majjhatteneva bhavitabban’’ ti vatvā tassovādavasena imaṃ gāthamāha– "
484499,110,1909,2,4,1,0,0,64.
484500,110,1910,2,15,1,46,11,"‘ ‘ Mā su nandi icchati maṃ, mā su soci na micchati; "
484501,110,1911,2,11,1,46,6,"Thīnaṃ bhāvo durājāno, macchassevodake gatan’’ ti. "
484502,110,1912,2,29,1,118,21,"Tattha mā su nandi icchati man ti su -kāro nipātamattaṃ,‘‘ ayaṃ itthī maṃ icchati pattheti, mayi sinehaṃ karotī’’ ti mā tussi. "
484503,110,1912,30,60,1,139,23,"Mā su soci na {micchatī}ti‘‘ ayaṃ maṃ na icchatī’’ tipi mā soci, tassā icchamānāya nandiṃ, na icchamānāya ca sokaṃ akatvā majjhattova hohīti dīpeti. "
484504,110,1912,61,71,1,79,9,Thīnaṃ bhāvo {durājāno}ti itthīnaṃ bhāvo nāma itthimāyāya paṭicchannattā durājāno. 
484505,110,1912,72,74,1,9,2,Yathā kiṃ? 
484506,110,1912,75,120,1,303,37,"Macchassevodake gatan ti yathā macchassa gamanaṃ udakena paṭicchannattā dujjānaṃ, teneva so kevaṭṭe āgate udakena gamanaṃ paṭicchādetvā palāyati, attānaṃ gaṇhituṃ na deti, evameva itthiyo mahantampi dussīlakammaṃ katvā‘‘ mayaṃ evarūpaṃ na karomā’’ ti attanā katakammaṃ itthimāyāya paṭicchādetvā sāmike vañcenti . "
484507,110,1912,121,131,1,73,9,"Evaṃ itthiyo nāmetā pāpadhammā durājānā, tāsu majjhattoyeva sukhito hotīti. "
484508,110,1913,2,7,1,42,5,Evaṃ bodhisatto antevāsikassa ovādaṃ adāsi. 
484509,110,1913,8,15,1,46,7,Tato paṭṭhāya so tassā upari majjhattova ahosi. 
484510,110,1913,16,33,1,85,13,Sāpissa bhariyā‘‘ ācariyena kira me dussīlabhāvo ñāto’’ ti tato paṭṭhāya na anācāraṃ cari. 
484511,110,1913,34,54,1,117,16,Sāpi tassa upāsakassa itthī‘‘ sammāsambuddhena kira mayhaṃ durācārabhāvo ñāto’’ ti tato paṭṭhāya pāpakammaṃ nāma na akāsi. 
484512,110,1914,2,22,1,153,16,"Satthāpi imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne so upāsako sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi, satthā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
484513,110,1914,23,37,1,69,9,"‘‘ tadā jayampatikāyeva idāni jayampatikā, ācariyo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
484514,110,1915,2,4,1,30,2,Durājānajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
484515,110,1917,2,7,1,23,2,[ 65]5. Anabhiratijātakavaṇṇanā 
484516,110,1918,2,16,1,96,13,Yathā nadī ca pantho {cā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto tathārūpaṃyeva upāsakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484517,110,1918,17,29,1,110,12,So pana pariggaṇhanto tassā dussīlabhāvaṃ ñatvā bhaṇḍito cittabyākulatāya sattaṭṭha divase upaṭṭhānaṃ nāgamāsi. 
484518,110,1918,30,64,1,171,23,"So ekadivasaṃ vihāraṃ gantvā tathāgataṃ vanditvā nisinno‘‘ kasmā sattaṭṭha divasāni nāgatosī’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhariyā me, bhante, dussīlā, tassā upari byākulacittatāya nāgatomhī’’ ti āha. "
484519,110,1918,65,102,1,212,29,"Satthā‘‘ upāsaka, itthīsu‘ anācārā etā’ ti kopaṃ akatvā majjhatteneva bhavituṃ vaṭṭatīti pubbepi te paṇḍitā kathayiṃsu, tvaṃ pana bhavantarena paṭicchannattā taṃ kāraṇaṃ na sallakkhesī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
484520,110,1919,2,12,1,97,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto purimanayeneva disāpāmokkho ācariyo ahosi. 
484521,110,1919,13,27,1,128,14,Athassa antevāsiko bhariyāya dosaṃ disvā byākulacittatāya katipāhaṃ anāgantvā ekadivasaṃ ācariyena pucchito taṃ kāraṇaṃ nivedesi. 
484522,110,1919,28,56,1,129,19,"Athassa ācariyo‘‘ tāta, itthiyo nāma sabbasādhāraṇā , tāsu‘ dussīlā etā’ ti paṇḍitā kopaṃ na karontī’’ ti vatvā ovādavasena imaṃ gāthamāha– "
484523,110,1920,2,4,1,0,0,65.
484524,110,1921,2,13,1,43,9,"‘ ‘ Yathā nadī ca panto ca, pānāgāraṃ sabhā papā; "
484525,110,1922,2,12,1,47,7,"Evaṃ lokitthiyo nāma, nāsaṃ kujjhanti paṇḍitā’’ ti. "
484526,110,1923,2,22,1,155,18,"Tattha yathā {nadī}ti yathā anekatitthā nadī nhānatthāya sampattasampattānaṃ caṇḍālādīnampi khattiyādīnampi sādhāraṇā, na tattha koci nhāyituṃ na labhati nāma."
484527,110,1923,23,41,1,85,12,"‘‘ Pantho’’ tiādīsupi yathā mahāmaggopi sabbesaṃ sādhāraṇo , na koci tena gantuṃ na labhati. "
484528,110,1923,42,55,1,81,11,"Pānāgāra mpi surāgehaṃ sabbesaṃ sādhāraṇaṃ, yo yo pātukāmo, sabbo tattha pavisateva. "
484529,110,1923,56,72,1,111,15,"Puññatthikehi tattha tattha manussānaṃ nivāsatthāya katā sabhā pi sādhāraṇā, na tattha koci pavisituṃ na labhati. "
484530,110,1923,73,90,1,105,15,"Mahāmagge pānīyacāṭiyo ṭhapetvā katā papā pi sabbesaṃ sādhāraṇā, na tattha koci pānīyaṃ pivituṃ na labhati. "
484531,110,1923,91,107,1,142,14,"Evaṃ lokitthiyo {nāmā}ti evameva tāta māṇava imasmiṃ loke itthiyopi sabbasādhāraṇāva, teneva ca sādhāraṇaṭṭhena nadīpanthapānāgārasabhāpapāsadisā. "
484532,110,1923,108,131,1,143,18,"Tasmā nāsaṃ kujjhanti paṇḍitā, etāsaṃ itthīnaṃ‘‘ lāmikā etā anācārā dussīlā sabbasādhāraṇā’’ ti cintetvā paṇḍitā chekā buddhisampannā na kujjhantīti. "
484533,110,1924,2,14,1,78,11,"Evaṃ bodhisatto antevāsikassa ovādaṃ adāsi, so taṃ ovādaṃ sutvā majjhatto ahosi. "
484534,110,1924,15,29,1,72,10,Bhariyāpissa‘‘ ācariyena kiramhi ñātā’’ ti tato paṭṭhāya pāpakammaṃ na akāsi. 
484535,110,1924,30,46,1,85,12,Tassapi upāsakassa bhariyā‘‘ satthārā kiramhi ñātā’’ ti tato paṭṭhāya pāpakammaṃ na akāsi. 
484536,110,1925,2,13,1,101,10,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne upāsako sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. "
484537,110,1925,14,19,1,48,5,Satthāpi anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
484538,110,1925,20,34,1,77,9,"‘‘ tadā jayampatikāva etarahi jayampatikā, ācariyabrāhmaṇo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
484539,110,1926,2,4,1,31,2,Anabhiratijātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
484540,110,1928,2,7,1,25,2,[ 66]6. Mudulakkhaṇajātakavaṇṇanā 
484541,110,1929,2,14,1,78,11,Ekā icchā pure {āsī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto saṃkilesaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484542,110,1929,15,43,1,260,27,Eko kira sāvatthivāsī kulaputto satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā ratanasāsane uraṃ datvā pabbajitvā paṭipannako yogāvacaro avissaṭṭhakammaṭṭhāno hutvā ekadivasaṃ sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caranto ekaṃ alaṅkatapaṭiyattaṃ itthiṃ disvā subhavasena indriyāni bhinditvā olokesi. 
484543,110,1929,44,53,1,65,8,"Tassa abbhantare kileso cali, vāsiyā ākoṭitakhīrarukkho viya ahosi. "
484544,110,1929,54,72,1,157,16,"So tato paṭṭhāya kilesavasiko hutvā neva kāyassādaṃ na cittassādaṃ labhati, bhantamigasappaṭibhāgo sāsane anabhirato parūḷhakesalomanakho kiliṭṭhacīvaro ahosi. "
484545,110,1929,73,95,1,106,16,"Athassa indriyavikāraṃ disvā sahāyakā bhikkhū‘‘ kiṃ nu kho te, āvuso, na yathā porāṇāni indriyānī’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
484546,110,1929,96,99,1,21,2,"Anabhiratosmi, āvusoti. "
484547,110,1930,2,9,1,35,6,Atha naṃ te satthu santikaṃ nayiṃsu. 
484548,110,1930,10,25,1,68,9,"Satthā‘‘ kiṃ, bhikkhave, anicchamānaṃ bhikkhuṃ ādāya āgatatthā’’ ti pucchi."
484549,110,1930,26,37,1,33,5,"‘‘ Ayaṃ, bhante, bhikkhu anabhirato’’ ti?"
484550,110,1930,38,45,1,17,3,‘‘ Saccaṃ bhikkhū’’ ti.
484551,110,1930,46,53,1,17,3,‘‘ Saccaṃ bhagavā’’ ti.
484552,110,1930,54,62,1,22,4,‘‘ Ko taṃ ukkaṇṭhāpesī’’ ti?
484553,110,1930,63,88,1,116,17,"‘‘ Ahaṃ, bhante, piṇḍāya caranto ekaṃ itthiṃ disvā indriyāni bhinditvā olokesiṃ, atha me kileso cali, tenamhi ukkaṇṭhito’’ ti. "
484554,110,1930,89,126,1,349,33,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ anacchariyametaṃ bhikkhu, yaṃ tvaṃ indriyāni bhinditvā visabhāgārammaṇaṃ subhavasena olokento kilesehi kampito, pubbe pañcābhiññā aṭṭhasamāpattilābhino jhānabalena kilese vikkhambhetvā visuddhacittā gaganatalacarā bodhisattāpi indriyāni bhinditvā visabhāgārammaṇaṃ olokayamānā jhānā parihāyitvā kilesehi kampitā mahādukkhaṃ anubhaviṃsu. "
484555,110,1930,127,169,1,369,35,"Na hi sineruuppāṭanakavāto hatthimattaṃ muṇḍapabbataṃ, mahājambuummūlakavāto chinnataṭe virūḷhagacchakaṃ, mahāsamuddaṃ vā pana sosanakavāto khuddakataḷākaṃ kismiñcideva gaṇeti, evaṃ uttamabuddhīnaṃ nāma visuddhacittānaṃ bodhisattānaṃ aññāṇabhāvakarā kilesā tayi kiṃ lajjissanti, visuddhāpi sattā saṃkilissanti, uttamayasasamaṅginopi āyasakyaṃ pāpuṇantī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
484556,110,1931,2,37,1,322,35,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe ekassa mahāvibhavassa brāhmaṇassa kule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto sabbasippānaṃ pāraṃ gantvā kāme pahāya isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā kasiṇaparikammaṃ katvā pañca abhiññā ca aṭṭha samāpattiyo ca uppādetvā jhānasukhena vītināmento himavantappadese vāsaṃ kappesi. 
484557,110,1931,38,67,1,302,28,So ekasmiṃ kāle loṇambilasevanatthāya himavantā otaritvā bārāṇasiṃ patvā rājuyyāne vasitvā punadivase katasarīrapaṭijaggano rattavākamayaṃ nivāsanapārupanaṃ saṇṭhāpetvā ajinacammaṃ ekasmiṃ aṃse katvā jaṭāmaṇḍalaṃ bandhitvā bhikkhābhājanamādāya bārāṇasiyaṃ bhikkhāya caramāno rañño gharadvāraṃ sampāpuṇi. 
484558,110,1931,68,84,1,156,15,Rājā tassa iriyāpatheyeva pasīditvā pakkosāpetvā mahārahe āsane nisīdāpetvā paṇītena khādanīyabhojanīyena santappetvā katānumodanaṃ uyyāne vasanatthāya yāci. 
484559,110,1931,85,96,1,90,11,So sampaṭicchitvā rājagehe bhuñjitvā rājakulaṃ ovadamāno tasmiṃ uyyāne soḷasa vassāni vasi. 
484560,110,1932,2,22,1,142,16,Athekadivasaṃ rājā kupitaṃ paccantaṃ vūpasametuṃ gacchanto mudulakkhaṇaṃ nāma aggamahesiṃ‘‘ appamattā ayyassa upaṭṭhānaṃ karohī’’ ti vatvā agamāsi. 
484561,110,1932,23,31,1,76,8,Bodhisatto rañño gatakālato paṭṭhāya attano ruccanavelāya rājagehaṃ gacchati. 
484562,110,1932,32,37,1,58,5,Athekadivasaṃ mudulakkhaṇā bodhisattassa āhāraṃ sampādetvā–
484563,110,1932,38,57,1,142,14,‘‘ ajja ayyo cirāyatī’’ ti gandhodakena nhāyitvā sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍitā mahātale cūḷasayanaṃ paññāpetvā bodhisattassa āgamanaṃ olokayamānā nipajji. 
484564,110,1932,58,67,1,85,9,Bodhisattopi attano velaṃ sallakkhetvā jhānā vuṭṭhāya ākāseneva rājanivesanaṃ agamāsi. 
484565,110,1932,68,87,1,110,13,"Mudulakkhaṇā vākacīrasaddaṃ sutvāva‘‘ ayyo, āgato’’ ti vegena uṭṭhahi, tassā vegena uṭṭhahantiyā maṭṭhasāṭako bhassi. "
484566,110,1932,88,97,1,101,9,Tāpasopi sīhapañjarena pavisanto deviyā visabhāgarūpārammaṇaṃ indriyāni bhinditvā subhavasena olokesi. 
484567,110,1932,98,107,1,66,8,"Athassa abbhantare kileso cali, vāsiyā pahaṭakhīrarukkho viya ahosi. "
484568,110,1932,108,116,1,59,7,"Tāvadevassa jhānaṃ antaradhāyi, chinnapakkho kāko viya ahosi. "
484569,110,1932,117,143,1,262,26,So ṭhitakova āhāraṃ gahetvā abhuñjitvāva kilesakampito pāsādā oruyha uyyānaṃ gantvā paṇṇasālaṃ pavisitvā phalakattharaṇasayanassa heṭṭhā āhāraṃ ṭhapetvā visabhāgārammaṇena baddho kilesagginā ḍayhamāno nirāhāratāya sussamāno satta divasāni phalakattharaṇe nipajji. 
484570,110,1933,2,52,1,269,35,"Sattame divase rājā paccantaṃ vūpasametvā āgato nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ katvā nivesanaṃ agantvāva‘‘ ayyaṃ passissāmī’’ ti uyyānaṃ gantvā paṇṇasālaṃ pavisitvā taṃ nipannakaṃ disvā‘‘ ekaṃ aphāsukaṃ jātaṃ maññe’’ ti paṇṇasālaṃ sodhāpetvā pāde parimajjanto‘‘ kiṃ, ayya, aphāsukan’’ ti pucchi."
484571,110,1933,53,68,1,79,10,"‘‘ Mahārāja aññaṃ me aphāsukaṃ natthi, kilesavasena panamhi paṭibaddhacitto jāto’’ ti."
484572,110,1933,69,81,1,35,6,"‘‘ Kahaṃ paṭibaddhaṃ te, ayya, cittan’’ ti?"
484573,110,1933,82,90,1,26,3,"‘‘ Mudulakkhaṇāya, mahārājā’’ ti."
484574,110,1933,91,113,1,134,16,"‘‘ Sādhu ayya, ahaṃ mudulakkhaṇaṃ tumhākaṃ dammī’’ ti tāpasaṃ ādāya nivesanaṃ pavisitvā deviṃ sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍitaṃ katvā tāpasassa adāsi. "
484575,110,1933,114,129,1,93,11,Dadamānoyeva ca mudulakkhaṇāya saññamadāsi‘‘ tayā attano balena ayyaṃ rakkhituṃ vāyamitabban’’ ti.
484576,110,1933,130,140,1,25,4,"‘‘ Sādhu, deva, rakkhissāmī’’ ti. "
484577,110,1933,141,146,1,39,5,Tāpaso deviṃ gahetvā rājanivesanā otari. 
484578,110,1934,2,25,1,109,16,"Atha naṃ mahādvārato nikkhantakāle‘‘ ayya, amhākaṃ ekaṃ gehaṃ laddhuṃ vaṭṭati, gaccha, rājānaṃ gehaṃ yācāhī’’ ti āha. "
484579,110,1934,26,30,1,24,4,Tāpaso gantvā gehaṃ yāci. 
484580,110,1934,31,38,1,70,7,Rājā manussānaṃ vaccakuṭikiccaṃ sādhayamānaṃ ekaṃ chaḍḍitagehaṃ dāpesi. 
484581,110,1934,39,49,1,55,9,"So deviṃ gahetvā tattha agamāsi, sā pavisituṃ na icchati."
484582,110,1934,50,58,1,24,4,‘‘ Kiṃkāraṇā na pavisasī’’ ti?
484583,110,1934,59,65,1,15,2,‘‘ Asucibhāvenā’’ ti. 
484584,110,1934,66,74,1,19,4,Idāni‘‘ kiṃ karomī’’ ti.
484585,110,1934,75,133,1,302,39,"‘‘ Paṭijaggāhi nan’’ ti vatvā rañño santikaṃ pesetvā‘‘ gaccha, kuddālaṃ āhara, pacchiṃ āharā’’ ti āharāpetvā asuciñca saṅkārañca chaḍḍāpetvā gāmayaṃ āharāpetvā limpāpetvā punapi‘‘ gaccha, mañcaṃ āhara, pīṭhaṃ āhara, attharaṇaṃ āhara, cāṭiṃ āhara, ghaṭaṃ āharā’’ ti ekamekaṃ āharāpetvā puna udakāharaṇādīnaṃ atthāya āṇāpesi. "
484586,110,1934,134,145,1,81,11,So ghaṭaṃ ādāya udakaṃ āharitvā cāṭiṃ pūretvā nhānodakaṃ sajjetvā sayanaṃ atthari. 
484587,110,1934,146,170,1,135,19,Atha naṃ sayane ekato nisinnaṃ dāṭhikāsu gahetvā‘‘ tava samaṇabhāvaṃ vā brāhmaṇabhāvaṃ vā na jānāsī’’ ti oṇametvā attano abhimukhaṃ ākaḍḍhi. 
484588,110,1934,171,182,1,62,10,"So tasmiṃ kāle satiṃ paṭilabhi, ettakaṃ pana kālaṃ aññāṇī ahosi. "
484589,110,1934,183,187,1,29,4,Evaṃ aññāṇakaraṇā kilesā nāma.
484590,110,1934,188,211,1,81,7,"‘‘ Kāmacchandanīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave, andhakaraṇaṃ aññāṇakaraṇan’’ tiādi( saṃ. ni.5.221) cettha vattabbaṃ. "
484591,110,1935,2,30,1,165,23,"So satiṃ paṭilabhitvā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ taṇhā vaḍḍhamānā mama catūhi apāyehi sīsaṃ ukkhipituṃ na dassati, ajjeva mayā imaṃ rañño niyyādetvā himavantaṃ pavisituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
484592,110,1935,31,58,1,138,21,"So taṃ ādāya rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ mahārāja, tava deviyā mayhaṃ attho natthi, kevalaṃ me imaṃ nissāya taṇhā vaḍḍhitā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
484593,110,1936,2,4,1,0,0,66.
484594,110,1937,2,11,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Ekā icchā pure āsi, aladdhā mudulakkhaṇaṃ; "
484595,110,1938,2,12,1,47,7,"Yato laddhā aḷārakkhī, icchā icchaṃ vijāyathā’’ ti. "
484596,110,1939,2,31,1,143,21,"Tatrāyaṃ piṇḍattho– mahārāja, mayhaṃ imaṃ tava deviṃ mudulakkhaṇaṃ alabhitvā pure‘‘ aho vatāhaṃ etaṃ labheyyan’’ ti ekā icchā āsi, ekāva taṇhā uppajji. "
484597,110,1939,32,56,1,192,23,"Yato pana me ayaṃ aḷārakkhī visālanettā sobhanalocanā laddhā, atha me sā purimikā icchā gehataṇhaṃ upakaraṇataṇhaṃ upabhogataṇhanti uparūpari aññaṃ nānappakāraṃ icchaṃ vijāyatha janesi uppādesi. "
484598,110,1939,57,108,1,355,47,"Sā kho pana me evaṃ vaḍḍhamānā icchā apāyato sīsaṃ ukkhipituṃ na dassati, alaṃ me imāya, tvaññeva tava bhariyaṃ gaṇha, ahaṃ pana himavantaṃ gamissāmīti tāvadeva naṭṭhaṃ jhānaṃ uppādetvā ākāse nisinno dhammaṃ desetvā rañño ovādaṃ datvā ākāseneva himavantaṃ gantvā puna manussapathaṃ nāma nāgamāsi, brahmavihāre pana bhāvetvā aparihīnajjhāno brahmaloke nibbatti. "
484599,110,1940,2,14,1,103,11,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne so bhikkhu arahattaphale patiṭṭhahi. "
