484602,110,1941,2,4,1,33,2,Mudulakkhaṇajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
484603,110,1943,2,7,1,21,2,[ 67]7. Ucchaṅgajātakavaṇṇanā 
484604,110,1944,2,16,1,95,12,Ucchaṅge deva me {putto}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ jānapaditthiṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484605,110,1944,17,25,1,71,8,Ekasmiñhi samaye kosalaraṭṭhe tayo janā aññatarasmiṃ aṭavimukhe kasanti. 
484606,110,1944,26,33,1,60,7,Tasmiṃ samaye antoaṭaviyaṃ corā manusse vilumpitvā palāyiṃsu. 
484607,110,1944,34,67,1,160,24,Manussā te core pariyesitvā apassantā taṃ ṭhānaṃ āgamma‘‘ tumhe aṭaviyaṃ vilumpitvā idāni kassakā viya hothā’’ ti‘‘ te corā ime’’ ti bandhitvā ānetvā kosalarañño adaṃsu. 
484608,110,1944,68,87,1,109,14,"Athekā itthī āgantvā‘‘ acchādanaṃ me detha, acchādanaṃ me dethā’’ ti paridevantī punappunaṃ rājanivesanaṃ pariyāti. "
484609,110,1944,88,103,1,64,10,"Rājā tassā saddaṃ sutvā‘‘ gacchatha, detha imissā acchādanan’’ ti āha. "
484610,110,1944,104,108,1,30,4,Manussā sāṭakaṃ gahetvā adaṃsu. 
484611,110,1944,109,126,1,71,11,"Sā taṃ disvā‘‘ nāhaṃ etaṃ acchādanaṃ yācāmi , sāmikacchādanaṃ yācāmī’’ ti āha. "
484612,110,1944,127,144,1,92,12,"Manussā gantvā rañño ārocayiṃsu‘‘ na kiresā idaṃ acchādanaṃ katheti, sāmikacchādanaṃ kathetī’’ ti. "
484613,110,1944,145,159,1,69,10,Atha naṃ rājā pakkosāpetvā‘‘ tvaṃ kira sāmikacchādanaṃ yācasī’’ ti pucchi. 
484614,110,1944,160,179,1,111,16,"Āma, deva, itthiyā hi sāmiko acchādanaṃ nāma, sāmike hi asati sahassamūlampi sāṭakaṃ nivatthā itthī naggāyeva nāma. "
