484620,110,1948,18,35,1,41,9,"‘‘ Eko me, deva, sāmiko, eko bhātā, eko putto’’ ti. "
484621,110,1948,36,54,1,66,12,"Rājā‘‘ ahaṃ te tuṭṭho, imesu tīsu ekaṃ demi, kataraṃ icchasī’’ ti pucchi. "
484622,110,1948,55,86,1,143,21,"Sā āha‘‘ ahaṃ, deva, jīvamānā ekaṃ sāmikaṃ labhissāmi, puttampi labhissāmiyeva, mātāpitūnaṃ pana me matattā bhātāva dullabho, bhātaraṃ me dehi, devā’’ ti. "
484623,110,1948,87,91,1,31,4,Rājā tussitvā tayopi vissajjesi. 
484624,110,1948,92,101,1,51,9,Evaṃ taṃ ekikaṃ nissāya te tayo janā dukkhato muttā. 
