484637,110,1953,2,15,1,62,9,"Tattha ucchaṅge, deva, me {putto}ti deva, mayhaṃ putto ucchaṅgeyeva. "
484638,110,1953,16,38,1,163,21,"Yathā hi araññaṃ pavisitvā ucchaṅge katvā ḍākaṃ uccinitvā tattha pakkhipantiyā ucchaṅge ḍākaṃ nāma sulabhaṃ hoti, evaṃ itthiyā puttopi sulabho ucchaṅge ḍākasadisova. "
