484641,110,1953,70,80,1,36,6,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ pathe dhāvantiyā patī’’ ti. 
484642,110,1953,81,103,1,135,19,"Tañca desaṃ na passāmi, yato {sodariyamānaye}ti yasmā pana me mātāpitaro natthi, tasmā idāni taṃ mātukucchisaṅkhātaṃ aññaṃ desaṃ na passāmi. "
484643,110,1953,104,117,1,96,12,"Yato ahaṃ samāne udare jātattā saudariyasaṅkhātaṃ bhātaraṃ āneyyaṃ, tasmā bhātaraṃyeva me dethāti. "
