484648,110,1958,2,7,1,19,2,[ 68]8. Sāketajātakavaṇṇanā 
484649,110,1959,2,17,1,102,13,Yasmiṃ mano {nivisatī}ti idaṃ satthā sāketaṃ nissāya añjanavane viharanto ekaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484650,110,1959,18,58,1,306,34,"Bhagavato kira bhikkhusaṅghaparivutassa sāketaṃ piṇḍāya pavisanakāle eko sāketanagaravāsī mahallakabrāhmaṇo nagarato bahi gacchanto antaradvāre dasabalaṃ disvā pādesu patitvā gopphakesu gāḷhaṃ gahetvā‘‘ tāta, nanu nāma puttehi jiṇṇakāle mātāpitaro paṭijaggitabbā, kasmā ettakaṃ kālaṃ amhākaṃ attānaṃ na dassesi? "
484651,110,1959,59,75,1,86,13,"Mayā tāva diṭṭhosi, mātaraṃ pana passituṃ ehī’’ ti satthāraṃ gahetvā attano gehaṃ agamāsi. "
484652,110,1959,76,84,1,66,8,Satthā tattha gantvā nisīdi paññatte āsane saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghena. 
484653,110,1959,85,108,1,132,17,"Brāhmaṇīpi āgantvā satthu pādesu patitvā‘‘ tāta, ettakaṃ kālaṃ kahaṃ gatosi, nanu nāma mātāpitaro mahallakakāle upaṭṭhātabbā’’ ti paridevi. "
484654,110,1959,109,120,1,50,6,"Puttadhītaropi‘‘ etha, bhātaraṃ vandathā’’ ti vandāpesi. "
484655,110,1959,121,125,1,34,4,Ubho tuṭṭhamānasā mahādānaṃ adaṃsu. 
484656,110,1959,126,142,1,74,8,Satthā bhattakiccaṃ niṭṭhāpetvā tesaṃ dvinnampi janānaṃ jarāsuttaṃ( su. ni.810 ādayo) kathesi. 
484657,110,1959,143,147,1,49,4,Suttapariyosāne ubhopi anāgāmiphale patiṭṭhahiṃsu. 
484658,110,1959,148,152,1,41,4,Satthā uṭṭhāyāsanā añjanavanameva agamāsi. 
484659,110,1960,2,36,1,206,24,"Bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ sannisinnā kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, brāhmaṇo‘ tathāgatassa pitā suddhodano, mātā mahāmāyā’ ti jānāti, jānantova saddhiṃ brāhmaṇiyā tathāgataṃ‘ amhākaṃ putto’ ti vadati, satthāpi adhivāseti. "
484660,110,1960,37,44,1,21,5,Kiṃ nu kho kāraṇan’’ ti? 
484661,110,1960,45,68,1,101,16,"Satthā tesaṃ kathaṃ sutvā‘‘ bhikkhave, ubhopi te attano puttameva‘ putto’ ti vadantī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
