484680,110,1970,67,72,1,40,5,Therena tasmiṃ paribhutte daharo agamāsi. 
484681,110,1970,73,89,1,72,10,"Atha naṃ thero‘‘ mayaṃ, āvuso, tuyhaṃ ṭhapitakhādanīyaṃ paribhuñjimhā’’ ti āha. "
484682,110,1970,90,104,1,44,8,"So‘‘ madhuraṃ nāma, bhante, kassa appiyan’’ ti āha. "
484683,110,1970,105,108,1,28,3,Mahātherassa saṃvego uppajji. 
484684,110,1970,109,121,1,60,8,So ito paṭṭhāya‘‘ piṭṭhakhādanīyaṃ na khādissāmī’’ ti adhiṭṭhāsi. 
484685,110,1970,122,130,1,75,8,Tato paṭṭhāya kira sāriputtattherena piṭṭhakhādanīyaṃ nāma na khāditapubbaṃ. 
