484687,110,1970,138,144,1,52,6,Bhikkhū taṃ kathaṃ kathentā dhammasabhāyaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
484688,110,1970,145,188,1,205,28,"Atha satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhave, sāriputto ekavāraṃ jahitakaṃ jīvitaṃ pariccajantopi puna na gaṇhātiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
