484690,110,1971,14,27,1,88,11,"Athekaṃ janapadamanussaṃ sappo ḍaṃsi, tassa ñātakā pamādaṃ akatvā khippaṃ vejjaṃ ānayiṃsu . "
484691,110,1971,28,49,1,118,15,"Vejjo āha‘‘ kiṃ tāva osadhena, paribhāvetvā visaṃ harāmi, daṭṭhasappaṃ āvāhetvā daṭṭhaṭṭhānato teneva visaṃ ākaḍḍhāpemī’’ ti."
