484696,110,1971,96,112,1,83,11,"‘‘ Mayā ekavāraṃ jahitakaṃ puna na gahitapubbaṃ, nāhaṃ mayā jahitavisaṃ ākaḍḍhissāmī’’ ti. "
484697,110,1971,113,132,1,86,14,"So dārūni āharāpetvā aggiṃ katvā āha‘‘ sace attano visaṃ nākaḍḍhasi, imaṃ aggiṃ pavisā’’ ti. "
