484709,110,1980,2,7,1,20,2,[ 70]10. Kuddālajātakavaṇṇanā 
484710,110,1981,2,16,1,96,13,Na taṃ jitaṃ sādhu jitan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto cittahatthasāriputtaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484711,110,1981,17,22,1,34,5,So kira sāvatthiyaṃ eko kuladārako. 
484712,110,1981,23,55,1,241,26,"Athekadivasaṃ kasitvā āgacchanto vihāraṃ pavisitvā ekassa therassa pattato siniddhaṃ madhuraṃ paṇītabhojanaṃ labhitvā cintesi‘‘ mayaṃ rattindivaṃ sahatthena nānākammāni kurumānāpi evarūpaṃ madhurāhāraṃ na labhāma, mayāpi samaṇena bhavitabban’’ ti . "
484713,110,1981,56,72,1,149,15,So pabbajitvā māsaḍḍhamāsaccayena ayoniso manasikaronto kilesavasiko hutvā vibbhamitvā puna bhattena kilamanto āgantvā pabbajitvā abhidhammaṃ uggaṇhi. 
484714,110,1981,73,79,1,46,6,Imināva upāyena cha vāre vibbhamitvā pabbajito. 
484715,110,1981,80,93,1,115,13,Tato sattame bhikkhubhāve sattappakaraṇiko hutvā bahū bhikkhū dhammaṃ vācento vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
484716,110,1981,94,118,1,116,18,"Athassa sahāyakā bhikkhū‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, āvuso cittahattha, pubbe viya te etarahi kilesā na vaḍḍhantī’’ ti parihāsaṃ kariṃsu."
484717,110,1981,119,132,1,51,8,"‘‘ Āvuso, abhabbo dāni ahaṃ ito paṭṭhāya gihibhāvāyā’’ ti. "
484718,110,1982,2,29,1,190,21,"Evaṃ tasmiṃ arahattaṃ patte dhammasabhāyaṃ kathā udapādi‘‘ āvuso, evarūpassa nāma arahattassa upanissaye sati āyasmā cittahatthasāriputto chakkhattuṃ uppabbajito, aho mahādoso puthujjanabhāvo’’ ti. "
484719,110,1982,30,79,1,260,33,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhave, puthujjanacittaṃ nāma lahukaṃ dunniggahaṃ, ārammaṇavasena gantvā allīyati, ekavāraṃ allīnaṃ na sakkā hoti khippaṃ mocetuṃ, evarūpassa cittassa damatho sādhu. "
484720,110,1982,80,85,1,31,5,Dantameva hi taṃ sukhaṃ āvahati.
484721,110,1983,2,8,1,39,4,"‘ ‘ Dunniggahassa lahuno, yatthakāmanipātino; "
484722,110,1984,2,19,1,47,6,"Cittassa damatho sādhu, cittaṃ dantaṃ sukhāvahaṃ’’.( dha. pa.35); "
484723,110,1985,2,29,1,207,25,Tassa pana dunniggahatāya pubbe paṇḍitā ekaṃ kuddālakaṃ nissāya taṃ jahituṃ asakkontā lobhavasena chakkhattuṃ uppabbajitvā sattame pabbajitabhāve jhānaṃ uppādetvā taṃ lobhaṃ niggaṇhiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. 
484724,110,1986,2,22,1,128,14,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto paṇṇikakule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ pāpuṇi,‘‘ kuddālapaṇḍito’’ tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
484725,110,1986,23,35,1,121,12,So kuddālakena bhūmiparikammaṃ katvā ḍākañceva alābukumbhaṇḍaeḷālukādīni ca vapitvā tāni vikkiṇanto kapaṇajīvikaṃ kappesi. 
484726,110,1986,36,44,1,58,8,Tañhissa ekaṃ kuddālakaṃ ṭhapetvā aññaṃ dhanaṃ nāma natthi. 
