484826,110,2015,2,10,1,45,5,"Varuṇakaṭṭhabhañjova , sa pacchā manutappatī’’ ti. "
484827,110,2016,2,41,1,258,32,"Tattha sa pacchā {manutappatī}ti yo koci puggalo‘‘ idaṃ pubbe kattabbaṃ, idaṃ pacchā’’ ti avīmaṃsitvā pubbe karaṇīyāni paṭhamameva kattabbakammāni pacchā karoti, ayaṃ varuṇakaṭṭhabhañjo amhākaṃ māṇavako viya so bālapuggalo pacchā anutappati socati paridevatīti attho. "
484828,110,2017,2,14,1,110,12,Evaṃ bodhisatto antevāsikānaṃ imaṃ kāraṇaṃ kathetvā dānādīni puññāni karitvā jīvitapariyosāne yathākammaṃ gato. 
484829,110,2018,2,47,1,266,31,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevesa tumhākaṃ antarāyaṃ karoti, pubbepi akāsiyevā’’ ti imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ tadā akkhibhedaṃ patto māṇavo ūrubhedaṃ pattabhikkhu ahosi, sesamāṇavā buddhaparisā, ācariyabrāhmaṇo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
484830,110,2019,2,4,1,27,2,Varuṇajātakavaṇṇanā paṭhamā.
484831,110,2021,2,7,1,27,2,[ 72]2. Sīlavanāgarājajātakavaṇṇanā 
484832,110,2022,2,12,1,79,9,Akataññussa {posassā}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484833,110,2022,13,30,1,99,12,"Dhammasabhāyañhi bhikkhū‘‘ āvuso, devadatto akataññū tathāgatassa guṇe na jānātī’’ ti kathentā nisīdiṃsu. "
484834,110,2022,31,82,1,221,32,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva devadatto akataññū, pubbepi akataññūyeva, na kadāci mayhaṃ guṇaṃ jānātī’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
484835,110,2023,2,11,1,95,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto himavantappadese hatthiyoniyaṃ nibbatti. 
484836,110,2023,12,40,1,251,23,"So mātukucchito nikkhanto sabbaseto ahosi rajatapuñjasannibho, akkhīni panassa maṇiguḷasadisāni, paññāyamānāni pañca pasādāni ahesuṃ, mukhaṃ rattakambalasadisaṃ, soṇḍā rattasuvaṇṇabindupaṭimaṇḍitaṃ rajatadāmaṃ viya, cattāro pādā katalākhārasaparikammā viya. "
484837,110,2023,41,48,1,68,7,Evamassa dasahi pāramīhi alaṅkato rūpasobhaggappatto attabhāvo ahosi. 
484838,110,2023,49,59,1,83,9,Atha naṃ viññutaṃ pattaṃ sakalahimavante vāraṇā sannipatitvā upaṭṭhahantā vicariṃsu. 
484839,110,2023,60,75,1,138,15,Evaṃ so asītisahassavāraṇaparivāro himavantappadese vasamāno aparabhāge gaṇe dosaṃ disvā gaṇamhā kāyavivekāya ekakova araññe vāsaṃ kappesi. 
484840,110,2023,76,87,1,57,7,Sīlavantatāya ca panassa‘‘ sīlavanāgarājā’’ tveva nāmaṃ ahosi. 
484841,110,2024,2,20,1,185,18,Atheko bārāṇasivāsiko vanacarako himavantaṃ pavisitvā attano ājīvabhaṇḍakaṃ gavesamāno disā vavatthāpetuṃ asakkonto maggamūḷho hutvā maraṇabhayabhīto bāhā paggayha paridevamāno vicarati. 
484842,110,2024,21,40,1,117,15,Bodhisatto tassa taṃ balavaparidevitaṃ sutvā‘‘ imaṃ purisaṃ dukkhā mocessāmī’’ ti kāruññena codito tassa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
484843,110,2024,41,46,1,27,5,So taṃ disvāva bhīto palāyi. 
484844,110,2024,47,53,1,48,6,Bodhisatto taṃ palāyantaṃ disvā tattheva aṭṭhāsi. 
484845,110,2024,54,61,1,42,6,So puriso bodhisattaṃ ṭhitaṃ disvā aṭṭhāsi . 
484846,110,2024,62,100,1,223,30,"Bodhisatto puna agamāsi, so puna palāyitvā tassa ṭhitakāle ṭhatvā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ vāraṇo mama palāyanakāle tiṭṭhati, ṭhitakāle āgacchati, nāyaṃ mayhaṃ anatthakāmo, imamhā pana maṃ dukkhā mācetukāmo bhavissatī’’ ti sūro hutvā aṭṭhāsi. "
484847,110,2024,101,117,1,82,11,"Bodhisatto taṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ kasmā bho tvaṃ purisa, paridevamāno vicarasī’’ ti pucchi."
484848,110,2024,118,131,1,67,8,"‘‘ Sāmi, disā vavatthāpetuṃ asakkonto maggamūḷho hutvā maraṇabhayenā’’ ti. "
484849,110,2024,132,163,1,182,23,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃ netvā katipāhaṃ phalāphalehi santappetvā‘‘ bho, purisa, mā bhāyi, ahaṃ taṃ manussapathaṃ nessāmī’’ ti attano piṭṭhe nisīdāpetvā manussapathaṃ pāyāsi. "
484850,110,2025,2,25,1,167,18,"Atha kho so mittadubbhī puriso‘‘ sace koci pucchissati, ācikkhitabbaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti bodhisattassa piṭṭhe nisinnoyeva rukkhanimittaṃ pabbatanimittaṃ upadhārentova gacchati. "
484851,110,2025,26,58,1,217,26,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto araññā nīharitvā bārāṇasigāmimahāmagge ṭhapetvā‘‘ bho purisa, iminā maggena gaccha, mayhaṃ pana vasanaṭṭhānaṃ pucchitopi apucchitopi mā kassaci ācikkhī’’ ti taṃ uyyojetvā attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃyeva agamāsi. "
484852,110,2025,59,84,1,155,19,"Atha so puriso bārāṇasiṃ gantvā anuvicaranto dantakāravīthiṃ patvā dantakāre dantavikatiyo kurumāne disvā‘‘ kiṃ pana bho, jīvadantampi labhitvā gaṇheyyāthā’’ ti?"
484853,110,2025,85,99,1,63,8,"‘‘ Bho, kiṃ vadesi, jīvadanto nāma matahatthidantato mahagghataro’’ ti."
484854,110,2025,100,118,1,113,14,‘‘ Tena hi ahaṃ vo jīvadantaṃ āharissāmī’’ ti pātheyyaṃ gahetvā kharakakacaṃ ādāya bodhisattassa vasanaṭṭhānaṃ agamāsi. 
484855,110,2026,2,13,1,48,7,Bodhisatto taṃ disvā‘‘ kimatthaṃ āgatosī’’ ti pucchi.
484856,110,2026,14,41,1,144,20,"‘‘ Ahaṃ, sāmi, duggato kapaṇo jīvituṃ asakkonto tumhe dantakhaṇḍaṃ yācitvā sace dassatha, taṃ ādāya gantvā vikkiṇitvā tena mūlena jīvissāmī’’ ti āgatoti."
484857,110,2026,42,58,1,67,10,"‘‘ Hotu bho, dantaṃ te dassāmi, sace dantakappanatthāya kakacaṃ atthī’’ ti."
484858,110,2026,59,68,1,32,5,‘‘ Kakacaṃ gahetvā āgatomhi sāmī’’ ti.
484859,110,2026,69,86,1,94,13,‘‘ Tena hi dante kakacena kantitvā ādāya gacchā’’ ti bodhisatto pāde samiñjitvā gonisinnakaṃ nisīdi. 
484860,110,2026,87,91,1,25,4,So dvepi aggadante chindi. 
484861,110,2026,92,138,1,342,37,"Bodhisatto te dante soṇḍāya gahetvā‘‘ bho purisa, nāhaṃ‘ ete dantā mayhaṃ appiyā amanāpā’ ti dammi, imehi pana me dantehi sataguṇena sahassaguṇena satasahassaguṇena sabbadhammapaṭivedhanasamatthā sabbaññutaññāṇadantāva piyatarā, tassa me idaṃ dantadānaṃ sabbaññutaññāṇapaṭivijjhanatthāya hotū’’ ti sabbaññutaññāṇassa ārādhanaṃ katvā dantayugalaṃ adāsi. "
484862,110,2027,2,34,1,185,24,"So taṃ ādāya gantvā vikkiṇitvā tasmiṃ mūle khīṇe puna bodhisattassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ sāmi, tumhākaṃ dante vikkiṇitvā laddhamūlaṃ mayhaṃ iṇasodhanamattameva jātaṃ, avasesadante dethā’’ ti āha. "
484863,110,2027,35,47,1,77,8,Bodhisatto‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā purimanayeneva kappāpetvā avasesadante adāsi. 
484864,110,2027,48,68,1,81,14,"So tepi vikkiṇitvā puna āgantvā‘‘ sāmi, jīvituṃ na sakkomi, mūladāṭhā me dethā’’ ti āha. "
484865,110,2027,69,79,1,54,6,Bodhisatto‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā purimanayeneva nisīdi. 
484866,110,2027,80,101,1,207,21,So pāpapuriso mahāsattassa rajatadāmasadisaṃ soṇḍaṃ maddamāno kelāsakūṭasadisaṃ kumbhaṃ abhiruhitvā ubho dantakoṭiyo paṇhiyā paharanto maṃsaṃ viyūhitvā kumbhaṃ āruyha kharakakacena mūladāṭhā kappetvā pakkāmi. 
484867,110,2027,102,126,1,274,23,Bodhisattassa dassanūpacāraṃ vijahanteyeva pana tasmiṃ pāpapurise catunahutādhikadviyojanasatasahassabahalā ghanapathavī sineruyugandharādayo mahābhāre duggandhajegucchāni gūthamuttādīni ca dhāretuṃ samatthāpi tassa aguṇarāsiṃ dhāretuṃ asakkontī viya bhijjitvā vivaraṃ adāsi. 
484868,110,2027,127,139,1,129,12,Tāvadeva avīcimahānirayato aggijālā nikkhamitvā taṃ mittadubbhipurisaṃ kulasantakena kambalena pārupantī viya parikkhipitvā gaṇhi. 
484869,110,2028,2,30,1,212,24,Evaṃ tassa pāpapuggalassa pathaviṃ paviṭṭhakāle tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe adhivatthā rukkhadevatā‘‘ akataññū mittadubbhī puggalo cakkavattirajjaṃ datvāpi tosetuṃ na sakkā’’ ti vanaṃ unnādetvā dhammaṃ desayamānā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
484870,110,2029,2,4,1,0,0,72.
484871,110,2030,2,9,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Akataññussa posassa, niccaṃ vivaradassino; "
484872,110,2031,2,13,1,48,8,"Sabbaṃ ce pathaviṃ dajjā, neva naṃ abhirādhaye’’ ti. "
484873,110,2032,2,8,1,49,5,Tattha {akataññussā}ti attano kataguṇaṃ ajānantassa. 
484874,110,2032,9,12,1,19,2,{Posassā}ti purisassa. 
484875,110,2032,13,18,1,48,4,{Vivaradassino}ti chiddameva okāsameva olokentassa. 
484876,110,2032,19,37,1,137,16,"Sabbaṃ ce pathaviṃ {dajjā}ti sacepi tādisassa puggalassa sakalaṃ cakkavattirajjaṃ, imaṃ vā pana mahāpathaviṃ parivattetvā pathavojaṃ dadeyya. "
484877,110,2032,38,54,1,122,15,Neva naṃ {abhirādhaye}ti evaṃ karontopi evarūpaṃ kataguṇaviddhaṃsakaṃ koci paritosetuṃ vā pasādetuṃ vā na sakkuṇeyyāti attho. 
484878,110,2033,2,9,1,45,7,Evaṃ sā devatā vanaṃ unnādetvā dhammaṃ desesi. 
484879,110,2033,10,15,1,49,5,Bodhisatto yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā yathākammaṃ agamāsi. 
484880,110,2034,2,46,1,246,29,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, devadatto idāneva akataññū, pubbepi akataññūyevā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ tadā mittadubbhī puggalo devadatto ahosi, rukkhadevatā sāriputto, sīlavanāgarājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
484881,110,2035,2,4,1,34,2,Sīlavanāgarājajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
484882,110,2037,2,7,1,23,2,[ 73]3. Saccaṃkirajātakavaṇṇanā 
484883,110,2038,2,14,1,103,11,Saccaṃ {kirevamāhaṃsū}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattassa vadhāya parisakkanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484884,110,2038,15,81,1,338,42,"Bhikkhusaṅghasmiñhi dhammasabhāyaṃ nisīditvā‘‘ āvuso, devadatto satthu guṇaṃ na jānāti, vadhāyayeva parisakkatī’’ ti devadattassa aguṇaṃ kathente satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva devadatto mayhaṃ vadhāya parisakkati, pubbepi parisakkiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
484885,110,2039,2,24,1,169,21,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente tassa duṭṭhakumāro nāma putto ahosi kakkhaḷo pharuso pahaṭāsīvisūpamo, anakkositvā vā apaharitvā vā kenaci saddhiṃ na katheti. "
484886,110,2039,25,41,1,112,15,"So antojanassa ca bahijanassa ca akkhimhi patitarajaṃ viya, khādituṃ āgatapisāco viya ca amanāpo ahosi ubbejanīyo. "
484887,110,2039,42,50,1,73,8,So ekadivasaṃ nadīkīḷaṃ kīḷitukāmo mahantena parivārena nadītīraṃ agamāsi. 
484888,110,2039,51,59,1,50,7,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe mahāmegho uṭṭhahi, disā andhakārā jātā. "
484889,110,2039,60,77,1,81,12,"So dāsapessajanaṃ āha‘‘ etha bhaṇe, maṃ gahetvā nadīmajjhaṃ netvā nhāpetvā ānethā’’ ti. "
484890,110,2039,78,111,1,162,24,"Te taṃ tattha netvā‘‘ kiṃ no rājā karissati, imaṃ pāpapurisaṃ ettheva māremā’’ ti mantayitvā‘‘ ettha gaccha kāḷakaṇṇī’’ ti udake naṃ opilāpetvā paccuttaritvā tīre aṭṭhaṃsu."
484891,110,2039,112,140,1,115,18,"‘‘ Kahaṃ kumāro’’ ti ca vutte‘‘ na mayaṃ kumāraṃ passāma, meghaṃ uṭṭhitaṃ disvā udake nimujjitvā purato āgato bhavissatī’’ ti. "
484892,110,2039,141,145,1,30,4,Amaccā rañño santikaṃ agamaṃsu. 
484893,110,2039,146,156,1,29,6,Rājā‘‘ kahaṃ me putto’’ ti pucchi. 
484894,110,2039,157,173,1,74,11,"Na jānāma deva, meghe uṭṭhite‘‘ purato āgato bhavissatī’’ ti saññāya āgatamhāti. "
484895,110,2039,174,192,1,99,13,"Rājā dvāraṃ vivarāpetvā‘‘ nadītīraṃ gantvā vicinathā’’ ti tattha tattha vicināpesi, koci kumāraṃ nāddasa. "
484896,110,2040,2,18,1,136,15,Sopi kho meghandhakāre deve vassante nadiyā vuyhamāno ekaṃ dārukkhandhaṃ disvā tattha nisīditvā maraṇabhayatajjito paridevamāno gacchati. 
484897,110,2040,19,34,1,135,15,Tasmiṃ pana kāle bārāṇasivāsī eko seṭṭhi nadītīre cattālīsakoṭidhanaṃ nidahitvāva maranto dhanataṇhāya dhanapiṭṭhe sappo hutvā nibbatti. 
484898,110,2040,35,46,1,90,11,Aparo tasmiṃyeva padese tiṃsa koṭiyo nidahitvā dhanataṇhāya tattheva undūro hutvā nibbatti. 
484899,110,2040,47,51,1,33,4,Tesaṃ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ udakaṃ pāvisi. 
484900,110,2040,52,74,1,178,20,"Te udakassa paviṭṭhamaggeneva nikkhamitvā sotaṃ chindantā gantvā taṃ rājakumārena abhinisinnaṃ dārukkhandhaṃ patvā eko ekaṃ koṭiṃ, itaro itaraṃ āruyha khandhapiṭṭheyeva nipajjiṃsu. "
484901,110,2040,75,87,1,81,11,"Tassāyeva kho pana nadiyā tīre eko simbalirukkho atthi, tattheko suvapotako vasati. "
484902,110,2040,88,106,1,139,17,"Sopi rukkho udakena dhotamūlo nadīpiṭṭhe pati, suvapotako deve vassante uppatitvā gantuṃ asakkonto gantvā tasseva khandhassa ekapasse nilīyi. "
484903,110,2040,107,114,1,46,7,Evaṃ te cattāro janā ekato vuyhamānā gacchanti. 
484904,110,2041,2,17,1,155,15,Bodhisattopi kho tasmiṃ kāle kāsiraṭṭhe udiccabrāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vuḍḍhippatto isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā ekasmiṃ nadīnivattane paṇṇasālaṃ māpetvā vasati. 
484905,110,2041,18,46,1,218,23,"So aḍḍharattasamaye caṅkamamāno tassa rājakumārassa balavaparidevanasaddaṃ sutvā cintesi‘‘ mādise nāma mettānuddayasampanne tāpase passante etassa purisassa maraṇaṃ ayuttaṃ, udakato uddharitvā tassa jīvitadānaṃ dassāmī’’ ti. "
484906,110,2041,47,78,1,197,26,"So taṃ‘‘ mā bhāyi, mā bhāyī’’ ti assāsetvā udakasotaṃ chindanto gantvā taṃ dārukkhandhaṃ ekāya koṭiyā gahetvā ākaḍḍhanto nāgabalo thāmasampanno ekavegena tīraṃ patvā kumāraṃ ukkhipitvā tīre patiṭṭhāpesi. "
484907,110,2041,79,114,1,255,31,Tepi sappādayo disvā ukkhipitvā assamapadaṃ netvā aggiṃ jāletvā‘‘ ime dubbalatarā’’ ti paṭhamaṃ sappādīnaṃ sarīraṃ sedetvā pacchā rājakumārassa sarīraṃ sedetvā tampi arogaṃ katvā āhāraṃ dentopi paṭhamaṃ sappādīnaṃyeva datvā pacchā tassa phalāphalāni upanāmesi. 
484908,110,2041,115,132,1,114,13,Rājakumāro‘‘ ayaṃ kūṭatāpaso maṃ rājakumāraṃ agaṇetvā tiracchānagatānaṃ sammānaṃ karotī’’ ti bodhisatte āghātaṃ bandhi. 
484909,110,2042,2,59,1,350,45,"Tato katipāhaccayena sabbesupi tesu thāmabalappattesu nadiyā oghe pacchinne sappo tāpasaṃ vanditvā āha‘‘ bhante, tumhehi mayhaṃ mahāupakāro kato, na kho panāhaṃ daliddo, asukaṭṭhāne me cattālīsa hiraññakoṭiyo nidahitvā ṭhapitā, tumhākaṃ dhanena kicce sati sabbampetaṃ dhanaṃ tumhākaṃ dātuṃ sakkomi, taṃ ṭhānaṃ āgantvā‘ dīghā’ ti pakkoseyyāthā’’ ti vatvā pakkāmi. "
484910,110,2042,60,79,1,95,12,Undūropi tatheva tāpasaṃ nimantetvā‘‘ asukaṭṭhāne ṭhatvā‘ undūrā’ ti pakkoseyyāthā’’ ti vatvā pakkāmi. 
484911,110,2042,80,124,1,259,33,"Suvapotako pana tāpasaṃ vanditvā‘‘ bhante, mayhaṃ dhanaṃ natthi, rattasālīhi pana vo atthe sati asukaṃ nāma mayhaṃ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ, tattha gantvā‘ suvā’ ti pakkoseyyātha, ahaṃ ñātakānaṃ ārocetvā anekasakaṭapūramattā rattasāliyo āharāpetvā dātuṃ sakkomī’’ ti vatvā pakkāmi. "
484912,110,2042,125,165,1,223,29,"Itaro pana mittadubbhī‘‘ dhammasudhammatāya kiñci avatvā gantuṃ ayuttaṃ, evaṃ taṃ attano santikaṃ āgataṃ māressāmī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ bhante, mayi rajje patiṭṭhite āgaccheyyātha, ahaṃ vo catūhi paccayehi upaṭṭhahissāmī’’ ti vatvā pakkāmi. "
484913,110,2042,166,172,1,39,6,So gantvā na cirasseva rajje patiṭṭhāsi. 
484914,110,2043,2,24,1,100,14,Bodhisatto ‘‘ vīmaṃsissāmi tāva ne’’ ti paṭhamaṃ sappassa santikaṃ gantvā avidūre ṭhatvā‘‘ dīghā’’ ti pakkosi. 
484915,110,2043,25,47,1,131,16,"So ekavacaneneva nikkhamitvā bodhisattaṃ vanditvā‘‘ bhante, imasmiṃ ṭhāne cattālīsa hiraññakoṭiyo, tā sabbāpi nīharitvā gaṇhathā’’ ti āha. "
484916,110,2043,48,65,1,100,12,"Bodhisatto‘‘ evamatthu, uppanne kicce jānissāmī’’ ti taṃ nivattetvā undūrassa santikaṃ gantvā saddamakāsi. "
484917,110,2043,66,69,1,22,3,Sopi tatheva paṭipajji. 
484918,110,2043,70,83,1,67,9,Bodhisatto tampi nivattetvā suvassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ suvā’’ ti pakkosi. 
484919,110,2043,84,108,1,166,18,"Sopi ekavacaneneva rukkhaggato otaritvā bodhisattaṃ vanditvā‘‘ kiṃ, bhante, mayhaṃ ñātakānaṃ santikaṃ gantvā himavantappadesato tumhākaṃ sayaṃjātasālī āharāpemī’’ ti pucchi. "
484920,110,2043,109,137,1,176,20,Bodhisatto‘‘ atthe sati jānissāmī’’ ti tampi nivattetvā‘‘ idāni rājānaṃ pariggaṇhissāmī’’ ti gantvā rājuyyāne vasitvā punadivase ākappasampattiṃ katvā bhikkhācāravattena nagaraṃ pāvisi. 
484921,110,2043,138,150,1,111,11,Tasmiṃ khaṇe so mittadubbhī rājā alaṅkatahatthikkhandhavaragato mahantena parivārena nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ karoti. 
484922,110,2043,151,181,1,192,24,"So bodhisattaṃ dūratova disvā‘‘ ayaṃ so kūṭatāpaso mama santike bhuñjitvā vasitukāmo āgato, yāva parisamajjhe attano mayhaṃ kataguṇaṃ nappakāseti, tāvadevassa sīsaṃ chindāpessāmī’’ ti purise olokesi."
484923,110,2043,182,228,1,266,35,"‘‘ Kiṃ karoma, devā’’ ti ca vutte‘‘ esa kūṭatāpaso maṃ kiñci yācitukāmo āgacchati maññe, etassa kāḷakaṇṇitāpasassa maṃ passituṃ adatvāva etaṃ gahetvā pacchābāhaṃ bandhitvā catukke catukke paharantā nagarā nikkhāmetvā āghātane sīsamassa chinditvā sarīraṃ sūle uttāsethā’’ ti āha. "
