484984,110,2064,2,7,1,19,2,[ 75]5. Macchajātakavaṇṇanā 
484985,110,2065,2,15,1,93,10,Abhitthanaya {pajjunnā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto attanā vassāpitavassaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
484986,110,2065,16,32,1,114,14,"Ekasmiṃ kira samaye kosalaraṭṭhe devo na vassi, sassāni milāyanti, tesu tesu ṭhānesu taḷākapokkharaṇisarāni sussanti. "
484987,110,2065,33,37,1,64,4,Jetavanadvārakoṭṭhakasamīpe jetavanapokkharaṇiyāpi udakaṃ chijji. 
484988,110,2065,38,50,1,139,12,Kalalagahanaṃ pavisitvā nipanne macchakacchape kākakulalādayo kaṇayaggasadisehi tuṇḍehi koṭṭetvā nīharitvā nīharitvā vipphandamāne khādanti. 
484989,110,2066,2,53,1,434,40,"Satthā macchakacchapānaṃ taṃ byasanaṃ disvā mahākaruṇāya ussāhitahadayo‘‘ ajja mayā devaṃ vassāpetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti pabhātāya rattiyā sarīrapaṭijagganaṃ katvā bhikkhācāravelaṃ sallakkhetvā mahābhikkhusaṅghaparivuto buddhalīlāya sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya pavisitvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto sāvatthito vihāraṃ gacchanto jetavanapokkharaṇiyā sopāne ṭhatvā ānandattheraṃ āmantesi‘‘ ānanda, udakasāṭikaṃ āhara, jetavanapokkharaṇiyaṃ nhāyissāmī’’ ti."
484990,110,2066,54,69,1,78,8,"‘‘ Nanu, bhante, jetavanapokkharaṇiyaṃ udakaṃ chinnaṃ, kalalamattameva avasiṭṭhan’’ ti?"
484991,110,2066,70,84,1,59,8,"‘‘ Ānanda, buddhabalaṃ nāma mahantaṃ, āhara tvaṃ udakasāṭikan’’ ti. "
484992,110,2066,85,88,1,20,3,Thero āharitvā adāsi. 
484993,110,2066,89,105,1,120,12,Satthā ekenantena udakasāṭikaṃ nivāsetvā ekenantena sarīraṃ pārupitvā‘‘ jetavanapokkharaṇiyaṃ nhāyissāmī’’ ti sopāne aṭṭhāsi. 
484994,110,2066,106,111,1,62,5,Taṅkhaṇaññeva sakkassa paṇḍukambalasilāsanaṃ uṇhākāraṃ dassesi. 
484995,110,2066,112,148,1,205,24,"So‘‘ kiṃ nu kho’’ ti āvajjento taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā vassavalāhakadevarājānaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ tāta, satthā‘ jetavanapokkharaṇiyaṃ nhāyissāmī’ ti dhurasopāne ṭhito, khippaṃ sakalakosalaraṭṭhaṃ ekameghaṃ katvā vassāpehī’’ ti. "
484996,110,2066,149,166,1,120,13,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā ekaṃ valāhakaṃ nivāsetvā ekaṃ pārupitvā meghagītaṃ gāyanto pācīnalokadhātuabhimukho pakkhandi. 
484997,110,2066,167,185,1,225,18,Pācīnadisābhāge khalamaṇḍalamattaṃ ekaṃ meghapaṭalaṃ uṭṭhāya satapaṭalaṃ sahassapaṭalaṃ hutvā abhitthanantaṃ vijjulatā nicchārentaṃ adhomukhaṃ ṭhapitaudakakumbhākārena vassamānaṃ sakalakosalaraṭṭhaṃ mahoghena viya ajjhotthari. 
484998,110,2066,186,198,1,102,10,"Devo acchinnadhāraṃ vassanto muhutteneva jetavanapokkharaṇiṃ pūresi, dhurasopānaṃ āhacca udakaṃ aṭṭhāsi. "
484999,110,2067,2,133,1,1112,104,"Satthā pokkharaṇiyaṃ nhāyitvā surattadupaṭṭaṃ nivāsetvā kāyabandhanaṃ bandhitvā sugatamahācīvaraṃ ekaṃsaṃ katvā bhikkhusaṅghaparivuto gantvā gandhakuṭipariveṇe paññattavarabuddhāsane nisīditvā bhikkhusaṅghena vatte dassite uṭṭhāya maṇisopānaphalake ṭhatvā bhikkhusaṅghassa ovādaṃ datvā uyyojetvā surabhigandhakuṭiṃ pavisitvā dakkhiṇena passena sīhaseyyaṃ kappetvā sāyanhasamaye dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ‘‘ passathāvuso, dasabalassa khantimettānuddayasampattiṃ, vividhasassesu milāyantesu nānājalāsayesu sussantesu macchakacchapesu mahādukkhaṃ pāpuṇantesu kāruññaṃ paṭicca‘ mahājanaṃ dukkhā mocessāmī’ ti udakasāṭikaṃ nivāsetvā jetavanapokkharaṇiyā dhurasopāne ṭhatvā muhuttena sakalakosalaraṭṭhaṃ mahoghena opilāpento viya devaṃ vassāpetvā mahājanaṃ kāyikacetasikadukkhato mocetvā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho’’ ti kathāya vattamānāya gandhakuṭito nikkhamitvā dhammasabhaṃ āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, tathāgato idāneva mahājane kilamante devaṃ vassāpeti, pubbe tiracchānayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā maccharājakālepi vassāpesiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
485000,110,2068,2,13,1,126,11,Atīte imasmiṃyeva kosalaraṭṭhe imissā sāvatthiyā imasmiṃyeva jetavanapokkharaṇiṭṭhāne ekā valligahanaparikkhittā kandarā ahosi. 
485001,110,2068,14,21,1,78,7,Tadā bodhisatto macchayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā macchagaṇaparivuto tattha paṭivasati. 
485002,110,2068,22,45,1,163,19,"Yathā pana idāni, evameva tadāpi tasmiṃ raṭṭhe devo na vassi, manussānaṃ sassāni milāyiṃsu, vāpitaḷākakandarādīsu udakaṃ chijji, macchakacchapā kalalagahanaṃ pavisiṃsu. "
485003,110,2068,46,55,1,87,9,Imissāpi kandarāya macchakacchapā kalalagahanaṃ pavisitvā tasmiṃ tasmiṃ ṭhāne nilīyiṃsu. 
485004,110,2068,56,61,1,44,5,Kākādayo tuṇḍena koṭṭetvā nīharitvā khādiṃsu. 
485005,110,2069,2,64,1,465,52,"Bodhisatto ñātisaṅghassa taṃ byasanaṃ disvā‘‘ imaṃ tesaṃ dukkhaṃ ṭhapetvā maṃ añño mocetuṃ samattho nāma natthi, saccakiriyaṃ katvā devaṃ vassāpetvā ñātake maraṇadukkhā mocessāmī’’ ti kāḷavaṇṇaṃ kaddamaṃ dvidhā viyūhitvā nikkhamitvā añjanarukkhasāraghaṭikavaṇṇo mahāmaccho sudhotalohitaṅgamaṇiguḷasadisāni akkhīni ummīletvā ākāsaṃ ulloketvā pajjunnadevarājassa saddaṃ datvā‘‘ bho pajjunna, ahaṃ ñātake nissāya dukkhito, tvaṃ mayi sīlavante kilamante kasmā devaṃ na vassāpesi? "
485006,110,2069,65,103,1,292,34,"Mayā samānajātikānaṃ khādanaṭṭhāne nibbattitvā taṇḍulappamāṇampi macchaṃ ādiṃ katvā khāditapubbo nāma natthi, aññopi me pāṇo jīvitā na voropitapubbo, iminā saccena devaṃ vassāpetvā ñātisaṅghaṃ me dukkhā mocehī’’ ti vatvā paricārakaceṭakaṃ āṇāpento viya pajjunnadevarājānaṃ ālapanto imaṃ gāthamāha– "
485007,110,2070,2,4,1,0,0,75.
485008,110,2071,2,12,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Abhitthanaya pajjunna, nidhiṃ kākassa nāsaya; "
485009,110,2072,2,12,1,44,7,"Kākaṃ sokāya randhehi, mañca sokā pamocayā’’ ti. "
485010,110,2073,2,16,1,120,12,"Tattha abhitthanaya {pajjunnā}ti pajjunno vuccati megho, ayaṃ pana meghavasena laddhanāmaṃ vassavalāhakadevarājānaṃ ālapati. "
485011,110,2073,17,36,1,152,17,"Ayaṃ kirassa adhippāyo– devo nāma anabhitthananto vijjulatā anicchārento vassantopi na sobhati, tasmā tvaṃ abhitthananto vijjulatā nicchārento vassāpehīti. "
485012,110,2073,37,71,1,216,27,"Nidhiṃ kākassa {nāsayā}ti kākā kalalaṃ pavisitvā ṭhite macche tuṇḍena koṭṭetvā nīharitvā khādanti, tasmā tesaṃ antokalale macchā‘‘ nidhī’’ ti vuccanti, taṃ kākasaṅghassa nidhiṃ devaṃ vassāpento udakena paṭicchādetvā nāsehīti. "
485013,110,2073,72,99,1,205,24,"Kākaṃ sokāya {randhehī}ti kākasaṅgho imissā kandarāya udakena puṇṇāya macche alabhamāno socissati, taṃ kākagaṇaṃ tvaṃ imaṃ kandaraṃ pūrento sokāya randhehi, sokassatthāya macchassa assāsatthāya devaṃ vassāpehi. "
485014,110,2073,100,126,1,169,22,"Yathā antonijjhānalakkhaṇaṃ sokaṃ pāpuṇāti, evaṃ karohīti attho, mañca sokā {pamocayā}ti ettha ca -kāro sampiṇḍanattho, mañca mama ñātake ca sabbeva imamhā maraṇasokā mocehīti. "
485015,110,2074,2,19,1,172,16,Evaṃ bodhisatto paricārakaceṭakaṃ āṇāpento viya pajjunnaṃ ālapitvā sakalakosalaraṭṭhe mahāvassaṃ vassāpetvā mahājanaṃ maraṇadukkhā mocetvā jīvitapariyosāne yathākammaṃ gato. 
485016,110,2075,2,29,1,175,20,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, tathāgato idāneva devaṃ vassāpeti, pubbe macchayoniyaṃ nibbattopi vassāpesiyevā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
485017,110,2075,30,47,1,93,11,"‘‘ tadā macchagaṇā buddhaparisā ahesuṃ, pajjunnadevarājā ānando, maccharājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485018,110,2076,2,4,1,27,2,Macchajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
485019,110,2078,2,7,1,21,2,[ 76]6. Asaṅkiyajātakavaṇṇanā 
485020,110,2079,2,15,1,96,11,Asaṅkiyomhi {gāmamhī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ sāvatthivāsiṃ upāsakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485021,110,2079,16,38,1,221,22,So kira sotāpanno ariyasāvako kenacideva karaṇīyena ekena sakaṭasatthavāhena saddhiṃ maggaṃ paṭipajjitvā ekasmiṃ araññaṭṭhāne sakaṭāni mocetvā khandhāvārabandhe kate satthavāhassa avidūre aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle caṅkamati. 
485022,110,2079,39,56,1,118,12,Athattano kālaṃ sallakkhetvā pañcasatā corā‘‘ khandhāvāraṃ vilumpissāmā’’ ti dhanumuggarādihatthā taṃ ṭhānaṃ parivārayiṃsu. 
485023,110,2079,57,59,1,23,2,Upāsakopi caṅkamatiyeva. 
485024,110,2079,60,82,1,147,17,"Corā naṃ disvā‘‘ addhā esa khandhāvārarakkhako bhavissati, imassa niddaṃ okkantakāle vilumpissāmā’’ ti ajjhottharituṃ asakkontā tattha tattheva aṭṭhaṃsu. "
485025,110,2079,83,90,1,79,7,Sopi upāsako paṭhamayāmepi majjhimayāmepi pacchimayāmepi caṅkamantoyeva aṭṭhāsi. 
485026,110,2079,91,100,1,83,9,Paccūsakāle jāte corā okāsaṃ alabhantā gahite pāsāṇamuggarādayo chaḍḍetvā palāyiṃsu. 
485027,110,2080,2,23,1,137,16,"Upāsakopi attano kammaṃ niṭṭhāpetvā puna sāvatthiṃ āgantvā satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ bhante, attānaṃ rakkhamānā pararakkhakā hontī’’ ti pucchi."
485028,110,2080,24,42,1,84,11,"‘‘ Āma, upāsaka, attānaṃ rakkhanto parampi rakkhati, paraṃ rakkhanto attānampi rakkhatī’’ ti. "
485029,110,2080,43,73,1,159,20,"So‘‘ yāva subhāsitañcidaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā, ahaṃ ekena satthavāhena saddhiṃ maggaṃ paṭipanno rukkhamūle caṅkamanto‘ maṃ rakkhissāmī’ ti sakalasatthaṃ rakkhin’’ ti āha. "
485030,110,2080,74,93,1,98,14,"Satthā‘‘ upāsaka, pubbepi paṇḍitā attānaṃ rakkhantā paraṃ rakkhiṃsū’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
485031,110,2081,2,40,1,388,38,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto kāmesu ādīnavaṃ disvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā himavante vasanto loṇambilasevanatthāya janapadaṃ āgantvā janapadacārikaṃ caranto ekena satthavāhena saddhiṃ maggaṃ paṭipajjitvā ekasmiṃ araññaṭṭhāne satthe niviṭṭhe satthato avidūre jhānasukhena vītināmento aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle caṅkamanto aṭṭhāsi. 
485032,110,2081,41,57,1,108,12,Atha kho pañcasatā corā‘‘ sāyamāsabhattassa bhuttakāle taṃ sakaṭasatthaṃ vilumpissāmā’’ ti āgantvā parivārayiṃsu. 
485033,110,2081,58,80,1,132,16,"Te taṃ tāpasaṃ disvā‘‘ sace ayaṃ amhe passissati, satthavāsikānaṃ ārocessati, etassa niddūpagatavelāya vilumpissāmā’’ ti tattheva aṭṭhaṃsu. "
485034,110,2081,81,85,1,35,4,Tāpaso sakalampi rattiṃ caṅkamiyeva. 
485035,110,2081,86,122,1,260,28,"Corā okāsaṃ alabhitvā gahitagahite muggarapāsāṇe chaḍḍetvā sakaṭasatthavāsīnaṃ saddaṃ datvā‘‘ bhonto, satthavāsino sace esa rukkhamūle caṅkamanakatāpaso ajja nābhavissa, sabbe mahāvilopaṃ pattā abhavissatha, sve tāpasassa mahāsakkāraṃ kareyyāthā’’ ti vatvā pakkamiṃsu. "
485036,110,2082,2,26,1,140,18,"Te pabhātāya rattiyā corehi chaḍḍite muggarapāsāṇādayo disvā bhītā bodhisattassa santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā‘‘ bhante, diṭṭhā vo corā’’ ti pucchiṃsu."
485037,110,2082,27,35,1,17,3,"‘‘ Āmāvuso, diṭṭhā’’ ti."
485038,110,2082,36,52,1,62,11,"‘‘ Bhante, ettakevo core disvā bhayaṃ vā sārajjaṃ vā na uppajjī’’ ti? "
485039,110,2082,53,71,1,96,14,"Bodhisatto‘‘ āvuso core disvā bhayaṃ nāma sadhanassa hoti, ahaṃ pana niddhano, svāhaṃ kiṃ bhāyissāmi. "
485040,110,2082,72,90,1,110,16,Mayhañhi gāmepi araññepi vasantassa bhayaṃ vā sārajjaṃ vā natthī’’ ti vatvā tesaṃ dhammaṃ desento imaṃ gāthamāha– 
485041,110,2083,2,4,1,0,0,76.
485042,110,2084,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Asaṅkiyomhi gāmamhi, araññe natthi me bhayaṃ; "
485043,110,2085,2,11,1,42,6,"Ujumaggaṃ samāruḷho, mettāya karuṇāya cā’’ ti. "
485044,110,2086,2,15,1,85,10,"Tattha asaṅkiyomhi {gāmamhī}ti saṅkāya niyutto patiṭṭhitoti saṅkiyo, na saṅkiyo asaṅkiyo. "
485045,110,2086,16,25,1,80,9,Ahaṃ gāme vasantopi saṅkāya appatiṭṭhitattā asaṅkiyo nibbhayo nirāsaṅkoti dīpeti. 
485046,110,2086,26,30,1,38,3,{Araññe}ti gāmagāmūpacāravinimutte ṭhāne. 
485047,110,2086,31,46,1,145,13,"Ujumaggaṃ samāruḷho, mettāya karuṇāya {cā}ti ahaṃ tikacatukkajjhānikāhi mettākaruṇāhi kāyavaṅkādivirahitaṃ ujuṃ brahmalokagāmimaggaṃ āruḷhoti vadati. "
485048,110,2086,47,65,1,186,18,Atha vā parisuddhasīlatāya kāyavacīmanovaṅkavirahitaṃ ujuṃ devalokamaggaṃ āruḷhomhīti dassetvā tato uttari mettāya karuṇāya ca patiṭṭhitattā ujuṃ brahmalokamaggampi āruḷhomhītipi dasseti. 
485049,110,2086,66,73,1,82,7,Aparihīnajjhānassa hi ekantena brahmalokaparāyaṇattā mettākaruṇādayo ujumaggā nāma. 
485050,110,2087,2,19,1,149,17,Evaṃ bodhisatto imāya gāthāya dhammaṃ desetvā tuṭṭhacittehi tehi manussehi sakkato pūjito yāvajīvaṃ cattāro brahmavihāre bhāvetvā brahmaloke nibbatti. 
485051,110,2088,2,10,1,74,8,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
