485054,110,2091,2,7,1,23,2,[ 77]7. Mahāsupinajātakavaṇṇanā 
485055,110,2092,2,14,1,81,10,Lābūni {sīdantī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto soḷasa mahāsupine ārabbha kathesi. 
485056,110,2092,15,45,1,227,25,Ekadivasaṃ kira kosalamahārājā rattiṃ niddūpagato pacchimayāme soḷasa mahāsupine disvā bhītatasito pabujjhitvā‘‘ imesaṃ supinānaṃ diṭṭhattā kiṃ nu kho me bhavissatī’’ ti maraṇabhayatajjito sayanapiṭṭhe nisinnakova rattiṃ vītināmesi. 
485057,110,2093,2,18,1,95,11,"Atha naṃ pabhātāya rattiyā brāhmaṇapurohitā upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ sukhaṃ sayittha, mahārājā’’ ti pucchiṃsu."
485058,110,2093,19,40,1,118,15,"‘‘ Kuto me ācariyā sukhaṃ, ajjāhaṃ paccūsasamaye soḷasa mahāsupine passiṃ, somhi tesaṃ diṭṭhakālato paṭṭhāya bhayappatto’’ ti."
485059,110,2093,41,70,1,131,18,"‘‘ Vadetha, mahārāja, sutvā jānissāmā’’ ti vuttaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ diṭṭhasupine kathetvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho me imesaṃ diṭṭhakāraṇā bhavissatī’’ ti pucchi. "
485060,110,2093,71,74,1,26,3,Brāhmaṇā hatthe vidhuniṃsu.
485061,110,2093,75,95,1,63,10,"‘‘ Kasmā hatthe vidhunathā’’ ti ca vutte‘‘ kakkhaḷā, mahārāja, supinā’’ ti."
485062,110,2093,96,105,1,32,5,‘‘ Kā tesaṃ nipphatti bhavissatī’’ ti?
485063,110,2093,106,118,1,79,8,‘‘ Rajjantarāyo jīvitantarāyo bhogantarāyoti imesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ antarāyānaṃ aññataro’’ ti.
485064,110,2093,119,127,1,27,3,"‘‘ Sappaṭikammā, appaṭikammā’’ ti?"
485065,110,2093,128,153,1,155,19,"‘‘ Kāmaṃ ete supinā atipharusattā appaṭikammā, mayaṃ pana te sappaṭikamme karissāma, ete paṭikkamāpetuṃ asakkontānaṃ amhākaṃ sikkhitabhāvo nāma kiṃ karissatī’’ ti."
485066,110,2093,154,163,1,35,5,‘‘ Kiṃ pana katvā paṭikkamāpessathā’’ ti?
485067,110,2093,164,174,1,43,5,"‘‘ Sabbacatukkena yaññaṃ yajissāma, mahārājā’’ ti. "
485068,110,2093,175,196,1,100,16,"Rājā bhītatasito‘‘ tena hi ācariyā mama jīvitaṃ tumhākaṃ hatthe hotu, khippaṃ me sotthiṃ karothā’’ ti āha. "
485069,110,2093,197,243,1,295,32,"Brāhmaṇā‘‘ bahuṃ dhanaṃ labhissāma, bahuṃ khajjabhojjaṃ āharāpessāmā’’ ti haṭṭhatuṭṭhā‘‘ mā cintayittha, mahārājā’’ ti rājānaṃ samassāsetvā rājanivesanā nikkhamitvā bahinagare yaññāvāṭaṃ katvā bahū catuppadagaṇe thūṇūpanīte katvā pakkhigaṇe samāharitvā‘‘ idañcidañca laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti punappunaṃ sañcaranti. "
485070,110,2094,2,26,1,122,18,"Atha kho mallikā devī taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā pucchi‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, mahārāja, brāhmaṇā punappunaṃ sañcarantī’’ ti?"
485071,110,2094,27,43,1,68,10,"‘‘ Sukhitā, tvaṃ bhadde, amhākaṃ kaṇṇamūle āsīvisaṃ carantaṃ na jānāsī’’ ti."
485072,110,2094,44,53,1,20,4,"‘‘ Kiṃ etaṃ, mahārājā’’ ti? "
485073,110,2094,54,85,1,154,20,"Mayā evarūpā dussupinā diṭṭhā, brāhmaṇā‘‘ tiṇṇaṃ antarāyānaṃ aññataro paññāyatī’’ ti vatvā‘‘‘ tesaṃ paṭighātāya yaññaṃ yajissāmā’ ti vatvā punappunaṃ sañcarantī’’ ti."
485074,110,2094,86,102,1,76,10,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana te, mahārāja, sadevake loke aggabrāhmaṇo supinapaṭikammaṃ pucchito’’ ti?"
485075,110,2094,103,116,1,50,7,"‘‘ Kataro panesa, bhadde, sadevake loke aggabrāhmaṇo’’ ti."
485076,110,2094,117,129,1,81,9,‘‘ Sadevake loke aggapuggalaṃ sabbaññuṃ visuddhaṃ nikkilesaṃ mahābrāhmaṇaṃ na jānāsi. 
485077,110,2094,130,145,1,69,11,"So hi bhagavā supinantaraṃ jāneyya, gaccha tvaṃ puccha taṃ, mahārājā’’ ti."
485078,110,2094,146,160,1,59,9,"‘‘ Sādhu, devī’’ ti rājā vihāraṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā nisīdi. "
485079,110,2095,2,19,1,78,11,"Satthā madhurassaraṃ nicchāretvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, mahārāja, atippagova āgatosī’’ ti āha. "
485080,110,2095,20,32,1,76,9,"Ahaṃ, bhante, paccūsasamaye soḷasa mahāsupine disvā bhīto brāhmaṇānaṃ ārocesiṃ. "
485081,110,2095,33,75,1,260,30,"Brāhmaṇā‘‘ kakkhaḷā, mahārāja , supinā, etesaṃ paṭighātatthāya sabbacatukkena yaññaṃ yajissāmā’’ ti yaññaṃ sajjenti, bahū pāṇā maraṇabhayatajjitā, tumhe ca sadevake loke aggapuggalā, atītānāgatapaccuppannaṃ upādāya natthi so ñeyyadhammo, yo vo ñāṇamukhe āpāthaṃ nāgacchati."
485082,110,2095,76,87,1,50,7,‘‘ Etesaṃ me supinānaṃ nipphattiṃ kathetha bhagavā’’ ti.
485083,110,2095,88,123,1,195,27,"‘‘ Evametaṃ, mahārāja, sadevake loke maṃ ṭhapetvā añño etesaṃ supinānaṃ antaraṃ vā nipphattiṃ vā jānituṃ samattho nāma natthi, ahaṃ te kathessāmi, apica kho tvaṃ diṭṭhadiṭṭhaniyāmeneva supine kathehī’’ ti."
485084,110,2095,124,135,1,46,6,"‘‘ Sādhu, bhante’’ ti rājā diṭṭhaniyāmeneva kathento–"
485085,110,2096,2,9,1,28,6,"‘ ‘ Usabhā rukkhā gāviyo gavā ca, "
485086,110,2097,2,7,1,28,5,Asso kaṃso siṅgālī ca kumbho; 
485087,110,2098,2,5,1,27,3,Pokkharaṇī ca apākacandanaṃ.
