485186,110,2116,2,27,1,152,17,"( 15) Bhante, dasahi asaddhammehi samannāgataṃ gāmagocaraṃ kākaṃ kañcanavaṇṇatāya‘‘ suvaṇṇā’’ ti laddhanāme suvaṇṇarājahaṃse parivārente addasaṃ, imassa ko vipākoti? "
485187,110,2116,28,33,1,54,5,Imassāpi anāgate dubbalarājakāleyeva vipāko bhavissati. 
485188,110,2116,34,75,1,414,38,"Anāgatasmiñhi rājāno hatthisippādīsu akusalā yuddhesu avisāradā bhavissanti, te attano rajjavipattiṃ āsaṅkamānā samānajātikānaṃ kulaputtānaṃ issariyaṃ adatvā attano pādamūlikanhāpakakappakādīnaṃ dassanti, jātigottasampannā kulaputtā rājakule patiṭṭhaṃ alabhamānā jīvikaṃ kappetuṃ asamatthā hutvā issariye ṭhite jātigottahīne akulīne upaṭṭhahantā vicarissanti, suvaṇṇarājahaṃsehi kākassa parivāritakālo viya bhavissati. "
485189,110,2116,76,83,1,49,6,"Itonidānampi te bhayaṃ natthi, soḷasamaṃ kathehīti."
485190,110,2117,2,20,1,98,14,"( 16) Bhante, pubbe dīpino eḷake khādanti, ahaṃ pana eḷake dīpino anubandhitvā murumurūti khādante addasaṃ. "
485191,110,2117,21,43,1,156,19,"Athaññe tasā vakā eḷake dūratova disvā tasitā tāsappattā hutvā eḷakānaṃ bhayāpalāyitvā gumbagahanādīni pavisitvā nilīyiṃsu, evāhaṃ addasaṃ, imassa ko vipākoti? "
485192,110,2117,44,49,1,56,5,Imassapi anāgate adhammikarājakāleyeva vipāko bhavissati. 
485193,110,2117,50,60,1,71,9,"Tadā hi akulīnā rājavallabhā issarā bhavissanti, kulīnā apaññātā duggatā. "
485194,110,2117,61,121,1,417,45,"Te rājavallabhā rājānaṃ attano kathaṃ gāhāpetvā vinicchayaṭṭhānādīsu balavanto hutvā kulīnānaṃ paveṇiāgatāni khettavatthādīni‘‘ amhākaṃ santakāni etānī’’ ti abhiyuñjitvā tesu‘‘ na tumhākaṃ, amhākan’’ ti āgantvā vinicchayaṭṭhānādīsu vivadantesu vettalatādīhi paharāpetvā gīvāyaṃ gahetvā apakaḍḍhāpetvā‘‘ attano pamāṇaṃ na jānātha, amhehi saddhiṃ vivadatha, idāni vo rañño kathetvā hatthapādacchedanādīni kāressāmā’’ ti santajjessanti. "
485195,110,2117,122,141,1,126,15,Te tesaṃ bhayena attano santakāni vatthūni‘‘ tumhākaṃyevetāni gaṇhathā’’ ti niyyādetvā attano gehāni pavisitvā bhītā nipajjissanti. 
485196,110,2117,142,157,1,139,14,"Pāpabhikkhūpi pesale bhikkhū yathāruci viheṭhessanti, te pesalā bhikkhū paṭisaraṇaṃ alabhamānā araññaṃ pavisitvā gahanaṭṭhānesu nilīyissanti. "
485197,110,2117,158,172,1,153,14,Evaṃ hīnajaccehi ceva pāpabhikkhūhi ca upaddutānaṃ jātimantakulaputtānañceva pesalabhikkhūnañca eḷakānaṃ bhayena tasavakānaṃ palāyanakālo viya bhavissati. 
485198,110,2117,173,177,1,29,4,Itonidānampi te bhayaṃ natthi. 
485199,110,2117,178,185,1,44,6,Ayampi hi supino anāgataṃyeva ārabbha diṭṭho. 
485200,110,2117,186,206,1,135,14,"Brāhmaṇā pana na dhammasudhammatāya tayi sinehena kathayiṃsu,‘‘ bahudhanaṃ labhissāmā’’ ti āmisāpekkhatāya jīvitavuttiṃ nissāya kathayiṃsūti. "
485201,110,2118,2,23,1,134,16,"Evaṃ satthā soḷasannaṃ mahāsupinānaṃ nipphattiṃ kathetvā‘‘ na kho, mahārāja, etarahi tvaññeva ime supine addasa, porāṇakarājānopi addasaṃsu. "
485202,110,2118,24,39,1,122,14,"Brāhmaṇāpi nesaṃ evameva ime supine gahetvā yaññamatthake khipiṃsu, tato paṇḍitehi dinnanayena gantvā bodhisattaṃ pucchiṃsu. "
485203,110,2118,40,57,1,104,15,Porāṇakā paṇḍitāpi nesaṃ ime supine kathentā imināva niyāmena kathesun’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. 
485204,110,2119,2,23,1,206,20,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto udiccabrāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ceva samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā himavantappadese jhānakīḷaṃ kīḷanto viharati. 
485205,110,2119,24,34,1,78,10,Tadā bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatto imināva niyāmena ime supine disvā brāhmaṇe pucchi. 
