485207,110,2119,41,48,1,61,7,Tesu purohitassa antevāsikamāṇavo paṇḍito byatto ācariyaṃ āha–
485208,110,2119,49,71,1,111,16,"‘‘ ācariya, tumhehi mayaṃ tayo vede uggaṇhāpitā, nanu tesu ekaṃ māretvā ekassa sotthikammassa kāraṇaṃ nāma natthī’’ ti. "
485209,110,2119,72,86,1,94,12,"Tāta, iminā upāyena amhākaṃ bahudhanaṃ uppajjissati, tvaṃ pana rañño dhanaṃ rakkhitukāmo maññeti. "
485210,110,2119,87,112,1,123,18,"Māṇavo‘‘ tena hi, ācariya, tumhe tumhākaṃ kammaṃ karotha, ahaṃ tumhākaṃ santike kiṃ karissāmī’’ ti vicaranto rañño uyyānaṃ agamāsi. "
485211,110,2120,2,29,1,189,23,Taṃ divasameva bodhisattopi taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā‘‘ ajja mayi manussapathaṃ gate mahājanassa bandhanā mokkho bhavissatī’’ ti ākāsena gantvā uyyāne otaritvā suvaṇṇapaṭimā viya maṅgalasilātale nisīdi. 
485212,110,2120,30,37,1,80,7,Māṇavo bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīditvā paṭisanthāramakāsi. 
