485245,110,2132,29,46,1,69,11,"‘‘ tadā rājā ānando ahosi, māṇavo sāriputto, tāpaso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485246,110,2133,2,29,1,166,19,Parinibbute pana bhagavati saṅgītikārakā‘‘ usabhā’’ tiādīni tīṇi padāni aṭṭhakathaṃ āropetvā‘‘ lābūnī’’ tiādīni cattāri padāni ekaṃ gāthaṃ katvā ekakanipātapāḷiṃ āropesunti. 
485247,110,2134,2,4,1,31,2,Mahāsupinajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
485248,110,2136,2,7,1,19,2,[ 78]8. Illisajātakavaṇṇanā 
485249,110,2137,2,12,1,84,9,Ubho {khañjā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto macchariyakosiyaseṭṭhiṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485250,110,2137,13,27,1,123,13,"Rājagahanagarassa kira avidūre sakkāraṃ nāma nigamo ahosi, tattheko macchariyakosiyo nāma seṭṭhi asītikoṭivibhavo paṭivasati. "
485251,110,2137,28,38,1,71,9,"So tiṇaggena telabindumattampi neva paresaṃ deti, na attanā paribhuñjati. "
485252,110,2137,39,55,1,139,14,"Iti tassa taṃ vibhavajātaṃ neva puttadārādīnaṃ, na samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ atthaṃ anubhoti, rakkhasapariggahitapokkharaṇī viya aparibhogaṃ tiṭṭhati. "
485253,110,2138,2,18,1,217,16,Satthā ekadivasaṃ paccūsasamaye mahākaruṇāsamāpattito vuṭṭhāya sakalalokadhātuyaṃ bodhaneyyabandhave olokento pañcacattālīsayojanamatthake vasantassa tassa seṭṭhino sapajāpatikassa sotāpattiphalassa upanissayaṃ addasa. 
485254,110,2138,19,77,1,431,47,"Tato purimadivase pana rājānaṃ upaṭṭhātuṃ rājagehaṃ gantvā rājūpaṭṭhānaṃ katvā āgacchanto ekaṃ chātajjhattaṃ janapadamanussaṃ kummāsapūraṃ kapallapūvaṃ khādantaṃ disvā tattha pipāsaṃ uppādetvā attano gharaṃ gantvā cintesi‘‘ sacāhaṃ‘ kapallapūvaṃ khāditukāmomhī’ ti vakkhāmi, bahū mayā saddhiṃ khāditukāmā bhavissanti, evaṃ me bahūni taṇḍulasappimadhuphāṇitādīni parikkhayaṃ gamissanti, na kassaci kathessāmī’’ ti taṇhaṃ adhivāsento vicarati. "
485255,110,2138,78,86,1,72,7,So gacchante gacchante kāle uppaṇḍupaṇḍukajāto dhamanisanthatagatto jāto . 
485256,110,2138,87,96,1,79,9,Tato taṇhaṃ adhivāsetuṃ asakkonto gabbhaṃ pavisitvā mañcakaṃ upagūhitvā nipajji. 
485257,110,2138,97,103,1,52,6,Evaṃgatopi dhanahānibhayena kassaci kiñci na kathesi. 
485258,110,2139,2,19,1,83,12,"Atha naṃ bhariyā upasaṅkamitvā piṭṭhiṃ parimajjitvā‘‘ kiṃ te sāmi, aphāsukan’’ ti pucchi."
485259,110,2139,20,30,1,30,6,‘‘ Na me kiñci aphāsukaṃ atthī’’ ti.
485260,110,2139,31,42,1,28,7,‘‘ Kiṃ nu kho te rājā kupito’’ ti?
485261,110,2139,43,52,1,23,5,‘‘ Rājāpi me na kuppatī’’ ti.
485262,110,2139,53,69,1,78,12,‘‘ Atha kiṃ te puttadhītāhi vā dāsakammakarādīhi vā kiñci amanāpaṃ kataṃ atthī’’ ti?
485263,110,2139,70,77,1,20,3,‘‘ Evarūpampi natthī’’ ti.
485264,110,2139,78,88,1,31,6,‘‘ Kismiñci pana te taṇhā atthī’’ ti? 
485265,110,2139,89,96,1,61,7,Evaṃ vuttepi dhanahānibhayena kiñci avatvā nissaddova nipajji. 
485266,110,2139,97,113,1,52,10,"Atha naṃ bhariyā‘‘ kathehi, sāmi, kismiṃ te taṇhā’’ ti āha. "
485267,110,2139,114,128,1,53,10,So vacanaṃ parigilanto viya‘‘ atthi me ekā taṇhā’’ ti āha.
485268,110,2139,129,138,1,17,4,"‘‘ Kiṃ taṇhā, sāmī’’ ti?"
485269,110,2139,139,146,1,30,3,‘‘ Kapallapūvaṃ khāditukāmomhī’’ ti.
485270,110,2139,147,166,1,109,13,"‘‘ Atha kimatthaṃ na kathesi, kiṃ tvaṃ daliddo, idāni sakalasakkāranigamavāsīnaṃ pahonake kapallapūve pacissāmī’’ ti?"
485271,110,2139,167,181,1,50,9,"‘‘ Kiṃ te etehi, te attano kammaṃ katvā khādissantī’’ ti?"
485272,110,2139,182,192,1,43,6,‘‘ Tena hi ekaracchavāsīnaṃ pahonake pacāmī’’ ti. 
485273,110,2139,193,196,1,33,3,Jānāmahaṃ tava mahaddhanabhāvanti.
485274,110,2139,197,210,1,60,9,‘‘ Tena hi imasmiṃ gehamatte sabbesaṃ pahonakaṃ katvā pacāmī’’ ti.
485275,110,2139,211,219,1,36,4,‘‘ Jānāmahaṃ tava mahajjhāsayabhāvan’’ ti.
485276,110,2139,220,232,1,56,8,‘‘ Tena hi te puttadāramattasseva pahonakaṃ katvā pacāmī’’ ti.
485277,110,2139,233,242,1,20,5,‘‘ Kiṃ pana te etehī’’ ti?
485278,110,2139,243,255,1,51,8,‘‘ Tena hi tuyhañca mayhañca pahonakaṃ katvā pacāmī’’ ti.
485279,110,2139,256,264,1,21,4,‘‘ Tvaṃ kiṃ karissasī’’ ti?
485280,110,2139,265,277,1,45,8,‘‘ Tena hi ekasseva te pahonakaṃ katvā pacāmī’’ ti.
485281,110,2139,278,309,1,244,25,"‘‘ Imasmiṃ ṭhāne paccamānaṃ bahū paccāsīsanti, sakalataṇḍule ṭhapetvā bhinnataṇḍule ca uddhanakapallādīni ca ādāya thokaṃ khīrasappimadhuphāṇitañca gahetvā sattabhūmikassa pāsādassa uparimatalaṃ āruyha paca, tatthāhaṃ ekakova nisīditvā khādissāmī’’ ti. "
485282,110,2139,310,326,1,99,12,Sā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā gahetabbaṃ gāhāpetvā pāsādaṃ āruyha dāsiyo vissajjetvā seṭṭhiṃ pakkosāpesi. 
485283,110,2139,327,341,1,126,14,So ādito paṭṭhāya dvārāni pidahanto sabbadvāresu sūcighaṭikāni datvā sattamatalaṃ abhiruhitvā tatthapi dvāraṃ pidahitvā nisīdi. 
485284,110,2139,342,351,1,74,9,Bhariyāpissa uddhane aggiṃ jāletvā kapallakaṃ āropetvā pūve pacituṃ ārabhi. 
485285,110,2140,2,31,1,217,20,"Atha satthā pātova mahāmoggallānattheraṃ āmantesi,‘‘ eso, moggallāna, rājagahanagarassa avidūre sakkāranigame macchariyakosiyaseṭṭhi‘ kapallapūve khādissāmī’ ti aññesaṃ dassanabhayena sattabhūmike pāsāde kapallapūve pacāpeti. "
485286,110,2140,32,52,1,154,19,Tvaṃ tattha gantvā taṃ seṭṭhiṃ dametvā nibbisevanaṃ katvā ubhopi jayampatike pūve ca khīrasappimadhuphāṇitādīni ca gāhāpetvā attano balena jetavanaṃ ānehi. 
485287,110,2140,53,66,1,95,10,"Ajjāhaṃ pañcahi bhikkhusatehi saddhiṃ vihāreyeva nisīdissāmi, pūveheva bhattakiccaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
485288,110,2140,67,93,1,179,21,"Thero‘‘ sādhu, bhante’’ ti satthu vacanaṃ sampaṭicchitvā tāvadeva iddhibalena taṃ nigamaṃ gantvā tassa pāsādassa sīhapañjaradvāre sunivattho supāruto ākāseyeva maṇirūpakaṃ viya aṭṭhāsi. "
485289,110,2141,2,7,1,46,5,Mahāseṭṭhino theraṃ disvāva hadayamaṃsaṃ kampi. 
485290,110,2141,8,53,1,276,34,"So‘‘ ahaṃ evarūpānaññeva bhayena imaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgato, ayañca āgantvā vātapānadvāre ṭhito’’ ti gahetabbagahaṇaṃ apassanto aggimhi pakkhittaloṇasakkharā viya dosena taṭataṭāyanto evamāha‘‘ samaṇa, ākāse ṭhatvā tvaṃ kiṃ labhissasi, ākāse apade padaṃ dassetvā caṅkamantopi neva labhissasī’’ ti. "
485291,110,2141,54,59,1,41,5,Thero tasmiṃyeva ṭhāne aparāparaṃ caṅkami. 
485292,110,2141,60,76,1,87,11,"Seṭṭhi‘‘ caṅkamanto kiṃ labhissasi, ākāse pallaṅkena nisīdamānopi na labhissasiyevā’’ ti āha. "
485293,110,2141,77,81,1,32,4,Thero pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā nisīdi. 
