485298,110,2141,136,168,1,160,22,"Gehajjhāyanabhayena pana naṃ‘‘ pajjalantopi na labhissasī’’ ti avatvā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ samaṇo suṭṭhu laggo, aladdhā na gamissati, ekamassa pūvaṃ dāpessāmī’’ ti bhariyaṃ āha–"
485299,110,2141,169,183,1,65,9,"‘‘ bhadde, ekaṃ khuddakapūvaṃ pacitvā samaṇassa datvā uyyojehi nan’’ ti. "
485300,110,2141,184,196,1,98,11,"Sā thokaññeva piṭṭhaṃ kapallapātiyaṃ pakkhipi, mahāpūvo hutvā sakalapātiṃ pūretvā uddhumāto aṭṭhāsi. "
