485303,110,2142,38,53,1,57,10,"So nibbinno bhariyaṃ āha‘‘ bhadde, imassa ekaṃ pūvaṃ dehī’’ ti. "
485304,110,2142,54,62,1,62,8,Tassā pacchito ekaṃ pūvaṃ gaṇhantiyā sabbe ekābaddhā allīyiṃsu. 
