485345,110,2150,2,51,1,350,40,"So ekadivasaṃ rājūpaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā attano gharaṃ āgacchanto ekaṃ maggakilantaṃ jānapadamanussaṃ, ekaṃ surāvārakaṃ, ādāya pīṭhake nisīditvā ambilasurāya kosakaṃ pūretvā pūretvā pūtimacchakena uttaribhaṅgena pivantaṃ disvā suraṃ pātukāmo hutvā cintesi‘‘ sacāhaṃ suraṃ pivissāmi, mayi pivante bahū pivitukāmā bhavissanti, evaṃ me dhanaparikkhayo bhavissatī’’ ti. "
