485524,110,2193,2,4,1,13,2,9 . Apāyimhavaggo
485525,110,2195,2,7,1,21,2,[ 81]1. Surāpānajātakavaṇṇanā 
485526,110,2196,2,16,1,104,11,Apāyimha {anaccimhā}ti idaṃ satthā kosambiṃ upanissāya ghositārāme viharanto sāgatattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485527,110,2196,17,61,1,302,36,"Bhagavati hi sāvatthiyaṃ vassaṃ vasitvā cārikāgamanena bhaddavatikaṃ nāma nigamaṃ sampatte gopālakā pasupālakā kassakā pathāvino ca satthāraṃ disvā vanditvā‘‘ mā, bhante, bhagavā ambatitthaṃ agamāsi, ambatitthe jaṭilassa assame ambatitthako nāma nāgo āsīviso ghoraviso, so bhagavantaṃ viheṭheyyā’’ ti vārayiṃsu. "
485528,110,2196,62,71,1,80,9,Bhagavāpi tesaṃ kathaṃ asuṇanto viya tesu yāvatatiyaṃ vārayamānesupi agamāsiyeva. 
485529,110,2197,2,10,1,74,8,Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā bhaddavatikāya avidūre aññatarasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe viharati. 
485530,110,2197,11,32,1,192,21,Tena kho pana samayena buddhūpaṭṭhāko sāgato nāma thero pothujjanikāya iddhiyā samannāgato taṃ assamaṃ upasaṅkamitvā tassa nāgarājassa vasanaṭṭhāne tiṇasanthārakaṃ paññāpetvā pallaṅkena nisīdi. 
485531,110,2197,33,40,1,46,6,"Nāgo makkhaṃ asahamāno dhūmāyi, theropi dhūmāyi. "
485532,110,2197,41,46,1,28,4,"Nāgo pajjali, theropi pajjali. "
485533,110,2197,47,58,1,58,9,"Nāgassa tejo theraṃ na bādhati, therassa tejo nāgaṃ bādhati. "
485534,110,2197,59,73,1,99,14,Evaṃ so khaṇena taṃ nāgarājānaṃ dametvā saraṇesu ca sīlesu ca patiṭṭhāpetvā satthu santikaṃ agamāsi. 
485535,110,2198,2,8,1,64,6,Satthā bhaddavatikāyaṃ yathābhirantaṃ viharitvā kosambiṃ agamāsi. 
485536,110,2198,9,14,1,59,5,Sāgatattherena nāgassa damitabhāvo sakalajanapadaṃ patthari. 
485537,110,2198,15,45,1,208,23,"Kosambinagaravāsino satthu paccuggamanaṃ katvā satthāraṃ vanditvā sāgatattherassa santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ ṭhitā evamāhaṃsu‘‘ bhante, yaṃ tumhākaṃ dullabhaṃ, taṃ vadeyyātha, tadeva mayaṃ paṭiyādessāmā’’ ti. "
485538,110,2198,46,49,1,17,3,Thero tuṇhī ahosi. 
485539,110,2198,50,64,1,83,11,"Chabbaggiyā panāhaṃsu‘‘ āvuso, pabbajitānaṃ nāma kāpotikā surā dullabhā ceva manāpā ca. "
485540,110,2198,65,76,1,58,8,"Sace tumhe therassa pasannā, kāpotikaṃ suraṃ paṭiyādethā’’ ti. "
485541,110,2198,77,111,1,203,26,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā satthāraṃ svātanāya nimantetvā nagaraṃ pavisitvā attano attano gehe‘‘ therassa dassāmā’’ ti kāpotikaṃ suraṃ pasannaṃ paṭiyādetvā theraṃ nimantetvā ghare ghare pasannaṃ suraṃ adaṃsu. 
485542,110,2198,112,121,1,86,9,Thero pivitvā surāmadamatto nagarato nikkhamanto dvārantare patitvā vilapamāno nipajji. 
485543,110,2199,2,25,1,129,15,"Satthā katabhattakicco nagarā nikkhamanto theraṃ tenākārena nipannaṃ disvā‘‘ gaṇhatha, bhikkhave, sāgatan’’ ti gāhāpetvā ārāmaṃ agamāsi . "
485544,110,2199,26,41,1,120,14,"Bhikkhū therassa sīsaṃ tathāgatassa pādamūle katvā taṃ nipajjāpesuṃ, so parivattitvā pāde tathāgatābhimukhe katvā nipajji. "
485545,110,2199,42,65,1,98,16,"Satthā bhikkhū paṭipucchi‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, bhikkhave, yaṃ pubbe sāgatassa mayi gāravaṃ, taṃ idāni atthī’’ ti?"
485546,110,2199,66,74,1,16,3,"‘‘ Natthi, bhante’’ ti."
485547,110,2199,75,86,1,48,6,"‘‘ Bhikkhave, ambatitthakaṃ nāgarājānaṃ ko damesī’’ ti."
485548,110,2199,87,95,1,16,3,"‘‘ Sāgato, bhante’’ ti."
485549,110,2199,96,110,1,72,8,"‘‘ Kiṃ panetarahi, bhikkhave, sāgato udakadeḍḍūbhakampi dametuṃ sakkuṇeyyā’’ ti."
485550,110,2199,111,119,1,15,3,"‘‘ No hetaṃ, bhante’’."
485551,110,2199,120,139,1,74,12,"‘‘ Api nu kho, bhikkhave, evarūpaṃ pātuṃ yuttaṃ, yaṃ pivitvā evaṃvisaññī hotī’’ ti."
485552,110,2199,140,148,1,17,3,"‘‘ Ayuttaṃ, bhante’’ ti. "
485553,110,2199,149,173,1,134,15,Atha kho bhagavā theraṃ garahitvā bhikkhū āmantetvā‘‘ surāmerayapāne pācittiyan’’ ti( pāci.327) sikkhāpadaṃ paññāpetvā uṭṭhāyāsanā gandhakuṭiṃ pāvisi. 
485554,110,2200,2,35,1,202,24,"Dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitā bhikkhū surāpānassa avaṇṇaṃ kathayiṃsu‘‘ yāva mahādosañcetaṃ, āvuso, surāpānaṃ nāma, tāva paññāsampannaṃ nāma iddhimantaṃ sāgataṃ yathā satthu guṇamattampi na jānāti, tathā akāsī’’ ti. "
485555,110,2200,36,81,1,198,28,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva suraṃ pivitvā pabbajitā visaññino honti, pubbepi ahesuṃyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
485556,110,2201,2,26,1,245,24,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe udiccabrāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca uppādetvā jhānakīḷaṃ kīḷanto himavantappadese vasati pañcahi antevāsikasatehi parivuto. 
485557,110,2201,27,45,1,110,13,"Atha naṃ vassānasamaye sampatte antevāsikā āhaṃsu‘‘ ācariya, manussapathaṃ gantvā loṇambilaṃ sevitvā āgacchāmā’’ ti."
485558,110,2201,46,65,1,98,13,"‘‘ Āvuso, ahaṃ idheva vasissāmi, tumhe pana gantvā sarīraṃ santappetvā vassaṃ vītināmetvā āgacchathā’’ ti. "
485559,110,2201,66,88,1,153,18,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti ācariyaṃ vanditvā bārāṇasiṃ gantvā rājuyyāne vasitvā punadivase bahidvāragāmeyeva bhikkhāya caritvā suhitā hutvā punadivase nagaraṃ pavisiṃsu. 
485560,110,2201,89,93,1,37,4,Manussā sampiyāyamānā bhikkhaṃ adaṃsu. 
485561,110,2201,94,114,1,132,15,"Katipāhaccayena ca raññopi ārocesuṃ‘‘ deva, himavantato pañcasatā isayo āgantvā uyyāne vasanti ghoratapā paramadhitindriyā sīlavanto’’ ti. "
485562,110,2201,115,139,1,185,22,"Rājā tesaṃ guṇe sutvā uyyānaṃ gantvā vanditvā katapaṭisanthāro vassānaṃ catumāsaṃ tattheva vasanatthāya paṭiññaṃ gahetvā nimantesi, te tato paṭṭhāya rājageheyeva bhuñjitvā uyyāne vasanti. "
485563,110,2202,2,8,1,46,5,Athekadivasaṃ nagare surānakkhattaṃ nāma ahosi. 
485564,110,2202,9,21,1,59,8,Rājā‘‘ pabbajitānaṃ surā dullabhā’’ ti bahuṃ uttamasuraṃ dāpesi. 
485565,110,2202,22,131,1,720,85,"Tāpasā suraṃ pivitvā uyyānaṃ gantvā surāmadamattā hutvā ekacce uṭṭhāya nacciṃsu, ekacce gāyiṃsu, naccitvā gāyitvā khārikādīni avattharitvā niddāyitvā surāmade chinne pabujjhitvā taṃ attano vippakāraṃ disvā‘‘ na amhehi pabbajitasāruppaṃ katan’’ ti roditvā paridevitvā‘‘ mayaṃ ācariyena vinābhūtattā evarūpaṃ pāpakammaṃ karimhā’’ ti taṅkhaṇaññeva uyyānaṃ pahāya himavantaṃ gantvā paṭisāmitaparikkhārā ācariyaṃ vanditvā nisīditvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, tātā, manussapathe bhikkhāya akilamamānā sukhaṃ vasittha, samaggavāsañca pana vasitthā’’ ti pucchitā‘‘ ācariya, sukhaṃ vasimha, apica kho pana mayaṃ apātabbayuttakaṃ pivitvā visaññībhūtā satiṃ paccupaṭṭhāpetuṃ asakkontā naccimha ceva gāyimha cā’’ ti etamatthaṃ ārocentā imaṃ gāthaṃ samuṭṭhāpetvā āhaṃsu– "
485566,110,2203,2,4,1,0,0,81.
485567,110,2204,2,10,1,38,6,"‘ ‘ Apāyimha anaccimha, agāyimha rudimha ca; "
485568,110,2205,2,11,1,45,6,"Visaññīkaraṇiṃ pitvā, diṭṭhā nāhumha vānarā’’ ti. "
485569,110,2206,2,7,1,31,4,Tattha {apāyimhā}ti suraṃ pivimha. 
485570,110,2206,8,15,1,51,6,{Anaccimhā}ti taṃ pivitvā hatthapāde lāḷentā naccimha. 
485571,110,2206,16,23,1,52,6,{Agāyimhā}ti mukhaṃ vivaritvā āyatakena sarena gāyimha. 
485572,110,2206,24,40,1,72,11,Rudimha {cā}ti puna vippaṭisārino‘‘ evarūpaṃ nāma amhehi katan’’ ti rodimha ca. 
485573,110,2206,41,64,1,134,16,"Visaññīkaraṇiṃ pitvā, diṭṭhā nāhumha {vānarā}ti evarūpaṃ saññāvināsanato visaññīkaraṇiṃ suraṃ pivitvā‘‘ etadeva sādhu, yaṃ vānarā nāhumhā’’ ti. "
485574,110,2206,65,70,1,30,5,Evaṃ te attano aguṇaṃ kathesuṃ. 
485575,110,2207,2,29,1,165,19,Bodhisatto ‘‘ garusaṃvāsarahitānaṃ nāma evarūpaṃ hotiyevā’’ ti te tāpase garahitvā‘‘ puna evarūpaṃ mākaritthā’’ ti tesaṃ ovādaṃ datvā aparihīnajjhāno brahmalokaparāyaṇo ahosi. 
485576,110,2208,2,9,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi. 
485577,110,2208,10,23,1,57,9,Ito paṭṭhāya hi‘‘ anusandhiṃ ghaṭetvā’’ ti idampi na vakkhāma. 
485578,110,2208,24,33,1,64,8,"Tadā isigaṇo buddhaparisā ahosi, gaṇasatthā pana ahameva ahosinti. "
485579,110,2209,2,4,1,29,2,Surāpānajātakavaṇṇanā paṭhamā.
485580,110,2211,2,7,1,25,2,[ 82]2. Mittavindakajātakavaṇṇanā 
485581,110,2212,2,14,1,90,11,Atikkamma ramaṇakan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ dubbacabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485582,110,2212,15,42,1,112,10,"Imassa pana jātakassa kassapasammāsambuddhakālikaṃ vatthu, taṃ dasakanipāte mahāmittavindakajātake( jā.1.1.82;1.5.100 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. "
485583,110,2212,43,48,1,35,5,Tadā pana bodhisatto imaṃ gāthamāha– 
485584,110,2213,2,4,1,0,0,82.
485585,110,2214,2,10,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Atikkamma ramaṇakaṃ, sadāmattañca dūbhakaṃ; "
485586,110,2215,2,12,1,45,7,"Svāsi pāsāṇamāsīno, yasmā jīvaṃ na mokkhasī’’ ti. "
485587,110,2216,2,13,1,86,10,"Tattha ramaṇakan ti tasmiṃ kāle phalikassa nāmaṃ, phalikapāsādañca atikkantosīti dīpeti. "
485588,110,2216,14,22,1,67,6,"{Sadāmattañcā}ti rajatassa nāmaṃ, rajatapāsādañca atikkantosīti dīpeti. "
485589,110,2216,23,31,1,59,7,"Dūbhakan ti maṇino nāmaṃ, maṇipāsādañca atikkantosīti dīpeti. "
485590,110,2216,32,37,1,19,4,{Svāsī}ti so asi tvaṃ. 
485591,110,2216,38,53,1,103,13,"{Pāsāṇamāsīno}ti khuracakkaṃ nāma pāsāṇamayaṃ vā hoti rajatamayaṃ vā maṇimayaṃ vā, taṃ pana pāsāṇamayameva. "
485592,110,2216,54,60,1,40,6,So ca tena āsīno atiniviṭṭho ajjhotthaṭo. 
485593,110,2216,61,81,1,104,12,Tasmā pāsāṇena āsīnattā‘‘ pāsāṇāsīno’’ ti vattabbe byañjanasandhivasena makāraṃ ādāya‘‘ pāsāṇamāsīno’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
485594,110,2216,82,92,1,63,9,"Pāsāṇaṃ vā āsīno, taṃ khuracakkaṃ āsajja pāpuṇitvā ṭhitoti attho. "
485595,110,2216,93,113,1,112,17,"Yasmā jīvaṃ na {mokkhasī}ti yasmā khuracakkā yāva te pāpaṃ na khīyati, tāva jīvantoyeva na muccissasi, taṃ āsīnosīti. "
485596,110,2217,2,9,1,58,7,Imaṃ gāthaṃ vatvā bodhisatto attano vasanaṭṭhānaṃyeva gato. 
485597,110,2217,10,19,1,100,9,Mittavindakopi khuracakkaṃ ukkhipitvā mahādukkhaṃ anubhavamāno pāpakamme parikkhīṇe yathākammaṃ gato. 
485598,110,2218,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
485599,110,2218,9,23,1,70,9,"‘‘ tadā mittavindako dubbacabhikkhu ahosi, devarājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485600,110,2219,2,4,1,32,2,Mittavindakajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
485601,110,2221,2,7,1,22,2,[ 83]3. Kāḷakaṇṇijātakavaṇṇanā 
485602,110,2222,2,18,1,105,13,Mitto have sattapadena {hotī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ anāthapiṇḍikassa mittaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485603,110,2222,19,30,1,106,11,So kira anāthapiṇḍikena saddhiṃ sahapaṃsukīḷiko ekācariyasseva santike uggahitasippo nāmena kāḷakaṇṇī nāma. 
485604,110,2222,31,42,1,76,10,So gacchante kāle duggato hutvā jīvituṃ asakkonto seṭṭhissa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
485605,110,2222,43,51,1,65,8,So taṃ samassāsetvā paribbayaṃ datvā attano kuṭumbaṃ paṭicchāpesi. 
485606,110,2222,52,58,1,47,6,So seṭṭhino upakārako hutvā sabbakiccāni karoti. 
485607,110,2222,59,79,1,94,12,"Taṃ seṭṭhissa santikaṃ āgatakāle‘‘ tiṭṭha, kāḷakaṇṇi, nisīda, kāḷakaṇṇi, bhuñja kāḷakaṇṇī’’ ti vadanti. "
485608,110,2222,80,128,1,246,34,"Athekadivasaṃ seṭṭhino mittāmaccā seṭṭhiṃ upasaṅkamitvā evamāhaṃsu‘‘ mahāseṭṭhi, mā etaṃ tava santike kari,‘ tiṭṭha, kāḷakaṇṇi, nisīda kāḷakaṇṇi, bhuñja kāḷakaṇṇī’ ti hi iminā saddena yakkhopi palāyeyya, na cesa tayā samāno, duggato durūpeto, kiṃ te iminā’’ ti. "
485609,110,2222,129,170,1,276,34,"Anāthapiṇḍiko‘‘ nāmaṃ nāma vohāramattaṃ, na taṃ paṇḍitā pamāṇaṃ karonti, sutamaṅgalikena nāma bhavituṃ na vaṭṭati, na sakkā mayā nāmamattaṃ nissāya sahapaṃsukīḷikaṃ sahāyaṃ pariccajitun’’ ti tesaṃ vacanaṃ anādāya ekadivasaṃ attano bhogagāmaṃ gacchanto taṃ geharakkhakaṃ katvā agamāsi. "
485610,110,2223,2,20,1,111,13,"Corā ‘‘ seṭṭhi kira bhogagāmaṃ gato, gehamassa vilumpissāmā’’ ti nānāvudhahatthā rattibhāge āgantvā gehaṃ parivāresuṃ. "
485611,110,2223,21,27,1,60,6,Itaropi corānaññeva āgamanaṃ āsaṅkamāno aniddāyantova nisīdi. 
485612,110,2223,28,52,1,149,19,"So corānaṃ āgatabhāvaṃ ñatvā manusse pabodhetuṃ‘‘ tvaṃ saṅkhaṃ dhama, tvaṃ mudiṅgaṃ vādehī’’ ti mahāsamajjaṃ karonto viya sakalanivesanaṃ ekasaddaṃ kāresi. "
485613,110,2223,53,71,1,109,13,"Corā‘‘ suññaṃ gehanti dussutaṃ amhehi, attheva idha mahāseṭṭhī’’ ti pāsāṇamuggarādīni tattheva chaḍḍetvā palāyiṃsu. "
485614,110,2224,2,46,1,326,38,"Punadivase manussā tattha tattha chaḍḍite pāsāṇamuggarādayo disvā saṃvegappattā hutvā‘‘ sace ajja evarūpo buddhisampanno gharavicārako nābhavissa, corehi yathāruciyā pavisitvā sabbaṃ gehaṃ viluttaṃ assa, imaṃ daḷhamittaṃ nissāya seṭṭhino vuḍḍhi jātā’’ ti taṃ pasaṃsitvā seṭṭhissa bhogagāmato āgatakāle sabbaṃ taṃ pavattiṃ ārocayiṃsu. "
485615,110,2224,47,108,1,341,46,"Atha ne seṭṭhi avoca‘‘ tumhe evarūpaṃ mama geharakkhakaṃ mittaṃ nikkaḍḍhāpetha, sacāyaṃ tumhākaṃ vacanena mayā nikkaḍḍhito assa, ajja me kuṭumbaṃ kiñci nābhavissa, nāmaṃ nāma appamāṇaṃ, hitacittameva pamāṇan’’ ti tassa uttaritaraṃ paribbayaṃ datvā‘‘ atthi dāni me idaṃ kathāpābhatan’’ ti satthu santikaṃ gantvā ādito paṭṭhāya sabbaṃ taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesi. "
485616,110,2224,109,135,1,138,19,"Satthā‘‘ na kho, gahapati, idāneva kāḷakaṇṇimitto attano mittassa ghare kuṭumbaṃ rakkhati, pubbepi rakkhiyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
485617,110,2225,2,11,1,77,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto mahāyaso seṭṭhi ahosi. 
485618,110,2225,12,18,1,63,6,Tassa kāḷakaṇṇī nāma mittoti sabbaṃ paccuppannavatthusadisameva. 
485619,110,2225,19,47,1,164,23,"Bodhisatto bhogagāmato āgato taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā‘‘ sace mayā tumhākaṃ vacanena evarūpo mitto nikkaḍḍhito assa, ajja me kuṭumbaṃ kiñci nābhavissā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
485620,110,2226,2,4,1,0,0,83.
485621,110,2227,2,13,1,56,9,"‘ ‘ Mitto have sattapadena hoti, sahāyo pana dvādasakena hoti; "
485622,110,2228,2,10,1,54,7,"Māsaḍḍhamāsena ca ñāti hoti, tatuttariṃ attasamopi hoti; "
485623,110,2229,2,13,1,67,8,"Sohaṃ kathaṃ attasukhassa hetu, cirasanthutaṃ kāḷakaṇṇiṃ jaheyyan’’ ti. "
485624,110,2230,2,6,1,26,3,Tattha {have}ti nipātamattaṃ. 
485625,110,2230,7,16,1,63,7,"Mettāyatīti mitto, mettaṃ paccupaṭṭhāpeti, sinehaṃ karotīti attho. "
485626,110,2230,17,26,1,76,8,"So panesa sattapadena hoti, ekato sattapadavītihāragamanamattena hotīti attho. "
485627,110,2230,27,39,1,102,11,Sahāyo pana dvādasakena {hotī}ti sabbakiccāni ekato karaṇavasena sabbiriyāpathesu saha gacchatīti sahāyo. 
485628,110,2230,40,50,1,65,9,"So panesa dvādasakena hoti, dvādasāhaṃ ekato nivāsena hotīti attho. "
485629,110,2230,51,58,1,44,6,Māsaḍḍhamāsena {cā}ti māsena vā aḍḍhamāsena vā. 
485630,110,2230,59,64,1,25,4,Ñāti {hotī}ti ñātisamo hoti. 
485631,110,2230,65,74,1,60,9,Tatuttarin ti tato uttariṃ ekato vāsena attasamopi hoti yeva. 
485632,110,2230,75,89,1,70,10,Jaheyyan ti‘‘ evarūpaṃ sahāyaṃ kathaṃ jaheyyan’’ ti mittassa guṇaṃ kathesi. 
485633,110,2230,90,99,1,56,9,Tato paṭṭhāya puna koci tassa antare vattā nāma nāhosīti. 
485634,110,2231,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
485635,110,2231,9,23,1,65,9,"‘‘ tadā kāḷakaṇṇī ānando ahosi, bārāṇasiseṭṭhi pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485636,110,2232,2,4,1,29,2,Kāḷakaṇṇijātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
485637,110,2234,2,7,1,26,2,[ 84]4. Atthassadvārajātakavaṇṇanā 
485638,110,2235,2,18,1,108,13,Ārogyamicche paramañca lābhan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ atthakusalaṃ kulaputtaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485639,110,2235,19,28,1,88,9,Sāvatthiyañhi ekassa mahāvibhavassa seṭṭhino putto jātiyā sattavasso paññavā atthakusalo. 
485640,110,2235,29,42,1,85,12,"So ekadivasaṃ pitaraṃ upasaṅkamitvā atthassa dvārapañhaṃ nāma pucchi, so taṃ na jānāti. "
485641,110,2235,43,71,1,175,22,"Athassa etadahosi‘‘ ayaṃ pañho atisukhumo, ṭhapetvā sabbaññubuddhaṃ añño upari bhavaggena, heṭṭhā ca avīcinā paricchinne lokasannivāse etaṃ pañhaṃ kathetuṃ samattho nāma natthī’’ ti. "
485642,110,2235,72,121,1,305,39,"So puttamādāya bahuṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ gāhāpetvā jetavanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ pūjetvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno bhagavantaṃ etadavoca‘‘ ayaṃ, bhante, dārako paññavā atthakusalo maṃ atthassa dvārapañhaṃ nāma pucchi, ahaṃ taṃ pañhaṃ ajānanto tumhākaṃ santikaṃ āgato, sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā taṃ pañhaṃ kathetū’’ ti. "
485643,110,2235,122,156,1,179,25,"Satthā‘‘ pubbepāhaṃ, upāsaka, iminā kumārakenetaṃ pañhaṃ puṭṭho, mayā cassa kathito, tadā naṃ esa jānāti, idāni pana bhavasaṅkhepagatattā na sallakkhetī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
485644,110,2236,2,11,1,80,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto mahāvibhavo seṭṭhi ahosi. 
485645,110,2236,12,18,1,53,6,Athassa putto sattavassiko jātiyā paññavā atthakusalo. 
485646,110,2236,19,37,1,96,13,"So ekadivasaṃ pitaraṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ tāta, atthassa dvāraṃ nāma kin’’ ti atthassa dvārapañhaṃ pucchi. "
485647,110,2236,38,45,1,47,7,Athassa pitā taṃ pañhaṃ kathento imaṃ gāthamāha– 
485648,110,2237,2,4,1,0,0,84.
485649,110,2238,2,11,1,59,7,"‘ ‘ Ārogyamicche paramañca lābhaṃ, sīlañca vuddhānumataṃ sutañca; "
485650,110,2239,2,14,1,61,9,"Dhammānuvattī ca alīnatā ca, atthassa dvārā pamukhā chaḷete’’ ti. "
485651,110,2240,2,9,1,59,7,Tattha ārogyamicche paramañca lābhan ti ca-kāro nipātamattaṃ. 
485652,110,2240,10,20,1,85,9,"Tāta, paṭhamameva ārogyasaṅkhātaṃ paramaṃ lābhaṃ iccheyyāti imamatthaṃ dīpento evamāha. "
485653,110,2240,21,30,1,67,9,Tattha ārogyaṃ nāma sarīrassa ceva cittassa ca arogabhāvo anāturatā. 
485654,110,2240,31,49,1,121,15,"Sarīre hi rogāture neva aladdhaṃ bhogalābhaṃ uppādetuṃ sakkoti, na laddhaṃ paribhuñjituṃ, anāture pana ubhayampetaṃ sakkoti. "
485655,110,2240,50,66,1,118,14,"Citte ca kilesāture neva aladdhaṃ jhānādibhedaṃ lābhaṃ uppādetuṃ sakkoti, na laddhaṃ puna samāpattivasena paribhuñjituṃ. "
485656,110,2240,67,93,1,167,22,"Etasmiṃ anārogye sati aladdhopi lābho na labbhati, laddhopi niratthako hoti, asati panetasmiṃ aladdhopi lābho labbhati, laddhopi sātthako hotīti ārogyaṃ paramo lābho nāma. "
485657,110,2240,94,97,1,29,3,Taṃ sabbapaṭhamaṃ icchitabbaṃ. 
485658,110,2240,98,103,1,42,5,Idamekaṃ atthassa dvāranti ayamettha attho. 
485659,110,2240,104,107,1,20,2,{Sīlañcā}ti ācārasīlaṃ. 
485660,110,2240,108,111,1,26,3,Iminā lokacārittaṃ dasseti. 
485661,110,2240,112,117,1,50,5,Vuddhānumatan ti guṇavuddhānaṃ paṇḍitānaṃ anumataṃ. 
485662,110,2240,118,123,1,44,5,Iminā ñāṇasampannānaṃ garūnaṃ ovādaṃ dasseti. 
485663,110,2240,124,128,1,30,3,{Sutañcā}ti kāraṇanissitaṃ sutaṃ. 
485664,110,2240,129,135,1,51,6,Iminā imasmiṃ loke atthanissitaṃ bāhusaccaṃ dasseti. 
485665,110,2240,136,142,1,59,5,Dhammānuvattī {cā}ti tividhassa sucaritadhammassa anuvattanaṃ. 
485666,110,2240,143,149,1,74,6,Iminā duccaritadhammaṃ vajjetvā sucaritadhammassa anuvattanabhāvaṃ dasseti. 
485667,110,2240,150,156,1,37,5,Alīnatā {cā}ti cittassa alīnatā anīcatā. 
485668,110,2240,157,163,1,60,6,Iminā cittassa asaṅkocataṃ paṇītabhāvaṃ uttamabhāvaṃ dasseti. 
485669,110,2240,164,184,1,155,18,"Atthassa dvārā pamukhā {chaḷete}ti attho nāma vuḍḍhi, tassa vuḍḍhisaṅkhātassa lokiyalokuttarassa atthassa ete pamukhā uttamā cha dvārā upāyā adhigamamukhānīti. "
485670,110,2241,2,8,1,53,6,Evaṃ bodhisatto puttassa atthassa dvārapañhaṃ kathesi. 
485671,110,2241,9,16,1,42,7,So tato paṭṭhāya tesu chasu dhammesu vatti. 
485672,110,2241,17,23,1,52,6,Bodhisattopi dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
485673,110,2242,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
485674,110,2242,9,22,1,63,8,"‘‘ tadā puttova paccuppannaputto, mahāseṭṭhi pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485675,110,2243,2,4,1,35,2,Atthassadvārajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
485676,110,2245,2,7,1,21,2,[ 85]5. Kiṃpakkajātakavaṇṇanā 
485677,110,2246,2,14,1,93,11,Āyatiṃ dosaṃ {nāññāyā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485678,110,2246,15,30,1,131,15,Aññataro kira kulaputto buddhasāsane uraṃ datvā pabbajito ekadivasaṃ sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caranto ekaṃ alaṅkataitthiṃ disvā ukkaṇṭhi. 
485679,110,2246,31,37,1,49,6,Atha naṃ ācariyupajjhāyā satthu santikaṃ ānayiṃsu. 
485680,110,2246,38,66,1,126,17,Satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā ‘‘ saccan’’ ti vutte‘‘ pañca kāmaguṇā nāmete bhikkhu paribhogakāle ramaṇīyā. 
485681,110,2246,67,75,1,88,8,So pana tesaṃ paribhogo nirayādīsu paṭisandhidāyakattā kiṃpakkaphalaparibhogasadiso hoti. 
485682,110,2246,76,86,1,96,9,"Kiṃpakkaphalaṃ nāma vaṇṇagandharasasampannaṃ, khāditaṃ pana antāni khaṇḍitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpeti. "
485683,110,2246,87,109,1,149,19,Pubbe bahū bālajanā tassa dosaṃ adisvā vaṇṇagandharasesu bajjhitvā taṃ phalaṃ paribhuñjitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇiṃsū’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. 
485684,110,2247,2,39,1,271,31,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto satthavāho hutvā pañcahi sakaṭasatehi pubbantāparantaṃ gacchanto aṭavimukhaṃ patvā manusse sannipātetvā‘‘ imissā aṭaviyā visarukkhā nāma atthi, mā kho maṃ anāpucchā pubbe akhāditapubbāni phalāphalāni khāditthā’’ ti ovadi. "
485685,110,2247,40,48,1,92,8,Manussā aṭaviṃ atikkamitvā aṭavimukhe ekaṃ kiṃpakkarukkhaṃ phalabhāraoṇamitasākhaṃ addasaṃsu. 
485686,110,2247,49,53,1,71,4,Tassa khandhasākhāpattaphalāni saṇṭhānavaṇṇarasagandhehi ambasadisāneva. 
485687,110,2247,54,73,1,133,14,"Tesu ekacce vaṇṇagandharasesu bajjhitvā ambaphalasaññāya phalāni khādiṃsu, ekacce‘‘ satthavāhaṃ pucchitvā khādissāmā’’ ti gahetvā aṭṭhaṃsu. "
485688,110,2247,74,96,1,130,19,"Bodhisatto taṃ ṭhānaṃ patvā ye gahetvā ṭhitā, te phalāni chaḍḍāpetvā, ye khādamānā aṭṭhaṃsu, te vamanaṃ kāretvā tesaṃ bhesajjaṃ adāsi. "
485689,110,2247,97,108,1,74,10,"Tesu ekacce arogā jātā, paṭhamameva khāditvā ṭhitā pana jīvitakkhayaṃ pattā. "
485690,110,2247,109,123,1,127,14,Bodhisattopi icchitaṭṭhānaṃ sotthinā gantvā lābhaṃ labhitvā puna sakaṭṭhānameva āgantvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
485691,110,2248,2,10,1,62,8,Satthā taṃ vatthuṃ kathetvā abhisambuddho hutvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
485692,110,2249,2,4,1,0,0,85.
485693,110,2250,2,11,1,39,7,"‘ ‘ Āyatiṃ dosaṃ nāññāya, yo kāme paṭisevati; "
485694,110,2251,2,11,1,48,6,"Vipākante hananti naṃ, kiṃpakkamiva bhakkhitan’’ ti. "
485695,110,2252,2,14,1,70,10,"Tattha āyatiṃ dosaṃ {nāññāyā}ti anāgate dosaṃ na aññāya, ajānitvāti attho. "
485696,110,2252,15,25,1,62,9,Yo kāme {paṭisevatī}ti yo vatthukāme ca kilesakāme ca paṭisevati. 
485697,110,2252,26,43,1,136,17,Vipākante hananti nan ti te kāmā taṃ purisaṃ attano vipākasaṅkhāte ante nirayādīsu uppannaṃ nānappakārena dukkhena saṃyojayamānā hananti. 
485698,110,2252,44,45,1,6,1,Kathaṃ? 
485699,110,2252,46,82,1,318,30,"Kiṃpakkamiva bhakkhitan ti, yathā paribhogakāle vaṇṇagandharasasampattiyā manāpaṃ kiṃpakkaphalaṃ anāgatadosaṃ adisvā bhakkhitaṃ ante hanati, jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpeti, evaṃ paribhogakāle manāpāpi kāmā vipākakāle hanantīti desanaṃ yathānusandhiṃ pāpetvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphalaṃ pāpuṇi. "
485700,110,2252,83,96,1,83,10,"Sesaparisāyapi keci sotāpannā, keci sakadāgāmino, keci anāgāmino, keci arahanto ahesuṃ. "
485701,110,2253,2,8,1,56,6,Satthāpi imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
485702,110,2253,9,23,1,64,9,"‘‘ tadā parisā buddhaparisā ahosi, satthavāho pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485703,110,2254,2,4,1,29,2,Kiṃpakkajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
485704,110,2256,2,7,1,26,2,[ 86]6. Sīlavīmaṃsakajātakavaṇṇanā 
485705,110,2257,2,16,1,101,13,Sīlaṃ kireva kalyāṇan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ sīlavīmaṃsakaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485706,110,2257,17,28,1,90,11,So kira kosalarājānaṃ nissāya jīvati tisaraṇaṃ gato akhaṇḍapañcasīlo tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū. 
485707,110,2257,29,40,1,48,7,Rājā‘‘ ayaṃ sīlavā’’ ti tassa atirekasammānaṃ karoti. 
485708,110,2257,41,78,1,225,29,"So cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ rājā mayhaṃ aññehi brāhmaṇehi atirekasammānaṃ karoti, ativiya maṃ garuṃ katvā passati, kiṃ nu kho esa mama jātigottakulappadesasippasampattiṃ nissāya imaṃ sammānaṃ karoti, udāhu sīlasampattiṃ, vīmaṃsissāmi tāvā’’ ti. "
485709,110,2257,79,100,1,177,20,"So ekadivasaṃ rājūpaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā gharaṃ āgacchanto ekassa heraññikassa phalakato anāpucchitvā ekaṃ kahāpaṇaṃ gahetvā agamāsi, heraññiko brāhmaṇe garubhāvena kiñci avatvā nisīdi. "
485710,110,2257,101,109,1,58,7,"Punadivase dve kahāpaṇe gaṇhi, heraññiko tatheva adhivāsesi. "
485711,110,2257,110,138,1,164,19,"Tatiyadivase kahāpaṇamuṭṭhiṃ aggahesi, atha naṃ heraññiko‘‘ ajja te tatiyo divaso rājakuṭumbaṃ vilumpantassā’’ ti‘‘ rājakuṭumbavilumpakacoro me gahito’’ ti tikkhattuṃ viravi. "
485712,110,2257,139,163,1,120,20,Atha naṃ manussā ito cito ca āgantvā‘‘ ciraṃdāni tvaṃ sīlavā viya vicarī’’ ti dve tayo pahāre datvā bandhitvā rañño dassesuṃ. 
485713,110,2258,2,30,1,115,16,"Rājā vippaṭisārī hutvā‘‘ kasmā, brāhmaṇa, evarūpaṃ dussīlakammaṃ karosī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ gacchatha, tassa rājāṇaṃ karothā’’ ti āha. "
485714,110,2258,31,43,1,35,6,"Brāhmaṇo‘‘ nāhaṃ, mahārāja, coro’’ ti āha. "
485715,110,2258,44,55,1,55,7,Atha‘‘ kasmā rājakuṭumbikassa phalakato kahāpaṇe gaṇhī’’ ti?
485716,110,2258,56,88,1,173,26,"‘‘ Etaṃ mayā tayi mama atisammānaṃ karonte‘ kiṃ nu kho rājā mama jātiādīni nissāya atisammānaṃ karoti, udāhu sīlaṃ nissāyā’ ti vīmaṃsanatthāya kataṃ, idāni pana mayā ekaṃsena ñātaṃ. "
485717,110,2258,89,99,1,58,9,"Yathā sīlameva nissāya tayā mama sammāno kato, na jātiādīni. "
485718,110,2258,100,121,1,120,18,"Tathā hi me idāni rājāṇaṃ kāresi, svāhaṃ iminā kāraṇena‘ imasmiṃ loke sīlameva uttamaṃ sīlaṃ pamukhan’ ti sanniṭṭhānaṃ gato. "
485719,110,2258,122,156,1,226,28,"Imassa panāhaṃ sīlassa anucchavikaṃ karonto gehe ṭhito kilese paribhuñjanto na sakkhissāmi kātuṃ, ajjeva jetavanaṃ gantvā satthu santike pabbajissāmi, pabbajjaṃ me detha, devā’’ ti vatvā rājānaṃ anujānāpetvā jetavanābhimukho pāyāsi. "
485720,110,2259,2,9,1,72,7,Atha naṃ ñātisuhajjabandhavā sannipatitvā nivāretuṃ asakkontā nivattiṃsu. 
485721,110,2259,10,40,1,217,24,"So satthu santikaṃ gantvā pabbajjaṃ yācitvā pabbajjañca upasampadañca labhitvā avissaṭṭhakammaṭṭhāno vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ patvā satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ bhante, mayhaṃ pabbajjā matthakaṃ pattā’’ ti aññaṃ byākāsi. "
485722,110,2259,41,47,1,52,6,Tassa taṃ aññabyākaraṇaṃ bhikkhusaṅghe pākaṭaṃ jātaṃ. 
485723,110,2259,48,75,1,200,22,"Athekadivasaṃ dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitā bhikkhū‘‘ āvuso, asuko nāma rañño upaṭṭhākabrāhmaṇo attano sīlaṃ vīmaṃsitvā rājānaṃ āpucchitvā pabbajitvā arahatte patiṭṭhito’’ ti tassa guṇaṃ kathayamānā nisīdiṃsu. "
485724,110,2259,76,134,1,300,41,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāni ayameva brāhmaṇo attano sīlaṃ vīmaṃsitvā pabbajitvā attano patiṭṭhaṃ akāsi, pubbepi paṇḍitā attano sīlaṃ vīmaṃsitvā pabbajitvā attano patiṭṭhaṃ kariṃsū’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
485725,110,2260,2,14,1,119,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa purohito ahosi dānādhimutto sīlajjhāsayo akhaṇḍapañcasīlo. 
485726,110,2260,15,23,1,76,8,Rājā sesabrāhmaṇehi atirekaṃ tassa sammānaṃ karotīti sabbaṃ purimasadisameva. 
485727,110,2260,24,43,1,141,16,"Bodhisatte pana bandhitvā rañño santikaṃ nīyamāne ahituṇḍikā antaravīthiyaṃ sappaṃ kīḷāpentā naṅguṭṭhe gaṇhanti, gīvāya gaṇhanti, gale veṭhenti. "
485728,110,2260,44,65,1,94,15,"Bodhisatto te disvā‘‘ mā, tātā, evaṃ sappaṃ naṅguṭṭhe gaṇhatha, mā gīvāya gaṇhatha, mā gale veṭhetha. "
485729,110,2260,66,75,1,47,7,Ayañhi vo ḍaṃsitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpeyyā’’ ti āha. 
485730,110,2260,76,103,1,167,20,"Ahituṇḍikā‘‘ ayaṃ, brāhmaṇa, sappo sīlavā ācārasampanno tādiso dussīlo na hoti, tvaṃ pana attano dussīlatāya anācārena rājakuṭumbavilumpakacoroti bandhitvā nīyasī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
485731,110,2261,2,20,1,100,13,"So cintesi‘‘ sappāpi tāva aḍaṃsantā aviheṭhentā‘ sīlavanto’ ti nāmaṃ labhanti, kimaṅgaṃ pana manussabhūtā. "
485732,110,2261,21,33,1,56,8,"Sīlameva imasmiṃ loke uttamaṃ, natthi tato uttaritaran’’ ti. "
485733,110,2261,34,39,1,29,5,Atha naṃ netvā rañño dassesuṃ. 
485734,110,2261,40,51,1,28,6,"Rājā‘‘ kiṃ idaṃ, tātā’’ ti pucchi."
485735,110,2261,52,61,1,33,4,"‘‘ Rājakuṭumbavilumpako coro, devā’’ ti."
485736,110,2261,62,71,1,29,5,‘‘ Tena hissa rājāṇaṃ karothā’’ ti. 
485737,110,2261,72,84,1,35,6,"Brāhmaṇo‘‘ nāhaṃ, mahārāja, coro’’ ti āha."
485738,110,2261,85,136,1,255,35,"‘‘ Atha kasmā kahāpaṇe aggahesī’’ ti ca vutte purimanayeneva sabbaṃ ārocento‘‘ svāhaṃ iminā kāraṇena‘ imasmiṃ loke sīlameva uttamaṃ, sīlaṃ pāmokkhan’ ti sanniṭṭhānaṃ gato’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tiṭṭhatu tāva idaṃ, āsīvisopi tāva aḍaṃsanto aviheṭhento‘ sīlavā’ ti vattabbataṃ labhati. "
485739,110,2261,137,151,1,80,11,"Imināpi kāraṇena sīlameva uttamaṃ, sīlaṃ pavaran’’ ti sīlaṃ vaṇṇento imaṃ gāthamāha– "
485740,110,2262,2,4,1,0,0,86.
485741,110,2263,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Sīlaṃ kireva kalyāṇaṃ, sīlaṃ loke anuttaraṃ; "
485742,110,2264,2,12,1,43,7,"Passa ghoraviso nāgo, sīlavāti na haññatī’’ ti. "
485743,110,2265,2,10,1,71,6,Tattha sīlaṃ {kirevā}ti kāyavācācittehi avītikkamasaṅkhātaṃ ācārasīlameva. 
485744,110,2265,11,15,1,28,3,{Kirā}ti anussavavasena vadati. 
485745,110,2265,16,19,1,24,3,Kalyāṇan ti sundarataraṃ. 
485746,110,2265,20,24,1,39,4,Anuttaran ti jeṭṭhakaṃ sabbaguṇadāyakaṃ. 
485747,110,2265,25,32,1,55,6,{Passā}ti attanā diṭṭhakāraṇaṃ abhimukhaṃ karonto katheti. 
485748,110,2265,33,48,1,120,13,"Sīlavāti na {haññatī}ti ghoravisopi samāno aḍaṃsanaaviheṭhanamattakena sīlavāti pasaṃsaṃ labhati, na haññati na vihaññatīti. "
485749,110,2265,49,53,1,35,4,Imināpi kāraṇena sīlameva uttamanti. 
485750,110,2266,2,21,1,175,19,Evaṃ bodhisatto imāya gāthāya rañño dhammaṃ desetvā kāme pahāya isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā himavantaṃ pavisitvā pañcābhiññā aṭṭha samāpattiyo nibbattetvā brahmalokaparāyaṇo ahosi. 
485751,110,2267,2,9,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
485752,110,2267,10,27,1,78,11,"‘‘ tadā rājā ānando ahosi, rājaparisā buddhaparisā, purohito pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485753,110,2268,2,4,1,34,2,Sīlavīmaṃsakajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
485754,110,2270,2,7,1,20,2,[ 87]7. Maṅgalajātakavaṇṇanā 
485755,110,2271,2,14,1,100,11,Yassa maṅgalā {samūhatā}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto ekaṃ sāṭakalakkhaṇabrāhmaṇaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485756,110,2271,15,34,1,165,17,"Rājagahavāsiko kireko brāhmaṇo kotuhalamaṅgaliko tīsu ratanesu appasanno micchādiṭṭhiko aḍḍho mahaddhano mahābhogo, tassa samugge ṭhapitaṃ sāṭakayugaṃ mūsikā khādiṃsu. "
485757,110,2271,35,49,1,85,10,Athassa sīsaṃ nhāyitvā‘‘ sāṭake āharathā’’ ti vuttakāle mūsikāya khāditabhāvaṃ ārocayiṃsu. 
485758,110,2271,50,64,1,92,11,"So cintesi‘‘ sace idaṃ mūsikādaṭṭhaṃ sāṭakayugaṃ imasmiṃ gehe bhavissati, mahāvināso bhavissati. "
485759,110,2271,65,75,1,91,10,Idañhi avamaṅgalaṃ kāḷakaṇṇisadisaṃ puttadhītādīnaṃ vā dāsakammakarādīnaṃ vā na sakkā dātuṃ. 
485760,110,2271,76,96,1,132,17,"Yo hi idaṃ gaṇhissati, sabbassa mahāvināso bhavissati, āmakasusāne taṃ chaḍḍāpessāmi, na kho pana sakkā dāsakammakarādīnaṃ hatthe dātuṃ. "
485761,110,2271,97,114,1,91,14,"Te hi ettha lobhaṃ uppādetvā imaṃ gahetvā vināsaṃ pāpuṇeyyuṃ, puttassa taṃ hatthe dassāmī’’ ti. "
485762,110,2271,115,140,1,145,19,"So puttaṃ pakkosāpetvā tamatthaṃ ārocetvā‘‘ tvampi naṃ, tāta, hatthena aphusitvā daṇḍakena gahetvā āmakasusāne chaḍḍetvā sīsaṃ nhāyitvā ehī’’ ti pesesi. "
485763,110,2272,2,24,1,224,21,Satthāpi kho taṃ divasaṃ paccūsasamaye bodhaneyyabandhave olokento imesaṃ pitāputtānaṃ sotāpattiphalassa upanissayaṃ disvā migavīthiṃ gahetvā migaluddako viya gantvā āmakasusānadvāre nisīdi chabbaṇṇabuddharasmiyo vissajjento. 
485764,110,2272,25,37,1,117,12,Māṇavopi pitu vacanaṃ sampaṭicchitvā ajagarasappaṃ viya taṃ yugasāṭakaṃ yaṭṭhikoṭiyā gahetvā āmakasusānadvāraṃ pāpuṇi. 
485765,110,2272,38,50,1,40,8,Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ kiṃ karosi māṇavā’’ ti āha.
485766,110,2272,51,89,1,215,27,"‘‘ Bho gotama, idaṃ sāṭakayugaṃ mūsikādaṭṭhaṃ kāḷakaṇṇisadisaṃ halāhalavisūpamaṃ, mama pitā‘ añño etaṃ chaḍḍento lobhaṃ uppādetvā gaṇheyyā’ ti bhayena maṃ pahiṇi, ahametaṃ chaḍḍetvā sīsaṃ nhāyissāmīti āgatomhi, bho gotamā’’ ti."
485767,110,2272,90,98,1,19,4,‘‘ Tena hi chaḍḍehī’’ ti. 
485768,110,2272,99,114,1,69,10,"Māṇavo chaḍḍesi, satthā‘‘ amhākaṃ dāni vaṭṭatī’’ ti tassa sammukhāva gaṇhi."
485769,110,2272,115,138,1,123,16,"‘‘ Avamaṅgalaṃ, bho gotama, etaṃ kāḷakaṇṇisadisaṃ, mā gaṇhi mā gaṇhī’’ ti tasmiṃ vārayamāneyeva taṃ gahetvā veḷuvanābhimukho pāyāsi. "
485770,110,2273,2,30,1,154,21,"Māṇavo vegena gantvā pitu ārocesi‘‘ tāta, mayā āmakasusāne chaḍḍitaṃ sāṭakayugaṃ samaṇo gotamo‘ amhākaṃ vaṭṭatī’ ti mayā vāriyamānopi gahetvā veḷuvanaṃ gato’’ ti. "
485771,110,2273,31,65,1,218,26,"Brāhmaṇo cintesi‘‘ taṃ sāṭakayugaṃ avamaṅgalaṃ kāḷakaṇṇisadisaṃ, taṃ vaḷañjento samaṇopi gotamo nassissati, vihāropi nassissati, tato amhākaṃ garahā bhavissati, samaṇassa gotamassa aññe bahū sāṭake datvā taṃ chaḍḍāpessāmī’’ ti. "
485772,110,2273,66,95,1,158,22,"So bahū sāṭake gāhāpetvā puttena saddhiṃ veḷuvanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ disvā ekamantaṃ ṭhito evamāha‘‘ saccaṃ kira vo, bho gotama, āmakasusāne sāṭakayugaṃ gahitan’’ ti?"
485773,110,2273,96,104,1,18,3,"‘‘ Saccaṃ, brāhmaṇā’’ ti."
485774,110,2273,105,121,1,101,11,"‘‘ Bho gotama, taṃ sāṭakayugaṃ avamaṅgalaṃ, tumhe taṃ paribhuñjamānā nassissatha, sakalavihāropi nassissati. "
485775,110,2273,122,138,1,81,13,"Sace vo nivāsanaṃ vā pārupanaṃ vā nappahoti, ime sāṭake gahetvā taṃ chaḍḍāpethā’’ ti. "
485776,110,2273,139,180,1,268,34,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ mayaṃ brāhmaṇa pabbajitā nāma, amhākaṃ āmakasusāne antaravīthiyaṃ saṅkāraṭṭhāne nhānatitthe mahāmaggeti evarūpesu ṭhānesu chaḍḍitā vā patitā vā pilotikā vaṭṭati, tvaṃ pana na idāneva evaṃladdhiko, pubbepi evaṃladdhikoyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
485777,110,2274,2,9,1,69,7,Atīte magadharaṭṭhe rājagahanagare dhammiko magadharājā rajjaṃ kāresi. 
485778,110,2274,10,39,1,280,29,Tadā bodhisatto ekasmiṃ udiccabrāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā himavante vasamāno ekasmiṃ kāle himavantato nikkhamitvā rājagahanagare rājuyyānaṃ patvā tattha vasitvā dutiyadivase bhikkhācāratthāya nagaraṃ pāvisi. 
485779,110,2274,40,52,1,94,11,Rājā taṃ disvā pakkosāpetvā pāsāde nisīdāpetvā bhojetvā uyyāneyeva vasanatthāya paṭiññaṃ gaṇhi. 
485780,110,2274,53,59,1,49,6,Bodhisatto rañño nivesane bhuñjitvā uyyāne vasati. 
485781,110,2274,60,67,1,59,6,Tasmiṃ kāle rājagahanagare dussalakkhaṇabrāhmaṇo nāma ahosi. 
485782,110,2274,68,74,1,60,6,Tassa samugge ṭhapitaṃ sāṭakayuganti sabbaṃ purimasadisameva. 
485783,110,2275,2,17,1,133,15,Māṇave pana susānaṃ gacchante bodhisatto paṭhamataraṃ gantvā susānadvāre nisīditvā tena chaḍḍitaṃ sāṭakayugaṃ gahetvā uyyānaṃ agamāsi. 
485784,110,2275,18,22,1,26,4,Māṇavo gantvā pitu ārocesi. 
485785,110,2275,23,49,1,116,16,"Pitā‘‘ rājakulūpako tāpaso nasseyyā’’ ti bodhisattassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ tāpasa, tayā gahitasāṭake chaḍḍehi, mā nassī’’ ti āha. "
485786,110,2275,50,80,1,228,23,"Tāpaso‘‘ amhākaṃ susāne chaḍḍitapilotikā vaṭṭati, na mayaṃ kotuhalamaṅgalikā, kotuhalamaṅgalaṃ nāmetaṃ na buddhapaccekabuddhabodhisattehi vaṇṇitaṃ, tasmā paṇḍitena nāma kotuhalamaṅgalikena na bhavitabban’’ ti brāhmaṇassa dhammaṃ desesi. "
485787,110,2275,81,89,1,65,8,Brāhmaṇo dhammaṃ sutvā diṭṭhiṃ bhinditvā bodhisattaṃ saraṇaṃ gato. 
485788,110,2275,90,94,1,53,4,Bodhisattopi aparihīnajjhāno brahmalokaparāyaṇo ahosi. 
485789,110,2276,2,14,1,92,11,Satthāpi imaṃ atītaṃ āharitvā abhisambuddho hutvā brāhmaṇassa dhammaṃ desento imaṃ gāthamāha– 
485790,110,2277,2,4,1,0,0,87.
485791,110,2278,2,13,1,51,9,"‘ ‘ Yassa maṅgalā samūhatā, uppātā supinā ca lakkhaṇā ca; "
485792,110,2279,2,11,1,54,6,"So maṅgaladosavītivatto, yugayogādhigato na jātumetī’’ ti. "
485793,110,2280,2,18,1,125,13,"Tattha yassa maṅgalā {samūhatā}ti yassa arahato khīṇāsavassa diṭṭhamaṅgalaṃ, sutamaṅgalaṃ, mutamaṅgalanti ete maṅgalā samucchinnā. "
485794,110,2280,19,96,1,531,54,"Uppātā supinā ca lakkhaṇā {cā}ti‘‘ evarūpo candaggāho bhavissati, evarūpo sūriyaggāho bhavissati, evarūpo nakkhattaggāho bhavissati, evarūpo ukkāpāto bhavissati, evarūpo disāḍāho bhavissatī’’ ti ime pañca mahāuppātā, nānappakārā supinā, subhagalakkhaṇaṃ, dubbhagalakkhaṇaṃ, itthilakkhaṇaṃ, purisalakkhaṇaṃ, dāsilakkhaṇaṃ, dāsalakkhaṇaṃ, asilakkhaṇaṃ, hatthilakkhaṇaṃ, assalakkhaṇaṃ, usabhalakkhaṇaṃ, āvudhalakkhaṇaṃ, vatthalakkhaṇanti evamādikāni lakkhaṇāni ime ca diṭṭhiṭṭhānā yassa samūhatā, na etehi uppātādīhi attano maṅgalaṃ vā avamaṅgalaṃ vā pacceti. "
485795,110,2280,97,108,1,91,9,So {maṅgaladosavītivatto}ti so khīṇāsavo sabbamaṅgaladose vītivatto atikkanto pajahitvā ṭhito. 
485796,110,2280,109,138,1,109,17,"{Yugayogādhigato}ti‘‘ kodho ca upanāho ca, makkho ca paḷāso cā’’ tiādinā ( vibha.833) nayena dve dve ekato āgatakilesā yugā nāma. "
485797,110,2280,139,152,1,86,10,"Kāmayogo, bhavayogo, diṭṭhiyogo, avijjāyogoti ime saṃsāre yojanabhāvato cattāro yogā nāma. "
485798,110,2280,153,166,1,97,13,Te yuge ca yoge cāti yugayoge adhigato abhibhavitvā gato vītivatto samatikkanto khīṇāsavo bhikkhu. 
485799,110,2280,167,178,1,77,10,Na {jātumetī}ti puna paṭisandhivasena ekaṃseneva imaṃ lokaṃ na eti nāgacchatīti. 
485800,110,2281,2,18,1,137,15,"Evaṃ satthā imāya gāthāya brāhmaṇassa dhammaṃ desetvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne brāhmaṇo saddhiṃ puttena sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. "
485801,110,2281,19,22,1,26,3,Satthā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
485802,110,2281,23,39,1,73,11,"‘‘ tadā eteva pitāputtā idāni pitāputtā ahesuṃ, tāpaso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485803,110,2282,2,4,1,28,2,Maṅgalajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
485804,110,2284,2,7,1,21,2,[ 88]8. Sārambhajātakavaṇṇanā 
485805,110,2285,2,17,1,90,9,Kalyāṇimeva {muñceyyā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto omasavādasikkhāpadaṃ( pāci.15) ārabbha kathesi. 
485806,110,2285,18,23,1,55,5,Dvepi vatthūni heṭṭhā nandivisālajātake vuttasadisāneva. 
485807,110,2285,24,37,1,112,12,Imasmiṃ pana jātake bodhisatto gandhāraraṭṭhe takkasilāyaṃ aññatarassa brāhmaṇassa sārambho nāma balibaddo ahosi. 
485808,110,2285,38,46,1,68,8,Satthā idaṃ atītavatthuṃ kathetvā abhisambuddho hutvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
485809,110,2286,2,4,1,0,0,88.
485810,110,2287,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Kalyāṇimeva muñceyya, na hi muñceyya pāpikaṃ; "
485811,110,2288,2,12,1,47,7,"Mokkho kalyāṇiyā sādhu, mutvā tappati pāpikan’’ ti. "
485812,110,2289,2,14,1,115,11,Tattha kalyāṇimeva {muñceyyā}ti catudosavinimuttaṃ kalyāṇiṃ sundaraṃ anavajjaṃ vācameva muñceyya vissajjeyya katheyya. 
485813,110,2289,15,29,1,90,14,Na hi muñceyya pāpikan ti pāpikaṃ lāmikaṃ paresaṃ appiyaṃ amanāpaṃ na muñceyya na katheyya. 
485814,110,2289,30,42,1,91,10,Mokkho kalyāṇiyā {sādhū}ti kalyāṇavācāya vissajjanameva imasmiṃ loke sādhu sundaraṃ bhaddakaṃ. 
485815,110,2289,43,57,1,112,14,Mutvā tappati pāpikan ti pāpikaṃ pharusavācaṃ muñcitvā vissajjetvā kathetvā so puggalo tappati socati kilamatīti. 
485816,110,2290,2,9,1,59,7,Evaṃ satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
485817,110,2290,10,27,1,79,11,"‘‘ tadā brāhmaṇo ānando ahosi, brāhmaṇī uppalavaṇṇā, sārambho pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485818,110,2291,2,4,1,29,2,Sārambhajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
485819,110,2293,2,7,1,19,2,[ 89]9. Kuhakajātakavaṇṇanā 
485820,110,2294,2,16,1,87,12,Vācāva kira te {āsī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kuhakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485821,110,2294,17,21,1,42,4,Kuhakavatthu uddālakajātake āvi bhavissati. 
485822,110,2295,2,14,1,103,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente ekaṃ gāmakaṃ upanissāya eko kūṭajaṭilo kuhakatāpaso vasati. 
485823,110,2295,15,28,1,101,13,Eko kuṭumbiko tassa araññe paṇṇasālaṃ kāretvā tattha naṃ vāsento attano gehe paṇītāhārena paṭijaggati. 
485824,110,2295,29,57,1,144,19,"So taṃ kūṭajaṭilaṃ‘‘ sīlavā eso’’ ti saddahitvā corabhayena suvaṇṇanikkhasataṃ tassa paṇṇasālaṃ netvā bhūmigataṃ katvā‘‘ idaṃ olokeyyāsi, bhante’’ ti āha. "
485825,110,2295,58,84,1,118,18,"Atha naṃ tāpaso‘‘ pabbajitānaṃ nāma, āvuso, evarūpaṃ kathetuṃ, na vaṭṭati, amhākaṃ pana parasantake lobho nāma natthī’’ ti āha. "
485826,110,2295,85,98,1,51,8,"So‘‘ sādhu, bhante’’ ti tassa vacanaṃ saddahitvā pakkāmi. "
485827,110,2295,99,164,1,415,52,"Duṭṭhatāpaso‘‘ sakkā ettakena jīvitun’’ ti katipāhaṃ atikkamitvā taṃ suvaṇṇaṃ gahetvā antarāmagge ekasmiṃ ṭhāne ṭhapetvā āgantvā paṇṇasālāyameva vasitvā punadivase tassa gehe bhattakiccaṃ katvā evamāha‘‘ āvuso, mayaṃ tumhe nissāya ciraṃ vasimha, aticiraṃ ekasmiṃ ṭhāne vasantānaṃ manussehi saddhiṃ saṃsaggo hoti, saṃsaggo ca nāma pabbajitānaṃ malaṃ, tasmā gacchāmahan’’ ti vatvā tena punappunaṃ yāciyamānopi nivattituṃ na icchi. "
485828,110,2295,165,182,1,76,12,"Atha naṃ so‘‘ evaṃ sante gacchatha, bhante’’ ti yāva gāmadvāraṃ anugantvā nivatti. "
485829,110,2295,183,203,1,116,15,Tāpasopi thokaṃ gantvāva‘‘ imaṃ kuṭumbikaṃ mayā vañcetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintetvā jaṭānaṃ antare tiṇaṃ ṭhapetvā paṭinivatti. 
485830,110,2295,204,216,1,42,6,"Kuṭumbiko‘‘ kiṃ, bhante, nivattitthā’’ ti pucchi. "
485831,110,2295,217,234,1,119,15,"Āvuso tumhākaṃ gehacchadanato me jaṭāsu ekatiṇaṃ laggaṃ, adinnādānañca nāma pabbajitānaṃ na vaṭṭati, taṃ ādāya āgatomhīti. "
485832,110,2295,235,264,1,142,19,"Kuṭumbiko‘‘ chaḍḍetvā gacchatha, bhante’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tiṇasalākampi nāma parasantakaṃ na gaṇhāti, aho kukkuccako me ayyo’’ ti pasīditvā vanditvā uyyojesi. "
485833,110,2296,2,13,1,92,11,Tadā pana bodhisattena bhaṇḍatthāya paccantaṃ gacchantena tasmiṃ nivesane nivāso gahito hoti. 
485834,110,2296,14,48,1,173,24,"So tāpasassa vacanaṃ sutvāva‘‘ addhā iminā duṭṭhatāpasena imassa kiñci gahitaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti kuṭumbikaṃ pucchi‘‘ atthi pana te, samma, kiñci etassa tāpasassa santike nikkhittan’’ ti?"
485835,110,2296,49,59,1,33,4,"‘‘ Atthi, samma, suvaṇṇanikkhasatan’’ ti."
485836,110,2296,60,72,1,32,6,"‘‘ Tena hi gaccha, taṃ upadhārehī’’ ti . "
485837,110,2296,73,88,1,64,10,"So paṇṇasālaṃ gantvā taṃ adisvā vegenāgantvā‘‘ natthi, sammā’’ ti āha."
485838,110,2296,89,121,1,186,25,"‘‘ Na te suvaṇṇaṃ aññena gahitaṃ, teneva kuhakatāpasena gahitaṃ, ehi, taṃ anubandhitvā gaṇhāmā’’ ti vegena gantvā kūṭatāpasaṃ gaṇhitvā hatthehi ca pādehi ca pothetvā suvaṇṇaṃ āharāpetvā gaṇhiṃsu. "
485839,110,2296,122,140,1,112,14,Bodhisatto suvaṇṇaṃ disvā‘‘ nikkhasataṃ haramāno asajjitvā tiṇamatte sattosī’’ ti vatvā taṃ garahanto imaṃ gāthamāha– 
485840,110,2297,2,4,1,0,0,89.
485841,110,2298,2,11,1,39,7,"‘ ‘ Vācāva kira te āsi, saṇhā sakhilabhāṇino; "
485842,110,2299,2,12,1,47,7,"Tiṇamatte asajjittho, no ca nikkhasataṃ haran’’ ti. "
485843,110,2300,2,38,1,205,28,"Tattha vācāva kira te āsi, saṇhā {sakhilabhāṇino}ti‘‘ pabbajitānaṃ tiṇamattampi adinnaṃ ādātuṃ na vaṭṭatī’’ ti evaṃ sakhilaṃ muduvacanaṃ vadantassa vācā eva kira te saṇhā āsi, vacanamattameva maṭṭhaṃ ahosīti attho. "
485844,110,2300,39,52,1,102,12,Tiṇamatte {asajjittho}ti kūṭajaṭila ekissā tiṇasalākāya kukkuccaṃ kurumāno tvaṃ satto āsatto laggo ahosi. 
485845,110,2300,53,65,1,83,12,No ca nikkhasataṃ haran ti imaṃ pana nikkhasataṃ haranto asatto nillaggova jātosīti. 
485846,110,2301,2,21,1,95,13,"Evaṃ bodhisatto taṃ garahitvā‘‘ mā puna, kūṭajaṭila, evarūpamakāsī’’ ti ovādaṃ datvā yathākammaṃ gato. "
485847,110,2302,2,24,1,120,15,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevesa bhikkhu kuhako, pubbepi kuhakoyevā’’ ti vatvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
485848,110,2302,25,40,1,72,9,"‘‘ tadā kūṭatāpaso kuhakabhikkhu ahosi, paṇḍitapuriso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485849,110,2303,2,4,1,26,2,Kuhakajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
485850,110,2305,2,7,1,21,2,[ 90]10. Akataññujātakavaṇṇanā 
485851,110,2306,2,13,1,84,10,Yo pubbe {katakalyāṇo}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto anāthapiṇḍikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485852,110,2306,14,20,1,54,6,Tassa kireko paccantavāsiko seṭṭhi adiṭṭhasahāyo ahosi. 
485853,110,2306,21,30,1,85,9,So ekadā paccante uṭṭhānakabhaṇḍassa pañca sakaṭasatāni pūretvā kammantikamanusse āha–
485854,110,2306,31,52,1,136,14,"‘‘ gacchatha, bho, imaṃ bhaṇḍaṃ sāvatthiṃ netvā amhākaṃ sahāyakassa anāthapiṇḍikamahāseṭṭhissa paccagghena vikkiṇitvā paṭibhaṇḍaṃ āharathā’’ ti. "
485855,110,2306,53,72,1,114,15,Te‘‘ sādhū’’ ti tassa vacanaṃ sampaṭicchitvā sāvatthiṃ gantvā mahāseṭṭhiṃ disvā paṇṇākāraṃ datvā taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesuṃ. 
485856,110,2306,73,92,1,128,15,Mahāseṭṭhi‘‘ svāgataṃ vo’’ ti tesaṃ āvāsañca paribbayañca dāpetvā sahāyakassa sukhaṃ pucchitvā bhaṇḍaṃ vikkiṇitvā paṭibhaṇḍaṃ dāpesi. 
485857,110,2306,93,100,1,55,7,Te paccantaṃ gantvā tamatthaṃ attano seṭṭhissa ārocesuṃ. 
485858,110,2307,2,9,1,67,7,Aparabhāge anāthapiṇḍikopi tatheva pañca sakaṭasatāni tattha pesesi. 
485859,110,2307,10,17,1,69,7,Manussā tattha gantvā paṇṇākāraṃ ādāya paccantavāsikaseṭṭhiṃ passiṃsu. 
485860,110,2307,18,67,1,248,31,"So‘‘ kuto āgacchathā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ sāvatthito tumhākaṃ sahāyakassa anāthapiṇḍikassa santikā’’ ti vutte‘‘ anāthapiṇḍikoti kassaci purisassa nāmaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti parihāsaṃ katvā paṇṇākāraṃ gahetvā‘‘ gacchatha tumhe’’ ti uyyojesi, neva nivāsaṃ, na paribbayaṃ dāpesi. "
485861,110,2307,68,80,1,98,12,Te sayameva bhaṇḍaṃ vikkiṇitvā paṭibhaṇḍaṃ ādāya sāvatthiṃ āgantvā seṭṭhissa taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesuṃ. 
485862,110,2308,2,19,1,126,15,"Atha so paccantavāsī punapi ekavāraṃ tatheva pañca sakaṭasatāni sāvatthiṃ pesesi, manussā paṇṇākāraṃ ādāya mahāseṭṭhiṃ passiṃsu. "
485863,110,2308,20,83,1,454,51,"Te pana disvā anāthapiṇḍikassa manussā‘‘ mayaṃ, sāmi, etesaṃ nivāsañca bhattañca paribbayañca jānissāmā’’ ti vatvā tesaṃ sakaṭāni bahinagare tathārūpe ṭhāne mocāpetvā‘‘ tumhe idheva vasatha, amhākaṃ vo ghare yāgubhattañca paribbayo ca bhavissatī’’ ti gantvā dāsakammakare sannipātetvā majjhimayāmasamanantare pañca sakaṭasatāni vilumpitvā nivāsanapārupanānipi nesaṃ acchinditvā goṇe palāpetvā sakaṭāni vicakkāni katvā bhūmiyaṃ ṭhapetvā cakkānipi gaṇhitvāva agamaṃsu. "
485864,110,2308,84,93,1,88,9,Paccantavāsino nivāsanamattassapi sāmikā ahutvā bhītā vegena palāyitvā paccantameva gatā. 
485865,110,2308,94,98,1,47,4,Seṭṭhimanussāpi tamatthaṃ mahāseṭṭhino ārocesuṃ. 
485866,110,2308,99,117,1,99,14,So‘‘ atthi dānidaṃ kathāpābhatan’’ ti satthu santikaṃ gantvā ādito paṭṭhāya sabbaṃ taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesi. 
485867,110,2308,118,142,1,116,17,"Satthā‘‘ na kho, gahapati, so paccantavāsī idāneva evaṃsīlo, pubbepi evaṃsīloyeva ahosī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
485868,110,2309,2,12,1,92,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto bārāṇasiyaṃ mahāvibhavo seṭṭhi ahosi. 
485869,110,2309,13,18,1,49,5,Tasseko paccantavāsiko seṭṭhi adiṭṭhasahāyo ahosi. 
485870,110,2309,19,56,1,244,29,Sabbaṃ atītavatthu paccuppannavatthusadisameva bodhisatto pana attano manussehi‘‘ ajja amhehi idaṃ nāma katan’’ ti ārocite‘‘ paṭhamaṃ attano kataṃ upakāraṃ ajānantā pacchā evarūpaṃ labhantiyevā’’ ti vatvā sampattaparisāya dhammaṃ desento imaṃ gāthamāha– 
485871,110,2310,2,4,1,0,0,90.
485872,110,2311,2,11,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Yo pubbe katakalyāṇo, katattho nāvabujjhati; "
485873,110,2312,2,11,1,49,6,"Pacchā kicce samuppanne, kattāraṃ nādhigacchatī’’ ti. "
485874,110,2313,2,37,1,267,33,"Tatrāyaṃ piṇḍattho– khattiyādīsu yo koci puriso pubbe paṭhamataraṃ aññena katakalyāṇo katūpakāro katattho nipphāditakicco hutvā taṃ parena attani kataṃ kalyāṇañceva atthañca na jānāti, so pacchā attano kicce samuppanne tassa kiccassa kattāraṃ nādhigacchati na labhatīti. "
485875,110,2314,2,13,1,85,11,Evaṃ bodhisatto imāya gāthāya dhammaṃ desetvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
485876,110,2315,2,10,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
485877,110,2315,11,25,1,80,9,"‘‘ tadā paccantavāsī idānīpi paccantavāsīyeva, bārāṇasiseṭṭhi pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
485878,110,2316,2,4,1,28,2,Akataññujātakavaṇṇanā dasamā. 
485879,110,2317,2,4,1,20,2,Apāyimhavaggo navamo. 
485880,110,2318,2,3,1,11,1,Tassuddānaṃ – 
485881,110,2319,2,7,1,43,4,"Surāpānaṃ mittavindaṃ, kāḷakaṇṇī atthadvāraṃ; "
485882,110,2320,2,6,1,43,3,"Kiṃpakkasīlavīmaṃsaṃ , maṅgalañcāpi sārambhaṃ; "
485883,110,2321,2,5,1,21,3,Kuhakaṃ akataññū cāti.
485884,110,2322,2,4,1,10,2,10 . Littavaggo
485885,110,2324,2,7,1,18,2,[ 91]1. Littajātakavaṇṇanā 
485886,110,2325,2,14,1,96,10,Littaṃ paramena {tejasā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto apaccavekkhitaparibhogaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485887,110,2325,15,24,1,85,9,Tasmiṃ kira kāle bhikkhū cīvarādīni labhitvā yebhuyyena apaccavekkhitvā paribhuñjanti. 
485888,110,2325,25,34,1,95,9,Te cattāro paccaye apaccavekkhitvā paribhuñjamānā yebhuyyena nirayatiracchānayonito na muccanti. 
485889,110,2325,35,125,1,551,57,"Satthā taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā bhikkhūnaṃ anekapariyāyena dhammiṃ kathaṃ kathetvā apaccavekkhitaparibhoge ādīnavaṃ dassetvā‘‘ bhikkhave, bhikkhunā nāma cattāro paccaye labhitvā apaccavekkhitvā paribhuñjituṃ na vaṭṭati, tasmā ito paṭṭhāya cattāro paccaye paccavekkhitvā paribhuñjeyyāthā’’ ti paccavekkhanavidhiṃ dassento‘‘ idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu paṭisaṅkhā yoniso cīvaraṃ paṭisevati sītassa paṭighātāyā’’ tiādinā( ma. ni.1.23; a. ni.6.58) nayena tantiṃ ṭhapetvā‘‘ bhikkhave, cattāro paccaye evaṃ paccavekkhitvā paribhuñjituṃ vaṭṭati, apaccavekkhitvā paribhogo nāma halāhalavisaparibhogasadiso. "
485890,110,2325,126,142,1,118,14,Porāṇakā hi apaccavekkhitvā dosaṃ ajānitvā visaṃ paribhuñjitvā vipākante mahādukkhaṃ anubhaviṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. 
485891,110,2326,2,15,1,123,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto aññatarasmiṃ mahābhogakule nibbattitvā vayappatto akkhadhutto ahosi. 
485892,110,2326,16,43,1,191,22,"Athāparo kūṭakkhadhutto bodhisattena saddhiṃ kīḷanto attano jaye vattamāne keḷimaṇḍalaṃ na bhindati, parājayakāle pana akkhaṃ mukhe pakkhipitvā‘‘ akkho naṭṭho’’ ti keḷimaṇḍalaṃ bhinditvā pakkamati. "
485893,110,2326,44,84,1,207,28,"Bodhisatto tassa taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā‘‘ hotu, jānissāmettha patirūpakāraṇan’’ ti akkhe ādāya attano ghare halāhalavisena rañjitvā punappunaṃ sukkhāpetvā te ādāya tassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ ehi, samma, akkhehi kīḷāmā’’ ti āha. "
485894,110,2326,85,105,1,107,15,"So‘‘ sādhu, sammā’’ ti keḷimaṇḍalaṃ sajjetvā tena saddhiṃ kīḷanto attano parājayakāle ekaṃ akkhaṃ mukhe pakkhipi. "
485895,110,2326,106,127,1,110,16,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto tathā karontaṃ disvā‘‘ gilāhi tāva, pacchā idaṃ nāmetanti jānissasī’’ ti codetuṃ imaṃ gāthamāha– "
485896,110,2327,2,4,1,0,0,91.
485897,110,2328,2,13,1,53,8,"‘ ‘ Littaṃ paramena tejasā, gilamakkhaṃ puriso na bujjhati; "
485898,110,2329,2,14,1,57,9,"Gila re gila pāpadhuttaka, pacchā te kaṭukaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti. "
485899,110,2330,2,7,1,35,5,Tattha littan ti makkhitaṃ rañjitaṃ. 
485900,110,2330,8,13,1,53,4,Paramena {tejasā}ti uttamatejasampannena halāhalavisena. 
485901,110,2330,14,17,1,16,3,Gilan ti gilanto. 
485902,110,2330,18,21,1,17,3,Akkhan ti guḷakaṃ. 
485903,110,2330,22,38,1,61,11,Na {bujjhatī}ti‘‘ ayaṃ me gilato idaṃ nāma karissatī’’ ti na jānāti. 
485904,110,2330,39,44,1,20,4,Gila {re}ti gilāhi are. 
485905,110,2330,45,50,1,28,4,{Gilā}ti punapi codento vadati. 
485906,110,2330,51,66,1,100,14,Pacchā te kaṭukaṃ {bhavissatī}ti imasmiṃ te akkhe gilite pacchā etaṃ visaṃ tikhiṇaṃ bhavissatīti attho. 
485907,110,2331,2,12,1,93,10,So bodhisattassa kathentasseva visavegena mucchito akkhīni parivattetvā khandhaṃ nāmetvā pati. 
485908,110,2331,13,46,1,221,25,Bodhisatto‘‘ idānissa jīvitadānaṃ dātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti osadhaparibhāvitaṃ vamanayogaṃ datvā vametvā sappiphāṇitamadhusakkarādayo khādāpetvā arogaṃ katvā‘‘ puna evarūpaṃ mā akāsī’’ ti ovaditvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
485909,110,2332,2,21,1,147,14,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ bhikkhave, apaccavekkhitaparibhogo nāma apaccavekkhitvā katavisaparibhogasadiso hotī’’ ti vatvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
485910,110,2332,22,41,1,96,13,"‘‘ tadā paṇḍitadhutto ahameva ahosiṃ, kūṭadhutto panettha na kathīyati, yathā ca ettha, evaṃ sabbattha. "
485911,110,2332,42,55,1,54,10,"Yo pana imasmiṃ kāle na paññāyati, so na kathīyatevā’’ ti. "
485912,110,2333,2,4,1,26,2,Littajātakavaṇṇanā paṭhamā.
485913,110,2335,2,7,1,21,2,[ 92]2. Mahāsārajātakavaṇṇanā 
485914,110,2336,2,14,1,96,10,Ukkaṭṭhe {sūramicchantī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto āyasmantaṃ ānandattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
485915,110,2336,15,31,1,117,12,"Ekasmiñhi samaye kosalarañño itthiyo cintayiṃsu‘‘ buddhuppādo nāma dullabho, tathā manussapaṭilābho, paripuṇṇāyatanatā ca. "
485916,110,2336,32,83,1,350,46,"Mayañca imaṃ dullabhaṃ khaṇasamavāyaṃ labhitvāpi attano ruciyā vihāraṃ gantvā dhammaṃ vā sotuṃ buddhapūjaṃ vā kātuṃ dānaṃ vā dātuṃ na labhāma, mañjūsāya pakkhittā viya vasāma, rañño kathetvā amhākaṃ dhammaṃ desetuṃ anucchavikaṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ pakkosāpetvā tassa santike dhammaṃ sossāma, tato yaṃ sakkhissāma, taṃ uggaṇhissāma, dānādīni ca puññāni karissāma. "
485917,110,2336,84,93,1,49,7,Evaṃ no ayaṃ khaṇapaṭilābho saphalo bhavissatī’’ ti. 
485918,110,2336,94,101,1,65,7,Tā sabbāpi rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā attanā cintitakāraṇaṃ kathayiṃsu. 
485919,110,2336,102,110,1,25,4,Rājā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
485920,110,2337,2,17,1,89,10,Athekadivasaṃ rājā uyyānakīḷaṃ kīḷitukāmo uyyānapālaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ uyyānaṃ sodhehī’’ ti āha. 
485921,110,2337,18,46,1,176,21,"Uyyānapālo uyyānaṃ sodhento satthāraṃ aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle nisinnaṃ disvā rañño santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ suddhaṃ, deva, uyyānaṃ, apicettha aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle bhagavā nisinno’’ ti āha. "
485922,110,2337,47,68,1,118,15,"Rājā‘‘ sādhu, samma, satthu santike dhammampi sossāmā’’ ti alaṅkatarathaṃ abhiruhitvā uyyānaṃ gantvā satthu santikaṃ agamāsi. "
485923,110,2338,2,14,1,94,12,Tasmiñca samaye chattapāṇi nāmeko anāgāmī upāsako satthu santike dhammaṃ suṇamāno nisinno hoti. 
485924,110,2338,15,47,1,204,26,"Rājā taṃ disvā āsaṅkamāno muhuttaṃ ṭhatvā puna‘‘ sacāyaṃ pāpako bhaveyya, na satthu santike nisīditvā dhammaṃ suṇeyya, apāpakena iminā bhavitabban’’ ti cintetvā satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
485925,110,2338,48,63,1,95,13,"Upāsako buddhagāravena rañño paccuṭṭhānaṃ vā vandanaṃ vā na akāsi, tenassa rājā anattamano ahosi. "
485926,110,2338,64,113,1,233,33,"Satthā tassa anattamanabhāvaṃ ñatvā upāsakassa guṇaṃ kathesi‘‘ ayaṃ, mahārāja, upāsako bahussuto āgatāgamo kāmesu vītarāgo’’ ti rājā‘‘ na iminā orakena bhavitabbaṃ, yassa satthā guṇaṃ vaṇṇetī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ upāsaka, vadeyyāsi yena te attho’’ ti āha. "
485927,110,2338,114,122,1,28,4,Upāsako‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
485928,110,2338,123,132,1,69,9,Rājā satthu santike dhammaṃ sutvā satthāraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. 
485929,110,2339,2,43,1,275,33,"So ekadivasaṃ uparipāsāde mahāvātapānaṃ vivaritvā ṭhito taṃ upāsakaṃ bhuttapātarāsaṃ chattamādāya jetavanaṃ gacchantaṃ disvā pakkosāpetvā evamāha‘‘ tvaṃ kira, upāsaka, bahussuto, amhākañca itthiyo dhammaṃ sotukāmā ceva uggahetukāmā ca, sādhu vatassa sace tāsaṃ dhammaṃ vāceyyāsī’’ ti."
485930,110,2339,44,65,1,97,14,"‘‘ Deva, gihīnaṃ nāma rājantepure dhammaṃ desetuṃ vā vācetuṃ vā nappatirūpaṃ, ayyānaṃ eva patirūpan’’ ti. "
485931,110,2339,66,103,1,208,27,"Rājā‘‘ saccaṃ esa vadatī’’ ti uyyojetvā itthiyo pakkosāpetvā‘‘ bhadde, ahaṃ tumhākaṃ dhammadesanatthāya ca dhammavācanatthāya ca satthu santikaṃ gantvā ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ yācāmi, asītiyā mahāsāvakesu kataraṃ yācāmī’’ ti āha. "
485932,110,2339,104,110,1,65,6,Tā sabbāpi mantetvā dhammabhaṇḍāgārikaṃ ānandattherameva ārocesuṃ. 
485933,110,2339,111,147,1,222,30,"Rājā satthu santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno evamāha‘‘ bhante, amhākaṃ gehe itthiyo ānandattherassa santike dhammaṃ sotuñca uggaṇhituñca icchanti, sādhu vata sace thero amhākaṃ gehe dhammaṃ deseyya ceva vāceyya cā’’ ti. "
485934,110,2339,148,158,1,45,6,Satthā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā theraṃ āṇāpesi. 
485935,110,2339,159,170,1,79,11,Tato paṭṭhāya rañño itthiyo therassa santike dhammaṃ suṇanti ceva uggaṇhanti ca. 
485936,110,2340,2,6,1,35,4,Athekadivasaṃ rañño cūḷāmaṇi naṭṭho. 
485937,110,2340,7,25,1,106,13,Rājā tassa naṭṭhabhāvaṃ sutvā amacce āṇāpesi‘‘ sabbe antovaḷañjanake manusse gahetvā cūḷāmaṇiṃ āharāpethā’’ ti. 
485938,110,2340,26,35,1,77,9,Amaccā mātugāme ādiṃ katvā cūḷāmaṇiṃ paripucchantā adisvā mahājanaṃ kilamenti. 
485939,110,2340,36,41,1,47,5,Taṃ divasaṃ ānandatthero rājanivesanaṃ paviṭṭho. 
485940,110,2340,42,60,1,129,17,"Yathā tā itthiyo pubbe theraṃ disvāva haṭṭhatuṭṭhā dhammaṃ suṇanti ceva uggaṇhanti ca, tathā akatvā sabbā domanassappattāva ahesuṃ. "
485941,110,2340,61,103,1,212,28,"Tato therena‘‘ kasmā tumhe ajja evarūpā jātā’’ ti pucchitā evamāhaṃsu‘‘ bhante, rañño cūḷāmaṇiṃ pariyesāmāti amaccā mātugāme upādāya antovaḷañjanake kilamenti, na jānāma kassa‘ kiṃ bhavissatī’ ti, tenamha domanassappattā’’ ti. "
485942,110,2340,104,132,1,123,18,"Thero‘‘ mā cintayitthā’’ ti tā samassāsetvā rañño santikaṃ gantvā paññattāsane nisīditvā‘‘ maṇi kira te, mahārāja, naṭṭho’’ ti pucchi."
485943,110,2340,133,141,1,13,3,"‘‘ Āma, bhante’’ ti."
485944,110,2340,142,151,1,30,5,‘‘ Asakkhi pana taṃ āharāpetun’’ ti.
485945,110,2340,152,166,1,68,9,"‘‘ Bhante, sabbaṃ antojanaṃ gahetvā kilamentopi na sakkomi āharāpetun’’ ti."
485946,110,2340,167,178,1,52,6,"‘‘ Mahārāja, mahājanaṃ akilametvāva āharaṇūpāyo atthī’’ ti."
485947,110,2340,179,187,1,16,3,"‘‘ Kataro, bhante’’ ti?"
485948,110,2340,188,196,1,22,3,"‘‘ Piṇḍadānaṃ, mahārājā’’ ti."
485949,110,2340,197,206,1,28,4,"‘‘ Kataraṃ piṇḍadānaṃ, bhante’’ ti?"
485950,110,2340,207,234,1,161,21,"‘‘ Mahārāja, yattakesu āsaṅkā atthi, te gahetvā ekekassa ekekaṃ palālapiṇḍaṃ vā mattikāpiṇḍaṃ vā datvā‘ imaṃ paccūsakāle āharitvā asukaṭṭhāne nāma pātethā’ ti vattabbaṃ. "
485951,110,2340,235,243,1,55,7,"Yena gahito bhavissati, so tasmiṃ pakkhipitvā āharissati. "
485952,110,2340,244,250,1,46,5,"Sace paṭhamadivaseyeva pātenti, iccetaṃ kusalaṃ. "
485953,110,2340,251,259,1,60,7,"No ce pātenti, dutiyadivasepi tatiyadivasepi tatheva kātabbaṃ. "
485954,110,2340,260,275,1,78,12,"Evaṃ mahājano ca na kilamissati, maṇiñca labhissasī’’ ti evaṃ vatvā thero agamāsi. "
485955,110,2341,2,11,1,57,8,"Rājā vuttanayeneva tayo divase dāpesi, neva maṇiṃ āhariṃsu. "
485956,110,2341,12,28,1,61,9,"Thero tatiyadivase āgantvā‘‘ kiṃ, mahārāja, pātito maṇī’’ ti pucchi."
485957,110,2341,29,38,1,20,4,"‘‘ Na pātenti, bhante’’ ti."
485958,110,2341,39,79,1,281,32,"‘‘ Tena hi, mahārāja, mahātalasmiṃyeva paṭicchannaṭṭhāne mahācāṭiṃ ṭhapāpetvā udakassa pūrāpetvā sāṇiṃ parikkhipāpetvā‘ sabbe antovaḷañjanakamanussā ca itthiyo ca uttarāsaṅgaṃ katvā ekekova antosāṇiṃ pavisitvā hatthaṃ dhovitvā āgacchantū’ ti vadehī’’ ti thero imaṃ upāyaṃ ācikkhitvā pakkāmi. "
485959,110,2341,80,83,1,17,3,Rājā tathā kāresi. 
485960,110,2341,84,112,1,201,23,"Maṇicoro cintesi‘‘ dhammabhaṇḍāgāriko imaṃ adhikaraṇaṃ ādāya maṇiṃ adassetvā osakkissatīti aṭṭhānametaṃ, pātetuṃ dāni vaṭṭatī’’ ti maṇiṃ paṭicchannaṃ katvā ādāya antosāṇiṃ pavisitvā cāṭiyaṃ pātetvā nikkhami. "
485961,110,2341,113,119,1,55,6,Sabbesaṃ nikkhantakāle udakaṃ chaḍḍetvā maṇiṃ addasaṃsu. 
485962,110,2341,120,146,1,140,17,"Rājā‘‘ theraṃ nissāya mahājanaṃ akilametvāva me maṇi laddho’’ ti tussi, antovaḷañjanakamanussāpi‘‘ theraṃ nissāya mahādukkhato muttamhā’’ ti tussiṃsu."
485963,110,2341,147,164,1,105,12,‘‘ Therassānubhāvena rañño cūḷāmaṇi laddho’’ ti therassānubhāvo sakalanagare ceva bhikkhusaṅghe ca pākaṭo jāto. 
485964,110,2342,2,27,1,180,19,"Dhammasabhāyaṃ sannisinnā bhikkhū therassa guṇaṃ vaṇṇayiṃsu‘‘ āvuso, ānandatthero attano bahussutatāya paṇḍiccena upāyakusalatāya mahājanaṃ akilametvā upāyeneva rañño maṇiṃ dassesī’’ ti. "
485965,110,2342,28,78,1,269,33,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāni ānandeneva parahatthagataṃ bhaṇḍaṃ dassitaṃ, pubbepi paṇḍitā mahājanaṃ akilametvā upāyeneva tiracchānahatthagataṃ bhaṇḍaṃ dassayiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
485966,110,2343,2,14,1,106,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sabbasippesu nipphattiṃ patto tasseva amacco ahosi. 
485967,110,2343,15,29,1,147,14,Athekadivasaṃ rājā mahantena parivārena uyyānaṃ gantvā vanantarāni vicaritvā udakakīḷaṃ kīḷitukāmo maṅgalapokkharaṇiṃ otaritvā itthāgārampi pakkosi. 
485968,110,2343,30,44,1,156,14,Itthiyo attano attano sīsūpagagīvūpagādīni ābharaṇāni omuñcitvā uttarāsaṅgesu pakkhipitvā samuggapiṭṭhesu ṭhapetvā dāsiyo paṭicchāpetvā pokkharaṇiṃ otariṃsu. 
485969,110,2343,45,76,1,270,29,"Athekā uyyānamakkaṭī sākhantare nisinnā deviṃ piḷandhanāni omuñcitvā uttarāsaṅge pakkhipitvā samuggapiṭṭhe ṭhapayamānaṃ disvā tassā muttāhāraṃ piḷandhitukāmā hutvā dāsiyā pamādaṃ olokayamānā nisīdi, dāsīpi taṃ rakkhamānā tahaṃ tahaṃ oloketvā nisinnāyeva niddāyituṃ ārabhi. "
485970,110,2343,77,101,1,242,24,Makkaṭī tassā pamādabhāvaṃ ñatvā vātavegena otaritvā mahāmuttāhāraṃ gīvāya paṭimuñcitvā vātavegena uppatitvā sākhantare nisīditvā aññāsaṃ makkaṭīnaṃ dassanabhayena ekasmiṃ rukkhasusiraṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā upasantūpasantā viya taṃ rakkhamānā nisīdi. 
485971,110,2344,2,24,1,140,18,Sāpi kho dāsī paṭibujjhitvā muttāhāraṃ apassantī kampamānā aññaṃ upāyaṃ adisvā‘‘ puriso deviyā muttāhāraṃ gahetvā palāto’’ ti mahāviravaṃ viravi. 
485972,110,2344,25,34,1,74,9,Ārakkhamanussā tato tato sannipatitvā tassā vacanaṃ sutvā rañño ārocayiṃsu. 
485973,110,2344,35,44,1,26,5,Rājā‘‘ coraṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti āha. 
485974,110,2344,45,63,1,79,12,"Purisā uyyānā nikkhamitvā‘‘ coraṃ gaṇhatha, coraṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti ito cito ca olokenti. "
485975,110,2344,64,72,1,66,8,Atheko jānapado balikārakapuriso taṃ saddaṃ sutvā kampamāno palāyi. 
485976,110,2344,73,103,1,154,20,"Taṃ disvā rājapurisā‘‘ ayaṃ coro bhavissatī’’ ti anubandhitvā taṃ gahetvā pothetvā‘‘ are, duṭṭhacora, evaṃ mahāsāraṃ nāma piḷandhanaṃ avaharissasī’’ ti paribhāsiṃsu. "
485977,110,2344,104,130,1,113,17,"So cintesi‘‘ sacāhaṃ‘ na gaṇhāmī’ ti vakkhāmi, ajja me jīvitaṃ natthi, pothentāyeva maṃ māressanti, sampaṭicchāmi nan’’ ti. "
485978,110,2344,131,144,1,29,7,"So‘‘ āma, sāmi, gahitaṃ me’’ ti āha. "
485979,110,2344,145,151,1,42,6,Atha naṃ bandhitvā rañño santikaṃ ānayiṃsu. 
485980,110,2344,152,163,1,51,7,Rājāpi naṃ pucchi‘‘ gahitaṃ te mahāsārapiḷandhanan’’ ti?
485981,110,2344,164,173,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, devā’’ ti ."
485982,110,2344,174,182,1,18,4,‘‘ Idāni taṃ kahan’’ ti.
485983,110,2344,183,212,1,150,21,"‘‘ Deva, mayā mahāsāraṃ nāma mañcapīṭhampi na diṭṭhapubbaṃ, seṭṭhi pana maṃ mahāsārapiḷandhanaṃ gaṇhāpesi, sohaṃ taṃ gahetvāva tassa adāsiṃ, so naṃ jānātī’’ ti. "
485984,110,2345,2,16,1,82,10,Rājā seṭṭhiṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ gahitaṃ te imassa hatthato mahāsārapiḷandhanan’’ ti pucchi.
485985,110,2345,17,25,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, devā’’ ti."
485986,110,2345,26,33,1,12,3,‘‘ Kahaṃ tan’’ ti.
485987,110,2345,34,42,1,24,4,‘‘ Purohitassa me dinnan’’ ti. 
485988,110,2345,43,59,1,89,11,"Purohitampi pakkosāpetvā tatheva pucchi, sopi sampaṭicchitvā‘‘ gandhabbassa me dinnan’’ ti āha. "
485989,110,2345,60,73,1,80,9,Tampi pakkosāpetvā‘‘ purohitassa hatthato te mahāsārapiḷandhanaṃ gahitan’’ ti pucchi.
485990,110,2345,74,82,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, devā’’ ti."
485991,110,2345,83,90,1,12,3,‘‘ Kahaṃ tan’’ ti.
485992,110,2345,91,101,1,37,5,‘‘ Kilesavasena me vaṇṇadāsiyā dinnan’’ ti. 
485993,110,2345,102,115,1,46,8,"Tampi pakkosāpetvā pucchi, sā‘‘ na gaṇhāmī’’ ti āha. "
485994,110,2345,116,123,1,49,7,Te pañca jane pucchantānaññeva sūriyo atthaṃ gato. 
485995,110,2345,124,143,1,84,14,"Rājā‘‘ idāni vikālo jāto, sve jānissāmā’’ ti te pañca jane amaccānaṃ datvā nagaraṃ pāvisi. "
485996,110,2346,2,4,1,18,2,Bodhisatto cintesi–
485997,110,2346,5,26,1,145,16,"‘‘ idaṃ piḷandhanaṃ antovaḷañje naṭṭhaṃ, ayañca gahapatiko bahivaḷañjo, dvārepi balavārakkho, tasmā antovaḷañjanakānampi taṃ gahetvā palāyituṃ na sakkā. "
485998,110,2346,27,38,1,77,9,"Evaṃ neva bahivaḷañjanakānaṃ, na anto, uyyāne vaḷañjanakānaṃ gahaṇūpāyo dissati. "
485999,110,2346,39,129,1,567,67,"Iminā duggatamanussena‘ seṭṭhissa me dinnan’ ti kathentena attano mokkhatthāya kathitaṃ bhavissati, seṭṭhināpi‘ purohitassa me dinnan’ ti kathentena‘ ekato hutvā nittharissāmī’ ti cintetvā kathitaṃ bhavissati, purohitenāpi‘ gandhabbassa me dinnan’ ti kathentena‘ bandhanāgāre gandhabbaṃ nissāya sukhena vasissāmā’ ti cintetvā kathitaṃ bhavissati, gandhabbenāpi‘ vaṇṇadāsiyā me dinnan’ ti kathentena‘ ekantena anukkaṇṭhitā bhavissāmā’ ti cintetvā kathitaṃ bhavissati, imehi pañcahipi corehi na bhavitabbaṃ, uyyāne makkaṭā bahū, piḷandhanena ekissā makkaṭiyā hatthe āruḷhena bhavitabban’’ ti. "
486000,110,2346,130,149,1,92,13,"So rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ mahārāja, core amhākaṃ niyyādetha, mayaṃ taṃ kiccaṃ sodhessāmā’’ ti āha. "
486001,110,2346,150,163,1,45,7,"Rājā‘‘ sādhu, paṇḍita, sodhehī’’ ti tassa niyyādesi. "
486002,110,2347,2,32,1,183,25,"Bodhisatto attano dāsapurise pakkosāpetvā te pañca jane ekasmiṃyeva ṭhāne vasāpetvā samantā ārakkhaṃ katvā kaṇṇaṃ datvā‘‘ yaṃ te aññamaññaṃ kathenti, taṃ mayhaṃ ārocethā’’ ti vatvā pakkāmi. "
486003,110,2347,33,36,1,15,3,Te tathā akaṃsu. 
486004,110,2347,37,44,1,59,7,Tato manussānaṃ sannisinnavelāya seṭṭhi taṃ gahapatikaṃ āha–
486005,110,2347,45,70,1,100,16,"‘‘ are, duṭṭhagahapati, tayā ahaṃ, mayā vā tvaṃ kahaṃ diṭṭhapubbo, kadā te mayhaṃ piḷandhanaṃ dinnan’’ ti āha. "
486006,110,2347,71,105,1,156,24,"So‘‘ sāmi mahāseṭṭhi, ahaṃ mahāsāraṃ nāma rukkhasārapādakaṃ mañcapīṭhampi na jānāmi,‘ taṃ nissāya pana mokkhaṃ labhissāmī’ ti evaṃ avacaṃ, mā me kujjha, sāmī’’ ti āha. "
486007,110,2347,106,124,1,87,12,"Purohitopi seṭṭhiṃ āha‘‘ mahāseṭṭhi, tvaṃ iminā attano adinnakameva mayhaṃ kathaṃ adāsī’’ ti?"
486008,110,2347,125,142,1,92,12,"‘‘ Mayampi dve issarā, amhākaṃ ekato hutvā ṭhitakāle kammaṃ khippaṃ nipphajjissatī’’ ti kathesinti. "
486009,110,2347,143,158,1,73,10,"Gandhabbopi purohitaṃ āha‘‘ brāhmaṇa, kadā tayā mayhaṃ piḷandhanaṃ dinnan’’ ti?"
486010,110,2347,159,171,1,60,8,‘‘ Ahaṃ taṃ nissāya vasanaṭṭhāne sukhaṃ vasissāmī’’ ti kathesinti. 
486011,110,2347,172,200,1,150,21,"Vaṇṇadāsīpi gandhabbaṃ āha‘‘ are duṭṭhagandhabba, ahaṃ kadā tava santikaṃ gatapubbā, tvaṃ vā mama santikaṃ āgatapubbo, kadā te mayhaṃ piḷandhanaṃ dinnan’’ ti? "
486012,110,2347,201,221,1,124,14,"Bhagini kiṃkāraṇā kujjhasi,‘‘ amhesu pañcasu ekato vasantesu gharāvāso bhavissati, anukkaṇṭhamānā sukhaṃ vasissāmā’’ ti kathesinti. "
486013,110,2347,222,252,1,264,26,Bodhisatto payojitamanussānaṃ santikā taṃ kathaṃ sutvā tesaṃ tathato acorabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ makkaṭiyā gahitapiḷandhanaṃ upāyeneva pātessāmī’’ ti geṇḍumayāni bahūni piḷandhanāni kāretvā uyyāne makkaṭiyo gāhāpetvā hatthapādagīvāsu geṇḍupiḷandhanāni piḷandhāpetvā vissajjesi. 
486014,110,2347,253,260,1,54,7,Itarā makkaṭī piḷandhanaṃ rakkhamānā uyyāne eva nisīdi. 
486015,110,2348,2,27,1,146,18,"Bodhisatto manusse āṇāpesi‘‘ gacchatha tumhe, uyyāne sabbā makkaṭiyo upadhāretha, yassā taṃ piḷandhanaṃ passatha, taṃ uttāsetvā piḷandhanaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti. "
486016,110,2348,28,55,1,136,18,Tāpi kho makkaṭiyo‘‘ piḷandhanaṃ no laddhan’’ ti tuṭṭhapahaṭṭhā uyyāne vicarantiyo tassā santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ passa amhākaṃ piḷandhanan’’ ti āhaṃsu. 
486017,110,2348,56,70,1,83,10,Sā makkaṭī asahamānā‘‘ kiṃ iminā geṇḍupiḷandhanenā’’ ti muttāhāraṃ piḷandhitvā nikkhami. 
486018,110,2348,71,81,1,78,10,Atha naṃ te purisā disvā piḷandhanaṃ chaḍḍāpetvā āharitvā bodhisattassa adaṃsu. 
486019,110,2348,82,107,1,111,19,"So taṃ ādāya rañño dassetvā‘‘ idaṃ te deva piḷandhanaṃ, te pañcapi acorā, idaṃ pana uyyāne makkaṭiyā ābhatan’’ ti āha."
486020,110,2348,108,127,1,78,12,"‘‘ Kathaṃ pana te, paṇḍita, makkaṭiyā hatthaṃ āruḷhabhāvo ñāto, kathaṃ te gahitan’’ ti? "
486021,110,2348,128,131,1,17,3,So sabbaṃ ācikkhi. 
486022,110,2348,132,150,1,111,13,Rājā tuṭṭhamānaso‘‘ saṅgāmasīsādīsu nāma sūrādayo icchitabbā hontī’’ ti bodhisattassa thutiṃ karonto imaṃ gāthamāha– 
486023,110,2349,2,4,1,0,0,92.
486024,110,2350,2,9,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Ukkaṭṭhe sūramicchanti, mantīsu akutūhalaṃ; "
486025,110,2351,2,12,1,45,7,"Piyañca annapānamhi, atthe jāte ca paṇḍitan’’ ti. "
486026,110,2352,2,12,1,76,8,"Tattha {ukkaṭṭhe}ti upakaṭṭhe, ubhatobyūḷhe saṅgāme sampahāre vattamāneti attho. "
486027,110,2352,13,29,1,122,13,"{Sūramicchantī}ti asaniyāpi matthake patamānāya apalāyinaṃ sūraṃ icchanti, tasmiṃ khaṇe evarūpo saṅgāmayodho patthetabbo hoti. "
486028,110,2352,30,52,1,170,20,"Mantīsu akutūhalan ti kattabbākattabbakiccaṃ sammantanakāle uppanne mantīsu yo akutūhalo avikiṇṇavāco mantaṃ na bhindati, taṃ icchanti, tādiso tesu ṭhānesu patthetabbo hoti. "
486029,110,2352,53,68,1,134,13,"Piyañca {annapānamhī}ti madhure annapāne paccupaṭṭhite sahaparibhuñjanatthāya piyapuggalaṃ patthenti, tādiso tasmiṃ kāle patthetabbo hoti. "
486030,110,2352,69,85,1,124,16,Atthe jāte ca paṇḍitan ti atthagambhīre dhammagambhīre kismiñcideva kāraṇe vā pañhe vā uppanne paṇḍitaṃ vicakkhaṇaṃ icchanti. 
486031,110,2352,86,92,1,45,6,Tathārūpo hi tasmiṃ samaye patthetabbo hotīti. 
486032,110,2353,2,25,1,187,22,"Evaṃ rājā bodhisattaṃ vaṇṇetvā thometvā ghanavassaṃ vassento mahāmegho viya sattāhi ratanehi pūjetvā tassovāde ṭhatvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato, bodhisattopi yathākammaṃ gato. "
486033,110,2354,2,11,1,78,9,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā therassa guṇaṃ kathetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
486034,110,2354,12,26,1,58,9,"‘‘ tadā rājā ānando ahosi, paṇḍitāmacco pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
486035,110,2355,2,4,1,28,2,Mahāsārajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
486036,110,2357,2,7,1,27,2,[ 93]3. Vissāsabhojanajātakavaṇṇanā 
486037,110,2358,2,14,1,86,10,Na vissase {avissatthe}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto vissāsabhojanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486038,110,2358,15,42,1,138,18,"Tasmiṃ kira samaye yebhuyyena bhikkhū‘‘ mātarā no dinnaṃ, pitarā no dinnaṃ, bhātarā, bhaginiyā, cūḷamātarā, cūḷapitarā, mātulena, mātulāniyā dinnaṃ. "
486039,110,2358,43,60,1,132,15,Amhākaṃ gihikālepi bhikkhukālepi ete dātuṃ yuttarūpāvā’’ ti ñātīhi dinne cattāro paccaye vissatthā hutvā apaccavekkhitvā paribhuñjanti. 
486040,110,2358,61,92,1,198,23,"Satthā taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā‘‘ bhikkhūnaṃ mayā dhammadesanaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti bhikkhū sannipātāpetvā‘‘ bhikkhave, bhikkhunā nāma ñātīhipi aññātīhipi dinnake cattāro paccaye paccavekkhitvāva paribhogo kātabbo. "
486041,110,2358,93,107,1,142,13,"Apaccavekkhitvā paribhogaṃ katvā hi kālaṃ kurumāno bhikkhu yakkhapetaattabhāvato na muccati, apaccavekkhitaparibhogo nāmesa visaparibhogasadiso. "
486042,110,2358,108,114,1,65,6,Visañhi vissāsikena dinnakampi avissāsikena dinnakampi māretiyeva. 
486043,110,2358,115,128,1,86,11,Pubbepi vissāsena dinnaṃ visaṃ paribhuñjitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pattā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. 
486044,110,2359,2,12,1,80,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto mahāvibhavo seṭṭhi ahosi. 
486045,110,2359,13,25,1,106,12,Tasseko gopālako kiṭṭhasambādhasamaye gāvo gahetvā araññaṃ pavisitvā tattha gosālaṃ katvā rakkhanto vasati. 
486046,110,2359,26,32,1,40,6,Seṭṭhino ca kālena kālaṃ gorasaṃ āharati. 
486047,110,2359,33,39,1,43,6,Athassa gosālāya avidūre sīho nivāsaṃ gaṇhi. 
486048,110,2359,40,46,1,51,6,Gāvīnaṃ sīhasantāsena milātānaṃ khīraṃ mandaṃ ahosi. 
486049,110,2359,47,69,1,95,16,"Atha naṃ ekadivasaṃ sappiṃ ādāya āgataṃ seṭṭhi pucchi‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, samma gopālaka, mandaṃ sappī’’ ti? "
486050,110,2359,70,74,1,22,4,So taṃ kāraṇaṃ ācikkhi.
486051,110,2359,75,89,1,53,8,"‘‘ Atthi pana, samma, tassa sīhassa katthaci paṭibandho’’ ti?"
486052,110,2359,90,102,1,52,7,"‘‘ Atthissa sāmi, ekāya migamātukāya saddhiṃ saṃsaggo’’ ti."
486053,110,2359,103,112,1,27,5,‘‘ Sakkā pana taṃ gāhāpetun’’ ti?
486054,110,2359,113,121,1,13,3,"‘‘ Sakkā, sāmī’’ ti."
486055,110,2359,122,152,1,210,27,"‘‘ Tena hi taṃ gahetvā tassā nalāṭato paṭṭhāya sarīre lomāni visena punappunaṃ rajitvā sukkhāpetvā dve tayo divase atikkāmetvā taṃ migamātukaṃ vissajjehi, so tassā sinehena sarīraṃ lehitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇissati. "
486056,110,2359,153,166,1,98,11,Athassa cammanakhadāṭhā ceva vasañca maṃsañca gahetvā āgaccheyyāsī’’ ti halāhalavisaṃ datvā uyyojesi. 
486057,110,2360,2,13,1,71,10,So gopālako jālaṃ khipitvā upāyena taṃ migamātukaṃ gaṇhitvā tathā akāsi. 
486058,110,2360,14,23,1,74,9,Sīho taṃ disvāva balavasinehena tassā sarīraṃ lehitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇi. 
486059,110,2360,24,30,1,59,6,Gopālakopi cammādīni gahetvā bodhisattassa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
486060,110,2360,31,66,1,250,30,"Bodhisatto taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā‘‘ paresu sineho nāma na kātabbo, evaṃ balasampannopi sīho migarājā kilesavasena saṃsaggaṃ nissāya migamātukāya sarīraṃ lehanto visaparibhogaṃ katvā jīvitakkhayaṃ patto’’ ti vatvā sampattaparisāya dhammaṃ desento imaṃ gāthamāha– "
486061,110,2361,2,4,1,0,0,93.
486062,110,2362,2,12,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Na vissase avissatthe, vissatthepi na vissase; "
486063,110,2363,2,10,1,42,5,"Vissāsā bhayamanveti, sīhaṃva migamātukā’’ ti. "
486064,110,2364,2,29,1,173,22,"Tatrāyaṃ saṅkhepattho– yo pubbe sabhayo attani avissattho ahosi, tasmiṃ avissatthe, yo pubbepi nibbhayo attani vissāsikoyeva, tasmiṃ vissatthepi na vissase, neva vissāsaṃ kareyya. "
486065,110,2364,30,31,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
486066,110,2364,32,44,1,76,10,"Vissāsā bhayamanveti, yo hi mittepi amittepi vissāso, tato bhayameva āgacchati. "
486067,110,2364,45,46,1,6,1,Kathaṃ? 
486068,110,2364,47,62,1,128,13,"Sīhaṃva migamātukā, yathā mittasanthavavasena katavissāsāya migamātukāya santikā sīhassa bhayaṃ anveti, upagataṃ sampattanti attho. "
486069,110,2364,63,71,1,64,8,Yathā vā vissāsavasena sīhaṃ migamātukā anvetā upagatātipi attho. 
486070,110,2365,2,13,1,88,10,Evaṃ bodhisatto sampattaparisāya dhammaṃ desetvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
