486106,110,2378,9,20,1,39,7,‘‘ ahaṃ tena samayena so ājīvako ahosin’’ ti. 
486107,110,2379,2,4,1,31,2,Lomahaṃsajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
486108,110,2381,2,7,1,26,2,[ 95]5. Mahāsudassanajātakavaṇṇanā 
486109,110,2382,2,34,1,147,16,"Aniccā vata {saṅkhārā}ti idaṃ satthā parinibbānamañce nipanno ānandattherassa‘‘ mā, bhante, bhagavā imasmiṃ khuddakanagarake’’ tyādivacanaṃ( dī. ni.2.210) ārabbha kathesi. "
486110,110,2382,35,48,1,154,12,"Tathāgate hi jetavane viharante sāriputtatthero kattikapuṇṇamāyaṃ nāḷakagāmake jātovarake parinibbāyi, mahāmoggallāno kattikamāsasseva kāḷapakkhaamāvasiyaṃ. "
486111,110,2382,49,70,1,178,17,Evaṃ parinibbute aggasāvakayuge‘‘ ahampi kusinārāyaṃ parinibbāyissāmī’’ ti anupubbena cārikaṃ caramāno tattha gantvā yamakasālānamantare uttarasīsake mañcake anuṭṭhānaseyyāya nipajji. 
486112,110,2382,71,100,1,206,21,"Atha naṃ āyasmā ānandatthero‘‘ mā, bhante, bhagavā imasmiṃ khuddakanagarake visame ujjaṅgalanagarake, sākhānagarake parinibbāyi, aññesaṃ campārājagahādīnaṃ mahānagarānaṃ aññatarasmiṃ bhagavā parinibbāyatū’’ ti yāci. "
486113,110,2382,101,153,1,287,30,"Satthā‘‘ mā, ānanda, imaṃ‘ khuddakanagarakaṃ, ujjaṅgalanagarakaṃ sākhānagarakan’ ti vadehi, ahañhi pubbe sudassanacakkavattirājakāle imasmiṃ nagare vasiṃ, tadā idaṃ dvādasayojanikena ratanapākārena parikkhittaṃ mahānagaraṃ ahosī’’ ti vatvā therena yācito atītaṃ āharanto mahāsudassanasuttaṃ( dī. ni.2.241 ādayo) kathesi. "
486114,110,2383,2,82,1,445,55,"Tadā pana mahāsudassanaṃ sudhammapāsādā otaritvā avidūre sattaratanamaye tālavane paññattasmiṃ kappiyamañcake dakkhiṇena passena anuṭṭhānaseyyāya nipannaṃ disvā‘‘ imāni te, deva, caturāsīti nagarasahassāni kusāvatirājadhānippamukhāni, ettha chandaṃ karohī’’ ti subhaddāya deviyā vutte mahāsudassano‘‘ mā devi evaṃ avaca, atha kho‘ ettha chandaṃ vinehi, mā apekkhaṃ akāsī’ ti evaṃ maṃ ovadā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kiṃkāraṇā, devā’’ ti pucchito‘‘ ajjāhaṃ kālakiriyaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
486115,110,2383,83,96,1,84,12,Atha naṃ devī rodamānā akkhīni puñchitvā kicchena kasirena tathā vatvā rodi paridevi. 
486116,110,2383,97,101,1,51,4,Sesāpi caturāsītisahassaitthiyo rodiṃsu parideviṃsu. 
486117,110,2383,102,109,1,55,6,"Amaccādīsupi ekopi adhivāsetuṃ nāsakkhi, sabbepi rodiṃsu. "
486118,110,2383,110,135,1,103,16,"Bodhisatto‘‘ alaṃ, bhaṇe, mā saddamakatthā’’ ti sabbe nivāretvā deviṃ āmantetvā‘‘ mā tvaṃ devi rodi, mā paridevi. "
