486140,110,2393,2,18,1,156,16,Samatittikaṃ anavasesakan ti idaṃ satthā sumbharaṭṭhe sedakaṃ nāma nigamaṃ upanissāya aññatarasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe viharanto janapadakalyāṇisuttaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486141,110,2393,19,22,1,16,3,Tatra hi bhagavā–
486142,110,2394,2,29,1,167,18,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave,‘ janapadakalyāṇī janapadakalyāṇī’ ti kho, bhikkhave, mahājanakāyo sannipateyya, sā kho panassa janapadakalyāṇī paramapāsāvinī nacce, paramapāsāvinī gīte."
486143,110,2394,30,43,1,89,9,"‘ Janapadakalyāṇī naccati gāyatī’ ti kho, bhikkhave, bhiyyosomattāya mahājanakāyo sannipateyya. "
486144,110,2394,44,51,1,70,7,Atha puriso āgaccheyya jīvitukāmo amaritukāmo sukhakāmo dukkhapaṭikūlo. 
486145,110,2394,52,94,1,260,32,"Tamenaṃ evaṃ vadeyya‘‘ ayaṃ te, ambho purisa, samatittiko telapatto antarena ca mahājanakāyassa antarena ca janapadakalyāṇiyā pariharitabbo, puriso ca taṃ ukkhittāsiko piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandhissati‘ yattheva naṃ thokampi chaḍḍessasi, tattheva te sīsaṃ pātessāmī’’’ ti."
