486177,110,2399,36,60,1,173,19,Iti bhagavā‘‘ kāyagatāsatiṃ bhāvetukāmena bhikkhunā telapattahatthena tena purisena viya satiṃ avissajjetvā appamattena kāyagatāsati bhāvetabbā’’ ti imaṃ suttaṃ āharitvā dassesi. 
