486214,110,2404,2,21,1,113,13,"Athekā yakkhinī‘‘ atikharamanto vatāyaṃ, ahaṃ taṃ khāditvāva nivattissāmī’’ ti bodhisattassa pacchato pacchato agamāsi. "
