486224,110,2404,154,163,1,80,9,Sā bodhisattassa tejena pavisituṃ asakkontī dibbarūpaṃ māpetvā sālādvāre aṭṭhāsi. 
486225,110,2405,2,24,1,141,16,"Tasmiṃ samaye takkasilarājā uyyānaṃ gacchanto taṃ disvā paṭibaddhacitto hutvā‘‘ gaccha, imissā sassāmikaassāmikabhāvaṃ jānāhī’’ ti manussaṃ pesesi. "
486226,110,2405,25,35,1,42,6,So taṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ sassāmikāsī’’ ti pucchi.
486227,110,2405,36,50,1,41,8,"‘‘ Āma, ayya, ayaṃ me sālāya nisinno sāmiko’’ ti. "
486228,110,2405,51,70,1,82,13,"Bodhisatto‘‘ nesā mayhaṃ pajāpati, yakkhinī esā, etāya me pañca manussā khāditā’’ ti āha. "
486229,110,2405,71,87,1,64,11,"Sāpi‘‘ purisā nāma ayyā kuddhakāle yaṃ icchanti, taṃ vadantī’’ ti āha. "
486230,110,2405,88,93,1,35,5,So ubhinnampi vacanaṃ rañño ārocesi. 
486231,110,2405,94,116,1,170,18,Rājā‘‘ assāmikabhaṇḍaṃ nāma rājasantakaṃ hotī’’ ti yakkhiniṃ pakkosāpetvā ekahatthipiṭṭhe nisīdāpetvā nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pāsādaṃ abhiruyha taṃ aggamahesiṭṭhāne ṭhapesi. 
486232,110,2406,2,8,1,56,6,So nhātavilitto sāyamāsaṃ bhuñjitvā sirīsayanaṃ abhiruhi. 
486233,110,2406,9,29,1,187,20,Sāpi yakkhinī attano upakappanakaṃ āhāraṃ āharitvā alaṅkatapaṭiyattā sirisayane raññā saddhiṃ nipajjitvā rañño rativasena sukhaṃ samappitassa nipannakāle ekena passena parivattitvā parodi. 
486234,110,2406,30,44,1,41,8,"Atha naṃ rājā‘‘ kiṃ, bhadde, rodasī’’ ti pucchi."
486235,110,2406,45,92,1,258,39,"‘‘ Deva, ahaṃ tumhehi magge disvā ānītā, tumhākañca gehe bahū itthiyo, ahaṃ sapattīnaṃ antare vasamānā kathāya uppannāya‘ ko tuyhaṃ mātaraṃ vā pitaraṃ vā gottaṃ vā jātiṃ vā jānāti, tvaṃ antarāmagge disvā ānītā nāmā’ ti sīse gahetvā nippīḷiyamānā viya maṅku bhavissāmi. "
486236,110,2406,93,112,1,113,15,"Sace tumhe sakalarajje issariyañca āṇañca mayhaṃ dadeyyātha, koci mayhaṃ cittaṃ kopetvā kathetuṃ na sakkhissatī’’ ti ."
486237,110,2406,113,126,1,67,9,"‘‘ Bhadde, mayhaṃ sakalaraṭṭhavāsino na kiñci honti, nāhaṃ etesaṃ sāmiko. "
486238,110,2406,127,136,1,62,8,"Ye pana rājāṇaṃ kopetvā akattabbaṃ karonti, tesaññevāhaṃ sāmiko. "
486239,110,2406,137,152,1,84,13,Iminā kāraṇena na sakkā tuyhaṃ sakalaraṭṭhe vā nagare vā issariyañca āṇañca dātun’’ ti.
486240,110,2406,153,182,1,137,21,"‘‘ Tena hi, deva, sace raṭṭhe vā nagare vā āṇaṃ dātuṃ na sakkotha, antonivesane antovaḷañjanakānaṃ upari mama vasaṃ vattanatthāya āṇaṃ dethā’’ ti. "
486241,110,2406,183,211,1,152,20,"Rājā dibbaphoṭṭhabbena baddho tassā vacanaṃ atikkamituṃ asakkonto‘‘ sādhu, bhadde, antovaḷañjanakesu tuyhaṃ āṇaṃ dammi, tvaṃ ete attano vase vattāpehī’’ ti āha. "
486242,110,2406,212,249,1,295,32,"Sā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā rañño niddaṃ okkantakāle yakkhanagaraṃ gantvā yakkhe pakkositvā attanā rājānaṃ jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā aṭṭhimattaṃ sesetvā sabbaṃ nhārucammamaṃsalohitaṃ khādi, avasesā yakkhā mahādvārato paṭṭhāya antonivesane kukkuṭakukkure ādiṃ katvā sabbe khāditvā aṭṭhimattasese akaṃsu. "
486243,110,2407,2,32,1,195,25,"Punadivase dvāraṃ yathāpihitameva disvā manussā pharasūhi kavāṭāni koṭṭetvā anto pavisitvā sabbaṃ nivesanaṃ aṭṭhikaparikiṇṇaṃ disvā‘‘ saccaṃ vata so puriso āha‘ nāyaṃ mayhaṃ pajāpati, yakkhinī esā’ ti. "
486244,110,2407,33,55,1,127,19,"Rājā pana kiñci ajānitvā taṃ gahetvā attano bhariyaṃ akāsi, sā yakkhe pakkositvā sabbaṃ janaṃ khāditvā gatā bhavissatī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
486245,110,2407,56,71,1,141,15,Bodhisattopi taṃ divasaṃ tassāyeva sālāyaṃ parittavālukaṃ sīse katvā parittasuttañca parikkhipitvā khaggaṃ gahetvā ṭhitakova aruṇaṃ uṭṭhāpesi. 
486246,110,2407,72,126,1,411,46,"Manussā sakalarājanivesanaṃ sodhetvā haritūpalittaṃ katvā upari gandhehi vilimpitvā pupphāni vikiritvā pupphadāmāni osāretvā dhūmaṃ datvā navamālā bandhitvā sammantayiṃsu‘‘ ambho, yo puriso dibbarūpaṃ māpetvā pacchato āgacchantiṃ yakkhiniṃ indriyāni bhinditvā olokanamattampi na akāsi, so ativiya uḷārasatto dhitimā ñāṇasampanno, tādise purise rajjaṃ anusāsante sabbaraṭṭhaṃ sukhitaṃ bhavissati, taṃ rājānaṃ karomā’’ ti. "
486247,110,2407,127,155,1,185,23,"Atha sabbe amaccā ca nāgarā ca ekacchandā hutvā bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ deva, tumhe imaṃ rajjaṃ kārethā’’ ti nagaraṃ pavesetvā ratanarāsimhi ṭhapetvā abhisiñcitvā takkasilarājānaṃ akaṃsu. "
