486299,110,2446,2,7,1,23,2,[ 97]7. Nāmasiddhijātakavaṇṇanā 
486300,110,2447,2,16,1,98,12,Jīvakañca mataṃ {disvā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ nāmasiddhikaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486301,110,2447,17,23,1,37,6,Eko kira kulaputto nāmena pāpako nāma. 
486302,110,2447,24,61,1,193,24,"So sāsane uraṃ datvā pabbajito bhikkhūhi ‘‘ ehāvuso, pāpaka, tiṭṭhāvuso, pāpakā’’ ti vuccamāno cintesi‘‘ loke pāpakaṃ nāma lāmakaṃ kāḷakaṇṇibhūtaṃ vuccati, aññaṃ maṅgalapaṭisaṃyuttaṃ nāmaṃ āharāpessāmī’’ ti. "
486303,110,2447,62,81,1,94,13,"So ācariyupajjhāye upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ bhante, mayhaṃ nāmaṃ avamaṅgalaṃ, aññaṃ me nāmaṃ karothā’’ ti āha. "
486304,110,2447,82,86,1,22,4,Atha naṃ te evamāhaṃsu–
486305,110,2447,87,108,1,101,14,"‘‘ āvuso, nāmaṃ nāma paṇṇattimattaṃ, nāmena kāci atthasiddhi nāma natthi, attano nāmeneva santuṭṭho hohī’’ ti. "
486306,110,2447,109,112,1,22,3,So punappunaṃ yāciyeva. 
486307,110,2447,113,118,1,52,5,Tassāyaṃ nāmasiddhikabhāvo bhikkhusaṅghe pākaṭo jāto. 
486308,110,2447,119,139,1,134,15,"Athekadivasaṃ dhammasabhāyaṃ sannisinnā bhikkhū kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, asuko kira bhikkhu nāmasiddhiko maṅgalaṃ nāmaṃ āharāpetī’’ ti. "
486309,110,2447,140,183,1,185,26,"Atha satthā dhammasabhaṃ āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, so idāneva, pubbepi nāmasiddhikoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
486310,110,2448,2,13,1,90,10,Atīte takkasilāyaṃ bodhisatto disāpāmokkho ācariyo hutvā pañca māṇavakasatāni mante vācesi. 
486311,110,2448,14,19,1,33,5,Tasseko māṇavo pāpako nāma nāmena. 
486312,110,2448,20,47,1,99,15,"So‘‘ ehi, pāpaka, yāhi, pāpakā’’ ti vuccamāno cintesi‘‘ mayhaṃ nāmaṃ avamaṅgalaṃ, aññaṃ nāmaṃ āharāpessāmī’’ ti. "
486313,110,2448,48,67,1,88,13,"So ācariyaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ ācariya, mayhaṃ nāmaṃ avamaṅgalaṃ, aññaṃ me nāmaṃ karothā’’ ti āha. "
486314,110,2448,68,97,1,163,22,"Atha naṃ ācariyo avoca‘‘ gaccha, tāta, janapadacārikaṃ caritvā attano abhirucitaṃ ekaṃ maṅgalanāmaṃ gahetvā ehi, āgatassa te nāmaṃ parivattetvā aññaṃ nāmaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
486315,110,2448,98,114,1,80,12,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti pātheyyaṃ gahetvā nikkhanto gāmena gāmaṃ caranto ekaṃ nagaraṃ pāpuṇi. 
486316,110,2448,115,122,1,46,7,Tattha ceko puriso kālakato jīvako nāma nāmena. 
486317,110,2448,123,139,1,74,12,So taṃ ñātijanena āḷāhanaṃ nīyamānaṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ nāmako esa puriso’’ ti pucchi.
486318,110,2448,140,147,1,16,3,‘‘ Jīvako nāmeso’’ ti.
486319,110,2448,148,155,1,18,3,‘‘ Jīvakopi maratī’’ ti?
486320,110,2448,156,174,1,77,11,"‘‘ Jīvakopi marati, ajīvakopi marati, nāmaṃ nāma paṇṇattimattaṃ, tvaṃ bālo maññe’’ ti. "
486321,110,2448,175,184,1,59,9,So taṃ kathaṃ sutvā nāme majjhatto hutvā antonagaraṃ pāvisi. 
486322,110,2449,2,23,1,107,15,"Athekaṃ dāsiṃ bhatiṃ adadamānaṃ sāmikā dvāre nisīdāpetvā rajjuyā paharanti, tassā ca‘‘ dhanapālī’’ ti nāmaṃ hoti. "
486323,110,2449,24,40,1,79,11,So antaravīthiyā gacchanto taṃ pothiyamānaṃ disvā‘‘ kasmā imaṃ pothethā’’ ti pucchi.
486324,110,2449,41,50,1,26,5,‘‘ Bhatiṃ dātuṃ na sakkotī’’ ti.
486325,110,2449,51,59,1,20,4,‘‘ Kiṃ panassā nāman’’ ti?
486326,110,2449,60,67,1,17,3,‘‘ Dhanapālī nāmā’’ ti. 
486327,110,2449,68,87,1,143,17,"Nāmena dhanapālī samānāpi bhatimattaṃ dātuṃ na sakkotīti dhanapāliyopi adhanapāliyopi duggatā honti, nāmaṃ nāma paṇṇattimattaṃ, tvaṃ bālo maññeti. "
486328,110,2449,88,109,1,134,17,So nāme majjhattataro hutvā nagarā nikkhamma maggaṃ paṭipanno antarāmagge maggamūḷhapurisaṃ disvā‘‘ ambho kiṃ karonto vicarasī’’ ti pucchi.
486329,110,2449,110,118,1,21,3,"‘‘ Maggamūḷhomhi, sāmī’’ ti."
486330,110,2449,119,128,1,20,5,‘‘ Kiṃ pana te nāman’’ ti?
486331,110,2449,129,136,1,16,3,‘‘ Panthako nāmā’’ ti.
486332,110,2449,137,145,1,29,4,‘‘ Panthakopi maggamūḷho hotī’’ ti?
486333,110,2449,146,162,1,87,11,"‘‘ Panthakopi apanthakopi maggamūḷho hoti, nāmaṃ nāma paṇṇattimattaṃ tvaṃ pana bālo maññeti’’. "
486334,110,2449,163,212,1,283,35,"So nāme atimajjhatto hutvā bodhisattassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ kiṃ, tāta, nāmaṃ rocetvā āgatosī’’ ti vutte‘‘ ācariya, jīvakāpi nāma maranti ajīvakāpi, dhanapāliyopi duggatā honti adhanapāliyopi, panthakāpi maggamūḷhā honti apanthakāpi, nāmaṃ nāma paṇṇattimattaṃ, nāmena siddhi natthi, kammeneva siddhi. "
486335,110,2449,213,226,1,53,10,"Alaṃ mayhaṃ aññena nāmena, tadeva me nāmaṃ hotū’’ ti āha. "
486336,110,2449,227,234,1,60,7,Bodhisatto tena diṭṭhañca katañca saṃsandetvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
486337,110,2450,2,4,1,0,0,97.
486338,110,2451,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Jīvakañca mataṃ disvā, dhanapāliñca duggataṃ; "
486339,110,2452,2,11,1,44,6,"Panthakañca vane mūḷhaṃ, pāpako punarāgato’’ ti. "
486340,110,2453,2,15,1,82,11,"Tattha {punarāgato}ti imāni tīṇi kāraṇāni disvā puna āgato, ra-kāro sandhivasena vutto. "
486341,110,2454,2,22,1,111,13,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa nāmasiddhikoyevā’’ ti vatvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
486342,110,2454,23,40,1,100,11,"‘‘ tadā nāmasiddhiko idānipi nāmasiddhikoyeva, ācariyaparisā buddhaparisā, ācariyo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
486343,110,2455,2,4,1,31,2,Nāmasiddhijātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
486344,110,2457,2,7,1,23,2,[ 98]8. Kūṭavāṇijajātakavaṇṇanā 
486345,110,2458,2,17,1,88,12,Sādhu kho paṇḍito {nāmā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kūṭavāṇijaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486346,110,2458,18,30,1,108,12,Sāvatthiyañhi dve janā ekato vaṇijjaṃ karontā bhaṇḍaṃ sakaṭenādāya janapadaṃ gantvā laddhalābhā paccāgamiṃsu. 
486347,110,2458,31,52,1,161,18,"Tesu kūṭavāṇijo cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ bahū divase dubbhojanena dukkhaseyyāya kilanto, idāni attano ghare nānaggarasehi yāvadatthaṃ subhojanaṃ bhuñjitvā ajīrakena marissati. "
486348,110,2458,53,71,1,102,15,"Athāhaṃ imaṃ bhaṇḍaṃ tayo koṭṭhāse katvā ekaṃ tassa dārakānaṃ dassāmi, dve koṭṭhāse attanā gahessāmī’’ ti. "
486349,110,2458,72,87,1,62,10,"So‘‘ ajja bhājessāma, sve bhājessāmā’’ ti bhaṇḍaṃ bhājetuṃ na icchi. "
486350,110,2458,88,117,1,207,24,"Atha naṃ paṇḍitavāṇijo akāmakaṃ nippīḷetvā bhājāpetvā vihāraṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā katapaṭisanthāro‘‘ atipapañco te kato, idhāgantvāpi cirena buddhupaṭṭhānaṃ āgatosī’’ ti vutte taṃ pavattiṃ bhagavato ārocesi. "
486351,110,2458,118,132,1,66,9,"Satthā‘‘ na kho so, upāsaka, idāneva kūṭavāṇijo, pubbepi kūṭavāṇijoyeva. "
486352,110,2458,133,151,1,97,15,"Idāni pana taṃ vañcetukāmo jāto, pubbe paṇḍitepi vañcetuṃ ussahī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
486353,110,2459,2,23,1,135,15,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto bārāṇasiyaṃ vāṇijakule nibbatti, nāmaggahaṇadivase cassa‘‘ paṇḍito’’ ti nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
486354,110,2459,24,43,1,97,14,"So vayappatto aññena vāṇijena saddhiṃ ekato hutvā vaṇijjaṃ karoti, tassa‘‘ atipaṇḍito’’ ti nāmaṃ ahosi. "
486355,110,2459,44,58,1,116,14,Te bārāṇasito pañcahi sakaṭasatehi bhaṇḍaṃ ādāya janapadaṃ gantvā vaṇijjaṃ katvā laddhalābhā puna bārāṇasiṃ āgamiṃsu. 
486356,110,2459,59,73,1,74,10,Atha nesaṃ bhaṇḍabhājanakāle atipaṇḍito āha‘‘ mayā dve koṭṭhāsā laddhabbā’’ ti.
486357,110,2459,74,80,1,12,2,‘‘ Kiṃkāraṇā’’ ti?
486358,110,2459,81,88,1,28,4,"‘‘ Tvaṃ paṇḍito, ahaṃ atipaṇḍito. "
486359,110,2459,89,99,1,46,7,"Paṇḍito ekaṃ laddhuṃ arahati, atipaṇḍito dve’’ ti."
486360,110,2459,100,118,1,103,13,"‘‘ Nanu amhākaṃ dvinnaṃ bhaṇḍamūlakampi goṇādayopi samasamāyeva, tvaṃ kasmā dve koṭṭhāse laddhuṃ arahasī’’ ti."
486361,110,2459,119,125,1,20,2,‘‘ Atipaṇḍitabhāvenā’’ ti. 
486362,110,2459,126,132,1,39,6,Evaṃ te kathaṃ vaḍḍhetvā kalahaṃ akaṃsu. 
486363,110,2460,2,76,1,372,50,"Tato atipaṇḍito‘‘ attheko upāyo’’ ti cintetvā attano pitaraṃ ekasmiṃ susirarukkhe pavesetvā‘‘ tvaṃ amhesu āgatesu ‘ atipaṇḍito dve koṭṭhāse laddhuṃ arahatī’ ti vadeyyāsī’’ ti vatvā bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ samma, mayhaṃ dvinnaṃ koṭṭhāsānaṃ yuttabhāvaṃ vā ayuttabhāvaṃ vā esā rukkhadevatā jānāti, ehi, taṃ pucchissāmā’’ ti taṃ tattha netvā‘‘ ayye rukkhadevate, amhākaṃ aṭṭaṃ pacchindā’’ ti āha. "
486364,110,2460,77,90,1,55,9,Athassa pitā saraṃ parivattetvā‘‘ tena hi kathethā’’ ti āha.
486365,110,2460,91,100,1,33,5,"‘‘ Ayye, ayaṃ paṇḍito, ahaṃ atipaṇḍito. "
486366,110,2460,101,110,1,53,8,"Amhehi ekato vohāro kato, tattha kena kiṃ laddhabbanti. "
486367,110,2460,111,123,1,66,9,"Paṇḍitena eko koṭṭhāso, atipaṇḍitena pana dve koṭṭhāsā laddhabbā’’ ti. "
486368,110,2460,124,162,1,267,33,"Bodhisatto evaṃ vinicchitaṃ aṭṭaṃ sutvā‘‘ idāni devatābhāvaṃ vā adevatābhāvaṃ vā jānissāmī’’ ti palālaṃ āharitvā susiraṃ pūretvā aggiṃ adāsi, atipaṇḍitassa pitā jālāya phuṭṭhakāle aḍḍhajjhāmena sarīrena upari āruyha sākhaṃ gahetvā olambanto bhūmiyaṃ patitvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
486369,110,2461,2,4,1,0,0,98.
486370,110,2462,2,12,1,42,8,"‘ ‘ Sādhu kho paṇḍito nāma, na tveva atipaṇḍito; "
486371,110,2463,2,10,1,41,5,"Atipaṇḍitena puttena, manamhi upakūḷito’’ ti. "
486372,110,2464,2,16,1,105,13,Tattha sādhu kho paṇḍito {nāmā}ti imasmiṃ loke paṇḍiccena samannāgato kāraṇākāraṇaññū puggalo sādhu sobhano. 
486373,110,2464,17,25,1,61,7,{Atipaṇḍito}ti nāmamattena atipaṇḍito kūṭapuriso na tveva varaṃ. 
486374,110,2464,26,35,1,66,7,"Manamhi {upakūḷito}ti thokenamhi jhāmo, aḍḍhajjhāmakova muttoti attho. "
486375,110,2464,36,45,1,72,9,Te ubhopi majjhe bhinditvā samaññeva koṭṭhāsaṃ gaṇhitvā yathākammaṃ gatā. 
486376,110,2465,2,17,1,77,10,Satthā ‘‘ pubbepi esa kūṭavāṇijoyevā’’ ti imaṃ atītaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
486377,110,2465,18,32,1,81,9,"‘‘ tadā kūṭavāṇijo paccuppannepi kūṭavāṇijoyeva, paṇḍitavāṇijo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
486378,110,2466,2,4,1,31,2,Kūṭavāṇijajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
486379,110,2468,2,7,1,24,2,[ 99]9. Parosahassajātakavaṇṇanā 
486380,110,2469,2,14,1,101,10,Parosahassampi samāgatānan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto puthujjanapucchāpañcakaṃ ārabbha kathesi . 
486381,110,2469,15,29,1,35,4,Vatthu sarabhajātake( jā.1.13.134 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
486382,110,2469,30,54,1,177,19,"Ekasmiṃ pana samaye bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitvā‘‘ āvuso, dasabalena saṃkhittena kathitaṃ dhammasenāpati sāriputto vitthārena byākāsī’’ ti therassa guṇaṃ kathayamānā nisīdiṃsu. "
486383,110,2469,55,101,1,216,29,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, sāriputto idāneva mayā saṃkhittena bhāsitaṃ vitthārena byākaroti, pubbepi byākāsiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
486384,110,2470,2,23,1,218,21,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto udiccabrāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā kāme pahāya isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā pañcābhiññā aṭṭha samāpattiyo nibbattetvā himavante vihāsi. 
486385,110,2470,24,28,1,39,4,Parivāropissa pañca tāpasasatāni ahesuṃ. 
486386,110,2470,29,38,1,108,9,Athassa jeṭṭhantevāsiko vassārattasamaye upaḍḍhaṃ isigaṇaṃ ādāya loṇambilasevanatthāya manussapathaṃ agamāsi. 
486387,110,2470,39,43,1,40,4,Tadā bodhisattassa kālakiriyāsamayo jāto. 
486388,110,2470,44,60,1,72,11,"Atha naṃ antevāsikā‘‘ ācariya, kataro vo guṇo laddho’’ ti adhigamaṃ pucchiṃsu. "
486389,110,2470,61,72,1,53,7,So‘‘ natthi kiñcī’’ ti vatvā ābhassarabrahmaloke nibbatti. 
486390,110,2470,73,81,1,82,8,Bodhisattā hi arūpasamāpattilābhino hutvāpi abhabbaṭṭhānattā āruppe na nibbattanti. 
486391,110,2470,82,95,1,68,9,Antevāsikā‘‘ ācariyassa adhigamo natthī’’ ti āḷāhane sakkāraṃ na kariṃsu. 
486392,110,2471,2,29,1,109,15,Jeṭṭhantevāsiko āgantvā‘‘ kahaṃ ācariyo’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ kālakato’’ ti sutvā‘‘ api ācariyaṃ adhigamaṃ pucchitthā’’ ti āha.
486393,110,2471,30,38,1,16,3,"‘‘ Āma, pucchimhā’’ ti."
486394,110,2471,39,46,1,14,3,‘‘ Kiṃ kathesī’’ ti?
486395,110,2471,47,63,1,67,11,"‘‘ Natthi kiñcīti tena vuttaṃ, athassa amhehi sakkāro na kato’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
486396,110,2471,64,80,1,100,10,"Jeṭṭhantevāsiko‘‘ tumhe ācariyassa vacanatthaṃ na jānātha, ākiñcaññāyatanasamāpattilābhī ācariyo’’ ti āha. "
486397,110,2471,81,87,1,45,6,Te tasmiṃ punappunaṃ kathentepi na saddahiṃsu. 
486398,110,2471,88,100,1,84,10,Bodhisatto taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā‘‘ andhabālā mama jeṭṭhantevāsikassa vacanaṃ na saddahanti. 
486399,110,2471,101,121,1,166,17,Imaṃ tesaṃ kāraṇaṃ pākaṭaṃ karissāmī’’ ti brahmalokā āgantvā assamapadamatthake mahantenānubhāvena ākāse ṭhatvā jeṭṭhantevāsikassa paññānubhāvaṃ vaṇṇento imaṃ gāthamāha– 
486400,110,2472,2,4,1,0,0,99.
486401,110,2473,2,12,1,57,7,"‘ ‘ Parosahassampi samāgatānaṃ, kandeyyuṃ te vassasataṃ apaññā; "
486402,110,2474,2,14,1,59,9,"Ekova seyyo puriso sapañño, yo bhāsitassa vijānāti atthan’’ ti. "
486403,110,2475,2,6,1,41,3,Tattha {parosahassampī}ti atirekasahassampi. 
486404,110,2475,7,15,1,76,8,Samāgatānan ti sannipatitānaṃ bhāsitassa atthaṃ jānituṃ asakkontānaṃ bālānaṃ. 
486405,110,2475,16,42,1,187,24,"Kandeyyuṃ te vassasataṃ {apaññā}ti te evaṃ samāgatā apaññā ime bālatāpasā viya vassasatampi vassasahassampi rodeyyuṃ parideveyyuṃ, rodamānāpi pana atthaṃ vā kāraṇaṃ vā neva jāneyyunti dīpeti. "
486406,110,2475,43,56,1,106,12,Ekova seyyo puriso {sapañño}ti evarūpānaṃ bālānaṃ parosahassatopi eko paṇḍitapurisova seyyo varataroti attho. 
486407,110,2475,57,59,1,16,2,Kīdiso sapaññoti? 
486408,110,2475,60,67,1,57,7,Yo bhāsitassa vijānāti atthaṃ ayaṃ jeṭṭhantevāsiko viyāti. 
486409,110,2476,2,12,1,88,10,Evaṃ mahāsatto ākāse ṭhitova dhammaṃ desetvā tāpasagaṇaṃ bujjhāpetvā brahmalokameva gato. 
486410,110,2476,13,18,1,54,5,Tepi tāpasā jīvitapariyosāne brahmalokaparāyaṇā ahesuṃ. 
486411,110,2477,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
