486467,110,2504,2,14,1,59,9,"Ekova seyyo puriso sapañño, yo bhāsitassa vijānāti atthan’’ ti."
486468,110,2504,15,15,1,0,0,– 
486469,110,2505,2,12,1,84,9,Idaṃ jātakaṃ vatthuto ca veyyākaraṇato ca samodhānato ca parosahassajātakasadisameva. 
