486512,110,2526,7,10,1,21,2,{Nivisatī}ti patiṭṭhāti. 
486513,110,2526,11,30,1,125,17,"Na vase tattha {paṇḍito}ti so verīpuggalo yasmiṃ ṭhāne patiṭṭhito hutvā vasati, tattha paṇḍito paṇḍiccena samannāgato na vaseyya. "
486514,110,2526,31,32,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
