486564,110,2552,2,4,1,34,2,Dubbalakaṭṭhajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
486565,110,2554,2,7,1,21,2,[ 106]6. Udañcanījātakavaṇṇanā 
486566,110,2555,2,14,1,99,12,Sukhaṃ vata maṃ jīvantan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto thullakumārikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486567,110,2555,15,30,1,60,5,Vatthu terasakanipāte cūḷanāradakassapajātake( jā.1.13.40 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
486568,110,2555,31,65,1,138,21,"Taṃ pana bhikkhuṃ satthā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhitosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhagavā’’ ti vutte‘‘ kattha te cittaṃ paṭibaddhan’’ ti pucchi. "
486569,110,2555,66,75,1,33,5,So‘‘ ekissā thullakumārikāyā’’ ti āha. 
486570,110,2555,76,105,1,161,23,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ ayaṃ te bhikkhu anatthakārikā, pubbepi tvaṃ etaṃ nissāya sīlabyasanaṃ patvā kampanto vicaramāno paṇḍite nissāya sukhaṃ labhī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
486571,110,2556,2,11,1,103,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārenteti atītavatthupi cūḷanāradakassapajātakeyeva āvi bhavissati. 
486572,110,2556,12,54,1,265,33,"Tadā pana bodhisatto sāyaṃ phalāphale ādāya āgantvā paṇṇasālādvāraṃ vivaritvā pavisitvā puttaṃ cūḷatāpasaṃ etadavoca‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ aññesu divasesu dārūni āharasi, pānīyaṃ paribhojanīyaṃ āharasi, aggiṃ karosi, ajja pana ekampi akatvā kasmā dummukho pajjhāyanto nipannosī’’ ti?"
486573,110,2556,55,94,1,210,29,"‘‘ Tāta, tumhesu phalāphalatthāya gatesu ekā itthī āgantvā maṃ palobhetvā ādāya gantuṃ ārabhi, ahaṃ pana‘ tumhehi vissajjito gamissāmī’ ti na gacchiṃ, asukaṭṭhāne pana naṃ nisīdāpetvā āgatomhi, idāni gacchāmahaṃ tātā’’ ti. "
486574,110,2556,95,139,1,219,30,"Bodhisatto‘‘ na sakkā etaṃ nivattetun’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ tena hi, tāta, gaccha, esā pana taṃ netvā yadā macchamaṃsādīni vā khāditukāmā bhavissati, sappiloṇataṇḍulādīhi vā panassā attho bhavissati, tadā‘ idañcidañcāharā’ ti taṃ kilamessati. "
486575,110,2556,140,151,1,69,9,Tadā mayhaṃ guṇaṃ saritvā palāyitvā idheva āgaccheyyāsī’’ ti vissajjesi. 
486576,110,2556,152,157,1,37,5,So tāya saddhiṃ manussapathaṃ agamāsi. 
486577,110,2556,158,182,1,103,18,"Atha naṃ sā attano vasaṃ gametvā‘‘ maṃsaṃ āhara, macchaṃ āharā’’ ti yena yena atthikā hoti, taṃ taṃ āharāpeti. "
486578,110,2556,183,209,1,143,22,Tadā so‘‘ ayaṃ maṃ attano dāsaṃ viya kammakāraṃ viya ca katvā pīḷetī’’ ti palāyitvā pitu santikaṃ āgantvā pitaraṃ vanditvā ṭhitakova imaṃ gāthamāha– 
486579,110,2557,2,4,1,0,0,106.
486580,110,2558,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Sukhaṃ vata maṃ jīvantaṃ, pacamānā udañcanī; "
486581,110,2559,2,11,1,42,6,"Corī jāyappavādena, telaṃ loṇañca yācatī’’ ti. "
486582,110,2560,2,15,1,76,12,"Tattha sukhaṃ vata maṃ jīvantan ti tāta, tumhākaṃ santike maṃ sukhaṃ jīvantaṃ. "
486583,110,2560,16,30,1,77,11,"{Pacamānā}ti tāpayamānā pīḷayamānā, yaṃ yaṃ vā khāditukāmā hoti, taṃ taṃ pacamānā. "
486584,110,2560,31,42,1,84,10,"Udakaṃ añcanti etāyāti udañcanī, cāṭito vā kūpato vā udakaussiñcanaghaṭikāyetaṃ nāmaṃ. "
486585,110,2560,43,61,1,92,14,"Sā pana udañcanī viya, udakaṃ viya ghaṭikā, yena yenatthikā hoti, taṃ taṃ ākaḍḍhatiyevāti attho . "
486586,110,2560,62,99,1,212,30,"Corī {jāyappavādenā}ti‘‘ bhariyā’’ ti nāmena ekā corī maṃ madhuravacanena upalāpetvā tattha netvā telaṃ loṇañca yañca aññaṃ icchati, taṃ sabbaṃ yācati, dāsaṃ viya kammakāraṃ viya ca katvā āharāpetīti tassā aguṇaṃ kathesi. "
486587,110,2561,2,29,1,147,19,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto assāsetvā‘‘ hotu, tāta, ehi tvaṃ mettaṃ bhāvehi, karuṇaṃ bhāvehī’’ ti cattāro brahmavihāre ācikkhi, ācikkhitvā kasiṇaparikammaṃ ācikkhi. "
486588,110,2561,30,44,1,108,14,So na cirasseva abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca uppādetvā brahmavihāre bhāvetvā saddhiṃ pitarā brahmaloke nibbatti. 
486589,110,2562,2,16,1,125,13,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne so bhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi."
486590,110,2563,2,9,1,44,5,‘ ‘ Tadā thullakumārikāva etarahi thullakumārikā. 
486591,110,2563,10,21,1,62,8,"Cūḷatāpaso ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu ahosi, pitā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
486592,110,2564,2,4,1,29,2,Udañcanījātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
486593,110,2566,2,7,1,22,2,[ 107]7. Sālittakajātakavaṇṇanā 
486594,110,2567,2,17,1,103,13,Sādhū kho sippakaṃ {nāmā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ haṃsapaharanakaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486595,110,2567,18,25,1,64,7,So kireko sāvatthivāsī kulaputto sālittakasippe nipphattiṃ patto.
486596,110,2567,26,34,1,48,4,‘‘ Sālittakasippan’’ ti sakkharākhipanasippaṃ vuccati. 
486597,110,2567,35,53,1,119,16,"So ekadivasaṃ dhammaṃ sutvā sāsane uraṃ datvā pabbajitvā upasampadaṃ labhi, na pana sikkhākāmo, na paṭipattisādhako ahosi. "
486598,110,2567,54,64,1,83,10,So ekadivasaṃ ekaṃ daharabhikkhuṃ ādāya aciravatiṃ gantvā nhāyitvā nadītīre aṭṭhāsi. 
486599,110,2567,65,71,1,45,6,Tasmiṃ samaye dve setahaṃsā ākāsena gacchanti. 
486600,110,2567,72,88,1,87,12,So taṃ daharaṃ āha‘‘ imaṃ pacchimahaṃsaṃ sakkharāya akkhimhi paharitvā pādamūle pātemī’’ ti. 
486601,110,2567,89,102,1,54,8,"Itaro‘‘ kathaṃ pātessasi, na sakkhissasi paharitun’’ ti āha. "
486602,110,2567,103,118,1,66,10,"Itaro‘‘ tiṭṭhatu tāvassa orato akkhi, parato akkhimhi taṃ paharāmī’’ ti. "
486603,110,2567,119,124,1,33,5,Idāni pana tvaṃ asantaṃ kathesīti.
486604,110,2567,125,144,1,106,14,‘‘ Tena hi upadhārehī’’ ti ekaṃ tikhiṇasakkharaṃ gahetvā aṅguliyā pariyante katvā tassa haṃsassa pacchato khipi. 
486605,110,2567,145,167,1,86,13,"Sā‘‘ run’’ ti saddaṃ akāsi, haṃso‘‘ parissayena bhavitabban’’ ti nivattitvā saddaṃ sotuṃ ārabhi. "
486606,110,2567,168,180,1,99,12,Itaro tasmiṃ khaṇe ekaṃ vaṭṭasakkharaṃ gahetvā tassa nivattitvā olokentassa parabhāge akkhiṃ pahari. 
486607,110,2567,181,186,1,43,5,Sakkharā itarampi akkhiṃ vinivijjhitvā gatā. 
486608,110,2567,187,192,1,41,5,Haṃso mahāravaṃ ravanto pādamūleyeva pati. 
486609,110,2567,193,222,1,135,20,"Tato tato bhikkhū āgantvā garahitvā‘‘ ananucchavikaṃ te katan’’ ti satthu santikaṃ netvā‘‘ bhante, iminā idaṃ nāma katan’’ ti tamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. "
486610,110,2567,223,247,1,120,17,"Satthā taṃ bhikkhuṃ garahitvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevesa etasmiṃ sippe kusalo, pubbepi kusaloyeva ahosī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
486611,110,2568,2,11,1,74,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa amacco ahosi. 
486612,110,2568,12,27,1,103,14,"Tasmiṃ kāle rañño purohito atimukharo hoti bahubhāṇī, tasmiṃ kathetuṃ āraddhe aññe okāsameva na labhanti. "
486613,110,2568,28,42,1,69,10,Rājā cintesi‘‘ kadā nu kho etassa vacanupacchedakaṃ kañci labhissāmī’’ ti. 
486614,110,2568,43,50,1,53,7,So tato paṭṭhāya tathārūpaṃ ekaṃ upadhārento vicarati. 
486615,110,2568,51,60,1,81,9,Tasmiṃ kāle bārāṇasiyaṃ eko pīṭhasappī sakkharākhipanasippe nipphattiṃ patto hoti. 
486616,110,2568,61,90,1,201,21,"Gāmadārakā taṃ rathakaṃ āropetvā ākaḍḍhamānā bārāṇasinagaradvāramūle eko viṭapasampanno mahānigrodho atthi, tattha ānetvā samparivāretvā kākaṇikādīni datvā‘‘ hatthirūpakaṃ kara, assarūpakaṃ karā’’ ti vadanti. "
486617,110,2568,91,103,1,106,11,"So sakkharā khipitvā khipitvā nigrodhapaṇṇesu nānārūpāni dasseti, sabbāni paṇṇāni chiddāvachiddāneva ahesuṃ. "
486618,110,2569,2,9,1,53,7,Atha bārāṇasirājā uyyānaṃ gacchanto taṃ ṭhānaṃ pāpuṇi. 
486619,110,2569,10,18,1,66,7,"Ussāraṇābhayena sabbe dārakā palāyiṃsu, pīṭhasappī tattheva nipajji. "
486620,110,2569,19,43,1,162,20,Rājā nigrodhamūlaṃ patvā rathe nisinno pattānaṃ chiddatāya chāyaṃ kabarakabaraṃ disvā olokento sabbesaṃ pattānaṃ chiddabhāvaṃ disvā‘‘ kenetāni evaṃ katānī’’ ti pucchi.
486621,110,2569,44,52,1,20,3,"‘‘ Pīṭhasappinā, devā’’ ti. "
486622,110,2569,53,78,1,113,15,"Rājā‘‘ imaṃ nissāya brāhmaṇassa vacanupacchedaṃ kātuṃ sakkā bhavissatī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ kahaṃ, bhaṇe, pīṭhasappī’’ ti pucchi. "
486623,110,2569,79,92,1,54,8,"Vicinantā mūlantare nipannaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ, devā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
486624,110,2569,93,114,1,123,16,"Rājā naṃ pakkosāpetvā parisaṃ ussāretvā pucchi‘‘ amhākaṃ santike eko mukharabrāhmaṇo atthi, sakkhissasi taṃ nissaddaṃ kātun’’ ti. "
486625,110,2569,115,121,1,48,5,"Nāḷimattā ajalaṇḍikā labhanto sakkhissāmi, devāti. "
486626,110,2569,122,150,1,260,27,Rājā pīṭhasappiṃ gharaṃ netvā antosāṇiyaṃ nisīdāpetvā sāṇiyaṃ chiddaṃ kāretvā brāhmaṇassa chiddābhimukhaṃ āsanaṃ paññapetvā nāḷimattā sukkhā ajalaṇḍikā pīṭhasappissa santike ṭhapāpetvā brāhmaṇaṃ upaṭṭhānakāle āgataṃ tasmiṃ āsane nisīdāpetvā kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesi. 
486627,110,2569,151,159,1,60,8,Brāhmaṇo aññesaṃ okāsaṃ adatvā raññā saddhiṃ kathetuṃ ārabhi. 
486628,110,2569,160,183,1,184,21,"Athassa so pīṭhasappī sāṇicchiddena ekekaṃ ajalaṇḍikaṃ pacchiyaṃ pavesento viya tālutalamhiyeva pāteti, brāhmaṇo āgatāgataṃ nāḷiyaṃ telaṃ pavesento viya gilati, sabbā parikkhayaṃ gamiṃsu. "
486629,110,2569,184,191,1,68,7,Tassetā nāḷimattā ajalaṇḍikā kucchiṃ paviṭṭhā aḍḍhāḷhakamattā ahesuṃ. 
486630,110,2570,2,7,1,37,5,Rājā tāsaṃ parikkhīṇabhāvaṃ ñatvā āha–
486631,110,2570,8,27,1,117,15,"‘‘ ācariya, tumhe atimukharatāya nāḷimattā ajalaṇḍikā gilantā kiñci na jānittha, ito dāni uttari jīrāpetuṃ na sakkhissatha. "
486632,110,2570,28,50,1,152,18,"Gacchatha, piyaṅgudakaṃ pivitvā chaḍḍetvā attānaṃ arogaṃ karothā’’ ti brāhmaṇo tato paṭṭhāya pihitamukho viya hutvā kathentenāpi saddhiṃ akathanasīlo ahosi. "
486633,110,2570,51,68,1,101,13,Rājā‘‘ iminā me kaṇṇasukhaṃ katan’’ ti pīṭhasappissa satasahassuṭṭhānake catūsu disāsu cattāro gāme adāsi. 
486634,110,2570,69,93,1,154,18,"Bodhisatto rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ deva, sippaṃ nāma loke paṇḍitehi uggahitabbaṃ, pīṭhasappinā sālittakamattenāpi ayaṃ sampatti laddhā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
486635,110,2571,2,4,1,0,0,107.
486636,110,2572,2,13,1,43,8,"‘ ‘ Sādhuṃ kho sippakaṃ nāma, api yādisa kīdisaṃ; "
486637,110,2573,2,11,1,46,6,"Passa khañjappahārena, laddhā gāmā catuddisā’’ ti. "
486638,110,2574,2,24,1,179,18,"Tattha passa {khañjappahārenā}ti passa, mahārāja, iminā khañjapīṭhasappinā ajalaṇḍikāpahārena catuddisā cattāro gāmā laddhā, aññesaṃ sippānaṃ ko ānisaṃsaparicchedoti sippaguṇaṃ kathesi. "
486639,110,2575,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
486640,110,2575,9,27,1,82,12,"‘‘ tadā pīṭhasappī ayaṃ bhikkhu ahosi, rājā ānando, paṇḍitāmacco pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
486641,110,2576,2,4,1,30,2,Sālittakajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
486642,110,2578,2,7,1,19,2,[ 108]8. Bāhiyajātakavaṇṇanā 
486643,110,2579,2,17,1,122,13,Sikkheyya {sikkhitabbānī}ti idaṃ satthā vesāliṃ upanissāya mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ viharanto ekaṃ licchaviṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486644,110,2579,18,30,1,113,12,So kira licchavirājā saddho pasanno buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ nimantetvā attano nivesane mahādānaṃ pavattesi. 
486645,110,2579,31,37,1,80,6,Bhariyā panassa thūlaṅgapaccaṅgā uddhumātakanimittasadisā anākappasampannā ahosi. 
486646,110,2579,38,49,1,99,11,Satthā bhattakiccāvasāne anumodanaṃ katvā vihāraṃ gantvā bhikkhūnaṃ ovādaṃ datvā gandhakuṭiṃ pāvisi. 
486647,110,2579,50,76,1,177,20,"Bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, tassa nāma licchavirañño tāva abhirūpassa tādisā bhariyā thūlaṅgapaccaṅgā anākappasampannā, kathaṃ so tāya saddhiṃ abhiramatī’’ ti. "
486648,110,2579,77,124,1,206,30,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, esa idāneva, pubbepi thūlasarīrāya eva itthiyā saddhiṃ abhiramī’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
486649,110,2580,2,12,1,74,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa amacco ahosi. 
486650,110,2580,13,32,1,216,19,Athekā janapaditthī thūlasarīrā anākappasampannā bhatiṃ kurumānā rājaṅgaṇassa avidūrena gacchamānā sarīravaḷañjapīḷitā hutvā nivatthasāṭakena sarīraṃ paṭicchādetvā nisīditvā sarīravaḷañjaṃ muñcitvā khippameva uṭṭhāsi. 
486651,110,2580,33,87,1,385,45,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe bārāṇasirājā vātapānena rājaṅgaṇaṃ olokento taṃ disvā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ evarūpe aṅgaṇaṭṭhāne sarīravaḷañjaṃ muñcamānā hirottappaṃ appahāya nivāsaneneva paṭicchannā hutvā sarīravaḷañjaṃ mocetvā khippaṃ uṭṭhitā, imāya nirogāya bhavitabbaṃ, etissā vatthu visadaṃ bhavissati, visade pana vatthusmiṃ eko putto labbhamāno visado puññavā bhavissati, imaṃ mayā aggamahesiṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
486652,110,2580,88,95,1,68,7,So tassā apariggahitabhāvaṃ ñatvā āharāpetvā aggamahesiṭṭhānaṃ adāsi. 
486653,110,2580,96,107,1,58,10,"Sā tassa piyā ahosi manāpā, na cirasseva ekaṃ puttaṃ vijāyi. "
486654,110,2580,108,114,1,38,6,So panassā putto cakkavattī rājā ahosi. 
486655,110,2581,2,45,1,325,36,"Bodhisatto tassā sampattiṃ disvā tathārūpaṃ vacanokāsaṃ labhitvā‘‘ deva, sikkhitabbayuttakaṃ nāma sippaṃ kasmā na sikkhitabbaṃ, yatra hi nāmāyaṃ mahāpuññā hirottappaṃ appahāya paṭicchannākārena sarīravaḷañjaṃ kurumānā tumhe ārādhetvā evarūpaṃ sampattiṃ pattā’’ ti vatvā sikkhitabbayuttakānaṃ sippānaṃ vaṇṇaṃ kathento imaṃ gāthamāha– "
486656,110,2582,2,4,1,0,0,108.
486657,110,2583,2,10,1,46,6,"‘ ‘ Sikkheyya sikkhitabbāni, santi sacchandino janā; "
486658,110,2584,2,10,1,41,5,"Bāhiyā hi suhannena, rājānamabhirādhayī’’ ti. "
486659,110,2585,2,13,1,74,10,Tattha santi sacchandino {janā}ti tesu tesu sippesu sacchandā janā atthiyeva. 
486660,110,2585,14,20,1,42,5,{Bāhiyā}ti bahijanapade jātā saṃvaḍḍhā itthī. 
486661,110,2585,21,32,1,88,9,"{Suhannenā}ti hirottappaṃ appahāya paṭicchannenākārena hannaṃ suhannaṃ nāma, tena suhannena. "
486662,110,2585,33,40,1,64,6,{Rājānamabhirādhayī}ti devaṃ abhirādhayitvā imaṃ sampattiṃ pattāti. 
486663,110,2585,41,47,1,59,6,Evaṃ mahāsatto sikkhitabbayuttakānaṃ sippānaṃ guṇaṃ kathesi. 
486664,110,2586,2,9,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
