486760,110,2628,2,7,1,22,2,[ 114]4. Mitacintījātakavaṇṇanā 
486761,110,2629,2,13,1,88,10,Bahucintī {appacintī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto dve mahallakatthere ārabbha kathesi. 
486762,110,2629,14,71,1,373,46,"Te kira janapade ekasmiṃ araññāvāse vassaṃ vasitvā‘‘ satthu dassanatthāya gacchissāmā’’ ti pātheyyaṃ sajjetvā‘‘ ajja gacchāma, sve gacchāmā’’ ti māsaṃ atikkāmetvā puna pātheyyaṃ sajjetvā tatheva māsaṃ, puna māsanti evaṃ attano kusītabhāvena ceva nivāsaṭṭhāne ca apekkhāya tayo māse atikkāmetvā tato nikkhamma jetavanaṃ gantvā sabhāgaṭṭhāne pattacīvaraṃ paṭisāmetvā satthāraṃ passiṃsu. "
486763,110,2629,72,92,1,93,13,"Atha ne bhikkhū pucchiṃsu‘‘ ciraṃ vo, āvuso, buddhupaṭṭhānaṃ akarontānaṃ, kasmā evaṃ cirāyitthā’’ ti? "
486764,110,2629,93,96,1,21,3,Te tamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. 
486765,110,2629,97,105,1,58,7,Atha nesaṃ so ālasiyakusītabhāvo bhikkhusaṅghe pākaṭo jāto. 
486766,110,2629,106,113,1,79,7,Dhammasabhāyampi tesaṃ bhikkhūnameva ālasiyabhāvaṃ nissāya kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ. 
486767,110,2629,114,185,1,291,43,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte te pakkosāpetvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, alasā kusītā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevete alasā, pubbepi alasā ceva nivāsaṭṭhāne ca sālayā sāpekkhā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
486768,110,2630,2,19,1,124,14,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bārāṇasinadiyaṃ tayo macchā ahesuṃ, bahucintī, appacintī, mitacintīti tesaṃ nāmāni. "
486769,110,2630,20,24,1,34,4,Te araññato manussapathaṃ āgamiṃsu. 
486770,110,2630,25,51,1,169,20,"Tattha mitacintī itare dve evamāha‘‘ ayaṃ manussapatho nāma sāsaṅko sappaṭibhayo, kevaṭṭā nānappakārāni jālakuminādīni khipitvā macche gaṇhanti, mayaṃ araññameva gacchāmā’’ ti. "
486771,110,2630,52,73,1,100,15,"Itare dve janā alasatāya ceva āmisagiddhatāya ca‘‘ ajja gacchāma, sve gacchāmā’’ ti tayo māse atikkāmesuṃ. "
486772,110,2630,74,79,1,35,5,Atha kevaṭṭā nadiyaṃ jālaṃ khipiṃsu. 
486773,110,2630,80,88,1,59,8,Bahucintī ca appacintī ca gocaraṃ gaṇhantā purato gacchanti. 
486774,110,2630,89,96,1,74,7,Te attano andhabālatāya jālagandhaṃ asallakkhetvā jālakucchimeva pavisiṃsu. 
486775,110,2630,97,139,1,379,38,Mitacintī pacchato āgacchanto jālagandhaṃ sallakkhetvā tesañca jālakucchiṃ paviṭṭhabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ imesaṃ kusītānaṃ andhabālānaṃ jīvitadānaṃ dassāmī’’ ti cintetvā bahipassena jālakucchiṭṭhānaṃ gantvā jālakucchiṃ phāletvā nikkhantasadiso hutvā udakaṃ āluḷento jālassa purato patitvā puna jālakucchiṃ pavisitvā pacchimabhāgena phāletvā nikkhantasadiso udakaṃ āluḷento pacchimabhāge pati. 
486776,110,2630,140,154,1,78,10,Kevaṭṭā‘‘ macchā jālaṃ phāletvā gatā’’ ti maññamānā jālakoṭiyaṃ gahetvā ukkhipiṃsu. 
486777,110,2630,155,162,1,45,7,Te dvepi macchā jālato muccitvā udake patiṃsu. 
486778,110,2630,163,169,1,43,6,Iti tehi mitacintiṃ nissāya jīvitaṃ laddhaṃ. 
486779,110,2631,2,11,1,62,8,Satthā imaṃ atītaṃ āharitvā abhisambuddho hutvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
486780,110,2632,2,4,1,0,0,114.
486781,110,2633,2,11,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Bahucintī appacintī, ubho jāle abajjhare; "
486782,110,2634,2,11,1,42,6,"Mitacintī pamocesi, ubho tattha samāgatā’’ ti. "
486783,110,2635,2,8,1,67,5,Tattha {bahucintī}ti bahucintanatāya vitakkabahulatāya evaṃladdhanāmo. 
486784,110,2635,9,13,1,28,4,Itaresupi dvīsu ayameva nayo. 
486785,110,2635,14,30,1,121,15,Ubho tattha {samāgatā}ti mitacintiṃ nissāya laddhajīvitā tattha udake puna ubhopi janā mitacintinā saddhiṃ samāgatāti attho. 
486786,110,2636,2,17,1,140,14,"Evaṃ satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne mahallakā bhikkhū sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahiṃsu. "
486787,110,2636,18,31,1,77,12,"Tadā bahucintī ca appacintī ca ime dve ahesuṃ, mitacintī pana ahameva ahosinti. "
486788,110,2637,2,4,1,31,2,Mitacintījātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
486789,110,2639,2,7,1,22,2,[ 115]5. Anusāsikajātakavaṇṇanā 
486790,110,2640,2,14,1,94,11,Yāyaññe {manusāsatī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ anusāsikaṃ bhikkhuniṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486791,110,2640,15,39,1,193,22,"Sā kira sāvatthivāsinī ekā kuladhītā pabbajitvā upasampannakālato paṭṭhāya samaṇadhamme ananuyuttā āmisagiddhā hutvā yattha aññā bhikkhuniyo na gacchanti, tādise nagarassa ekadese piṇḍāya carati. "
486792,110,2640,40,44,1,38,4,Athassā manussā paṇītapiṇḍapātaṃ denti. 
486793,110,2640,45,61,1,109,13,"Sā rasataṇhāya bajjhitvā‘‘ sace imasmiṃ padese aññāpi bhikkhuniyo piṇḍāya carissanti, mayhaṃ lābho parihāyissati. "
486794,110,2640,62,107,1,241,32,"Yathā etaṃ padesaṃ aññā nāgacchanti, evaṃ mayā kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintetvā bhikkhunūpassayaṃ gantvā‘‘ ayye, asukaṭṭhāne caṇḍo hatthī, caṇḍo asso, caṇḍo meṇḍo, caṇḍo kukkuro carati, saparissayaṭṭhānaṃ, mā tattha piṇḍāya caritthā’’ ti bhikkhuniyo anusāsati. "
486795,110,2640,108,119,1,77,11,Tassā vacanaṃ sutvā ekā bhikkhunīpi taṃ padesaṃ gīvaṃ parivattetvā na olokesi. 
486796,110,2640,120,136,1,122,15,Tassā ekasmiṃ divase tasmiṃ padese piṇḍāya carantiyā vegenekaṃ gehaṃ pavisantiyā caṇḍo meṇḍako paharitvā ūruṭṭhikaṃ bhindi. 
486797,110,2640,137,150,1,121,13,Manussā vegena upadhāvitvā dvidhā bhinnaṃ ūruṭṭhikaṃ ekato bandhitvā taṃ bhikkhuniṃ mañcenādāya bhikkhunūpassayaṃ nayiṃsu. 
486798,110,2640,151,170,1,121,15,Bhikkhuniyo‘‘ ayaṃ aññā bhikkhuniyo anusāsitvā sayaṃ tasmiṃ padese carantī ūruṭṭhikaṃ bhindāpetvā āgatā’’ ti parihāsaṃ akaṃsu. 
486799,110,2640,171,179,1,63,8,Tampi tāya katakāraṇaṃ na cirasseva bhikkhusaṅghe pākaṭaṃ ahosi. 
486800,110,2641,2,29,1,178,21,"Athekadivasaṃ dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū ‘‘ āvuso, asukā anusāsikā bhikkhunī aññaṃ anusāsitvā sayaṃ tasmiṃ padese caramānā caṇḍena meṇḍakena ūruṃ bhindāpesī’’ ti tassā aguṇakathaṃ kathesuṃ. "
486801,110,2641,30,80,1,221,31,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesā aññe anusāsatiyeva, sayaṃ pana na vattati, niccakālaṃ dukkhameva anubhotī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
486802,110,2642,2,17,1,165,15,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto araññe sakuṇayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā vayappatto sakuṇajeṭṭhako hutvā anekasakuṇasahassaparivāro himavantaṃ pāvisi. 
486803,110,2642,18,27,1,82,9,Tassa tattha vasanakāle ekā caṇḍasakuṇikā mahāvattanimaggaṃ gantvā gocaraṃ gaṇhāti. 
486804,110,2642,28,77,1,307,37,"Sā tattha sakaṭehi patitāni vīhimuggabījādīni labhitvā‘‘ yathā idāni imaṃ padesaṃ aññe sakuṇā nāgacchanti, tathā karissāmī’’ ti cintetvā sakuṇasaṅghassa ovādaṃ deti‘‘ vattanimahāmaggo nāma sappaṭibhayo, hatthiassādayo ceva caṇḍagoṇayuttayānādīni ca sañcaranti, sahasā uppatitumpi na sakkā hoti, na tattha gantabban’’ ti. "
486805,110,2642,78,88,1,45,6,Sakuṇasaṅgho tassā‘‘ anusāsikā’’ teva nāmaṃ akāsi. 
486806,110,2643,2,22,1,131,15,Sā ekadivasaṃ vattanimahāmagge carantī atimahāvegena āgacchantassa yānassa saddaṃ sutvā nivattitvā oloketvā‘‘ dūre tāvā’’ ti caratiyeva. 
486807,110,2643,23,38,1,96,13,"Atha naṃ yānaṃ vātavegena sīghameva sampāpuṇi, sā uṭṭhātuṃ nāsakkhi, cakkena dvidhā chinditvā gatā. "
486808,110,2643,39,56,1,86,12,"Sakuṇajeṭṭhako sakuṇe samānento taṃ adisvā‘‘ anusāsikā na dissati, upadhāretha nan’’ ti āha. "
486809,110,2643,57,66,1,80,9,Sakuṇā upadhārentā taṃ mahāmagge dvidhā chinnaṃ disvā sakuṇajeṭṭhakassa ārocesuṃ. 
486810,110,2643,67,85,1,99,14,Sakuṇajeṭṭhako‘‘ sā aññā sakuṇikā vāretvā sayaṃ tattha caramānā dvidhā chinnā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
486811,110,2644,2,4,1,0,0,115.
486812,110,2645,2,10,1,38,5,"‘ ‘ Yāyaññe manusāsati, sayaṃ loluppacārinī; "
486813,110,2646,2,12,1,44,7,"Sāyaṃ vipakkhikā seti, hatā cakkena sāsikā’’ ti. "
486814,110,2647,2,14,1,75,9,"Tattha yāyaññe {manusāsatī}ti yakāro padasandhikaro, yā aññe anusāsatīti attho. "
486815,110,2647,15,21,1,49,5,Sayaṃ {loluppacārinī}ti attanā loluppacārinī samānā. 
486816,110,2647,22,32,1,66,9,Sāyaṃ vipakkhikā {setī}ti sā esā vihatapakkhā hutvā mahāmagge sayati. 
486817,110,2647,33,41,1,56,7,Hatā cakkena {sāsikā}ti yānacakkena hatā sāsikā sakuṇikāti. 
486818,110,2648,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
486819,110,2648,9,26,1,92,12,"‘‘ tadā anusāsikā sakuṇikā ayaṃ anusāsikā bhikkhunī ahosi, sakuṇajeṭṭhako pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
486820,110,2649,2,4,1,30,2,Anusāsikajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
486821,110,2651,2,7,1,20,2,[ 116]6. Dubbacajātakavaṇṇanā 
486822,110,2652,2,12,1,89,9,{Atikaramakarācariyā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ dubbacabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486823,110,2652,13,29,1,53,6,Tassa vatthu navakanipāte gijjhajātake( jā.1.9.1 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
486824,110,2652,30,45,1,86,12,"Satthā pana taṃ bhikkhuṃ āmantetvā‘‘ bhikkhu na tvaṃ idāneva dubbaco, pubbepi dubbacoyeva. "
486825,110,2652,46,59,1,102,11,Dubbacabhāveneva paṇḍitānaṃ ovādaṃ akaronto sattippahārena jīvitakkhayaṃ pattosī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. 
486826,110,2653,2,15,1,132,13,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto laṅghanaṭakayoniyaṃ paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā vayappatto paññavā upāyakusalo ahosi. 
486827,110,2653,16,27,1,104,11,So ekassa laṅghanakassa santike sattilaṅghanasippaṃ sikkhitvā ācariyena saddhiṃ sippaṃ dassento vicarati. 
486828,110,2653,28,38,1,72,8,"Ācariyo panassa catunnaṃyeva sattīnaṃ laṅghanasippaṃ jānāti, na pañcannaṃ. "
486829,110,2653,39,56,1,106,13,So ekadivasaṃ ekasmiṃ gāmake sippaṃ dassento surāmadamatto‘‘ pañca sattiyo laṅghissāmī’’ ti paṭipāṭiyā ṭhapesi. 
486830,110,2653,57,73,1,88,12,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto āha‘‘ ācariya, tvaṃ pañcasattilaṅghanasippaṃ na jānāsi, ekaṃ sattiṃ hara. "
486831,110,2653,74,84,1,54,7,"Sace laṅghissasi, pañcamāya sattiyā viddho marissasī’’ ti. "
486832,110,2653,85,112,1,170,22,So suṭṭhu mattatāya‘‘ tvañhi mayhaṃ pamāṇaṃ na jānāsī’’ ti tassa vacanaṃ anādiyitvā catasso laṅghitvā pañcamāya sattiyā daṇḍake madhukapupphaṃ viya āvuto paridevamāno nipajji. 
486833,110,2653,113,129,1,85,12,Atha naṃ bodhisatto‘‘ paṇḍitānaṃ vacanaṃ akatvā imaṃ byasanaṃ pattosī’’ ti imaṃ gāthamāha– 
486834,110,2654,2,4,1,0,0,116.
486835,110,2655,2,10,1,42,5,"‘ ‘ Atikaramakarācariya , mayhampetaṃ na ruccati; "
486836,110,2656,2,10,1,43,5,"Catutthe laṅghayitvāna, pañcamāyasi āvuto’’ ti. "
486837,110,2657,2,17,1,108,13,"Tattha {atikaramakarācariyā}ti ācariya ajja tvaṃ atikaraṃ akari, attano karaṇato atirekaṃ karaṇaṃ akarīti attho. "
486838,110,2657,18,37,1,129,17,"Mayhampetaṃ na {ruccatī}ti mayhaṃ antevāsikassapi samānassa etaṃ tava karaṇaṃ na ruccati, tena te ahaṃ paṭhamameva kathesinti dīpeti. "
486839,110,2657,38,46,1,73,7,Catutthe {laṅghayitvānā}ti catutthe sattithale apatitvā attānaṃ laṅghayitvā. 
486840,110,2657,47,57,1,83,9,Pañcamāyasi {āvuto}ti paṇḍitānaṃ vacanaṃ aggaṇhanto idāni pañcamāya sattiyā āvutosīti. 
486841,110,2657,58,65,1,59,7,Idaṃ vatvā ācariyaṃ sattito apanetvā kattabbayuttakaṃ akāsi. 
486842,110,2658,2,8,1,47,6,Satthā imaṃ atītaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
486843,110,2658,9,24,1,65,10,"‘‘ tadā ācariyo ayaṃ dubbaco ahosi, antevāsiko pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
486844,110,2659,2,4,1,28,2,Dubbacajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
486845,110,2661,2,7,1,20,2,[ 117]7. Tittirajātakavaṇṇanā 
486846,110,2662,2,11,1,76,8,{Accuggatātibalatā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kokālikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486847,110,2662,12,28,1,58,6,Tassa vatthu terasakanipāte takkāriyajātake( jā.1.13.104 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
486848,110,2662,29,52,1,110,16,"Satthā pana‘‘ na, bhikkhave, kokāliko idāneva attano vācaṃ nissāya naṭṭho, pubbepi naṭṭhoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
486849,110,2663,2,24,1,211,20,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto udiccabrāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā kāme pahāya isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā pañcābhiññā aṭṭha samāpattiyo nibbattesi. 
486850,110,2663,25,33,1,77,8,Himavantappadese sabbo isigaṇo sannipatitvā taṃ ovādācariyaṃ katvā parivāresi. 
486851,110,2663,34,43,1,77,9,So pañcannaṃ isisatānaṃ ovādācariyo hutvā jhānakīḷaṃ kīḷanto himavante vasati. 
486852,110,2663,44,53,1,65,9,Tadā eko cettha paṇḍurogī tāpaso kuṭhāriṃ gahetvā kaṭṭhaṃ phāleti. 
486853,110,2663,54,75,1,102,15,"Atheko mukharatāpaso tassa santike nisīditvā‘‘ idha pahāraṃ dehi, idha pahāraṃ dehī’’ ti taṃ tāpasaṃ rosesi. "
486854,110,2663,76,96,1,135,16,So kujjhitvā‘‘ na dāni me tvaṃ dāruphālanasippaṃ sikkhāpanakācariyo’’ ti tiṇhaṃ kuṭhāriṃ ukkhipitvā naṃ ekappahāreneva jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpesi. 
486855,110,2663,97,101,1,36,4,Bodhisatto tassa sarīrakiccaṃ kāresi. 
486856,110,2663,102,110,1,60,8,Tadā assamato avidūre ekasmiṃ vammikapāde eko tittiro vasati. 
486857,110,2663,111,119,1,65,8,So sāyaṃ pātaṃ tasmiṃ vammikamatthake ṭhatvā mahāvassitaṃ vassati. 
486858,110,2663,120,139,1,106,15,Taṃ sutvā eko luddako‘‘ tittirena bhavitabban’’ ti cintetvā saddasaññāya tattha gantvā taṃ vadhitvā ādāya gato. 
486859,110,2664,2,24,1,109,17,"Bodhisatto tassa saddaṃ asuṇanto‘‘ asukaṭṭhāne tittiro vasati, kiṃ nu kho tassa saddo na sūyatī’’ ti tāpase pucchi. "
486860,110,2664,25,29,1,27,4,Te tassa tamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. 
486861,110,2664,30,38,1,64,8,So ubhopi tāni kāraṇāni saṃsandetvā isigaṇamajjhe imaṃ gāthamāha– 
486862,110,2665,2,4,1,0,0,117.
486863,110,2666,2,8,1,36,4,"‘ ‘ Accuggatātibalatā, ativelaṃ pabhāsitā; "
486864,110,2667,2,11,1,46,6,"Vācā hanati dummedhaṃ, tittiraṃ vātivassitan’’ ti. "
486865,110,2668,2,6,1,28,3,Tattha {accuggatā}ti atiuggatā. 
486866,110,2668,7,12,1,47,4,{Atibalatā}ti punappunaṃ bhāsanena atibalasabhāvā. 
486867,110,2668,13,19,1,58,5,Ativelaṃ {pabhāsitā}ti atikkantavelā pamāṇātikkamena bhāsitā. 
486868,110,2668,20,34,1,109,13,"Tittiraṃ vātivassitan ti yathā tittiraṃ ativassitaṃ hanati, tathā evarūpā vācā dummedhaṃ bālapuggalaṃ hanatīti. "
486869,110,2669,2,12,1,94,10,Evaṃ bodhisatto isigaṇassa ovādaṃ datvā cattāro brahmavihāre bhāvetvā brahmalokaparāyaṇo ahosi. 
486870,110,2670,2,28,1,142,18,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, kokāliko idāneva attano vacanaṃ nissāya naṭṭho, pubbepi naṭṭhoyevā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
486871,110,2670,29,46,1,88,11,"‘‘ tadā mukharatāpaso kokāliko ahosi, isigaṇo buddhaparisā, gaṇasatthā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
486872,110,2671,2,4,1,28,2,Tittirajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
486873,110,2673,2,7,1,18,2,[ 118]8. Vaṭṭajātakavaṇṇanā 
486874,110,2674,2,13,1,87,9,Nācintayanto {puriso}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto uttaraseṭṭhiputtaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486875,110,2674,14,20,1,52,6,Sāvatthiyaṃ kira uttaraseṭṭhi nāma ahosi mahāvibhavo. 
486876,110,2674,21,37,1,129,15,Tassa bhariyāya kucchiyaṃ eko puññavā satto brahmalokā cavitvā paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā vayappatto abhirūpo pāsādiko ahosi brahmavaṇṇī. 
486877,110,2674,38,48,1,92,10,Atha ekadivasaṃ sāvatthiyaṃ kattikachaṇe nakkhatte ghuṭṭhe sabbo loko nakkhattanissito ahosi. 
486878,110,2674,49,55,1,51,6,Tassa sahāyakā aññe seṭṭhiputtā sapajāpatikā ahesuṃ. 
486879,110,2674,56,65,1,86,9,Uttaraseṭṭhiputtassa pana dīgharattaṃ brahmaloke vasitattā kilesesu cittaṃ na allīyati. 
486880,110,2674,66,101,1,215,25,"Athassa sahāyakā‘‘ uttaraseṭṭhiputtassapi ekaṃ itthiṃ ānetvā nakkhattaṃ kīḷissāmā’’ ti sammantayitvā taṃ upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ samma, imasmiṃ nagare kattikachaṇo ghuṭṭho, tuyhampi ekaṃ itthiṃ ānetvā nakkhattaṃ kīḷissāmā’’ ti āhaṃsu."
486881,110,2674,102,135,1,211,25,‘‘ Na me attho itthiyā’’ ti ca vuttepi punappunaṃ nibandhitvā sampaṭicchāpetvā ekaṃ vaṇṇadāsiṃ sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍitaṃ katvā tassa gharaṃ netvā‘‘ tvaṃ seṭṭhiputtassa santikaṃ gacchā’’ ti sayanigharaṃ pesetvā nikkhamiṃsu. 
486882,110,2674,136,144,1,62,7,"Taṃ sayanigharaṃ paviṭṭhampi seṭṭhiputto neva oloketi, nālapati. "
486883,110,2674,145,174,1,207,23,"Sā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ evaṃ rūpasobhaggappattaṃ uttamavilāsasampannaṃ maṃ neva oloketi, nālapati, idāni naṃ attano itthikuttalīlāya olokāpessāmī’’ ti itthilīlaṃ dassentī pahaṭṭhākārena aggadante vivaritvā hasitaṃ akāsi. "
486884,110,2674,175,180,1,47,5,Seṭṭhiputto oloketvā dantaṭṭhike nimittaṃ gaṇhi. 
486885,110,2674,181,191,1,81,9,"Athassa aṭṭhikasaññā uppajji, sakalampi taṃ sarīraṃ aṭṭhikasaṅkhalikā viya paññāyi. "
486886,110,2674,192,203,1,44,7,So tassā paribbayaṃ datvā‘‘ gacchā’’ ti uyyojesi. 
486887,110,2675,2,20,1,127,17,"Taṃ tassa gharā otiṇṇaṃ eko issaro antaravīthiyaṃ disvā paribbayaṃ datvā attano gharaṃ nesi, sattāhe vītivatte nakkhattaṃ ositaṃ. "
486888,110,2675,21,38,1,88,12,Vaṇṇadāsiyā mātā dhītu āgamanaṃ adisvā seṭṭhiputtānaṃ santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ kahaṃ sā’’ ti pucchi. 
486889,110,2675,39,51,1,59,8,Te uttaraseṭṭhiputtassa gharaṃ gantvā‘‘ kahaṃ sā’’ ti pucchiṃsu.
486890,110,2675,52,62,1,49,6,‘‘ Taṅkhaṇaññeva tassā paribbayaṃ datvā uyyojesin’’ ti. 
486891,110,2675,63,84,1,116,16,"Athassā mātā rodantī‘‘ dhītaraṃ me na passāmi, dhītaraṃ me samānethā’’ ti uttaraseṭṭhiputtaṃ ādāya rañño santikaṃ agamāsi. "
486892,110,2675,85,101,1,85,12,Rājā aṭṭaṃ vinicchinanto‘‘ ime te seṭṭhiputtā vaṇṇadāsiṃ ānetvā tuyhaṃ adaṃsū’’ ti pucchi.
486893,110,2675,102,110,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, devā’’ ti."
486894,110,2675,111,119,1,17,4,‘‘ Idāni sā kahan’’ ti?
486895,110,2675,120,131,1,40,6,"‘‘ Na jānāmi, taṅkhaṇaññeva naṃ uyyojesin’’ ti."
486896,110,2675,132,141,1,30,5,‘‘ Idāni taṃ samānetuṃ sakkosī’’ ti?
486897,110,2675,142,151,1,18,4,"‘‘ Na sakkomi, devā’’ ti. "
486898,110,2675,152,166,1,57,9,"Rājā‘‘ sace samānetuṃ na sakkoti, rājāṇamassa karothā’’ ti āha. "
486899,110,2675,167,180,1,70,9,Atha naṃ pacchābāhaṃ bandhitvā‘‘ rājāṇaṃ karissāmā’’ ti gahetvā pakkamiṃsu.
486900,110,2675,181,198,1,105,12,‘‘ Seṭṭhiputtaṃ kira vaṇṇadāsiṃ samānetuṃ asakkontaṃ rājā rājāṇaṃ kāretī’’ ti sakalanagaraṃ ekakolāhalaṃ ahosi. 
486901,110,2675,199,218,1,92,13,"Mahājano ure hatthe ṭhapetvā‘‘ kiṃ nāmetaṃ, sāmi, attano te ananucchavikaṃ laddhan’’ ti paridevati. "
486902,110,2675,219,225,1,56,6,Seṭṭhipi puttassa pacchato pacchato paridevanto gacchati. 
486903,110,2676,2,14,1,77,9,Seṭṭhiputto cintesi‘‘ idaṃ mayhaṃ evarūpaṃ dukkhaṃ agāre vasanabhāvena uppannaṃ. 
486904,110,2676,15,25,1,71,7,"Sace ito muccissāmi, mahāgotamasammāsambuddhassa santike pabbajissāmī’’ ti. "
486905,110,2676,26,62,1,183,25,"Sāpi kho vaṇṇadāsī taṃ kolāhalasaddaṃ sutvā‘‘ kiṃsaddo nāmeso’’ ti pucchitvā taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā vegena otaritvā‘‘ ussaratha, ussaratha, sāmī, maṃ rājapurisānaṃ daṭṭhuṃ dethā’’ ti attānaṃ dassesi. "
486906,110,2676,63,71,1,75,8,Rājapurisā taṃ disvā mātaraṃ paṭicchāpetvā seṭṭhiputtaṃ muñcitvā pakkamiṃsu. 
486907,110,2676,72,105,1,323,33,So sahāyakaparivutova nadiṃ gantvā sasīsaṃ nhāyitvā gehaṃ gantvā bhuttapātarāso mātāpitaro vanditvā pabbajjaṃ anujānāpetvā cīvarasāṭake ādāya mahantena parivārena satthu santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā pabbajjaṃ yācitvā pabbajjañca upasampadañca labhitvā avissaṭṭhakammaṭṭhāno vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā na cirasseva arahatte patiṭṭhāsi. 
486908,110,2677,2,40,1,263,30,"Athekadivasaṃ dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitā bhikkhū‘‘ āvuso, uttaraseṭṭhiputto attano bhaye uppanne sāsanassa guṇaṃ jānitvā‘ imamhā dukkhā muccamāno pabbajissāmī’ ti cintetvā tena sucintitena maraṇamutto ceva, pabbajito ca aggaphale patiṭṭhito’’ ti tassa guṇakathaṃ kathesuṃ. "
486909,110,2677,41,110,1,356,47,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, uttaraseṭṭhiputtova attano bhaye uppanne‘ iminā upāyena imamhā dukkhā muccissāmī’ ti cintetvā maraṇabhayā mutto, atīte paṇḍitāpi attano bhaye uppanne‘ iminā upāyena imamhā dukkhā muccissāmā’ ti cintetvā maraṇabhayato mucciṃsuyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
486910,110,2678,2,12,1,113,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto cutipaṭisandhivasena parivattanto vaṭṭakayoniyaṃ nibbatti. 
486911,110,2678,13,32,1,149,19,Tadā eko vaṭṭakaluddako araññā bahū vaṭṭake āharitvā gehe ṭhapetvā gocaraṃ datvā mūlaṃ gahetvā āgatāgatānaṃ hatthe vaṭṭake vikkiṇanto jīvikaṃ kappeti. 
486912,110,2678,33,41,1,66,8,So ekadivasaṃ bahūhi vaṭṭakehi saddhiṃ bodhisattampi gahetvā ānesi. 
486913,110,2678,42,59,1,120,14,"Bodhisatto cintesi‘‘ sacāhaṃ iminā dinnaṃ gocarañca pānīyañca paribhuñjissāmi, ayaṃ maṃ gahetvā āgatānaṃ manussānaṃ dassati. "
486914,110,2678,60,75,1,94,13,"Sace pana na paribhuñjissāmi, ahaṃ milāyissāmi, atha maṃ milāyantaṃ disvā manussā na gaṇhissanti. "
486915,110,2678,76,87,1,50,8,"Evaṃ me sotthi bhavissati, imaṃ upāyaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
486916,110,2678,88,95,1,48,6,So tathā karonto milāyitvā aṭṭhicammamatto ahosi. 
486917,110,2678,96,101,1,29,5,Manussā taṃ disvā na gaṇhiṃsu. 
486918,110,2678,102,129,1,173,22,Luddako bodhisattaṃ ṭhapetvā sesesu vaṭṭakesu parikkhīṇesu pacchiṃ nīharitvā dvāre ṭhapetvā bodhisattaṃ hatthatale katvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho ayaṃ vaṭṭako’’ ti cintetvā oloketuṃ āraddho. 
486919,110,2678,130,139,1,81,9,Athassa pamattabhāvaṃ ñatvā bodhisatto pakkhe pasāretvā uppatitvā araññameva gato. 
486920,110,2678,140,175,1,134,22,"Aññe vaṭṭakā taṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho na paññāyasi, kahaṃ gatosī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ luddakena gahitomhī’’ ti vutte‘‘ kinti katvā muttosī’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
486921,110,2678,176,194,1,105,14,Bodhisatto‘‘ ahaṃ tena dinnaṃ gocaraṃ aggahetvā pānīyaṃ apivitvā upāyacintāya mutto’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
486922,110,2679,2,4,1,0,0,118.
486923,110,2680,2,8,1,39,4,"‘ ‘ Nācintayanto puriso, visesamadhigacchati; "
486924,110,2681,2,11,1,49,6,"Cintitassa phalaṃ passa, muttosmi vadhabandhanā’’ ti. "
486925,110,2682,2,25,1,151,18,Tatthāyaṃ piṇḍattho– puriso dukkhaṃ patvā‘‘ iminā nāma upāyena imamhā dukkhā muccissāmī’’ ti acintayanto attano dukkhā mokkhasaṅkhātaṃ visesaṃ nādhigacchati. 
486926,110,2682,26,33,1,45,7,Idāni pana mayā cintita kammassa phalaṃ passa. 
486927,110,2682,34,46,1,79,10,"Teneva upāyena muttosmi vadhabandhanā, maraṇato ca bandhanato ca muttosmi ahanti. "
486928,110,2682,47,52,1,42,5,Evaṃ bodhisatto attanā katakāraṇaṃ ācikkhi. 
486929,110,2683,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
486930,110,2683,9,19,1,42,6,‘‘ tadā maraṇamutto vaṭṭako ahameva ahosin’’ ti. 
486931,110,2684,2,4,1,26,2,Vaṭṭajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
486932,110,2686,2,7,1,22,2,[ 119]9. Akālarāvijātakavaṇṇanā 
486933,110,2687,2,13,1,94,10,{Amātāpitarasaṃvaddho}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ akālarāviṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486934,110,2687,14,26,1,80,12,So kira sāvatthivāsī kulaputto sāsane pabbajitvā vattaṃ vā sikkhaṃ vā na uggaṇhi. 
486935,110,2687,27,64,1,246,28,"So‘‘ imasmiṃ kāle mayā vattaṃ kātabbaṃ, imasmiṃ kāle upaṭṭhātabbaṃ, imasmiṃ kāle uggahetabbaṃ, imasmiṃ kāle sajjhāyitabban’’ ti na jānāti, paṭhamayāmepi majjhimayāmepi pacchimayāmepi pabuddhapabuddhakkhaṇeyeva mahāsaddaṃ karoti, bhikkhū niddaṃ na labhanti. "
486936,110,2687,65,93,1,159,23,"Dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū‘‘ āvuso, asuko nāma bhikkhu evarūpe ratanasāsane pabbajitvā vattaṃ vā sikkhaṃ vā kālaṃ vā akālaṃ vā na jānātī’’ ti tassa aguṇakathaṃ kathesuṃ. "
486937,110,2687,94,144,1,238,31,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha , bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevesa akālarāvī, pubbepi akālarāvīyeva, kālākālaṃ ajānanabhāvena ca gīvāya vaṭṭitāya jīvitakkhayaṃ patto’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
486938,110,2688,2,23,1,193,20,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto udiccabrāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto sabbasippesu pāraṃ gantvā bārāṇasiyaṃ disāpāmokkho ācariyo hutvā pañcasate māṇave sippaṃ vāceti. 
486939,110,2688,24,37,1,91,12,"Tesaṃ māṇavānaṃ eko kālarāvī kukkuṭo atthi, te tassa vassitasaddena uṭṭhāya sippaṃ sikkhanti. "
486940,110,2688,38,40,1,13,2,So kālamakāsi. 
486941,110,2688,41,46,1,37,5,Te aññaṃ kukkuṭaṃ pariyesantā caranti. 
486942,110,2688,47,59,1,100,12,Atheko māṇavako susānavane dārūni uddharanto ekaṃ kukkuṭaṃ disvā ānetvā pañjare ṭhapetvā paṭijaggati. 
486943,110,2688,60,78,1,107,13,"So susāne vaḍḍhitattā‘‘ asukavelāya nāma vassitabban’’ ti ajānanto kadāci atirattiṃ vassati, kadāci aruṇuggamane. "
486944,110,2688,79,96,1,131,15,"Māṇavā tassa atirattiṃ vassitakāle sippaṃ sikkhantā yāva aruṇuggamanā sikkhituṃ na sakkonti, niddāyamānā gahitaṭṭhānampi na passanti. "
486945,110,2688,97,103,1,56,6,Atipabhāte vassitakāle sajjhāyassa okāsameva na labhanti. 
486946,110,2688,104,140,1,199,27,"Māṇavā‘‘ ayaṃ atirattiṃ vā vassati atipabhāte vā, imaṃ nissāya amhākaṃ sippaṃ na niṭṭhāyissatī’’ ti taṃ gahetvā gīvaṃ vaṭṭetvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā‘‘ akālarāvī kukkuṭo amhehi ghātito’’ ti ācariyassa kathesuṃ. "
486947,110,2688,141,155,1,81,10,Ācariyo‘‘ ovādaṃ aggahetvā saṃvaḍḍhitabhāvena maraṇaṃ patto’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
486948,110,2689,2,4,1,0,0,119.
486949,110,2690,2,8,1,38,4,"‘ ‘ Amātāpitara-saṃvaddho, anācerakule vasaṃ; "
486950,110,2691,2,12,1,43,7,"Nāyaṃ kālaṃ akālaṃ vā, abhijānāti kukkuṭo’’ ti. "
486951,110,2692,2,11,1,81,8,Tattha {amātāpitarasaṃvaddho}ti mātāpitaro nissāya tesaṃ ovādaṃ aggahetvā saṃvaḍḍho. 
486952,110,2692,12,23,1,94,10,"Anācerakule vasan ti ācariyakulepi avasamāno, ācārasikkhāpakaṃ kañci nissāya avasitattāti attho. "
486953,110,2692,24,55,1,178,24,"Nāyaṃ kālaṃ akālaṃ {vā}ti‘‘ imasmiṃ kāle vassitabbaṃ, imasmiṃ na vassitabban’’ ti evaṃ vassitabbayuttakaṃ kālaṃ vā akālaṃ vā esa kukkuṭo na jānāti, ajānanabhāveneva jīvitakkhayaṃ pattoti. "
486954,110,2692,56,64,1,68,8,Idaṃ kāraṇaṃ dassetvā bodhisatto yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
486955,110,2693,2,9,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
486956,110,2693,10,29,1,96,13,"‘‘ tadā akālarāvī kukkuṭo ayaṃ bhikkhu ahosi, antevāsikā buddhaparisā, ācariyo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
486957,110,2694,2,4,1,29,2,Akālarāvijātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
486958,110,2696,2,7,1,27,2,[ 120]10. Bandhanamokkhajātakavaṇṇanā 
486959,110,2697,2,14,1,88,10,Abaddhā tattha {bajjhantī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ciñcamāṇavikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
486960,110,2697,15,31,1,60,6,Tassā vatthu dvādasakanipāte mahāpadumajātake( jā.1.12.106 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
486961,110,2697,32,55,1,124,16,"Tadā pana satthā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, ciñcamāṇavikā idāneva maṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhati, pubbepi abbhācikkhiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
486962,110,2698,2,18,1,132,15,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto purohitassa gehe nibbattitvā vayappatto pitu accayena tasseva purohito ahosi. 
486963,110,2698,19,36,1,69,11,"Tena aggamahesiyā varo dinno hoti‘‘ bhadde, yaṃ icchasi, taṃ vadeyyāsī’’ ti. "
486964,110,2698,37,60,1,106,18,"Sā evamāha‘‘ na mayhaṃ añño varo nāma dullabho, ito pana te paṭṭhāya aññā itthī kilesavasena na oloketabbā’’ ti. "
486965,110,2698,61,78,1,170,17,So paṭikkhipitvā punappunaṃ nippīḷiyamāno tassā vacanaṃ atikkamituṃ asakkonto sampaṭicchitvā tato paṭṭhāya soḷasasu nāṭakitthisahassesu kilesavasena ekitthimpi na olokesi. 
486966,110,2699,2,28,1,133,21,"Athassa paccanto kuppi, paccante ṭhitā yodhā corehi saddhiṃ dve tayo saṅgāme katvā‘‘ ito uttari mayaṃ na sakkomā’’ ti rañño paṇṇaṃ pesesuṃ. "
486967,110,2699,29,64,1,218,26,"Rājā tattha gantukāmo balakāyaṃ saṃharitvā taṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ bhadde, ahaṃ paccantaṃ gacchāmi, tattha nānappakārāni yuddhāni honti, jayaparājayopi anibaddho, tādisesu ṭhānesu mātugāmo dupparihāro, tvaṃ idheva nivattāhī’’ ti āha. "
486968,110,2699,65,97,1,158,22,"Sā‘‘ na sakkā, deva, mayā nivattitun’’ ti punappunaṃ raññā paṭikkhittā āha‘‘ tena hi ekekaṃ yojanaṃ gantvā mayhaṃ sukhadukkhajānanatthaṃ ekekaṃ manussaṃ peseyyāthā’’ ti. "
486969,110,2699,98,130,1,199,24,Rājā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā bodhisattaṃ nagare ṭhapetvā mahantena balakāyena nikkhamitvā gacchanto yojane yojane ekekaṃ purisaṃ‘‘ amhākaṃ ārogyaṃ ārocetvā deviyā sukhadukkhaṃ jānitvā āgacchā’’ ti pesesi. 
486970,110,2699,131,165,1,153,21,Sā āgatāgataṃ purisaṃ‘‘ rājā kimatthaṃ taṃ pesetī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ tumhākaṃ sukhadukkhajānanatthāyā’’ ti vutte‘‘ tena hi ehī’’ ti tena saddhiṃ asaddhammaṃ paṭisevati. 
486971,110,2699,166,180,1,98,12,"Rājā dvattiṃsayojanamaggaṃ gacchanto dvattiṃsa jane pesesi, sā sabbehipi tehi saddhiṃ tatheva akāsi. "
486972,110,2700,2,19,1,140,16,"Rājā paccantaṃ vūpasametvā janapadaṃ samassāsetvā puna āgacchantopi tatheva dvattiṃsa jane pesesi, sā tehipi saddhiṃ tatheva vippaṭipajjiyeva. "
486973,110,2700,20,34,1,95,10,Rājā āgantvā jayakkhandhāvāraṭṭhāne ṭhatvā‘‘ nagaraṃ paṭijaggāpetū’’ ti bodhisattassa paṇṇaṃ pesesi. 
486974,110,2700,35,43,1,97,8,Bodhisatto sakalanagaraṃ paṭijaggāpetvā rājanivesanaṃ paṭijaggāpento deviyā vasanaṭṭhānaṃ agamāsi. 
486975,110,2700,44,64,1,105,13,"Sā bodhisattassa rūpasobhaggappattaṃ kāyaṃ disvā saṇṭhātuṃ asakkontī‘‘ ehi , brāhmaṇa, sayanaṃ abhiruhā’’ ti āha. "
486976,110,2700,65,87,1,87,15,"Bodhisatto‘‘ mā evaṃ avaca, rājāpi garu, akusalampi bhāyāmi, na sakkā mayā evaṃ kātun’’ ti āha."
486977,110,2700,88,99,1,62,8,"‘‘ Catusaṭṭhiyā pādamūlikānaṃ neva rājā garu, na akusalaṃ bhāyanti. "
486978,110,2700,100,111,1,48,8,"Taveva rājā garu, tvaṃyeva ca akusalaṃ bhāyasī’’ ti."
486979,110,2700,112,128,1,56,9,"‘‘ Āma, devi, sace tesampi evaṃ bhaveyya, na evarūpaṃ kareyyuṃ’’."
486980,110,2700,129,141,1,58,8,‘‘ Ahaṃ pana jānamāno evarūpaṃ sāhasiyakammaṃ na karissāmī’’ ti.
486981,110,2700,142,160,1,73,12,"‘‘ Kiṃ bahuṃ vippalapasi, sace me vacanaṃ na karosi, sīsaṃ te chindāpessāmī’’ ti."
486982,110,2700,161,180,1,103,14,"‘‘ Tiṭṭhatu tāva ekasmiṃ attabhāve sīsaṃ, attabhāvasahassepi sīse chijjante na sakkā mayā evarūpaṃ kātun’’ ti. "
486983,110,2700,181,222,1,233,30,"Sā‘‘ hotu, jānissāmī’’ ti bodhisattaṃ tajjetvā attano gabbhaṃ pavisitvā sarīre nakhavaḷañjaṃ dassetvā telena gattāni abbhañjitvā kiliṭṭhavatthaṃ nivāsetvā gilānālayaṃ katvā dāsiyo āṇāpesi‘ raññā kahaṃ devī’ ti vutte‘ gilānā’ ti katheyyāthā’’ ti. "
486984,110,2701,2,6,1,37,4,Bodhisattopi rañño paṭipathaṃ agamāsi. 
486985,110,2701,7,24,1,82,12,"Rājā nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pāsādaṃ āruyha deviṃ apassanto‘‘ kahaṃ, devī’’ ti pucchi."
486986,110,2701,25,33,1,14,3,"‘‘ Gilānā, devā’’ ti. "
486987,110,2701,34,52,1,87,12,"Sopi sirigabbhaṃ pavisitvā tassā piṭṭhiṃ parimajjanto‘‘ kiṃ te, bhadde, aphāsukan’’ ti pucchi. "
486988,110,2701,53,56,1,14,3,Sā tuṇhī ahosi. 
486989,110,2701,57,77,1,98,13,"Tatiyavāre rājānaṃ oloketvā‘‘ tvampi, mahārāja, jīvasi nāma, mādisāpi itthiyo sassāmikāyeva nāmā’’ ti āha."
486990,110,2701,78,87,1,18,4,"‘‘ Kiṃ etaṃ, bhadde’’ ti? "
486991,110,2701,88,112,1,159,19,Tumhehi nagaraṃ rakkhanatthāya ṭhapito purohito‘‘ tumhākaṃ nivesanaṃ paṭijaggāmī’’ ti idhāgantvā attano vacanaṃ akarontiṃ maṃ paharitvā attano manaṃ pūretvā gatoti. 
486992,110,2701,113,144,1,253,25,"Rājā aggimhi pakkhittaloṇasakkharā viya kodhena taṭataṭāyanto sirigabbhā nikkhamitvā dovārikapādamūlikādayo pakkosāpetvā‘‘ gacchatha, bhaṇe, purohitaṃ pacchābāhaṃ bandhitvā vajjhabhāvappattaṃ katvā nagarā nīharitvā āghātanaṃ netvā sīsamassa chindathā’’ ti āha. "
486993,110,2701,145,153,1,65,8,Te vegena gantvā taṃ pacchābāhaṃ bandhitvā vajjhabheriṃ carāpesuṃ. 
486994,110,2702,2,5,1,18,2,Bodhisatto cintesi–
486995,110,2702,6,24,1,102,13,"‘‘ addhā tāya duṭṭhadeviyā rājā puretarameva paribhinno, ajja dānāhaṃ attano baleneva attānaṃ mocessāmī’’ ti. "
486996,110,2702,25,42,1,66,12,"So te purise āha‘‘ bho, tumhe maṃ mārentā rañño dassetvāva mārethā’’ ti."
486997,110,2702,43,49,1,12,2,‘‘ Kiṃkāraṇā’’ ti?
486998,110,2702,50,67,1,97,12,"‘‘ Ahaṃ rājakammiko, bahu me kammaṃ kataṃ, bahūni mahānidhiṭṭhānāni jānāmi, rājakuṭumbaṃ mayā vicāritaṃ. "
486999,110,2702,68,88,1,109,15,"Sace maṃ rañño na dassessatha, bahudhanaṃ nassissati, mayā rañño sāpateyye ācikkhite pacchā kātabbaṃ karothā’’ ti. "
487000,110,2702,89,93,1,23,4,Te taṃ rañño dassayiṃsu. 
