487074,110,2731,2,7,1,21,2,[ 122]2. Dummedhajātakavaṇṇanā 
487075,110,2732,2,14,1,83,10,Yasaṃ laddhāna {dummedho}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487076,110,2732,15,40,1,312,21,"Dhammasabhāyañhi bhikkhū‘‘ āvuso devadatto, tathāgatassa puṇṇacandasassirikamukhaṃ asītānubyañjanadvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇapaṭimaṇḍitaṃ byāmappabhāparikkhittaṃ āveḷāveḷābhūtā yamakayamakabhūtā ghanabuddharasmiyo vissajjentaṃ paramasobhaggappattaṃ attabhāvañca oloketvā cittaṃ pasādetuṃ na sakkoti, usūyameva karoti."
487077,110,2732,41,67,1,184,21,"‘ Buddhā nāma evarūpena sīlena samādhinā paññāya vimuttiyā vimuttiñāṇadassanena samannāgatā’ ti vuccamāne vaṇṇaṃ sahituṃ na sakkoti, usūyameva karotī’’ ti devadattassa aguṇakathaṃ kathayiṃsu. "
487078,110,2732,68,116,1,203,29,"Satthā āgantvā ‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave , idāneva devadatto mama vaṇṇe bhaññamāne usūyaṃ karoti, pubbepi akāsiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487079,110,2733,2,18,1,172,16,Atīte magadharaṭṭhe rājagahanagare ekasmiṃ magadharāje rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto hatthiyoniyaṃ nibbattitvā sabbaseto ahosi heṭṭhā vaṇṇitasadisāya rūpasampattiyā samannāgato. 
487080,110,2733,19,32,1,62,9,Atha naṃ‘‘ lakkhaṇasampanno ayan’’ ti so rājā maṅgalahatthiṃ akāsi. 
487081,110,2733,33,47,1,169,14,Athekasmiṃ chaṇadivase sakalanagaraṃ devanagaraṃ viya alaṅkārāpetvā sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍitaṃ maṅgalahatthiṃ abhiruhitvā mahantena rājānubhāvena nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ akāsi. 
487082,110,2733,48,80,1,218,24,"Mahājano tattha tattha ṭhatvā maṅgalahatthino rūpasobhaggappattaṃ sarīraṃ disvā‘‘ aho rūpaṃ, aho gati, aho līḷā, aho lakkhaṇasampatti, evarūpo nāma sabbasetavaravāraṇo cakkavattirañño anucchaviko’’ ti maṅgalahatthimeva vaṇṇesi. "
487083,110,2734,2,35,1,199,25,Rājā maṅgalahatthissa vaṇṇaṃ sutvā sahituṃ asakkonto usūyaṃ uppādetvā‘‘ ajjeva taṃ pabbatapāde pātetvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpessāmī’’ ti hatthācariyaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ kinti katvā tayā ayaṃ nāgo sikkhāpito’’ ti āha.
487084,110,2734,36,44,1,20,3,"‘‘ Susikkhāpito, devā’’ ti."
487085,110,2734,45,54,1,27,4,"‘‘ Na susikkhito, dusikkhito’’ ti."
487086,110,2734,55,63,1,18,3,"‘‘ Susikkhito, devā’’ ti."
487087,110,2734,64,77,1,67,7,"‘‘ Yadi susikkhito , sakkhissasi naṃ vepullapabbatamatthakaṃ āropetun’’ ti."
487088,110,2734,78,86,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, devā’’ ti."
487089,110,2734,87,134,1,322,36,"‘‘ Tena hi ehī’’ ti sayaṃ otaritvā hatthācariyaṃ āropetvā pabbatapādaṃ gantvā hatthācariyena hatthipiṭṭhiyaṃ nisīditvāva hatthimhi vepullapabbatamatthakaṃ āropite sayampi amaccagaṇaparivuto pabbatamatthakaṃ abhiruhitvā hatthiṃ papātābhimukhaṃ kāretvā‘‘ tvaṃ‘ mayā esa susikkhāpito’ ti vadesi, tīhiyeva tāva naṃ pādehi ṭhapehī’’ ti āha. "
487090,110,2734,135,155,1,115,15,"Hatthācariyo piṭṭhiyaṃ nisīditvāva‘‘ bho tīhi pādehi tiṭṭhā’’ ti hatthissa paṇhikāya saññaṃ adāsi, mahāsatto tathā akāsi. "
487091,110,2734,156,174,1,106,13,"Puna rājā‘‘ dvīhi purimapādehiyeva ṭhapehī’’ ti āha, mahāsatto dve pacchimapāde ukkhipitvā purimapādehi aṭṭhāsi."
487092,110,2734,175,201,1,132,16,"‘‘ Pacchimapādehiyevā’’ ti vuttepi dve purimapāde ukkhipitvā pacchimapādehi aṭṭhāsi,‘‘ ekenā’’ ti vuttepi tayo pāde ukkhipitvā ekeneva aṭṭhāsi. "
487093,110,2734,202,217,1,64,10,"Athassa apatanabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ sace pahosi, ākāse naṃ ṭhapehī’’ ti āha. "
487094,110,2735,2,4,1,15,2,Ācariyo cintesi–
487095,110,2735,5,25,1,122,15,"‘‘ sakalajambudīpe iminā sadiso susikkhito hatthī nāma natthi, nissaṃsayaṃ panetaṃ esa papāte pātetvā māretukāmo bhavissatī’’ ti. "
487096,110,2735,26,45,1,98,15,"So tassa kaṇṇamūle mantesi‘‘ tāta, ayaṃ rājā taṃ papāte pātetvā māretukāmo, na tvaṃ etassa anucchaviko. "
487097,110,2735,46,64,1,103,14,"Sace te ākāsena gantuṃ balaṃ atthi, maṃ yathānisinnaṃyeva ādāya vehāsaṃ abbhuggantvā bārāṇasiṃ gacchā’’ ti. "
487098,110,2735,65,71,1,61,6,Puññiddhiyā samannāgato mahāsatto taṅkhaṇaññeva ākāse aṭṭhāsi. 
487099,110,2735,72,115,1,326,35,"Hatthācariyo‘‘ mahārāja, ayaṃ hatthī puññiddhiyā samannāgato, na tādisassa mandapuññassa dubbuddhino anucchaviko, paṇḍitassa puññasampannassa rañño anucchaviko, tādisā nāma mandapuññā evarūpaṃ vāhanaṃ labhitvā tassa guṇaṃ ajānantā tañceva vāhanaṃ avasesañca yasasampattiṃ nāsentiyevā’’ ti vatvā hatthikkhandhe nisinnova imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487100,110,2736,2,4,1,0,0,122.
487101,110,2737,2,11,1,46,7,"‘ ‘ Yasaṃ laddhāna dummedho, anatthaṃ carati attano; "
487102,110,2738,2,11,1,42,6,"Attano ca paresañca, hiṃsāya paṭipajjatī’’ ti. "
487103,110,2739,2,17,1,113,12,"Tatrāyaṃ saṅkhepattho– mahārāja, tādiso dummedho nippañño puggalo parivārasampattiṃ labhitvā attano anatthaṃ carati. "
487104,110,2739,18,19,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
487105,110,2739,20,30,1,86,10,So hi yasamadamatto kattabbākattabbaṃ ajānanto attano ca paresañca hiṃsāya paṭipajjati. 
487106,110,2739,31,39,1,67,7,"Hiṃsā vuccati kilamanaṃ dukkhuppādanaṃ, tadatthāya eva paṭipajjatīti. "
487107,110,2740,2,24,1,129,18,Evaṃ imāya gāthāya rañño dhammaṃ desetvā‘‘ tiṭṭha dāni tvan’’ ti vatvā ākāse uppatitvā bārāṇasinagaraṃ gantvā rājaṅgaṇe ākāse aṭṭhāsi. 
487108,110,2740,25,41,1,109,12,Sakalanagaraṃ saṅkhubhitvā‘‘ amhākaṃ rañño ākāsena setavaravāraṇo āgantvā rājaṅgaṇe ṭhito’’ ti ekakolāhalaṃ ahosi. 
487109,110,2740,42,45,1,23,3,Vegena raññopi ārocesuṃ. 
487110,110,2740,46,61,1,78,10,"Rājā nikkhamitvā‘‘ sace mayhaṃ upabhogatthāya āgatosi, bhūmiyaṃ patiṭṭhāhī’’ ti āha. "
487111,110,2740,62,90,1,135,18,"Bodhisatto bhūmiyaṃ patiṭṭhāsi, ācariyo otaritvā rājānaṃ vanditvā‘‘ kuto āgatosi, tātā’’ ti vutte‘‘ rājagahato’’ ti vatvā sabbaṃ pavattiṃ ārocesi. "
487112,110,2740,91,125,1,209,25,"Rājā‘‘ manāpaṃ te, tāta, kataṃ idhāgacchantenā’’ ti tuṭṭhahaṭṭho nagaraṃ sajjāpetvā vāraṇaṃ maṅgalahatthiṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā sakalarajjaṃ tayo koṭṭhāse katvā ekaṃ bodhisattassa adāsi, ekaṃ ācariyassa, ekaṃ attanā aggahesi. "
487113,110,2740,126,135,1,91,9,Bodhisattassa āgatakālato paṭṭhāyeva pana rañño sakalajambudīpe rajjaṃ hatthagatameva jātaṃ. 
487114,110,2740,136,145,1,70,9,So jambudīpe aggarājā hutvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ agamāsi. 
487115,110,2741,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487116,110,2741,9,29,1,105,13,"‘‘ tadā magadharājā devadatto ahosi, bārāṇasirājā sāriputto, hatthācariyo ānando, hatthī pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487117,110,2742,2,4,1,28,2,Dummedhajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
487118,110,2744,2,7,1,22,2,[ 123]3. Naṅgalīsajātakavaṇṇanā 
487119,110,2745,2,13,1,87,10,Asabbatthagāmiṃ vācan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto lāḷudāyittheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487120,110,2745,14,56,1,240,31,"So kira dhammaṃ kathento‘‘ imasmiṃ ṭhāne idaṃ kathetabbaṃ, imasmiṃ ṭhāne idaṃ na kathetabban’’ ti yuttāyuttaṃ na jānāti, maṅgale avamaṅgalaṃ vadanto‘‘ tirokuṭṭesu tiṭṭhanti, sandhisiṅghāṭakesu cā’’ ti idaṃ avamaṅgalaṃ maṅgalaṃ katvā anumodanaṃ katheti. "
487121,110,2745,57,87,1,153,20,"Avamaṅgalesu anumodanaṃ karonto‘‘ bahū devā manussā ca, maṅgalāni acintayun’’ ti vatvā‘‘ evarūpānaṃ maṅgalānaṃ satampi sahassampi kātuṃ samatthā hothā’’ ti vadati. "
487122,110,2745,88,108,1,132,14,"Athekadivasaṃ dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū‘‘ āvuso, lāḷudāyī yuttāyuttaṃ na jānāti, sabbattha abhāsitabbavācaṃ bhāsatī’’ ti kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ. "
487123,110,2745,109,159,1,232,32,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, lāḷudāyī idāneva dandhaparisakkano yuttāyuttaṃ na jānāti, pubbepi evarūpo ahosi, niccaṃ lāḷakoyeva eso’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487124,110,2746,2,23,1,210,20,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto brāhmaṇamahāsālakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā bārāṇasiyaṃ disāpāmokkho ācariyo hutvā pañca māṇavakasatāni sippaṃ vācesi. 
487125,110,2746,24,41,1,134,16,"Tadā tesu māṇavesu eko dandhaparisakkano lāḷako māṇavo dhammantevāsiko hutvā sippaṃ uggaṇhāti, dandhabhāvena pana uggaṇhituṃ na sakkoti. "
487126,110,2746,42,51,1,61,8,"Bodhisattassa pana upakāro hoti, dāso viya sabbakiccāni karoti. "
487127,110,2746,52,74,1,158,17,"Athekadivasaṃ bodhisatto sāyamāsaṃ bhuñjitvā sayane nipanno taṃ māṇavaṃ hatthapādapiṭṭhiparikammāni katvā gacchantaṃ āha‘‘ tāta, mañcapāde upatthambhetvā yāhī’’ ti. "
487128,110,2746,75,87,1,102,12,Māṇavo ekaṃ pādaṃ upatthambhetvā ekassa upatthambhakaṃ alabhanto attano ūrumhi ṭhapetvā rattiṃ khepesi. 
487129,110,2747,2,18,1,71,10,"Bodhisatto paccūsasamaye uṭṭhāya taṃ disvā‘‘ kiṃ, tāta, nisinnosī’’ ti pucchi."
487130,110,2747,19,33,1,82,9,"‘‘ Ācariya, ekassa mañcapādassa upatthambhakaṃ alabhanto ūrumhi ṭhapetvā nisinnomhī’’ ti. "
487131,110,2747,34,67,1,190,27,"Bodhisatto saṃviggamānaso hutvā‘‘ ayaṃ ati viya mayhaṃ upakāro, ettakānaṃ pana māṇavakānaṃ antare ayameva dandho sippaṃ sikkhituṃ na sakkoti, kathaṃ nu kho ahaṃ imaṃ paṇḍitaṃ kareyyan’’ ti cintesi. "
487132,110,2747,68,95,1,141,21,"Athassa etadahosi‘‘ attheko upāyo, ahaṃ imaṃ māṇavaṃ dāruatthāya paṇṇatthāya ca vanaṃ gantvā āgataṃ‘ ajja te kiṃ diṭṭhaṃ, kiṃ katan’ ti pucchissāmi. "
487133,110,2747,96,110,1,62,11,"Atha me‘ idaṃ nāma ajja mayā diṭṭhaṃ, idaṃ katan’ ti ācikkhissati. "
487134,110,2747,111,135,1,108,17,"Atha naṃ ‘ tayā diṭṭhañca katañca kīdisan’ ti pucchissāmi, so‘ evarūpaṃ nāmā’ ti upamāya ca kāraṇena ca kathessati. "
487135,110,2747,136,150,1,85,12,Iti naṃ navaṃ navaṃ upamañca kāraṇañca kathāpetvā iminā upāyena paṇḍitaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. 
487136,110,2747,151,189,1,193,32,"So taṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ tāta māṇava, ito paṭṭhāya dāruatthāya vā paṇṇatthāya vā gataṭṭhāne yaṃ te tattha diṭṭhaṃ vā sutaṃ vā bhuttaṃ vā pītaṃ vā khāditaṃ vā hoti, taṃ āgantvā mayhaṃ āroceyyāsī’’ ti āha. "
487137,110,2748,2,31,1,140,20,"So ‘‘ sādhū’’ ti paṭissuṇitvā ekadivasaṃ māṇavehi saddhiṃ dāruatthāya araññaṃ gato tattha sappaṃ disvā āgantvā‘‘ ācariya, sappo me diṭṭho’’ ti ārocesi."
487138,110,2748,32,44,1,30,6,"‘‘ Sappo nāma, tāta, kīdiso hotī’’ ti?"
487139,110,2748,45,52,1,23,3,‘‘ Seyyathāpi naṅgalīsā’’ ti.
487140,110,2748,53,71,1,70,11,"‘‘ Sādhu, tāta, manāpā te upamā āhaṭā, sappā nāma naṅgalīsasadisāva hontī’’ ti. "
487141,110,2748,72,89,1,87,12,"Atha bodhisatto‘‘ māṇavakena manāpā upamā āhaṭā, sakkhissāmi naṃ paṇḍitaṃ kātun’’ ti cintesi. "
487142,110,2748,90,106,1,75,12,Māṇavo puna ekadivasaṃ araññe hatthiṃ disvā‘‘ hatthī me ācariya diṭṭho’’ ti āha.
487143,110,2748,107,118,1,26,5,"‘‘ Hatthī nāma, tāta, kīdiso’’ ti?"
487144,110,2748,119,127,1,23,3,"‘‘ Seyyathāpi, naṅgalīsā’’ ti. "
487145,110,2748,128,142,1,80,10,"Bodhisatto‘‘ hatthissa soṇḍā naṅgalīsasadisā honti, dantādayo evarūpā ca evarūpā ca. "
487146,110,2748,143,158,1,93,13,Ayaṃ pana bālatāya vibhajitvā kathetuṃ asakkonto soṇḍaṃ sandhāya kathesi maññe’’ ti tuṇhī ahosi. 
487147,110,2748,159,175,1,80,11,"Athekadivasaṃ nimantane ucchuṃ labhitvā‘‘ ācariya, ajja mayaṃ ucchu khādimhā’’ ti āha."
487148,110,2748,176,193,1,54,9,‘‘ Ucchu nāma kīdiso’’ ti vutte‘‘ seyyathāpi naṅgalīsā’’ ti āha. 
487149,110,2748,194,206,1,54,8,Ācariyo‘‘ thokaṃ patirūpaṃ kāraṇaṃ kathesī’’ ti tuṇhī jāto. 
487150,110,2749,2,12,1,76,9,"Punekadivasaṃ nimantane ekacce māṇavā guḷaṃ dadhinā bhuñjiṃsu, ekacce khīrena. "
487151,110,2749,13,47,1,134,21,"So āgantvā‘‘ ācariya, ajja mayaṃ dadhinā khīrena ca bhuñjimhā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ dadhikhīraṃ nāma kīdisaṃ hotī’’ ti vutte‘‘ seyyathāpi naṅgalīsā’’ ti āha. "
487152,110,2749,48,73,1,148,18,"Ācariyo‘‘ ayaṃ māṇavo‘ sappo naṅgalīsasadiso’ ti kathento tāva sukathitaṃ kathesi,‘ hatthī naṅgalīsasadiso’ ti kathentenāpi soṇḍaṃ sandhāya lesena kathitaṃ."
487153,110,2749,74,110,1,207,27,"‘ Ucchu naṅgalīsasadisan’ ti kathanepi leso atthi,‘ dadhikhīrāni pana niccaṃ paṇḍarāni pakkhittabhājanasaṇṭhānānī’ ti idha sabbena sabbaṃ upamaṃ na kathesi, na sakkā imaṃ lāḷakaṃ sikkhāpetun’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487154,110,2750,2,4,1,0,0,123.
487155,110,2751,2,10,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Asabbatthagāmiṃ vācaṃ, bālo sabbattha bhāsati; "
487156,110,2752,2,14,1,65,9,"Nāyaṃ dadhiṃ vedi na naṅgalīsaṃ, dadhippayaṃ maññati naṅgalīsan’’ ti. "
487157,110,2753,2,39,1,191,24,"Tatrāyaṃ saṅkhepattho– yā vācā opammavasena sabbattha na gacchati, taṃ asabbatthagāmiṃ vācaṃ bālo dandhapuggalo sabbattha bhāsati,‘‘ dadhi nāma kīdisan’’ ti puṭṭhopi‘‘ seyyathāpi, naṅgalīsā’’ ti vadateva. "
487158,110,2753,40,47,1,44,7,Evaṃ vadanto nāyaṃ dadhiṃ vedi na naṅgalīsaṃ. 
487159,110,2753,48,49,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
487160,110,2753,50,59,1,72,8,"Dadhippayaṃ maññati naṅgalīsaṃ, yasmā ayaṃ dadhimpi naṅgalīsameva maññati. "
487161,110,2753,60,74,1,70,11,"Atha vā {dadhī}ti dadhimeva, payan ti khīraṃ, dadhi ca payañca dadhippayaṃ. "
487162,110,2753,75,94,1,142,17,"Yasmā dadhikhīrānipi ayaṃ naṅgalīsameva maññati, ediso cāyaṃ bālo, kiṃ imināti antevāsikānaṃ dhammakathaṃ kathetvā paribbayaṃ datvā taṃ uyyojesi. "
487163,110,2754,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487164,110,2754,9,24,1,76,10,"‘‘ tadā lāḷakamāṇavo lāḷudāyī ahosi, disāpāmokkho ācariyo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487165,110,2755,2,4,1,29,2,Naṅgalīsajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
487166,110,2757,2,7,1,17,2,[ 124]4. Ambajātakavaṇṇanā 
487167,110,2758,2,15,1,96,11,Vāyametheva {puriso}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ vattasampannaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487168,110,2758,16,51,1,332,30,"So kira sāvatthivāsī kulaputto sāsane uraṃ datvā pabbajito vattasampanno ahosi, ācariyupajjhāyavattāni pānīyaparibhojanīyauposathāgārajantāgharādivattāni ca sādhukaṃ karoti, cuddasasu mahāvattesu asītikhandhakavattesu ca paripūrakārīyeva hoti, vihāraṃ sammajjati, pariveṇaṃ vitakkamāḷakaṃ vihāramaggaṃ sammajjati, manussānaṃ pānīyaṃ deti. "
487169,110,2758,52,62,1,103,9,"Manussā tassa vattasampattiyaṃ pasīditvā pañcasatamattāni dhuvabhattāni adaṃsu, mahālābhasakkāro uppajji. "
487170,110,2758,63,68,1,36,5,Taṃ nissāya bahūnaṃ phāsuvihāro jāto. 
487171,110,2758,69,96,1,185,21,"Athekadivasaṃ dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, asuko nāma bhikkhu attano vattasampattiyā mahantaṃ lābhasakkāraṃ nibbattesi, etaṃ ekaṃ nissāya bahūnaṃ phāsuvihāro jāto’’ ti. "
487172,110,2758,97,151,1,279,35,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave , etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepāyaṃ bhikkhu vattasampanno, pubbepetaṃ ekaṃ nissāya pañca isisatāni phalāphalatthāya araññaṃ agantvā eteneva ānītaphalāphalehi yāpesun’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487173,110,2759,2,17,1,161,14,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto udiccabrāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā pañcasataisiparivāro pabbatapāde vihāsi. 
487174,110,2759,18,33,1,107,13,"Tadā himavante caṇḍo nidāgho ahosi, tattha tattha pānīyāni chijjiṃsu, tiracchānā pānīyaṃ alabhamānā kilamanti. "
487175,110,2759,34,54,1,143,20,Atha tesu tāpasesu eko tāpaso tesaṃ pipāsadukkhaṃ disvā ekaṃ rukkhaṃ chinditvā doṇiṃ katvā pānīyaṃ ussiñcitvā doṇiṃ pūretvā tesaṃ pānīyaṃ adāsi. 
487176,110,2759,55,63,1,82,8,Bahūsu sannipatitvā pānīyaṃ pivantesu tāpasassa phalāphalatthāya gamanokāso nāhosi. 
487177,110,2759,64,68,1,30,4,So nirāhāropi pānīyaṃ detiyeva. 
487178,110,2759,69,93,1,145,18,"Migagaṇā cintesuṃ‘‘ ayaṃ amhākaṃ pānīyaṃ dento phalāphalatthāya gantuṃ okāsaṃ na labhati, nirāhāratāya ativiya kilamati, handamayaṃ katikaṃ karomā’’ ti. "
487179,110,2759,94,112,1,120,14,Te katikaṃ akaṃsu‘‘ ito paṭṭhāya pānīyaṃ pivanatthāya āgacchantena attano balānurūpena phalāphalaṃ gahetvāva āgantabban’’ ti. 
487180,110,2759,113,125,1,116,11,Te tato paṭṭhāya ekeko tiracchāno attano attano balānurūpena madhuramadhurāni ambajambupanasādīnigahetvāva āgacchati. 
487181,110,2759,126,132,1,70,6,Ekassa atthāya ābhataṃ phalāphalaṃ aḍḍhateyyasakaṭabhārappamāṇaṃ ahosi. 
487182,110,2759,133,136,1,36,3,Pañcasatatāpasā tadeva paribhuñjanti. 
487183,110,2759,137,139,1,21,2,Atirekaṃ chaḍḍiyittha. 
487184,110,2760,2,27,1,164,20,"Bodhisatto taṃ disvā‘‘ ekaṃ nāma vattasampannaṃ nissāya ettakānaṃ tāpasānaṃ phalāphalatthāya agantvā yāpanaṃ uppannaṃ, vīriyaṃ nāma kātabbamevā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487185,110,2761,2,4,1,0,0,124.
487186,110,2762,2,10,1,41,6,"‘ ‘ Vāyametheva puriso, na nibbindeyya paṇḍito; "
487187,110,2763,2,12,1,46,7,"Vāyāmassa phalaṃ passa, bhuttā ambā anītihan’’ ti. "
487188,110,2764,2,13,1,89,9,"Tatrāyaṃ saṅkhepattho– paṇḍito attano vattapūraṇādike kammasmiṃ vāyametheva, na ukkaṇṭheyya. "
487189,110,2764,14,15,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
487190,110,2764,16,19,1,31,3,Vāyāmassa nipphalatāya abhāvato. 
487191,110,2764,20,43,1,93,14,Iti mahāsatto ‘‘ vāyāmo nāmesa saphalova hotī’’ ti isigaṇaṃ ālapanto‘‘ vāyāmassa phalaṃ passā’’ ti āha. 
487192,110,2764,44,45,1,7,1,Kīdisaṃ? 
487193,110,2764,46,49,1,20,3,Bhuttā ambā anītihaṃ. 
487194,110,2764,50,60,1,72,8,"Tattha {ambā}ti desanāmattaṃ, tehi pana nānappakārāni phalāphalāni ābhatāni. "
487195,110,2764,61,73,1,60,8,Tesu sampannatarānaṃ ussannatarānaṃ vā vasena‘‘ ambā’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
487196,110,2764,74,90,1,103,15,"Ye imehi pañcahi isisatehi sayaṃ araññaṃ agantvā ekassa atthāya ānītā ambā bhuttā, idaṃ vāyāmassa phalaṃ. "
487197,110,2764,91,115,1,111,18,"Tañca kho pana anītihaṃ,‘‘ iti āha iti āhā’’ ti evaṃ itihītihena gahetabbaṃ na hoti, paccakkhameva taṃ phalaṃ passāti. "
487198,110,2764,116,121,1,38,5,Evaṃ mahāsatto isigaṇassa ovādaṃ adāsi. 
487199,110,2765,2,9,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487200,110,2765,10,26,1,78,11,"‘‘ tadā vattasampanno tāpaso ayaṃ bhikkhu ahosi, gaṇasatthā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487201,110,2766,2,4,1,26,2,Ambajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
487202,110,2768,2,7,1,21,2,[ 125]5. Kaṭāhakajātakavaṇṇanā 
487203,110,2769,2,15,1,95,11,Bahumpi so {vikattheyyā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ vikatthakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487204,110,2769,16,20,1,37,4,Tassa vatthu heṭṭhā kathitasadisameva. 
487205,110,2770,2,12,1,85,10,Atīte pana bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto mahāvibhavo seṭṭhi ahosi. 
487206,110,2770,13,23,1,67,9,"Tassa bhariyā puttaṃ vijāyi, dāsīpissa taṃ divasaññeva puttaṃ vijāyi. "
487207,110,2770,24,27,1,20,3,Te ekatova vaḍḍhiṃsu. 
487208,110,2770,28,47,1,129,17,"Seṭṭhiputte lekhaṃ sikkhante dāsopissa phalakaṃ vahamāno gantvā teneva saddhiṃ lekhaṃ sikkhi, gaṇanaṃ sikkhi, dve tayo vohāre akāsi. "
487209,110,2770,48,59,1,80,10,"So anukkamena vacanakusalo vohārakusalo yuvā abhirūpo ahosi, nāmena kaṭāheko nāma. "
487210,110,2770,60,83,1,195,20,"So seṭṭhighare bhaṇḍāgārikakammaṃ karonto cintesi‘‘ na maṃ ime sabbakālaṃ bhaṇḍāgārikakammaṃ kāressanti, kiñcideva dosaṃ disvā tāḷetvā bandhitvā lakkhaṇena aṅketvā dāsaparibhogenapi paribhuñjissanti. "
487211,110,2770,84,116,1,195,27,"Paccante kho pana seṭṭhissa sahāyako seṭṭhi atthi, yaṃnūnāhaṃ seṭṭhissa vacanena lekhaṃ ādāya tattha gantvā‘ ahaṃ seṭṭhiputto’ ti vatvā taṃ seṭṭhiṃ vañcetvā tassa dhītaraṃ gahetvā sukhaṃ vaseyyan’’ ti. "
487212,110,2770,117,176,1,402,50,"So sayameva paṇṇaṃ gahetvā ‘‘ ahaṃ asukaṃ nāma mama puttaṃ tava santikaṃ pahiṇiṃ, āvāhavivāhasambandho nāma mayhañca tayā, tuyhañca mayā saddhiṃ patirūpo, tasmā tvaṃ imassa dārakassa attano dhītaraṃ datvā etaṃ tattheva vasāpehi, ahampi okāsaṃ labhitvā āgamissāmī’’ ti likhitvā seṭṭhisseva muddikāya lañjetvā yathārucitaṃ paribbayañceva gandhavatthādīni ca gahetvā paccantaṃ gantvā seṭṭhiṃ disvā vanditvā aṭṭhāsi. "
487213,110,2771,2,15,1,43,8,"Atha naṃ seṭṭhi‘‘ kuto āgatosi, tātā’’ ti pucchi."
487214,110,2771,16,22,1,13,2,‘‘ Bārāṇasito’’ ti.
487215,110,2771,23,30,1,16,3,‘‘ Kassa puttosī’’ ti?
487216,110,2771,31,37,1,20,2,‘‘ Bārāṇasiseṭṭhissā’’ ti.
487217,110,2771,38,44,1,19,2,‘‘ Kenatthenāgatosī’’ ti? 
487218,110,2771,45,58,1,59,9,Tasmiṃ khaṇe kaṭāhako‘‘ idaṃ disvā jānissathā’’ ti paṇṇaṃ adāsi. 
487219,110,2771,59,74,1,85,11,Seṭṭhi paṇṇaṃ vācetvā‘‘ idānāhaṃ jīvāmi nāmā’’ ti tuṭṭhacitto dhītaraṃ datvā patiṭṭhāpesi. 
487220,110,2771,75,79,1,28,4,Tassa parivāro mahanto ahosi. 
487221,110,2771,80,109,1,152,20,"So yāgukhajjakādīsu vā vatthagandhādīsu vā upanītesu‘‘ evampi nāma yāguṃ pacanti, evaṃ khajjakaṃ, evaṃ bhattaṃ, aho paccantavāsikā nāmā’’ ti yāguādīni garahati."
487222,110,2771,110,131,1,137,15,"‘‘ Ime paccantavāsibhāveneva ahatasāṭake vaḷañjituṃ na jānanti, gandhe pisituṃ, pupphāni ganthituṃ na jānantī’’ ti vatthakammantikādayo garahati. "
487223,110,2772,2,22,1,103,14,"Bodhisattopi dāsaṃ apassanto‘‘ kaṭāhako na dissati, kahaṃ gato, pariyesatha nan’’ ti samantā manusse payojesi. "
487224,110,2772,23,35,1,92,12,Tesu eko tattha gantvā taṃ disvā sañjānitvā attānaṃ ajānāpetvā āgantvā bodhisattassa ārocesi. 
487225,110,2772,36,58,1,132,17,"Bodhisatto taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā‘‘ ayuttaṃ tena kataṃ, gantvā naṃ gahetvā āgacchissāmī’’ ti rājānaṃ āpucchitvā mahantena parivārena nikkhami."
487226,110,2772,59,71,1,55,8,‘‘ Seṭṭhi kira paccantaṃ gacchatī’’ ti sabbattha pākaṭo jāto. 
487227,110,2772,72,95,1,121,16,"Kaṭāhako‘‘ seṭṭhi kira āgacchatī’’ ti sutvā cintesi‘‘ na so aññena kāraṇena āgacchissati, maṃ nissāyevassa āgamanena bhavitabbaṃ. "
487228,110,2772,96,105,1,57,8,"Sace panāhaṃ palāyissāmi, puna āgantuṃ na sakkā bhavissati. "
487229,110,2772,106,109,1,18,3,Atthi panesa upāyo. 
487230,110,2772,110,121,1,71,9,Mama sāmikassa paṭipathaṃ gantvā dāsakammaṃ katvā tameva ārādhessāmī’’ ti. 
487231,110,2772,122,176,1,426,45,"So tato paṭṭhāya parisamajjhe evaṃ bhāsati‘‘ aññe bālamanussā attano bālabhāvena mātāpitūnaṃ guṇaṃ ajānantā tesaṃ bhojanavelāya apacitikammaṃ akatvā tehi saddhiṃyeva bhuñjanti, mayaṃ pana mātāpitūnaṃ bhojanakāle paṭiggahaṃ upanema, kheḷamallakaṃ upanema, bhājanāni upanema, pānīyampi bījanimpi gahetvā upatiṭṭhāmā’’ ti yāva sarīravaḷañjanakāle udakakalasaṃ ādāya paṭicchannaṭṭhānagamanā sabbaṃ dāsehi sāmikānaṃ kattabbakiccaṃ pakāsesi. "
487232,110,2773,2,34,1,223,25,"So evaṃ parisaṃ uggaṇhāpetvā bodhisattassa paccantasamīpaṃ āgatakāle sasuraṃ avoca‘‘ tāta, mama kira pitā tumhākaṃ dassanatthāya āgacchati, tumhe khādanīyabhojanīyaṃ paṭiyādāpetha, ahaṃ paṇṇākāraṃ gahetvā paṭipathaṃ gamissāmī’’ ti. "
487233,110,2773,35,45,1,28,5,"So‘‘ sādhu, tātā’’ ti sampaṭicchi. "
487234,110,2773,46,56,1,96,10,Kaṭāhako bahuṃ paṇṇākāramādāya mahantena parivārena gantvā bodhisattaṃ vanditvā paṇṇākāraṃ adāsi. 
487235,110,2773,57,70,1,148,13,Bodhisattopi paṇṇākāraṃ gahetvā tena saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā pātarāsakāle khandhāvāraṃ nivāsetvā sarīravaḷañjanatthāya paṭicchannaṭṭhānaṃ pāvisi. 
487236,110,2773,71,105,1,214,26,"Kaṭāhako attano parivāraṃ nivattetvā kalasaṃ ādāya bodhisattassa santikaṃ gantvā udakakiccapariyosāne pādesu patitvā‘‘ sāmi, ahaṃ tumhākaṃ yattakaṃ icchatha, tattakaṃ dhanaṃ dassāmi, mā me yasaṃ antaradhāpayitthā’’ ti āha. "
487237,110,2773,106,126,1,121,15,"Bodhisatto tassa vattasampadāya pasīditvā‘‘ mā bhāyi, natthi te mama santikā antarāyo’’ ti samassāsetvā paccantanagaraṃ pāvisi. "
487238,110,2773,127,137,1,75,8,"Mahanto sakkāro ahosi, kaṭāhakopissa nirantaraṃ dāsena kattabbakiccaṃ karoti. "
487239,110,2773,138,169,1,214,26,"Atha naṃ ekāya velāya sukhanisinnaṃ paccantaseṭṭhi āha‘‘ mahāseṭṭhi, mayā tumhākaṃ paṇṇaṃ disvāva tumhākaṃ puttassa dārikā dinnā’’ ti bodhisatto kaṭāhakaṃ puttameva katvā tadanucchavikaṃ piyavacanaṃ vatvā seṭṭhiṃ tosesi. "
487240,110,2773,170,178,1,63,8,Tato paṭṭhāya kaṭāhakassa mukhaṃ ulloketuṃ samattho nāma nāhosi. 
487241,110,2774,2,50,1,247,34,"Athekadivasaṃ mahāsatto seṭṭhidhītaraṃ pakkositvā‘‘ ehi, amma, sīse me ūkā vicināhī’’ ti vatvā taṃ āgantvā ūkā gahetvā ṭhitaṃ piyavacanaṃ vatvā‘‘ kathehi, amma, kacci te mama putto sukhadukkhesu appamatto , ubho janā sammodamānā samaggavāsaṃ vasathā’’ ti pucchi."
487242,110,2774,51,68,1,77,11,"‘‘ Tāta, mahāseṭṭhi tumhākaṃ puttassa añño doso natthi, kevalaṃ āhāraṃ garahatī’’ ti."
487243,110,2774,69,104,1,252,28,"‘‘ Amma, niccakālamesa dukkhasīlova, apica te ahaṃ tassa mukhabandhanamantaṃ dassāmi, taṃ tvaṃ sādhukaṃ uggaṇhitvā mama puttassa bhojanakāle garahantassa uggahitaniyāmeneva purato ṭhatvā vadeyyāsī’’ ti gāthaṃ uggaṇhāpetvā katipāhaṃ vasitvā bārāṇasimeva agamāsi. "
487244,110,2774,105,115,1,93,10,Kaṭāhakopi bahuṃ khādanīyabhojanīyaṃ ādāya anumaggaṃ gantvā bahudhanaṃ datvā vanditvā nivatti. 
487245,110,2774,116,122,1,54,6,So bodhisattassa gatakālato paṭṭhāya atirekamānī ahosi. 
487246,110,2774,123,134,1,111,11,So ekadivasaṃ seṭṭhidhītāya nānaggarasabhojanaṃ upanetvā kaṭacchuṃ ādāya parivisantiyā bhattaṃ garahituṃ ārabhi. 
487247,110,2774,135,141,1,67,6,Seṭṭhidhītā bodhisattassa santike uggahitaniyāmeneva imaṃ gāthamāha– 
487248,110,2775,2,4,1,0,0,125.
487249,110,2776,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Bahumpi so vikattheyya, aññaṃ janapadaṃ gato; "
487250,110,2777,2,11,1,45,6,"Anvāgantvāna dūseyya, bhuñja bhoge kaṭāhakā’’ ti. "
487251,110,2778,2,32,1,189,24,"Tattha bahumpi so vikattheyya, aññaṃ janapadaṃ {gato}ti yo attano jātibhūmito aññaṃ janapadaṃ gato hoti, yatthassa jātiṃ na jānanti, so bahumpi vikattheyya, vambhanavacanaṃ vañcanavacanaṃ vadeyya. "
487252,110,2778,33,51,1,156,17,Anvāgantvāna {dūseyyā}ti imaṃ tāva vāraṃ sāmikassa paṭipathaṃ gantvā dāsakiccassa katattā kasāhi paharitvā piṭṭhicammuppāṭanato ca lakkhaṇāhananato ca muttosi. 
487253,110,2778,52,76,1,183,22,"Sace anācāraṃ karosi, puna aññasmiṃ āgamanavāre tava sāmiko anvāgantvāna dūseyya, imaṃ gehaṃ anuāgantvā kasābhighātehi ceva lakkhaṇāhananena ca jātippakāsanena ca taṃ dūseyya upahaneyya. "
487254,110,2778,77,96,1,141,18,"Tasmā imaṃ anācāraṃ pahāya bhuñja bhoge kaṭāhaka, mā pacchā attano dāsabhāvaṃ pākaṭaṃ kāretvā vippaṭisārī ahosīti ayamettha seṭṭhino adhippāyo. "
487255,110,2779,2,10,1,79,7,Seṭṭhidhītā pana etamatthaṃ ajānantī uggahitaniyāmena byañjanameva payirudāhāsi. 
487256,110,2779,11,39,1,180,23,"Kaṭāhako‘‘ addhā seṭṭhinā mama kulaṃ ācikkhitvā etissā sabbaṃ kathitaṃ bhavissatī’’ ti tato paṭṭhāya puna bhattaṃ garahituṃ na visahi, nihatamāno yathāladdhaṃ bhuñjitvā yathākammaṃ gato. "
487257,110,2780,2,23,1,130,15,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ tadā kaṭāhako vikatthakabhikkhu ahosi, bārāṇasiseṭṭhi pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487258,110,2781,2,4,1,29,2,Kaṭāhakajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
487259,110,2783,2,7,1,24,2,[ 126]6. Asilakkhaṇajātakavaṇṇanā 
487260,110,2784,2,14,1,113,12,Tathevekassa kalyāṇan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kosalarañño asilakkhaṇapāṭhakaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487261,110,2784,15,25,1,81,10,So kira kammārehi rañño asīnaṃ āhaṭakāle asiṃ upasiṅghitvā asilakkhaṇaṃ udāharati. 
487262,110,2784,26,42,1,86,11,"So yesaṃ hatthato lābhaṃ labhati, tesaṃ asiṃ‘‘ lakkhaṇasampanno maṅgalasaṃyutto’’ ti vadati. "
487263,110,2784,43,58,1,67,10,"Yesaṃ hatthato lābhaṃ na labhati, tesaṃ asiṃ‘‘ avalakkhaṇo’’ ti garahati. "
487264,110,2784,59,70,1,84,11,Atheko kammāro asiṃ katvā kosiyaṃ sukhumaṃ maricacuṇṇaṃ pakkhipitvā rañño asiṃ āhari. 
487265,110,2784,71,82,1,47,7,Rājā brāhmaṇaṃ pakkosāpetvā‘‘ asiṃ vīmaṃsā’’ ti āha. 
487266,110,2784,83,93,1,98,9,Brāhmaṇassa asiṃ ākaḍḍhitvā upasiṅghantassa maricacuṇṇāni nāsaṃ pavisitvā khipitukāmataṃ uppādesuṃ. 
487267,110,2784,94,101,1,58,7,Tassa khipantassa nāsikā asidhārāya paṭihatā dvidhā chijji. 
487268,110,2784,102,108,1,55,6,Tassevaṃ nāsikāya chinnabhāvo bhikkhusaṅghe pākaṭo jāto. 
487269,110,2784,109,128,1,133,14,"Athekadivasaṃ dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, rañño kira asilakkhaṇapāṭhako asiṃ upasiṅghanto nāsikaṃ chindāpesī’’ ti. "
487270,110,2784,129,175,1,206,29,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva so brāhmaṇo asiṃ upasiṅghanto nāsikāchedaṃ patto, pubbepi pattoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487271,110,2785,2,13,1,121,11,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente tassa asilakkhaṇapāṭhako brāhmaṇo ahosīti sabbaṃ paccuppannavatthusadisameva. 
487272,110,2785,14,29,1,115,15,Rājā pana tassa vejje datvā nāsikākoṭiṃ phāsukaṃ kārāpetvā lākhāya paṭināsikaṃ kāretvā puna taṃ upaṭṭhākameva akāsi. 
487273,110,2785,30,41,1,67,10,"Bārāṇasirañño pana putto natthi, ekā dhītā ceva bhāgineyyo ca ahesuṃ. "
487274,110,2785,42,48,1,42,6,So ubhopi te attano santikeyeva vaḍḍhāpesi. 
487275,110,2785,49,55,1,52,6,Te ekato vaḍḍhantā aññamaññaṃ paṭibaddhacittā ahesuṃ. 
487276,110,2785,56,112,1,339,42,"Rājāpi amacce pakkosāpetvā‘‘ mayhaṃ bhāgineyyopi imassa rajjassa sāmikova, dhītaraṃ etasseva datvā abhisekamassa karomī’’ ti vatvā puna cintesi ‘‘ mayhaṃ bhāgineyyo sabbathāpi ñātakoyeva, etassa aññaṃ rājadhītaraṃ ānetvā abhisekaṃ katvā dhītaraṃ aññassa rañño dassāmi, evaṃ no ñātakā bahū bhavissanti, dvinnampi rajjānaṃ mayameva sāmikā bhavissāmā’’ ti. "
487277,110,2785,113,133,1,118,15,"So amaccehi saddhiṃ sammantetvā‘‘ ubhopete visuṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti bhāgineyyaṃ aññasmiṃ nivesane, dhītaraṃ aññasmiṃ vāsesi. "
487278,110,2786,2,8,1,64,6,Te soḷasavassuddesikabhāvaṃ pattā ativiya paṭibaddhacittā ahesuṃ. 
487279,110,2786,9,73,1,334,45,"Rājakumāro‘‘ kena nu kho upāyena mātuladhītaraṃ rājagehā nīharāpetuṃ sakkā bhaveyyā’’ ti cintento‘‘ attheko upāyo’’ ti mahāikkhaṇikaṃ pakkosāpetvā tassā sahassabhaṇḍikaṃ datvā‘‘ kiṃ mayā kattabban’’ ti vutte‘‘ amma, tayi karontiyā anipphatti nāma natthi, kiñcideva kāraṇaṃ vatvā yathā mama mātulo rājā dhītaraṃ antogehā nīharāpeti, tathā karohī’’ ti āha. "
487280,110,2786,74,167,1,755,82,"Sādhu, sāmi, ahaṃ rājānaṃ upasaṅkamitvā evaṃ vakkhāmi‘‘ deva, rājadhītāya upari kāḷakaṇṇī atthi, ettakaṃ kālaṃ nivattitvā olokentopi natthi, ahaṃ rājadhītaraṃ asukadivase nāma rathaṃ āropetvā bahuāvudhahatthe purise ādāya mahantena parivārena susānaṃ gantvā maṇḍalapīṭhikāya heṭṭhāmañce matamanussaṃ nipajjāpetvā uparimañce rājadhītaraṃ ṭhapetvā gandhodakaghaṭānaṃ aṭṭhuttarasatena nhāpetvā kāḷakaṇṇiṃ pavāhessāmī’’ ti evaṃ vatvā rājadhītaraṃ susānaṃ nessāmi, tvaṃ amhākaṃ tattha gamanadivase amhehi puretarameva thokaṃ maricacuṇṇaṃ ādāya āvudhahatthehi attano manussehi parivuto rathaṃ abhiruyha susānaṃ gantvā rathaṃ susānadvāre ekapadese ṭhapetvā āvudhahatthe manusse susānavanaṃ pesetvā sayaṃ susāne maṇḍalapīṭhikaṃ pasāretvā matako viya paṭikujjo hutvā nipajja. "
487281,110,2786,168,190,1,169,21,"Ahaṃ tattha āgantvā tava upari mañcakaṃ attharitvā rājadhītaraṃ ukkhipitvā mañce sayāpessāmi, tvaṃ tasmiṃ khaṇe maricacuṇṇaṃ nāsikāya pakkhipitvā dve tayo vāre khipeyyāsi. "
487282,110,2786,191,198,1,54,6,Tayā khipitakāle mayaṃ rājadhītaraṃ pahāya palāyissāma. 
487283,110,2786,199,212,1,101,13,Atha tvaṃ rājadhītaraṃ sīsaṃ nhāpetvā sayampi sīsaṃ nhāyitvā taṃ ādāya attano nivesanaṃ gaccheyyāsīti. 
487284,110,2786,213,223,1,37,6,So‘‘ sādhu sundaro upāyo’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
487285,110,2787,2,10,1,54,7,"Sāpi gantvā rañño tamatthaṃ ārocesi, rājāpi sampaṭicchi. "
487286,110,2787,11,18,1,50,6,"Rājadhītāyapi taṃ antaraṃ ācikkhi, sāpi sampaṭicchi. "
487287,110,2787,19,31,1,120,12,Sā nikkhamanadivase kumārassa saññaṃ datvā mahantena parivārena susānaṃ gacchantī ārakkhamanussānaṃ bhayajananatthaṃ āha–
487288,110,2787,32,59,1,170,19,"‘‘ mayā rājadhītāya mañce ṭhapitakāle heṭṭhāmañce matapuriso khipissati, khipitvā ca heṭṭhāmañcā nikkhamitvā yaṃ paṭhamaṃ passissati , tameva gahessati, appamattā bhaveyyāthā’’ ti. "
487289,110,2787,60,66,1,56,6,Rājakumāro puretaraṃ gantvā vuttanayeneva tattha nipajji. 
487290,110,2787,67,82,1,105,11,Mahāikkhaṇikā rājadhītaraṃ ukkhipitvā maṇḍalapīṭhikāṭhānaṃ gacchantī‘‘ mā bhāyī’’ ti saññāpetvā mañce ṭhapesi. 
487291,110,2787,83,90,1,57,7,Tasmiṃ khaṇe kumāro maricacuṇṇaṃ nāsāya pakkhipitvā khipi. 
487292,110,2787,91,115,1,207,22,"Tena khipitamatteyeva mahāikkhaṇikā rājadhītaraṃ pahāya mahāravaṃ ravamānā sabbapaṭhamaṃ palāyi, tassā palātakālato paṭṭhāya ekopi ṭhātuṃ samattho nāma nāhosi, gahitagahitāni āvudhāni chaḍḍetvā sabbe palāyiṃsu. "
487293,110,2787,116,125,1,80,9,Kumāro yathāsammantitaṃ sabbaṃ katvā rājadhītaraṃ ādāya attano nivesanaṃ agamāsi. 
487294,110,2788,2,9,1,42,6,Ikkhaṇikā gantvā taṃ kāraṇaṃ rañño ārocesi. 
487295,110,2788,10,34,1,158,19,"Rājā‘‘ pakatiyāpi sā mayā tassevatthāya puṭṭhā, pāyāse chaḍḍitasappi viya jātan’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā aparabhāge bhāgineyyassa rajjaṃ datvā dhītaraṃ mahādeviṃ kāresi. "
487296,110,2788,35,43,1,60,8,So tāya saddhiṃ samaggavāsaṃ vasamāno dhammena rajjaṃ kāresi. 
487297,110,2788,44,49,1,47,5,Sopi asilakkhaṇapāṭhako tasseva upaṭṭhāko ahosi. 
487298,110,2788,50,62,1,109,11,"Tassekadivasaṃ rājūpaṭṭhānaṃ āgantvā paṭisūriyaṃ ṭhatvā upaṭṭhahantassa lākhā vilīyi, paṭināsikā bhūmiyaṃ pati. "
487299,110,2788,63,67,1,28,4,So lajjāya adhomukho aṭṭhāsi. 
487300,110,2788,68,87,1,98,14,"Atha naṃ rājā parihasanto‘‘ ācariya, mā cintayittha, khipitaṃ nāma ekassa kalyāṇaṃ hoti, ekassa pāpakaṃ. "
487301,110,2788,88,107,1,122,15,"Tumhehi khipitena nāsikā chijjīyittha, mayaṃ pana khipantā mātuladhītaraṃ labhitvā rajjaṃ pāpuṇimhā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487302,110,2789,2,4,1,0,0,126.
487303,110,2790,2,9,1,42,5,"‘ ‘ Tathevekassa kalyāṇaṃ, tathevekassa pāpakaṃ; "
487304,110,2791,2,14,1,50,9,"Tasmā sabbaṃ na kalyāṇaṃ, sabbaṃ vāpi na pāpakan’’ ti. "
487305,110,2792,2,6,1,33,3,Tattha {tathevekassā}ti tadevekassa. 
487306,110,2792,7,10,1,16,3,Ayameva vā pāṭho. 
487307,110,2792,11,14,1,23,3,Dutiyapadepi eseva nayo. 
487308,110,2793,2,14,1,81,12,Iti so imāya gāthāya taṃ kāraṇaṃ āharitvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
487309,110,2794,2,11,1,100,9,Satthā imāya desanāya lokasammatānaṃ kalyāṇapāpakānaṃ anekaṃsikabhāvaṃ pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
