487311,110,2795,2,4,1,32,2,Asilakkhaṇajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
487312,110,2797,2,7,1,22,2,[ 127]7. Kalaṇḍukajātakavaṇṇanā 
487313,110,2798,2,16,1,94,12,Te desā tāni {vatthūnī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ vikatthakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487314,110,2798,17,21,1,46,4,Tattha dvepi vatthūni kaṭāhakajātakasadisāneva. 
487315,110,2799,2,10,1,54,7,Idha panesa bārāṇasiseṭṭhino dāso kalaṇḍuko nāma ahosi. 
487316,110,2799,11,37,1,207,21,"Tassa palāyitvā paccantavāsiseṭṭhino dhītaraṃ gahetvā mahantena parivārena vasanakāle bārāṇasiseṭṭhi pariyesāpetvāpi tassa gataṭṭhānaṃ ajānanto‘‘ gaccha, kalaṇḍukaṃ pariyesā’’ ti attanā puṭṭhaṃ sukapotakaṃ pesesi. "
487317,110,2799,38,46,1,51,8,Sukapotako ito cito ca vicaranto taṃ nagaraṃ pāpuṇi. 
487318,110,2799,47,65,1,169,18,Tasmiñca kāle kalaṇḍuko nadīkīḷaṃ kīḷitukāmo bahuṃ mālāgandhavilepanañceva khādanīyabhojanīyāni ca gāhāpetvā nadiṃ gantvā seṭṭhidhītāya saddhiṃ nāvaṃ āruyha udake kīḷati. 
487319,110,2799,66,84,1,149,16,"Tasmiñca padese nadīkīḷaṃ kīḷantā issarajātikā tikhiṇabhesajjaparibhāvitaṃ khīraṃ pivanti, tena tesaṃ divasabhāgampi udake kīḷantānaṃ sītaṃ na bādhati. "
487320,110,2799,85,95,1,83,10,Ayaṃ pana kalaṇḍuko khīragaṇḍūsaṃ gahetvā mukhaṃ vikkhāletvā taṃ khīraṃ nuṭṭhubhati. 
487321,110,2799,96,102,1,65,6,Nuṭṭhubhantopi udake anuṭṭhubhitvā seṭṭhidhītāya sīse nuṭṭhubhati. 
487322,110,2799,103,149,1,345,38,"Sukapotakopi nadītīraṃ gantvā ekissā udumbarasākhāya nisīditvā oloketvā kalaṇḍukaṃ sañjānitvā seṭṭhidhītāya sīse nuṭṭhubhantaṃ disvā‘‘ are, kalaṇḍuka dāsa, attano jātiñca vasanaṭṭhānañca anussara, khīragaṇḍūsaṃ gahetvā mukhaṃ vikkhāletvā jātisampannāya sukhasaṃvaḍḍhāya seṭṭhidhītāya sīse mā nuṭṭhubhi, attano pamāṇaṃ na jānāsī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487323,110,2800,2,4,1,0,0,127.
487324,110,2801,2,11,1,39,7,"‘ ‘ Te desā tāni vatthūni, ahañca vanagocaro; "
487325,110,2802,2,13,1,51,8,"Anuvicca kho taṃ gaṇheyyuṃ, piva khīraṃ kalaṇḍukā’’ ti. "
487326,110,2803,2,11,1,58,8,Tattha te desā tāni {vatthūnī}ti mātukucchiṃ sandhāya vadati. 
487327,110,2803,12,22,1,71,8,"Ayametthādhippāyo– yattha te vasitaṃ, na te khattiyadhītādīnaṃ kucchidesā. "
487328,110,2803,23,31,1,64,7,"Yattha vāsi patiṭṭhito, na tāni khattiyadhītādīnaṃ kucchivatthūni. "
487329,110,2803,32,40,1,53,8,Atha kho dāsikucchiyaṃ tvaṃ vasi ceva patiṭṭhito cāti. 
487330,110,2803,41,48,1,64,6,Ahañca {vanagocaro}ti tiracchānabhūtopi etamatthaṃ jānāmīti dīpeti. 
487331,110,2803,49,83,1,242,32,"Anuvicca kho taṃ gaṇheyyun ti evaṃ anācāraṃ caramānaṃ mayā gantvā ārocite anuvicca jānitvā tava sāmikā tāḷetvā ceva lakkhaṇāhatañca katvā taṃ gaṇheyyuṃ, gahetvā gamissanti, tasmā attano pamāṇaṃ ñatvā seṭṭhidhītāya sīse anuṭṭhubhitvā piva khīraṃ. "
487332,110,2803,84,88,1,28,3,{Kalaṇḍukā}ti taṃ nāmenālapati. 
487333,110,2804,2,28,1,94,14,"Kalaṇḍukopi suvapotakaṃ sañjānitvā‘‘ maṃ pākaṭaṃ kareyyā’’ ti bhayena‘‘ ehi, sāmi, kadā āgatosī’’ ti āha. "
487334,110,2804,29,64,1,176,26,"Suko‘‘ na esa maṃ hitakāmatāya pakkosati, gīvaṃ pana me vaṭṭetvā māretukāmo’’ ti ñatvāva‘‘ na me tayā attho’’ ti tato uppatitvā bārāṇasiṃ gantvā yathādiṭṭhaṃ seṭṭhino vitthārena kathesi. "
487335,110,2804,65,84,1,111,15,Seṭṭhi‘‘ ayuttaṃ tena katan’’ ti vatvā gantvā tassa āṇaṃ kāretvā bārāṇasimeva naṃ ānetvā dāsaparibhogena paribhuñji. 
487336,110,2805,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487337,110,2805,9,24,1,71,10,"‘‘ tadā kalaṇḍuko ayaṃ bhikkhu ahosi, bārāṇasiseṭṭhi pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487338,110,2806,2,4,1,30,2,Kalaṇḍukajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
487339,110,2808,2,7,1,23,2,[ 128]8. Biḷāravatajātakavaṇṇanā 
487340,110,2809,2,17,1,95,13,Yo ve dhammaṃ dhajaṃ {katvā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kuhakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487341,110,2809,18,40,1,104,15,"Tadā hi satthā tassa kuhakabhāve ārocite‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepesa kuhakoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487342,110,2810,2,19,1,184,17,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto mūsikayoniyaṃ paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā vuḍḍhimanvāya mahāsarīro sūkaracchāpakasadiso hutvā anekasatamūsikāhi parivuto araññe viharati. 
487343,110,2810,20,48,1,179,24,Atheko siṅgālo ito cito ca vicaranto taṃ mūsikayūthaṃ disvā‘‘ imā mūsikā vañcetvā khādissāmī’’ ti cintetvā mūsikānaṃ āsayassa avidūre sūriyābhimukho vātaṃ pivanto ekena pādena aṭṭhāsi. 
487344,110,2810,49,76,1,115,18,"Bodhisatto gocarāya caramāno taṃ disvā‘‘ sīlavā eso bhavissatī’’ ti tassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ bhante, tvaṃ ko nāmo’’ ti pucchi."
487345,110,2810,77,84,1,16,3,‘‘ Dhammiko nāmā’’ ti.
487346,110,2810,85,97,1,56,8,‘‘ Cattāro pāde bhūmiyaṃ aṭhapetvā kasmā ekeneva ṭhitosī’’ ti.
487347,110,2810,98,116,1,90,13,"‘‘ Mayi cattāro pāde pathaviyaṃ ṭhapente pathavī vahituṃ na sakkoti, tasmā ekeneva tiṭṭhāmī’’ ti."
487348,110,2810,117,126,1,33,5,‘‘ Mukhaṃ vivaritvā kasmā ṭhitosī’’ ti?
487349,110,2810,127,139,1,50,7,"‘‘ Mayaṃ aññaṃ na bhakkhayāma, vātameva bhakkhayāmā’’ ti."
487350,110,2810,140,150,1,37,5,‘‘ Atha kasmā sūriyābhimukho tiṭṭhasī’’ ti?
487351,110,2810,151,158,1,20,3,‘‘ Sūriyaṃ namassāmī’’ ti. 
487352,110,2810,159,180,1,128,17,Bodhisatto tassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ sīlavā eso bhavissatī’’ ti tato paṭṭhāya mūsikagaṇena saddhiṃ sāyaṃ pātaṃ tassa upaṭṭhānaṃ gacchati. 
487353,110,2811,2,17,1,129,14,Athassa upaṭṭhānaṃ katvā gamanakāle siṅgālo sabbapacchimaṃ mūsikaṃ gahetvā maṃsaṃ khāditvā ajjhoharitvā mukhaṃ puñchitvā tiṭṭhati. 
487354,110,2811,18,22,1,33,4,Anupubbena mūsikagaṇo tanuko jāto. 
487355,110,2811,23,34,1,60,8,"Mūsikā‘‘ pubbe amhākaṃ ayaṃ āsayo nappahoti, nirantarā tiṭṭhāma. "
487356,110,2811,35,54,1,93,15,"Idāni sithilā, evampi āsayo na pūrateva, kiṃ nu kho etan’’ ti bodhisattassa taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesuṃ. "
487357,110,2811,55,87,1,168,23,Bodhisatto‘‘ kena nu kho kāraṇena musikā tanuttaṃ gatā’’ ti cintento siṅgāle āsaṅkaṃ ṭhapetvā‘‘ vīmaṃsissāmi nan’’ ti upaṭṭhānakāle sesamūsikā purato katvā sayaṃ pacchato ahosi. 
487358,110,2811,88,124,1,232,29,"Siṅgālo tassa upari pakkhandi, bodhisatto attano gahaṇatthāya taṃ pakkhandantaṃ disvā nivattitvā‘‘ bho siṅgāla, idaṃ te vatasamādānaṃ na dhammasudhammatāya, paresaṃ pana vihiṃsanatthāya dhammaṃ dhajaṃ katvā carasī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487359,110,2812,2,4,1,0,0,128.
487360,110,2813,2,12,1,45,8,"‘ ‘ Yo ve dhammaṃ dhajaṃ katvā, nigūḷho pāpamācare; "
487361,110,2814,2,12,1,46,7,"Vissāsayitvā bhūtāni, biḷāraṃ nāma taṃ vatan’’ ti. "
487362,110,2815,2,9,1,39,6,Tattha yo {ve}ti khattiyādīsu yo kocideva. 
487363,110,2815,10,24,1,111,12,"Dhammaṃ dhajaṃ {katvā}ti dasakusalakammapathadhammaṃ dhajaṃ karitvā, kūṭaṃ karonto viya ussāpetvā dassentoti attho. "
487364,110,2815,25,37,1,60,7,{Vissāsayitvā}ti‘‘ sīlavā ayan’’ ti saññāya sañjātavissāsāni katvā. 
487365,110,2815,38,56,1,116,18,Biḷāraṃ nāma taṃ vatan ti taṃ evaṃ dhammaṃ dhajaṃ katvā raho pāpāni karontassa vataṃ kerāṭikavataṃ nāma hotīti attho. 
487366,110,2816,2,16,1,135,14,Mūsikarājā kathentova uppatitvā tassa gīvāyaṃ patitvā hanukassa heṭṭhā antogalanāḷiyaṃ ḍaṃsitvā galanāḷiṃ phāletvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpesi. 
487367,110,2816,17,29,1,60,8,Mūsikagaṇo nivattitvā siṅgālaṃ‘‘ muru murū’’ ti khāditvā agamāsi. 
487368,110,2816,30,39,1,62,8,"Paṭhamāgatāva kirassa maṃsaṃ labhiṃsu, pacchā āgatā na labhiṃsu. "
487369,110,2816,40,45,1,38,5,Tato paṭṭhāya mūsikagaṇo nibbhayo jāto. 
