487372,110,2818,2,4,1,31,2,Biḷāravatajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
487373,110,2820,2,7,1,29,2,[ 129]9. Aggikabhāradvājajātakavaṇṇanā 
487374,110,2821,2,15,1,91,11,Nāyaṃ sikhā {puññahetū}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kuhakaññeva bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487375,110,2822,2,12,1,92,10,Atītasmiñhi bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto mūsikarājā hutvā araññe vasati. 
487376,110,2822,13,25,1,87,11,Atheko siṅgālo davaḍāhe uṭṭhite palāyituṃ asakkonto ekasmiṃ rukkhe sīsaṃ āhacca aṭṭhāsi. 
487377,110,2822,26,41,1,109,14,"Tassa sakalasarīre lomāni jhāyiṃsu, rukkhaṃ āhacca ṭhitaṭṭhāne pana matthake cūḷā viya thokāni lomāni aṭṭhaṃsu. "
487378,110,2822,42,78,1,208,28,So ekadivasaṃ soṇḍiyaṃ pānīyaṃ pivanto chāyaṃ olokento cūḷaṃ disvā‘‘ uppannaṃ dāni me bhaṇḍamūlan’’ ti araññe vicaranto taṃ mūsikādariṃ disvā‘‘ imā mūsikā vañcetvā khādissāmī’’ ti heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva avidūre aṭṭhāsi. 
487379,110,2822,79,102,1,104,15,Atha naṃ bodhisatto gocarāya caranto disvā‘‘ sīlavā ayan’’ ti saññāya upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ tvaṃ kinnāmosī’’ ti pucchi.
487380,110,2822,103,111,1,29,4,‘‘ Ahaṃ aggikabhāradvājo nāmā’’ ti.
487381,110,2822,112,120,1,21,4,‘‘ Atha kasmā āgatosī’’ ti?
487382,110,2822,121,128,1,26,3,‘‘ Tumhākaṃ rakkhanatthāyā’’ ti.
487383,110,2822,129,138,1,31,5,‘‘ Kinti katvā amhe rakkhissasī’’ ti?
487384,110,2822,139,167,1,166,20,"‘‘ Ahaṃ aṅguṭṭhagaṇanaṃ nāma jānāmi, tumhākaṃ pātova nikkhamitvā gocarāya gamanakāle‘ ettakā’ ti gaṇetvā paccāgamanakālepi gaṇessāmi, evaṃ sāyaṃ pātaṃ gaṇento rakkhissāmī’’ ti."
487385,110,2822,168,177,1,24,5,‘‘ Tena hi rakkha mātulā’’ ti. 
487386,110,2822,178,202,1,130,16,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā nikkhamanakāle‘‘ eko dve tayo’’ ti gaṇetvā paccāgamanakālepi tatheva gaṇetvā sabbapacchimaṃ gahetvā khādati. 
487387,110,2822,203,205,1,22,2,Sesaṃ purimasadisameva. 
487388,110,2823,2,28,1,160,20,"Idha pana mūsikarājā nivattitvā ṭhito‘‘ bho aggikabhāradvāja, nāyaṃ tava dhammasudhammatāya matthake cūḷā ṭhapitā, kucchikāraṇā pana ṭhapitā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487389,110,2824,2,4,1,0,0,129.
487390,110,2825,2,12,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Nāyaṃ sikhā puññahetu, ghāsahetu ayaṃ sikhā; "
487391,110,2826,2,12,1,43,7,"Nāguṭṭhigaṇanaṃ yāti, alaṃ te hotu aggikā’’ ti. "
487392,110,2827,2,28,1,162,19,"Tattha nāguṭṭhigaṇanaṃ {yātī}ti‘‘ aṅguṭṭhigaṇanā’’ ti aṅguṭṭhagaṇanā vuccati, ayaṃ mūsikagaṇo aṅguṭṭhagaṇanaṃ na gacchati na upeti na pūreti, parikkhayaṃ gacchatīti attho. "
487393,110,2827,29,38,1,50,8,Alaṃ te hotu {aggikā}ti siṅgālaṃ nāmena ālapanto āha. 
487394,110,2827,39,50,1,52,9,"Ettāvatā te alaṃ hotu, na ito paraṃ mūsike khādissasi . "
487395,110,2827,51,66,1,88,14,"Amhehi vā tayā saddhiṃ saṃvāso alaṃ hotu, na mayaṃ idāni tayā saddhiṃ vasissāmātipi attho. "
487396,110,2827,67,69,1,22,2,Sesaṃ purimasadisameva. 
487397,110,2828,2,23,1,120,16,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ tadā siṅgālo ayaṃ bhikkhu ahosi, mūsikarājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487398,110,2829,2,4,1,36,2,Aggikabhāradvājajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
487399,110,2831,2,7,1,19,2,[ 130]10. Kosiyajātakavaṇṇanā 
487400,110,2832,2,17,1,99,13,Yathā vācā ca {bhuñjassū}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ sāvatthiyaṃ mātugāmaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487401,110,2832,18,35,1,164,17,Sā kirekassa saddhāsampannassa upāsakabrāhmaṇassa brāhmaṇī dussīlā pāpadhammā rattiṃ aticaritvā divā kiñci kammaṃ akatvā gilānālayaṃ dassetvā nitthunamānā nipajjati. 
487402,110,2832,36,49,1,51,9,Atha naṃ brāhmaṇo‘‘ kiṃ te bhadde aphāsukan’’ ti pucchi.
487403,110,2832,50,58,1,20,4,‘‘ Vātā me vijjhantī’’ ti.
487404,110,2832,59,68,1,27,5,‘‘ Atha kiṃ laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti?
487405,110,2832,69,77,1,54,4,‘‘ Siniddhamadhurāni paṇītapaṇītāni yāgubhattatelādīnī’’ ti. 
487406,110,2832,78,93,1,79,13,"Brāhmaṇo yaṃ yaṃ sā icchati, taṃ taṃ āharitvā deti, dāso viya sabbakiccāni karoti. "
487407,110,2832,94,106,1,93,11,"Sā pana brāhmaṇassa gehaṃ paviṭṭhakāle nipajjati, bahi nikkhantakāle jārehi saddhiṃ vītināmeti. "
487408,110,2833,2,67,1,404,48,"Atha brāhmaṇo‘‘ imissā sarīre vijjhanavātānaṃ pariyanto na paññāyatī’’ ti ekadivasaṃ gandhamālādīni ādāya jetavanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ pūjetvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīditvā‘‘ kiṃ, brāhmaṇa, na paññāyasī’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhante, brāhmaṇiyā kira me sarīre vātā vijjhanti, svāhaṃ tassā sappitelādīni ceva paṇītapaṇītabhojanāni ca pariyesāmi, sarīramassā ghanaṃ vippasannacchavivaṇṇaṃ jātaṃ, vātarogassa pana pariyanto na paññāyati. "
487409,110,2833,68,79,1,62,9,Ahaṃ taṃ paṭijaggantova idhāgamanassa okāsaṃ na labhāmī’’ ti āha. 
487410,110,2833,80,117,1,233,29,"Satthā brāhmaṇiyā pāpabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ brāhmaṇa,‘ evaṃ nipannassa mātugāmassa roge avūpasamante idañcidañca bhesajjaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’ ti pubbepi te paṇḍitehi kathitaṃ, bhavasaṅkhepagatattā pana na sallakkhesī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
487411,110,2834,2,19,1,175,16,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto brāhmaṇamahāsālakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā bārāṇasiyaṃ disāpāmokkho ācariyo ahosi. 
487412,110,2834,20,30,1,99,10,Ekasatarājadhānīsu khattiyakumārā ca brāhmaṇakumārā ca yebhuyyena tasseva santike sippaṃ uggaṇhanti. 
487413,110,2834,31,52,1,203,20,Atheko janapadavāsī brāhmaṇamāṇavo bodhisattassa santike tayo vede aṭṭhārasa ca vijjāṭṭhānāni uggaṇhitvā bārāṇasiyaṃyeva kuṭumbaṃ saṇṭhapetvā divase divase dvattikkhattuṃ bodhisattassa santikaṃ āgacchati . 
487414,110,2834,53,60,1,76,7,Tassa brāhmaṇī dussīlā ahosi pāpadhammāti sabbaṃ paccuppannavatthusadisameva. 
487415,110,2835,2,94,1,537,71,"Bodhisatto pana‘‘ iminā kāraṇena ovādagahaṇāya okāsaṃ na labhāmī’’ ti vutte‘‘ sā māṇavikā imaṃ vañcetvā nipajjatī’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ tassā rogānucchavikaṃ bhesajjaṃ ācikkhissāmī’’ ti cintetvā āha‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ ito paṭṭhāya tassā sappikhīrarasādīni mā adāsi, gomutte pana pañcapaṇṇāni phalādīni ca pakkhipitvā koṭṭetvā navatambalohabhājane pakkhipitvā lohagandhaṃ gāhāpetvā rajjuṃ vā yottaṃ vā rukkhaṃ vā lataṃ vā gahetvā‘ idaṃ te rogassa anucchavikabhesajjaṃ, idaṃ vā piva, uṭṭhāya vā tayā bhuttabhattassa anucchavikaṃ kammaṃ karohī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthaṃ vadeyyāsi."
487416,110,2835,95,129,1,193,28,"‘‘ Sace bhesajjaṃ na pivati, atha naṃ rajjuyā vā yottena vā rukkhena vā latāya vā katici pahāre paharitvā kesesu gahetvā ākaḍḍhitvā kapparena potheyyāsi, sā taṅkhaṇaññeva uṭṭhāya kammaṃ karissatī’’ ti. "
487417,110,2835,130,152,1,92,13,"So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā vuttaniyāmeneva bhesajjaṃ katvā‘‘ bhadde, imaṃ bhesajjaṃ pivā’’ ti āha."
487418,110,2835,153,162,1,26,5,‘‘ Kena te idaṃ ācikkhitan’’ ti? 
487419,110,2835,163,172,1,19,3,"‘‘ Ācariyena, bhadde’’ ti."
487420,110,2835,173,183,1,27,5,"‘‘ Apanehi taṃ, na pivissāmī’’ ti. "
487421,110,2835,184,216,1,165,23,"Māṇavo‘‘ na tvaṃ attano ruciyā pivissasī’’ ti rajjuṃ gahetvā‘‘ attano rogassa anucchavikaṃ bhesajjaṃ vā piva, yāgubhattānucchavikaṃ kammaṃ vā karohī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487422,110,2836,2,4,1,0,0,130.
487423,110,2837,2,10,1,45,6,"‘ ‘ Yathāvācā ca bhuñjassu, yathābhuttañca byāhara; "
487424,110,2838,2,13,1,45,8,"Ubhayaṃ te na sameti, vācā bhuttañca kosiye’’ ti. "
487425,110,2839,2,27,1,129,18,"Tattha yathāvācā ca {bhuñjassū}ti yathā te vācā, tathā bhuñjassu,‘‘ vātā me vijjhantī’’ ti vācāya anucchavikameva katvā bhuñjassūti attho."
487426,110,2839,28,49,1,82,11,"‘‘ Yathāvācaṃ vā’’ tipi pāṭho yujjati,‘‘ yathāvācāyā’’ tipi paṭhanti, sabbattha ayameva attho. "
487427,110,2839,50,74,1,123,16,"Yathābhuttañca {byāharā}ti yaṃ yathā te bhuttaṃ, tassa anucchavikameva byāhara,‘‘ arogamhī’’ ti vatvā gehe kattabbaṃ karosīti attho."
487428,110,2839,75,92,1,86,11,"‘‘ Yathābhūtañcā’’ tipi pāṭho, atha vā arogamhīti yathābhūtameva vatvā kammaṃ karohīti attho. "
487429,110,2839,93,130,1,181,29,"Ubhayaṃ te na sameti, vācābhuttañca {kosiye}ti yā ca te ayaṃ vācā‘‘ vātā maṃ vijjhantī’’ ti yañca te idaṃ paṇītabhojanaṃ bhuttaṃ, idaṃ ubhayampi tuyhaṃ na sameti, tasmā uṭṭhāya kammaṃ karohi."
487430,110,2839,131,139,1,27,4,‘‘ Kosiye’’ ti taṃ gottenālapati. 
487431,110,2840,2,26,1,147,19,"Evaṃ vutte kosiyabrāhmaṇadhītā‘‘ ācariyena ussukkaṃ āpannakālato paṭṭhāya na sakkā mayā esa vañcetuṃ, uṭṭhāya kammaṃ karissāmī’’ ti uṭṭhāya kammaṃ akāsi."
487432,110,2840,27,51,1,137,19,"‘‘ Ācariyena me dussīlabhāvo ñāto, idāni na sakkā ito paṭṭhāya puna evarūpaṃ kātun’’ ti ācariye gāravena pāpakammatopi viramitvā sīlavatī ahosi. "
487433,110,2840,52,68,1,89,12,Sāpi brāhmaṇī‘‘ sammāsambuddhena kiramhi ñātā’’ ti sattharipi gāravena na puna anācāraṃ akāsi. 
487434,110,2841,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487435,110,2841,9,23,1,67,9,"‘‘ tadā jayampatikā idāni jayampatikāva, ācariyo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487436,110,2842,2,4,1,26,2,Kosiyajātakavaṇṇanā dasamā. 
487437,110,2843,2,4,1,22,2,Kusanāḷivaggo terasamo. 
487438,110,2844,2,3,1,11,1,Tassuddānaṃ – 
487439,110,2845,2,8,1,41,4,"Kusanāḷi ca dummedhaṃ, naṅgalīsambakaṭāhaṃ; "
487440,110,2846,2,5,1,42,2,"Asilakkhaṇakalaṇḍukaṃ , biḷāraggikakosiyanti."
487441,110,2847,2,4,1,15,2,14 . Asampadānavaggo
487442,110,2849,2,7,1,23,2,[ 131]1. Asampadānajātakavaṇṇanā 
487443,110,2850,2,12,1,83,8,{Asampadānenitarītarassā}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487444,110,2850,13,32,1,114,14,"Tasmiñhi kāle bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso devadatto, akataññū tathāgatassa guṇaṃ na jānātī’’ ti. "
487445,110,2850,33,75,1,179,25,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva devadatto akataññū, pubbepi akataññūyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487446,110,2851,2,17,1,135,14,Atīte magadharaṭṭhe rājagahe ekasmiṃ magadharaññe rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tasseva seṭṭhi ahosi asītikoṭivibhavo saṅkhaseṭṭhīti nāmena. 
487447,110,2851,18,23,1,54,5,Bārāṇasiyaṃ pīḷiyaseṭṭhi nāma asītikoṭivibhavova ahosi. 
487448,110,2851,24,28,1,29,4,Te aññamaññaṃ sahāyakā ahesuṃ. 
487449,110,2851,29,41,1,103,11,"Tesu bārāṇasiyaṃ pīḷiyaseṭṭhissa kenacideva kāraṇena mahantaṃ bhayaṃ uppajji, sabbaṃ sāpateyyaṃ parihāyi. "
487450,110,2851,42,59,1,155,17,So daliddo appaṭisaraṇo hutvā bhariyaṃ ādāya saṅkhaseṭṭhiṃ paccayaṃ katvā bārāṇasito nikkhamitvā padasāva rājagahaṃ patvā saṅkhaseṭṭhissa nivesanaṃ agamāsi. 
487451,110,2851,60,87,1,136,18,"So taṃ disvāva‘‘ sahāyo me āgato’’ ti parissajitvā sakkārasammānaṃ katvā katipāhaṃ vītināmetvā ekadivasaṃ‘‘ samma, kenaṭṭhena āgatosī’’ ti pucchi."
487452,110,2851,88,107,1,73,11,"‘‘ Bhayaṃ me, samma, uppannaṃ, sabbaṃ dhanaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ, upatthambho me hohī’’ ti."
487453,110,2851,108,134,1,190,21,"‘‘ Sādhu samma, mā bhāyī’’ ti bhaṇḍāgāraṃ vivarāpetvā cattālīsa hiraññakoṭiyo dāpetvā sesampi paricchadaparivāraṃ sabbaṃ attano santakaṃ saviññāṇakaṃ aviññāṇakaṃ majjhe bhinditvā upaḍḍhameva adāsi. "
487454,110,2851,135,144,1,59,9,So taṃ vibhavaṃ ādāya puna bārāṇasiṃ gantvā nivāsaṃ kappesi. 
487455,110,2852,2,8,1,54,5,Aparabhāge saṅkhaseṭṭhissapi tādisameva bhayaṃ uppajji. 
487456,110,2852,9,22,1,84,10,"So attano paṭisaraṇaṃ upadhārento‘‘ sahāyassa me mahāupakāro kato, upaḍḍhavibhavo dinno. "
487457,110,2852,23,63,1,245,32,"Na so maṃ disvā pariccajissati, tassa santikaṃ gamissāmī’’ ti cintetvā bhariyaṃ ādāya padasāva bārāṇasiṃ gantvā bhariyaṃ āha‘‘ bhadde, tava mayā saddhiṃ antaravīthiyā gamanaṃ nāma na yuttaṃ, mayā pesitayānamāruyha mahantena parivārena pacchā āgamissasi. "
487458,110,2852,64,96,1,181,25,"Yāva yānaṃ pesemi, tāva idheva hohī’’ ti vatvā taṃ sālāya ṭhapetvā sayaṃ nagaraṃ pavisitvā seṭṭhissa gharaṃ gantvā‘‘ rājagahanagarato tumhākaṃ sahāyo saṅkhaseṭṭhi nāma āgato’’ ti ārocāpesi. "
487459,110,2852,97,124,1,117,17,"So‘‘ āgacchatū’’ ti pakkosāpetvā taṃ disvā neva āsanā vuṭṭhāsi, na paṭisanthāraṃ akāsi, kevalaṃ‘‘ kimatthaṃ āgatosī’’ ti pucchi."
487460,110,2852,125,133,1,33,4,‘‘ Tumhākaṃ dassanatthaṃ āgatomhī’’ ti.
487461,110,2852,134,144,1,25,5,‘‘ Nivāso te kahaṃ gahito’’ ti?
487462,110,2852,145,159,1,74,9,"‘‘ Na tāva nivāsaṭṭhānaṃ atthi, seṭṭhigharaṇimpi sālāya ṭhapetvāva āgatomhī’’ ti."
487463,110,2852,160,198,1,218,28,"‘‘ Tumhākaṃ idha nivāsaṭṭhānaṃ natthi, nivāpaṃ gahetvā ekasmiṃ ṭhāne pacāpetvā bhuñjitvā gacchatha, puna amhākaṃ gharaṃ mā pavisathā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ mayhaṃ sahāyassa dussante bandhitvā ekaṃ bahalapalāpatumbaṃ dehī’’ ti dāsaṃ āṇāpesi. "
487464,110,2852,199,218,1,174,18,"Taṃ divasaṃ kira so rattasālīnaṃ sakaṭasahassamattaṃ ophunāpetvā koṭṭhāgāraṃ pūrāpesi, cattālīsakoṭidhanaṃ gahetvā āgato akataññū mahācoro sahāyakassa tumbamatte palāpe dāpesi. "
487465,110,2852,219,227,1,75,8,Dāso pacchiyaṃ ekaṃ palāpatumbaṃ pakkhipitvā bodhisattassa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
487466,110,2853,2,4,1,18,2,Bodhisatto cintesi–
487467,110,2853,5,26,1,112,15,"‘‘ ayaṃ asappuriso mama santikā cattālīsakoṭidhanaṃ labhitvā idāni palāpatumbaṃ dāpesi, gaṇhāmi nu kho, na gaṇhāmī’’ ti? "
487468,110,2853,27,40,1,100,11,Athassa etadahosi‘‘ ayaṃ tāva akataññū mittadubbhī katavināsakabhāvena mayā saddhiṃ mittabhāvaṃ bhindi. 
487469,110,2853,41,52,1,88,10,"Sacāhaṃ etena dinnaṃ palāpatumbaṃ lāmakattā na gaṇhissāmi, ahampi mittabhāvaṃ bhindissāmi. "
487470,110,2853,53,73,1,148,17,"Andhabālā parittakaṃ laddhaṃ aggaṇhantā mittabhāvaṃ vināsenti, ahaṃ pana etena dinnaṃ palāpatumbaṃ gahetvā mama vasena mittabhāvaṃ patiṭṭhāpessāmī’’ ti. "
487471,110,2853,74,82,1,62,8,So palāpatumbaṃ dussante bandhitvā pāsādā oruyha sālaṃ agamāsi. 
487472,110,2853,83,98,1,46,9,"Atha naṃ bhariyā‘‘ kiṃ te, ayya, laddhan’’ ti pucchi."
487473,110,2853,99,114,1,79,10,‘‘ Bhadde amhākaṃ sahāyo pīḷiyaseṭṭhi palāpatumbaṃ datvā amhe ajjeva vissajjesī’’ ti. 
487474,110,2853,115,132,1,88,11,"Sā‘‘ ayya, kimatthaṃ aggahesi, kiṃ etaṃ cattālīsakoṭidhanassa anucchavikan’’ ti rodituṃ ārabhi. "
487475,110,2853,133,160,1,161,20,"Bodhisattopi‘‘ bhadde, mā rodi, ahaṃ tena saddhiṃ mittabhāvabhedanabhayena mama vasena mittabhāvaṃ patiṭṭhāpetuṃ gaṇhiṃ, tvaṃ kiṃkāraṇā rodasī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487476,110,2854,2,4,1,0,0,131.
487477,110,2855,2,9,1,52,5,"‘ ‘ Asampadānenitarītarassa, bālassa mittāni kalībhavanti; "
487478,110,2856,2,16,1,65,10,"Tasmā harāmi bhusaṃ aḍḍhamānaṃ, mā me mitti jīyittha sassatāyan’’ ti. "
487479,110,2857,2,7,1,34,3,Tattha {asampadānenā}ti asampādānena. 
487480,110,2857,8,13,1,35,4,"Akāralope sandhi, aggahaṇenāti attho. "
487481,110,2857,14,19,1,44,4,{Itarītarassā}ti yassa kassaci lāmakālāmakassa. 
487482,110,2857,20,33,1,107,11,"Bālassa mittāni {kalībhavantī}ti dandhassa apaññassa mittāni kalīni kāḷakaṇṇisadisāni honti, bhijjantīti attho. "
487483,110,2857,34,48,1,109,14,Tasmā harāmi bhusaṃ aḍḍhamānan ti tena kāraṇena ahaṃ sahāyena dinnaṃ ekapalāpatumbaṃ harāmi gaṇhāmīti dasseti.
487484,110,2857,49,68,1,84,13,"‘‘ Mānan’’ ti hi aṭṭhannaṃ nāḷīnaṃ nāmaṃ, catunnaṃ aḍḍhamānaṃ, catasso ca nāḷiyo tumbo nāma. "
487485,110,2857,69,77,1,27,4,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ palāpatumban’’ ti. 
487486,110,2857,78,95,1,104,16,"Mā me mitti jīyittha sassatāyan ti mama sahāyena saddhiṃ mitti mā bhijjittha, sassatāva ayaṃ hotūti attho. "
487487,110,2858,2,6,1,35,4,Evaṃ vuttepi seṭṭhibhariyā rodateva. 
487488,110,2858,7,37,1,228,25,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe saṅkhaseṭṭhinā pīḷiyaseṭṭhissa dinno kammantadāso sālādvārena āgacchanto seṭṭhibhariyāya rodanasaddaṃ sutvā sālaṃ pavisitvā attano sāmike disvā pādesu nipatitvā roditvā kanditvā‘‘ kimatthaṃ idhāgatattha, sāmī’’ ti pucchi. "
487489,110,2858,38,41,1,21,3,Seṭṭhi sabbaṃ ārocesi. 
487490,110,2858,42,83,1,231,30,"Kammantadāso‘‘ hotu, sāmi, mā cintayitthā’’ ti ubhopi assāsetvā attano gehaṃ netvā gandhodakena nhāpetvā bhojetvā‘‘ sāmikā, vo āgatā’’ ti sesadāse sannipātetvā dassetvā katipāhaṃ vītināmetvā sabbe dāse gahetvā rājaṅgaṇaṃ gantvā uparavaṃ akāsi. "
487491,110,2858,84,101,1,74,12,"Rājā pakkosāpetvā‘‘ kiṃ etan’’ ti pucchi, te sabbaṃ taṃ pavattiṃ rañño ārocesuṃ. "
487492,110,2859,2,24,1,146,17,Rājā tesaṃ vacanaṃ sutvā ubhopi seṭṭhī pakkosāpetvā saṅkhaseṭṭhiṃ pucchi‘‘ saccaṃ kira tayā mahāseṭṭhi pīḷiyaseṭṭhissa cattālīsakoṭidhanaṃ dinnan’’ ti?
487493,110,2859,25,50,1,160,20,"‘‘ Āma, mahārāja, mama sahāyassa maṃ takketvā rājagahaṃ āgatassa na kevalaṃ dhanaṃ, sabbaṃ vibhavajātaṃ saviññāṇakaṃ aviññāṇakaṃ dve koṭṭhāse katvā samabhāge adāsinti. "
487494,110,2859,51,60,1,39,5,Rājā‘‘ saccametan’’ ti pīḷiyaseṭṭhiṃ pucchi.
487495,110,2859,61,69,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, devā’’ ti."
487496,110,2859,70,87,1,79,13,‘‘ Tayā panassa taññeva takketvā āgatassa atthi koci sakkāro vā sammāno vā kato’’ ti. 
487497,110,2859,88,91,1,14,3,So tuṇhī ahosi. 
487498,110,2859,92,102,1,75,9,Api pana te etassa palāpatumbamattaṃ dussante pakkhipāpetvā dāpitaṃ atthīti. 
487499,110,2859,103,107,1,27,4,Tampi sutvā tuṇhīyeva ahosi. 
487500,110,2859,108,135,1,140,18,"Rājā‘‘ kiṃ kātabban’’ ti amaccehi saddhiṃ mantetvā taṃ paribhāsitvā‘‘ gacchatha, pīḷiyaseṭṭhissa ghare sabbaṃ vibhavaṃ saṅkhaseṭṭhissa dethā’’ ti āha. "
487501,110,2859,136,154,1,93,12,"Bodhisatto‘‘ mahārāja, mayhaṃ parasantakena attho natthi, mayā dinnamattameva pana dāpethā’’ ti āha. "
487502,110,2859,155,159,1,34,4,Rājā bodhisattassa santakaṃ dāpesi. 
487503,110,2859,160,175,1,145,15,Bodhisatto sabbaṃ attano dinnavibhavaṃ paṭilabhitvā dāsaparivuto rājagahameva gantvā kuṭumbaṃ saṇṭhapetvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
487504,110,2860,2,9,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487505,110,2860,10,24,1,69,9,"‘‘ tadā pīḷiyaseṭṭhi devadatto ahosi, saṅkhaseṭṭhi pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487506,110,2861,2,4,1,31,2,Asampadānajātakavaṇṇanā paṭhamā.
487507,110,2863,2,7,1,20,2,[ 132]2. Bhīrukajātakavaṇṇanā 
487508,110,2864,2,16,1,128,13,Kusalūpadese dhitiyā daḷhāya {cā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ajapālanigrodhe māradhītānaṃ palobhanasuttantaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487509,110,2864,17,22,1,34,5,Bhagavatā hi ādito paṭṭhāya vuttaṃ–
487510,110,2865,2,11,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Daddallamānā āgañchuṃ, taṇhā ca aratī ragā; "
487511,110,2866,2,23,1,50,8,"Tā tattha panudī satthā, tūlaṃ bhaṭṭhaṃva māluto’’ ti.( saṃ. ni.1.161); "
487512,110,2867,2,37,1,271,28,"Evaṃ yāva pariyosānā tassa suttantassa kathitakāle dhammasabhāyaṃ sannipatitā bhikkhū kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, sammāsambuddho māradhītaro anekasatānipi dibbarūpāni māpetvā palobhanatthāya upasaṅkamantiyo akkhīnipi ummīletvā na olokesi, aho buddhabalaṃ nāma acchariyan’’ ti. "
487513,110,2867,38,99,1,378,44,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva mayhaṃ sabbāsave khepetvā sabbaññutaṃ sampattassa māradhītānaṃ anolokanaṃ nāma acchariyaṃ, ahañhi pubbe bodhiñāṇaṃ pariyesamāno sakilesakālepi abhisaṅkhataṃ dibbarūpaṃ indriyāni bhinditvā kilesavasena anoloketvāva gantvā mahārajjaṃ pāpuṇin’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487514,110,2868,2,17,1,146,14,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto bhātikasatassa kaniṭṭho ahosīti sabbaṃ heṭṭhā takkasilājātake vuttanayeneva vitthāretabbaṃ. 
487515,110,2868,18,39,1,211,20,"Tadā pana takkasilānagaravāsīhi bahinagare sālāyaṃ bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā yācitvā rajjaṃ paṭicchāpetvā abhiseke kate takkasilānagaravāsino nagaraṃ devanagaraṃ viya, rājabhavanañca indabhavanaṃ viya alaṅkariṃsu. "
487516,110,2868,40,70,1,351,27,"Tadā bodhisatto nagaraṃ pavisitvā rājabhavane pāsāde mahātale samussitasetacchattaṃ ratanavarapallaṅkaṃ abhiruyha devarājalīlāya nisīdi, amaccā ca brāhmaṇagahapatikādayo ca khattiyakumārā ca sabbālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍitā parivāretvā aṭṭhaṃsu, devaccharāpaṭibhāgā soḷasasahassanāṭakitthiyo naccagītavāditakusalā uttamavilāsasampannā naccagītavāditāni payojesuṃ. "
487517,110,2868,71,78,1,91,7,Gītavāditasaddena rājabhavanaṃ meghatthanitapūritā mahāsamuddakucchi viya ekaninnādaṃ ahosi. 
487518,110,2868,79,102,1,181,19,"Bodhisatto taṃ attano sirisobhaggaṃ olokayamānova cintesi‘‘ sacāhaṃ tāsaṃ yakkhinīnaṃ abhisaṅkhataṃ dibbarūpaṃ olokessaṃ, jīvitakkhayaṃ patto abhavissaṃ, imaṃ sirisobhaggaṃ na olokessaṃ. "
487519,110,2868,103,113,1,63,8,Paccekabuddhānaṃ pana ovāde ṭhitabhāvena idaṃ mayā sampattan’’ ti. 
487520,110,2868,114,121,1,51,7,Evañca pana cintetvā udānaṃ udānento imaṃ gāthamāha– 
487521,110,2869,2,4,1,0,0,132.
487522,110,2870,2,12,1,63,8,"‘ ‘ Kusalūpadese dhitiyā daḷhāya ca, anivattitattā bhayabhīrutāya ca; "
487523,110,2871,2,14,1,66,9,"Na rakkhasīnaṃ vasamāgamimhase, sa sotthibhāvo mahatā bhayena me’’ ti. "
487524,110,2872,2,12,1,70,7,"Tattha {kusalūpadese}ti kusalānaṃ upadese, paccekabuddhānaṃ ovādeti attho. "
487525,110,2872,13,25,1,87,10,"Dhitiyā daḷhāya {cā}ti daḷhāya dhitiyā ca, thirena abbocchinnanirantaravīriyena cāti attho. "
487526,110,2872,26,33,1,66,6,Anivattitattā bhayabhīrutāya {cā}ti bhayabhīrutāya anivattitatāya ca. 
487527,110,2872,34,39,1,47,5,Tattha bhayan ti cittutrāsamattaṃ parittabhayaṃ. 
487528,110,2872,40,44,1,41,3,{Bhīrutā}ti sarīrakampanappattaṃ mahābhayaṃ. 
487529,110,2872,45,59,1,94,10,Idaṃ ubhayampi mahāsattassa‘‘ yakkhiniyo nāmetā manussakhādikā’’ ti bheravārammaṇaṃ disvāpi nāhosi. 
487530,110,2872,60,69,1,41,5,Tenāha‘‘ anivattitattā bhayabhīrutāya cā’’ ti. 
487531,110,2872,70,76,1,75,6,Bhayabhīrutāya abhāveneva bheravārammaṇaṃ disvāpi anivattanabhāvenāti attho. 
487532,110,2872,77,87,1,82,9,Na rakkhasīnaṃ {vasamāgamimhase}ti yakkhakantāre tāsaṃ rakkhasīnaṃ vasaṃ na agamimha. 
487533,110,2872,88,109,1,145,18,"Yasmā amhākaṃ kusalūpadese dhiti ca daḷhā ahosi, bhayabhīrutābhāvena ca anivattanasabhāvā ahumhā, tasmā rakkhasīnaṃ vasaṃ na agamimhāti vuttaṃ hoti. "
487534,110,2872,110,130,1,171,19,Sa sotthibhāvo mahatā bhayena {me}ti so mayhaṃ ayaṃ ajja mahatā bhayena rakkhasīnaṃ santikā pattabbena dukkhadomanassena sotthibhāvo khemabhāvo pītisomanassabhāvoyeva jātoti. 
487535,110,2873,2,16,1,108,14,Evaṃ mahāsatto imāya gāthāya dhammaṃ desetvā dhammena rajjaṃ kāretvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
487536,110,2874,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487537,110,2874,9,21,1,64,8,‘‘ ahaṃ tena samayena takkasilaṃ gantvā rajjappattakumāro ahosin’’ ti. 
487538,110,2875,2,4,1,27,2,Bhīrukajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
487539,110,2877,2,7,1,22,2,[ 133]3. Ghatāsanajātakavaṇṇanā 
487540,110,2878,2,14,1,81,11,Khemaṃ yahin ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487541,110,2878,15,30,1,122,15,So hi bhikkhu satthu santike kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā paccantaṃ gantvā ekaṃ gāmakaṃ upanissāya araññasenāsane vassaṃ upagañchi. 
487542,110,2878,31,37,1,61,6,Tassa paṭhamamāseyeva piṇḍāya paviṭṭhassa paṇṇasālā jhāyittha. 
487543,110,2878,38,43,1,53,5,So vasanaṭṭhānābhāvena kilamanto upaṭṭhākānaṃ ācikkhi. 
487544,110,2878,44,66,1,96,13,"Te‘‘ hotu, bhante, paṇṇasālaṃ karissāma, kasāma tāva, vapāma tāvā’’ tiādīni vadantā temāsaṃ vītināmesuṃ. "
487545,110,2878,67,73,1,65,6,So senāsanasappāyābhāvena kammaṭṭhānaṃ matthakaṃ pāpetuṃ nāsakkhi. 
487546,110,2878,74,84,1,95,10,So nimittamattampi anuppādetvā vutthavasso jetavanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
487547,110,2878,85,106,1,99,15,"Satthā tena saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ kiṃ nu kho te, bhikkhu, kammaṭṭhānaṃ sappāyaṃ jātan’’ ti pucchi. "
487548,110,2878,107,112,1,40,5,So ādito paṭṭhāya asappāyabhāvaṃ kathesi. 
487549,110,2878,113,147,1,216,27,"Satthā‘‘ pubbe kho, bhikkhu, tiracchānāpi attano sappāyāsappāyaṃ ñatvā sappāyakāle vasitvā asappāyakāle vasanaṭṭhānaṃ pahāya aññattha agamaṃsu, tvaṃ kasmā attano sappāyāsappāyaṃ na aññāsī’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
487550,110,2879,2,25,1,251,23,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sakuṇayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patvā sobhaggappatto sakuṇarājā hutvā ekasmiṃ araññāyatane jātassaratīre sākhāviṭapasampannaṃ bahalapattapalāsaṃ mahārukkhaṃ upanissāya saparivāro vāsaṃ kappesi. 
487551,110,2879,26,37,1,94,10,Bahū sakuṇā tassa rukkhassa udakamatthake patthaṭasākhāsu vasantā sarīravaḷañjaṃ udake pātenti. 
487552,110,2879,38,43,1,40,5,Tasmiñca jātassare caṇḍo nāgarājā vasati. 
487553,110,2879,44,67,1,144,18,"Tassa etadahosi‘‘ ime sakuṇā mayhaṃ nivāse jātassare sarīravaḷañjaṃ pātenti, yaṃnūnāhaṃ udakato aggiṃ uṭṭhāpetvā rukkhaṃ jhāpetvā ete palāpeyyan’’ ti. "
487554,110,2879,68,89,1,216,21,So kuddhamānaso rattibhāge sabbesaṃ sakuṇānaṃ sannipatitvā rukkhasākhāsu nipannakāle paṭhamaṃ tāva uddhanāropitaṃ viya udakaṃ pakkudhāpetvā dutiyavāre dhūmaṃ uṭṭhāpetvā tatiyavāre tālakkhandhappamāṇaṃ jālaṃ uṭṭhāpesi. 
487555,110,2879,90,111,1,122,16,"Bodhisatto udakato jālaṃ uṭṭhahamānaṃ disvā‘‘ bho, sakuṇā, agginā ādittaṃ nāma udakena nibbāpenti, idāni pana udakameva ādittaṃ. "
487556,110,2879,112,126,1,71,11,"Na sakkā amhehi idha vasituṃ, aññattha gamissāmā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487557,110,2880,2,4,1,0,0,133.
487558,110,2881,2,14,1,63,10,"‘ ‘ Khemaṃ yahiṃ tattha arī udīrito, dakassa majjhe jalate ghatāsano; "
487559,110,2882,2,15,1,64,10,"Na ajja vāso mahiyā mahīruhe, disā bhajavho saraṇājja nobhayan’’ ti. "
487560,110,2883,2,19,1,123,14,"Tattha khemaṃ yahiṃ tattha arī {udīrito}ti yasmiṃ udakapiṭṭhe khemabhāvo nibbhayabhāvo, tasmiṃ attapaccatthiko sapatto uṭṭhito. "
487561,110,2883,20,23,1,18,2,{Dakassā}ti udakassa. 
487562,110,2883,24,27,1,16,2,{Ghatāsano}ti aggi. 
487563,110,2883,28,42,1,46,8,"So hi ghataṃ asnāti, tasmā‘‘ ghatāsano’’ ti vuccati. "
487564,110,2883,43,51,1,34,7,Na ajja {vāso}ti ajja no vāso natthi. 
487565,110,2883,52,65,1,82,11,"Mahiyā {mahīruhe}ti mahiruho vuccati rukkho, tasmiṃ imissā mahiyā jāte rukkheti attho. "
487566,110,2883,66,72,1,39,5,Disā {bhajavho}ti disā bhajatha gacchatha. 
487567,110,2883,73,87,1,100,13,"Saraṇājja no bhayan ti ajja amhākaṃ saraṇato bhayaṃ jātaṃ, paṭisaraṇaṭṭhānato bhayaṃ uppannanti attho. "
487568,110,2884,2,12,1,76,10,Evaṃ vatvā bodhisatto attano vacanakare sakuṇe ādāya uppatitvā aññattha gato. 
487569,110,2884,13,19,1,63,6,Bodhisattassa vacanaṃ aggahetvā ṭhitasakuṇā jīvitakkhayaṃ pattā. 
487570,110,2885,2,16,1,119,13,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne so bhikkhu arahatte patiṭṭhāsi. "
487571,110,2886,2,13,1,89,10,"Tadā bodhisattassa vacanakarā sakuṇā buddhaparisā ahesuṃ, sakuṇarājā pana ahameva ahosinti. "
487572,110,2887,2,4,1,29,2,Ghatāsanajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
487573,110,2889,2,7,1,25,2,[ 134]4. Jhānasodhanajātakavaṇṇanā 
487574,110,2890,2,18,1,151,14,Ye {saññino}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto saṅkassanagaradvāre attanā saṃkhittena pucchitapañhassa dhammasenāpatino vitthārabyākaraṇaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487575,110,2890,19,49,1,202,23,Tatridaṃ atītavatthu– atīte kira bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto araññāyatane kālaṃ karonto antevāsikehi pucchito‘‘ nevasaññīnāsaññī’’ ti āha… pe… tāpasā jeṭṭhantevāsikassa kathaṃ na gaṇhiṃsu. 
487576,110,2890,50,57,1,58,7,Bodhisatto ābhassarato āgantvā ākāse ṭhatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
487577,110,2891,2,4,1,0,0,134.
487578,110,2892,2,13,1,50,9,"‘ ‘ Ye saññino tepi duggatā, yepi asaññino tepi duggatā; "
487579,110,2893,2,12,1,55,7,"Etaṃ ubhayaṃ vivajjaya, taṃ samāpattisukhaṃ anaṅgaṇan’’ ti. "
487580,110,2894,2,12,1,89,8,Tattha ye {saññino}ti ṭhapetvā nevasaññānāsaññāyatanalābhino avasese sacittakasatte dasseti. 
487581,110,2894,13,22,1,59,8,Tepi {duggatā}ti tassā samāpattiyā alābhato tepi duggatā nāma. 
487582,110,2894,23,31,1,58,6,Yepi {asaññino}ti asaññabhave nibbatte acittakasatte dasseti. 
487583,110,2894,32,41,1,68,8,Tepi {duggatā}ti tepi imissāyeva samāpattiyā alābhato duggatāyeva nāma. 
487584,110,2894,42,54,1,107,11,Etaṃ ubhayaṃ {vivajjayā}ti etaṃ ubhayampi saññibhavañca asaññibhavañca vivajjaya pajahāti antevāsikaṃ ovadati. 
487585,110,2894,55,78,1,197,19,Taṃ samāpattisukhaṃ anaṅgaṇan ti taṃ nevasaññānāsaññāyatanasamāpattilābhino santaṭṭhena‘‘ sukhan’’ ti saṅkhaṃ gataṃ jhānasukhaṃ anaṅgaṇaṃ niddosaṃ balavacittekaggatāsabhāvenapi taṃ anaṅgaṇaṃ nāma jātaṃ. 
487586,110,2895,2,11,1,83,9,Evaṃ bodhisatto dhammaṃ desetvā antevāsikassa guṇaṃ kathetvā brahmalokameva agamāsi. 
487587,110,2895,12,16,1,45,4,Tadā sesatāpasā jeṭṭhantevāsikassa saddahiṃsu. 
487588,110,2896,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487589,110,2896,9,22,1,64,8,"‘‘ tadā jeṭṭhantevāsiko sāriputto, mahābrahmā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487590,110,2897,2,4,1,34,2,Jhānasodhanajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
487591,110,2899,2,7,1,21,2,[ 135]5. Candābhajātakavaṇṇanā 
487592,110,2900,2,14,1,106,11,Candābhan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto saṅkassanagaradvāre therasseva pañhabyākaraṇaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487593,110,2900,15,37,1,158,18,Atīte kira bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto araññāyatane kālaṃ karonto antevāsikehi pucchito‘‘ candābhaṃ sūriyābhan’’ ti vatvā ābhassare nibbatto. 
487594,110,2900,38,42,1,39,4,Tāpasā jeṭṭhantevāsikassa na saddahiṃsu. 
487595,110,2900,43,50,1,57,7,Bodhisatto ābhassarato āgantvā ākāse ṭhito imaṃ gāthamāha– 
487596,110,2901,2,4,1,0,0,135.
487597,110,2902,2,10,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Candābhaṃ sūriyābhañca, yodha paññāya gādhati; "
487598,110,2903,2,10,1,40,5,"Avitakkena jhānena, hoti ābhassarūpago’’ ti. "
487599,110,2904,2,7,1,40,5,Tattha candābhan ti odātakasiṇaṃ dasseti. 
487600,110,2904,8,11,1,25,3,Sūriyābhan ti pītakasiṇaṃ. 
487601,110,2904,12,32,1,133,16,"Yodha paññāya {gādhatī}ti yo puggalo idha sattaloke idaṃ kasiṇadvayaṃ paññāya gādhati, ārammaṇaṃ katvā anupavisati, tattheva patiṭṭhahati . "
487602,110,2904,33,65,1,225,28,"Atha vā candābhaṃ sūriyābhañca, yodha paññāya {gādhatī}ti yattakaṃ ṭhānaṃ candābhā ca sūriyābhā ca patthaṭā, tatthake ṭhāne paṭibhāgakasiṇaṃ vaḍḍhetvā taṃ ārammaṇaṃ katvā jhānaṃ nibbattento ubhayampetaṃ ābhaṃ paññāya gādhati nāma. "
487603,110,2904,66,69,1,26,3,Tasmā ayampettha atthoyeva. 
487604,110,2904,70,85,1,123,13,"Avitakkena jhānena, hoti {ābhassarūpago}ti so puggalo tathā katvā paṭiladdhena dutiyena jhānena ābhassarabrahmalokūpago hotīti. "
487605,110,2905,2,11,1,85,9,Evaṃ bodhisatto tāpase bodhetvā jeṭṭhantevāsikassa guṇaṃ kathetvā brahmalokameva gato. 
487606,110,2906,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487607,110,2906,9,22,1,64,8,"‘‘ tadā jeṭṭhantevāsiko sāriputto, mahābrahmā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487608,110,2907,2,4,1,29,2,Candābhajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
487609,110,2909,2,7,1,25,2,[ 136]6. Suvaṇṇahaṃsajātakavaṇṇanā 
487610,110,2910,2,15,1,101,13,Yaṃ laddhaṃ tena tuṭṭhabban ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto thullanandaṃ bhikkhuniṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487611,110,2910,16,39,1,160,18,"Sāvatthiyañhi aññataro upāsako bhikkhunisaṅghaṃ lasuṇena pavāretvā khettapālaṃ āṇāpesi‘‘ sace bhikkhuniyo āgacchanti, ekekāya bhikkhuniyā dve tayo bhaṇḍike dehī’’ ti. "
487612,110,2910,40,49,1,72,8,Tato paṭṭhāya bhikkhuniyo tassa gehampi khettampi lasuṇatthāya gacchanti. 
487613,110,2910,50,57,1,62,7,Athekasmiṃ ussavadivase tassa gehe lasuṇaṃ parikkhayaṃ agamāsi. 
487614,110,2910,58,92,1,193,24,"Thullanandā bhikkhunī saparivārā gehaṃ gantvā‘‘ lasuṇenāvuso attho’’ ti vatvā‘‘ natthayye, yathābhataṃ lasuṇaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ, khettaṃ gacchathā’’ ti vuttā khettaṃ gantvā na mattaṃ jānitvā lasuṇaṃ āharāpesi. "
487615,110,2910,93,108,1,86,11,Khettapālo ujjhāyi‘‘ kathañhi nāma bhikkhuniyo na mattaṃ jānitvā lasuṇaṃ harāpessantī’’ ti? 
487616,110,2910,109,124,1,83,12,"Tassa kathaṃ sutvā yā tā bhikkhuniyo appicchā, tāpi, tāsaṃ sutvā bhikkhūpi, ujjhāyiṃsu. "
487617,110,2910,125,131,1,48,6,Ujjhāyitvā ca pana bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. 
487618,110,2910,132,171,1,253,31,"Bhagavā thullanandaṃ bhikkhaniṃ garahitvā‘‘ bhikkhave, mahiccho puggalo nāma vijātamātuyāpi appiyo hoti amanāpo, appasanne pasādetuṃ, pasannānaṃ vā bhiyyosomattāya pasādaṃ janetuṃ, anuppannaṃ vā lābhaṃ uppādetuṃ, uppannaṃ vā pana lābhaṃ thiraṃ kātuṃ na sakkoti. "
487619,110,2910,172,223,1,308,38,"Appiccho pana puggalo appasanne pasādetuṃ, pasannānaṃ vā bhiyyosomattāya pasādaṃ janetuṃ, anuppannaṃ vā lābhaṃ uppādetuṃ, uppannaṃ vā pana lābhaṃ thiraṃ kātuṃ sakkotī’’ tiādinā nayena bhikkhūnaṃ tadanucchavikaṃ dhammaṃ kathetvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, thullanandā idāneva mahicchā, pubbepi mahicchāyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487620,110,2911,2,11,1,90,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto aññatarasmiṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbatti. 
487621,110,2911,12,18,1,56,6,Tassa vayappattassa samānajātikā kulā pajāpatiṃ āhariṃsu. 
487622,110,2911,19,26,1,57,7,Tassā nandā nandāvatī sundarīnandāti tisso dhītaro ahesuṃ. 
487623,110,2911,27,38,1,106,10,"Tāsu patikulaṃ agatāsuyeva bodhisatto kālaṃ katvā suvaṇṇahaṃsayoniyaṃ nibbatti, jātissarañāṇañcassa uppajji. "
487624,110,2911,39,118,1,412,57,"So vayappatto suvaṇṇasañchannaṃ sobhaggappattaṃ mahantaṃ attabhāvaṃ disvā‘‘ kuto nu kho cavitvā ahaṃ idhūpapanno’’ ti āvajjento‘‘ manussalokato’’ ti ñatvā puna‘‘ kathaṃ nu kho me brāhmaṇī ca dhītaro ca jīvantī’’ ti upadhārento‘‘ paresaṃ bhatiṃ katvā kicchena jīvantī’’ ti ñatvā cintesi‘‘ mayhaṃ sarīre sovaṇṇamayāni pattāni koṭṭanaghaṭṭanakhamāni, ito tāsaṃ ekekaṃ pattaṃ dassāmi, tena me pajāpati ca dhītaro ca sukhaṃ jīvissantī’’ ti. "
487625,110,2911,119,142,1,114,16,"So tattha gantvā piṭṭhivaṃsakoṭiyaṃ nilīyi, brāhmaṇī ca dhītaro ca bodhisattaṃ disvā‘‘ kuto āgatosi, sāmī’’ ti pucchiṃsu."
487626,110,2911,143,155,1,79,10,‘‘ Ahaṃ tumhākaṃ pitā kālaṃ katvā suvaṇṇahaṃsayoniyaṃ nibbatto tumhe daṭṭhuṃ āgato. 
487627,110,2911,156,183,1,167,23,"Ito paṭṭhāya tumhākaṃ paresaṃ bhatiṃ katvā dukkhajīvikāya jīvanakiccaṃ natthi, ahaṃ vo ekekaṃ pattaṃ dassāmi, taṃ vikkiṇitvā sukhena jīvathā’’ ti ekaṃ pattaṃ datvā agamāsi. "
487628,110,2911,184,200,1,102,15,"So eteneva niyāmena antarantarā āgantvā ekekaṃ pattaṃ deti, brāhmaṇī ca dhītaro ca aḍḍhā sukhitā ahesuṃ. "
487629,110,2912,2,15,1,82,10,"Athekadivasaṃ sā brāhmaṇī dhītaro āmantesi‘‘ ammā, tiracchānānaṃ nāma cittaṃ dujjānaṃ. "
487630,110,2912,16,31,1,88,12,"Kadāci vo pitā idha nāgaccheyya, idānissa āgatakāle sabbāni pattānipi luñcitvā gaṇhāmā’’ ti. "
487631,110,2912,32,44,1,48,8,Tā‘‘ evaṃ no pitā kilamissatī’’ ti na sampaṭicchiṃsu. 
487632,110,2912,45,72,1,167,21,"Brāhmaṇī pana mahicchatāya puna ekadivasaṃ suvaṇṇahaṃsarājassa āgatakāle‘‘ ehi tāva, sāmī’’ ti vatvā taṃ attano santikaṃ upagataṃ ubhohi hatthehi gahetvā sabbapattāni luñci. "
487633,110,2912,73,83,1,89,10,Tāni pana bodhisattassa ruciṃ vinā balakkārena gahitattā sabbāni bakapattasadisāni ahesuṃ. 
487634,110,2912,84,89,1,43,5,Bodhisatto pakkhe pasāretvā gantuṃ nāsakkhi. 
487635,110,2912,90,96,1,42,6,Atha naṃ sā mahācāṭiyaṃ pakkhipitvā posesi. 
487636,110,2912,97,103,1,50,6,Tassa puna uṭṭhahantāni pattāni setāni sampajjiṃsu. 
487637,110,2912,104,113,1,72,9,So sañjātapatto uppatitvā attano vasanaṭṭhānameva gantvā na puna āgamāsi. 
487638,110,2913,2,25,1,131,16,"Satthā imaṃ atītaṃ āharitvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, thullanandā idāneva mahicchā, pubbepi mahicchāyeva , mahicchatāya ca pana suvaṇṇamhā parihīnā. "
487639,110,2913,26,41,1,110,14,"Idāni pana attano mahicchatāya eva lasuṇamhāpi parihāyissati, tasmā ito paṭṭhāya lasuṇaṃ khādituṃ na labhissati. "
487640,110,2913,42,50,1,55,7,"Yathā ca thullanandā, evaṃ taṃ nissāya sesabhikkhuniyopi. "
487641,110,2913,51,73,1,143,18,"Tasmā bahuṃ labhitvāpi pamāṇameva jānitabbaṃ, appaṃ labhitvā pana yathāladdheneva santoso kātabbo, uttari na patthetabban’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487642,110,2914,2,4,1,0,0,136.
487643,110,2915,2,12,1,46,8,"‘ ‘ Yaṃ laddhaṃ tena tuṭṭhabbaṃ, atilobho hi pāpako; "
487644,110,2916,2,10,1,43,5,"Haṃsarājaṃ gahetvāna, suvaṇṇā parihāyathā’’ ti. "
487645,110,2917,2,6,1,32,4,Tattha tuṭṭhabban ti tussitabbaṃ. 
487646,110,2918,2,30,1,140,17,"Idaṃ pana vatvā satthā anekapariyāyena garahitvā‘‘ yā pana bhikkhunī lasuṇaṃ khādeyya, pācittiyan’’ ti( pāci.794) sikkhāpadaṃ paññāpetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
487647,110,2918,31,52,1,116,15,"‘‘ tadā brāhmaṇī ayaṃ thullanandā ahosi, tisso dhītaro idāni tissoyeva bhaginiyo, suvaṇṇahaṃsarājā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487648,110,2919,2,4,1,33,2,Suvaṇṇahaṃsajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
487649,110,2921,2,7,1,18,2,[ 137]7. Babbujātakavaṇṇanā 
487650,110,2922,2,19,1,91,10,Yattheko labhate {babbū}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kāṇamātusikkhāpadaṃ( pāci.230 ādayo) ārabbha kathesi. 
487651,110,2922,20,30,1,86,9,Sāvatthiyañhi kāṇamātā nāma dhītuvasena pākaṭanāmā upāsikā ahosi sotāpannā ariyasāvikā. 
487652,110,2922,31,39,1,69,8,Sā dhītaraṃ kāṇaṃ aññatarasmiṃ gāmake samānajātikassa purisassa adāsi. 
487653,110,2922,40,46,1,46,6,Kāṇā kenacideva karaṇīyena mātu gharaṃ agamāsi. 
487654,110,2922,47,63,1,85,11,"Athassā sāmiko katipāhaccayena dūtaṃ pāhesi‘‘ āgacchatu kāṇā, icchāmi kāṇāya āgamanan’’ ti. "
487655,110,2922,64,78,1,60,9,"Kāṇā dūtassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ amma, gamissāmī’’ ti mātaraṃ āpucchi. "
487656,110,2922,79,93,1,76,10,Kāṇamātā‘‘ ettakaṃ kālaṃ vasitvā kathaṃ tucchahatthāva gamissasī’’ ti pūvaṃ paci. 
487657,110,2922,94,109,1,112,14,"Tasmiṃyeva khaṇe eko piṇḍacāriko bhikkhu tassā nivesanaṃ agamāsi, upāsikā taṃ nisīdāpetvā pattapūraṃ pūvaṃ dāpesi. "
487658,110,2922,110,119,1,61,8,"So bhikkhu nikkhamitvā aññassa ācikkhi, tassapi tatheva dāpesi. "
487659,110,2922,120,132,1,79,10,"Sopi nikkhamitvā aññassa ācikkhi, tassapi tathevāti evaṃ catunnaṃ janānaṃ dāpesi . "
487660,110,2922,133,142,1,68,8,"Yathāpaṭiyattaṃ pūvaṃ parikkhayaṃ agamāsi, kāṇāya gamanaṃ na sampajji. "
487661,110,2922,143,150,1,47,6,"Athassā sāmiko dutiyampi, tatiyampi dūtaṃ pāhesi. "
487662,110,2922,151,168,1,82,12,"Tatiyaṃ pāhento ca‘‘ sace kāṇā nāgacchissati, ahaṃ aññaṃ pajāpatiṃ ānessāmī’’ ti pāhesi. "
487663,110,2922,169,182,1,82,12,"Tayopi vāre teneva upāyena gamanaṃ na sampajji, kāṇāya sāmiko aññaṃ pajāpatiṃ ānesi. "
487664,110,2922,183,189,1,40,6,Kāṇā taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā rodamānā aṭṭhāsi. 
487665,110,2923,2,24,1,162,18,Satthā taṃ kāraṇaṃ ñatvā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya kāṇamātāya nivesanaṃ gantvā paññattāsane nisīditvā kāṇamātaraṃ pucchi‘‘ kissāyaṃ kāṇā rodatī’’ ti?
487666,110,2923,25,43,1,108,14,‘‘ Iminā nāma kāraṇenā’’ ti ca sutvā kāṇamātaraṃ samassāsetvā dhammiṃ kathaṃ kathetvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ agamāsi. 
487667,110,2923,44,58,1,127,14,Atha tesaṃ catunnaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ tayo vāre yathāpaṭiyattapūvaṃ gahetvā kāṇāya gamanassa upacchinnabhāvo bhikkhusaṅghe pākaṭo jāto. 
487668,110,2923,59,89,1,230,25,"Athekadivasaṃ bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, catūhi nāma bhikkhūhi tayo vāre kāṇamātāya pakkapūvaṃ khāditvā kāṇāya gamanantarāyaṃ katvā sāmikena pariccattaṃ dhītaraṃ nissāya mahāupāsikāya domanassaṃ uppāditan’’ ti. "
487669,110,2923,90,140,1,236,32,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva te cattāro bhikkhū kāṇamātāya santakaṃ khāditvā tassā domanassaṃ uppādesuṃ, pubbepi uppādesuṃyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487670,110,2924,2,14,1,118,11,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto pāsāṇakoṭṭakakule nibbattitvā vayappatto pariyodātasippo ahosi. 
487671,110,2924,15,28,1,107,12,"Kāsiraṭṭhe ekasmiṃ nigame eko mahāvibhavo seṭṭhi ahosi, tassa nidhānagatāyeva cattālīsa hiraññakoṭiyo ahesuṃ. "
487672,110,2924,29,39,1,85,10,Athassa bhariyā kālaṃ katvā dhanasinehena gantvā dhanapiṭṭhiyaṃ mūsikā hutvā nibbatti. 
487673,110,2924,40,50,1,70,9,"Evaṃ anukkamena sabbampi taṃ kulaṃ abbhatthaṃ agamāsi, vaṃso upacchijji. "
487674,110,2924,51,56,1,44,5,So gāmopi chaḍḍito apaṇṇattikabhāvaṃ agamāsi. 
487675,110,2924,57,64,1,64,7,Tadā bodhisatto tasmiṃ purāṇagāmaṭṭhāne pāsāṇe uppāṭetvā koṭṭeti. 
487676,110,2924,65,97,1,212,27,"Atha sā mūsikā gocarāya caramānā bodhisattaṃ punappunaṃ passantī uppannasinehā hutvā cintesi‘‘ mayhaṃ dhanaṃ bahu nikkāraṇena nassissati, iminā saddhiṃ ekato hutvā idaṃ dhanaṃ datvā maṃsaṃ vikkiṇāpetvā khādissāmī’’ ti. "
487677,110,2924,98,107,1,76,9,Sā ekadivasaṃ ekaṃ kahāpaṇaṃ mukhena ḍaṃsitvā bodhisattassa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
487678,110,2924,108,128,1,84,14,"So taṃ disvā piyavācāya samālapanto‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, amma, kahāpaṇaṃ gahetvā āgatāsī’’ ti āha. "
487679,110,2924,129,139,1,61,8,"Tāta, imaṃ gahetvā attanāpi paribhuñja, mayhampi maṃsaṃ āharāti. "
487680,110,2924,140,160,1,107,15,So‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā kahāpaṇaṃ ādāya gharaṃ gantvā ekena māsakena maṃsaṃ kiṇitvā āharitvā tassā adāsi. 
487681,110,2924,161,169,1,60,8,Sā taṃ gahetvā attano nivāsaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā yathāruciyā khādi. 
487682,110,2924,170,183,1,96,12,"Tato paṭṭhāya imināva niyāmena divase divase bodhisattassa kahāpaṇaṃ deti, sopissā maṃsaṃ āharati. "
487683,110,2925,2,7,1,41,5,Athekadivasaṃ taṃ mūsikaṃ biḷāro aggahesi. 
487684,110,2925,8,23,1,42,9,"Atha naṃ sā evamāha‘‘ mā, samma, maṃ māresī’’ ti. "
487685,110,2925,24,27,1,22,3,Kiṃkāraṇā na māressāmi? 
487686,110,2925,28,38,1,58,9,"Ahañhi chāto maṃsaṃ khāditukāmo, na sakkā mayā na māretunti. "
487687,110,2925,39,47,1,62,7,"Kiṃ pana ekadivasameva maṃsaṃ khāditukāmosi, udāhu niccakālanti?"
487688,110,2925,48,56,1,40,4,‘‘ Labhamāno niccakālampi khāditukāmomhī’’ ti.
487689,110,2925,57,73,1,61,10,"‘‘ Yadi evaṃ ahaṃ te niccakālaṃ maṃsaṃ dassāmi, vissajjehi man’’ ti. "
487690,110,2925,74,87,1,52,9,Atha naṃ biḷāro‘‘ tena hi appamattā hohī’’ ti vissajjesi. 
487691,110,2925,88,104,1,96,15,"Tato paṭṭhāya sā attano ābhataṃ maṃsaṃ dve koṭṭhāse katvā ekaṃ biḷārassa deti, ekaṃ sayaṃ khādati. "
487692,110,2925,105,117,1,88,11,"Atha naṃ ekadivasaṃ aññopi biḷāro aggahesi, tampi tatheva saññāpetvā attānaṃ vissajjāpesi. "
487693,110,2925,118,124,1,42,6,Tato paṭṭhāya tayo koṭṭhāse katvā khādanti. 
487694,110,2925,125,135,1,60,8,"Puna añño aggahesi, tampi tatheva saññāpetvā attānaṃ mocāpesi. "
487695,110,2925,136,142,1,45,6,Tato paṭṭhāya cattāro koṭṭhāse katvā khādanti. 
487696,110,2925,143,152,1,60,8,"Puna añño aggahesi, tampi tatheva saññāpetvā attānaṃ mocāpesi. "
487697,110,2925,153,159,1,43,6,Tato paṭṭhāya pañca koṭṭhāse katvā khādanti. 
487698,110,2925,160,168,1,79,9,Sā pañcamaṃ koṭṭhāsaṃ khādamānā appāhāratāya kilantā kisā ahosi appamaṃsalohitā 
487699,110,2926,2,62,1,304,41,"Bodhisatto taṃ disvā‘‘ amma, kasmā milātāsī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ iminā nāma kāraṇenā’’ ti vutte‘‘ tvaṃ ettakaṃ kālaṃ kasmā mayhaṃ nācikkhi, ahamettha kātabbaṃ jānissāmī’’ ti taṃ samassāsetvā suddhaphalikapāsāṇena guhaṃ katvā āharitvā‘‘ amma, tvaṃ imaṃ guhaṃ pavisitvā nipajjitvā āgatāgatānaṃ pharusāhi vācāhi santajjeyyāsī’’ ti āha. "
487700,110,2926,63,67,1,26,4,Sā guhaṃ pavisitvā nipajji. 
487701,110,2926,68,82,1,48,9,"Atheko biḷāro āgantvā‘‘ dehi, ajja me maṃsan’’ ti āha. "
487702,110,2926,83,105,1,96,15,"Atha naṃ mūsikā‘‘ are, duṭṭhabiḷāra, kiṃ te ahaṃ maṃsahārikā, attano puttānaṃ maṃsaṃ khādā’’ ti tajjesi. "
487703,110,2926,106,121,1,130,13,Biḷāro phalikaguhāya nipannabhāvaṃ ajānanto kodhavasena mūsikaṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti sahasāva pakkhanditvā hadayena phalikaguhāyaṃ pahari. 
487704,110,2926,122,129,1,64,6,"Tāvadevassa hadayaṃ bhijji, akkhīni nikkhamanākārappattāni jātāni. "
487705,110,2926,130,137,1,64,7,So tattheva jīvitakkhayaṃ patvā ekamantaṃ paṭicchannaṭṭhāne pati. 
487706,110,2926,138,145,1,68,7,Etenūpāyena aparopi aparopīti cattāropi janā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇiṃsu. 
487707,110,2926,146,157,1,82,11,Tato paṭṭhāya mūsikā nibbhayā hutvā bodhisattassa devasikaṃ dve tayo kahāpaṇe deti. 
487708,110,2926,158,164,1,53,6,Evaṃ anukkamena sabbampi dhanaṃ bodhisattasseva adāsi. 
487709,110,2926,165,172,1,54,7,Te ubhopi yāvajīvaṃ mettiṃ abhinditvā yathākammaṃ gatā. 
487710,110,2927,2,11,1,62,8,Satthā imaṃ atītaṃ āharitvā abhisambuddho hutvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
487711,110,2928,2,4,1,0,0,137.
487712,110,2929,2,12,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Yattheko labhate babbu, dutiyo tattha jāyati; "
487713,110,2930,2,14,1,46,9,"Tatiyo ca catuttho ca, idaṃ te babbukā bilan’’ ti. "
487714,110,2931,2,7,1,28,4,Tattha {yatthā}ti yasmiṃ ṭhāne. 
487715,110,2931,8,11,1,14,2,{Babbū}ti biḷāro. 
487716,110,2931,12,35,1,130,20,"Dutiyo tattha {jāyatī}ti yattha eko mūsikaṃ vā maṃsaṃ vā labhati, dutiyopi tattha biḷāro jāyati uppajjati, tathā tatiyo ca catuttho ca. "
487717,110,2931,36,42,1,34,6,Evaṃ te tadā cattāro biḷārā ahesuṃ. 
487718,110,2931,43,60,1,124,17,Hutvā ca pana divase divase maṃsaṃ khādantā te babbukā idaṃ phalikamayaṃ bilaṃ urena paharitvā sabbepi jīvitakkhayaṃ pattāti. 
487719,110,2932,2,10,1,59,7,Evaṃ satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487720,110,2932,11,30,1,103,13,"‘‘ tadā cattāro biḷārā cattāro bhikkhū ahesuṃ, mūsikā kāṇamātā, pāsāṇakoṭṭakamaṇikāro pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487721,110,2933,2,4,1,26,2,Babbujātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
487722,110,2935,2,7,1,18,2,[ 138]8. Godhājātakavaṇṇanā 
487723,110,2936,2,15,1,91,12,Kiṃ te jaṭāhi {dummedhā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kuhakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487724,110,2936,16,19,1,42,3,Paccuppannavatthu heṭṭhā kathitasadisameva. 
487725,110,2937,2,12,1,91,10,Atīte pana bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto godhāyoniyaṃ paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
487726,110,2937,13,29,1,138,15,"Tadā eko pañcābhiñño uggatapo tāpaso ekaṃ paccantagāmaṃ nissāya araññāyatane paṇṇasālāyaṃ vasati, gāmavāsino tāpasaṃ sakkaccaṃ upaṭṭhahanti. "
487727,110,2937,30,55,1,214,24,"Bodhisatto tassa caṅkamanakoṭiyaṃ ekasmiṃ vammike vasati, vasanto ca pana divase divase dve tayo vāre tāpasaṃ upasaṅkamitvā dhammūpasaṃhitaṃ atthūpasaṃhitañca vacanaṃ sutvā tāpasaṃ vanditvā vasanaṭṭhānameva gacchati. "
487728,110,2937,56,61,1,47,5,Aparabhāge tāpaso gāmavāsino āpucchitvā pakkāmi. 
487729,110,2937,62,75,1,105,13,Pakkamante ca pana tasmiṃ sīlavatasampanne tāpase añño kūṭatāpaso āgantvā tasmiṃ assamapade vāsaṃ kappesi. 
487730,110,2937,76,89,1,78,9,Bodhisatto‘‘ ayampi sīlavā’’ ti sallakkhetvā purimanayeneva tassa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
487731,110,2938,2,15,1,111,11,"Athekadivasaṃ nidāghasamaye akālameghe vuṭṭhe vammikehi makkhikā nikkhamiṃsu, tāsaṃ khādanatthaṃ godhā āhiṇḍiṃsu. "
487732,110,2938,16,28,1,133,11,Gāmavāsino nikkhamitvā makkhikākhādakā godhā gahetvā siniddhasambhārasaṃyuttaṃ ambilānambilaṃ godhāmaṃsaṃ sampādetvā tāpasassa adaṃsu. 
487733,110,2938,29,69,1,200,26,"Tāpaso godhāmaṃsaṃ khāditvā rasataṇhāya baddho‘‘ idaṃ maṃsaṃ atimadhuraṃ, kissa maṃsaṃ nāmetan’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ godhāmaṃsan’’ ti sutvā‘‘ mama santikaṃ mahāgodhā āgacchati, taṃ māretvā maṃsaṃ khādissāmī’’ ti cintesi. "
487734,110,2938,70,128,1,441,47,"Cintetvā ca pana bhājanañca sappiloṇādīni ca āharāpetvā ekamante ṭhapetvā muggaramādāya kāsāvena paṭicchādetvā paṇṇasālādvāre bodhisattassa āgamanaṃ olokayamāno upasantūpasanto viya hutvā nisīdi bodhisatto sāyanhasamaye‘‘ tāpasassa santikaṃ gamissāmī’’ ti nikkhamitvā upasaṅkamantova tassa indriyavippakāraṃ disvā cintesi‘‘ nāyaṃ tāpaso aññesu divasesu nisīdanākārena nisinno, ajjesa maṃ olokentopi duṭṭhindriyo hutvā oloketi, pariggaṇhissāmi nan’’ ti. "
487735,110,2938,129,166,1,291,32,"So tāpasassa heṭṭhāvāte ṭhatvā godhāmaṃsagandhaṃ ghāyitvā‘‘ iminā kūṭatāpasena ajja godhāmaṃsaṃ khāditaṃ bhavissati, tenesa rasataṇhāya baddho ajja maṃ attano santikaṃ upasaṅkamantaṃ muggarena paharitvā maṃsaṃ pacitvā khāditukāmo bhavissatī’’ ti tassa santikaṃ anupagantvāva paṭikkamitvā vicarati. "
487736,110,2939,2,31,1,175,21,"Tāpaso bodhisattassa anāgamanabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ iminā‘ ayaṃ maṃ paharitukāmo’ ti ñātaṃ bhavissati, tena kāraṇena nāgacchati, anāgacchantassāpissa kuto muttī’’ ti muggaraṃ nīharitvā khipi. "
487737,110,2939,32,36,1,34,4,So tassa agganaṅguṭṭhameva āsādesi. 
487738,110,2939,37,81,1,269,35,"Bodhisatto vegena vammikaṃ pavisitvā aññena chiddena sīsaṃ ukkhipitvā‘‘ ambho kūṭajaṭila, ahaṃ tava santikaṃ upasaṅkamanto‘ sīlavā’ ti saññāya upasaṅkamiṃ, idāni pana te mayā kūṭabhāvo ñāto, tādisassa mahācorassa kiṃ iminā pabbajjāliṅgenā’’ ti vatvā taṃ garahanto imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487739,110,2940,2,4,1,0,0,138.
487740,110,2941,2,12,1,41,8,"‘ ‘ Kiṃ te jaṭāhi dummedha, kiṃ te ajinasāṭiyā; "
487741,110,2942,2,11,1,45,6,"Abbhantaraṃ te gahanaṃ, bāhiraṃ parimajjasī’’ ti. "
487742,110,2943,2,24,1,136,18,"Tattha kiṃ te jaṭāhi {dummedhā}ti ambho dummedha, nippañña etā pabbajitena dhāretabbā jaṭā, pabbajjāguṇarahitassa kiṃ te tāhi jaṭāhīti attho. "
487743,110,2943,25,37,1,99,11,Kiṃ te {ajinasāṭiyā}ti ajinasāṭiyā anucchavikassa saṃvarassa abhāvakālato paṭṭhāya kiṃ te ajinasāṭiyā. 
487744,110,2943,38,48,1,92,10,Abbhantaraṃ te gahanan ti tava abbhantaraṃ hadayaṃ rāgadosamohagahanena gahanaṃ paṭicchannaṃ. 
487745,110,2943,49,98,1,348,41,"Bāhiraṃ {parimajjasī}ti so tvaṃ abbhantare gahane nhānādīhi ceva liṅgagahanena ca bāhiraṃ parimajjasi, taṃ parimajjanto kañjikapūritalābu viya visapūritacāṭi viya āsīvisapūritavammiko viya gūthapūritacittaghaṭo viya ca bahimaṭṭhova hosi, kiṃ tayā corena idha vasantena, sīghaṃ ito palāyāhi, no ce palāyasi, gāmavāsīnaṃ te ācikkhitvā niggahaṃ kārāpessāmīti. "
487746,110,2944,2,12,1,81,9,"Evaṃ bodhisatto kūṭatāpasaṃ tajjetvā vammikameva pāvisi, kūṭatāpasopi tato pakkāmi. "
487747,110,2945,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
487748,110,2945,9,28,1,102,13,"‘‘ tadā kūṭatāpaso ayaṃ kuhako ahosi, purimo sīlavantatāpaso sāriputto, godhāpaṇḍito pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487749,110,2946,2,4,1,26,2,Godhājātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
487750,110,2948,2,7,1,26,2,[ 139]9. Ubhatobhaṭṭhajātakavaṇṇanā 
487751,110,2949,2,14,1,84,11,Akkhī bhinnā paṭo {naṭṭho}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487752,110,2949,15,61,1,326,37,"Tadā kira dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, seyyathāpi nāma chavālātaṃ ubhatopadittaṃ majjhe gūthagataṃ nevāraññe kaṭṭhatthaṃ pharati, na gāme kaṭṭhatthaṃ pharati, evameva devadatto evarūpe niyyānikasāsane pabbajitvā ubhato bhaṭṭho ubhato paribāhiro jāto, gihiparibhogā ca parihīno, sāmaññatthañca na paripūretī’’ ti. "
487753,110,2949,62,108,1,202,29,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, devadatto idāneva ubhato bhaṭṭho hoti, atītepi ubhato bhaṭṭho ahosiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487754,110,2950,2,11,1,83,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto rukkhadevatā hutvā nibbatti. 
487755,110,2950,12,17,1,36,5,Tadā ekasmiṃ gāmake bāḷisikā vasanti. 
487756,110,2950,18,36,1,132,17,"Atheko bāḷisiko baḷisaṃ ādāya daharena puttena saddhiṃ yasmiṃ sobbhe pakatiyāpi bāḷisikā macche gaṇhanti, tattha gantvā baḷisaṃ khipi. "
487757,110,2950,37,43,1,45,5,Baḷiso udakapaṭicchanne ekasmiṃ khāṇuke laggi. 
487758,110,2950,44,75,1,196,25,"Bāḷisiko taṃ ākaḍḍhituṃ asakkonto cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ baḷiso mahāmacche laggo bhavissati, puttakaṃ mātu santikaṃ pesetvā paṭivissakehi saddhiṃ kalahaṃ kārāpemi, evaṃ ito na koci koṭṭhāsaṃ paccāsīsissatī’’ ti. "
487759,110,2950,76,104,1,129,18,"So puttaṃ āha‘‘ gaccha, tāta, amhehi mahāmacchassa laddhabhāvaṃ mātu ācikkhāhi,‘ paṭivissakehi kira saddhiṃ kalahaṃ karohī’ ti vadehī’’ ti. "
487760,110,2950,105,126,1,187,20,So puttaṃ pesetvā baḷisaṃ ākaḍḍhituṃ asakkonto rajjucchedanabhayena uttarisāṭakaṃ thale ṭhapetvā udakaṃ otaritvā macchalobhena macchaṃ upadhārento khāṇukehi paharitvā dvepi akkhīni bhindi. 
487761,110,2950,127,131,1,35,4,Thale ṭhapitasāṭakaṃpissa coro hari. 
487762,110,2950,132,144,1,104,12,So vedanāppatto hutvā hatthena akkhīni uppīḷayamāno gahetvā udakā uttaritvā kampamāno sāṭakaṃ pariyesati. 
487763,110,2951,2,26,1,190,20,Sāpissa bhariyā‘‘ kalahaṃ katvā kassaci apaccāsīsanabhāvaṃ karissāmī’’ ti ekasmiṃyeva kaṇṇe tālapaṇṇaṃ piḷandhitvā ekaṃ akkhiṃ ukkhalimasiyā añjetvā kukkuraṃ aṅkenādāya paṭivissakagharaṃ agamāsi. 
487764,110,2951,27,58,1,176,24,"Atha naṃ ekā sahāyikā evamāha‘‘ ekasmiṃyeva te kaṇṇe tālapaṇṇaṃ piḷandhitaṃ, ekaṃ akkhi añjitaṃ, piyaputtaṃ viya kukkuraṃ aṅkenādāya gharato gharaṃ gacchasi, kiṃ ummattikāsi jātā’’ ti."
487765,110,2951,59,89,1,191,24,"‘‘ Nāhaṃ ummattikā, tvaṃ pana maṃ akāraṇena akkosasi paribhāsasi, idāni taṃ gāmabhojakassa santikaṃ gantvā aṭṭha kahāpaṇe daṇḍāpessāmī’’ ti evaṃ kalahaṃ katvā ubhopi gāmabhojakassa santikaṃ agamaṃsu. "
487766,110,2951,90,96,1,50,6,Kalahe visodhiyamāne tassāyeva matthake daṇḍo pati. 
487767,110,2951,97,109,1,52,8,Atha naṃ bandhitvā‘‘ daṇḍaṃ dehī’’ ti pothetuṃ ārabhiṃsu. 
487768,110,2952,2,35,1,190,26,"Rukkhadevatā gāme tassā imaṃ pavattiṃ, araññe cassā patino taṃ byasanaṃ disvā khandhantare ṭhitā‘‘ bho purisa, tuyhaṃ udakepi kammanto paduṭṭho thalepi, ubhatobhaṭṭho jāto’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487769,110,2953,2,4,1,0,0,139.
487770,110,2954,2,12,1,47,8,"‘ ‘ Akkhī bhinnā paṭo naṭṭho, sakhigehe ca bhaṇḍanaṃ; "
487771,110,2955,2,12,1,48,7,"Ubhato paduṭṭhā kammantā, udakamhi thalamhi cā’’ ti. "
487772,110,2956,2,26,1,148,21,"Tattha sakhigehe ca bhaṇḍanan ti sakhī nāma sahāyikā, tassā ca gehe tava bhariyāya bhaṇḍanaṃ kataṃ, bhaṇḍanaṃ katvā bandhitvā pothetvā daṇḍaṃ dāpiyati. "
487773,110,2956,27,38,1,85,10,Ubhato paduṭṭhā {kammantā}ti evaṃ tava dvīsupi ṭhānesu kammantā paduṭṭhāyeva bhinnāyeva. 
487774,110,2956,39,41,1,14,2,Kataresu dvīsu? 
487775,110,2956,42,59,1,120,14,"Udakamhi thalamhi {cā}ti, akkhibhedena paṭanāsena ca udake kammantā paduṭṭhā, sakhigehe bhaṇḍanena thale kammantā paduṭṭhāti. "
487776,110,2957,2,24,1,120,15,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi‘‘ tadā bāḷisiko devadatto ahosi, rukkhadevatā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
487777,110,2958,2,4,1,33,2,Ubhatobhaṭṭhajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
487778,110,2960,2,7,1,17,2,[ 140]10. Kākajātakavaṇṇanā 
487779,110,2961,2,12,1,85,9,Niccaṃ {ubbiggahadayā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ñātatthacariyaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487780,110,2961,13,28,1,65,5,Paccuppannavatthu dvādasakanipāte bhaddasālajātake( jā.1.12.13 ādayo) āvi bhavissati. 
487781,110,2962,2,10,1,76,8,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kākayoniyaṃ nibbatti. 
487782,110,2962,11,24,1,126,13,Athekadivasaṃ rañño purohito bahinagare nadiyaṃ nhāyitvā gandhe vilimpitvā mālaṃ piḷandhitvā varavatthanivattho nagaraṃ pāvisi. 
487783,110,2962,25,30,1,40,5,Nagaradvāratoraṇe dve kākā nisinnā honti. 
487784,110,2962,31,35,1,17,4,Tesu eko ekaṃ āha–
487785,110,2962,36,49,1,66,8,"‘‘ samma, ahaṃ imassa brāhmaṇassa matthake sarīravaḷañjaṃ pātessāmī’’ ti. "
487786,110,2962,50,68,1,86,14,"Itaro‘‘ mā te etaṃ rucci, ayaṃ brāhmaṇo issaro, issarajanena ca saddhiṃ veraṃ nāma pāpakaṃ. "
487787,110,2962,69,77,1,39,6,Ayañhi kuddho sabbepi kāke vināseyyā’’ ti.
487788,110,2962,78,88,1,25,6,‘‘ Na sakkā mayā na kātun’’ ti.
487789,110,2962,89,101,1,47,8,‘‘ Tena hi paññāyissasī’’ ti vatvā itaro kāko palāyi. 
487790,110,2962,102,114,1,95,12,So toraṇassa heṭṭhābhāgaṃ sampatte brāhmaṇe olambakaṃ cālento viya tassa matthake vaccaṃ pātesi. 
487791,110,2962,115,120,1,38,5,Brāhmaṇo kujjhitvā kākesu veraṃ bandhi. 
487792,110,2963,2,15,1,107,13,Tasmiṃ kāle ekā bhatiyā vīhikoṭṭikadāsī vīhiṃ gehadvāre ātape pattharitvā rakkhantī nisinnāva niddaṃ okkami. 
487793,110,2963,16,31,1,95,14,"Tassā pamādaṃ ñatvā eko dīghalomako eḷako āgantvā vīhiṃ khādi, sā pabujjhitvā taṃ disvā palāpesi. "
487794,110,2963,32,42,1,73,9,"Eḷako dutiyampi, tatiyampi tassā tatheva niddāyanakāle āgantvā vīhiṃ khādi. "
487795,110,2963,43,69,1,155,19,"Sāpi taṃ tikkhattuṃ palāpetvā cintesi‘‘ ayaṃ punappunaṃ khādanto upaḍḍhavīhiṃ khādissati, bahu me chedo bhavissati, idānissa puna anāgamanakāraṇaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
487796,110,2963,70,88,1,129,16,"Sā alātaṃ gahetvā niddāyamānā viya nisīditvā vīhikhādanatthāya eḷake sampatte uṭṭhāya alātena eḷakaṃ pahari, lomāni aggiṃ gaṇhiṃsu. "
487797,110,2963,89,110,1,118,16,"So sarīre jhāyante‘‘ aggiṃ nibbāpessāmī’’ ti vegena gantvā hatthisālāya samīpe ekissā tiṇakuṭiyā sarīraṃ ghaṃsi, sā pajjali. "
487798,110,2963,111,116,1,35,5,Tato uṭṭhitā jālā hatthisālaṃ gaṇhi. 
487799,110,2963,117,126,1,79,8,"Hatthisālāsu jhāyantīsu hatthipiṭṭhāni jhāyiṃsu, bahū hatthī vaṇitasarīrā ahesuṃ. "
487800,110,2963,127,135,1,49,7,Vejjā hatthī aroge kātuṃ asakkontā rañño ārocesuṃ. 
487801,110,2963,136,156,1,99,14,"Rājā purohitaṃ āha‘‘ ācariya, hatthivejjā hatthī tikicchituṃ na sakkonti, api kiñci bhesajjaṃ jānāsī’’ ti."
487802,110,2963,157,165,1,18,3,"‘‘ Jānāmi, mahārājā’’ ti."
487803,110,2963,166,174,1,22,4,‘‘ Kiṃ laddhuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti?
487804,110,2963,175,183,1,20,3,"‘‘ Kākavasā, mahārājā’’ ti. "
487805,110,2963,184,197,1,47,9,Rājā‘‘ tena hi kāke māretvā vasaṃ āharathā’’ ti āha. 
487806,110,2963,198,212,1,99,13,"Tato paṭṭhāya kāke māretvā vasaṃ alabhitvā tattha tattheva rāsiṃ karonti, kākānaṃ mahābhayaṃ uppajji. "
487807,110,2964,2,7,1,58,5,Tadā bodhisatto asītikākasahassaparivāro mahāsusāne vasati. 
487808,110,2964,8,15,1,62,7,Atheko kāko gantvā kākānaṃ uppannabhayaṃ bodhisattassa ārocesi. 
487809,110,2964,16,50,1,243,29,"So cintesi‘‘ ṭhapetvā maṃ añño mayhaṃ ñātakānaṃ uppannabhayaṃ harituṃ samattho nāma natthi, harissāmi nan’’ ti dasa pāramiyo āvajjetvā mettāpāramiṃ purecārikaṃ katvā ekavegena pakkhanditvā vivaṭamahāvātapānena pavisitvā rañño āsanassa heṭṭhā pāvisi. "
487810,110,2964,51,57,1,37,6,Atha naṃ eko manusso gahitukāmo ahosi. 
487811,110,2964,58,70,1,40,7,"Rājā‘‘ saraṇaṃ paviṭṭho, mā gaṇhī’’ ti vāresi. "
487812,110,2964,71,80,1,85,9,Mahāsatto thokaṃ vissamitvā mettāpāramiṃ āvajjetvā heṭṭhāsanā nikkhamitvā rājānaṃ āha–
487813,110,2964,81,92,1,65,8,"‘‘ mahārāja, raññā nāma chandādivasena agantvā rajjaṃ kāretuṃ vaṭṭati. "
487814,110,2964,93,104,1,70,10,"Yaṃ yaṃ kammaṃ kattabbaṃ hoti, sabbaṃ nisamma upadhāretvā kātuṃ vaṭṭati. "
487815,110,2964,105,115,1,60,8,"Yañca kayiramānaṃ nipphajjati, tadeva kātuṃ vaṭṭati, na itaraṃ. "
487816,110,2964,116,132,1,113,13,"Sace hi rājāno yaṃ kayiramānaṃ na nipphajjati, taṃ karonti, mahājanassa maraṇabhayapariyosānaṃ mahābhayaṃ uppajjati . "
487817,110,2964,133,146,1,70,10,"Purohito veravasiko hutvā musāvādaṃ abhāsi, kākānaṃ vasā nāma natthī’’ ti. "
487818,110,2964,147,211,1,433,51,"Taṃ sutvā rājā pasannacitto bodhisattassa kañcanabhaddapīṭhaṃ dāpetvā tattha nisinnassa pakkhantarāni satapākasahassapākatelehi makkhāpetvā kañcanataṭṭake rājārahaṃ subhojanaṃ bhojāpetvā pānīyaṃ pāyetvā suhitaṃ vigatadarathaṃ mahāsattaṃ etadavoca‘‘ paṇḍita, tvaṃ‘ kākānaṃ vasā nāma natthī’ ti vadesi, kena kāraṇena nesaṃ vasā na hotī’’ ti bodhisatto‘‘ iminā ca iminā ca kāraṇenā’’ ti sakalanivesanaṃ ekaravaṃ katvā dhammaṃ desento imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487819,110,2965,2,4,1,0,0,140.
487820,110,2966,2,8,1,38,4,"‘ ‘ Niccaṃ ubbiggahadayā, sabbalokavihesakā; "
487821,110,2967,2,12,1,46,7,"Tasmā nesaṃ vasā natthi, kākānamhāka ñātinan’’ ti. "
487822,110,2968,2,38,1,275,30,"Tatrāyaṃ saṅkhepattho– mahārāja, kākā nāma niccaṃ ubbiggamānasā bhayappattāva viharanti, sabbalokassa ca vihesakā, khattiyādayo manussepi itthipurisepi kumārakumārikādayopi viheṭhentā kilamentāva vicaranti, tasmā imehi dvīhi kāraṇehi nesaṃ amhākaṃ ñātīnaṃ kākānaṃ vasā nāma natthi. "
487823,110,2968,39,46,1,47,6,"Atītepi na bhūtapubbā, anāgatepi na bhavissatīti. "
487824,110,2969,2,24,1,123,17,"Evaṃ mahāsatto imaṃ kāraṇaṃ uttānaṃ katvā‘‘ mahārāja, raññā nāma anisamma anupadhāretvā kammaṃ na kattabban’’ ti rājānaṃ bodhesi. "
487825,110,2969,25,30,1,40,5,Rājā tussitvā bodhisattaṃ rajjena pūjesi. 
487826,110,2969,31,42,1,101,11,Bodhisatto rajjaṃ raññoyeva paṭidatvā rājānaṃ pañcasu sīlesu patiṭṭhāpetvā sabbasattānaṃ abhayaṃ yāci. 
487827,110,2969,43,53,1,91,10,Rājā tassa dhammadesanaṃ sutvā sabbasattānaṃ abhayaṃ datvā kākānaṃ nibaddhadānaṃ paṭṭhapesi. 
487828,110,2969,54,68,1,127,13,"Divase divase taṇḍulambaṇassa bhattaṃ pacitvā nānaggarasehi omadditvā kākānaṃ dīyati, mahāsattassa pana rājabhojanameva dīyittha. "
