487973,110,3028,2,7,1,18,2,[ 145]5. Rādhajātakavaṇṇanā 
487974,110,3029,2,14,1,96,11,Na tvaṃ rādha {vijānāsī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto purāṇadutiyikāpalobhanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
487975,110,3029,15,19,1,46,4,Paccuppannavatthu indriyajātake āvi bhavissati. 
487976,110,3029,20,38,1,118,15,"Satthā pana taṃ bhikkhuṃ āmantetvā‘‘ bhikkhu mātugāmo nāma arakkhiyo, ārakkhaṃ ṭhapetvā rakkhantāpi rakkhituṃ na sakkonti. "
487977,110,3029,39,57,1,113,15,"Tvampi pubbe etaṃ ārakkhaṃ ṭhapetvā rakkhantopi rakkhituṃ nāsakkhi, idāni kathaṃ rakkhissasī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
487978,110,3030,2,10,1,76,8,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sukayoniyaṃ nibbatti. 
487979,110,3030,11,19,1,87,8,Kāsiraṭṭhe eko brāhmaṇo bodhisattañca kaniṭṭhabhātarañcassa puttaṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā posesi. 
487980,110,3030,20,38,1,62,9,"Tesu bodhisattassa‘‘ poṭṭhapādo’’ ti nāmaṃ ahosi, itarassa‘‘ rādho’’ ti. "
487981,110,3030,39,46,1,51,7,Tassa pana brāhmaṇassa bhariyā anācārā hoti dussīlā. 
487982,110,3030,47,53,1,44,6,So vohāratthāya gacchanto ubhopi bhātaro āha–
487983,110,3030,54,70,1,61,10,"‘‘ tātā, sace vo mātā brāhmaṇī anācāraṃ ācarati, vāreyyātha nan’’ ti. "
487984,110,3030,71,90,1,82,11,"Bodhisatto āha‘‘ sādhu, tāta, vāretuṃ sakkontā vāreyyāma, asakkontā tuṇhī bhavissāmā’’ ti. "
487985,110,3030,91,98,1,60,7,Evaṃ brāhmaṇo brāhmaṇiṃ sukānaṃ niyyādetvā vohāratthāya gato. 
487986,110,3031,2,22,1,146,17,"Tassa pana gatadivasato paṭṭhāya brāhmaṇī aticarituṃ āraddhā, pavisantānañca nikkhamantānañca anto natthi, tassā kiriyaṃ disvā rādho bodhisattaṃ āha–"
487987,110,3031,23,52,1,117,19,"‘‘ bhātika, amhākaṃ pitā‘ sace vo mātā anācāraṃ ācarati, vāreyyāthā’ ti vatvā gato, idāni cesā anācāraṃ ācarati, vārema nan’’ ti. "
487988,110,3031,53,72,1,121,15,"Bodhisatto‘‘ tāta, tvaṃ attano abyattatāya bālabhāvena evaṃ vadesi, mātugāmaṃ nāma ukkhipitvā carantāpi rakkhituṃ na sakkonti. "
487989,110,3031,73,89,1,70,13,"Yaṃ kammaṃ kātuṃ na sakkā, na taṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
487990,110,3032,2,4,1,0,0,145.
487991,110,3033,2,12,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Na tvaṃ rādha vijānāsi, aḍḍharatte anāgate; "
487992,110,3034,2,10,1,40,5,"Abyayataṃ vilapasi, virattā kosiyāyane’’ ti. "
487993,110,3035,2,31,1,167,23,"Tattha na tvaṃ rādha vijānāsi, aḍḍharatte {anāgate}ti tāta rādha, tvaṃ na jānāsi, aḍḍharatte anāgate paṭhamayāmeyeva ettakā janā āgatā, idāni ko jānāti, kittakāpi āgamissanti. "
487994,110,3035,32,38,1,49,5,Abyayataṃ {vilapasī}ti tvaṃ abyattavilāpaṃ vilapasi. 
487995,110,3035,39,51,1,84,11,Virattā {kosiyāyane}ti mātā no kosiyāyanī brāhmaṇī virattā amhākaṃ pitari nippemā jātā. 
487996,110,3035,52,68,1,110,15,"Sacassā tasmiṃ sineho vā pemaṃ vā bhaveyya, na evarūpaṃ anācāraṃ kareyyāti imamatthaṃ etehi byañjanehi pakāsesi. "
487997,110,3036,2,12,1,66,10,Evaṃ pakāsetvā ca pana brāhmaṇiyā saddhiṃ rādhassa vattuṃ na adāsi. 
487998,110,3036,13,19,1,50,6,Sāpi yāva brāhmaṇassa anāgamanā yathāruciyā vicari. 
487999,110,3036,20,24,1,35,4,Brāhmaṇo āgantvā poṭṭhapādaṃ pucchi–
488000,110,3036,25,35,1,22,5,"‘‘ tāta, kīdisī vo mātā’’ ti. "
488001,110,3036,36,78,1,234,31,"Bodhisatto brāhmaṇassa sabbaṃ yathābhūtaṃ kathetvā‘‘ kiṃ te, tāta, evarūpāya dussīlāyā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tāta, amhehi mātuyā dosassa kathitakālato paṭṭhāya na sakkā idha vasitun’’ ti brāhmaṇassa pāde vanditvā saddhiṃ rādhena uppatitvā araññaṃ agamāsi. "
488002,110,3037,2,13,1,111,10,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi."
488003,110,3037,14,36,1,99,16,"‘‘ Tadā brāhmaṇo ca brāhmaṇī ca eteyeva dve janā ahesuṃ, rādho ānando, poṭṭhapādo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
488004,110,3038,2,4,1,26,2,Rādhajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
488005,110,3040,2,7,1,24,2,[ 146]6. Samuddakākajātakavaṇṇanā 
488006,110,3041,2,18,1,96,13,Api nu hanukā {santā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto sambahule mahallake bhikkhū ārabbha kathesi. 
488007,110,3041,19,65,1,347,39,"Te kira gihikāle sāvatthiyaṃ kuṭumbikā aḍḍhā mahaddhanā aññamaññasahāyakā ekato hutvā puññāni karontā satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā‘‘ mayaṃ mahallakā, kiṃ no gharāvāsena, satthu santike ramaṇīye buddhasāsane pabbajitvā dukkhassantaṃ karissāmā’’ ti sabbaṃ sāpateyyaṃ puttadhītādīnaṃ datvā assumukhaṃ ñātisaṅghaṃ pahāya satthāraṃ pabbajjaṃ yācitvā pabbajiṃsu. "
488008,110,3041,66,86,1,181,18,"Pabbajitvā pana pabbajjānurūpaṃ samaṇadhammaṃ na kariṃsu, mahallakabhāvena dhammampi na pariyāpuṇiṃsu, gihikāle viya pabbajitakālepi vihārapariyante paṇṇasālaṃ kāretvā ekatova vasiṃsu. "
488009,110,3041,87,97,1,90,10,Piṇḍāya carantāpi aññattha agantvā yebhuyyena attano puttadārasseva gehaṃ gantvā bhuñjiṃsu. 
488010,110,3041,98,116,1,148,17,"Tesu ekassa purāṇadutiyikā sabbesampi mahallakattherānaṃ upakārā ahosi, tasmā sesāpi attanā laddhaṃ āhāraṃ gahetvā tassāyeva gehe nisīditvā bhuñjanti. "
488011,110,3041,117,122,1,45,5,Sāpi tesaṃ yathāsannihitaṃ sūpabyañjanaṃ deti. 
488012,110,3041,123,128,1,39,5,Sā aññatarena rogena phuṭṭhā kālamakāsi. 
488013,110,3041,129,148,1,135,15,Atha te mahallakattherā vihāraṃ gantvā aññamaññaṃ gīvāsu gahetvā‘‘ madhurahattharasā upāsikā kālakatā’’ ti vihārapaccante rodantā vicariṃsu. 
488014,110,3041,149,167,1,84,13,"Tesaṃ saddaṃ sutvā ito cito ca bhikkhū sannipatitvā‘‘ āvuso, kasmā rodathā’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
488015,110,3041,168,194,1,155,19,"Te‘‘ amhākaṃ sahāyassa purāṇadutiyikā madhurahattharasā kālakatā amhākaṃ ativiya upakārā,‘ idāni kuto tathārūpiṃ labhissāmā’ ti iminā kāraṇena rodimhā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
488016,110,3042,2,27,1,174,20,"Tesaṃ taṃ vippakāraṃ disvā bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, iminā nāma kāraṇena mahallakattherā aññamaññaṃ gīvāsu gahetvā vihārapaccante rodantā vicarantī’’ ti. "
488017,110,3042,28,89,1,327,42,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevete tassā kālakiriyāya rodantā vicaranti, pubbepete imaṃ kākayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā samudde mataṃ nissāya‘ samuddaudakaṃ ussiñcitvā etaṃ nīharissāmā’ ti vāyamantā paṇḍite nissāya jīvitaṃ labhiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
488018,110,3043,2,11,1,84,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto samuddadevatā hutvā nibbatti. 
488019,110,3043,12,23,1,81,10,Atheko kāko attano bhariyaṃ kākiṃ ādāya gocaraṃ pariyesamāno samuddatīraṃ agamāsi . 
488020,110,3043,24,32,1,94,8,Tasmiṃ kāle manussā samuddatīre khīrapāyāsamacchamaṃsasurādīhi nāgabalikammaṃ katvā pakkamiṃsu. 
488021,110,3043,33,48,1,121,14,Atha so kāko balikammaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā khīrādīni disvā saddhiṃ kākiyā khīrapāyāsamacchamaṃsādīni bhuñjitvā bahuṃ suraṃ pivi. 
488022,110,3043,49,71,1,137,17,Te ubhopi surāmadamattā‘‘ samuddakīḷaṃ kīḷissāmā’’ ti velante nisīditvā nhāyituṃ ārabhiṃsu athekā ūmi āgantvā kākiṃ gahetvā samuddaṃ pavesesi. 
488023,110,3043,72,77,1,39,5,Tameko maccho maṃsaṃ khāditvā ajjhohari. 
488024,110,3043,78,89,1,37,7,Kāko‘‘ bhariyā me matā’’ ti rodi paridevi. 
488025,110,3043,90,104,1,83,10,Athassa paridevanasaddaṃ sutvā bahū kākā sannipatitvā‘‘ kiṃkāraṇā rodasī’’ ti pucchiṃsu.
488026,110,3043,105,116,1,43,7,‘‘ Sahāyikā vo velante nhāyamānā ūmiyā haṭā’’ ti. 
488027,110,3043,117,122,1,35,5,Te sabbepi ekaravaṃ ravantā rodiṃsu. 
488028,110,3043,123,145,1,129,17,"Atha nesaṃ etadahosi‘‘ idaṃ samuddaudakaṃ nāma amhākaṃ kiṃ pahosi, udakaṃ ussiñcitvā samuddaṃ tucchaṃ katvā sahāyikaṃ nīharissāmā’’ ti. "
488029,110,3043,146,162,1,115,15,"Te mukhaṃ pūretvā pūretvā udakaṃ bahi chaḍḍenti, loṇūdakena ca gale sussamāne uṭṭhāyuṭṭhāya thalaṃ gantvā vissamanti. "
488030,110,3044,2,40,1,246,31,"Te hanūsu kilantesu mukhesu sukkhantesu akkhīsu rattesu dīnā kilantā hutvā aññamaññaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ ambho, mayaṃ samuddaudakaṃ gahetvā bahi pātema, gahitagahitaṭṭhānaṃ puna udakena pūrati, samuddaṃ tucchaṃ kātuṃ na sakkhissāmā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāhaṃsu– "
488031,110,3045,2,4,1,0,0,146.
488032,110,3046,2,11,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Api nu hanukā santā, mukhañca parisussati; "
488033,110,3047,2,11,1,39,6,"Oramāma na pārema, pūrateva mahodadhī’’ ti. "
488034,110,3048,2,17,1,75,13,"Tattha api nu hanukā {santā}ti api no hanukā santā, api amhākaṃ hanukā kilantā. "
488035,110,3048,18,35,1,109,15,"Oramāma na {pāremā}ti mayaṃ attano balena mahāsamuddaudakaṃ ākaḍḍhāma osārema, tucchaṃ pana naṃ kātuṃ na sakkoma. "
488036,110,3048,36,40,1,27,3,Ayañhi pūrateva {mahodadhī}ti. 
488037,110,3049,2,25,1,140,18,"Evañca pana vatvā sabbepi te kākā‘‘ tassā kākiyā evarūpaṃ nāma tuṇḍaṃ ahosi, evarūpāni vaṭṭakkhīni, evarūpaṃ chavisaṇṭhānaṃ, evarūpo madhurasaddo. "
488038,110,3049,26,37,1,60,9,Sā no imaṃ corasamuddaṃ nissāya naṭṭhā’’ ti bahuṃ vippalapiṃsu. 
488039,110,3049,38,51,1,90,11,"Te evaṃ vippalapamāne samuddadevatā bheravarūpaṃ dassetvā palāpesi, evaṃ tesaṃ sotthi ahosi. "
488040,110,3050,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
488041,110,3050,9,30,1,122,14,"‘‘ tadā kākī ayaṃ purāṇadutiyikā ahosi, kāko mahallakatthero, sesakākā sesamahallakattherā, samuddadevatā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
488042,110,3051,2,4,1,32,2,Samuddakākajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
488043,110,3053,2,7,1,24,2,[ 147]7. Puppharattajātakavaṇṇanā 
488044,110,3054,2,17,1,102,13,Nayidaṃ dukkhaṃ aduṃ dukkhan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488045,110,3054,18,73,1,204,32,"So hi bhagavatā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ bhikkhu ukkaṇṭhito’’ ti vutte‘‘ saccan’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kena ukkaṇṭhāpitosī’’ ti ca puṭṭho‘‘ purāṇadutiyikāyā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ madhurahattharasā, bhante, sā itthī, na sakkomi taṃ vinā vasitun’’ ti āha. "
488046,110,3054,74,108,1,186,28,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ esā te bhikkhu anatthakārikā, pubbepi tvaṃ etaṃ nissāya sūle uttāsito etaññeva patthayamāno kālaṃ katvā niraye nibbatto, idāni naṃ kasmā puna patthesī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
488047,110,3055,2,10,1,77,8,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto ākāsaṭṭhadevatā ahosi. 
488048,110,3055,11,21,1,89,9,"Atha bārāṇasiyaṃ kattikarattivārachaṇo sampatto hoti, nagaraṃ devanagaraṃ viya alaṅkariṃsu. "
488049,110,3055,22,26,1,33,4,Sabbo jano khaṇakīḷānissito ahosi. 
488050,110,3055,27,33,1,60,6,Ekassa pana duggatamanussassa ekameva ghanasāṭakayugaṃ ahosi. 
488051,110,3055,34,43,1,82,9,So taṃ sudhotaṃ dhovāpetvā obhañjāpetvā satavalikaṃ sahassavalikaṃ kāretvā ṭhapesi. 
488052,110,3055,44,67,1,132,17,"Atha naṃ bhariyā evamāha‘‘ icchāmahaṃ, sāmi, ekaṃ kusumbharattaṃ nivāsetvā ekaṃ pārupitvā tava kaṇṭhe laggā kattikarattivāraṃ caritun’’ ti."
488053,110,3055,68,83,1,74,9,"‘‘ Bhadde, kuto amhākaṃ daliddānaṃ kusumbhaṃ, suddhavatthaṃ nivāsetvā kīḷāhī’’ ti?"
488054,110,3055,84,100,1,86,11,"‘‘ Kusumbharattaṃ alabhamānā chaṇakīḷaṃ na kīḷissāmi, tvaṃ aññaṃ itthiṃ gahetvā kīḷassū’’ ti."
488055,110,3055,101,115,1,47,8,"‘‘ Bhadde, kiṃ maṃ pīḷesi, kuto amhākaṃ kusumbhan’’ ti?"
488056,110,3055,116,135,1,91,13,"‘‘ Sāmi, purisassa icchāya sati kiṃ nāma natthi, nanu rañño kusumbhavatthusmiṃ bahu kusumbhan’’ ti."
488057,110,3055,136,161,1,135,15,"‘‘ Bhadde , taṃ ṭhānaṃ rakkhasapariggahitapokkharaṇisadisaṃ, balavārakkhā, na sakkā upasaṅkamituṃ, mā te etaṃ rucci, yathāladdheneva tussassū’’ ti."
488058,110,3055,162,176,1,72,9,"‘‘ Sāmi, rattibhāge andhakāre sati purisassa agamanīyaṭṭhānaṃ nāma natthī’’ ti. "
488059,110,3055,177,210,1,229,28,"Iti so tāya punappunaṃ kathentiyā kilesavasena tassā vacanaṃ gahetvā‘‘ hotu bhadde, mā cintayitthā’’ ti taṃ samassāsetvā rattibhāge jīvitaṃ pariccajitvā nagarā nikkhamitvā rañño kusumbhavatthuṃ gantvā vatiṃ madditvā antovatthuṃ pāvisi. "
488060,110,3055,211,230,1,129,15,Ārakkhamanussā vatisaddaṃ sutvā‘‘ coro coro’’ ti parivāretvā gahetvā paribhāsitvā koṭṭetvā bandhitvā pabhātāya rattiyā rañño dassesuṃ. 
488061,110,3055,231,244,1,40,7,"Rājā ‘‘ gacchatha, naṃ sūle uttāsethā’’ ti āha. "
488062,110,3055,245,255,1,92,10,Atha naṃ pacchābāhaṃ bandhitvā vajjhabheriyā vajjamānāya nagarā nikkhamāpetvā sūle uttāsesuṃ. 
488063,110,3055,256,266,1,87,9,"Balavavedanā pavattanti, kākā sīse nilīyitvā kaṇayaggasadisehi tuṇhehi akkhīni vijjhanti. "
488064,110,3056,2,26,1,199,19,So tathārūpampi dukkhaṃ amanasikaritvā tameva itthiṃ anussaritvā‘‘ tāya nāmamhi ghanapuppharattavatthanivatthāya kaṇṭhe āsattabāhuyugaḷāya saddhiṃ kattikarattivārato parihīno’’ ti cintetvā imaṃ gāthamāha– 
488065,110,3057,2,4,1,0,0,147.
488066,110,3058,2,13,1,50,9,"‘ ‘ Nayidaṃ dukkhaṃ aduṃ dukkhaṃ, yaṃ maṃ tudati vāyaso; "
488067,110,3059,2,11,1,47,6,"Yaṃ sāmā puppharattena, kattikaṃ nānubhossatī’’ ti. "
488068,110,3060,2,39,1,235,32,"Tattha nayidaṃ dukkhaṃ aduṃ dukkhaṃ, yaṃ maṃ tudati {vāyaso}ti yañca idaṃ sūle lagganapaccayaṃ kāyikacetasikadukkhaṃ, yañca lohamayehi viya tuṇḍehi vāyaso tudati, idaṃ sabbampi mayhaṃ na dukkhaṃ, aduṃ dukkhaṃ etaṃyeva pana me dukkhanti attho. "
488069,110,3060,40,41,1,7,1,Kataraṃ? 
488070,110,3060,42,78,1,267,31,"Yaṃ sāmā puppharattena, kattikaṃ {nānubhossatī}ti, yaṃ sā piyaṅgusāmā mama bhariyā ekaṃ kusumbharattaṃ nivāsetvā ekaṃ pārupitvā evaṃ ghanapuppharattena vatthayugena acchannā mama kaṇṭhe gahetvā kattikarattivāraṃ nānubhavissati, idaṃ mayhaṃ dukkhaṃ, etadeva hi maṃ bādhatīti? "
488071,110,3060,79,88,1,70,9,So evaṃ mātugāmaṃ ārabbha vippalapantoyeva kālaṃ katvā niraye nibbatti. 
488072,110,3061,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
488073,110,3061,9,28,1,110,14,"‘‘ tadā jayampatikāva idāni jayampatikā, taṃ kāraṇaṃ paccakkhaṃ katvā ṭhitā ākāsaṭṭhadevatā pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
488074,110,3062,2,4,1,32,2,Puppharattajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
488075,110,3064,2,7,1,20,2,[ 148]8. Siṅgālajātakavaṇṇanā 
488076,110,3065,2,16,1,88,13,Nāhaṃ punaṃ na ca punan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto kilesaniggahaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488077,110,3065,17,33,1,156,16,Sāvatthiyaṃ kira pañcasatamattā sahāyakā mahāvibhavā seṭṭhiputtā satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā sāsane uraṃ datvā pabbajitvā jetavane antokoṭisanthāre vihariṃsu. 
488078,110,3065,34,40,1,67,6,Athekadivasaṃ tesaṃ aḍḍharattasamaye kilesanissito saṅkappo uppajji. 
488079,110,3065,41,50,1,67,8,Te ukkaṇṭhitvā attanā jahitakilese puna gaṇhituṃ cittaṃ uppādayiṃsu. 
488080,110,3065,51,77,1,225,22,Atha satthā aḍḍharattasamanantare sabbaññutaññāṇadaṇḍadīpakaṃ ukkhipitvā‘‘ katarāya nu kho ratiyā jetavane bhikkhū viharantī’’ ti bhikkhūnaṃ ajjhāsayaṃ olokento tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ abbhantare kāmarāgasaṅkappassa uppannabhāvaṃ aññāsi. 
488081,110,3065,78,95,1,105,15,"Satthā ca nāma ekaputtikā itthī attano puttaṃ viya, ekacakkhuko puriso cakkhuṃ viya attano sāvake rakkhati. "
488082,110,3065,96,115,1,137,18,"Pubbaṇhādīsu yasmiṃ yasmiṃ samaye tesaṃ kilesā uppajjanti, te tesaṃ kilese tato paraṃ vaḍḍhituṃ adatvā tasmiṃ tasmiṃyeva samaye niggaṇhāti. "
488083,110,3065,116,140,1,163,19,"Tenassa etadahosi‘‘ ayaṃ cakkavattirañño antonagareyeva corānaṃ uppannakālo viya vattati, idāneva tesaṃ dhammadesanaṃ katvā te kilese niggaṇhitvā arahattaṃ dassāmī’’ ti. "
488084,110,3065,141,155,1,113,10,So surabhigandhakuṭito nikkhamitvā madhurassarena‘‘ ānandā’’ ti āyasmantaṃ dhammabhaṇḍāgārikaṃ ānandattheraṃ āmantesi. 
488085,110,3065,156,168,1,44,7,"Thero‘‘ kiṃ, bhante’’ ti āgantvā vanditvā aṭṭhāsi."
488086,110,3065,169,184,1,91,9,"‘‘ Ānanda, yattakā bhikkhū antokoṭisanthāre viharanti, sabbeva gandhakuṭipariveṇe sannipātehī’’ ti. "
488087,110,3065,185,195,1,66,8,Evaṃ kirassa ahosi‘‘ sacāhaṃ teyeva pañcasate bhikkhū pakkosāpessāmi.
488088,110,3065,196,213,1,116,13,‘ Satthārā no abbhantare kilesānaṃ uppannabhāvo ñāto’ ti saṃviggamānasā dhammadesanaṃ sampaṭicchituṃ na sakkhissantī’’ ti. 
488089,110,3065,214,223,1,30,5,Tasmā‘‘ sabbe sannipātehī’’ ti āha. 
488090,110,3065,224,244,1,137,15,"Thero‘‘ sādhu, bhante’’ ti avāpuraṇaṃ ādāya pariveṇena pariveṇaṃ āhiṇḍitvā sabbe bhikkhū gandhakuṭipariveṇe sannipātetvā buddhāsanaṃ paññapesi. "
488091,110,3066,2,19,1,179,17,Satthā pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya silāpathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhahamāno sineru viya paññatte buddhāsane nisīdi āveḷāveḷā yamakayamakā chabbaṇṇaghanabuddharasmiyo vissajjento. 
488092,110,3066,20,37,1,168,16,"Tāpi rasmiyo pātimattā chattamattā kūṭāgārakucchimattā chijjitvā chijjitvā gaganatale vijjulatā viya sañcariṃsu, aṇṇavakucchiṃ khobhetvā bālasūriyuggamanakālo viya ahosi. "
488093,110,3066,38,48,1,119,10,Bhikkhusaṅghopi satthāraṃ vanditvā garucittaṃ paccupaṭṭhapetvā rattakambalasāṇiyā parikkhipanto viya parivāretvā nisīdi. 
488094,110,3066,49,72,1,167,17,"Satthā brahmassaraṃ nicchārento bhikkhū āmantetvā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, bhikkhunā nāma kāmavitakkaṃ byāpādavitakkaṃ vihiṃsāvitakkanti ime tayo akusalavitakke vitakketuṃ vaṭṭati. "
488095,110,3066,73,87,1,86,11,"Anto uppannakileso hi‘ parittako’ ti avamaññituṃ na vaṭṭati, kileso nāma paccāmittasadiso. "
488096,110,3066,88,107,1,146,17,"Paccāmitto ca khuddako nāma natthi, okāsaṃ labhitvā vināsameva pāpeti, evameva appamattakopi kileso uppajjitvā vaḍḍhituṃ labhanto mahāvināsaṃ pāpeti. "
488097,110,3066,108,118,1,120,10,Kileso nāmesa halāhalavisūpamo uppāṭitacchavigaṇḍasadiso āsīvisapaṭibhāgo asaniaggisadiso allīyituṃ na yutto āsaṅkitabbo. 
488098,110,3066,119,133,1,146,13,"Uppannuppannakkhaṇeyeva paṭisaṅkhānabalena bhāvanābalena yathā muhuttampi hadaye aṭṭhatvā paduminipattā udakabindu viya vivaṭṭati, evaṃ pajahitabbo. "
488099,110,3066,134,152,1,123,15,"Porāṇakapaṇḍi tāpi appamattakampi kilesaṃ garahitvā yathā puna abbhantare nuppajjati, evaṃ niggaṇhiṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
488100,110,3067,2,16,1,122,13,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto siṅgālayoniyaṃ paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā araññe nadītīre nivāsaṃ kappesi. 
488101,110,3067,17,21,1,38,4,Atheko jarahatthī gaṅgātīre kālamakāsi. 
488102,110,3067,22,45,1,132,18,"Siṅgālo gocarappasuto taṃ matahatthisarīraṃ disvā‘‘ mahā me gocaro uppanno’’ ti gantvā taṃ soṇḍe ḍaṃsi, naṅgalīsāya daṭṭhakālo viya ahosi. "
488103,110,3067,46,61,1,79,10,"So‘‘ natthettha khāditabbayuttakan’’ ti dantesu ḍaṃsi, thambhe daṭṭhakālo viya ahosi. "
488104,110,3067,62,69,1,46,6,"Kaṇṇe ḍaṃsi, suppakoṭiyaṃ daṭṭhakālo viya ahosi. "
488105,110,3067,70,77,1,40,6,"Udare ḍaṃsi, kusūle daṭṭhakālo viya ahosi. "
488106,110,3067,78,85,1,42,6,"Pāde ḍaṃsi, udukkhale daṭṭhakālo viya ahosi. "
488107,110,3067,86,93,1,44,6,"Naṅguṭṭhe ḍaṃsi, musale daṭṭhakālo viya ahosi. "
488108,110,3067,94,113,1,115,14,"So‘‘ etthāpi natthi khāditabbayuttakan’’ ti sabbattha assādaṃ alabhanto vaccamagge ḍaṃsi, mudupūve daṭṭhakālo viya ahosi. "
488109,110,3067,114,141,1,212,23,So‘‘ laddhaṃ dāni me imasmiṃ sarīre mudu khāditabbayuttakaṭṭhānan’’ ti tato paṭṭhāya khādanto antokucchiṃ pavisitvā vakkahadayādīni khāditvā pipāsitakāle lohitaṃ pivitvā nipajjitukāmakāle udaraṃ pattharitvā nipajjati. 
488110,110,3068,2,4,1,17,2,Athassa etadahosi–
488111,110,3068,5,33,1,181,21,"‘‘ idaṃ hatthisarīraṃ mayhaṃ nivāsasukhatāya gehasadisaṃ, khāditukāmatāya sati pahūtamaṃsaṃ, kiṃ dāni me aññattha kamman’’ ti so aññattha agantvā hatthikucchiyaṃyeva maṃsaṃ khāditvā vasati. "
488112,110,3068,34,56,1,175,19,"Gacchante gacchante kāle nidāghe vātasamphassena ceva sūriyarasmisantāpena ca taṃ kuṇapaṃ sussitvā valiyo gaṇhi, siṅgālassa paviṭṭhadvāraṃ pihitaṃ, antokucchiyaṃ andhakāro ahosi. "
488113,110,3068,57,61,1,38,4,Siṅgālassa lokantarikanivāso viya jāto. 
488114,110,3068,62,69,1,50,6,"Kuṇape sussante maṃsampi sussi, lohitampi pacchijji. "
488115,110,3068,70,83,1,120,13,So nikkhamanadvāraṃ alabhanto bhayappatto hutvā sandhāvanto ito cito ca paharitvā nikkhamanadvāraṃ pariyesamāno vicarati. 
488116,110,3068,84,94,1,97,10,Evaṃ tasmiṃ ukkhaliyaṃ piṭṭhapiṇḍi viya antokucchiyaṃ paccamāne katipāhaccayena mahāmegho pāvassi. 
488117,110,3068,95,102,1,57,7,Atha naṃ kuṇapaṃ temetvā uṭṭhāya pakatisaṇṭhānena aṭṭhāsi. 
488118,110,3068,103,109,1,43,6,Vaccamaggo vivaṭo hutvā tārakā viya paññāyi. 
488119,110,3068,110,132,1,140,18,Siṅgālo taṃ chiddaṃ disvā‘‘ idāni me jīvitaṃ laddhan’’ ti yāva hatthisīsā paṭikkamitvā vegena pakkhanditvā vaccamaggaṃ sīsena paharitvā nikkhami. 
488120,110,3068,133,138,1,57,5,Tassa sañchannasarīrattā sabbalomāni vaccamagge allīyiṃsu. 
488121,110,3068,139,187,1,325,41,"So tālakkhandhasadisena nillomena sarīrena ubbiggacitto muhuttaṃ dhāvitvā nivattitvā nisinno sarīraṃ oloketvā‘‘ idaṃ dukkhaṃ mayhaṃ na aññena kataṃ, lobhahetu pana lobhakāraṇā lobhaṃ nissāya mayā etaṃ kataṃ, ito dāni paṭṭhāya na lobhavasiko bhavissāmi, puna hatthisarīraṃ nāma na pavisissāmī’’ ti saṃviggahadayo hutvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
488122,110,3069,2,4,1,0,0,148.
488123,110,3070,2,13,1,43,9,"‘ ‘ Nāhaṃ punaṃ na ca punaṃ, na cāpi apunappunaṃ; "
488124,110,3071,2,11,1,48,6,"Hatthibondiṃ pavekkhāmi, tathā hi bhayatajjito’’ ti. "
488125,110,3072,2,10,1,47,7,Tattha na cāpi apunappunan ti a-kāro nipātamatto. 
488126,110,3072,11,33,1,157,20,"Ayaṃ panetissā sakalāyapi gāthāya attho– ahañhi ito puna, tato ca punāti vuttavārato puna tatopi ca punappunaṃ vāraṇasarīrasaṅkhātaṃ hatthibondiṃ na pavekkhāmi. "
488127,110,3072,34,35,1,9,1,Kiṃkāraṇā? 
488128,110,3072,36,50,1,111,13,"Tathā hi bhayatajjito, tathā hi ahaṃ imasmiññeva pavesane bhayatajjito maraṇabhayena santāsaṃ saṃvegaṃ āpāditoti. "
488129,110,3073,2,17,1,93,14,Evañca pana vatvā tatova palāyitvā puna taṃ vā aññaṃ vā hatthisarīraṃ nivattitvāpi na olokesi. 
488130,110,3073,18,23,1,34,5,Tato paṭṭhāya na lobhavasiko ahosi. 
488131,110,3074,2,29,1,175,21,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ bhikkhave, anto uppannakilesassa nāma vaḍḍhituṃ adatvā tattha tattheva naṃ niggaṇhituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti vatvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi. "
488132,110,3074,30,47,1,126,14,"Saccapariyosāne pañcasatāpi te bhikkhū arahatte patiṭṭhahiṃsu, avasesesu keci sotāpannā, keci sakadāgāmino, keci anāgāmino ahesuṃ. "
488133,110,3074,48,52,1,29,4,Tadā siṅgālo ahameva ahosinti. 
488134,110,3075,2,4,1,28,2,Siṅgālajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
488135,110,3077,2,7,1,21,2,[ 149]9. Ekapaṇṇajātakavaṇṇanā 
488136,110,3078,2,17,1,136,14,Ekapaṇṇo ayaṃ {rukkho}ti idaṃ satthā vesāliṃ upanissāya mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ viharanto vesālikaṃ duṭṭhalicchavikumāraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488137,110,3078,18,29,1,127,11,Tasmiñhi kāle vesālinagaraṃ gāvutagāvutantare tīhi pākārehi parikkhittaṃ tīsu ṭhānesu gopuraṭṭālakayuttaṃ paramasobhaggappattaṃ. 
488138,110,3078,30,53,1,168,20,"Tattha niccakālaṃ rajjaṃ kāretvā vasantānaññeva rājūnaṃ satta sahassāni satta satāni satta ca rājāno honti, tattakāyeva uparājāno, tattakā senāpatino, tattakā bhaṇḍāgārikā. "
488139,110,3078,54,72,1,147,17,"Tesaṃ rājakumārānaṃ antare eko duṭṭhalicchavikumāro nāma ahosi kodhano caṇḍo pharuso sāhasiko, daṇḍena ghaṭṭitaāsīviso viya niccaṃ pajjalito kodhena. "
488140,110,3078,73,82,1,60,9,Tassa purato dve tīṇi vacanāni kathetuṃ samattho nāma natthi. 
488141,110,3078,83,94,1,67,9,"Taṃ neva mātāpitaro, na ñātayo, na mittasuhajjā sikkhāpetuṃ sakkhiṃsu. "
488142,110,3078,95,119,1,156,18,"Athassa mātāpitūnaṃ etadahosi‘‘ ayaṃ kumāro atipharuso sāhasiko, ṭhapetvā sammāsambuddhaṃ añño imaṃ vinetuṃ samattho nāma natthi, buddhaveneyyena bhavitabban’’ ti. "
488143,110,3078,120,145,1,125,19,"Te taṃ ādāya satthu santikaṃ gantvā vanditvā āhaṃsu‘‘ bhante, ayaṃ kumāro caṇḍo pharuso kodhena pajjalati, imassa ovādaṃ dethā’’ ti. "
488144,110,3079,2,8,1,24,4,Satthā taṃ kumāraṃ ovadi–
488145,110,3079,9,55,1,363,39,"‘‘ kumāra, imesu nāma sattesu caṇḍena pharusena sāhasikena viheṭhakajātikena na bhavitabbaṃ, pharusavāco ca nāma vijātamātuyāpi pitunopi puttadārassapi bhātibhaginīnampi pajāpatiyāpi mittabandhavānampi appiyo hoti amanāpo, ḍaṃsituṃ āgacchanto sappo viya, aṭaviyaṃ uṭṭhitacoro viya, khādituṃ āgacchanto yakkho viya ca ubbejanīyo hutvā dutiyacittavāre nirayādīsu nibbattati. "
488146,110,3079,56,75,1,191,18,"Diṭṭheyeva ca dhamme kodhano puggalo maṇḍitapasādhitopi dubbaṇṇova hoti, puṇṇacandasassirikampissa mukhaṃ jālābhihatapadumaṃ viya malaggahitakañcanādāsamaṇḍalaṃ viya ca virūpaṃ hoti duddasikaṃ. "
488147,110,3079,76,94,1,116,15,"Kodhaṃ nissāya hi sattā satthaṃ ādāya attanāva attānaṃ paharanti, visaṃ khādanti, rajjuyā ubbandhanti, papātā papatanti. "
488148,110,3079,95,120,1,201,22,"Evaṃ kodhavasena kālaṃ katvā nirayādīsu uppajjanti, viheṭhakajātikāpi diṭṭheva dhamme garahaṃ patvā kāyassa bhedā nirayādīsu uppajjanti, puna manussattaṃ labhitvā vijātakālato paṭṭhāya rogabahulāva honti. "
488149,110,3079,121,144,1,187,21,"Cakkhurogo sotarogotiādīsu ca rogesu ekato uṭṭhāya ekasmiṃ patanti, rogena aparimuttāva hutvā niccaṃ dukkhitāva honti, tasmā sabbesu sattesu mettacittena hitacittena muducittena bhavitabbaṃ. "
488150,110,3079,145,154,1,52,7,Evarūpo hi puggalo nirayādibhayehi na parimuccatī’’ ti. 
488151,110,3079,155,167,1,97,12,So kumāro satthu ovādaṃ sutvā ekovādeneva nihatamāno danto nibbisevano mettacitto muducitto ahosi. 
488152,110,3079,168,188,1,137,17,"Aññaṃ akkosantampi paharantampi nivattitvā na olokesi, uddhaṭadāṭho viya sappo, aḷacchinno viya kakkaṭako, chinnavisāṇo viya ca usabho ahosi. "
488153,110,3080,2,36,1,281,29,"Tassa taṃ pavattiṃ ñatvā bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, duṭṭhalicchavikumāraṃ sucirampi ovaditvā neva mātāpitaro, na ñātimittādayo dametuṃ sakkhiṃsu, sammāsambuddho pana taṃ ekovādeneva dametvā nibbisevanaṃ katvā mattavaravāraṇaṃ viya samuggahitāneñjakāraṇaṃ akāsi. "
488154,110,3080,37,40,1,21,3,Yāva subhāsitaṃ cidaṃ–
488155,110,3080,41,59,1,118,15,"‘ hatthidamakena, bhikkhave, hatthidammo sārito ekaṃyeva disaṃ dhāvati puratthimaṃ vā pacchimaṃ vā uttaraṃ vā dakkhiṇaṃ vā. "
488156,110,3080,60,70,1,42,6,Assadamakena… pe… godamakena… pe… dakkhiṇaṃ vā. 
488157,110,3080,71,87,1,109,13,"Tathāgatena hi, bhikkhave, arahatā sammāsambuddhena purisadammo sārito aṭṭha disā vidhāvati, rūpī rūpāni passati. "
488158,110,3080,88,111,1,72,9,Ayamekā disā… pe… so vuccati‘ yoggācariyānaṃ anuttaro purisadammasārathī’ ti( ma. ni.3.312). 
488159,110,3080,112,125,1,68,9,"Na hi, āvuso, sammāsambuddhena sadiso purisadammasārathī nāma atthī’’ ti. "
488160,110,3080,126,171,1,201,28,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevesa mayā ekovādeneva damito, pubbepāhaṃ imaṃ ekovādeneva damesin’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
488161,110,3081,2,34,1,284,31,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto udiccabrāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ tayo vede sabbasippāni ca uggahetvā kiñci kālaṃ gharāvāsaṃ vasitvā mātāpitūnaṃ accayena isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā himavante vāsaṃ kappesi. 
488162,110,3081,35,55,1,190,19,Tattha ciraṃ vasitvā loṇambilasevanatthāya janapadaṃ gantvā bārāṇasiṃ patvā rājuyyāne vasitvā punadivase sunivattho supāruto tāpasākappasampanno bhikkhāya nagaraṃ pavisitvā rājaṅgaṇaṃ pāpuṇi. 
488163,110,3081,56,78,1,184,19,"Rājā sīhapañjarena olokento taṃ disvā iriyāpathe pasīditvā‘‘ ayaṃ tāpaso santindriyo santamānaso yugamattadaso, padavāre padavāre sahassatthavikaṃ ṭhapento viya sīhavijambhitena āgacchati. "
488164,110,3081,79,94,1,95,12,"Sace santadhammo nāmeko atthi, imassa tenabbhantare bhavitabban’’ ti cintetvā ekaṃ amaccaṃ olokesi. "
488165,110,3081,95,106,1,25,6,"So‘‘ kiṃ karomi, devā’’ ti āha. "
488166,110,3081,107,115,1,21,4,Etaṃ‘‘ tāpasaṃ ānehī’’ ti. 
488167,110,3081,116,151,1,140,20,"So‘‘ sādhu, devā’’ ti bodhisattaṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā hatthato bhikkhābhājanaṃ gahetvā‘‘ kiṃ, mahāpuññā’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhante, rājā taṃ pakkosatī’’ ti āha. "
488168,110,3081,152,165,1,59,8,"Bodhisatto‘‘ na mayaṃ rājakulūpakā, hemavantikā nāmamhā’’ ti āha. "
488169,110,3081,166,171,1,37,5,Amacco gantvā tamatthaṃ rañño ārocesi. 
488170,110,3081,172,186,1,50,9,"Rājā‘‘ añño amhākaṃ kulūpako natthi, ānehi nan’’ ti āha. "
488171,110,3081,187,194,1,65,7,Amacco gantvā bodhisattaṃ vanditvā yācitvā rājanivesanaṃ pavesesi. 
488172,110,3082,2,23,1,152,15,"Rājā bodhisattaṃ vanditvā samussitasetacchatte kañcanapallaṅke nisīdāpetvā attano paṭiyattaṃ nānaggarasabhojanaṃ bhojetvā‘‘ kahaṃ, bhante, vasathā’’ ti pucchi."
488173,110,3082,24,33,1,29,4,"‘‘ Hemavantikā mayaṃ, mahārājā’’ ti."
488174,110,3082,34,42,1,24,4,‘‘ Idāni kahaṃ gacchathā’’ ti?
488175,110,3082,43,53,1,50,5,"‘‘ Vassārattānurūpaṃ senāsanaṃ upadhārema, mahārājā’’ ti."
488176,110,3082,54,86,1,230,25,"‘‘ Tena hi, bhante, amhākaññeva uyyāne vasathā’’ ti paṭiññaṃ gahetvā sayampi bhuñjitvā bodhisattaṃ ādāya uyyānaṃ gantvā paṇṇasālaṃ māpetvā rattiṭṭhānadivāṭṭhānāpi kāretvā pabbajitaparikkhāre datvā uyyānapālaṃ paṭicchāpetvā nagaraṃ pāvisi. "
488177,110,3082,87,92,1,38,5,Tato paṭṭhāya bodhisatto uyyāne vasati. 
488178,110,3082,93,99,1,58,6,Rājāpissa divase divase dvattikkhattuṃ upaṭṭhānaṃ gacchati. 
488179,110,3083,2,20,1,104,16,"Tassa pana rañño duṭṭhakumāro nāma putto ahosi caṇḍo pharuso, neva naṃ rājā dametuṃ asakkhi, na sesañātakā. "
488180,110,3083,21,45,1,133,18,"Amaccāpi brāhmaṇagahapatikāpi ekato hutvā‘‘ sāmi, mā evaṃ kari, evaṃ kātuṃ na labbhā’’ ti kujjhitvā kathentāpi kathaṃ gāhāpetuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu. "
488181,110,3083,46,68,1,120,17,"Rājā cintesi‘‘ ṭhapetvā mama ayyaṃ himavantatāpasaṃ añño imaṃ kumāraṃ dametuṃ samattho nāma natthi, soyeva naṃ damessatī’’ ti. "
488182,110,3083,69,104,1,189,26,"So kumāraṃ ādāya bodhisattassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ bhante, ayaṃ kumāro caṇḍo pharuso , mayaṃ imaṃ dametuṃ na sakkoma, tumhe naṃ ekena upāyena sikkhāpethā’’ ti kumāraṃ bodhisattassa niyyādetvā pakkāmi. "
488183,110,3083,105,122,1,123,16,"Bodhisatto kumāraṃ gahetvā uyyāne vicaranto ekato ekena, ekato ekenāti dvīhiyeva pattehi ekaṃ nimbapotakaṃ disvā kumāraṃ āha–"
488184,110,3083,123,137,1,66,9,"‘‘ kumāra, etassa tāva rukkhapotakassa paṇṇaṃ khāditvā rasaṃ jānāhī’’ ti? "
488185,110,3083,138,155,1,80,13,So tassa ekaṃ pattaṃ khāditvā rasaṃ ñatvā‘‘ dhī’’ ti saha kheḷena bhūmiyaṃ nuṭṭhābhi.
488186,110,3083,156,189,1,170,22,"‘‘ Kiṃ etaṃ, kumārā’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhante, idānevesa rukkho halāhalavisūpamo, vaḍḍhanto pana bahū manusse māressatī’’ ti taṃ nimbapotakaṃ uppāṭetvā hatthehi parimadditvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
488187,110,3084,2,4,1,0,0,149.
488188,110,3085,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Ekapaṇṇo ayaṃ rukkho, na bhūmyā caturaṅgulo; "
488189,110,3086,2,11,1,45,6,"Phalena visakappena, mahāyaṃ kiṃ bhavissatī’’ ti. "
488190,110,3087,2,8,1,43,5,Tattha {ekapaṇṇo}ti ubhosu passesu ekekapaṇṇo. 
488191,110,3087,9,17,1,63,7,Na bhūmyā {caturaṅgulo}ti bhūmito caturaṅgulamattampi na vaḍḍhito. 
488192,110,3087,18,21,1,21,2,{Phalenā}ti phalarasena. 
488193,110,3087,22,25,1,34,2,{Visakappenā}ti halāhalavisasadisena. 
488194,110,3087,26,34,1,70,8,Evaṃ khuddakopi samāno evarūpena tittakena paṇṇena samannāgatoti attho. 
488195,110,3087,35,58,1,164,20,"Mahāyaṃ kiṃ {bhavissatī}ti yadā panāyaṃ vuddhippatto mahā bhavissati, tadā kiṃ nāma bhavissati, addhā manussamārako bhavissatīti etaṃ uppāṭetvā madditvā chaḍḍesinti āha. "
488196,110,3088,2,31,1,164,21,"Atha naṃ bodhisatto etadavoca‘‘ kumāra, tvaṃ imaṃ nimbapotakaṃ‘ idāneva evaṃtittako, mahallakakāle kiṃ bhavissati, kuto imaṃ nissāya vuḍḍhī’ ti uppāṭetvā madditvā chaḍḍesi? "
488197,110,3088,32,84,1,368,44,"Yathā tvaṃ etasmiṃ paṭipajji, evameva tava raṭṭhavāsinopi‘ ayaṃ kumāro daharakāleyeva evaṃ caṇḍo pharuso, mahallakakāle rajjaṃ patvā kiṃ nāma karissati, kuto amhākaṃ etaṃ nissāya vuḍḍhī’ ti tava kulasantakaṃ rajjaṃ adatvā nimbapotakaṃ viya taṃ uppāṭetvā raṭṭhā pabbājanīyakammaṃ karissanti, tasmā nimbarukkhapaṭibhāgataṃ hitvā ito paṭṭhāya khantimettānuddayasampanno hohī’’ ti. "
488198,110,3088,85,105,1,169,19,So tato paṭṭhāya nihatamāno nibbisevano khantimettānuddayasampanno hutvā bodhisattassa ovāde ṭhatvā pitu accayena rajjaṃ patvā dānādīni puññāni katvā yathākammaṃ agamāsi. 
488199,110,3089,2,26,1,147,17,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevesa duṭṭhalicchavikumāro mayā damito, pubbepāhaṃ etaṃ damesiṃyevā’’ ti vatvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
488200,110,3089,27,45,1,96,12,"‘‘ tadā duṭṭhakumāro ayaṃ licchavikumāro ahosi, rājā ānando, ovādadāyakatāpaso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
488201,110,3090,2,4,1,28,2,Ekapaṇṇajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
488202,110,3092,2,7,1,20,2,[ 150]10. Sañjīvajātakavaṇṇanā 
488203,110,3093,2,16,1,105,12,Asantaṃ yo {paggaṇhātī}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto ajātasattussa rañño asantapaggahaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488204,110,3093,17,57,1,327,36,So hi buddhānaṃ paṭikaṇṭakabhūte dussīle pāpadhamme devadatte pasīditvā taṃ asantaṃ asappurisaṃ paggayha‘‘ tassa sakkāraṃ karissāmī’’ ti bahuṃ dhanaṃ pariccajitvā gayāsīse vihāraṃ kāretvā tasseva vacanaṃ gahetvā pitaraṃ dhammarājānaṃ sotāpannaṃ ariyasāvakaṃ ghātetvā attano sotāpattimaggassa upanissayaṃ bhinditvā mahāvināsaṃ patto. 
488205,110,3093,58,95,1,203,27,"So hi‘‘ devadatto pathaviyaṃ paviṭṭho’’ ti sutvā‘‘ kacci nu kho mampi pathavī gileyyā’’ ti bhītatasito rajjasukhaṃ na labhati, sayane assādasukhaṃ na vindati, tibbakāraṇābhitunno hatthipoto viya kampamāno vicarati. "
488206,110,3093,96,120,1,179,20,"So pathaviṃ phalamānaṃ viya, avīcijālaṃ nikkhamantiṃ viya, pathaviyā attānaṃ giliyamānaṃ viya, ādittāya lohapathaviyā uttānakaṃ nipajjāpetvā ayasūlehi koṭiyamānaṃ viya ca samanupassi. "
488207,110,3093,121,128,1,73,7,Tenassa pahaṭakukkuṭasseva muhuttampi kampamānassa avatthānaṃ nāma nāhosi. 
488208,110,3093,129,143,1,127,13,"So sammāsambuddhaṃ passitukāmo khamāpetukāmo pañhaṃ pucchitukāmo ahosi, attano pana aparādhamahantatāya upasaṅkamituṃ na sakkoti. "
488209,110,3094,2,92,1,614,75,"Athassa rājagahanagare kattikarattivāre sampatte devanagaraṃ viya nagare alaṅkate mahātale amaccagaṇaparivutassa kañcanāsane nisinnassa jīvakaṃ komārabhaccaṃ avidūre nisinnaṃ disvā etadahosi‘‘ jīvakaṃ gahetvā sammāsambuddhassa santikaṃ gamissāmi, na kho pana sakkā mayā ujukameva vattuṃ‘ ahaṃ, samma jīvaka, sayaṃ gantuṃ na sakkomi, ehi maṃ satthu santikaṃ nehī’ ti, pariyāyena pana rattisampadaṃ vaṇṇetvā‘ kaṃ nu khvajja mayaṃ samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā payirupāseyyāma, yaṃ no payirupāsataṃ cittaṃ pasīdeyyā’ ti vakkhāmi, taṃ sutvā amaccā attano attano satthārānaṃ vaṇṇaṃ kathessanti, jīvakopi sammāsambuddhassa vaṇṇaṃ kathessati. "
488210,110,3094,93,102,1,45,7,Atha naṃ gahetvā satthu santikaṃ gamissāmī’’ ti. 
488211,110,3094,103,167,1,291,45,"So pañcahi padehi rattiṃ vaṇṇesi‘‘ lakkhaññā vata bho dosinā ratti, abhirūpā vata bho dosinā ratti, dassanīyā vata bho dosinā ratti, pāsādikā vata bho dosinā ratti, ramaṇīyā vata bho dosinā ratti, kaṃ nu khvajja mayaṃ samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā payirupāseyyāma, yaṃ no payirupāsataṃ cittaṃ pasīdeyyā’’ ti( dī. ni.1.150). "
488212,110,3095,2,24,1,174,16,"Atheko amacco pūraṇakassapassa vaṇṇaṃ kathesi, eko makkhaligosālassa, eko ajitakesakambalassa, eko pakudhakaccāyanassa, eko sañcayassa belaṭṭhaputtassa, eko nāṭaputtanigaṇṭhassāti . "
488213,110,3095,25,31,1,35,6,Rājā tesaṃ kathaṃ sutvā tuṇhī ahosi. 
488214,110,3095,32,38,1,50,6,So hi jīvakasseva mahāamaccassa kathaṃ paccāsīsati. 
488215,110,3095,39,53,1,72,10,Jīvakopi‘‘ raññā maṃ ārabbha kathiteyeva jānissāmī’’ ti avidūre tuṇhī nisīdi. 
488216,110,3095,54,71,1,53,11,"Atha naṃ rājā āha‘‘ tvaṃ pana, samma jīvaka, kiṃ tuṇhī’’ ti? "
488217,110,3095,72,96,1,166,19,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe jīvako uṭṭhāyāsanā yena bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā‘‘ eso, deva, bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho amhākaṃ ambavane viharati saddhiṃ aḍḍhateḷasehi bhikkhusatehi. "
488218,110,3095,97,133,1,224,28,"Taṃ kho pana bhagavantaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato’’ ti nava arahādiguṇe vatvā jātito paṭṭhāya pubbanimittādibhedaṃ bhagavato ānubhāvaṃ pakāsetvā‘‘ taṃ bhagavantaṃ devo payirupāsatu, dhammaṃ suṇātu, pañhaṃ pucchatū’’ ti āha. "
488219,110,3096,2,62,1,452,50,"Rājā sampuṇṇamanoratho hutvā‘‘ tena hi, samma jīvaka, hatthiyānāni kappāpehī’’ ti yānāni kappāpetvā mahantena rājānubhāvena jīvakambavanaṃ gantvā tattha maṇḍalamāḷe bhikkhusaṅghaparivutaṃ tathāgataṃ disvā santavīcimajjhe mahānāvaṃ viya niccalaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ ito cito ca anuviloketvā‘‘ evarūpā nāma me parisā na diṭṭhapubbā’’ ti iriyāpatheyeva pasīditvā saṅghassa añjaliṃ paggaṇhitvā thutiṃ katvā bhagavantaṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno sāmaññaphalapañhaṃ pucchi. "
488220,110,3096,63,80,1,73,7,Athassa bhagavā dvīhi bhāṇavārehi paṭimaṇḍitaṃ sāmaññaphalasuttaṃ( dī. ni.1.150 ādayo) kathesi. 
488221,110,3096,81,90,1,88,9,So suttapariyosāne attamano bhagavantaṃ khamāpetvā uṭṭhāyāsanā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. 
488222,110,3096,91,109,1,97,11,"Satthā acirapakkantassa rañño bhikkhū āmantetvā‘‘ khatāyaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā, upahatāyaṃ, bhikkhave, rājā. "
488223,110,3096,110,131,1,160,17,"Sacāyaṃ , bhikkhave, rājā issariyassa kāraṇā pitaraṃ dhammikaṃ dhammarājānaṃ jīvitā na voropessatha, imasmiṃyeva āsane virajaṃ vītamalaṃ dhammacakkhuṃ uppajjissatha. "
488224,110,3096,132,142,1,70,8,Devadattaṃ nissāya asantapaggahaṃ katvā sotāpattiphalā parihīno’’ ti āha. 
488225,110,3097,2,30,1,216,22,"Punadivase bhikkhū dhammasabhāyaṃ kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, ajātasattu kira asantapaggahaṃ katvā dussīlaṃ pāpadhammaṃ devadattaṃ nissāya pitughātakakammassa katattā sotāpattiphalā parihīno, devadattena nāsito rājā’’ ti. "
488226,110,3097,31,78,1,232,30,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, ajātasattu idāneva asantapaggahaṃ katvā mahāvināsaṃ patto, pubbepesa asantapaggaheneva attānaṃ nāsesī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
488227,110,3098,2,26,1,219,22,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto mahāvibhave brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilaṃ gantvā sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā bārāṇasiyaṃ disāpāmokkho ācariyo hutvā pañca māṇavakasatāni sippaṃ vācesi. 
488228,110,3098,27,39,1,89,11,"Tesu māṇavesu eko sañjīvo nāma māṇavo atthi, bodhisatto tassa matakuṭṭhāpanakamantaṃ adāsi. "
488229,110,3098,40,67,1,193,22,"So uṭṭhāpanakamantameva gahetvā paṭibāhanamantaṃ pana aggahetvāva ekadivasaṃ māṇavehi saddhiṃ dāruatthāya araññaṃ gantvā ekaṃ matabyagghaṃ disvā māṇave āha‘‘ bho, imaṃ matabyagghaṃ uṭṭhāpessāmī’’ ti. "
488230,110,3098,68,77,1,31,5,Māṇavā‘‘ na sakkhissasī’’ ti āhaṃsu.
488231,110,3098,78,87,1,38,5,‘‘ Passantānaññeva vo taṃ uṭṭhāpessāmī’’ ti.
488232,110,3098,88,100,1,32,5,"‘‘ Sace, māṇava, sakkosi, uṭṭhāpehī’’ ti. "
488233,110,3098,101,108,1,47,7,Evañca pana vatvā te māṇavā rukkhaṃ abhiruhiṃsu. 
488234,110,3098,109,130,1,177,19,"Sañjīvo mantaṃ parivattetvā matabyagghaṃ sakkharāhi pahari, byaggho uṭṭhāya vegenāgantvā sañjīvaṃ galanāḷiyaṃ ḍaṃsitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā tattheva pati, sañjīvopi tattheva pati. "
488235,110,3098,131,135,1,36,4,Ubhopi ekaṭṭhāneyeva matā nipajjiṃsu. 
488236,110,3099,2,10,1,60,8,Māṇavā dārūni ādāya āgantvā taṃ pavattiṃ ācariyassa ārocesuṃ. 
488237,110,3099,11,32,1,147,16,"Ācariyo māṇave āmantetvā‘‘ tātā, asantapaggahakārā nāma ayuttaṭṭhāne sakkārasammānaṃ karontā evarūpaṃ dukkhaṃ paṭilabhantiyevā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ gāthamāha– "
