488241,110,3103,2,10,1,68,8,Tattha asantan ti tīhi duccaritehi samannāgataṃ dussīlaṃ pāpadhammaṃ. 
488242,110,3103,11,31,1,179,17,"Yo {paggaṇhātī}ti khattiyādīsu yo koci evarūpaṃ dussīlaṃ pabbajitaṃ vā cīvarādisampadānena, gahaṭṭhaṃ vā uparajjasenāpatiṭṭhānādisampadānena paggaṇhāti, sakkārasammānaṃ karotīti attho. "
488243,110,3103,32,43,1,83,10,Asantaṃ {cūpasevatī}ti yo ca evarūpaṃ asantaṃ dussīlaṃ upasevati bhajati payirupāsati. 
488244,110,3103,44,57,1,104,12,Tameva ghāsaṃ {kurute}ti tameva asantapaggaṇhakaṃ so dussīlo pāpapuggalo ghasati saṃkhādati vināsaṃ pāpeti. 
488245,110,3103,58,59,1,6,1,Kathaṃ? 
