488324,111,27,2,7,1,20,2,[ 152]2. Siṅgālajātakavaṇṇanā 
488325,111,28,2,14,1,110,11,Asamekkhitakammantan ti idaṃ satthā kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ viharanto vesālivāsikaṃ ekaṃ nhāpitaputtaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488326,111,28,15,36,1,234,20,"Tassa kira pitā rājūnaṃ rājorodhānaṃ rājakumārānaṃ rājakumārikānañca massukaraṇakesasaṇṭhapanaaṭṭhapadaṭṭhapanādīni sabbakiccāni karoti saddho pasanno tisaraṇagato samādinnapañcasīlo, antarantare satthu dhammaṃ suṇanto kālaṃ vītināmeti. "
488327,111,28,37,48,1,80,11,So ekasmiṃ divase rājanivesane kammaṃ kātuṃ gacchanto attano puttaṃ gahetvā gato. 
488328,111,28,49,82,1,275,28,"So tattha ekaṃ devaccharāpaṭibhāgaṃ alaṅkatapaṭiyattaṃ licchavikumārikaṃ disvā kilesavasena paṭibaddhacitto hutvā pitarā saddhiṃ rājanivesanā nikkhamitvā‘‘ etaṃ kumārikaṃ labhamāno jīvissāmi, alabhamānassa me ettheva maraṇan’’ ti āhārupacchedaṃ katvā mañcakaṃ parissajitvā nipajji. "
488329,111,29,2,38,1,215,27,"Atha naṃ pitā upasaṅkamitvā‘‘ tāta, avatthumhi chandarāgaṃ mā kari, hīnajacco tvaṃ nhāpitaputto, licchavikumārikā khattiyadhītā jātisampannā, na sā tuyhaṃ anucchavikā, aññaṃ te jātigottehi sadisaṃ kumārikaṃ ānessāmī’’ ti āha. "
488330,111,29,39,44,1,23,5,So pitu kathaṃ na gaṇhi. 
488331,111,29,45,61,1,132,16,Atha naṃ mātā bhātā bhaginī cūḷapitā cūḷamātāti sabbepi ñātakā ceva mittasuhajjā ca sannipatitvā saññāpentāpi saññāpetuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu. 
488332,111,29,62,68,1,54,6,So tattheva sussitvā parisussitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇi. 
488333,111,29,69,110,1,243,30,"Athassa pitā sarīrakiccapetakiccāni katvā tanusoko ‘‘ satthāraṃ vandissāmī’’ ti bahuṃ gandhamālāvilepanaṃ gahetvā mahāvanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ pūjetvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisinno‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, upāsaka, bahūni divasāni na dissasī’’ ti vutte tamatthaṃ ārocesi. "
488334,111,29,111,139,1,141,20,"Satthā‘‘ na kho, upāsaka, idāneva tava putto avatthusmiṃ chandarāgaṃ uppādetvā vināsaṃ pāpuṇi, pubbepi pattoyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
488335,111,30,2,11,1,92,9,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto himavantapadese sīhayoniyaṃ nibbatti. 
488336,111,30,12,23,1,77,10,"Tassa cha kaniṭṭhabhātaro ekā ca bhaginī ahosi, sabbepi kañcanaguhāyaṃ vasanti. "
488337,111,30,24,36,1,85,11,"Tassā pana guhāya avidūre rajatapabbate ekā phalikaguhā atthi, tattheko siṅgālo vasati. "
488338,111,30,37,41,1,41,4,Aparabhāge sīhānaṃ mātāpitaro kālamakaṃsu. 
488339,111,30,42,53,1,95,11,Te bhaginiṃ sīhapotikaṃ kañcanaguhāyaṃ ṭhapetvā gocarāya pakkamitvā maṃsaṃ āharitvā tassā denti. 
488340,111,30,54,61,1,54,7,So siṅgālo taṃ sīhapotikaṃ disvā paṭibaddhacitto ahosi. 
488341,111,30,62,86,1,219,22,"Tassā pana mātāpitūnaṃ dharamānakāle okāsaṃ nālattha, so sattannampi tesaṃ gocarāya pakkantakāle phalikaguhāya otaritvā kañcanaguhāya dvāraṃ gantvā sīhapotikāya purato lokāmisapaṭisaṃyuttaṃ evarūpaṃ rahassakathaṃ kathesi–"
488342,111,30,87,122,1,178,25,"‘‘ sīhapotike, ahampi catuppado, tvampi catuppadā, tvaṃ me pajāpatī hohi, ahaṃ te pati bhavissāmi, te mayaṃ samaggā sammodamānā vasissāma, tvaṃ ito paṭṭhāya maṃ kilesavasena saṅgaṇhāhī’’ ti. "
488343,111,30,123,128,1,30,5,Sā tassa vacanaṃ sutvā cintesi–
488344,111,30,129,165,1,238,28,"‘‘ ayaṃ siṅgālo catuppadānaṃ antare hīno paṭikuṭṭho caṇḍālasadiso, mayaṃ uttamarājakulasammatā, esa kho mayā saddhiṃ asabbhiṃ ananucchavikaṃ kathaṃ katheti, ahaṃ evarūpaṃ kathaṃ sutvā jīvitena kiṃ karissāmi, nāsāvātaṃ sannirujjhitvā marissāmī’’ ti. "
488345,111,30,166,168,1,17,2,Athassā etadahosi–
488346,111,30,169,188,1,85,12,"‘‘ mayhaṃ evameva maraṇaṃ ayuttaṃ, bhātikā tāva me āgacchantu, tesaṃ kathetvā marissāmī’’ ti. "
488347,111,30,189,207,1,123,14,Siṅgālopi tassā santikā paṭivacanaṃ alabhitvā‘‘ idāni esā mayhaṃ kujjhatī’’ ti domanassappatto phalikaguhāyaṃ pavisitvā nipajji. 
488348,111,31,2,22,1,124,15,"Atheko sīhapotako mahiṃsavāraṇādīsu aññataraṃ vadhitvā maṃsaṃ khāditvā bhaginiyā bhāgaṃ āharitvā‘‘ amma, maṃsaṃ khādassū’’ ti āha."
488349,111,31,23,35,1,41,6,"‘‘ Bhātika, nāhaṃ maṃsaṃ khādāmi, marissāmī’’ ti."
488350,111,31,36,43,1,13,3,‘‘ Kiṃ kāraṇā’’ ti? 
488351,111,31,44,48,1,23,4,Sā taṃ pavattiṃ ācikkhi.
488352,111,31,49,86,1,152,23,"‘‘ Idāni kahaṃ so siṅgālo’’ ti ca vutte phalikaguhāyaṃ nipannaṃ siṅgālaṃ‘‘ ākāse nipanno’’ ti maññamānā‘‘ bhātika, kiṃ na passasi, eso rajatapabbate ākāse nipanno’’ ti. "
488353,111,31,87,114,1,155,18,Sīhapotako tassa phalikaguhāyaṃ nipannabhāvaṃ ajānanto‘‘ ākāse nipanno’’ ti saññī hutvā‘‘ māressāmi nan’’ ti sīhavegena pakkhanditvā phalikaguhaṃ hadayeneva pahari. 
488354,111,31,115,123,1,67,8,So hadayena phalitena tattheva jīvitakkhayaṃ patvā pabbatapāde pati. 
488355,111,31,124,131,1,43,6,"Athāparo āgacchi, sā tassapi tatheva kathesi. "
488356,111,31,132,139,1,55,7,Sopi tatheva katvā jīvitakkhayaṃ patvā pabbatapāde pati. 
488357,111,32,2,9,1,60,7,Evaṃ chasupi bhātikesu matesu sabbapacchā bodhisatto āgacchi. 
488358,111,32,10,34,1,102,16,Sā tassapi taṃ kāraṇaṃ ārocetvā‘‘ idāni so kuhin’’ ti vutte‘‘ eso rajatapabbatamatthake ākāse nipanno’’ ti āha. 
488359,111,32,35,37,1,18,2,Bodhisatto cintesi–
488360,111,32,38,52,1,76,9,"‘‘ siṅgālānaṃ ākāse patiṭṭhā nāma natthi, phalikaguhāyaṃ nipannako bhavissatī’’ ti. "
488361,111,32,53,87,1,248,29,"So pabbatapādaṃ otaritvā cha bhātike mate disvā‘‘ ime attano bālatāya pariggaṇhanapaññāya abhāvena phalikaguhabhāvaṃ ajānitvā hadayena paharitvā matā bhavissanti, asamekkhitvā atituritaṃ karontānaṃ kammaṃ nāma evarūpaṃ hotī’’ ti vatvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
488362,111,33,2,4,1,0,0,3.
488363,111,34,2,7,1,39,3,"‘ ‘ Asamekkhitakammantaṃ, turitābhinipātinaṃ; "
488364,111,35,2,11,1,47,6,"Sāni kammāni tappenti, uṇhaṃvajjhohitaṃ mukhe’’ ti. "
488365,111,36,2,40,1,291,32,"Tattha asamekkhitakammantaṃ, turitābhinipātinan ti yo puggalo yaṃ kammaṃ kattukāmo hoti, tattha dosaṃ asamekkhitvā anupadhāretvā turito hutvā vegeneva taṃ kammaṃ kātuṃ abhinipatati pakkhandati paṭipajjati, taṃ asamekkhitakammantaṃ turitābhinipātinaṃ evaṃ sāni kammāni tappenti, socenti kilamenti. "
488366,111,36,41,43,1,9,2,Yathā kiṃ? 
488367,111,36,44,78,1,231,27,"Uṇhaṃvajjhohitaṃ {mukhe}ti, yathā bhuñjantena‘‘ idaṃ sītalaṃ idaṃ uṇhan’’ ti anupadhāretvā uṇhaṃ ajjhoharaṇīyaṃ mukhe ajjhoharitaṃ ṭhapitaṃ mukhampi kaṇṭhampi kucchimpi dahati soceti kilameti, evaṃ tathārūpaṃ puggalaṃ sāni kammāni tappenti. "
488368,111,37,2,49,1,336,39,"Iti so sīho imaṃ gāthaṃ vatvā‘‘ mama bhātikā anupāyakusalatāya‘ siṅgālaṃ māressāmā’ ti ativegena pakkhanditvā sayaṃ matā, ahaṃ pana evarūpaṃ akatvā siṅgālassa phalikaguhāyaṃ nipannasseva hadayaṃ phālessāmī’’ ti siṅgālassa ārohanaorohanamaggaṃ sallakkhetvā tadabhimukho hutvā tikkhattuṃ sīhanādaṃ nadi, pathaviyā saddhiṃ ākāsaṃ ekaninnādaṃ ahosi. "
488369,111,37,50,61,1,99,10,"Siṅgālassa phalikaguhāyaṃ nipannasseva sītatasitassa hadayaṃ phali, so tattheva jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇi. "
488370,111,38,2,21,1,105,14,Satthā ‘‘ evaṃ so siṅgālo sīhanādaṃ sutvā jīvitakkhayaṃ patto’’ ti vatvā abhisambuddho hutvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
488371,111,39,2,4,1,0,0,4.
488372,111,40,2,10,1,38,6,"‘ ‘ Sīho ca sīhanādena, daddaraṃ abhinādayi; "
488373,111,41,2,9,1,45,6,"Sutvā sīhassa nigghosaṃ, siṅgālo daddare vasaṃ; "
488374,111,42,2,10,1,43,5,"Bhīto santāsamāpādi, hadayañcassa apphalī’’ ti. "
488375,111,43,2,16,1,85,9,"Tattha {sīho}ti cattāro sīhā– tiṇasīho, paṇḍusīho, kāḷasīho, surattahatthapādo kesarasīhoti. "
488376,111,43,17,21,1,30,4,Tesu kesarasīho idha adhippeto. 
488377,111,43,22,34,1,122,11,Daddaraṃ {abhinādayī}ti tena asanipātasaddasadisena bheravatarena sīhanādena taṃ rajatapabbataṃ abhinādayi ekaninnādaṃ akāsi. 
488378,111,43,35,41,1,53,6,Daddare vasan ti phalikamissake rajatapabbate vasanto. 
488379,111,43,42,49,1,59,6,Bhīto {santāsamāpādī}ti maraṇabhayena bhīto cittutrāsaṃ āpādi. 
488380,111,43,50,58,1,57,7,Hadayañcassa {apphalī}ti tena cassa bhayena hadayaṃ phalīti. 
488381,111,44,2,24,1,181,20,Evaṃ sīho siṅgālaṃ jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā bhātaro ekasmiṃ ṭhāne paṭicchādetvā tesaṃ matabhāvaṃ bhaginiyā ācikkhitvā taṃ samassāsetvā yāvajīvaṃ kañcanaguhāyaṃ vasitvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
488382,111,45,2,15,1,122,12,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne upāsako sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi."
488383,111,45,16,38,1,141,15,"‘‘ Tadā siṅgālo nhāpitaputto ahosi, sīhapotikā licchavikumārikā, cha kaniṭṭhabhātaro aññataratherā ahesuṃ, jeṭṭhabhātikasīho pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
488384,111,46,2,4,1,27,2,Siṅgālajātakavaṇṇanā dutiyā.
488385,111,48,2,7,1,19,2,[ 153]3. Sūkarajātakavaṇṇanā 
488386,111,49,2,15,1,96,11,"Catuppado ahaṃ, {sammā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto aññataraṃ mahallakattheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. "
488387,111,49,16,37,1,217,21,Ekasmiñhi divase rattiṃ dhammassavane vattamāne satthari gandhakuṭidvāre ramaṇīye sopānaphalake ṭhatvā bhikkhusaṅghassa sugatovādaṃ datvā gandhakuṭiṃ paviṭṭhe dhammasenāpati satthāraṃ vanditvā attano pariveṇaṃ agamāsi. 
488388,111,49,38,58,1,193,18,"Mahāmoggallānopi pariveṇameva gantvā muhuttaṃ vissamitvā therassa santikaṃ āgantvā pañhaṃ pucchi, pucchitapucchitaṃ dhammasenāpati gaganatale puṇṇacandaṃ uṭṭhāpento viya vissajjetvā pākaṭamakāsi. "
488389,111,49,59,64,1,43,5,Catassopi parisā dhammaṃ suṇamānā nisīdiṃsu. 
488390,111,49,65,68,1,32,3,Tattheko mahallakatthero cintesi–
488391,111,49,69,134,1,370,51,"‘‘ sacāhaṃ imissā parisāya majjhe sāriputtaṃ āluḷento pañhaṃ pucchissāmi, ayaṃ me parisā‘ bahussuto ayan’ ti ñatvā sakkārasammānaṃ karissatī’’ ti parisantarā uṭṭhāya theraṃ upasaṅkamitvā ekamantaṃ ṭhatvā‘‘ āvuso sāriputta, mayampi taṃ ekaṃ pañhaṃ pucchāma, amhākampi okāsaṃ karohi, dehi me vinicchayaṃ āvedhikāya vā nivedhikāya vā niggahe vā paggahe vā visese vā paṭivisese vā’’ ti āha. "
488392,111,49,135,167,1,206,26,"Thero taṃ oloketvā‘‘ ayaṃ mahallako icchācāre ṭhito tuccho na kiñci jānātī’’ ti tena saddhiṃ akathetvāva lajjamāno bījaniṃ ṭhapetvā āsanā otaritvā pariveṇaṃ pāvisi, moggallānattheropi attano pariveṇameva agamāsi. "
488393,111,50,2,18,1,100,11,"Manussā uṭṭhāya‘‘ gaṇhathetaṃ tucchamahallakaṃ, madhuradhammassavanaṃ no sotuṃ na adāsī’’ ti anubandhiṃsu. "
488394,111,50,19,27,1,84,8,So palāyanto vihārapaccante bhinnapadarāya vaccakuṭiyā patitvā gūthamakkhito aṭṭhāsi. 
488395,111,50,28,36,1,62,8,Manussā taṃ disvā vippaṭisārino hutvā satthu santikaṃ agamaṃsu. 
488396,111,50,37,55,1,82,12,"Satthā te disvā‘‘ kiṃ upāsakā avelāya āgatatthā’’ ti pucchi, manussā tamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. "
488397,111,50,56,94,1,260,33,"Satthā‘‘ na kho upāsakā idānevesa mahallako uppilāvito hutvā attano balaṃ ajānitvā mahābalehi saddhiṃ payojetvā gūthamakkhito jāto, pubbepesa uppilāvito hutvā attano balaṃ ajānitvā mahābalehi saddhiṃ payojetvā gūthamakkhito ahosī’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
488398,111,51,2,14,1,110,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto sīho hutvā himavantapadese pabbataguhāya vāsaṃ kappesi. 
488399,111,51,15,24,1,61,9,Tassā avidūre ekaṃ saraṃ nissāya bahū sūkarā nivāsaṃ kappesuṃ. 
488400,111,51,25,32,1,56,7,Tameva saraṃ nissāya tāpasāpi paṇṇasālāsu vāsaṃ kappesuṃ. 
488401,111,51,33,47,1,125,14,Athekadivasaṃ sīho mahiṃsavāraṇādīsu aññataraṃ vadhitvā yāvadatthaṃ maṃsaṃ khāditvā taṃ saraṃ otaritvā pānīyaṃ pivitvā uttari. 
488402,111,51,48,57,1,62,9,Tasmiṃ khaṇe eko thūlasūkaro taṃ saraṃ nissāya gocaraṃ gaṇhāti. 
488403,111,51,58,87,1,156,23,"Sīho taṃ disvā‘‘ aññaṃ ekadivasaṃ imaṃ khādissāmi, maṃ kho pana disvā puna na āgaccheyyā’’ ti tassa anāgamanabhayena sarato uttaritvā ekena passena gantuṃ ārabhi. "
488404,111,51,88,119,1,194,26,"Sūkaro oloketvā‘‘ esa maṃ disvā mama bhayena upagantuṃ asakkonto bhayena palāyati, ajja mayā iminā sīhena saddhiṃ payojetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti sīsaṃ ukkhipitvā taṃ yuddhatthāya avhayanto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
488405,111,52,2,4,1,0,0,5.
488406,111,53,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Catuppado ahaṃ samma, tvampi samma catuppado; "
488407,111,54,2,13,1,45,8,"Ehi samma nivattassu, kiṃ nu bhīto palāyasī’’ ti. "
488408,111,55,2,32,1,149,23,"Sīho tassa kathaṃ sutvā‘‘ samma sūkara, ajja amhākaṃ tayā saddhiṃ saṅgāmo natthi, ito pana sattame divase imasmiṃyeva ṭhāne saṅgāmo hotū’’ ti vatvā pakkāmi. "
488409,111,55,33,47,1,83,10,Sūkaro‘‘ sīhena saddhiṃ saṅgāmessāmī’’ ti haṭṭhapahaṭṭho taṃ pavattiṃ ñātakānaṃ ārocesi. 
488410,111,55,48,83,1,208,28,"Te tassa kathaṃ sutvā bhītatasitā‘‘ idāni tvaṃ sabbepi amhe nāsessasi, attano balaṃ ajānitvā sīhena saddhiṃ saṅgāmaṃ kattukāmoti, sīho āgantvā sabbepi amhe jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpessati, sāhasikakammaṃ mā karī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
488411,111,55,84,95,1,43,7,Sopi bhītatasito‘‘ idāni kiṃ karomī’’ ti pucchi. 
488412,111,55,96,139,1,310,37,"Sūkarā‘‘ samma, tvaṃ etesaṃ tāpasānaṃ uccārabhūmiṃ gantvā pūtigūthe satta divasāni sarīraṃ parivaṭṭetvā sukkhāpetvā sattame divase sarīraṃ ussāvabindūhi temetvā sīhassa āgamanato purimataraṃ gantvā vātayogaṃ ñatvā uparivāte tiṭṭha, sucijātiko sīho tava sarīragandhaṃ ghāyitvā tuyhaṃ jayaṃ datvā gamissatī’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
488413,111,55,140,147,1,44,7,So tathā katvā sattame divase tattha aṭṭhāsi. 
488414,111,55,148,197,1,278,38,"Sīho tassa sarīragandhaṃ ghāyitvā gūthamakkhitabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ samma sūkara, sundaro te leso cintito, sace tvaṃ gūthamakkhito nābhavissa, idheva taṃ jīvitakkhayaṃ apāpessaṃ, idāni pana te sarīraṃ neva mukhena ḍaṃsituṃ, na pādena paharituṃ sakkā, jayaṃ te dammī’’ ti vatvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
488415,111,56,2,4,1,0,0,6.
488416,111,57,2,10,1,38,6,"‘ ‘ Asuci pūtilomosi, duggandho vāsi sūkara; "
488417,111,58,2,12,1,43,7,"Sace yujjitukāmosi, jayaṃ samma dadāmi te’’ ti. "
488418,111,59,2,8,1,48,4,Tattha {pūtilomo}ti mīḷhamakkhitattā duggandhalomo. 
488419,111,59,9,15,1,59,5,Duggandho {vāsī}ti aniṭṭhajegucchapaṭikūlagandho hutvā vāyasi. 
488420,111,59,16,48,1,157,23,"Jayaṃ, samma, dadāmi {te}ti‘‘ tuyhaṃ jayaṃ demi, ahaṃ parājito, gaccha tvan’’ ti vatvā sīho tatova nivattitvā gocaraṃ gahetvā sare pānīyaṃ pivitvā pabbataguhameva gato. "
488421,111,59,49,61,1,42,7,Sūkaropi‘‘ sīho me jito’’ ti ñātakānaṃ ārocesi . 
488422,111,59,62,80,1,114,14,Te bhītatasitā‘‘ puna ekadivasaṃ āgacchanto sīho sabbeva amhe jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpessatī’’ ti palāyitvā aññattha agamaṃsu. 
488423,111,60,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
488424,111,60,9,23,1,55,9,"‘‘ tadā sūkaro mahallako ahosi, sīho pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
488425,111,61,2,4,1,26,2,Sūkarajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
488426,111,63,2,7,1,18,2,[ 154]4. Uragajātakavaṇṇanā 
488427,111,64,2,13,1,90,10,Idhūragānaṃ pavaro {paviṭṭho}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto seṇibhaṇḍanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488428,111,64,14,30,1,130,15,"Kosalarañño kira sevakā seṇipamukhā dve mahāmattā aññamaññaṃ diṭṭhaṭṭhāne kalahaṃ karonti, tesaṃ veribhāvo sakalanagare pākaṭo jāto. "
488429,111,64,31,40,1,49,8,"Te neva rājā, na ñātimittā samagge kātuṃ sakkhiṃsu. "
488430,111,64,41,60,1,194,19,Athekadivasaṃ satthā paccūsasamaye bodhaneyyabandhave olokento tesaṃ ubhinnampi sotāpattimaggassa upanissayaṃ disvā punadivase ekakova sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya pavisitvā tesu ekassa gehadvāre aṭṭhāsi. 
488431,111,64,61,71,1,92,10,So nikkhamitvā pattaṃ gahetvā satthāraṃ antonivesanaṃ pavesetvā āsanaṃ paññapetvā nisīdāpesi. 
488432,111,64,72,87,1,138,14,"Satthā nisīditvā tassa mettābhāvanāya ānisaṃsaṃ kathetvā kallacittataṃ ñatvā saccāni pakāsesi, so saccapariyosāne sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. "
488433,111,65,2,14,1,94,11,Satthā tassa sotāpannabhāvaṃ ñatvā tameva pattaṃ gāhāpetvā uṭṭhāya itarassa gehadvāraṃ agamāsi. 
488434,111,65,15,30,1,83,10,"Sopi nikkhamitvā satthāraṃ vanditvā‘‘ pavisatha, bhante’’ ti gharaṃ pavesetvā nisīdāpesi. "
488435,111,65,31,37,1,50,6,Itaropi pattaṃ gahetvā satthārā saddhiṃyeva pāvisi. 
488436,111,65,38,52,1,126,13,"Satthā tassa ekādasa mettānisaṃse vaṇṇetvā kallacittataṃ ñatvā saccāni pakāsesi, saccapariyosāne sopi sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi. "
488437,111,65,53,67,1,107,13,Iti te ubhopi sotāpannā hutvā aññamaññaṃ accayaṃ dassetvā khamāpetvā samaggā sammodamānā ekajjhāsayā ahesuṃ. 
488438,111,65,68,75,1,55,7,Taṃ divasaññeva ca bhagavato sammukhāva ekato bhuñjiṃsu. 
488439,111,65,76,81,1,47,5,Satthā bhattakiccaṃ niṭṭhāpetvā vihāraṃ agamāsi. 
488440,111,65,82,92,1,99,10,Te bahūni mālāgandhavilepanāni ceva sappimadhuphāṇitādīni ca ādāya satthārā saddhiṃyeva nikkhamiṃsu. 
488441,111,65,93,102,1,73,8,Satthā bhikkhusaṅghena vatte dassite sugatovādaṃ datvā gandhakuṭiṃ pāvisi. 
488442,111,66,2,38,1,232,28,"Bhikkhū sāyanhasamaye dhammasabhāyaṃ satthu guṇakathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ‘‘ āvuso, satthā adantadamako, ye nāma dve mahāmatte ciraṃ vāyamamānopi neva rājā samagge kātuṃ sakkhi, na ñātimittādayo sakkhiṃsu, te ekadivaseneva tathāgatena damitā’’ ti. "
488443,111,66,39,86,1,202,30,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imāya nāmā’’ ti vutte‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idānevāhaṃ ime dve jane samagge akāsiṃ, pubbepete mayā samaggā katāyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
488444,111,67,2,12,1,90,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bārāṇasiyaṃ ussave ghosite mahāsamajjaṃ ahosi. 
488445,111,67,13,20,1,73,7,Bahū manussā ceva devanāgasupaṇṇādayo ca samajjadassanatthaṃ sannipatiṃsu. 
488446,111,67,21,32,1,74,11,Tatrekasmiṃ ṭhāne eko nāgo ca supaṇṇo ca samajjaṃ passamānā ekato aṭṭhaṃsu. 
488447,111,67,33,40,1,59,7,Nāgo supaṇṇassa supaṇṇabhāvaṃ ajānanto aṃse hatthaṃ ṭhapesi. 
488448,111,67,41,56,1,72,11,Supaṇṇo‘‘ kena me aṃse hattho ṭhapito’’ ti nivattitvā olokento nāgaṃ sañjāni. 
488449,111,67,57,66,1,93,9,Nāgopi olokento supaṇṇaṃ sañjānitvā maraṇabhayatajjito nagarā nikkhamitvā nadīpiṭṭhena palāyi. 
488450,111,67,67,76,1,36,5,Supaṇṇopi‘‘ taṃ gahessāmī’’ ti anubandhi. 
488451,111,67,77,97,1,179,20,Tasmiṃ samaye bodhisatto tāpaso hutvā tassā nadiyā tīre paṇṇasālāya vasamāno divā darathapaṭippassambhanatthaṃ udakasāṭikaṃ nivāsetvā vakkalaṃ bahi ṭhapetvā nadiṃ otaritvā nhāyati. 
488452,111,67,98,115,1,121,13,Nāgo‘‘ imaṃ pabbajitaṃ nissāya jīvitaṃ labhissāmī’’ ti pakativaṇṇaṃ vijahitvā maṇikkhandhavaṇṇaṃ māpetvā vakkalantaraṃ pāvisi. 
488453,111,67,116,148,1,210,25,"Supaṇṇo anubandhamāno taṃ tattha paviṭṭhaṃ disvā vakkale garubhāvena aggahetvā bodhisattaṃ āmantetvā‘‘ bhante, ahaṃ chāto, tumhākaṃ vakkalaṃ gaṇhatha, imaṃ nāgaṃ khādissāmī’’ ti imamatthaṃ pakāsetuṃ paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
488454,111,68,2,4,1,0,0,7.
488455,111,69,2,14,1,59,7,"‘ ‘ Idhūragānaṃ pavaro paviṭṭho, selassa vaṇṇena pamokkhamicchaṃ; "
488456,111,70,2,13,1,63,8,"Brahmañca vaṇṇaṃ apacāyamāno, bubhukkhito no vitarāmi bhottun’’ ti. "
488457,111,71,2,13,1,86,10,Tattha idhūragānaṃ pavaro {paviṭṭho}ti imasmiṃ vakkale uragānaṃ pavaro nāgarājā paviṭṭho. 
488458,111,71,14,23,1,65,7,"Selassa {vaṇṇenā}ti maṇivaṇṇena, maṇikkhandho hutvā paviṭṭhoti attho. "
488459,111,71,24,30,1,49,6,Pamokkhamicchan ti mama santikā mokkhaṃ icchamāno. 
488460,111,71,31,43,1,97,11,Brahmañca vaṇṇaṃ {apacāyamāno}ti ahaṃ pana tumhākaṃ brahmavaṇṇaṃ seṭṭhavaṇṇaṃ pūjento garuṃ karonto. 
488461,111,71,44,58,1,108,14,Bubhukkhito no vitarāmi bhottun ti etaṃ nāgaṃ vakkalantaraṃ paviṭṭhaṃ chātopi samāno bhakkhituṃ na sakkomīti. 
488462,111,72,2,10,1,72,8,Bodhisatto udake ṭhitoyeva supaṇṇarājassa thutiṃ katvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
488463,111,73,2,4,1,0,0,8.
488464,111,74,2,14,1,61,10,"‘ ‘ So brahmagutto cirameva jīva, dibyā ca te pātubhavantu bhakkhā; "
488465,111,75,2,13,1,62,8,"Yo brahmavaṇṇaṃ apacāyamāno, bubhukkhito no vitarāsi bhottun’’ ti. "
488466,111,76,2,11,1,65,8,Tattha so {brahmagutto}ti so tvaṃ brahmagopito brahmarakkhito hutvā. 
488467,111,76,12,30,1,131,16,"Dibyā ca te pātubhavantu {bhakkhā}ti devatānaṃ paribhogārahā bhakkhā ca tava pātubhavantu, mā pāṇātipātaṃ katvā nāgamaṃsakhādako ahosi. "
488468,111,77,2,23,1,167,21,Iti bodhisatto udake ṭhitova anumodanaṃ katvā uttaritvā vakkalaṃ nivāsetvā te ubhopi gahetvā assamapadaṃ gantvā mettābhāvanāya vaṇṇaṃ kathetvā dvepi jane samagge akāsi. 
488469,111,77,24,31,1,51,7,Te tato paṭṭhāya samaggā sammodamānā sukhaṃ vasiṃsu. 
488470,111,78,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
488471,111,78,9,28,1,78,14,"‘‘ tadā nāgo ca supaṇṇo ca ime dve mahāmattā ahesuṃ, tāpaso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
488472,111,79,2,4,1,27,2,Uragajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
488473,111,81,2,7,1,19,2,[ 155]5. Bhaggajātakavaṇṇanā 
488474,111,82,2,21,1,136,15,Jīva vassasataṃ {bhaggā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavanasamīpe pasenadikosalena raññā kārite rājakārāme viharanto attano khipitakaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488475,111,82,22,31,1,83,9,Ekasmiñhi divase satthā rājakārāme catuparisamajjhe nisīditvā dhammaṃ desento khipi. 
488476,111,82,32,55,1,117,15,"Bhikkhū‘‘ jīvatu, bhante bhagavā, jīvatu, sugato’’ ti uccāsaddaṃ mahāsaddaṃ akaṃsu, tena saddena dhammakathāya antarāyo ahosi. "
488477,111,82,56,61,1,33,5,Atha kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
488478,111,82,62,84,1,78,14,"‘‘ api nu kho, bhikkhave, khipite‘ jīvā’ ti vutto tappaccayā jīveyya vā mareyya vā’’ ti?"
488479,111,82,85,93,1,18,4,‘‘ No hetaṃ bhante’’ ti.
488480,111,82,94,119,1,69,11,"‘‘ Na, bhikkhave, khipite‘ jīvā’ ti vattabbo, yo vadeyya āpatti dukkaṭassā’’ ti( cūḷava.288). "
488481,111,82,120,140,1,107,14,"Tena kho pana samayena manussā bhikkhūnaṃ khipite‘‘ jīvatha, bhante’’ ti vadanti, bhikkhū kukkuccāyantā nālapanti. "
488482,111,82,141,143,1,18,2,Manussā ujjhāyanti–
488483,111,82,144,161,1,77,10,"‘‘ kathañhi nāma samaṇā sakyaputtiyā‘ jīvatha, bhante’ ti vuccamānā nālapissantī’’ ti. "
488484,111,82,162,165,1,29,3,Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ. 
488485,111,82,166,194,1,105,14,"Gihī, bhikkhave, maṅgalikā, anujānāmi, bhikkhave, gihīnaṃ‘‘ jīvatha, bhante’’ ti vuccamānena‘‘ ciraṃ jīvā’’ ti vattunti. "
488486,111,82,195,198,1,29,3,Bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ pucchiṃsu–
488487,111,82,199,210,1,42,6,"‘‘ bhante, jīvapaṭijīvaṃ nāma kadā uppannan’’ ti? "
488488,111,82,211,226,1,77,10,"Satthā‘‘ bhikkhave, jīvapaṭijīvaṃ nāma porāṇakāle uppannan’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
488489,111,83,2,12,1,96,10,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe ekasmiṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbatti. 
488490,111,83,13,47,1,259,29,"Tassa pitā vohāraṃ katvā jīvikaṃ kappeti, so soḷasavassuddesikaṃ bodhisattaṃ maṇikabhaṇḍaṃ ukkhipāpetvā gāmanigamādīsu caranto bārāṇasiṃ patvā dovārikassa ghare bhattaṃ pacāpetvā bhuñjitvā nivāsaṭṭhānaṃ alabhanto‘‘ avelāya āgatā āgantukā kattha vasantī’’ ti pucchi. "
488491,111,83,48,61,1,70,10,"Atha naṃ manussā‘‘ bahinagare ekā sālā atthi, sā pana amanussapariggahitā. "
488492,111,83,62,71,1,38,6,"Sace icchatha, tattha vasathā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
488493,111,83,72,99,1,126,18,"Bodhisatto‘‘ etha, tāta, gacchāma, mā yakkhassa bhāyittha, ahaṃ taṃ dametvā tumhākaṃ pādesu pātessāmī’’ ti pitaraṃ gahetvā tattha gato. "
488494,111,83,100,110,1,62,9,"Athassa pitā phalake nipajji, sayaṃ pitu pāde sambāhanto nisīdi. "
488495,111,83,111,157,1,237,33,"Tattha adhivattho yakkho dvādasa vassāni vessavaṇaṃ upaṭṭhahitvā taṃ sālaṃ labhanto‘‘ imaṃ sālaṃ paviṭṭhamanussesu yo khipite‘ jīvā’ ti vadati, yo ca‘ jīvā’ ti vutte‘ paṭijīvā’ ti vadati, te jīvapaṭijīvabhāṇino ṭhapetvā avasese khādeyyāsī’’ ti labhi. "
488496,111,83,158,161,1,28,3,So piṭṭhivaṃsathūṇāya vasati. 
488497,111,83,162,181,1,119,14,"So‘‘ bodhisattassa pitaraṃ khipāpessāmī’’ ti attano ānubhāvena sukhumacuṇṇaṃ vissajjesi, cuṇṇo āgantvā tassa nāsapuṭe pāvisi. "
488498,111,83,182,197,1,54,9,"So phalake nipannakova khipi, bodhisatto na‘‘ jīvā’’ ti āha. "
488499,111,83,198,203,1,35,5,Yakkho taṃ khādituṃ thūṇāya otarati. 
488500,111,83,204,233,1,162,22,"Bodhisatto taṃ otarantaṃ disvā‘‘ iminā me pitā khipāpito bhavissati, ayaṃ so khipite‘ jīvā’ ti avadantaṃ khādakayakkho bhavissatī’’ ti pitaraṃ ārabbha paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
488501,111,84,2,4,1,0,0,9.
488502,111,85,2,11,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Jīva vassasataṃ bhagga, aparāni ca vīsatiṃ; "
488503,111,86,2,13,1,47,8,"Mā maṃ pisācā khādantu, jīva tvaṃ saradosatan’’ ti. "
488504,111,87,2,7,1,36,4,Tattha {bhaggā}ti pitaraṃ nāmenālapati. 
488505,111,87,8,17,1,52,9,Aparāni ca vīsatin ti aparāni ca vīsati vassāni jīva. 
488506,111,87,18,27,1,47,8,Mā maṃ pisācā {khādantū}ti maṃ pisācā mā khādantu. 
488507,111,87,28,37,1,63,9,Jīva tvaṃ saradosatan ti tvaṃ pana vīsuttaraṃ vassasataṃ jīvāti. 
488508,111,87,38,50,1,99,11,"Saradosatañhi gaṇiyamānaṃ vassasatameva hoti, taṃ purimehi vīsāya saddhiṃ vīsuttaraṃ idha adhippetaṃ. "
488509,111,88,2,29,1,139,20,"Yakkho bodhisattassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ imaṃ tāva māṇavaṃ‘ jīvā’ ti vuttattā khādituṃ na sakkā, pitaraṃ panassa khādissāmī’’ ti pitu santikaṃ agamāsi. "
488510,111,88,30,35,1,32,5,So taṃ āgacchantaṃ disvā cintesi–
488511,111,88,36,53,1,80,10,"‘‘ ayaṃ so‘ paṭijīvā’ ti abhaṇantānaṃ khādakayakkho bhavissati, paṭijīvaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
488512,111,88,54,59,1,35,5,So puttaṃ ārabbha dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
488513,111,89,2,4,1,0,0,10.
488514,111,90,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Tvampi vassasataṃ jīvaṃ, aparāni ca vīsatiṃ; "
488515,111,91,2,12,1,46,7,"Visaṃ pisācā khādantu, jīva tvaṃ saradosatan’’ ti. "
488516,111,92,2,11,1,60,7,Tattha visaṃ pisācā {khādantū}ti pisācā halāhalavisaṃ khādantu. 
488517,111,93,2,17,1,69,11,Yakkho tassa vacanaṃ sutvā‘‘ ubhopi me na sakkā khāditun’’ ti paṭinivatti. 
488518,111,93,18,22,1,26,4,Atha naṃ bodhisatto pucchi–
488519,111,93,23,37,1,59,9,"‘‘ bho yakkha, kasmā tvaṃ imaṃ sālaṃ paviṭṭhamanusse khādasī’’ ti?"
488520,111,93,38,48,1,52,6,‘‘ Dvādasa vassāni vessavaṇaṃ upaṭṭhahitvā laddhattā’’ ti.
488521,111,93,49,59,1,36,6,‘‘ Kiṃ pana sabbeva khādituṃ labhasī’’ ti?
488522,111,93,60,69,1,47,5,‘‘ Jīvapaṭijīvabhāṇino ṭhapetvā avasese khādāmī’’ ti.
488523,111,93,70,113,1,290,35,"‘‘ Yakkha, tvaṃ pubbepi akusalaṃ katvā kakkhaḷo pharuso paravihiṃsako hutvā nibbatto, idānipi tādisaṃ kammaṃ katvā tamo tamaparāyaṇo bhavissati, tasmā ito paṭṭhāya pāṇātipātādīhi viramassū’’ ti taṃ yakkhaṃ dametvā nirayabhayena tajjetvā pañcasu sīlesu patiṭṭhāpetvā yakkhaṃ pesanakārakaṃ viya akāsi. "
488524,111,94,2,14,1,96,11,Punadivase sañcarantā manussā yakkhaṃ disvā bodhisattena cassa damitabhāvaṃ ñatvā rañño ārocesuṃ–
488525,111,94,15,31,1,69,11,"‘‘ deva, eko māṇavo taṃ yakkhaṃ dametvā pesanakārakaṃ viya katvā ṭhito’’ ti. "
488526,111,94,32,43,1,84,10,"Rājā bodhisattaṃ pakkosāpetvā senāpatiṭṭhāne ṭhapesi, pitu cassa mahantaṃ yasaṃ adāsi. "
488527,111,94,44,56,1,101,12,So yakkhaṃ balipaṭiggāhakaṃ katvā bodhisattassa ovāde ṭhatvā dānādīni puññāni katvā saggapuraṃ pūresi. 
488528,111,95,2,19,1,103,13,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā‘‘ jīvapaṭijīvaṃ nāma tasmiṃ kāle uppannan’’ ti vatvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
488529,111,95,20,40,1,82,13,"‘‘ tadā yakkho aṅgulimālo ahosi, rājā ānando, pitā kassapo, putto pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
488530,111,96,2,4,1,27,2,Bhaggajātakavaṇṇanā pañcamā.
488531,111,98,2,7,1,23,2,[ 156]6. Alīnacittajātakavaṇṇanā 
488532,111,99,2,14,1,98,11,Alīnacittaṃ {nissāyā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ossaṭṭhavīriyaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488533,111,99,15,29,1,48,4,Vatthu ekādasanipāte saṃvarajātake( jā.1.11.97 ādayo) āvibhavissati. 
488534,111,99,30,58,1,95,16,"So pana bhikkhu satthārā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, bhikkhu, vīriyaṃ ossajī’’ ti vutte‘‘ saccaṃ, bhagavā’’ ti āha. "
488535,111,99,59,93,1,224,27,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ nanu tvaṃ, bhikkhu, pubbe vīriyaṃ avissajjetvā maṃsapesisadisassa daharakumārassa dvādasayojanike bārāṇasinagare rajjaṃ gahetvā adāsi, idāni kasmā evarūpe sāsane pabbajitvā vīriyaṃ ossajasī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
488536,111,100,2,16,1,116,13,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bārāṇasito avidūre vaḍḍhakīgāmo ahosi, tattha pañcasatā vaḍḍhakī vasanti. "
488537,111,100,17,56,1,333,37,"Te nāvāya uparisotaṃ gantvā araññe gehasambhāradārūni koṭṭetvā tattheva ekabhūmikadvibhūmikādibhede gehasambhāre sajjetvā thambhato paṭṭhāya sabbadārūsu saññaṃ katvā nadītīraṃ netvā nāvaṃ āropetvā anusotena nagaraṃ āgantvā ye yādisāni gehāni ākaṅkhanti, tesaṃ tādisāni katvā kahāpaṇe gahetvā puna tattheva gantvā gehasambhāre āharanti. "
488538,111,100,57,72,1,127,15,Evaṃ tesaṃ jīvikaṃ kappentānaṃ ekasmiṃ kāle khandhāvāraṃ bandhitvā dārūni koṭṭentānaṃ avidūre eko hatthī khadirakhāṇukaṃ akkami. 
488539,111,100,73,86,1,82,11,"Tassa so khāṇuko pādaṃ vijjhi, balavavedanā vattanti, pādo uddhumāyitvā pubbaṃ gaṇhi. "
488540,111,100,87,142,1,419,49,"So vedanāppatto tesaṃ dārukoṭṭanasaddaṃ sutvā‘‘ ime vaḍḍhakī nissāya mayhaṃ sotthi bhavissatī’’ ti maññamāno tīhi pādehi tesaṃ santikaṃ gantvā avidūre nipajji, vaḍḍhakī taṃ uddhumātapādaṃ disvā upasaṅkamitvā pāde khāṇukaṃ disvā tikhiṇavāsiyā khāṇukassa samantato odhiṃ datvā rajjuyā bandhitvā ākaḍḍhantā khāṇuṃ nīharitvā pubbaṃ mocetvā uṇhodakena dhovitvā tadanurūpehi bhesajjehi makkhetvā nacirasseva vaṇaṃ phāsukaṃ kariṃsu. "
488541,111,101,2,6,1,26,4,Hatthī arogo hutvā cintesi–
488542,111,101,7,25,1,84,13,"‘‘ mayā ime vaḍḍhakī nissāya jīvitaṃ laddhaṃ, idāni tesaṃ mayā upakāraṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. "
488543,111,101,26,46,1,147,16,"So tato paṭṭhāya vaḍḍhakīhi saddhiṃ rukkhe nīharati, tacchentānaṃ parivattetvā deti, vāsiādīni upasaṃharati, soṇḍāya veṭhetvā kāḷasuttakoṭiyaṃ gaṇhāti. "
488544,111,101,47,55,1,71,8,Vaḍḍhakīpissa bhojanavelāya ekekaṃ piṇḍaṃ dentā pañca piṇḍasatāni denti. 
488545,111,101,56,66,1,79,9,"Tassa pana hatthissa putto sabbaseto hatthājānīyapotako atthi, tenassa etadahosi–"
488546,111,101,67,72,1,22,3,‘‘ ahaṃ etarahi mahallako. 
488547,111,101,73,85,1,77,10,Idāni mayā imesaṃ vaḍḍhakīnaṃ kammakaraṇattāya puttaṃ datvā gantuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. 
488548,111,101,86,146,1,332,46,"So vaḍḍhakīnaṃ anācikkhitvāva araññaṃ pavisitvā puttaṃ ānetvā‘‘ ayaṃ hatthipotako mama putto, tumhehi mayhaṃ jīvitaṃ dinnaṃ, ahaṃ vo vejjavetanatthāya imaṃ dammi, ayaṃ tumhākaṃ ito paṭṭhāya kammāni karissatī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ ito paṭṭhāya, puttaka, yaṃ mayā kattabbaṃ kammaṃ, taṃ tvaṃ karohī’’ ti puttaṃ ovaditvā vaḍḍhakīnaṃ datvā sayaṃ araññaṃ pāvisi. "
488549,111,102,2,11,1,87,9,Tato paṭṭhāya hatthipotako vaḍḍhakīnaṃ vacanakaro ovādakkhamo hutvā sabbakiccāni karoti. 
488550,111,102,12,37,1,168,22,"Tepi taṃ pañcahi piṇḍasatehi posenti, so kammaṃ katvā nadiṃ otaritvā nhatvā kīḷitvā āgacchati, vaḍḍhakīdārakāpi taṃ soṇḍādīsu gahetvā udakepi thalepi tena saddhiṃ kīḷanti. "
488551,111,102,38,58,1,142,19,"Ājānīyā pana hatthinopi assāpi purisāpi udake uccāraṃ vā passāvaṃ vā na karonti, tasmā sopi udake uccārapassāvaṃ akatvā bahinadītīreyeva karoti. "
488552,111,102,59,77,1,152,17,"Athekasmiṃ divase uparinadiyā devo vassi, atha sukkhaṃ hatthilaṇḍaṃ udakena nadiṃ otaritvā gacchantaṃ bārāṇasīnagaratitthe ekasmiṃ gumbe laggetvā aṭṭhāsi. "
488553,111,102,78,91,1,71,9,Atha rañño hatthigopakā‘‘ hatthī nhāpessāmā’’ ti pañca hatthisatāni nayiṃsu. 
488554,111,102,92,101,1,70,9,Ājānīyalaṇḍassa gandhaṃ ghāyitvā ekopi hatthī nadiṃ otarituṃ na ussahi. 
488555,111,102,102,111,1,87,8,"Sabbepi naṅguṭṭhaṃ ukkhipitvā palāyituṃ ārabhiṃsu, hatthigopakā hatthācariyānaṃ ārocesuṃ. "
488556,111,102,112,151,1,227,29,"Te‘‘ udake paripanthena bhavitabban’’ ti udakaṃ sodhāpetvā tasmiṃ gumbe taṃ ājānīyalaṇḍaṃ disvā‘‘ idamettha kāraṇan’’ ti ñatvā cāṭiṃ āharāpetvā udakassa pūretvā taṃ tattha madditvā hatthīnaṃ sarīre siñcāpesuṃ, sarīrāni sugandhāni ahesuṃ. "
488557,111,102,152,158,1,38,6,Tasmiṃ kāle te nadiṃ otaritvā nhāyiṃsu. 
488558,111,103,2,21,1,100,13,"Hatthācariyā rañño taṃ pavattiṃ ārocetvā‘‘ taṃ hatthājānīyaṃ pariyesitvā ānetuṃ vaṭṭati, devā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
488559,111,103,22,31,1,102,9,Rājā nāvāsaṅghāṭehi nadiṃ pakkhanditvā uddhaṃgāmīhi nāvāsaṅghāṭehi vaḍḍhakīnaṃ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ sampāpuṇi. 
488560,111,103,32,41,1,81,9,Hatthipotako nadiyaṃ kīḷanto bherisaddaṃ sutvā gantvā vaḍḍhakīnaṃ santike aṭṭhāsi. 
488561,111,103,42,67,1,122,18,"Vaḍḍhakī rañño paccuggamanaṃ katvā‘‘ deva, sace dārūhi attho, kiṃ kāraṇā āgatattha, kiṃ pesetvā āharāpetuṃ na vaṭṭatī’’ ti āhaṃsu."
488562,111,103,68,86,1,75,11,"‘‘ Nāhaṃ, bhaṇe, dārūnaṃ atthāya āgato, imassa pana hatthissa atthāya āgatomhī’’ ti."
488563,111,103,87,96,1,27,4,"‘‘ Gāhāpetvā gacchatha, devā’’ ti. "
488564,111,103,97,101,1,28,4,Hatthipotako gantuṃ na icchi.
488565,111,103,102,113,1,28,5,"‘‘ Kiṃ kārāpeti, bhaṇe, hatthī’’ ti?"
488566,111,103,114,124,1,41,5,"‘‘ Vaḍḍhakīnaṃ posāvanikaṃ āharāpeti, devā’’ ti."
488567,111,103,125,143,1,119,13,"‘‘ Sādhu, bhaṇe’’ ti rājā hatthissa catunnaṃ pādānaṃ soṇḍāya naṅguṭṭhassa ca santike satasahassasatasahassakahāpaṇe ṭhapāpesi. "
488568,111,103,144,167,1,222,23,Hatthī ettakenāpi agantvā sabbavaḍḍhakīnaṃ dussayugesu vaḍḍhakībhariyānaṃ nivāsanasāṭakesu dinnesu saddhiṃkīḷitānaṃ dārakānañca dārakaparihāre kate nivattitvā vaḍḍhakī ca itthiyo ca dārake ca oloketvā raññā saddhiṃ agamāsi. 
488569,111,104,2,33,1,272,29,Rājā taṃ ādāya nagaraṃ gantvā nagarañca hatthisālañca alaṅkārāpetvā hatthiṃ nagaraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ kāretvā hatthisālaṃ pavesetvā sabbālaṅkārehi alaṅkaritvā abhisekaṃ datvā opavayhaṃ katvā attano sahāyaṭṭhāne ṭhapetvā upaḍḍharajjaṃ hatthissa datvā attanā samānaparihāraṃ akāsi. 
488570,111,104,34,42,1,80,8,Hatthissa āgatakālato paṭṭhāya rañño sakalajambudīpe rajjaṃ hatthagatameva ahosi. 
488571,111,104,43,53,1,83,10,Evaṃ kāle gacchante bodhisatto tassa rañño aggamahesiyā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
488572,111,104,54,58,1,40,4,Tassā gabbhaparipākakāle rājā kālamakāsi. 
488573,111,104,59,76,1,135,15,"Hatthī pana sace rañño kālakatabhāvaṃ jāneyya, tatthevassa hadayaṃ phaleyya, tasmā hatthiṃ rañño kālakatabhāvaṃ ajānāpetvāva upaṭṭhahiṃsu. "
488574,111,104,77,95,1,123,14,Rañño pana kālakatabhāvaṃ sutvā‘‘ tucchaṃ kira rajjan’’ ti anantarasāmantakosalarājā mahatiyā senāya āgantvā nagaraṃ parivāresi. 
488575,111,104,96,102,1,60,6,Nagaravāsino dvārāni pidahitvā kosalarañño sāsanaṃ pahiṇiṃsu–
488576,111,104,103,120,1,110,13,‘‘ amhākaṃ rañño aggamahesī paripuṇṇagabbhā‘ ito kira sattame divase puttaṃ vijāyissatī’ ti aṅgavijjāpāṭhakā āhaṃsu. 
488577,111,104,121,141,1,99,15,"Sace sā puttaṃ vijāyissati, mayaṃ sattame divase yuddhaṃ dassāma, na rajjaṃ, ettakaṃ kālaṃ āgamethā’’ ti. "
488578,111,104,142,150,1,25,4,Rājā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchi. 
488579,111,105,2,7,1,33,5,Devī sattame divase puttaṃ vijāyi. 
488580,111,105,8,23,1,110,11,Tassa nāmaggahaṇadivase pana mahājanassa alīnacittaṃ paggaṇhanto jātoti‘‘ alīnacittakumāro’’ tvevassa nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
488581,111,105,24,31,1,70,7,Jātadivasatoyeva panassa paṭṭhāya nāgarā kosalaraññā saddhiṃ yujjhiṃsu. 
488582,111,105,32,40,1,75,8,Ninnāyakattā saṅgāmassa mahantampi balaṃ yujjhamānaṃ thokaṃ thokaṃ osakkati. 
488583,111,105,41,78,1,240,28,"Amaccā deviyā tamatthaṃ ārocetvā‘‘ mayaṃ evaṃ osakkamāne bale parājayabhāvassa bhāyāma, amhākaṃ pana rañño kālakatabhāvaṃ, puttassa jātabhāvaṃ, kosalarañño āgantvā yujjhānabhāvañca rañño sahāyako maṅgalahatthī na jānāti, jānāpema nan’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
488584,111,105,79,147,1,414,51,"Sā‘‘ sādhū’’ ti sampaṭicchitvā puttaṃ alaṅkaritvā dukūlacumbaṭake nipajjāpetvā pāsādā oruyha amaccagaṇaparivutā hatthisālaṃ gantvā bodhisattaṃ hatthissa pādamūle nipajjāpetvā‘‘ sāmi, sahāyo te kālakato, mayaṃ tuyhaṃ hadayaphālanabhayena nārocayimha, ayaṃ te sahāyassa putto, kosalarājā āgantvā nagara ṃ parivāretvā tava puttena saddhiṃ yujjhati, balaṃ osakkati, tava puttaṃ tvaññeva vā mārehi, rajjaṃ vāssa gaṇhitvā dehī’’ ti āha. "
488585,111,106,2,26,1,181,20,Tasmiṃ kāle hatthī bodhisattaṃ soṇḍāya parāmasitvā ukkhipitvā kumbhe ṭhapetvā roditvā bodhisattaṃ otāretvā deviyā hatthe nipajjāpetvā‘‘ kosalarājaṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti hatthisālato nikkhami. 
488586,111,106,27,37,1,98,10,Athassa amaccā vammaṃ paṭimuñcitvā alaṅkaritvā nagaradvāraṃ avāpuritvā taṃ parivāretvā nikkhamiṃsu. 
488587,111,106,38,78,1,282,33,"Hatthī nagarā nikkhamitvā koñcanādaṃ katvā mahājanaṃ santāsetvā palāpetvā balakoṭṭhakaṃ bhinditvā kosalarājānaṃ cūḷāya gahetvā ānetvā bodhisattassa pādamūle nipajjāpetvā māraṇatthāyassa uṭṭhite vāretvā‘‘ ito paṭṭhāya appamatto hohi,‘ kumāro daharo’ ti saññaṃ mā karī’’ ti ovaditvā uyyojesi. "
488588,111,106,79,93,1,118,13,"Tato paṭṭhāya sakalajambudīpe rajjaṃ bodhisattassa hatthagatameva jātaṃ, añño paṭisattu nāma uṭṭhahituṃ samattho nāhosi. "
488589,111,106,94,107,1,128,13,Bodhisatto sattavassikakāle abhisekaṃ katvā alīnacittarājā nāma hutvā dhammena rajjaṃ kāretvā jīvitapariyosāne saggapuraṃ pūresi. 
488590,111,107,2,10,1,67,8,Satthā imaṃ atītaṃ āharitvā abhisambuddho hutvā imaṃ gāthādvayamāha– 
488591,111,108,2,4,1,0,0,11.
488592,111,109,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Alīnacittaṃ nissāya, pahaṭṭhā mahatī camū; "
488593,111,110,2,7,1,41,4,"Kosalaṃ senāsantuṭṭhaṃ, jīvaggāhaṃ agāhayi. "
488594,111,111,2,4,1,0,0,12.
488595,111,112,2,9,1,42,5,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ nissayasampanno, bhikkhu āraddhavīriyo; "
