488597,111,114,2,9,1,42,4,"Pāpuṇe anupubbena, sabbasaṃyojanakkhayan’’ ti. "
488598,111,115,2,10,1,60,6,Tattha alīnacittaṃ {nissāyā}ti alīnacittaṃ rājakumāraṃ nissāya. 
488599,111,115,11,27,1,80,11,Pahaṭṭhā mahatī {camū}ti‘‘ paveṇīrajjaṃ no diṭṭhan’’ ti haṭṭhatuṭṭhā hutvā mahatī senā. 
488600,111,115,28,38,1,88,9,Kosalaṃ senāsantuṭṭhan ti kosalarājānaṃ sena rajjena asantuṭṭhaṃ pararajjalobhena āgataṃ. 
488601,111,115,39,50,1,81,10,Jīvaggāhaṃ {agāhayī}ti amāretvāva sā camū taṃ rājānaṃ hatthinā jīvaggāhaṃ gaṇhāpesi. 
488602,111,115,51,70,1,134,16,"Evaṃ {nissayasampanno}ti yathā sā camū, evaṃ aññopi kulaputto nissayasampanno kalyāṇamittaṃ buddhaṃ vā buddhasāvakaṃ vā nissayaṃ labhitvā. "
488603,111,115,71,74,1,34,2,{Bhikkhū}ti parisuddhādhivacanametaṃ. 
488604,111,115,75,81,1,69,5,{Āraddhavīriyo}ti paggahitavīriyo catudosāpagatena vīriyena samannāgato. 
488605,111,115,82,91,1,96,9,Bhāvayaṃ kusalaṃ dhamman ti kusalaṃ niravajjaṃ sattatiṃsabodhipakkhiyasaṅkhātaṃ dhammaṃ bhāvento. 
488606,111,115,92,103,1,93,10,Yogakkhemassa {pattiyā}ti catūhi yogehi khemassa nibbānassa pāpuṇanatthāya taṃ dhammaṃ bhāvento. 
488607,111,115,104,133,1,307,28,"Pāpuṇe anupubbena, sabbasaṃyojanakkhayan ti evaṃ vipassanato paṭṭhāya imaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ bhāvento so kalyāṇamittupanissayasampanno bhikkhu anupubbena vipassanāñāṇāni ca heṭṭhimamaggaphalāni ca pāpuṇanto pariyosāne dasannampi saṃyojanānaṃ khayante uppannattā sabbasaṃyojanakkhayasaṅkhātaṃ arahattaṃ pāpuṇāti. "
488608,111,115,134,151,1,159,15,"Yasmā vā nibbānaṃ āgamma sabbasaṃyojanāni khīyanti, tasmā tampi sabbasaṃyojanakkhayameva, evaṃ anupubbena nibbānasaṅkhātaṃ sabbasaṃyojanakkhayaṃ pāpuṇātīti attho. "
488609,111,116,2,19,1,165,16,"Iti bhagavā amatamahānibbānena dhammadesanāya kūṭaṃ gahetvā uttaripi saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne ossaṭṭhavīriyo bhikkhu arahatte patiṭṭhahi."
488610,111,116,20,51,1,197,22,"‘‘ Tadā mātā mahāmāyā, pitā suddhodanamahārājā ahosi, rajjaṃ gahetvā dinnahatthī ayaṃ ossaṭṭhavīriyo bhikkhu, hatthissa pitā sāriputto, sāmantakosalarājā moggallāno, alīnacittakumāro pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
488611,111,117,2,4,1,31,2,Alīnacittajātakavaṇṇanā chaṭṭhā.
488612,111,119,2,7,1,17,2,[ 157]7. Guṇajātakavaṇṇanā 
488613,111,120,2,14,1,104,11,Yena kāmaṃ {paṇāmetī}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ānandattherassa sāṭakasahassalābhaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488614,111,120,15,31,1,80,7,Therassa kosalarañño antepure dhammavācanavatthu heṭṭhā mahāsārajātake( jā.1.1.92) āgatameva. 
488615,111,120,32,44,1,96,11,Iti there rañño antepure dhammaṃ vācente rañño sahassagghanikānaṃ sāṭakānaṃ sahassaṃ āhariyittha. 
488616,111,120,45,52,1,56,7,Rājā tato pañca sāṭakasatāni pañcannaṃ devīsatānaṃ adāsi. 
488617,111,120,53,67,1,126,14,Tā sabbāpi te sāṭake ṭhapetvā punadivase ānandattherassa datvā sayaṃ purāṇasāṭakeyeva pārupitvā rañño pātarāsaṭṭhānaṃ agamaṃsu. 
488618,111,121,2,22,1,92,13,"Rājā ‘‘ mayā tumhākaṃ sahassagghanikā sāṭakā dāpitā, kasmā tumhe te apārupitvāva āgatā’’ ti pucchi."
488619,111,121,23,34,1,39,6,"‘‘ Deva, amhehi te ānandattherassa dinnā’’ ti."
488620,111,121,35,43,1,30,4,‘‘ Ānandattherena sabbe gahitā’’ ti?
488621,111,121,44,52,1,11,3,"‘‘ Āma, devā’’ ti."
488622,111,121,53,83,1,218,24,"‘‘ Sammāsambuddhena ticīvaraṃ anuññātaṃ, ānandatthero dussavaṇijjaṃ maññe karissati, atibahū tena sāṭakā gahitā’’ ti therassa kujjhitvā bhuttapātarāso vihāraṃ gantvā therassa pariveṇaṃ pavisitvā theraṃ vanditvā nisinno pucchi–"
488623,111,121,84,103,1,85,13,"‘‘ api, bhante, amhākaṃ ghare itthiyo tumhākaṃ santike dhammaṃ uggaṇhanti vā suṇanti vā’’ ti?"
488624,111,121,104,118,1,66,7,"‘‘ Āma, mahārāja, gahetabbayuttakaṃ gaṇhanti, sotabbayuttakaṃ suṇantī’’ ti."
488625,111,121,119,135,1,70,11,"‘‘ Kiṃ tā suṇantiyeva, udāhu tumhākaṃ nivāsanaṃ vā pārupanaṃ vā dadantī’’ ti?"
