488749,111,148,2,8,1,39,5,"Suhanūpi tādisoyeva, yo soṇassa sagocaro. "
488750,111,149,2,4,1,0,0,16.
488751,111,150,2,10,1,44,5,"‘ ‘ Pakkhandinā pagabbhena, niccaṃ sandānakhādinā; "
488752,111,151,2,12,1,40,7,"Sameti pāpaṃ pāpena, sameti asatā asan’’ ti. "
488753,111,152,2,30,1,172,24,"Tattha nayidaṃ visamasīlena, soṇena suhanū {sahā}ti yaṃ idaṃ suhanu kūṭasso soṇena saddhiṃ pemaṃ karoti, idaṃ na attano visamasīlena, atha kho attano samasīleneva saddhiṃ karoti. "
488754,111,152,31,38,1,63,7,Ubhopi hete attano anācāratāya dussīlatāya samasīlā samadhātukā. 
488755,111,152,39,60,1,127,16,"Suhanūpi tādisoyeva, yo soṇassa {sagocaro}ti yādiso soṇo, suhanupi tādisoyeva, yo soṇassa sagocaro yaṃgocaro soṇo, sopi taṃgocaroyeva. "
488756,111,152,61,71,1,64,9,"Yatheva hi soṇo assagocaro asse ḍaṃsentova carati, tathā suhanupi. "
488757,111,152,72,76,1,35,4,Iminā nesaṃ samānagocarataṃ dasseti. 
488758,111,153,2,16,1,66,9,Te pana ācāragocare ekato katvā dassetuṃ‘‘ pakkhandinā’’ tiādi vuttaṃ. 
488759,111,153,17,24,1,72,6,Tattha {pakkhandinā}ti assānaṃ upari pakkhandanasīlena pakkhandanagocarena. 
488760,111,153,25,29,1,52,3,{Pagabbhenā}ti kāyapāgabbhiyādisamannāgatena dussīlena. 
488761,111,153,30,39,1,83,8,Niccaṃ {sandānakhādinā}ti sadā attano bandhanayottaṃ khādanasīlena khādanagocarena ca. 
488762,111,153,40,53,1,88,11,Sameti pāpaṃ {pāpenā}ti etesu aññatarena pāpena saddhiṃ aññatarassa pāpaṃ dussīlyaṃ sameti. 
488763,111,153,54,75,1,170,20,"Asatā asan ti etesu aññatarena asatā anācāragocarasampannena saha itarassa asaṃ asādhukammaṃ sameti, gūthādīni viya gūthādīhi ekato saṃsandati sadisaṃ nibbisesameva hotīti. "
488764,111,154,2,33,1,176,25,"Evaṃ vatvā ca pana bodhisatto‘‘ mahārāja, raññā nāma atiluddhena na bhavitabbaṃ, parassa santakaṃ nāma nāsetuṃ na vaṭṭatī’’ ti rājānaṃ ovaditvā asse agghāpetvā bhūtameva mūlaṃ dāpesi. "
488765,111,154,34,40,1,64,6,Assavāṇijā yathāsabhāvameva mūlaṃ labhitvā haṭṭhatuṭṭhā agamaṃsu. 
488766,111,154,41,47,1,50,6,Rājāpi bodhisattassa ovāde ṭhatvā yathākammaṃ gato. 
488767,111,155,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
488768,111,155,9,29,1,90,14,"‘‘ tadā dve assā ime dve duṭṭhabhikkhū ahesuṃ, rājā ānando, paṇḍitāmacco pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
488769,111,156,2,4,1,27,2,Suhanujātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
488770,111,158,2,7,1,17,2,[ 159]9. Morajātakavaṇṇanā 
488771,111,159,2,15,1,98,11,Udetayaṃ cakkhumā {ekarājā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ukkaṇṭhitabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488772,111,159,16,63,1,187,28,"So hi bhikkhu bhikkhūhi satthu santikaṃ nīto‘‘ saccaṃ kira, tvaṃ bhikkhu, ukkaṇṭhito’’ ti vutte‘‘ saccaṃ, bhante’’ ti vatvā‘‘ kiṃ disvā’’ ti vutte‘‘ ekaṃ alaṅkatapaṭiyattasarīraṃ mātugāmaṃ oloketvā’’ ti āha. "
488773,111,159,64,89,1,201,22,"Atha naṃ satthā‘‘ bhikkhu mātugāmo nāma kasmā tumhādisānaṃ cittaṃ nāluḷessati, porāṇakapaṇḍitānampi hi mātugāmassa saddaṃ sutvā satta vassasatāni asamudāciṇṇakilesā okāsaṃ labhitvā khaṇeneva samudācariṃsu. "
488774,111,159,90,106,1,113,12,"Visuddhāpi sattā saṃkilissanti, uttamayasasamaṅginopi āyasakyaṃ pāpuṇanti, pageva aparisuddhā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
488775,111,160,2,40,1,364,35,"Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto morayoniyaṃ paṭisandhiṃ gahetvā aṇḍakālepi kaṇikāramakuḷavaṇṇaaṇḍakoso hutvā aṇḍaṃ bhinditvā nikkhanto suvaṇṇavaṇṇo ahosi dassanīyo pāsādiko pakkhānaṃ antare surattarājivirājito, so attano jīvitaṃ rakkhanto tisso pabbatarājiyo atikkamma catutthāya pabbatarājiyā ekasmiṃ daṇḍakahiraññapabbatatale vāsaṃ kappesi. "
488776,111,160,41,60,1,158,15,So pabhātāya rattiyā pabbatamatthake nisinno sūriyaṃ uggacchantaṃ oloketvā attano gocarabhūmiyaṃ rakkhāvaraṇatthāya brahmamantaṃ bandhanto‘‘ udetayan’’ tiādimāha. 
488777,111,161,2,4,1,0,0,17.
488778,111,162,2,7,1,25,4,"‘ ‘ Udetayaṃ cakkhumā ekarājā, "
488779,111,163,2,4,1,28,2,Harissavaṇṇo pathavippabhāso; 
488780,111,164,2,7,1,48,5,"Taṃ taṃ namassāmi harissavaṇṇaṃ pathavippabhāsaṃ, "
488781,111,165,2,9,1,33,5,Tayājja guttā viharemu divasan’’ ti. 
488782,111,166,2,8,1,43,4,Tattha {udetī}ti pācīnalokadhātuto uggacchati. 
488783,111,166,9,24,1,131,13,"{Cakkhumā}ti sakalacakkavāḷavāsīnaṃ andhakāraṃ vidhamitvā cakkhupaṭilābhakaraṇena yaṃ tena tesaṃ dinnaṃ cakkhu, tena cakkhunā cakkhumā. "
488784,111,166,25,32,1,74,6,{Ekarājā}ti sakalacakkavāḷe ālokakarānaṃ antare seṭṭhavisiṭṭhaṭṭhena ekarājā. 
488785,111,166,33,39,1,51,4,"{Harissavaṇṇo}ti harisamānavaṇṇo, suvaṇṇavaṇṇoti attho. "
488786,111,166,40,44,1,35,3,{Pathavippabhāso}ti pathaviyā pabhāso. 
488787,111,166,45,55,1,66,9,Taṃ taṃ {namassāmī}ti tasmā taṃ evarūpaṃ bhavantaṃ namassāmi vandāmi. 
488788,111,166,56,71,1,120,15,Tayājja guttā viharemu divasan ti tayā ajja rakkhitā gopitā hutvā imaṃ divasaṃ catuiriyāpathavihārena sukhaṃ vihareyyāma. 
488789,111,167,2,16,1,116,14,Evaṃ bodhisatto imāya gāthāya sūriyaṃ namassitvā dutiyagāthāya atīte parinibbute buddhe ceva buddhaguṇe ca namassati.
488790,111,168,2,16,1,61,12,"‘ ‘ Ye brāhmaṇā vedagū sabbadhamme, te me namo te ca maṃ pālayantu; "
488791,111,169,2,11,1,66,8,"Namatthu buddhānaṃ namatthu bodhiyā, namo vimuttānaṃ namo vimuttiyā; "
488792,111,170,2,13,1,43,8,"Imaṃ so parittaṃ katvā, moro carati esanā’’ ti. "
488793,111,171,2,9,1,51,6,Tattha ye {brāhmaṇā}ti ye bāhitapāpā visuddhibrāhmaṇā. 
488794,111,171,10,21,1,67,9,"{Vedagū}ti vedānaṃ pāraṃ gatātipi vedagū, vedehi pāraṃ gatātipi vedagū. "
488795,111,171,22,31,1,72,9,Idha pana sabbe saṅkhatāsaṅkhatadhamme vidite pākaṭe katvā gatāti vedagū. 
488796,111,171,32,40,1,23,3,Tenevāha ‘‘ sabbadhamme’’ ti. 
488797,111,171,41,65,1,229,22,"Sabbe khandhāyatanadhātudhamme salakkhaṇasāmaññalakkhaṇavasena attano ñāṇassa vidite pākaṭe katvā gatā, tiṇṇaṃ mārānaṃ matthakaṃ madditvā dasasahassilokadhātuṃ unnādetvā bodhitale sammāsambodhiṃ patvā saṃsāraṃ vā atikkantāti attho. "
488798,111,171,66,75,1,48,8,Te me {namo}ti te mama imaṃ namakkāraṃ paṭicchantu. 
488799,111,171,76,91,1,88,14,Te ca maṃ {pālayantū}ti evaṃ mayā namassitā ca te bhagavanto maṃ pālentu rakkhantu gopentu. 
488800,111,171,92,145,1,435,46,"Namatthu buddhānaṃ namatthu bodhiyā, namo vimuttānaṃ namo {vimuttiyā}ti ayaṃ mama namakkāro atītānaṃ parinibbutānaṃ buddhānaṃ atthu, tesaññeva catūsu ca maggesu catūsu phalesu ñāṇasaṅkhātāya bodhiyā atthu, tathā tesaññeva arahattaphalavimuttiyā vimuttānaṃ atthu, yā ca nesaṃ tadaṅgavimutti vikkhambhanavimutti samucchedavimutti paṭippassaddhivimutti nissaraṇavimuttīti pañcavidhā vimutti, tassā nesaṃ vimuttiyāpi ayaṃ mayhaṃ namakkāro atthūti."
488801,111,171,146,166,1,95,15,"‘‘ Imaṃ so parittaṃ katvā, moro carati esanā’’ ti idaṃ pana padadvayaṃ satthā abhisambuddho hutvā āha. "
488802,111,171,167,185,1,136,16,"Tassattho– bhikkhave, so moro imaṃ parittaṃ imaṃ rakkhaṃ katvā attano gocarabhūmiyaṃ pupphaphalādīnaṃ atthāya nānappakārāya esanāya carati. "
488803,111,172,2,24,1,182,18,Evaṃ divasaṃ caritvā sāyaṃ pabbatamatthake nisīditvā atthaṅgataṃ sūriyaṃ olokento buddhaguṇe āvajjetvā nivāsaṭṭhāne rakkhāvaraṇatthāya puna brahmamantaṃ bandhanto‘‘ apetayan’’ tiādimāha. 
