488855,111,187,2,7,1,19,2,[ 160]10. Vinīlajātakavaṇṇanā 
488856,111,188,2,14,1,95,12,Evameva nūna rājānan ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattassa sugatālayaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488857,111,188,15,33,1,150,17,Devadatte hi gayāsīsagatānaṃ dvinnaṃ aggasāvakānaṃ sugatālayaṃ dassetvā nipanne ubhopi therā dhammaṃ desetvā attano nissitake ādāya veḷuvanaṃ agamiṃsu. 
488858,111,188,34,62,1,122,17,"Te satthārā‘‘ sāriputta, devadatto tumhe disvā kiṃ akāsī’’ ti puṭṭhā‘‘ bhante, sugatālayaṃ dassetvā mahāvināsaṃ pāpuṇī’’ ti ārocesuṃ. "
488859,111,188,63,89,1,135,19,"Satthā‘‘ na kho, sāriputta, devadatto idāneva mama anukiriyaṃ karonto vināsaṃ patto, pubbepi pāpuṇiyevā’’ ti vatvā therehi yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
488860,111,189,2,13,1,104,11,Atīte videharaṭṭhe mithilāyaṃ videharāje rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto tassa aggamahesiyā kucchimhi nibbatti. 
