488906,111,207,2,7,1,28,2,[ 161]1. Indasamānagottajātakavaṇṇanā 
488907,111,208,2,17,1,99,12,Na santhavaṃ kāpurisena {kayirā}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ dubbacajātikaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
488908,111,208,18,33,1,52,5,Tassa vatthu navakanipāte gijjhajātake( jā.1.9.1 ādayo) āvibhavissati. 
488909,111,208,34,57,1,134,17,"Satthā pana taṃ bhikkhuṃ‘‘ pubbepi tvaṃ, bhikkhu, dubbacatāya paṇḍitānaṃ vacanaṃ akatvā mattahatthipādehi sañcuṇṇito’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
488910,111,209,2,22,1,203,20,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vuḍḍhippatto gharāvāsaṃ pahāya isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā pañcannaṃ isisatānaṃ gaṇasatthā hutvā himavantapadese vāsaṃ kappesi. 
488911,111,209,23,33,1,72,9,Tadā tesu tāpasesu indasamānagotto nāmeko tāpaso ahosi dubbaco anovādako. 
488912,111,209,34,38,1,28,4,So ekaṃ hatthipotakaṃ posesi. 
488913,111,209,39,54,1,79,11,Bodhisatto sutvā taṃ pakkositvā‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ hatthipotakaṃ posesī’’ ti pucchi.
488914,111,209,55,68,1,55,7,"‘‘ Saccaṃ, ācariya, matamātikaṃ ekaṃ hatthipotakaṃ posemī’’ ti."
488915,111,209,69,83,1,62,9,"‘‘ Hatthino nāma vuḍḍhippattā posakeyeva mārenti, mā taṃ posehī’’ ti."
488916,111,209,84,95,1,40,7,‘‘ Tena vinā vattituṃ na sakkomi ācariyā’’ ti.
488917,111,209,96,104,1,23,4,‘‘ Tena hi paññāyissasī’’ ti. 
488918,111,209,105,111,1,46,6,So tena posiyamāno aparabhāge mahāsarīro ahosi. 
488919,111,210,2,12,1,89,10,Athekasmiṃ kāle te isayo vanamūlaphalāphalatthāya dūraṃ gantvā tattheva katipāhaṃ vasiṃsu. 
488920,111,210,13,42,1,248,25,Hatthīpi aggadakkhiṇavāte pabhinnamado hutvā tassa paṇṇasālaṃ viddhaṃsetvā pānīyaghaṭaṃ bhinditvā pāsāṇaphalakaṃ khipitvā ālambanaphalakaṃ luñcitvā‘‘ taṃ tāpasaṃ māretvāva gamissāmī’’ ti ekaṃ gahanaṭṭhānaṃ pavisitvā tassa āgamanamaggaṃ olokento aṭṭhāsi. 
488921,111,210,43,56,1,112,12,Indasamānagotto tassa gocaraṃ gahetvā sabbesaṃ puratova āgacchanto taṃ disvā pakatisaññāyevassa santikaṃ agamāsi. 
488922,111,210,57,77,1,166,20,Atha naṃ so hatthī gahanaṭṭhānā nikkhamitvā soṇḍāya parāmasitvā bhūmiyaṃ pātetvā sīsaṃ pādena akkamitvā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpetvā madditvā koñcanādaṃ katvā araññaṃ pāvisi. 
