488925,111,211,2,4,1,0,0,21.
488926,111,212,2,12,1,60,8,"‘ ‘ Na santhavaṃ kāpurisena kayirā, ariyo anariyena pajānamatthaṃ; "
488927,111,213,2,9,1,55,6,"Cirānuvutthopi karoti pāpaṃ, gajo yathā indasamānagottaṃ. "
488928,111,214,2,4,1,0,0,22.
488929,111,215,2,14,1,57,10,"‘ ‘ Yaṃ tveva jaññā sadiso mamanti, sīlena paññāya sutena cāpi; "
488930,111,216,2,14,1,65,9,"Teneva mettiṃ kayirātha saddhiṃ, sukho have sappurisena saṅgamo’’ ti. "
488931,111,217,2,17,1,121,14,Tattha na santhavaṃ kāpurisena {kayirā}ti kucchitena kodhapurisena saddhiṃ taṇhāsanthavaṃ vā mittasanthavaṃ vā na kayirātha. 
488932,111,217,18,31,1,106,11,Ariyo anariyena pajānamatthan ti {ariyo}ti cattāro ariyā ācāraariyo liṅgaariyo dassanaariyo paṭivedhaariyoti. 
488933,111,217,32,36,1,30,4,Tesu ācāraariyo idha adhippeto. 
488934,111,217,37,53,1,144,16,So pajānamatthaṃ atthaṃ pajānanto atthānatthakusalo ācāre ṭhito ariyapuggalo anariyena nillajjena dussīlena saddhiṃ santhavaṃ na kareyyāti attho. 
488935,111,217,54,56,1,10,2,Kiṃ kāraṇā? 
488936,111,217,57,75,1,132,17,"Cirānuvutthopi karoti pāpan ti, yasmā anariyo ciraṃ ekato anuvutthopi taṃ ekato nivāsaṃ agaṇetvā karoti pāpaṃ lāmakakammaṃ karotiyeva. "
488937,111,217,76,78,1,9,2,Yathā kiṃ? 
488938,111,217,79,92,1,89,12,"Gajo yathā indasamānagottan ti, yathā so gajo indasamānagottaṃ mārento pāpaṃ akāsīti attho. "
488939,111,217,93,122,1,166,23,"Yaṃ tveva jaññā sadiso maman tiādīsu yaṃ tveva puggalaṃ‘‘ ayaṃ mama sīlādīhi sadiso’’ ti jāneyya, teneva saddhiṃ mettiṃ kayirātha, sappurisena saddhiṃ samāgamo sukhāvahoti. "
488940,111,218,2,27,1,181,19,"Evaṃ bodhisatto‘‘ anovādakena nāma na bhavitabbaṃ, susikkhitena bhavituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti isigaṇaṃ ovaditvā indasamānagottassa sarīrakiccaṃ kāretvā brahmavihāre bhāvetvā brahmalokūpago ahosi. "
