489070,111,270,2,7,1,25,3,Tattha {parābhavo}ti vināso. 
489071,111,270,8,11,1,12,2,{Poso}ti satto. 
489072,111,271,2,8,1,43,6,Gijjhassa vacanaṃ sutvā rājā seṭṭhiṃ pucchi–
