489074,111,271,25,33,1,14,3,"‘‘ Saccaṃ, devā’’ ti."
489075,111,271,34,41,1,13,3,‘‘ Kahaṃ tānī’’ ti?
489076,111,271,42,72,1,163,22,"‘‘ Deva, mayā tāni sabbāni visuṃ ṭhapitāni, yaṃ yesaṃ santakaṃ, taṃ tesaṃ dassāmi, imaṃ gijjhaṃ vissajjethā’’ ti gijjhaṃ vissajjāpetvā mahāseṭṭhiṃ sabbesaṃ santakāni dāpesi. "
489077,111,272,2,16,1,132,12,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne mātuposakabhikkhu sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahi ."
