489131,111,296,2,9,1,35,4,"‘ ‘ Upasāḷakanāmāni , sahassāni catuddasa; "
489132,111,297,2,9,1,42,6,"Asmiṃ padese daḍḍhāni, natthi loke anāmataṃ. "
489133,111,298,2,4,1,0,0,32.
489134,111,299,2,12,1,44,8,"‘ ‘ Yamhi saccañca dhammo ca, ahiṃsā saṃyamo damo; "
489135,111,300,2,12,1,40,7,"Etaṃ ariyā sevanti, etaṃ loke anāmatan’’ ti. "
489136,111,301,2,6,1,30,4,Tattha anāmatan ti mataṭṭhānaṃ. 
489137,111,301,7,26,1,70,10,"Tañhi upacāravasena‘‘ amatan’’ ti vuccati, taṃ paṭisedhento‘‘ anāmatan’’ ti āha."
489138,111,301,27,41,1,75,9,"‘‘ Anamatan’’ tipi pāṭho, lokasmiñhi anamataṭṭhānaṃ asusānaṃ nāma natthīti attho. "
489139,111,301,42,54,1,108,11,Yamhi saccañca dhammo {cā}ti yasmiṃ puggale catusaccavatthukaṃ pubbabhāgasaccañāṇañca lokuttaradhammo ca atthi. 
489140,111,301,55,60,1,35,4,{Ahiṃsā}ti paresaṃ avihesā aviheṭhanā. 
489141,111,301,61,64,1,21,2,{Saṃyamo}ti sīlasaṃyamo. 
489142,111,301,65,68,1,21,2,{Damo}ti indriyadamanaṃ. 
489143,111,301,69,96,1,175,23,"Idañca guṇajātaṃ yamhi puggale atthi, etaṃ ariyā {sevantī}ti, ariyā buddhā ca paccekabuddhā ca buddhasāvakā ca etaṃ ṭhānaṃ sevanti, evarūpaṃ puggalaṃ upasaṅkamanti bhajantīti attho. "
489144,111,301,97,107,1,75,10,Etaṃ loke anāmatan ti etaṃ guṇajātaṃ loke amatabhāvasādhanato anāmataṃ nāma. 
489145,111,302,2,12,1,99,10,Evaṃ bodhisatto pitāputtānaṃ dhammaṃ desetvā cattāro brahmavihāre bhāvetvā brahmalokaparāyaṇo ahosi. 
489146,111,303,2,17,1,140,14,"Satthā imaṃ dhammaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne ubho pitāputtā sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhahiṃsu."
489147,111,303,18,33,1,71,10,"‘‘ Tadā pitāputtāva etarahi pitāputtā ahesuṃ, tāpaso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
