489149,111,306,2,7,1,21,2,[ 167]7. Samiddhijātakavaṇṇanā 
489150,111,307,2,17,1,112,12,Abhutvā bhikkhasi {bhikkhū}ti idaṃ satthā rājagahaṃ upanissāya tapodārāme viharanto samiddhitheraṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
489151,111,307,18,38,1,222,20,Ekadivasañhi āyasmā samiddhi sabbarattiṃ padhānaṃ padahitvā aruṇuggamanavelāya nhatvā suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ attabhāvaṃ sukkhāpayamāno antaravāsakaṃ nivāsetvā uttarāsaṅgaṃ hatthena gahetvā aṭṭhāsi suparikammakatā viya suvaṇṇapaṭimā. 
489152,111,307,39,50,1,53,6,Attabhāvasamiddhiyāyeva hissa ‘‘ samiddhī’’ ti nāmaṃ ahosi. 
489153,111,307,51,59,1,74,8,Athassa sarīrasobhaggaṃ disvā ekā devadhītā paṭibaddhacittā theraṃ evamāha–
489154,111,307,60,97,1,228,28,"‘‘ tvaṃ khosi, bhikkhu, daharo yuvā susu kāḷakeso bhadrena yobbanena samannāgato abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko, evarūpassa tava kāme aparibhuñjitvā ko attho pabbajjāya, kāme tāva paribhuñjassu, pacchā pabbajitvā samaṇadhammaṃ karissasī’’ ti. "
489155,111,307,98,102,1,18,4,Atha naṃ thero āha–
489156,111,307,103,134,1,167,22,"‘‘ devadhīte,‘ asukasmiṃ nāma vaye ṭhito marissāmī’ ti mama maraṇakālaṃ na jānāmi, esa me kālo paṭicchanno, tasmā taruṇakāleyeva samaṇadhammaṃ katvā dukkhassantaṃ karissāmī’’ ti. "
489157,111,307,135,142,1,64,7,Sā therassa santikā paṭisanthāraṃ alabhitvā tattheva antaradhāyi. 
489158,111,307,143,148,1,48,5,Thero satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
489159,111,307,149,174,1,140,18,"Satthā‘‘ na kho, samiddhi, tvaññeva etarahi devadhītāya palobhito, pubbepi devadhītaro pabbajite palobhiṃsuyevā’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
489160,111,308,2,29,1,256,27,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto ekasmiṃ kāsigāmake brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto sabbasippesu nipphattiṃ patvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā himavantapadese ekaṃ jātassaraṃ nissāya vāsaṃ kappesi. 
489161,111,308,30,46,1,137,16,So sabbarattiṃ padhānaṃ padahitvā aruṇuggamanavelāya nhatvā ekaṃ vakkalaṃ nivāsetvā ekaṃ hatthena gahetvā sarīraṃ vodakaṃ karonto aṭṭhāsi. 
489162,111,308,47,58,1,122,11,Athassa rūpasobhaggappattaṃ attabhāvaṃ oloketvā paṭibaddhacittā ekā devadhītā bodhisattaṃ palobhayamānā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
489163,111,309,2,4,1,0,0,33.
489164,111,310,2,12,1,50,8,"‘ ‘ Abhutvā bhikkhasi bhikkhu, na hi bhutvāna bhikkhasi; "
489165,111,311,2,13,1,51,8,"Bhutvāna bhikkhu bhikkhassu, mā taṃ kālo upaccagā’’ ti. "
489166,111,312,2,16,1,113,12,Tattha abhutvā bhikkhasi {bhikkhū}ti bhikkhu tvaṃ daharakāle kilesakāmavasena vatthukāme abhutvāva bhikkhāya carasi. 
489167,111,312,17,34,1,119,15,"Na hi bhutvāna {bhikkhasī}ti nanu nāma pañca kāmaguṇe bhutvā bhikkhāya caritabbaṃ, kāme abhutvāva bhikkhācariyaṃ upagatosi. "
489168,111,312,35,48,1,100,11,Bhutvāna bhikkhu {bhikkhassū}ti bhikkhu daharakāle tāva kāme bhuñjitvā pacchā mahallakakāle bhikkhassu. 
489169,111,312,49,62,1,76,11,"Mā taṃ kālo {upaccagā}ti ayaṃ kāme bhuñjanakālo daharakālo, taṃ mā atikkamatūti. "
489170,111,313,2,12,1,79,9,Bodhisatto devatāya vacanaṃ sutvā attano ajjhāsayaṃ pakāsento dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
489171,111,314,2,4,1,0,0,34.
489172,111,315,2,13,1,44,9,"‘ ‘ Kālaṃ vohaṃ na jānāmi, channo kālo na dissati; "
489173,111,316,2,13,1,47,8,"Tasmā abhutvā bhikkhāmi, mā maṃ kālo upaccagā’’ ti. "
489174,111,317,2,11,1,48,7,Tattha kālaṃ vohaṃ na {jānāmī}ti {vo}ti nipātamattaṃ. 
489175,111,317,12,32,1,109,16,Ahaṃ pana‘‘ paṭhamavaye vā mayā maritabbaṃ majjhimavaye vā pacchimavaye vā’’ ti evaṃ attano maraṇakālaṃ na jānāmi. 
489176,111,317,33,36,1,22,3,Paṇḍitena hi puggalena–
489177,111,318,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Jīvitaṃ byādhi kālo ca, dehanikkhepanaṃ gati; "
489178,111,319,2,11,1,42,6,"Pañcete jīvalokasmiṃ, animittā na nāyare’’ ti. "
489179,111,320,2,32,1,173,24,"Channo kālo na {dissatī}ti yasmā‘‘ asukasmiṃ nāma vayakāle hemantādiutukāle vā mayā maritabban’’ ti mayhampesa channo hutvā kālo na dissati, suppaṭicchanno hutvā ṭhito na paññāyati. "
489180,111,320,33,43,1,72,9,Tasmā abhutvā {bhikkhāmī}ti tena kāraṇena pañca kāmaguṇe abhutvā bhikkhāmi. 
489181,111,320,44,54,1,71,9,Mā maṃ kālo {upaccagā}ti maṃ samaṇadhammakaraṇakālo mā atikkamatūti attho. 
489182,111,320,55,62,1,64,7,Iminā kāraṇena daharova samāno pabbajitvā samaṇadhammaṃ karomīti. 
489183,111,320,63,69,1,58,6,Devadhītā bodhisattassa vacanaṃ sutvā tattheva antaradhāyi. 
489184,111,321,2,8,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
489185,111,321,9,25,1,74,11,"‘‘ tadā devadhītā ayaṃ devadhītā ahosi, ahameva tena samayena tāpaso ahosin’’ ti. "
489186,111,322,2,4,1,29,2,Samiddhijātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
489187,111,324,2,7,1,23,2,[ 168]8. Sakuṇagghijātakavaṇṇanā 
489188,111,325,2,25,1,100,11,Seno balasā {patamāno}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto attajjhāsayaṃ sakuṇovādasuttaṃ( saṃ. ni.5.372) ārabbha kathesi. 
489189,111,325,26,85,1,341,38,"Ekadivasañhi satthā bhikkhū āmantetvā‘‘ gocare, bhikkhave, caratha sake pettike visaye’’ ti( saṃ. ni.5.372) imaṃ saṃyuttamahāvagge suttantaṃ kathento ‘‘ tumhe tāva tiṭṭhatha, pubbe tiracchānagatāpi sakaṃ pettikavisayaṃ pahāya agocare carantā paccāmittānaṃ hatthapathaṃ gantvāpi attano paññāsampattiyā upāyakosallena paccāmittānaṃ hatthā mucciṃsū’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
489190,111,326,2,14,1,131,12,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto lāpasakuṇayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā naṅgalakaṭṭhakaraṇe leḍḍuṭṭhāne vāsaṃ kappesi. 
489191,111,326,15,30,1,102,11,So ekadivasaṃ‘‘ sakavisaye gocaragahaṇaṃ pahāya paravisaye gocaraṃ gaṇhissāmī’’ ti aṭavipariyantaṃ agamāsi. 
489192,111,326,31,41,1,78,10,Atha naṃ tattha gocaraṃ gaṇhantaṃ disvā sakuṇagghi sahasā ajjhappattā aggahesi. 
489193,111,326,42,47,1,42,5,So sakuṇagghiyā hariyamāno evaṃ paridevasi–
489194,111,326,48,80,1,180,24,"‘‘ mayamevamha alakkhikā, mayaṃ appapuññā, ye mayaṃ agocare carimha paravisaye, sacejja mayaṃ gocare careyyāma sake pettike visaye, na myāyaṃ sakuṇagghi alaṃ abhavissa yadidaṃ yuddhāyā’’ ti."
489195,111,326,81,96,1,45,9,"‘‘ Ko pana, te lāpa, gocaro sako pettiko visayo’’ ti?"
489196,111,326,97,105,1,44,4,‘‘ Yadidaṃ naṅgalakaṭṭhakaraṇaṃ leḍḍuṭṭhānan’’ ti. 
489197,111,326,106,113,1,48,7,Atha naṃ sakuṇagghi sake bale apatthaddhā amuñci–
489198,111,326,114,130,1,53,10,"‘‘ gaccha kho, tvaṃ lāpa, tatrapi me gantvā na mokkhasī’’ ti. "
489199,111,326,131,149,1,95,14,So tattha gantvā mahantaṃ leḍḍuṃ abhiruhitvā‘‘ ehi kho dāni sakuṇagghī’’ ti senaṃ avhayanto aṭṭhāsi. 
489200,111,326,150,160,1,84,10,Sakuṇagghi sake bale apatthaddhā ubho pakkhe sannayha lāpasakuṇaṃ sahasā ajjhappattā. 
489201,111,326,161,182,1,113,16,"Yadā pana taṃ lāpo‘‘ bahuāgatā kho myāyaṃ sakuṇagghī’’ ti aññāsi, atha parivattitvā tasseva leḍḍussa antaraṃ paccāpādi. "
489202,111,326,183,190,1,64,7,Sakuṇagghi vegaṃ sandhāretuṃ asakkontī tattheva uraṃ paccatāḷesi. 
489203,111,326,191,199,1,66,8,Evaṃ sā bhinnena hadayena nikkhantehi akkhīhi jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇi. 
489204,111,327,2,34,1,204,25,"Satthā imaṃ atītaṃ dassetvā‘‘ evaṃ, bhikkhave, tiracchānagatāpi agocare carantā sapattahatthaṃ gacchanti, gocare pana sake pettike visaye carantā sapatte niggaṇhanti, tasmā tumhepi mā agocare caratha paravisaye. "
