489347,111,391,2,11,1,45,6,"Jātimassa jigucchantā, tuṇhī sīhā samaccare’’ ti. "
489348,111,392,2,17,1,92,12,"Tattha {samaccare}ti san ti upasaggamattaṃ, accantīti attho, tuṇhī hutvā nisīdantīti vuttaṃ hoti. "
489349,111,392,18,27,1,38,5,Potthakesu pana‘‘ samacchare’’ ti likhanti. 
489350,111,393,2,30,1,148,19,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, kokāliko idāneva attano nādena attānaṃ pākaṭaṃ karoti, pubbepi akāsiyevā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
