489353,111,396,2,7,1,20,2,[ 173]3. Makkaṭajātakavaṇṇanā 
489354,111,397,2,13,1,85,10,Tātamāṇavako esoti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kuhakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
489355,111,397,14,28,1,51,4,Vatthu pakiṇṇakanipāte uddālakajātake( jā.1.14.62 ādayo) āvibhavissati. 
489356,111,397,29,54,1,133,19,"Tadā pana satthā‘‘ bhikkhave, nāyaṃ bhikkhu idāneva kuhako, pubbepi makkaṭo hutvā aggissa kāraṇā kohaññaṃ akāsiyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
489357,111,398,2,18,1,163,16,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto ekasmiṃ kāsigāmake brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sippaṃ uggaṇhitvā gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapesi. 
489358,111,398,19,29,1,94,10,Athassa brāhmaṇī ekaṃ puttaṃ vijāyitvā puttassa ādhāvitvā paridhāvitvā vicaraṇakāle kālamakāsi. 
489359,111,398,30,60,1,219,25,"Bodhisatto tassā petakiccaṃ katvā‘‘ kiṃ me dāni gharāvāsena, puttaṃ gahetvā pabbajissāmī’’ ti assumukhaṃ ñātimittavaggaṃ pahāya puttaṃ ādāya himavantaṃ pavisitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā tattha vanamūlaphalāhāro vāsaṃ kappesi. "
489360,111,398,61,79,1,153,17,"So ekadivasaṃ vassānakāle deve vassante sāradārūni aggiṃ jāletvā visibbanto phalakatthare nipajji, puttopissa tāpasakumārako pitu pāde sambāhantova nisīdi. "
489361,111,399,2,59,1,384,46,"Atheko vanamakkaṭo sītena pīḷiyamāno tassa paṇṇasālāya taṃ aggiṃ disvā‘‘ sacāhaṃ ettha pavisissāmi,‘ makkaṭo makkaṭo’ ti maṃ pothetvā nīharissanti, aggiṃ visibbetuṃ na labhissāmi, atthi dāni me upāyo, tāpasavesaṃ gahetvā kohaññaṃ katvā pavisissāmī’’ ti cintetvā ekassa matatāpasassa vakkalāni nivāsetvā pacchiñca aṅkusayaṭṭhiñca gahetvā paṇṇasāladvāre ekaṃ tālarukkhaṃ nissāya saṃkuṭito aṭṭhāsi. "
489362,111,399,60,96,1,231,27,Tāpasakumārako taṃ disvā makkaṭabhāvaṃ ajānanto‘‘ eko mahallakatāpaso sītena pīḷito aggiṃ visibbetuṃ āgato bhavissatī’’ ti pitu tāpasassa kathetvā‘‘ etaṃ paṇṇasālaṃ pavesetvā visibbāpessāmī’’ ti cintetvā pitaraṃ ālapanto paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
489363,111,400,2,4,1,0,0,45.
489364,111,401,2,11,1,36,6,"‘ ‘ Tāta māṇavako eso, tālamūlaṃ apassito; "
489365,111,402,2,10,1,43,5,"Agārakañcidaṃ atthi, handa demassagārakan’’ ti. "
489366,111,403,2,6,1,33,3,Tattha {māṇavako}ti sattādhivacanaṃ. 
489367,111,403,7,22,1,53,10,"Tena‘‘ tāta, eso eko māṇavako satto eko tāpaso’’ ti dīpeti. "
489368,111,403,23,29,1,48,5,Tālamūlaṃ {apassito}ti tālakkhandhaṃ nissāya ṭhito. 
489369,111,403,30,41,1,84,9,"Agārakañcidaṃ {atthī}ti idañca amhākaṃ pabbajitāgāraṃ atthi, paṇṇasālaṃ sandhāya vadati. "
489370,111,403,42,46,1,29,3,{Handā}ti vavassaggatthe nipāto. 
489371,111,403,47,54,1,60,7,Demassagārakan ti etassa ekamante vasanatthāya agārakaṃ dema. 
489372,111,404,2,35,1,203,26,"Bodhisatto puttassa vacanaṃ sutvā uṭṭhāya paṇṇasāladvāre ṭhatvā olokento tassa makkaṭabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ tāta, manussānaṃ nāma na evarūpaṃ mukhaṃ hoti, makkaṭo esa, nayidha pakkositabbo’’ ti vatvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
489373,111,405,2,4,1,0,0,46.
489374,111,406,2,13,1,44,9,"‘ ‘ Mā kho tvaṃ tāta pakkosi, dūseyya no agārakaṃ; "
489375,111,407,2,11,1,45,6,"Netādisaṃ mukhaṃ hoti, brāhmaṇassa susīlino’’ ti. "
489376,111,408,2,22,1,137,20,Tattha dūseyya no agārakan ti ayañhi idha paviṭṭho samāno imaṃ kicchena kataṃ paṇṇasālaṃ agginā vā jhāpento uccārādīni vā karonto dūseyya. 
489377,111,408,23,55,1,154,23,"Netādisan ti‘‘ etādisaṃ brāhmaṇassa susīlino mukhaṃ na hoti, makkaṭo eso’’ ti vatvā bodhisatto ekaṃ ummukaṃ gahetvā‘‘ kiṃ ettha tiṭṭhasī’’ ti khipitvā taṃ palāpesi. "
489378,111,408,56,63,1,65,7,Makkaṭo vakkalāni chaḍḍetvā rukkhaṃ abhiruhitvā vanasaṇḍaṃ pāvisi. 
489379,111,408,64,70,1,61,6,Bodhisatto cattāro brahmavihāre bhāvetvā brahmalokūpago ahosi. 
489380,111,409,2,9,1,54,6,Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–
489381,111,409,10,28,1,87,12,"‘‘ tadā makkaṭo ayaṃ kuhakabhikkhu ahosi, tāpasakumāro rāhulo, tāpaso pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
489382,111,410,2,4,1,27,2,Makkaṭajātakavaṇṇanā tatiyā.
489383,111,412,2,7,1,26,2,[ 174]4. Dubbhiyamakkaṭajātakaṇṇanā 
489384,111,413,2,16,1,87,12,Adamha te vāri pahūtarūpan ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto devadattaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
489385,111,413,17,24,1,93,7,Ekadivasañhi dhammasabhāyaṃ bhikkhū devadattassa akataññumittadubbhibhāvaṃ kathentā nisīdiṃsu. 
489386,111,413,25,47,1,110,15,"Satthā āgantvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, devadatto idāneva akataññū mittadubbhī, pubbepi evarūpo ahosī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
489387,111,414,2,15,1,132,13,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto ekasmiṃ kāsigāmake brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapesi. 
489388,111,414,16,41,1,226,24,"Tasmiṃ pana samaye kāsiraṭṭhe vattanimahāmagge eko gambhīro udapāno hoti anotaraṇīyo tiracchānānaṃ, maggappaṭipannā puññatthikā manussā dīgharajjukena vārakena udakaṃ ussiñcitvā ekissā doṇiyā pūretvā tiracchānānaṃ pānīyaṃ denti. "
489389,111,414,42,51,1,60,8,"Tassa sāmantato mahantaṃ araññaṃ, tattha bahū makkaṭā vasanti. "
489390,111,414,52,65,1,91,12,"Atha tasmiṃ magge dve tīṇi divasāni manussasañcāro pacchijji, tiracchānā pānīyaṃ na labhiṃsu. "
489391,111,414,66,75,1,76,9,Eko makkaṭo pipāsāturo hutvā pānīyaṃ pariyesanto udapānassa santike vicarati. 
489392,111,414,76,93,1,145,17,Bodhisatto kenacideva karaṇīyena taṃ maggaṃ paṭipajjitvā tattha gacchanto pānīyaṃ uttāretvā pivitvā hatthapāde dhovitvā ṭhito taṃ makkaṭaṃ addasa. 
489393,111,414,94,115,1,127,16,"Athassa pipāsitabhāvaṃ ñatvā pānīyaṃ ussiñcitvā doṇiyaṃ ākiritvā adāsi, datvā ca pana‘‘ vissamissāmī’’ ti ekasmiṃ rukkhamūle nipajji. "
489394,111,414,116,125,1,88,9,Makkaṭo pānīyaṃ pivitvā avidūre nisīditvā mukhamakkaṭikaṃ karonto bodhisattaṃ bhiṃsāpesi. 
489395,111,414,126,163,1,220,29,"Bodhisatto tassa taṃ kiriyaṃ disvā‘‘ are duṭṭhamakkaṭa, ahaṃ tava pipāsitassa kilantassa bahuṃ pānīyaṃ adāsiṃ, idāni tvaṃ mayhaṃ mukhamakkaṭikaṃ karosi, aho pāpajanassa nāma kato upakāro niratthako’’ ti vatvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
489396,111,415,2,4,1,0,0,47.
489397,111,416,2,12,1,56,7,"‘ ‘ Adamha te vāri pahūtarūpaṃ, ghammābhitattassa pipāsitassa; "
489398,111,417,2,13,1,56,8,"So dāni pitvāna kiriṅkarosi, asaṅgamo pāpajanena seyyo’’ ti. "
489399,111,418,2,25,1,127,18,Tattha so dāni pitvāna {kiriṅkarosī}ti so idāni tvaṃ mayā dinnapānīyaṃ pivitvā mukhamakkaṭikaṃ karonto‘‘ kiri kirī’’ ti saddaṃ karosi. 
489400,111,418,26,38,1,82,10,"Asaṅgamo pāpajanena {seyyo}ti pāpajanena saddhiṃ saṅgamo na seyyo, asaṅgamova seyyoti. "
489401,111,419,2,31,1,144,21,"Taṃ sutvā so mittadubbhī makkaṭo‘‘ tvaṃ‘ ettakenavetaṃ niṭṭhitan’ ti saññaṃ karosi, idāni te sīse vaccaṃ pātetvā gamissāmī’’ ti vatvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
489402,111,420,2,4,1,0,0,48.
489403,111,421,2,14,1,43,10,"‘ ‘ Ko te suto vā diṭṭho vā, sīlavā nāma makkaṭo; "
489404,111,422,2,13,1,45,8,"Idāni kho taṃ ohacchaṃ, esā asmāka dhammatā’’ ti. "
489405,111,423,2,50,1,285,39,"Tatrāyaṃ saṅkhepattho– bho brāhmaṇa,‘‘ makkaṭo kataguṇajānanako ācārasampanno sīlavā nāma atthī’’ ti kahaṃ tayā suto vā diṭṭho vā, idāni kho ahaṃ taṃ ohacchaṃ vaccaṃ te sīse katvā pakkamissāmi, asmākañhi makkaṭānaṃ nāma esā dhammatā ayaṃ jātisabhāvo, yadidaṃ upakārakassa sīse vaccaṃ kātabbanti. "
489406,111,424,2,8,1,42,6,Taṃ sutvā bodhisatto uṭṭhāya gantuṃ ārabhi. 
489407,111,424,9,24,1,128,15,Makkaṭo taṅkhaṇaññeva uppatitvā sākhāyaṃ nisīditvā olambakaṃ otaranto viya tassa sīse vaccaṃ pātetvā viravanto vanasaṇḍaṃ pāvisi. 
489408,111,424,25,28,1,25,3,Bodhisatto nhatvā agamāsi. 
489409,111,425,2,27,1,131,17,"Satthā ‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva devadatto, pubbepi mayā kataguṇaṃ na jānāsiyevā’’ ti vatvā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi–"
489410,111,425,28,42,1,60,9,"‘‘ tadā makkaṭo devadatto ahosi, brāhmaṇo pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
489411,111,426,2,4,1,37,2,Dubbhiyamakkaṭajātakavaṇṇanā catutthā.
489412,111,428,2,7,1,27,2,[ 175]5. Ādiccupaṭṭhānajātakavaṇṇanā 
489413,111,429,2,15,1,89,11,Sabbesu kira {bhūtesū}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ kuhakabhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
489414,111,429,16,19,1,31,3,Vatthu heṭṭhā kathitasadisameva. 
489415,111,430,2,28,1,255,26,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā abhiññā ca samāpattiyo ca nibbattetvā mahāparivāro gaṇasatthā hutvā himavante vāsaṃ kappesi. 
489416,111,430,29,44,1,117,14,So tattha ciraṃ vasitvā loṇambilasevanatthāya pabbatā oruyha paccante ekaṃ gāmaṃ nissāya paṇṇasālāyaṃ vāsaṃ upagañchi. 
489417,111,430,45,66,1,163,18,"Atheko lolamakkaṭo isigaṇe bhikkhācāraṃ gate assamapadaṃ āgantvā paṇṇasālā uttiṇṇā karoti, pānīyaghaṭesu udakaṃ chaḍḍeti, kuṇḍikaṃ bhindati, aggisālāyaṃ vaccaṃ karoti. "
489418,111,430,67,84,1,118,12,"Tāpasā vassaṃ vasitvā‘‘ idāni himavanto pupphaphalasamiddho ramaṇīyo, tattheva gamissāmā’’ ti paccantagāmavāsike āpucchiṃsu. "
489419,111,430,85,111,1,169,19,"Manussā‘‘ sve, bhante, mayaṃ bhikkhaṃ gahetvā assamapadaṃ āgamissāma, taṃ paribhuñjitvāva gamissathā’’ ti vatvā dutiyadivase pahūtaṃ khādanīyabhojanīyaṃ gahetvā tattha agamaṃsu. "
489420,111,430,112,117,1,28,5,Taṃ disvā so makkaṭo cintesi–
489421,111,430,118,130,1,77,8,‘‘ kohaññaṃ katvā manusse ārādhetvā mayhampi khādanīyabhojanīyaṃ āharāpessāmī’’ ti. 
489422,111,430,131,145,1,96,13,So tāpasacaraṇaṃ caranto viya sīlavā viya ca hutvā tāpasānaṃ avidūre sūriyaṃ namassamāno aṭṭhāsi. 
489423,111,430,146,162,1,90,12,Manussā taṃ disvā‘‘ sīlavantānaṃ santike vasantā sīlavantā hontī’’ ti vatvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
489424,111,431,2,4,1,0,0,49.
489425,111,432,2,10,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Sabbesu kira bhūtesu, santi sīlasamāhitā; "
489426,111,433,2,10,1,45,5,"Passa sākhamigaṃ jammaṃ, ādiccamupatiṭṭhatī’’ ti. "
489427,111,434,2,17,1,117,13,"Tattha santi {sīlasamāhitā}ti sīlena samannāgatā saṃvijjanti, sīlavantā ca samāhitā ca ekaggacittā saṃvijjantītipi attho. "
489428,111,434,18,21,1,17,3,Jamman ti lāmakaṃ. 
