489461,111,446,118,137,1,119,14,"Bodhisatto‘‘ mahārāja, bahuṃ anavaloketvā appaṃ oloketvā dubbuddhino bālā evarūpaṃ karontiyevā’’ ti vatvā paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– "
