489515,111,467,29,38,1,57,9,Kathan ti kena nu kho upāyena amhākaṃ mokkho bhavissatīti. 
489516,111,468,2,42,1,234,30,"Tesaṃ kathaṃ sutvā vānarindo‘‘ mā bhāyittha, manussā nāma bahukiccā, ajjapi majjhimayāmo vattati, api nāma tesaṃ‘ amhe māressāmā’ ti parivāritānaṃ imassa kiccassa antarāyakaraṃ aññaṃ kiccaṃ uppajjeyyā’’ ti vānare samassāsetvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
