489534,111,475,2,4,1,28,2,Tindukajātakavaṇṇanā sattamā.
489535,111,477,2,7,1,21,2,[ 178]8. Kacchapajātakavaṇṇanā 
489536,111,478,2,15,1,98,12,Janittaṃ me bhavittaṃ {me}ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekaṃ ahivātakarogamuttaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
489537,111,478,16,22,1,51,6,Sāvatthiyaṃ kira ekasmiṃ kule ahivātakarogo uppajji. 
489538,111,478,23,26,1,24,3,Mātāpitaro puttaṃ āhaṃsu–
489539,111,478,27,62,1,201,27,"‘‘ tāta, mā imasmiṃ gehe vasa, bhittiṃ bhinditvā palāyitvā yattha katthaci gantvā jīvitaṃ rakkha, pacchā āgantvā imasmiṃ nāma ṭhāne mahānidhānaṃ atthi, taṃ uddharitvā kuṭumbaṃ saṇṭhapetvā sukhena jīveyyāsī’’ ti. "
489540,111,478,63,80,1,153,17,Putto tesaṃ vacanaṃ sampaṭicchitvā bhittiṃ bhinditvā palāyitvā attano roge vūpasante āgantvā mahānidhānaṃ uddharitvā kuṭumbaṃ saṇṭhapetvā gharāvāsaṃ vasi. 
489541,111,478,81,93,1,107,12,So ekadivasaṃ sappitelādīni ceva vatthacchādanādīni ca gāhāpetvā jetavanaṃ gantvā satthāraṃ vanditvā nisīdi. 
489542,111,478,94,119,1,139,19,"Satthā tena saddhiṃ paṭisanthāraṃ katvā‘‘ tumhākaṃ gehe ahivātakarogo uppannoti assumha, kinti katvā muttosī’’ ti pucchi, so taṃ pavattiṃ ācikkhi. "
489543,111,478,120,154,1,197,27,"Satthā‘‘ pubbepi kho, upāsaka, bhaye uppanne attano vasanaṭṭhāne ālayaṃ katvā aññattha agatā jīvitakkhayaṃ pāpuṇiṃsu, anālayaṃ pana katvā aññattha gatā jīvitaṃ labhiṃsū’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
489544,111,479,2,15,1,134,13,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsigāmake kumbhakārakule nibbattitvā kumbhakārakammaṃ katvā puttadāraṃ posesi. 
489545,111,479,16,24,1,70,8,Tadā pana bārāṇasiyaṃ mahānadiyā saddhiṃ ekābaddho mahājātassaro ahosi. 
489546,111,479,25,37,1,72,10,"So bahuudakakāle nadiyā saddhiṃ ekodako hoti, udake mandībhūte visuṃ hoti. "
489547,111,479,38,55,1,104,11,"Macchakacchapā pana‘‘ imasmiṃ saṃvacchare suvuṭṭhikā bhavissati, imasmiṃ saṃvacchare dubbuṭṭhikā’’ ti jānanti. "
489548,111,479,56,78,1,156,17,Atha tasmiṃ sare nibbattamacchakacchapā‘‘ imasmiṃ saṃvacchare dubbuṭṭhikā bhavissatī’’ ti ñatvā udakassa ekābaddhakāleyeva tamhā sarā nikkhamitvā nadiṃ agamiṃsu. 
489549,111,479,79,102,1,122,17,"Eko pana kacchapo‘‘ idaṃ me jātaṭṭhānaṃ vaḍḍhitaṭṭhānaṃ, mātāpitūhi vasitaṭṭhānaṃ, na sakkomi imaṃ jahitun’’ ti nadiṃ na agamāsi. "
489550,111,479,103,116,1,108,12,"Atha nidāghasamaye tattha udakaṃ chijji, so kacchapo bodhisattassa mattikagahaṇaṭṭhāne bhūmiṃ khaṇitvā pāvisi. "
489551,111,479,117,140,1,165,19,Bodhisatto‘‘ mattikaṃ gahessāmī’’ ti tattha gantvā mahākuddālena bhūmiṃ khaṇanto kacchapassa piṭṭhiṃ bhinditvā mattikapiṇḍaṃ viya kuddāleneva naṃ uddharitvā thale pātesi. 
489552,111,479,141,161,1,118,16,So vedanāppatto hutvā‘‘ vasanaṭṭhāne ālayaṃ jahituṃ asakkonto evaṃ vināsaṃ pāpuṇin’’ ti vatvā paridevamāno imā gāthā avoca– 
489553,111,480,2,4,1,0,0,55.
489554,111,481,2,12,1,44,8,"‘ ‘ Janittaṃ me bhavittaṃ me, iti paṅke avassayiṃ; "
489555,111,482,2,10,1,47,7,"Taṃ maṃ paṅko ajjhabhavi, yathā dubbalakaṃ tathā; "
489556,111,483,2,10,1,43,7,"Taṃ taṃ vadāmi bhaggava, suṇohi vacanaṃ mama. "
489557,111,484,2,4,1,0,0,56.
489558,111,485,2,11,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Gāme vā yadi vāraññe, sukhaṃ yatrādhigacchati; "
489559,111,486,2,8,1,43,5,"Taṃ janittaṃ bhavittañca, purisassa pajānato; "
489560,111,487,2,13,1,45,8,"Yamhi jīve tamhi gacche, na niketahato siyā’’ ti. "
489561,111,488,2,15,1,81,11,"Tattha janittaṃ me bhavittaṃ {me}ti idaṃ mama jātaṭṭhānaṃ, idaṃ mama vaḍḍhitaṭṭhānaṃ. "
489562,111,488,16,30,1,98,13,"Iti paṅke avassayin ti iminā kāraṇenāhaṃ imasmiṃ kaddame avassayiṃ nipajjiṃ, vāsaṃ kappesinti attho. "
489563,111,488,31,36,1,38,4,{Ajjhabhavī}ti adhiabhavi vināsaṃ pāpesi. 
489564,111,488,37,41,1,30,3,{Bhaggavā}ti kumbhakāraṃ ālapati. 
489565,111,488,42,48,1,56,5,"Kumbhakārānañhi nāmagottapaññatti esā, yadidaṃ bhaggavāti. "
489566,111,488,49,52,1,30,3,Sukhan ti kāyikacetasikassādaṃ. 
489567,111,488,53,61,1,62,6,Taṃ janittaṃ {bhavittañcā}ti taṃ jātaṭṭhānañca vaḍḍhitaṭṭhānañca.
489568,111,488,62,73,1,52,6,"‘‘ Jānittaṃ bhāvittan’’ ti dīghavasenapi pāṭho, soyevattho. "
489569,111,488,74,79,1,48,4,{Pajānato}ti atthānatthaṃ kāraṇākāraṇaṃ jānantassa. 
489570,111,488,80,97,1,115,15,"Na niketahato {siyā}ti nikete ālayaṃ katvā aññattha agantvā niketena hato, evarūpaṃ maraṇadukkhaṃ pāpito na bhaveyyāti. "
489571,111,489,2,8,1,48,6,Evaṃ so bodhisattena saddhiṃ kathento kālamakāsi. 
489572,111,489,9,18,1,82,9,Bodhisatto taṃ gahetvā sakalagāmavāsino sannipātāpetvā te manusse ovadanto evamāha–
489573,111,489,19,44,1,187,20,"‘‘ passatha imaṃ kacchapaṃ, ayaṃ aññesaṃ macchakacchapānaṃ mahānadiṃ gamanakāle attano vasanaṭṭhāne ālayaṃ chindituṃ asakkonto tehi saddhiṃ agantvā mama mattikagahaṇaṭṭhānaṃ pavisitvā nipajji. "
489574,111,489,45,65,1,165,19,"Athassāhaṃ mattikaṃ gaṇhanto mahākuddālena piṭṭhiṃ bhinditvā mattikapiṇḍaṃ viya naṃ thale pātesiṃ, ayaṃ attanā katakammaṃ saritvā dvīhi gāthāhi paridevitvā kālamakāsi. "
489575,111,489,66,117,1,344,44,"Evamesa attano vasanaṭṭhāne ālayaṃ katvā maraṇaṃ patto, tumhepi mā iminā kacchapena sadisā ahuvattha, ito paṭṭhāya‘ mayhaṃ rūpaṃ mayhaṃ saddo mayhaṃ gandho mayhaṃ raso mayhaṃ phoṭṭhabbo mayhaṃ putto mayhaṃ dhītā mayhaṃ dāsadāsiparicchedo mayhaṃ hiraññasuvaṇṇan’ ti taṇhāvasena upabhogavasena mā gaṇhittha, ekakovesa satto tīsu bhavesu parivattatī’’ ti. "
489576,111,489,118,130,1,116,11,"Evaṃ buddhalīlāya mahājanassa ovādamadāsi, so ovādo sakalajambudīpaṃ pattharitvā saṭṭhimattāni vassasahassāni aṭṭhāsi. "
489577,111,489,131,148,1,143,16,"Mahājano bodhisattassa ovāde ṭhatvā dānādīni puññāni katvā āyupariyosāne saggapuraṃ pūresi, bodhisattopi tatheva puññāni katvā saggapuraṃ pūresi. "
489578,111,490,2,16,1,127,13,"Satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ āharitvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne so kulaputto sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhāsi."
489579,111,490,17,31,1,60,9,"‘‘ Tadā kacchapo ānando ahosi, kumbhakāro pana ahameva ahosin’’ ti. "
489580,111,491,2,4,1,29,2,Kacchapajātakavaṇṇanā aṭṭhamā.
489581,111,493,2,7,1,23,2,[ 179]9. Satadhammajātakavaṇṇanā 
489582,111,494,2,14,1,86,11,Tañca appan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto ekavīsatividhaṃ anesanaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
489583,111,494,15,29,1,156,14,Ekasmiñhi kāle bahū bhikkhū vejjakammena dūtakammena pahiṇakammena jaṅghapesanikena piṇḍapaṭipiṇḍenāti evarūpāya ekavīsatividhāya anesanāya jīvikaṃ kappesuṃ. 
489584,111,494,30,42,1,29,3,Sā sāketajātake( jā.1.2.173-174) āvibhavissati. 
489585,111,494,43,101,1,421,45,"Satthā tesaṃ tathā jīvikakappanabhāvaṃ ñatvā‘‘ etarahi kho bahū bhikkhū anesanāya jīvikaṃ kappenti, te pana evaṃ jīvikaṃ kappetvā yakkhattabhāvā petattabhāvā na muccissanti, dhuragoṇā hutvāva nibbattissanti, niraye paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhissanti, etesaṃ hitatthāya sukhatthāya attajjhāsayaṃ sakapaṭibhānaṃ ekaṃ dhammadesanaṃ kathetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti bhikkhusaṅghaṃ sannipātāpetvā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, ekavīsatividhāya anesanāya paccayā uppādetabbā. "
489586,111,494,102,108,1,68,6,Anesanāya hi uppanno piṇḍapāto ādittalohaguḷasadiso halāhalavisūpamo. 
489587,111,494,109,115,1,68,6,Anesanā hi nāmesā buddhapaccekabuddhasāvakehi garahitabbā paṭikuṭṭhā. 
489588,111,494,116,127,1,74,10,Anesanāya uppannaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjantassa hi hāso vā somanassaṃ vā natthi. 
489589,111,494,128,149,1,170,18,"Evaṃ uppanno hi piṇḍapāto mama sāsane caṇḍālassa ucchiṭṭhabhojanasadiso, tassa paribhogo satadhammamāṇavassa caṇḍālucchiṭṭhabhattaparibhogo viya hotī’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
489590,111,495,2,19,1,173,17,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto caṇḍālayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā vayappatto kenacideva karaṇīyena pātheyyataṇḍule ca bhattapuṭañca gahetvā maggaṃ paṭipajji. 
489591,111,495,20,30,1,94,10,Tasmiñhi kāle bārāṇasiyaṃ eko māṇavo atthi satadhammo nāma udiccabrāhmaṇamahāsālakule nibbatto. 
489592,111,495,31,45,1,113,13,"Sopi kenacideva karaṇīyena taṇḍule ca bhattapuṭañca agahetvāva maggaṃ paṭipajji, te ubhopi mahāmagge samāgacchiṃsu. "
489593,111,495,46,55,1,40,5,Māṇavo bodhisattaṃ‘‘ kiṃjātikosī’’ ti pucchi. 
489594,111,495,56,75,1,59,10,So‘‘ ahaṃ caṇḍālo’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tvaṃ kiṃjātikosī’’ ti māṇavaṃ pucchi .
489595,111,495,76,83,1,22,3,‘‘ Udiccabrāhmaṇo ahan’’ ti.
489596,111,495,84,95,1,43,7,‘‘ Sādhu gacchāmā’’ ti te ubhopi maggaṃ agamaṃsu. 
489597,111,495,96,114,1,121,13,"Bodhisatto pātarāsavelāya udakaphāsukaṭṭhāne nisīditvā hatthe dhovitvā bhattapuṭaṃ mocetvā‘‘ māṇava, bhattaṃ bhuñjāhī’’ ti āha."
489598,111,495,115,128,1,41,7,"‘‘ Natthi, are caṇḍāla, mama bhattena attho’’ ti. "
489599,111,495,129,166,1,251,28,"Bodhisatto‘‘ sādhū’’ ti puṭakabhattaṃ ucchiṭṭhaṃ akatvāva attano yāpanamattaṃ aññasmiṃ paṇṇe pakkhipitvā puṭakabhattaṃ bandhitvā ekamante ṭhapetvā bhuñjitvā pānīyaṃ pivitvā dhotahatthapādo taṇḍule ca sesabhattañca ādāya‘‘ gacchāma, māṇavā’’ ti maggaṃ paṭipajji. "
489600,111,496,2,11,1,84,9,Te sakaladivasaṃ gantvā sāyaṃ ubhopi ekasmiṃ udakaphāsukaṭṭhāne nhatvā paccuttariṃsu. 
489601,111,496,12,21,1,92,9,Bodhisatto phāsukaṭṭhāne nisīditvā bhattapuṭaṃ mocetvā māṇavaṃ anāpucchitvā bhuñjituṃ ārabhi. 
489602,111,496,22,40,1,111,13,"Māṇavo sakaladivasaṃ maggagamanena kilanto chātajjhatto‘‘ sace me bhattaṃ dassati, bhuñjissāmī’’ ti olokento aṭṭhāsi. "
489603,111,496,41,45,1,29,4,Itaro kiñci avatvā bhuñjateva. 
489604,111,496,46,48,1,14,2,Māṇavo cintesi–
489605,111,496,49,70,1,129,16,‘‘ ayaṃ caṇḍālo mayhaṃ avatvāva sabbaṃ bhuñjati nippīḷetvāpi taṃ gahetvā upari ucchiṭṭhabhattaṃ chaḍḍetvā sesaṃ bhuñjituṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti. 
489606,111,496,71,76,1,38,5,So tathā katvā ucchiṭṭhabhattaṃ bhuñji. 
489607,111,496,77,103,1,200,20,"Athassa bhuttamattasseva‘‘ mayā attano jātigottakulapadesānaṃ ananucchavikaṃ kataṃ, caṇḍālassa nāma me ucchiṭṭhabhattaṃ bhuttan’’ ti balavavippaṭisāro uppajji, tāvadevassa salohitaṃ bhattaṃ mukhato uggacchi. "
489608,111,496,104,121,1,117,13,So‘‘ appamattakassa vata me kāraṇā ananucchavikaṃ kammaṃ katan’’ ti uppannabalavasokatāya paridevamāno paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha– 
489609,111,497,2,4,1,0,0,57.
489610,111,498,2,13,1,46,8,"‘ ‘ Tañca appañca ucchiṭṭhaṃ, tañca kicchena no adā; "
489611,111,499,2,12,1,49,7,"Sohaṃ brāhmaṇajātiko, yaṃ bhuttaṃ tampi uggatan’’ ti. "
489612,111,500,2,42,1,240,32,"Tatrāyaṃ saṅkhepattho– yaṃ mayā bhuttaṃ, taṃ appañca ucchiṭṭhañca, tañca so caṇḍālo na attano ruciyā maṃ adāsi, atha kho nippīḷiyamāno kicchena kasirena adāsi, sohaṃ parisuddhabrāhmaṇajātiko, teneva me yaṃ bhuttaṃ, tampi saddhiṃ lohitena uggatanti. "
489613,111,501,2,25,1,150,19,Evaṃ māṇavo paridevitvā‘‘ kiṃ dāni me evarūpaṃ ananucchavikaṃ kammaṃ katvā jīvitenā’’ ti araññaṃ pavisitvā kassaci attānaṃ adassetvāva anāthamaraṇaṃ patto. 
489614,111,502,2,53,1,388,41,"Satthā imaṃ atītaṃ dassetvā‘‘ seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, satadhammamāṇavassa taṃ caṇḍālucchiṭṭhakaṃ bhuñjitvā attano ayuttabhojanassa bhuttattā neva hāso, na somanassaṃ uppajji, evameva yo imasmiṃ sāsane pabbajito anesanāya jīvikaṃ kappento tathāladdhapaccayaṃ paribhuñjati, tassa buddhapaṭikuṭṭhagarahitajīvitabhāvato neva hāso, na somanassaṃ uppajjatī’’ ti vatvā abhisambuddho hutvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– "
489615,111,503,2,4,1,0,0,58.
489616,111,504,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ dhammaṃ niraṃkatvā, yo adhammena jīvati; "
489617,111,505,2,11,1,45,6,"Satadhammova lābhena, laddhenapi na nandatī’’ ti. "
489618,111,506,2,6,1,44,4,Tattha dhamman ti ājīvapārisuddhisīladhammaṃ. 
489619,111,506,7,11,1,32,3,{Niraṃkatvā}ti nīharitvā chaḍḍetvā. 
489620,111,506,12,17,1,54,4,{Adhammenā}ti ekavīsatiyā anesanasaṅkhātena micchājīvena. 
489621,111,506,18,30,1,47,6,"{Satadhammo}ti tassa nāmaṃ,‘‘ santadhammo’’ tipi pāṭho. "
489622,111,506,31,73,1,248,30,"Na {nandatī}ti yathā satadhammo māṇavo‘‘ caṇḍālucchiṭṭhakaṃ me laddhan’’ ti tena lābhena na nandati, evaṃ imasmimpi sāsane pabbajito kulaputto anesanāya laddhalābhaṃ paribhuñjanto na nandati na tussati,‘‘ buddhagarahitajīvikāya jīvāmī’’ ti domanassappatto hoti. "
489623,111,506,74,84,1,105,10,Tasmā anesanāya jīvikaṃ kappentassa satadhammamāṇavasseva araññaṃ pavisitvā anāthamaraṇaṃ marituṃ varanti. 
489624,111,507,2,18,1,134,14,"Evaṃ satthā imaṃ dhammadesanaṃ desetvā saccāni pakāsetvā jātakaṃ samodhānesi, saccapariyosāne bahū bhikkhū sotāpattiphalādīni pāpuṇiṃsu."
489625,111,507,19,32,1,55,8,"‘‘ Tadā māṇavo ānando ahosi, ahameva caṇḍālaputto ahosin’’ ti. "
489626,111,508,2,4,1,30,2,Satadhammajātakavaṇṇanā navamā.
489627,111,510,2,7,1,20,2,[ 180]10. Duddadajātakavaṇṇanā 
489628,111,511,2,13,1,80,10,Duddadaṃ dadamānānan ti idaṃ satthā jetavane viharanto gaṇadānaṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
489629,111,511,14,33,1,205,19,Sāvatthiyaṃ kira dve sahāyakā kuṭumbiyaputtā chandakaṃ saṃharitvā sabbaparikkhāradānaṃ sajjetvā buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ nimantetvā sattāhaṃ mahādānaṃ pavattetvā sattame divase sabbaparikkhāre adaṃsu. 
489630,111,511,34,63,1,172,21,"Tesu gaṇajeṭṭhako satthāraṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīditvā‘‘ bhante, imasmiṃ dāne bahudāyakāpi atthi appadāyakāpi, tesaṃ sabbesampi‘ idaṃ dānaṃ mahapphalaṃ hotū’’’ ti dānaṃ niyyādesi. "
489631,111,511,64,92,1,191,23,"Satthā‘‘ tumhehi kho upāsakā buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa dānaṃ datvā evaṃ niyyādentehi mahākammaṃ kataṃ, porāṇakapaṇḍitāpi dānaṃ datvā evameva niyyādiṃsū’’ ti vatvā tena yācito atītaṃ āhari. "
489632,111,512,2,36,1,356,34,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ brahmadatte rajjaṃ kārente bodhisatto kāsiraṭṭhe brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto takkasilāyaṃ sabbasippāni uggaṇhitvā gharāvāsaṃ pahāya isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā gaṇasatthā hutvā himavantapadese ciraṃ vasitvā loṇambilasevanatthāya janapadacārikaṃ caramāno bārāṇasiṃ patvā rājuyyāne vasitvā punadivase dvāragāme saparivāro bhikkhāya cari. 
489633,111,512,37,40,1,23,3,Manussā bhikkhaṃ adaṃsu. 
489634,111,512,41,58,1,149,15,"Punadivase bārāṇasiyaṃ cari, manussā sampiyāyamānā bhikkhaṃ datvā gaṇabandhanena chandakaṃ saṃharitvā dānaṃ sajjetvā isigaṇassa mahādānaṃ pavattayiṃsu. "
489635,111,512,59,67,1,74,8,Dānapariyosāne gaṇajeṭṭhako evameva vatvā imināva niyāmena dānaṃ niyyādesi. 
489636,111,512,68,88,1,104,15,"Bodhisatto‘‘ āvuso, cittappasāde sati appakaṃ nāma dānaṃ natthī’’ ti vatvā anumodanaṃ karonto imā gāthā avoca– "
489637,111,513,2,4,1,0,0,59.
489638,111,514,2,11,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Duddadaṃ dadamānānaṃ, dukkaraṃ kamma kubbataṃ; "
489639,111,515,2,8,1,42,5,"Asanto nānukubbanti, sataṃ dhammo durannayo. "
489640,111,516,2,4,1,0,0,60.
489641,111,517,2,12,1,39,8,"‘ ‘ Tasmā satañca asataṃ, nānā hoti ito gati; "
489642,111,518,2,11,1,43,6,"Asanto nirayaṃ yanti, santo saggaparāyaṇā’’ ti. "
489643,111,519,2,21,1,99,14,"Tattha duddadan ti dānaṃ nāma lobhadosavasikehi apaṇḍitehi dātuṃ na sakkā, tasmā‘‘ duddadan’’ ti vuccati. "
489644,111,519,22,24,1,15,2,Taṃ dadamānānaṃ. 
489645,111,519,25,36,1,78,11,Dukkaraṃ kamma kubbatan ti tadeva dānakammaṃ sabbehi kātuṃ na sakkāti dukkaraṃ. 
489646,111,519,37,39,1,15,2,Taṃ kurumānānaṃ. 
489647,111,519,40,44,1,22,3,{Asanto}ti apaṇḍitā bālā. 
489648,111,519,45,51,1,37,4,{Nānukubbantī}ti taṃ kammaṃ nānukaronti. 
489649,111,519,52,57,1,33,4,Sataṃ {dhammo}ti paṇḍitānaṃ sabhāvo. 
489650,111,519,58,61,1,24,3,Dānaṃ sandhāyetaṃ vuttaṃ. 
489651,111,519,62,73,1,98,9,"{Durannayo}ti phalasambandhavasena dujjāno, evarūpassa dānassa evarūpo phalavipāko hotīti duranubodho. "
489652,111,519,74,88,1,95,12,"Apica {durannayo}ti duradhigamo, apaṇḍitehi dānaṃ datvā dānaphalaṃ nāma laddhuṃ na sakkātipi attho. "
489653,111,519,89,101,1,84,11,Nānā hoti ito {gatī}ti ito cavitvā paralokaṃ gacchantānaṃ paṭisandhiggahaṇaṃ nānā hoti. 
489654,111,519,102,114,1,87,11,Asanto nirayaṃ {yantī}ti apaṇḍitā dussīlā dānaṃ adatvā sīlaṃ arakkhitvā nirayaṃ gacchanti. 
489655,111,519,115,135,1,172,18,"Santo {saggaparāyaṇā}ti paṇḍitā pana dānaṃ datvā sīlaṃ rakkhitvā uposathakammaṃ karitvā tīṇi sucaritāni pūretvā saggaparāyaṇā honti, mahantaṃ saggasukhasampattiṃ anubhavantīti. "
