489747,111,549,14,73,1,481,48,"Satthari hi paṭhamagamanena kapilapuraṃ gantvā kaniṭṭhabhātikaṃ nandarājakumāraṃ pabbājetvā kapilapurā nikkhamma anupubbena sāvatthiṃ gantvā viharante āyasmā nando bhagavato pattaṃ ādāya tathāgatena saddhiṃ gehā nikkhamanakāle‘‘ nandakumāro kira satthārā saddhiṃ gacchatī’’ ti sutvā aḍḍhullikhitehi kesehi vātapānantarena oloketvā‘‘ tuvaṭaṃ kho, ayyaputta, āgaccheyyāsī’’ ti idaṃ janapadakalyāṇiyā vuttavacanaṃ anussaranto ukkaṇṭhito anabhirato uppaṇḍuppaṇḍukajāto dhamanisanthatagatto ahosi. "
