489842,111,581,2,7,1,22,2,[ 184]4. Giridattajātakavaṇṇanā 
489843,111,582,2,15,1,95,11,Dūsito {giridattenā}ti idaṃ satthā veḷuvane viharanto ekaṃ vipakkhaseviṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha kathesi. 
489844,111,582,16,29,1,43,4,Vatthu heṭṭhā mahiḷāmukhajātake( jā.1.1.26) kathitameva. 
489845,111,582,30,52,1,113,15,"Satthā pana‘‘ na, bhikkhave, ayaṃ bhikkhu idāneva vipakkhaṃ sevati, pubbepesa vipakkhasevakoyevā’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āhari. "
489846,111,583,2,8,1,40,5,Atīte bārāṇasiyaṃ sāmarājā rajjaṃ kāresi. 
489847,111,583,9,17,1,81,8,Tadā bodhisatto amaccakule nibbattitvā vayappatto tassa atthadhammānusāsako ahosi. 
489848,111,583,18,32,1,82,12,"Rañño pana paṇḍavo nāma maṅgalasso, tassa giridatto nāma assabandho, so khañjo ahosi. "
489849,111,583,33,54,1,122,17,Asso mukharajjuke gahetvā taṃ purato purato gacchantaṃ disvā‘‘ maṃ esa sikkhāpetī’’ ti saññāya tassa anusikkhanto khañjo ahosi. 
489850,111,583,55,64,1,59,8,"Tassa assassa khañjabhāvaṃ rañño ārocesuṃ, rājā vejje pesesi. "
489851,111,583,65,81,1,81,12,Te gantvā assassa sarīre rogaṃ apassantā‘‘ rogamassa na passāmā’’ ti rañño kathayiṃsu. 
489852,111,583,82,85,1,23,3,Rājā bodhisattaṃ pesesi–
489853,111,583,86,97,1,38,6,"‘‘ gaccha vayassa, ettha kāraṇaṃ jānāhī’’ ti. "
489854,111,583,98,119,1,152,17,So gantvā khañjaassabandhasaṃsaggena tassa khañjabhūtabhāvaṃ ñatvā rañño tamatthaṃ ārocetvā‘‘ saṃsaggadosena nāma evaṃ hotī’’ ti dassento paṭhamaṃ gāthamāha–- 
