489857,111,586,2,10,1,44,5,"Porāṇaṃ pakatiṃ hitvā, tassevānuvidhiyyatī’’ ti. "
489858,111,587,2,9,1,46,6,Tattha hayo {sāmassā}ti sāmassa rañño maṅgalasso. 
489859,111,587,10,18,1,65,7,Porāṇaṃ pakatiṃ {hitvā}ti attano porāṇapakatiṃ siṅgārabhāvaṃ pahāya. 
489860,111,587,19,22,1,27,2,{Anuvidhiyyatī}ti anusikkhati. 
489861,111,588,2,16,1,51,9,Atha naṃ rājā‘‘ idāni vayassa kiṃ kattabban’’ ti pucchi. 
489862,111,588,17,32,1,91,11,Bodhisatto‘‘ sundaraṃ assabandhaṃ labhitvā yathā porāṇo bhavissatī’’ ti vatvā dutiyaṃ gāthamāha– 
489863,111,589,2,4,1,0,0,68.
